UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I hear Greatfather Winter - with the generous support of Smokeywood Pastures - has put presents for everyone under the tree in Ironforge. I wish I could go, but I\'ve got to look after the PX-238 Winter Wondervolt.$B$BBut you should definitely check it out. I\'m sure Greatfather Winter has some presents with your name on them.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, ho hello there! You can only be here for one reason: to open your Winter Veil presents.$B$BNow, don\'t you worry, Greatfather Winter hasn\'t forgotten about his favorite $R $C. Look under the tree and you\'ll find your gifts.$B$BDuring this season of giving, perhaps your friends would also enjoy receiving some of Smokeywood Pasture\'s excellent products?' WHERE `entry`=8827;
