UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Perfect!$B$BThis will show the elves what the Horde is capable of when we\'re backed into a corner.$B$BListen, $N. You must say nothing of this to anyone!$B$BGarrosh will surely approve once he sees the results, but if we are found out beforehand, our heads will be placed on spikes!$B$B<Draaka hands you a hastily written note.>$B$BBring this to Durak. You can find him in the mines behind me, just to the north. He will instruct you further.',`objectives_loc1`='Draaka in Splintertree wants you to bring the Hastily Written Note to Durak.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'s this? Who are you!? Hrmphh... Draaka should know better than to be so brazen, but it looks like you\'re up to your eyes in this with as much to lose as anyone. Very well.' WHERE `entry`=13751;
