UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The grand melee is the most important of the tournament\'s competitions. Victory will not be easy, but I am confident that we will win. You must practice with your mount until the two of you work as one.$B$BIt will help prepare you for the rigors of tournament combat.$B$BGo to the stables outside the pavilion, equip your lance, mount the stabled Silvermoon hawkstrider, and challenge the valiants. They wait in the Horde Valiants\' Ring just outside our tent.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Training against the other valiants will sharpen your claws and hone your battle insticts. When the competition begins, you will be ready.' WHERE `entry`=13787;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Argent Crusade has doubled the guard since your exposure of the Cult of the Damned\'s infiltrator. They know the cultists won\'t stop until they\'ve destroyed this area and thwarted the tournament.$B$BThe Argent Crusade\'s scouts have reported sighting a frost wyrm named Chillmaw leading a cult raiding party.$B$BYou must intercept and destroy them before they attack. The scouts reporting seeing Chillmaw to the southwest, flying over the area between the Ironwall Rampart and Aldur\'thar.',`objectives_loc1`='Crok Scourgebane at the Argent Tournament wants you to defeat Chillmaw and 3 Cultist Bombardiers.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, you have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. The Argent Crusade and all who gather here are in our debt and we\'ll make certain they remember it. For all their bluster about providing protection, the peacekeepers and skytalons spend more time breaking up drunken brawls than keeping us safe from the Scourge.$B$BIt\'s no matter. We always protect our own.' WHERE `entry`=13788;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a true champion, $N, both inside the ring and on the field. We must all be vigilant against the Scourge and you are a great example to our brethren and your own people.' WHERE `entry`=13789;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Bring 4 Marks of the Champion to Luuri at the Argent Tournament Grounds.$B$BIf you lose your lance, you can get another from any of the Lance Racks near the stables or in the Silver Covenant Pavilion.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring 4 Marks of the Champion to Luuri at the Argent Tournament Grounds.$B$BIf you lose your lance, you can get another from any of the Lance Racks near the stables or in the Silver Covenant Pavilion.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. Training against the other valiants is one of the best ways to prepare yourself for tournament competition. I know you\'ll make the Alliance proud, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13790;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well in demonstrating our commitment to fighting the Scourge, no matter where we are or what we are doing.' WHERE `entry`=13791;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are brave to come here, $C, but you may be too late. All of the druids are either dead or have been driven insane. Still, your tale is intriguing, and if what you say is true, then Gnarl must have the Forest Heart and soon, or Ashenvale will begin to wither!' WHERE `entry`=13792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You handle your mount well, $N. In time, your competitors will learn to fear you.' WHERE `entry`=13793;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to finally meet you, champion. The highlord has asked me to help coordinate the efforts of all champions to train together and bolster the defenses of the tournament grounds.' WHERE `entry`=13794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Forest Heart! It\'s corrupted! Stand back, $N, I will try to cleanse the heart before all is lost!' WHERE `entry`=13796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! These should hold a curse long enough for our purposes....' WHERE `entry`=13797;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Just in time, $C. The elves have launched another attack!$B$BFrom the guard towers, use the Accursed Ore to mark targets for Draaka.$B$BHer projectiles will strike your target and erupt in fel magic flame, destroying any nearby enemies.$B$BThere is strong prejudice against the use of demonic magics. Unjustified, but real nonetheless. For this reason, I will transform you into an imp for the duration of the mission to prevent you from being identified.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did you feel it, $N!? The raw fel power seething through your being? There is nothing else like it!' WHERE `entry`=13798;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Get My Keys!',`objectives_loc1`='Find Dr. Fingers\' Keys.' WHERE `entry`=13800;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Woohooo!! You\'ve silenced the voices! Thank you, thank you!' WHERE `entry`=13801;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kadrak wants you to bring the Blood-Soaked Axe to Durak in Splintertree Post.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Tainting the Forest\'s Heart? How ruthless - an utterly vicious blow.... I adore the idea!' WHERE `entry`=13803;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='To Catch a Fish-Thing',`objectives_loc1`='Place a trap and use the remote to capture a live Slobberfang Murloc. Return the filled trap to Professor Flozz.' WHERE `entry`=13804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Durak wants you to use the Tainted Blood of the Kaldorei on the Forest\'s Heart.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done? Good work, $N. That will gradually weaken their forces, as well as their spirit.' WHERE `entry`=13805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $R. One less thing we have to worry about!' WHERE `entry`=13806;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kadrak wants you to use the Secret Signal Powder on the Smoldering Brazier across from Satyrnaar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have your work cut out for you here, friend. Let\'s hope that you\'re up to the task,,,,' WHERE `entry`=13808;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Highlord Tirion Fordring has doubled the guard since your exposure of the Cult of the Damned\'s infiltrator. He doesn\'t believe that they will stop just because their Black Knight has been defeated.$B$BOur skytalon scouts have reported sighting a frost wyrm named Chillmaw leading a cult raiding party. If we don\'t intercept them, the tournament will come under attack. The scouts reporting seeing Chillmaw to the southwest, flying over the area between the Ironwall Rampart and Aldur\'thar.',`objectives_loc1`='Eadric the Pure at the Argent Tournament wants you to defeat Chillmaw and 3 Cultist Bombardiers.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, you and your allies have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. Though our skytalon riders are brave, they have their hands full keeping the peace on the tournament grounds and would be hard-pressed to defend the skies against the cult\'s attack. You have the thanks of the Argent Crusade and all who have gathered here to compete.' WHERE `entry`=13809;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a true champion, $N, both inside the ring and on the field. We must all be vigilant against the Scourge and you are a great example to our brethren and your own people.' WHERE `entry`=13810;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. Training against the other valiants is one of the best ways to prepare yourself for tournament competition. I know you\'ll make the Horde proud, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13811;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Argent Crusade has doubled the guard since your exposure of the Cult of the Damned\'s infiltrator. They know the cultists won\'t stop until they\'ve destroyed this area and thwarted the tournament.$B$BThe Argent Crusade\'s scouts have reported sighting a frost wyrm named Chillmaw leading a cult raiding party.$B$BYou must intercept and destroy them before they attack. The scouts reporting seeing Chillmaw to the southwest, flying over the area between the Ironwall Rampart and Aldur\'thar.',`objectives_loc1`='Crok Scourgebane at the Argent Tournament wants you to defeat Chillmaw and 3 Cultist Bombardiers.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, you have spared the tournament from a devastating attack. The Argent Crusade and all who gather here are in our debt and we\'ll make certain they remember it. For all their bluster about providing protection, the peacekeepers and skytalons spend more time breaking up drunken brawls than keeping us safe from the Scourge.$B$BIt\'s no matter. We always protect our own.' WHERE `entry`=13812;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well in demonstrating our commitment to fighting the Scourge, no matter where we are or what we are doing.' WHERE `entry`=13813;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You handle your mount well, $N. In time, your competitors will learn to fear you.' WHERE `entry`=13814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, $N. You\'ve demoralized the enemy and harvested resources for the Horde. Let\'s hope the rest of the mission goes as well.' WHERE `entry`=13815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s locked?  Figures!$B$BI\'ll let Brann know... maybe he can uncover something in the Archivum.' WHERE `entry`=13816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The platinum disc fits perfectly inside the console. It begins to spin as its contents are scanned by white beams of light.' WHERE `entry`=13817;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Stand by for verification.$B$BAccess to the Celestial Planetarium granted. Please retrieve your key.' WHERE `entry`=13818;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re here. Let us hope this works. For all our sakes.' WHERE `entry`=13819;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So the justicar sent you to see us? Good, good...$B$BWe could always use more help with the, uh, "requisition" of materials.' WHERE `entry`=13820;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent job, $N. We\'re one step closer to saving Azeroth!' WHERE `entry`=13821;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ye did it! I don\'t know how, but ye did!' WHERE `entry`=13822;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ye never cease to impress, $N.$B$BYe and me are having a pint together after all this is done, ye hear me?' WHERE `entry`=13823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve got to hand it to you, $N. Our odds might not be the best, but I feel a lot better with you lending a hand.' WHERE `entry`=13824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well hello there, young $R. Either my memory is failing me, or I forgot to give you this the last time we spoke....' WHERE `entry`=13826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Keep the words of the master in mind as you practice with the training dummies.' WHERE `entry`=13828;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Keep the words of the master in mind as you practice with the training dummies.' WHERE `entry`=13829;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So eating it makes you invisible... what a strange defense this clever fish has developed.$B$BI\'d like to digest this for a bit. Pun not intended, $N. Really. Why don\'t you come see me tomorrow?' WHERE `entry`=13830;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' So the Forsaken have been studying Foulhoof\'s work? My gut crawls at the thought of what they might have done were they able to weaponize his corruption. You\'ve done well to destroy their work, but this raises deeper concerns. What brought the Forsaken to our doorstep? Are they working with the Shatterspear trolls to our north? Sorrows are heaping upon sorrows, $C. I\'m glad you\'re here.' WHERE `entry`=13831;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well now, that looks like it could be valuable. Difficult to know until it\'s cleaned up and appraised, but I\'m still willing to make the trade if you are.' WHERE `entry`=13832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a brave one, $N. I hope you didn\'t lose any extremities making your fishing spot. If you\'ve still got the fishing bug, come back tomorrow and we\'ll talk some more.' WHERE `entry`=13833;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My, my, my! You\'ve caught yourself some Terrorfish. Why, that reminds me of the time...$B$B<Marcia regales you with stories of adventure and fishing for as long as you\'re willing to listen.>' WHERE `entry`=13834;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Commit Valis\'s lesson to memory, $N. It will mean the difference between winning and losing your mounted combat matches.' WHERE `entry`=13835;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, hello there $N. Marcia said you\'d be coming by with that poor man\'s missing arm.$B$BShe also gave me this bag to give you as a reward. It smells horrible, and I\'m anxious to make the trade if you don\'t mind.' WHERE `entry`=13836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With a teacher like Rugan, you\'ll be an expert at mounted combat in no time.' WHERE `entry`=13837;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Commit Valis\'s lesson to memory, $N. It will mean the difference between winning and losing your mounted combat matches.' WHERE `entry`=13838;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With experience and practice, you will become deadly with the charge.' WHERE `entry`=13839;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This could be the end of me... Perhaps my actions were not thought out as well as they should have been...$B$BThe good news is that we pushed back an attack that would have otherwise meant the end of Splintertree. Let us pray that Commander Hellscream sees it that way.$B$BI am certain to be summoned to Orgrimmar to explain my actions.$B$BPlease, $N, go ahead of me and present this letter to Garrosh.$B$BDo what you can to soften his heart towards me.',`objectives_loc1`='Draaka wants you to bring her Letter of Explanation to Garrosh Hellscream in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fools!! This Draaka woman has allowed herself to be manipulated by a demon! And I smell its taint on you as well, $C....' WHERE `entry`=13841;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The demons want nothing more than for us to renew our dependence on their foul magics. That reliance can only lead to the entire orc race becoming enslaved.$B$BYou wish to see Draaka go unpunished? Then you must find the demons\' pawn who has manipulated her, and destroy him!$B$BIf you do not soon return to me with the head of this being, then I shall see both yours and Draaka\'s hoisted upon a spike!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Grah... very well. I\'ll remove the bounty I had placed upon your head. Though I am sorely tempted to end your life anyway, just on principle. Be sure that you never raise my ire again, $N. Now, get out of my sight...' WHERE `entry`=13842;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='The Scrapbot Construction Kit',`details_loc1`='Searching the databanks of the prototype console reveals schematics for a scrapbot construction kit. With your engineering expertise, you could learn this schematic and produce scrapbot construction kits of your own.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You take note of the information displayed in the schematic and the materials required to construct the scrapbot kit.' WHERE `entry`=13843;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s see what we\'ve got here.... By Elune, his notes are scrawled in a half dozen languages. What is this, blood? This archive makes my flesh seethe, but at least it\'s secure. It will take us some time to decipher these notes. Oh - your reward? Yes, here. Nice work with those undead scavengers. Now get back to the fight.' WHERE `entry`=13844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Bring the Seal Vial of Poison to Alchemist Cinesra in the Dalaran Sewers.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are brave to have carried this. If even one drop were to touch your skin, you\'d have died an agonizing death.$B$BAllow me to pay you for it... I can always use venom of exceptional potency.' WHERE `entry`=13845;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you. I just know the crusade will put it to good use!' WHERE `entry`=13846;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders what they already knew -- that our warriors are more than just parade ground decorations.' WHERE `entry`=13847;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kadrak wants you to speak to Commander Grimfang in Zoram Strand.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is grim news, indeed. May the spirits preserve them until we can fight our way to Splintertree....' WHERE `entry`=13848;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you! Now it\'s time to deal with the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=13849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You want to ride a Venomhide? Then I\'ve got bad news for you.$B$BThe Venomhide Ravasaurs, they\'re all poison: Poison blood, poison spit, poison skin. You climb on one, you fall off dead in a few hours.$B$BYou\'d have to build up a resistance to their toxins before I sold you one, and that takes a long, LONG time... you\'d need to be splashed with poisonous blood while fighting one numerous times. If you\'re really interested, the venomhides prefer the northern area of of the Marshlands, northwest of here.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it? You actually did it?!$B$BHo ho! Stubborn as my wife, you are.' WHERE `entry`=13850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that we are worthy allies.' WHERE `entry`=13851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the that we are a match for the Argent Crusade\'s own.' WHERE `entry`=13852;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re saved! You\'ve shot down enough of them that we should be able to handle the rest. I cannot thank you enough, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13853;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders what they already knew -- that our warriors are more than just parade ground decorations.' WHERE `entry`=13854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that they can rely on us in the battle against the Lich King.' WHERE `entry`=13855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders what they already knew -- that our warriors are the best in Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=13856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that we are fearless in the face of the Lich King\'s minions.' WHERE `entry`=13857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that we are steadfast allies in the battle against the Lich King.' WHERE `entry`=13858;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery on the field has shown the crusaders that we are ready to face any enemy.' WHERE `entry`=13859;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Argent Crusade has seen our resolve and they know that our warriors will see this through to the end.' WHERE `entry`=13860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Argent Crusade is heartened to have $Cs like you fighting alongside us in the battle against the Lich King.' WHERE `entry`=13861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Argent Crusade is heartened to have $Cs like you fighting alongside us in the battle against the Lich King.' WHERE `entry`=13862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Everywhere we have met the Scourge, we have made them fear us, and this campaign is no different.' WHERE `entry`=13863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Everywhere we have fought the Scourge, we have taught them to fear us and this campaign will be no different.' WHERE `entry`=13864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $C. They\'re in complete disarray. Just look at them!' WHERE `entry`=13865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Protector Arminon slain',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Ashenvale Scouts defeated' WHERE `entry`=13865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are just in time, $C. Old Kulg has been slinking around those woods too long. He grows too cautious, jumping at shadows. We will fear this forest no longer - the time has come to subdue Ashenvale once and for all!' WHERE `entry`=13866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N.$B$BWe are under constant threat from the furbolg. Hopefully this will keep them at bay for a bit longer.' WHERE `entry`=13867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A troll charm? What are the furbolg doing with such a thing? You\'re right, it does have a feeling of corruption about it... even I can sense that. There\'s someone here who might be able to help.' WHERE `entry`=13868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='While what the satyrs have done to the trees is horrible, nothing compares to the mass slaughter that the orcs have been engaging in!$B$B<The ancient shakes with visible rage, his leaves falling all around you.>$B$B$R, I would have you head across the road here at the lumber camp and recover the remains of those trees, treants, and ancients that the Horde have hewn down in their prime.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have lived a very long time in peace with the forest, but what these orc-things are doing makes me want to feed them back to the ground! I will put this wood to rest now. Thank you for this kindness, $N. I will never forget.' WHERE `entry`=13869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' If only you\'d arrived an hour ago.... The diplomat suffered mortal wounds at the hands of an elf assassin. How the enemy was able to infiltrate the camp undetected remains a mystery.' WHERE `entry`=13870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $C. One last request - it would probably be best if none of my laborers knew this assassin ever existed.' WHERE `entry`=13871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Guardian Menerin wants you to deliver the Sealed Missive to Guardian Gurtar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'ll deliver this to Hellscream personally, $R. In the meantime, there\'s something I need you to do for me....' WHERE `entry`=13873;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You\'ve likely saved the Thistlefur from themselves, at least in the short run. If they can keep from stealing objects of power that don\'t belong to them, that is. I understand that the night elves are having problems with the other furbolg tribe to the south. That\'s something that Raene is going to want to speak to you about. However, there are more immediate concerns that I would ask for your help with.' WHERE `entry`=13874;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oh, $N. Thank you for this gift! It means more than you could know. He hasn\'t forgotten...' WHERE `entry`=13875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What was done had to be done. As our leader, Dal\'s sickness from the troll charms was destroying us. It was better for the health and dignity of the tribe that it was you, outsider. This way there will be no civil war amongst us and we will easily find new leadership... hopefully one that does not have a tendency to so easily trust outsiders. Perhaps I am guilty of this as well? Here, allow me to repay the debt we owe you before we part ways forever.' WHERE `entry`=13876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My brother must have sent you. He wouldn\'t have done so unless you are capable of doing what must be done. For all of our sakes I hope that he\'s right. The elementals here are now my allies. You must do as they ask if we are to prevent the destruction of the rest of Ashenvale.' WHERE `entry`=13877;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You save the wolves! So brave! Someday, maybe you get a wolf just like that to ride. What should I do now?' WHERE `entry`=13878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' The spirits whispered that help would soon arrive. Pardon my surprise, but I was hoping the spirits would guide someone a little more... heroic. These elementals are trusted allies. Listen to them and do their bidding. If we fail, there will remain nothing in Ashenvale worth fighting for.' WHERE `entry`=13879;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $R. Lord Magmathar\'s fire is now trapped, restrained within the earth once more.' WHERE `entry`=13880;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' $N, this is terrible. What is that thing, and how did it get there? Something is devouring these animals, physically and spiritually. I had suspected the satyrs or some sort of disease was the culprit, but this is shaping up to be something ... unnatural.' WHERE `entry`=13881;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect, this is everything. Did you have fun collecting the wisp? I used to chase the wisps around Ashenvale when I was just a girl. I\'m afraid I\'ve found out what we\'re dealing with.' WHERE `entry`=13882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $R. I\'ll show them how an armored ship should be built!' WHERE `entry`=13883;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You acquitted yourself well in battle on the field. However, I\'m afraid that Lord Magmathar has taken notice of you and the destruction that you\'ve wreaked upon his minions. You will have to deal with him or he is sure to burn you alive, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13884;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So the animals are safe, then. Thank you, thank you! But now it\'s time to turn our attention to the source.' WHERE `entry`=13885;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done. The power of fire is subdued and the four elements are returned to harmony. You have saved the rest of Ashenvale through your brave and selfless actions, $N. You have our eternal thanks.' WHERE `entry`=13886;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work. Honestly, I\'m amazed you were able to find this many. With each clutch, they seem fewer in number.$B$BI\'ll let you raise one of the freshly-hatched venomhides. It shouldn\'t be shy about letting you know what it needs.' WHERE `entry`=13887;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it! The spirits were right after all! The power of fire is subdued and the four elements are returned to harmony. The rest of Ashenvale is spared this fiery fate. You have the eternal thanks of the Earthen Ring.' WHERE `entry`=13888;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The venomhide hatchling seems satisfied with the giant meal you\'ve provided, but there\'s no way of telling when it will be hungry again.' WHERE `entry`=13889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, $R! No more ships will run aground, thanks to you.' WHERE `entry`=13890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Love of Elune, look at you. That must\'ve been some fight! You\'re covered in what looks like... chowder. If a mere minion could cause so much agony here in Darkshore, I can\'t even imagine the suffering that a true Old One could bring about. Well, at least the animals are safe for now. I will plant the sapling you created to help rebuild this shattered land. Thank you, $N! I\'d give you a hug but, you know. Chowder.' WHERE `entry`=13891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is dire news, $N. If you are correct, then we\'d best act swiftly and decisively. We cannot allow this "Soggoth" to be brought back to life.' WHERE `entry`=13892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The dwarf\'s story is unsettling... yet informative. It seems we have few options left.' WHERE `entry`=13893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aros\'s body appears to be lifeless yet still warm. Perhaps his killers are nearby.' WHERE `entry`=13895;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, we know a thing or two about this Soggoth. The question is... do you really want to know?' WHERE `entry`=13896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We can finally rest here now, $N. It appears Darkshore has been saved -- and we have you to thank for it.' WHERE `entry`=13897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. The naga seek the destruction and subjugation of all surface-dwellers -- do not hesitate to drive them out of our lands and back into the shadowy ocean depths where they belong.' WHERE `entry`=13898;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The walord doesn\'t seem to have the horn on him. Perhaps he was telling the truth.' WHERE `entry`=13899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. Unfortunately the battle is far from over.' WHERE `entry`=13900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='There is more to this Naga problem than meets the eye, $C. It appears that the issue will not be resolved by merely thinning their numbers. To humble them, a more severe impression must be made.$B$BTravel to the northern end of Zoram Strand and enter Blackfathom Deep. Once there, demonstrate to the naga that their presence in this region will no longer be tolerated!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! Let the naga retreat back into the seas where they belong!' WHERE `entry`=13901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If Malfurion placed his trust in you, then so shall I. You\'ll find that our enemies greatly outnumber us this far south.$B$BWhere brute force and numbers fail us, strategy and guile will prove our biggest advantages.' WHERE `entry`=13902;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The venomhide hatchling looks at you expectantly, then begins to scrawl a pictogram into the dirt.$B$BThe hatchling\'s drawings seem to resemble various types of large insects, perhaps the gorishi silithids. The hatchling finishes his picture, then gestures at it with one short arm, snaps its jaws, and licks its lips.$B$BIt must want you to go to the Slithering Scar, in center of the southern part of Un\'Goro Crater, and gather silithid meat. When you have the meat, feed it to your hungry hatchling.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your venomhide hatchling flashes you a toothy smile and then settles in for a nap.' WHERE `entry`=13903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your hatchling licks its lips after devouring the meal of silithid eggs. For a moment, you think it seems disappointed that feeding time has come to an end.' WHERE `entry`=13904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The venomhide hatchling accepts the feathers and begins looking them over, holding several up to its armbands.' WHERE `entry`=13905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It looks like both of you have managed to do some growing without killing one another.$B$BThere, everything\'s finished. I\'ve trained your venomhide ravasaur to respond when you blow this whistle.$B$BFew have the dedication to hand-feed and raise a venomhide, but they\'re well worth the effort.' WHERE `entry`=13906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Bravo, $N! Now let\'s take a look-see at our new situation. What? MORE murlocs? I swear on my stones, the more murlocs you kill, the more murlocs appear. Is it just me? We\'re going to need a new approach.' WHERE `entry`=13907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Well, not much here that don\'t look stepped on, sat on, or soaked in a toilet. But toss some thatch on top and it\'ll do. Tell me, $N, do you consider yourself an architect?' WHERE `entry`=13909;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Har har, that sounds like quite a heap you built there. Did they take to it? Good, good! Let\'s see if my plan comes to fruition. What have I done?' WHERE `entry`=13910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you\'ve helped the Prospector find his missing journal! To think it was here all along. Someday you\'ll have to show me this other set of ruins he\'s always going on about.' WHERE `entry`=13911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Spectacular! Good work, $N. I\'m sure Remtravel would thank you himself if he could remember your name. Look at the surface of the disc - these microscopic etchings - this is amazing. I\'m certain this strange wheel holds information, if only we could read it...' WHERE `entry`=13912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Rescue Boog the "Gear Whisperer" and Minx from Painmaster Thundrak\'s Wagon of Unending Agony.',`objectives_loc1`='Rescue Boog the "Gear Whisperer" and Minx from Painmaster Thundrak\'s Wagon of Unending Agony.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. Grim news you bring of the rest of the gnome team, but at least you managed to save a few. For that I am grateful.' WHERE `entry`=13913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The venomhide hatchling accepts the feathers and begins looking them over, holding several up to its armbands.' WHERE `entry`=13914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The venomhide hatchling seems satisfied with the giant meal you\'ve provided, but there\'s no way of telling when it will be hungry again.' WHERE `entry`=13915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your hatchling licks its lips after devouring the meal of silithid eggs. For a moment, you think it seems disappointed that feeding time has come to an end.' WHERE `entry`=13916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The venomhide hatchling looks at you expectantly, then begins to scrawl a pictogram into the dirt.$B$BThe hatchling\'s drawings seem to resemble various types of large insects, perhaps the gorishi silithids. The hatchling finishes his picture, then gestures at it with one short arm, snaps its jaws, and licks its lips.$B$BIt must want you to go to the Slithering Scar, in center of the southern part of Un\'Goro Crater, and gather silithid meat. When you have the meat, feed it to your hungry hatchling.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your venomhide hatchling flashes you a toothy smile and then settles in for a nap.' WHERE `entry`=13917;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why yes, yes, this is it! See here, the slot is the exact dimensions of the ancient disc, just as I\'d surmised. Here\'s your reward, $N - you\'ve earned it. Are you ready to meet history face to face? Let\'s see what the ancients have to say!' WHERE `entry`=13918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These venison should make our soldiers\' spirits rise for the coming battles. Here\'s something for your troubles.' WHERE `entry`=13920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Finally, my redemption is at hand. I have waited long for this day and I think I know how to help you in turn.' WHERE `entry`=13921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have all of the moonstones that are needed. And yet, it is said that a sacrifice of life is the only way to be ensure the saving of another. I will ensure that no matter what, the moonstones will cure Relara.' WHERE `entry`=13922;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You come here as a child, $R. You shall leave here a battle-hardened $C of the Horde! That, or a corpse....' WHERE `entry`=13923;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Thank you for saving me from a fate worse than death, $N! For saving both the child and myself!$B$BWell, the child is almost saved. All you have to do is take the moonstones back west down the road to Astranaar. Hand them to Pelturas and he will know what to do.$B$BGo in peace, my friend. Elune be praised!',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver the Sanctified Moonstones to Pelturas Whitemoon at Astranaar in Ashenvale.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, $N, you have saved my daughter! I know the power of the moonstones will give back my daughter her strength! I can never repay you fully for the aid you have given me, but... please, take this. Other than Relara, it is my most dear possession.' WHERE `entry`=13924;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Interesting ... It sounds like our cure will keep the wildlife safe, but you say you saw something else? Some kind of angry presence? This is a good sign, $N. Whatever is behind this isn\'t happy, and that means we\'re on to something.' WHERE `entry`=13925;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You take us away from puppy-men hatchlings? Good. We like you already. Mean puppy-men hatchlings took all our favorite toys away.' WHERE `entry`=13926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You take Kekek hunting? Good to get away from mean old orphan lady who doesn\'t let Kekek hunt.' WHERE `entry`=13927;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. We have our hands full defending the retreat, but when I can catch my breath, I\'ll see to it that these sisters are returned to life, the goddess willing. You\'ve demonstrated your prowess... we can use your help.' WHERE `entry`=13928;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We never knew trees got that big! Nope. Maybe Great Ones had special plan for it?' WHERE `entry`=13929;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is Kekek\'s kind of city. Bear-men fight for home just like Frenzyheart do. Orphan lady tell Kekek not to fight with other pups, but Kekek fight anyway.' WHERE `entry`=13930;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Not only are we supplying brew to everyone, we also have steins to give out!  Beautiful, commemorative steins all obtained by the most legal of means!  Here\'s a voucher for one.$B$BTalk to Blix near the back of the Brewfest camp. He\'s pretty strange, even more so now that he\'s always wearing those goggles. He\'ll handle the voucher for you, and any other Brewfest transaction.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'s this? A stein voucher? So you like drinking? Great! After I give you this stein, go have a few drinks! Then a few more. Maybe have a few more after that... Then, now this is important, come see me.$B$BLook, I know you\'ll be back eventually. If you want your Brewfest tokens redeemed you have to see me.$B$BAnyways, here\'s the stein, and remember to talk to me later.' WHERE `entry`=13931;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aww, it\'s just a stein voucher... Maybe you\'re just playing hard to get. So here\'s this year\'s stein for you.$B$BBut I suspect I\'ll be seeing a lot more of you. After all, if you want any Brewfest tokens redeemed, I\'m your girl...$B$BOr maybe I\'m his girl...$B$BOooohhh... or his...' WHERE `entry`=13932;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We very glad you brought us here, $N. We always worried what would happen to us when the orphan matron found us in Sholazar.' WHERE `entry`=13933;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='See? Kekek never get tired of saying, "Kekek tell you so."$B$BMaybe now you believe other things Kekek tell you, like how sky is green.' WHERE `entry`=13934;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A brutal display, but one fitting for the enemies of Ashenvale. The Horde dares to think that they can take our beloved forest away from us. They are fatally mistaken! You have saved Raynewood from destruction, $N. Surely we can find a reward suitable for our champion?' WHERE `entry`=13935;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let me tell ya somethin\' $C! The bossman simply doesn\'t appreciate the art and craftsmanship that goes into making fine explosives.' WHERE `entry`=13936;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Purchase a Small Paper Zeppelin at the Wonderworks and then throw it to your orphan, Kekek.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Kekek like playing with paper zeppelin. Not as good as hunting, but give something to do when bored at orphanage.' WHERE `entry`=13938;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'d hoped to never return to Teldrassil for such grim business. I\'d hoped that its corruption had been wiped away completely. Something fowl lingers.$B$BThe corruption of the wicked fel moss still threatens to turn peaceful creatures against us. The grells and gellkin still infest the area and threaten Shadowglen\'s residents.$B$BEngage these grells and grellkin, $N, and see if they are indeed caught under the enchantment of the wicked fel moss. Once we know for certain, we will know how to proceed.',`objectives_loc1`='Collect 6 Fel Moss.' WHERE `entry`=13939;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re just in time, $N. I don\'t know how much longer we can hold.' WHERE `entry`=13940;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m definitely on to something here!$B$BI have enough volatile elements salvaged from our arsenal to make the explosives Goggath wants, but I need to stabilize it and pack it into bombs.$B$BWhat I need is some clay - and not just any clay... Moon-kissed Clay.$B$BIt\'s only found on the northern banks of Astranaar Lake, and it possesses the qualities I need to bring out the full potential of my discovery!',`objectives_loc1`='Tweedle at Hellscream\'s Watch wants you to collect 10 samples of Moon-kissed Clay.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is PERFECT! Oh, just wait \'til you see what I can do with this....' WHERE `entry`=13942;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $R. But there is much that remains to be done here.' WHERE `entry`=13943;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, Tweedle found a way to get those explosives working, eh? It\'s about time...' WHERE `entry`=13944;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Impressive. I hope my huntress carried her weight. If we continue with this fervor, we may yet still free Teldrassil from the corruption that Alexstrasza herself could not burn out.' WHERE `entry`=13945;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. I know this probably wasn\'t very pleasant work, but we greatly appreciate it. I fear for our dear Teldrassil... it seems it is becoming more corrupt by the day, and our ignorance to the cause is plaguing me greatly.' WHERE `entry`=13946;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your deeds today shall live long in the Horde\'s glorious history. Your efforts have dealt a devastating blow to the enemy!' WHERE `entry`=13947;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is dire news, $N. If you are correct, then we\'d best act swiftly and decisively. We cannot allow this "Soggoth" to be brought back to life.' WHERE `entry`=13948;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Halga grins disarmingly, holding up an enormous firearm.>$B$BHave you ever used one of these, $N? It\'s a beast. Hell with a handgrip. Too heavy to use on foot, but perfect when riding at the head of a caravan. I call it my \'street sweeper.\'$B$BWe need to get those supplies you\'ve collected to Crossroads, and I expect trouble. I\'d like for you to ride shotgun. Literally! Say the word when you\'re ready and I\'ll put you at the head of our next caravan.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re a sight, $R. That\'s the first caravan to make it through this week!' WHERE `entry`=13949;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That was fun! We go again sometime? We can\'t wait to see our new friend again!' WHERE `entry`=13950;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Kekek like new Snowfall friends, maybe come back and go hunting together sometime. Maybe we go tip over walrus-men when they sleeping.' WHERE `entry`=13951;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Human Spirit in Stormwind\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=13952;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The naga are in league with the Twilight\'s Hammer?  Just what we needed.' WHERE `entry`=13953;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do you think she ever saw an oracle before? We might be the first one ever to meet her! We thinks she liked us, but we\'re not sure. She doesn\'t talk a lot. Nope. But that was fun!' WHERE `entry`=13954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Kekek always liked dragons. Always wanted to be one, but orphan-lady said no. But she did say maybe you take Kekek to meet dragon queen.$B$BKekek think orphan-lady have good idea for once. You take Kekek to Wyrmrest Temple in the middle of Dragonblight? Fly all the way to top to meet dragon queen. She must be really big, to be queen of all dragons. Kekek can\'t wait to see!',`objectives_loc1`='Take your orphan, Kekek, to visit Alexstrasza the Life-Binder at the top of Wyrmrest Temple. Make sure to call for him if he is not present when you get there.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Queen not what Kekek expected, but Kekek understand why. Queen\'s visitors get crushed if she was always big dragon! Still want to see someday.' WHERE `entry`=13955;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We got to meet a Great One! Too bad it was during his nap time, but we understand. We like naps, too! Maybe we learn naps from Great Ones like we learn about shrines and shinies!$B$BCan we come back and visit the Great One again when not sleeping?' WHERE `entry`=13956;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You help Kekek learn him a book? Then, Kekek hunt with Hemet Nesingwary!' WHERE `entry`=13957;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Goggath wants you to bring the Battle Triage Kit to Thagg at Raynewood Retreat.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is good news indeed, $R. But right now, we need more than just good news here. These triage kits will be put to good use!' WHERE `entry`=13958;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We had the best time with you, $N. We wish you could be our $G daddy : mama; now, but you have to take us back to Orphan Matron Aria in Dalaran.$B$BMaybe you could come visit us again sometime? We loved meeting Winterfin hatchlings and getting to see the dragon queen. No one will believe us when we say we met a Great One!$B$BWe going to miss you, $N. We promise to write letter sometime, oki?',`objectives_loc1`='Return your ward to the Dalaran orphanage by handing in the Oracle Orphan Whistle to Orphan Matron Aria in Dalaran.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It sounds like little Roo had a great time this week. I know he was getting awfully lonely in the orphanage and was eager to make some new friends. Thank you so much for agreeing to look after him.' WHERE `entry`=13959;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Know what? You not so bad after all, $N. You take Kekek a lot of fun places. Kekek meet a lot of new friends and do things no other pup get to do.$B$BYou, and Hemet Nesingwary, and Snowfall Glade pups all new best friends. Maybe sometime you bring Kekek that green hills book? Kekek promise to write sometimes, too, tell you how things go. Maybe even be nice to big-tongue kids sometimes.$B$BKekek gotta go back to orphan-lady Aria now, back in purple human city.',`objectives_loc1`='Return your ward to the Dalaran orphanage by handing in the Wolvar Orphan Whistle to Orphan Matron Aria in Dalaran.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for agreeing to care for Kekek this week. I know he can be a handful, but I think that with more individual attention and a few more friends, he\'ll do a lot better. No doubt he\'s going to be telling stories of his adventures with you for weeks.' WHERE `entry`=13960;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh my. We want to question this Quilboar, not tenderize him!' WHERE `entry`=13961;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very well, $N. You have succeeded where I could not. You have earned my respect.' WHERE `entry`=13962;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very interesting - our brute here seems both enthralled and terrified of the one they call "Tortusk." A powerful leader can inspire his people to acts of greatness or atrocity... but we orcs would know that more than others. We should turn our attention to this Tortusk problem.' WHERE `entry`=13963;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to finally meet you, $N. I\'ve heard all about what you\'ve been up to and let me just say that I\'m impressed! Think you can lend us your expertise?' WHERE `entry`=13964;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You say that Faldreas sent you?  Good man. As it happens, we could use your help.' WHERE `entry`=13965;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $R. This should keep them licking their wounds for a time.' WHERE `entry`=13967;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, so Tortusk behaved as I expected? Went right for your throat? It is good that he\'s dead. The Razormane quilboar have been separated from their leadership in the southern Barrens, no doubt allowing an animal like him to come to power. Perhaps without his influence we can start a dialogue with the survivors... Although hotter heads may prevail.' WHERE `entry`=13968;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This poor battered kodo looks to be on the verge of death, but is still breathing. The Razormane haven\'t even plundered its cargo yet. If it can be revived, you may be able to save the entire shipment.' WHERE `entry`=13969;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Kodo is voracious! You might as well be pouring those sacks of grain into a hole! Already the animal is beginning to perk up.' WHERE `entry`=13970;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So that was your handiwork, $R? Yes, the missing Kodo arrived just minutes ago. It will take many nights to nurse the poor beast\'s wounds, but thanks to you it\'s alive. And you saved a whole shipment! Please, take your pick of the gear that the kodo was carrying.' WHERE `entry`=13971;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you\'ve left a string of corpses in your wake, $R. I couldn\'t have done better. The livestock may be lost, but the land remains ours - thank you!' WHERE `entry`=13973;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Tweedle wants you to take Tweedle\'s Tiny Package to Flooz at Silverwind Refuge.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, look at this! Little Tweedle has really come through this time. This stuff blew up Astranaar, you say? As you can see, we don\'t need any help taking over Silverwind Refuge, but Tweedle\'s ideas are as small as his hands. If this stuff\'s really as good as you say, there\'s no limit to what we might do....' WHERE `entry`=13974;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Rocco hands you a familiar-looking shotgun.>$B$BI took the liberty of cleaning up Halga\'s artillery for you. I\'m sure I don\'t need to warn you about the kickback. Just ask me when you\'re ready to mount up for Crossroads! Thork is waiting for you there. Be sure not to give him any lip.$B$BDon\'t stop for nothing, $N, and if someone gets too close, just give \'em a thump with the butt-end of your gun. Do us proud!',`objectives_loc1`='Talk to Rocco Whipshank at Grol\'dom Farm and escort his caravan all the way to Crossroads.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time we got some supplies through here. It\'s bad enough to be severed from Mulgore, but this city would fall apart if we lost our trade with Orgrimmar.' WHERE `entry`=13975;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$C, you must be wary! Kaliva, the foul demoness who has chained us is nearby!' WHERE `entry`=13976;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Wahoo!! Did you SEE that?!$B$BWe need to get this into production right away!$B$BHere. Take the rest of the stuff to Jinx. You\'ll find him setting up our new facility just west of here.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Hmmm. It\'ll take a little time. But yes, we can put this into a bomb....' WHERE `entry`=13977;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s better. Without him, their technicians are sure to fall back to their normal laziness, which should result in fewer bombs and more accidents.' WHERE `entry`=13979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, friend. Your skills have bought us the time we needed to prepare the bomb. It\'s almost complete!' WHERE `entry`=13980;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They what? IT\'S HOW BIG?!!! I have a very bad feeling about this, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13981;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Disgusting, I know, but if we three are to be free of Kaliva\'s chains, it is not enough that she is dead. We must eat of her fel heart!' WHERE `entry`=13982;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This looks right, $C. I should have your shredder put together in no time.' WHERE `entry`=13983;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A fine job, my little $R friend. But as you can see, I am a little busy here.' WHERE `entry`=13985;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, my shield! I won\'t be using it anytime soon, but thank you. I hate that I\'m sitting here useless when I could be helping on the front, but fighting with my arm like this won\'t help anyone.$B$BTake care out there, won\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=13986;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve saved us all, $N! I have the power to finish off these final few. No longer will the forest have to fear the Burning Legion!' WHERE `entry`=13987;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am glad Tonga was able to witness the overgrowth firsthand - words can\'t convey the scope of the damage. Did you bring his totem? I will return it to him when I am finished here.' WHERE `entry`=13988;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. Murgut sold his own tribe out to the Horde, allying with them when they took your precious Silverwind Refuge in order to \'save\' his people. He sold them into slavery, or worse. And now he has gotten what he deserved! Let us speak now of a different traitor, one whom I believe has something that will make that rod of yours even more powerful.' WHERE `entry`=13989;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I was hoping for a squad of grunts... but if you earned Sergra\'s respect, I suppose you\'ll be more than enough. Let me explain what\'s happening here.' WHERE `entry`=13991;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, ho! That was beautiful. I probably shouldn\'t have stayed to watch. Now that they\'re looking for you, I\'ll slip quietly away in the dust of their aimless gallopin\'. Be sure to look for my buds at the other pools. Boss has agents at every one.' WHERE `entry`=13992;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Okay, $N. You\'re all set.$B$BI\'ve pre-programmed the path to Stonetalon, so all you\'ll need to worry about is keeping the bomb intact.$B$BYou can use the sawblades to mow down any enemies from a distance, or short-circuit a fuse to zap anyone who gets too close.$B$BYou have ONE chance to repair the bomb if it gets dangerously damaged. Use it wisely!$B$BSpeak to me when you think you\'re ready.$B$BGood luck!',`objectives_loc1`='Foreman Jinx wants you to ride the Repurposed Shredder to Stonetalon Mountains and speak to Saurboz.' WHERE `entry`=13993;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aw mon, why you have to go settin\' Gorgal off like that? Still, I can\'t argue with results. We\'ll need to watch these animals closely to see what they do with Kurak outta the way. More watchin\' and waitin\'. Gorgal won\'t like that.' WHERE `entry`=13995;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Explosive spore clouds? You don\'t say ... tell me more. Choking? Stinging? Burning of the eyes? Was there itching? Nausea? Mortification? Delightful, DELIGHTFUL! You\'ve certainly earned your commission, $N. That skin rash of yours should pass in a day or two.' WHERE `entry`=13998;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Quiet! Give me those notes. Were you followed here?' WHERE `entry`=13999;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, thank heavens that you survived, $N! I thought for sure that you\'d drowned when I saw you go over the side! Look at all of these folks you saved!' WHERE `entry`=14001;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sputtervalve scored us a Samophlange? Lemme see that thing! Yeah, we can get this working again, no problem. Hand me that huge mallet...' WHERE `entry`=14003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wenikee said what? Copperplug? BOSS Copperplug? Oh no, this might be tricky.' WHERE `entry`=14004;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Elune be praised! Everything I had encountered suggested this corruption to be buried deep within Teldrassil itself... I had worried we might never be able to strike at the source without killing the world tree. I am thankful I was wrong! Malfurion was the start to this great turn of fortune. Perhaps I will seek him out before I depart to the wilds again. Thank you, $N. Thank you for everything you have done. You are sure to be a great hero someday!' WHERE `entry`=14005;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found it! Wow, it\'s over 600 pages, only 30 of which are intentionally left blank. Let\'s see. Chapter three: Backsplicing the Reverse Crankshaft Flywheel Pulley? Interesting. Chapter seven: Valve Timing for the High-Pressure Expansion Condenser!? This stuff is great! And I still don\'t even know what this thing does. Here, have some of my old tools. Let\'s fire this thing up one last time!' WHERE `entry`=14006;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m Bamm Megabomb, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to perform a Steady Shot. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn the ability from me and then practice it on a training dummy here.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Bamm Megabomb and train Steady Shot, then shoot a Training Dummy with it 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you go, boss! Come back anytime you want more training. I\'ll teach you what I know.' WHERE `entry`=14007;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m Fizz Lighter, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to cast Arcane Missiles. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn the spell from me and then go practice casting it a few times on a training dummy across the yard to the southeast.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Fizz Lighter and train Arcane Missiles, then cast the spell 2 times at a Training Dummy.$B$BRemember, Arcane Missiles have a chance to activate through the use of other offensive spells. Use your Fireball spell first on the Training Dummy to enable the casting of your Arcane Missiles spell.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you go, boss! Come back anytime you want more training. I\'ll teach you what I know.' WHERE `entry`=14008;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m Sister Goldskimmer, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to cast Flash Heal. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn it from me and then use it to heal the injured employees around the courtyard.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Sister Goldskimmer and train Flash Heal, then cast the spell 3 times on an Injured Employee.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you go, boss! Come back anytime you want more training. I\'ll teach you what I know.' WHERE `entry`=14009;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m Slinky Sharpshiv, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to perform an Eviscerate. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn the ability from me and then go practice it on a training dummy in the southeast corner of the courtyard.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Slinky Sharpshiv and train Eviscerate, then use it 3 times on a Training Dummy.$B$BRemember, Eviscerate requires combo points, so first hit the dummy with Sinister Stike.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you go, boss! Come back anytime you want more training. I\'ll teach you what I know.' WHERE `entry`=14010;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m Maxx Avalanche, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to perform a Primal Strike. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn it from me and then go use it on a training dummy to the southeast.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Maxx Avalanche and train Primal Strike, then use it 2 times on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you go, boss! Come back anytime you want more training. I\'ll teach you what I know.' WHERE `entry`=14011;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m Evol Fingers, your personal trainer, $G sir : ma\'am;.$B$BI understand that you\'re interested in some new insight about being a $C? Look no further.$B$BI think you\'ll gain a great deal by me teaching you how to cast Immolate. It just might help you climb the corporate ladder if you know what I mean.$B$BLearn the spell from me and then cast it on a training dummy to the southeast.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Evol Fingers and train Immolate, then cast it 3 times on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you go, boss! Come back anytime you want more training. I\'ll teach you what I know.' WHERE `entry`=14012;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<The Warrior-Matic NX-01 comes online.>$B$BBoss $N detected. I am Warrior-Matic NX-01.$B$BInsert coins to learn how to Charge your opponents. Once trained, use Charge on a Training Dummy in the immediate area.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Warrior-Matic NX-01 and train the Charge ability, then use it on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$C-Matic NX-01 is programmed to serve. Return anytime you seek more training. This unit will teach you what it knows.' WHERE `entry`=14013;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I thought we were doomed for sure. But now we can start working on a way to get off of this island!' WHERE `entry`=14014;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Crusader Rhydalla frowns.>$B$BDo you think they\'ve been planning this? I suppose it doesn\'t matter, but I don\'t like the implication that we\'ve been playing into their hands. Whatever is going on, we have to stop it.' WHERE `entry`=14016;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The doctor will not have time to complete his work, but his plan is already in motion. From what you\'ve reported, the Lich Kings servants have reanimated and empowered the Black Knight and there\'s no telling what the knight\'s master has in mind. You have done well in uncovering this plot. I will tell High Crusader Adelard of your findings and together, we will alert the tournament\'s participants.' WHERE `entry`=14017;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The voice of the goddess spoke to you at the moonwell, $N. The cure for Relara lies to the east at Raynewood Tower. The one who has fallen into corruption.$B$BAvrus Illwhisper seeks forgiveness and redemption. It is up to you to assist him and in so doing, hopefully help my child as well.' WHERE `entry`=14018;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They launched up into the air when they ate the bananas?! That is hilarious! I think I\'m going to take a bunch out there and feed them myself!' WHERE `entry`=14019;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve hit the mother lode!!! Now, what\'s all this about a pygmy witchdoctor in charge of the monkeys? Is he dead? Because if he\'s dead, then legally I can stake my claim... not that I wasn\'t going to do that anyway. By $R law, all Kaja\'mite belongs to us!' WHERE `entry`=14021;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If you\'d like to learn to cook Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, I can help. If you\'re not already a cook, all you have to do is train and you\'ll be cooking in no time!' WHERE `entry`=14022;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. This is just what we needed. It\'s going to be a chore keeping all the tables stocked with fresh food, but it\'s well worth it.' WHERE `entry`=14023;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The pumpkin pie\'s been a big hit up here. I\'ve never seen a dwarf get so excited about anything made from a vegetable.' WHERE `entry`=14024;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Finally, the cranberry chutney I was promised. You wouldn\'t believe how fast the celebrants go through the stuff here.' WHERE `entry`=14028;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for bringing everything. I was starting to get worried.$B$BWhile you\'re here, you should try your hand at making some candied sweet potatoes.' WHERE `entry`=14030;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What are these? Clearly that pygmy witchdoctor is from some new race never seen before. Maybe we should call them $N-ians? They must be the ones that painted all of that stuff in the cavern. I\'m not sure that I like what you\'re describing. It sounds to me like they\'re paintings of them and us on an island with an exploding volcano!' WHERE `entry`=14031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Cave Painting 3 Captured',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Pygmy Altar Captured' WHERE `entry`=14031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Your first task is one of cleansing, $N. A clan of kobolds have infested the woods to the north. Go there and fight the kobold vermin you find. Reduce their numbers so that we may one day drive them from Northshire.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 10 Kobold Vermin, then return to Marshal McBride.' WHERE `entry`=14032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, candied sweet potatoes! My favorite! Did Isaac tell you?' WHERE `entry`=14033;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, this is it - this is it right here! So his flagship is named "The Bellipotent" eh? Let\'s see what it\'ll take to send this nuisance to the bottom of the sea.' WHERE `entry`=14034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Every Pilgrim\'s Bounty feast requires a magnificent centerpiece, and I\'m not talking about a decorative horn of plenty, either. No, the focus of the meal is a magnificent roast turkey.$B$BThere\'s a good recipe for it in your bountiful cookbook. Why not hunt some wild turkeys and prepare a few? The turkeys wander all over Elwynn Forest, so you shouldn\'t have a problem finding one.$B$BOnce you\'re done roasting them, will you bring them to Isaac Allerton near the gates of Darnassus?',`objectives_loc1`='Make 5 Slow-Roasted Turkeys and bring them to Isaac Allerton near the gates of Darnassus.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are beautiful and just in time to feed hungry feasters. Thank you, $N. You\'ve truly mastered all the courses of a traditional Pilgrim\'s Bounty meal.' WHERE `entry`=14035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If you\'d like to learn to cook Pilgrim\'s Bounty foods, I can help. If you\'re not already a cook, all you have to do is train and you\'ll be cooking in no time.' WHERE `entry`=14036;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s a chore keeping all these tables stocked. If you stop and think about it, it\'s strange going to so much trouble when we needn\'t eat anymore.$B$B<William shrugs.>$B$BTradition is tradition.' WHERE `entry`=14037;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Gazlowe spreads the plans on the table and jabs a tiny finger aft of the ship below the waterline.>$B$BThere! The hull is thinnest here, where the crankshaft meets the paddlewheel. And it\'s right next to the magazine!$B$B$N, I can\'t be held responsible if some enterprising Horde $C were to attach a limpet mine to that part of the hull. Not even if I supplied the mine. And paid $Ghim:her;. Handsomely. The ship is anchored just southeast of here... go to it!$B$BThen radio me with this stolen gnomecorder.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! I wish I could\'ve seen the look on that Rear Admiral\'s face when his flagship went up like a candle. Let me use my telescope here to take a look at the damage. What - Whhhaaatt!? That thing is still floating? Hartley must\'ve moved the munitions ashore in case his ship was mined. I underestimated you, Hartley... but for the last time!' WHERE `entry`=14038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, the blessed waters from our moonwells. You have borne witness to the Spirit of the Kaldorei, then? In recent times, I\'ve come to find that the spirit offers more questions than it does answers, but such is the continuing nature of discovery that drives us in our darkest hours. I will offer you the simplest answers that I can. Malfurion has returned to me... to us... but harsh times are yet upon us. Staghelm is gone and the world is wracked with pain - Malfurion has much to mend, and he will need help.' WHERE `entry`=14039;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The pie always goes first. I think people must be skipping the meal and going directly for the dessert. Have you given it a try yet?' WHERE `entry`=14040;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Have you tried the cranberry chutney yet? It\'s made with fresh tangy Southfury cranberries. Just pick some up from the Pilgrim\'s Bounty vendor if you want to try your hand at making chutney.$B$BThe recipe should be in your bountiful cookbook.$B$BIf you\'ve got some extra time on your hands, would you mind making some of the chutney and bringing it to Dokin Farplain at the base of the elevator on the western side of Thunder Bluff.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more cranberry chutney! You wouldn\'t believe how fast the celebrants go through it.' WHERE `entry`=14041;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! Beautiful work, $N. Those Alliance cretins will never trace this back to me. Meanwhile, it\'s back to business as usual: smuggling, double-dealing, price-gouging... I\'ve got a lot of work to catch up on. Here, I\'ll let you in on a cut of my future profits. Enjoy!' WHERE `entry`=14042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So Dokin drafted you to help with the candied sweet potatoes?$B$B<Francis smiles.>$B$BIt\'s the only way he can keep up. Thanks for bringing these.' WHERE `entry`=14043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc1`='Prepare Candied Sweet Potato' WHERE `entry`=14043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for bringing everything. Some of the tables were starting to look a little bereft of serving dishes.' WHERE `entry`=14044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah-har! So ol\' Gazzy ain\'t given up on his goods yet, has he? Well, looks like that ol\' floppy-eared goldgrubbler jes\' gave me somethin\' ta bargain with.' WHERE `entry`=14045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oh I won\'t be runnin\' off just yet. I\'ll free me mates and murder my way out of here at a time of me choosin\'. As fer you - a deal\'s a deal. Let\'s talk about that treasure...' WHERE `entry`=14046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Every Pilgrim\'s Bounty feast requires a centerpiece, and for us, that\'s a slow-roasted wild turkey. I can\'t think of anything better to bring the meal together.$B$BThere\'s a good recipe for it in your bountiful cookbook. Why not hunt some wild turkeys and prepare a few? The turkeys wander all over Tirisfal Glades, so you shouldn\'t have a problem finding any.$B$BOnce you\'re done roasting them, will you bring them to Francis Eaton outside Orgrimmar?',`objectives_loc1`='Make 5 Slow-Roasted Turkeys and bring them to Francis Eaton near the gates of Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='These look perfect. Thank you, $N. You\'ve truly mastered all the courses of a traditional Pilgrim\'s Bounty meal.' WHERE `entry`=14047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are just what I need. Thanks, $N. You\'re a lifesaver.' WHERE `entry`=14048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What? What is this? I send you out to fetch my treasure and you bring me a big filthy head?' WHERE `entry`=14049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, $N! Oh, the Baron tried to stop you, did he? Well, I hope you gave him a pounding. Now, I promised you a cut of the goods you recovered. Let\'s see... what\'s one percent of a half percent? Ah, here you go.' WHERE `entry`=14050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank goodness! I wouldn\'t be able to serve the feast without spice bread stuffing.' WHERE `entry`=14051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey hey mon, did Dizzywig send you? Good, good. Did you bring the money? No? ...what about the guns?' WHERE `entry`=14052;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks. This looks great, and you\'re a fair bit faster than Jasper, but don\'t tell him I said so.' WHERE `entry`=14053;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are perfect. Isaac, and everyone else, will love them!' WHERE `entry`=14054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are perfect. Thanks for helping me with this, $N. The meal will get served on time and Ellen will be happy.' WHERE `entry`=14055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at that. We\'re loaded! In mutiny, you gotta make the money first. Then when you get the money, you get the power. Let\'s go get some power, $N...' WHERE `entry`=14056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oooh, very nice. Shiny. Loud. Now we\'re talkin\'. Not much left to do but close the deal...' WHERE `entry`=14057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks, $N. Now, I can help the hostess out and still keep my word to Roberta.' WHERE `entry`=14058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for your help, and let me know if you ever get to the bottom of the case of the disappearing chutney.' WHERE `entry`=14059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are great! Thank you for helping, $N.' WHERE `entry`=14060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These turkeys are exactly what I needed. Thanks for helping me out of a tough situation.' WHERE `entry`=14061;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect timing! I wouldn\'t be able to serve the feast without spice bread stuffing.' WHERE `entry`=14062;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So Tony is running the show there now? Good! We need more pirates like him in these waters. He\'s a real businessman. Speaking of business, I suppose I owe you a cut. Would you be interested in insuring any of your new loot? You never know what can happen in a town like this...' WHERE `entry`=14063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What a feast, hmmm?$B$BI\'m so glad you could celebrate the spirit of Pilgrim\'s Bounty with us.' WHERE `entry`=14064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What a feast, hmmm?$B$BI\'m so glad you could celebrate the spirit of Pilgrim\'s Bounty with us.' WHERE `entry`=14065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This Horde caravan was not merely robbed. It was savagely brutalized. Crates of supplies have been ripped apart by sharp claws. The wagon has been demolished. The food has been eaten and the silver is gone, and yet useful supplies have been left behind...' WHERE `entry`=14066;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' What!? Raptors? Just the raptors? Assaulting our caravans and looting them? Perhaps they are as intelligent as the rumors say. As if we didn\'t have enough problems, now we\'ve got to deal with brainy lizards with a lust for coin. Here, $N - you\'ve earned a share of the rescued silver. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=14067;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hooway! You twapped the waptors I was wooking for! Now we will twain them for twolls to wide to swaughter the Awwiance!' WHERE `entry`=14068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I couldn\'t have done better myself. In fact, I didn\'t. I\'m sure that in no time at all we\'ll all be talking about the great and powerful, and may I add extremely wealthy, Trade Prince $N!' WHERE `entry`=14069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A complete success if I do say so myself, sir! Your debtors will think twice now about not paying up! Perhaps we should increase interest rates on loans across the board?' WHERE `entry`=14070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Jack the Hammer beaten down',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Sudsy Magee beaten down' WHERE `entry`=14070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, sir. You all look very good riding around in the hot rod. I\'m sure you made quite an impression on the citizenry.' WHERE `entry`=14071;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Ace picked up',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Gobber picked up' WHERE `entry`=14071;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $N. Did you look through these? They\'re barely legible - more like angry graffiti than war plans. Hatred, jealousy, rage, personal conflicts - it\'s a wonder Verog can keep these centaur from killing each other, much less form them into an army. We can use this to our advantage.' WHERE `entry`=14072;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, I\'ve heard about your work, $C. Your timing is fortunate - I\'ve got a major offensive in the works.' WHERE `entry`=14073;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Argent Crusade dispatched a fast ship carrying tallstrider meat and other supplies for us here at the tournament grounds, but it never arrived. Scouts reported seeing it attacked by the kvaldir, fearsome vrykul raiders who roam the seas.$B$BThey\'ve slain the crew and taken the cargo to an island called Hrothgar\'s Landing. If you look to the north, you can see it shrouded in the mist. Would you help us in recovering the stolen supplies? Without those tallstrider legs, we\'ll soon be out of food.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='These look a little worse for wear, but they\'re still edible. The crusaders will be glad to hear that we\'ve managed to recover some of the ship\'s cargo.' WHERE `entry`=14074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I say good riddance to those pests!' WHERE `entry`=14075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. I\'ll take these to the Argent Crusade\'s keepers right away. They\'ll have no choice but to acknowledge that we\'re doing far more than the Sunreavers to keep the coliseum running smoothly.' WHERE `entry`=14076;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Narasi accepts the prayer book from you.>$B$BThank you. The book was a gift from Confessor Paletress herself. She would be honored to know that you have used it to bring tranquility to the slain.' WHERE `entry`=14077;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Deep claw marks run through the man\'s corpse.' WHERE `entry`=14078;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14079;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your actions have shown that we stand as one with the Argent Crusade, while the Sunreavers are too busy preening to take up their blades.' WHERE `entry`=14080;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14081;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Aalun.$B$BAalun can be found at the entrance to the Exodar on Azuremyst Isle.',`objectives_loc1`='Return this pamphlet to Aalun outside the Exodar on Azuremyst Isle.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This pamphlet advertising riding training and mount purchases was sent from Ultham Ironhorn.$B$BUltham can be found at the Amberstill Ranch in Dun Morogh, found along the road east out of Ironforge.',`objectives_loc1`='Return the pamphlet to Ultham Ironhorn at Amberstill Ranch in Dun Morogh.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14083;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14084;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, shall we begin your Apprentice Riding training?' WHERE `entry`=14089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Sunreavers the care of this creature. They\'re enough alike that they ought to be able to understand each other.' WHERE `entry`=14090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s you again. Looks like you\'re not one to hide in the face of danger. Very well, then.' WHERE `entry`=14091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll let the crusaders know that you\'ve just returned with a fresh load of food while the Silver Covenant was sitting on its heels.' WHERE `entry`=14092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s no use, $N!  They\'re not letting up.' WHERE `entry`=14093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent!  I\'ll make sure these get taken to a safe place.' WHERE `entry`=14094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew that Kraken was not a match for the likes of you. Without that Kraken disrupting those boats, those Kvaldir will have no choice but to retreat. Great job, Champion!' WHERE `entry`=14095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks to you, Kul and the aspirants will live fight the Scourge again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. My only hope is that the crusaders can find a better outlet for his enthusiasm than allowing him to impart all of his bad habits to impressionable young aspirants.' WHERE `entry`=14096;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, $N. Thanks to you, many Gilneans will live to see another day.' WHERE `entry`=14098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re all fine here. A little shaken... but alive.' WHERE `entry`=14099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The kvaldir, seafaring vrykul who raid ships and coastal settlements, have overrun a tuskarr  island across the strait to the north. Their leader is a veteran raider, Drottinn Hrothgar, who seeks to control these seas.$B$BWith him in power, our shipments and troop transports will never be safe. We will be stranded here at the Lich King\'s mercy.$B$BTake this captured kvaldir war horn to the circle of tuskarr statues on the northeastern part of Hrothgar\'s Landing and use it to challenge the kvaldir leader.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The defeat of the drottinn will set the kvaldir to fighting amongst themselves, buying us time to use our advantage. The crusade and the tournament are in your debt, champion.' WHERE `entry`=14101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have bought us valuable time to move against the Kvaldir and free the seas of these pests. Once again, the Argent Crusade is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=14102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful!  Another batch of powder! Just between us jewelcrafters, I\'ve been making hand over fist selling "pure titanium" jewelry to the local Dalaran mages. Even with their superior intellect, they aren\'t particularly savvy with their gold. If you get more, I\'ll be here.' WHERE `entry`=14103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Ornolf the Scarred is a fearsome raider renowned among his Kvaldir brethren for raiding and capturing ships. From aboard Bor\'s Fury, he and his crew attack our ships and steal our goods.$B$BOrnolf and his men are among those who slaughtered the inhabitants of a tuskarr island to the north and renamed it Hrothgar\'s Landing. His ship sits at anchor at the eastern end of the island\'s harbor. Take this captured banner and display it on his ship to provoke him into facing you in battle.',`objectives_loc1`='High Crusader Adelard at the Argent Tournament Grounds wants you to kill Ornolf the Scarred.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ornolf\'s crew will want to avenge their leader, but without him, they will be easier to defeat. We must live to carry out our mission, to see Icecrown rid of the Scourge and other evils.' WHERE `entry`=14104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are truly an example to all who have gathered beneath our banner, $N. Together, we will show the Scourge that we will not be defeated.' WHERE `entry`=14105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done our fallen brethren a great service and spared us the need to face them again on the field of battle. As our campaign against the Scourge progresses, I find myself thinking about my own fate.$B$BShould I fall, $N, I would want someone like you to do for me what you have done for the spirits of the fallen this day. I could not bear the thought of forcing my own brothers to slay me again and again.' WHERE `entry`=14107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Crusader Silverdawn wants you to mount an Argent Hippogryph, throw 6 Flaming Spears at the North Sea Kraken and take out 3 Vrykul Deepcallers.$B$BYou can find the Argent Hippogryphs right outside the Argent Crusade tent at the Tournament Grounds.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Crusader, you may have bought those sailors just enough time to escape, Maybe next time, those Silver Covenant and Sunreavers will listen before running head first at the enemy.' WHERE `entry`=14108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, you are going to look so fine, but not as gorgeous as me! You\'re going to replace the Trade Prince any day now at the rate you\'re going! I can\'t wait to not have to work anymore! You\'re going to buy me everything that I want, right babe? Let me have all that stuff and I\'ll help you get into it right before the party.' WHERE `entry`=14109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh yeah, you\'re going to look hot! You\'re going to replace the Trade Prince any day now at the rate you\'re going! I can\'t wait to be a kept man! Let me have all that stuff and I\'ll help you get into it right before the party.' WHERE `entry`=14110;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Sunreavers.' WHERE `entry`=14112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very nicely done, sir. The party appears to have been a smashing success! Er... what\'s that?' WHERE `entry`=14113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Oh my gosh! Pirates!$B$B$N, there are Southsea pirates crashing your party!$B$BYou have to get in there and do something about this or your career, and any chance of you being the next Trade $G Prince : Princess;, is going to be ruined!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Phew, that was close, boss. Unfortunately, I\'m the bearer of more bad news. Please don\'t shoot me....' WHERE `entry`=14115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, well, well, if it isn\'t my wayward protege, Mr. $N. I\'m hurt and disappointed. You didn\'t send me an invitation to your little party out there. Sorry about the crashers... you know how pirates can be. So, shall we get down to business?' WHERE `entry`=14116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. As their scouts fail to report in, Talrendis will feel the terror they\'ve tried in vain to inflict on us.' WHERE `entry`=14117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Meat - and lots of it! Well done. This will keep bellies full as we build our arsenal.' WHERE `entry`=14118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A bazillion macaroons?!?! Where are we going to get that kind of moolah? Um... did the Trade Prince say anything about letting me escape with you on his yacht?' WHERE `entry`=14120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We\'re all going to die!!!$B$B<You slap Megs to calm her down.>$B$BSorry about that, $G Mr. : Ms.; $N. Okay, we need to find a way to get a lot of moolah quickly.$B$BThere are reports of the Trade Prince sending hired looters into the streets.$B$BYou could take the hot rod out there and run them down, snatching the loot that they\'ve illegally stolen. There wouldn\'t be anything wrong with that, right?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, you really did it?! Well, they had it coming, I guess. That\'s an awful lot of loot. Do you think it\'s enough to get you a spot on the Trade Prince\'s yacht? Are you going to be able to bring anyone with you? I don\'t make too much working in marketing.' WHERE `entry`=14121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, you have been saving! I\'m so proud of you! Um, boss... this isn\'t nearly enough.' WHERE `entry`=14122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, wow! These are worth a fortune. I just hope that the Trade Prince doesn\'t notice them when you hand them over with the rest of your wealth....' WHERE `entry`=14123;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$G Sir : Ma\'am;, we need tons of moolah to pay the Trade Prince and get off Kezan! Well, tons of it is just waiting for the taking down there in the Kaja\'mine!$B$BThese are the last known deposits of kaja\'mite anywhere. This is the raw stuff that made us the genius tinkerers and alchemists we are today. If that\'s not worth a bazillion macaroons, I don\'t know what is!$B$BTake some of my kablooey bombs and blowup the deposits. Then, pick up the chunks.$B$BJust watch out for the rebellious trolls!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nicely done, sir, nicely done! That\'s a fortune you have there in your bags. With all of that, I bet the Trade Prince will let all of us come along on his yacht!' WHERE `entry`=14124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is nothing. You should see Bilgewater Port... the whole thing is going up in flames! Fine, fine, I don\'t have time to inspect this place. Here\'s the moolah from the Bilgewater Cartel\'s insurance policy. I\'ve got to find a way off the island! Good luck, $N!' WHERE `entry`=14125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Drop a Cigar on the Flammable Bed',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='KTC Headquarters Set Ablaze with Gasbot!' WHERE `entry`=14125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Congratulations, you just made it. I see that you\'ve brought me all that I asked for, including your hot rod. A bazillion macaroons couldn\'t have been easy to come by. I\'m now the wealthiest, most powerful, $R on all of Azeroth! TOO BAD FOR YOU THAT I\'M CHANGING THE TERMS OF OUR DEAL! You\'re now my slave. Get below deck and take a turn shoveling coal. Next stop, Azshara! Muahahahahahahahaha!' WHERE `entry`=14126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' No, I can\'t make sense of it either, but I don\'t like what I see. Are these arcane runes? I\'ll need you to deliver this to an expert.' WHERE `entry`=14127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What? Give that here, this instant! Ag\'tor is correct, these are arcane runes. They\'re scouting out magical sites? Experimenting with the arcane arts? This is a marked departure from thousands of years of night elven history. Hmph! The idea that they will achieve any competence in this field - even those who once counted themselves among the highborne - is absurd.' WHERE `entry`=14128;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'ve been trying to impress our new Horde allies with our legendary Goblin efficiency, but in hindsight automating the shredders was a bad idea. Now they\'re mindless killing machines, rampaging over the countryside. Don\'t get me wrong - that kind of thing has its place - but for the time being I need a brave $C to help me get these things under control.$B$BIt\'s easy. Automated shredders, like all machines, must first be beaten into submission. Afterwards, seize the controls and I\'ll radio you instructions.',`objectives_loc1`='Attack one of the runaway shredders near the rear gates of Orgrimmar and hop inside once it\'s been significantly damaged.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Hey $N! Are you reading this? Piloting that sucker is easy. Push the pedals for your pedal controls and, ah, move the levers for your lever controls. Got it?' WHERE `entry`=14129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello there! A new friend! So glad to meet you. My name is Ergll. The g is silent.' WHERE `entry`=14130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Beautiful beans! They smell absolutely delicious, don\'t they?' WHERE `entry`=14131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Too mean? Naw, not too mean. They deserved it. I don\'t gum up their plants. Not ever.' WHERE `entry`=14132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great! You\'ve loaded the shredder to capacity. You\'re getting pretty handy with that thing...' WHERE `entry`=14134;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work, $N! That\'s how we took care of business back on Kezan.' WHERE `entry`=14135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great job, Champion. The fight continues, but now the Kvaldir know that we do not tolerate such attacks.' WHERE `entry`=14136;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A gift from Sassy? I hope it\'s a bonus!' WHERE `entry`=14138;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your actions have shown that we Sunreavers are far better allies to the Argent Crusade than the Silver Covenant and it is we who will be triumphant.' WHERE `entry`=14140;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Silver Covenant the care of this creature. They\'re going to have to get their hands dirty when the battle for Icecrown Citadel starts and I have a feeling they\'ll prove fragile and fussy allies.' WHERE `entry`=14141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Crusader Kul has gone and gotten himself into trouble again, only this time he\'s not alone. When he saw the cultists making camp at Deathspeaker\'s Watch, west of the tourney grounds, Kul gathered the aspirants for an attack.$B$BThey were easily captured, and now Kul languishes in a cage on the platform in the camp. I am sure that the cult will sacrifice the prisoners unless we can rescue them. Any of those cultists could carry keys to the black cages. Find the keys and free Kul and the captive aspirants.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Kul will live to embarrass himself again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. With examples like him, it\'s no wonder most of the aspirants are taking up the habits of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE `entry`=14142;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Argent Crusade dispatched a fast ship carrying tallstrider meat and other supplies for us here at the tournament grounds, but it never arrived. Scouts reported seeing it attacked by the kvaldir, fearsome vrykul raiders who roam the seas.$B$BThey\'ve slain the crew and taken the cargo to an island called Hrothgar\'s Landing. If you look to the north, you can see it shrouded in the mist. Would you help us in recovering the stolen supplies? Without those tallstrider legs, we\'ll soon be out of food.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='These look a little worse for wear, but they\'re still edible. The crusaders will be glad to hear that we\'ve had some success. Maybe we can give the half-eaten ones to the Silver Covenant. That would make my day.' WHERE `entry`=14143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Girana accepts the prayer book from you.>$B$BThank you. We don\'t always see eye-to-eye with the crusaders, but I\'ve learned a lot from Confessor Paletress in my time here.' WHERE `entry`=14144;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE `entry`=14145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good, $N.$B$BNow, the trick is to align the facets just right...' WHERE `entry`=14151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It seems things are worse than we initially thought. You still made a valiant effort and saved many of The Wavecrest\'s crew\'s lives.' WHERE `entry`=14152;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very nicely done, ma\'am. The party appears to have been a smashing success! Er... what\'s that?' WHERE `entry`=14153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='One of those mangy fleabags got Dempsey real good. We cannot move him until we stabilize his bleeding.$B$BGive us a hand holding back these mongrels. A couple of minutes is all we need, $Gbrother:sister;!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We did it, $N. Thanks to you a good man has survived.' WHERE `entry`=14154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Use the shredder to destroy the Talrendis Ancient. Emergency Backup Shredders are available at the Orgrimmar Rear Gate if you lose yours.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it, $N! The invaders have pulled back. And they told me I was crazy for installing a grenade launcher on a woodchipper... Great work with the Shredder. With an impressive showing like that right here on the Warchief\'s doorstep, the Horde can\'t doubt what goblin technology can do for them. I owe you a big thanks!' WHERE `entry`=14155;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='If the king wants to rescue Lord Crowley and his band of traitors, then we will follow his orders.$B$BIt is just as well... one of my men was assigned to infiltrate Crowley\'s group in prison and it most certainly would be good to find out if he\'s survived this incident.$B$BApproach Sean Dempsey discretely... you do not want to give away his position among Crowley\'s men. They might prove to be more dangerous to his life than the worgen.',`objectives_loc1`='Find Sean Dempsey on the rooftop of the Gilneas City Prison.' WHERE `entry`=14156;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Greymane wants to save Crowley?  Has he gone mad?' WHERE `entry`=14157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Don\'t look at me!  Leave me alone!' WHERE `entry`=14159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is a fine list of deeds, $N!  You are to be rewarded handsomely for your accomplishments.' WHERE `entry`=14160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. One less nuisance to worry about.' WHERE `entry`=14161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re here to help? Excellent! Here, sign this indemnity waiver. And here, this noncompete clause. Let\'s get you started!' WHERE `entry`=14162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde will never be a match for our forces as long as we have people like you on our side, $N.' WHERE `entry`=14163;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nothing will stand between us and total victory. For the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=14164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well well, let\'s take a look at what we got here... Bah! Crumbly! Useless. Wouldn\'t even make a good countertop. My miners may be mediocre workers, but they make lousy bricks. . Well, I suppose we should re-fleshify these guys so I can get some return on my investment.' WHERE `entry`=14165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Dwarf Spirit in Ironforge\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Draenei Spirit in The Exodar\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Blood Elf Spirit in Silvermoon City\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Forsaken Spirit in Undercity\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Tauren Spirit in Thunder Bluff\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=14177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent news, $C! If our tactical deployments continue to be this successful, the Horde will be in full retreat before long.' WHERE `entry`=14178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Win an Eye of the Storm battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve come one step closer to achieving total victory over the Horde. We cannot allow the enemy to obtain a foothold in this world or any other.' WHERE `entry`=14179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE `entry`=14180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=14181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You bring honor to us all, $N. We must show the enemy that we will fight them wherever we find them.' WHERE `entry`=14182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`objectives_loc1`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE `entry`=14183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What!? Furien!! My brother is no more? They must pay! All of them!' WHERE `entry`=14184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Furien\'s passing is... regrettable. I shall do all that I can to assist you in avenging his death.' WHERE `entry`=14188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Sorrem wants you to find the Ancient Tablets.$B$BSpeak to Narimar at Furien\'s Post to ride to where Furien was known to study.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Comparing the characters on the ancient tablet to those in Furien\'s journal, it is clear that there is a distinct correlation.' WHERE `entry`=14189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Is that you, $N? Still alive? You aren\'t trashing my explosive stockpiles are you? Hmmm... you say you found a clear crystal pendant. That makes sense. A perfect prism would refract the gaze of the basilisk. Maybe we can use this to our advantage. Time to drop some science!' WHERE `entry`=14190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is clear to you now that these ruins are those that Furien recorded in his journal. After examining the engravings upon the ruins themselves, you feel that you are able to decipher more of Furien\'s writings.' WHERE `entry`=14191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='After filling it with liquid from the melons, you proceed to wash your eyes from the ancient font. Upon opening your eyes, you are able to see the spirits of ancient elves, still faithfully carrying out rituals to their goddess.' WHERE `entry`=14193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, good. Now we can get these slackers back to work. You\'ve earned a cut of the profits though - minus the usual company fees. Take your pick!' WHERE `entry`=14194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is clear to you now why you were guided here. You recognize this ancient runestone from Furien\'s final journal entry: "The ancients revered the gems created by this mystical object, claiming that they were gifts from the goddess herself. It was believed that they were weapons capable of delivering them from any enemy."' WHERE `entry`=14195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done! Furien\'s exhaustive research was not in vain. The raging Vortex is ready to be unleashed upon your enemies at last!' WHERE `entry`=14196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! When it comes to iron, always pick quantity over quality.' WHERE `entry`=14197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very impressive, $C. You completed Furien\'s work and rained vengeance down upon his killers. You have brought peace to my brother\'s soul, and to my mind. Please accept this gift for your diligence.' WHERE `entry`=14198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good to see that you have emerged victorious from the trial. Truly, you are a champion, not only of the Argent Crusade, but indeed of the Kirin Tor as well.$B$BOne can only hope that you have dealt the final blow to that dark villain and that\'s the last that we will see of him.' WHERE `entry`=14199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' So the spirits of the dead still haunt those old stones, hm? Well $N, as it happens, I\'m counting on their help. Let\'s see what the dead have to say...' WHERE `entry`=14201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Beautiful work! Now that we know the area better, we can tear this lake a new one.' WHERE `entry`=14202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is quite a find, <name>. I can\'t have you selling this to anyone else, so I\'m willing to offer generously.' WHERE `entry`=14203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. I\'ll start rounding up some help to get these cannons positioned.' WHERE `entry`=14204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Busted ball bearings! Look at this stuff - ugh, SMELL this stuff - my poor, poor dozer! $N, I consider myself a goop expert and this here goop ain\'t natural. It\'s supernatural. This is ghost goop. We\'re going to need more than a mechanic...' WHERE `entry`=14209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brace yourself, $N. Here they come.' WHERE `entry`=14212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The divine brazier indiscriminately endows you with a blessing.' WHERE `entry`=14213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew Crowley would come through. His weapons will be more than useful to us.' WHERE `entry`=14214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You reel as the spirit\'s vision fades, relieved to once again feel the earth beneath your feet and the comforting rhythm of your own quickened heart.' WHERE `entry`=14215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A Sarcen stone? That\'s the stuff of legend - let me see that! $N, Sarcen stones are used to redirect the ley lines of magical energy. You realize what this means? The mages of Mennar weren\'t staying behind out of misguided loyalty. They sacrificed their lives in order to create this artifact in an attempt to draw energy away from the portal through which the demons were flooding Azeroth. They were buying time for the rest of the world to fight back! History never recorded their deeds. What a discovery!' WHERE `entry`=14216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The divine brazier indiscriminately endows you with a blessing.' WHERE `entry`=14217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. You\'ve done more than could be asked of any Gilnean. We\'re running low on ammunition. It\'s time to regroup inside now.' WHERE `entry`=14218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the ritual completed, you are awarded a divine gift. You can\'t help but wonder what Elune would think of someone such as you receiving one of her boons.' WHERE `entry`=14219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve given them everything we have... yet still they come. Do not worry, $N. We\'ll slay many more before today is over.' WHERE `entry`=14221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They... they\'ve stopped coming. No, $N. That\'s not a good thing.' WHERE `entry`=14222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done. Sorrem should be able to sleep in peace now that Kohor\'s threats have been silenced.' WHERE `entry`=14223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is most fortunate that you took the time to search for this. No one would have expected the Burning Blade to be in possession of something so powerful!' WHERE `entry`=14225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Do not fret, and better yet, do not forget, to do not let the bug juice set or you will regret... well, you\'ll regret the smell of your boots really! It won\'t smell good today and it won\'t smell good even more tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=14226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You diverted what would have been a serious crisis, $C. If that summoning was delayed just a bit longer, the demon would have become far too powerful for our small forces here to contend with. Please accept this gift as our thanks for your service.' WHERE `entry`=14227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Peachy. Back to work then. Thanks, snookums.' WHERE `entry`=14230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ears of the Burning Blade? Well done, $C. This is just a shadow of what will soon become of that vile cult!' WHERE `entry`=14232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Orcs?! They were sunk and stranded too?  And now the Alliance are on the island? Do you think they\'re going to kill us? I think it\'s time for a little sitdown with these orcs.' WHERE `entry`=14233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I apologize. It has been a very rough couple of days for all of us. I am Aggra. All of us here are what remains of the crew of the Draka\'s Fury. Perhaps we can work together. We have a common enemy in the Alliance. Their SI:7 assassins are all over this island and they\'re not going to stop until we\'re all dead.' WHERE `entry`=14234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$R, can you fight? For your sake, I hope so. Otherwise, there may be no breaking through this hell of killer plants.' WHERE `entry`=14235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I saw it with my own eyes, and still I do not believe it! You have our thanks and the debt of our lives, little $R. I hope that soon we can repay you the honor. May I ask a small favor of you while my scouts and I move on?' WHERE `entry`=14236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Throm-Ka, $N. We have a problem.' WHERE `entry`=14237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N, well done. We\'ll make an orc of you yet! Time to move on. We\'d better hurry.' WHERE `entry`=14238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello, little $R. Bastia is fast, no? We have something very important that needs doing. Can you help us?' WHERE `entry`=14240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm, where the heck is the ignition? It\'ll be a wonder if it flies without doing something weird, like turning into a chicken or shrinking down to the size of an ant. Hey look, someone left their loose change in the ashtray! What else is in there?' WHERE `entry`=14241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If not for you, I would surely be on my way back to Stormwind to be paraded as a trophy and a slave. The Alliance dogs found me unconscious on the shore and put me in this magical cage. It was keeping me from connecting with the elements. No longer!' WHERE `entry`=14242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done what few others could have, $N. Our world owes you a debt larger than you can possibly understand.' WHERE `entry`=14243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='While you were rescuing the Warchief and saving us all from the Alliance, Foreman Dampwick built this rocket sling to shoot us over the shark-infested strait to the bigger island.$B$BLuckily for us, the foreman managed to salvage a Town-In-A-Box from the shipwreck. Once you get it set up, we\'ll have a town of our own. I can\'t wait to sleep in a bed again!$B$BDampwick\'s down there at the Landing Site, waiting for you. Why don\'t you take the next rocket over?',`objectives_loc1`='Survive the Rocket Sling shot across the Dire Strait.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, I sure am glad you survived the trip... not everyone did!' WHERE `entry`=14244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Hey! Where\'s the dock?! Someone stole the dock and the oil refinery from our town-in-a-box! Who would do such a thing? Where\'s the Trade Prince?' WHERE `entry`=14245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $C. This land is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=14246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You look around, scanning the horizon for what might be responsible for placing this stone here....' WHERE `entry`=14247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Boss! Er, well, I guess you\'re not the boss anymore, but still, good to see you! Can you believe it? We\'ve got a cave full of intelligent killer monkeys mining Kaja\'mite!' WHERE `entry`=14248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ha ha! Perfect! Let me toss this together really fast. The Archmage is sure to be taken in by my style!' WHERE `entry`=14249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work. This should keep us for another few hours before we have to go back for more. He doesn\'t seem to be the brightest of giants. I expect we\'ll be able to keep doing this for a while before he catches on.' WHERE `entry`=14250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='There\'s never been danger of centaur attack this far north before. Someone put \'em up to it, I just know it!$B$BRegardless, I\'m wiped out. I had everything invested in this haul.$B$BFortunately, there\'s one thing no centaur can take from me and that\'s goblin ingenuity! I\'ll start from scratch and build an empire!$B$B<Bizby spots a scorpion in the distance.>$B$BThere\'s always a market for poison. Whatdya say, friend?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is how I got my start, you know. Slingin\' poison to the rogues in Orgrimmar. Ahh, those were the days....' WHERE `entry`=14251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll do, $C. A few more friends like you and I\'ll be back on my feet in no time!' WHERE `entry`=14252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well now, that\'s quite a load of feathers, $C. They\'ll make for a good pillow \'til I get \'em to market!' WHERE `entry`=14253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'s this? Wahoo! I know someone who will be most interested in acquiring these samples. Most generous in payment for them as well, I\'ll wager. Here, $C. Take this as your finder\'s fee.' WHERE `entry`=14254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good that you have come. There is grave danger looming here.' WHERE `entry`=14255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So now you see. These are not a simple band of displaced naga, but a well organized army, capable of great devastation. Do you agree to assist me in my investigation?' WHERE `entry`=14256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $C. But I\'m afraid that your work here is just beginning.' WHERE `entry`=14257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sweet! Beautiful! Brilliant! Who loves you? With my mortars re-supplied, I can help you as you assault the Naga east of here. Use these markers to call in an artillery strike anywhere on the cliffs, and I\'ll splatter the whole area with fiery hurt. Oh delicious, merciless, random destruction! I hope you\'re well-armored...' WHERE `entry`=14258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='More Mortars, More!',`details_loc1`='Thanks for helping me restock my supplies, $N.$B$BI\'ll tell you what, bring me more mortars from the lab, and I\'ll keep supplying you with artillery signals. With me on the trigger and you in the field, we\'ll blast these cliffs until they go crashing into the sea!' WHERE `entry`=14259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Don\'t just stand around, when there is so much to be done! Must I instruct everyone on each detail?' WHERE `entry`=14260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What? So you didn\'t bring any of the drake pieces back? Disappointing. I knew I should have made you sign a contract before I sent you out...' WHERE `entry`=14261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' And still they come! They are like a plague, $N. But with strength like yours, we will crush them. Someday.' WHERE `entry`=14262;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect. It\'s quite interesting how useful the most random things end up being to incantations of this sort. So much more to learn!' WHERE `entry`=14263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The enemy\'s ranks are thinning, little minnow. Perhaps you are worthy of assisting in our search....' WHERE `entry`=14264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N!  Where have you been? Anyway... it\'s great to see you in one piece.' WHERE `entry`=14265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You\'re alive, $N!  That must mean I did something right.$B$BIt\'s a shame our lessons were cut off a little short. But perhaps there\'s a thing or two I can teach you that might be handy in a time like this.$B$BTry out your new technique against the bloodfang worgen to our west.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Sergeant Cleese and learn Charge. Practice using Charge against a Bloodfang Worgen.' WHERE `entry`=14266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The stone in the center of this shrine emits a faint glow and roars with the power of the angry sea.' WHERE `entry`=14267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes! You\'ve found it! Neptulon\'s engravings... there can be no mistake!' WHERE `entry`=14268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, hey!  There you are!' WHERE `entry`=14269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The keystone shard slides into place and previously invisible runes suddenly erupt onto the surface of the stone, shimmering in blue and violet hues. Your knees buckle as powerful arcane currents suddenly race into your body...' WHERE `entry`=14270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='An energy barrier, you say? This explains a great deal! I\'ve seen firsthand how Naga leaders have been able to turn aside the blades of some of my best warriors. Now we know the source of their power, $N. Let\'s finish this!' WHERE `entry`=14271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Good to see you alive!$B$BNo, of course I don\'t have that gold I owe you. Now\'s not really the time to bring that up is it?$B$BListen, maybe I can teach you a trick or two that might save your skin with all the carnage going on. I\'d call it more than even then. What do you say?$B$BAfter your lesson is over, try using your new technique against the Bloodfang Worgen to our west.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Loren the Fence and learn Eviscerate. Practice using Eviscerate against a Bloodfang Worgen.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Don\'t get ahead of yourself now. Just remember who taught you everything you know. And now let\'s see if we can get out of this city with our skins attached.' WHERE `entry`=14272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A darkness has descended over our lands. And not our kind of darkness, if you know what I mean.' WHERE `entry`=14273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It is true then!  You live!$B$BI never got a chance to share my greatest discovery with you. From the depths of the nigh-indecipherable books of Balcephoth of the felshadows... I\'ve learned the forbidden secrets of...$B$BImmolate!$B$BOf course I will share this knowledge with you... who else around here would appreciate such powerful understanding?$B$BGo now, and practice your new spell against the Bloodfang Worgen to our west.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Vitus Darkwalker and learn Immolate. Practice casting Immolate on a Bloodfang Worgen.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes!  You can feel the power, can\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=14274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N!  I knew you had to be around here.' WHERE `entry`=14275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='So I\'ve got good news and bad news.$B$BThe bad news is that there are more worgen in the woods than in here... so we really have no safe place to go to.$B$BThe good news is that I still have a thing or two to teach you. Who knows the sort of skill that might save your life in a time like this.$B$BTry your hand at it against the bloodfang worgen to our west.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Huntsman Blake and learn Steady Shot. Practice using Steady Shot 2 times against a Bloodfang Worg.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. These $R will regret ever setting foot in our lands.' WHERE `entry`=14276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A disciple of the arcane always finds a way forward. I\'m glad to see you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=14277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Light is with you, $N. It\'s still quite a relief to see you.' WHERE `entry`=14278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You have much to learn, $N. And I\'ve much to teach you.$B$BThese are perilous times, however, and I fear that we might have to accelerate certain lessons.$B$BHave no fear, $G brother:sister;. The Light will guide us through this.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Sister Almyra and learn Flash Heal. Use Flash Heal 2 times on a Wounded Guard.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are blessed, $N. The Light shines upon you, even in these dark times.' WHERE `entry`=14279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We have been blessed today!  You are alive and well!' WHERE `entry`=14280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The path ahead is difficult, $N. We must devote the entirety of our mental power to the task at hand.$B$BYet sometimes, that is not enough. Sometimes the situation calls for raw firepower.$B$BI know just the spell for such a situation and I\'ll be more than glad to share it with you. Once you\'ve learned it, practice using it against the Bloodfang Worgen to our west. You\'ll only get the chance to use your new spell after casting a different spell.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Myriam Spellwaker and learn Arcane Missiles. Use Arcane Missiles against a Bloodfang Worgen.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve learned with such speed and ease. Soon you\'ll be the one doing the teaching.' WHERE `entry`=14281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The vision was true! You have singlehandedly succeeded where others have failed. The Circle will be have no choice but to pay attention to these findings.' WHERE `entry`=14282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We were driven to the edge of extinction once before, $N. But we druids, keepers of the old ways, saved our people from famine.$B$BWhen we cut ourselves off from the outside world and our crops failed, it was our order who called upon the earth\'s blessings and restored the harvest.$B$BJust as we did then, it is best to put our fate in the hands of a higher power. Join me now and learn what the wild has to teach us.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Celestine of the Harvest and learn Rejuvenation. Practice using Rejuvenation on a Wounded Guard.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad at all. Perhaps there is still hope for the old ways.' WHERE `entry`=14283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The priestess is no more...' WHERE `entry`=14284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well in coming here. If we Gilneans stick together we might yet defeat this terrible enemy.' WHERE `entry`=14285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well in coming here. If we Gilneans stick together we might yet defeat this terrible enemy.' WHERE `entry`=14286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well in coming here. If we Gilneans stick together we might yet defeat this terrible enemy.' WHERE `entry`=14287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well in coming here. If we Gilneans stick together we might yet defeat this terrible enemy.' WHERE `entry`=14288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well in coming here. If we Gilneans stick together we might yet defeat this terrible enemy.' WHERE `entry`=14289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well in coming here. If we Gilneans stick together we might yet defeat this terrible enemy.' WHERE `entry`=14290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well in coming here. If we Gilneans stick together we might yet defeat this terrible enemy.' WHERE `entry`=14291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have witnessed your actions here, $R. Your presence here is both welcome and timely.' WHERE `entry`=14292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. We\'ll make sure Krennan makes it out of the city alive.' WHERE `entry`=14293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re left with very few choices, $N. What we do next will be a critical decision.' WHERE `entry`=14294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now THAT is how we used to handle serpents back in Durotar - we crushed them under our boots! You have done the Horde proud, $N. As soon as my reinforcements arrive we\'ll mop up the rest of those vermin and claim this peninsula once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=14295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is in this moment that most of my apprentices wonder if there was a logical purpose to storing the energy for my portal in those conduits so that it has to be collected in such a fashion. Of course there\'s a purpose! I wish to study your behavior... your strategies, your mistakes, your frustrations, your triumphs. Those are the entire point of these trials. Now, more. More trials! Doesn\'t that sound exciting?! Of course it does.' WHERE `entry`=14296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks there, pal. Here\'s your commission. If you\'ll excuse me, I\'ve gotta get these slackers back to work.' WHERE `entry`=14297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome! You seem to have survived the trials relatively unscathed. Good for you, love. You look to have come with a purpose in mind as well. A question. Your thoughts are very loud, it\'s hard for me to not hear them. Go ahead then, hon. Ask away.' WHERE `entry`=14299;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Trial of Fire... oooh... sounds intimidating, doesn\'t it? No? Hm. Well I kind of thought so. Firsts are first, you touch the fire crystal and the portal to the trial opens.$B$BTo beat this trial, you have to hop around in the fire runes without getting hit by the fire. If you stay unflamed long enough, you win!$B$BThere are little signs to help you - fire hopping to it\'s new rune, fizzles when a rune goes cold. You can figure that stuff out if you want. Or just guess! That\'s what most people do.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Woo! Good for you! That trial really put a fire under your bottom.' WHERE `entry`=14300;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Please accept this reward for your heroic accomplishments, $N. You have bought us precious time!' WHERE `entry`=14301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Cenarion Researcher Korrah wants you to take Korrah\'s Report to Karnum at Karnum\'s Grove.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is alarming news, indeeed, $R - something we have no shortage of here. I shall call a council regarding the issue. You will be summoned if you are needed.' WHERE `entry`=14302;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I am not easily impressed, but if what you are telling me is true, then I have never before heard of such a thing. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=14303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This should be enough. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=14304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are fine specimens, $R. I shall commence my studies immediately.' WHERE `entry`=14305;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='On behalf of Desolace herself, I thank you, $R. Please accept our deepest gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=14306;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $C. We will doubtlessly call upon you for assistance with more significant matters in the future.' WHERE `entry`=14307;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, $N! Now, we need to decouple the reaction core matrix from the fuel sumps, or that whole place is gonna blow itself to Outland...' WHERE `entry`=14308;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful! Karnum will be so pleased! Please, accept this as my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=14309;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Whew, the sample is secure. And it\'s still steaming! Thank you, $N.$B$BAzsharite is a complex mystery wrapped in a velvety enigma of danger. Grapplehammer insists that we learn more about this strange substance.' WHERE `entry`=14310;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The rejuvenation is so invigorating! Don\'t you think?' WHERE `entry`=14311;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Be not afraid, $R. I mean you no harm.' WHERE `entry`=14312;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It worked!  By the Light, it worked!' WHERE `entry`=14313;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $R. Our tribe may not have survived without your aid.' WHERE `entry`=14314;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Liam\'s Stupor',`details_loc1`='Go away!  You\'re just inside my head... You\'re not real.... you\'re dead!$B$BYou died in Gilneas City... the worgen... they got you...$B$BIt should\'ve been me... it should\'ve been me...$B$BAughhh... first the earth won\'t stop moving... and now I\'m seeing things... too much rye...$B$B<The prince seems out of it. Perhaps you can find someone else to speak to.>' WHERE `entry`=14315;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As we suspected, the Magram have been stealing our supplies. We shall guard them more closely.' WHERE `entry`=14316;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why is it that you meddle in centaur affairs, $R?' WHERE `entry`=14318;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Further Treatment',`details_loc1`='Listen, $N. I\'m not going to beat around the bush.$B$BThere\'s a good chance the potion Krennan made for you wasn\'t a complete success. Or perhaps you need more of it.$B$BEither way, he\'s probably better equipped to advise you than I am. Go see him.' WHERE `entry`=14319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The crate has been smashed and the vials inside of it appear to have been broken.' WHERE `entry`=14320;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Forsaken!  Quick, $N!  We must mount a defense.' WHERE `entry`=14321;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So the world is safe for science again? Excellent! Next time I\'ll try heated needles or something.' WHERE `entry`=14322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve collected all of the simmering water droplets that Ergll requested. Now it\'s just a matter of summoning the "jumbo" elemental.' WHERE `entry`=14323;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Convenient, no? Who needs hot springs anyway. This is perfect.' WHERE `entry`=14324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good, $R. This will sustain us for now.' WHERE `entry`=14325;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My mission is too critical to let these meddlers continue to dog us. It\'s up to you and I to put an end to this once and for all!' WHERE `entry`=14326;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $C. Now we must convince the Gelkis...' WHERE `entry`=14327;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My sons all slain... my clan in ruins.... Were I in my youth, I would tear you limb from limb! Go now... kill me or leave me to mourn alone, $R.' WHERE `entry`=14328;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<The Khan of the Gelkis clan stares at you with an empty gaze as you detail the demon threat and Leh\'prah\'s visions.>$B$BIt matters not to me what becomes of this land now. I have failed my clan and my forefathers....$B$BThere is but one thing left in this world that might bring my old soul hope, and she\'s likely dead as well.$B$BMy precious daughter, Kherrah, was taken from me by the Maraudine clan. If you can bring her back to me alive, I shall consider your proposal.',`objectives_loc1`='Khan Shodo wants you to kill 10 Maraudine Maulers in the Valley of Spears.$B$BYou are to search their corpses for clues to Kherrah\'s whereabouts.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='As you slaughter their enemy, the Gelkis clan cannot help but to acknowledge your prowess.' WHERE `entry`=14329;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='You are to find Kherrah somewhere behind the doors to Maraudon.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Is it safe for me to leave, $R?' WHERE `entry`=14330;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $R. And not a moment too soon....' WHERE `entry`=14332;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The destruction of those defiled relics will ease the minds of the Gelkis, and will strengthen their resolve. You have done well.' WHERE `entry`=14333;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oy, mon! Ya did it! We soon be havin\' fish to eat, thanks be to you.' WHERE `entry`=14334;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='On behalf of us all at Shadowprey Village, I thank you, $R.' WHERE `entry`=14335;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N!!!  You ARE alive! I thought I was having dreams about the old days when I heard your voice...' WHERE `entry`=14336;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Shadowprey Village, $R. I was not sure the Cenarion Circle would send anyone.' WHERE `entry`=14337;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Greetings, $C. It is good that you have finally arrived....' WHERE `entry`=14338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, yes. These will do nicely....' WHERE `entry`=14339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well look at you, aren\'t you just a marvel of modern Magery! Quite a fancy hat, I must say. Apprentices. Apprentici? I do think that I might have quite a few already, but I suppose one can never have too many appren..tici.' WHERE `entry`=14340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Nataka at Ghost Walker Post wants you to deliver Smeed\'s Harnesses to Smeed.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, my harnesses! Thanks, friend!' WHERE `entry`=14341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $R! The danger persists, but you have bought us some time.' WHERE `entry`=14342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Maurin wants you to deliver Maurin\'s Concoction to Karnum at Karnum\'s Grove.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hate to use such unnatural measures, but I fear we simply have no choice....' WHERE `entry`=14343;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You should be proud of how you manipulated the enemy\'s power and used it against them. You\'ve dealt the demons of Mannoroc a severe blow....' WHERE `entry`=14344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look buddy, I was in your shoes not a week ago. Big powerful Archmage actually takes on apprentices! Who could pass up an opportunity like that?! Sometimes, things really are just too good to be true.' WHERE `entry`=14345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your deeds continue to impress me, $N. Please accept this gift on behalf of the Cenarion Circle.' WHERE `entry`=14346;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Sea Giants Defeated',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Slitherblade Invaders Defeated' WHERE `entry`=14346;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, $N!  Just like old times... I\'m going to have to work hard at not shooting you, but Krennan explained everything to us.' WHERE `entry`=14347;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You and me, $N. We make a great team... It\'s good to have you back.' WHERE `entry`=14348;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Because you fought with such valor and perseverance in the Battle of Hillsbrad, I have written this commendation, extolling your heroics in combat for the high command to recognize.$B$BTake this sealed commendation to Bragor Bloodfist in the Undercity. Go with pride, $C.',`objectives_loc1`='Take Darthalia\'s Sealed Commendation to Bragor Bloodfist in the Undercity.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you\'re the $C who tore through the Alliance forces in the Hillsbrad Foothills? I\'ve heard your name already. Word travels fast.$B$BThe Horde can use someone like you if you keep this up, $N.$B$BWe need to keep our eyes on all threats around us, but with that king leading them, the humans will continue to be a problem. You\'ve confirmed that there\'s strength enough in the Horde to end that threat in time.' WHERE `entry`=14351;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Take the Small Scroll to Bragor Bloodfist in the Undercity.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve seen the insignia on this scroll before during my time in Northrend. You say this was on that crone who leads the pigs in Razorfen Kraul?$B$BI\'ll be damned if I\'m going to let the Scourge get a foothold here. The one who wrote this - this Malcin - is one of the Lich King\'s servants, obviously, and that makes him a target. Your target.$B$BThey\'re not going to take Kalimdor.' WHERE `entry`=14352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Supposedly this Malcin is outside Razorfen Downs. There\'s no question - he has to die.$B$BMy contacts in Orgrimmar tell me their scouts have found signs of the Plague down there. The quilboar are showing signs of being plagued, too; they\'re much more powerful. Whatever the Scourge are doing down there needs to end. Now.$B$BFind this Malcin and kill him. Report back here when he\'s dead.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring Ambassador Malcin\'s Head to Bragor Bloodfist in the Undercity.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $C! You\'ve done the Horde proud by stopping the Scourge from setting down roots on our soil. An act like that deserves a reward, and the Forsaken have enough lying around that I\'m sure they can spare a few things. We may not know everything they\'ve done in the Downs, but we\'ll find out. They can\'t slink around in the dark forever.' WHERE `entry`=14353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The relics are intact! Well, indeed, that is something. You have put my mind at ease, $R. Please accept this as my gift to you.' WHERE `entry`=14354;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m sure Sylvanas will be glad to have that problem taken care of, $N. The task I gave you wasn\'t easy, but here you stand, victorious. That commands respect, and what you\'ve done won\'t be forgotten.' WHERE `entry`=14355;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, $C. You\'ve done well. I\'ll keep these safe from prying eyes; the last thing we need is a strong Shadow Council rising up again.$B$BCheck back with me in the future; there\'s always something that needs doing around here, apparently, and I might need another able body.' WHERE `entry`=14356;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the ritual completed, you are awarded a divine gift. You can\'t help but to feel a great sense of honor as you receive one of Elune\'s boons.' WHERE `entry`=14357;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The divine brazier graciously endows you with a blessing.' WHERE `entry`=14358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The divine brazier graciously endows you with a blessing.' WHERE `entry`=14359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='After filling it with liquid from the melons, you proceed to wash your eyes from the ancient font. Upon opening your eyes, you are able to see the spirits of ancient elves, still faithfully carrying out rituals to their goddess. You ponder the significance of this revelation and determine to study Furien\'s research for more clues....' WHERE `entry`=14360;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done. Captain Pentigast should be able to sleep in peace now that Kohor\'s threats have been silenced.' WHERE `entry`=14361;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ears of the Burning Blade? Well done, $C. This is just a shadow of what will soon become of that vile cult!' WHERE `entry`=14362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is most fortunate that you took the time to search for this. No one would have expected the Burning Blade to be in possession of something so powerful!' WHERE `entry`=14363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You diverted what would have been a serious crisis, $C. If that summoning was delayed just a bit longer, the demon would have become far too powerful for our small forces here to contend with. Please accept this gift as our thanks for your service.' WHERE `entry`=14364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good that you have come. There is grave danger looming here.' WHERE `entry`=14365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great news, $N. I\'ve sent the remaining militia to the shore to meet the Forsaken force head on.' WHERE `entry`=14366;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Forsaken are here in full strength, $N. We barely have enough men to hold them back.' WHERE `entry`=14367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My children are safe!  You\'ve done a wonderful thing, $N. I don\'t know how to thank you!' WHERE `entry`=14368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, $N. It\'s a good thing you\'re on our side.' WHERE `entry`=14369;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, excellent. Some of these samples look fresh. I\'m going to be up to my neck in this stuff trying to solve this mystery!' WHERE `entry`=14370;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Phew! The stench! Well, hopefully that massive heap of carcasses smells more appetizing to a giant.' WHERE `entry`=14371;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Demons? Oh, there be lots I can tell yeh \'bout demons!' WHERE `entry`=14372;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, lad! Don\'t hesitate to knock a few more down for good measure!' WHERE `entry`=14373;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Here it is - the Hand of Iruxos.$B$BGot it from one o\' them Burning Blade leaders myself.$B$BPowerful thing! See, yeh use it on demon portals and they just disappear! Spooky magic, but these be desperate times....$B$BThe demons keep comin\' at this rate, and my camp will get overrun before ya know it.$B$BHere ya go, now. Get on with it.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aye, that\'ll buy us some time, $C. Thank yeh.' WHERE `entry`=14374;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You should be proud of how you manipulated the enemy\'s power and used it against them. You\'ve dealt the demons of Mannoroc a severe blow....' WHERE `entry`=14376;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Speak slower - what are you saying? Am I hearing you right? Those formations of azsharite are actually where the giants have - oh my. Groady!! Let\'s not tell Dr. Grapplehammer, he\'s made this stuff his life\'s work.$B$BWell, at least now we know where azsharite comes from, and why it\'s so rare. We\'ve got to figure out a way to speed up, uh, "production!"' WHERE `entry`=14377;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Justice is done! Now let\'s have a peek at what\'s left of my goods....' WHERE `entry`=14378;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ohhh, these will do nicely! Thargad will be so surprised!' WHERE `entry`=14379;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Take the Mysterious Concoction to Karnum at Karnum\'s Glade.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Yes, $C. Not only do I know what this is, I know just how you should use it....' WHERE `entry`=14380;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your deeds continue to impress me, $N. Please accept this gift on behalf of the Cenarion Circle.' WHERE `entry`=14381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Sea Giants Defeated',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Slitherblade Invaders Defeated' WHERE `entry`=14381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. You might be a bloody beast, but you\'re our beast.' WHERE `entry`=14382;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh - marvelous. Tell me more. And that precocious young Gadgetspring? Dead as well? Ah, wonderful. My work here is important but at times I do miss the carnage of demolishing my enemies on a more personal level. Here, perhaps you can make use of some of my discarded equipment.' WHERE `entry`=14383;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Nijel\'s Point, $R. Now, let\'s see about getting you briefed on our situation here.' WHERE `entry`=14384;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So it was a no-go? Literally? Well, Grapplehammer won\'t take no for an answer. We\'ll have to try something else.$B$BMaybe I\'ll have my interns smuggle this laxative into the night elf encampment. That\'ll be good for a laugh, at least.' WHERE `entry`=14385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it, $N. That should take the wind out of their sails.' WHERE `entry`=14386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A pleasure to meet you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=14387;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So scaring him didn\'t work, either? Double-nertz! I\'ll have to break the news to Grapplehammer: Azsharite\'s going to remain the rarest substance on the planet. We\'ll have to use it sparingly.' WHERE `entry`=14388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Azuregos! At last you\'ve found him!' WHERE `entry`=14389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Azuregos has agreed to rendezvous with Kalecgos. Success!' WHERE `entry`=14390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great to see you again! Thank you for finding Azuregos and sending him to me. I do feel I owe you an apology - I may have undersold how difficult it would be to accomplish the task I gave you. You performed quite admirably, $N.' WHERE `entry`=14391;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey there... again. Look, I gave you my hat. It was a gift. I thought you\'d make some use of it. More specifically though, I thought you\'d get it the heck away from me. Can you imagine my surprise when Xylem comes by himself to give it back to me? "Want to be more like my other apprentices, Sorata? Give your hat another try."  Not one of my proudest moments. So what... you just tossed it aside for him to find? No. I don\'t think so. You\'re going to take this hat and you\'re going to like it. Really.' WHERE `entry`=14392;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N! Let us finish this!' WHERE `entry`=14393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Defeat Agogridon',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Agogridon is no more. The demons shall never again take hold in our lands!' WHERE `entry`=14394;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did what you could, $N. With any luck a few others will find their way to shore.' WHERE `entry`=14395;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The ocean, $N. It swallowed everything... the land... the Forsaken... our men!' WHERE `entry`=14396;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Liam is right. We must get everyone to higher ground. You must help me spread the word while I manage the logistics of the evacuation.' WHERE `entry`=14397;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A visitor!  Are you staying for tea, sweetheart?' WHERE `entry`=14398;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why thank you, $N. I hope you didn\'t peek! Where are your manners, dear?' WHERE `entry`=14399;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re a peach, $N. Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=14400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There he is!  Grandma\'s special boy! Thank you so much for finding him. I hope it wasn\'t too much trouble. My... what manner of dirt found its way underneath my fingernails!' WHERE `entry`=14401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did the impossible, $N. You convinced Grandma Wahl to leave her home. You are something else, let me tell you.' WHERE `entry`=14402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You here to give us a hand?' WHERE `entry`=14403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is great, $N. I should be able to finish the repairs in no time.' WHERE `entry`=14404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s just as well, $N. Maybe the Haywards will fare better than us.' WHERE `entry`=14405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Stay back! Don\'t make me... Is it you?  By the Light!  It\'s you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=14406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for coming. I apologize for the discretion, but it\'s extremely important that I not be seen by certain individuals. I\'m in quite a bind and I\'ve taken notice of some of your recent deeds. Hear me out, help me, and I\'ll see to it that you\'re rewarded in kind.' WHERE `entry`=14407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='My benefactors used their diminutive intellect to construct an interplanetary transport. As designed, this so-called "Rocket" is a death trap. But I suspect a simple re-engineering of the fuel catalyst semifold would render a stable mixture, providing a breathable oxygen byproduct. To implement such changes, I require the original engineering plans.$B$BLocate the Laboratory Archives and ring the doorbell to gain entry. The plans will be held by the lab director himself, presuming he still lives.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' These are like the scrawling of children. Common sense precludes the routing of control hydraulics so near to the secondary stage burners! Still, this is salvageable. Do you know how to refactor fuel matrixes for pressure variations at a fixed acceleration? No? Very well, perhaps you can do something else for me while I reconfigure the rocket...' WHERE `entry`=14408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, the writings of Daros. He always was meticulous about tracking progress. His words may aid in explaining how far we\'ve come.$B$BYou have my thanks for bringing this to me, $R. Perhaps we will see more of each other once it is understood we mean no harm.' WHERE `entry`=14409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Feralas, $C. I thank you for coming to assist us.' WHERE `entry`=14410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent!  I\'m almost done here.' WHERE `entry`=14412;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Here so soon! Lovely trip I hope. Not too nauseous or anything? There will be much running and much jumping, so a settled stomach is of great practicality.' WHERE `entry`=14413;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve got the horses, I\'ll make sure Duskhaven gets them.' WHERE `entry`=14416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Syndicate? I would never have suspected. It seems the lords of Alterac have fallen far in the years since their betrayal.$B$BHawkins will be pleased to learn of this, and as you were so instrumental in this discovery, it would be fitting if you were the one to deliver it to him.$B$BAh, and how could I forget?$B$BWelcome to the Deathstalkers.',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver Andron\'s Ledger to Aleric Hawkins in the Hall of the Dark Lady in the Undercity.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm, this is interesting. The Deathstalkers have performed their duties admirably in ferreting this out.$B$BAs I\'m told, you deserve a reward for your part in these matters. Keep this up, $N; the Deathstalkers always have use of a good man.' WHERE `entry`=14418;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The letter of introduction should be enough to convince Andron that you are the messenger he\'s been waiting for. I\'ve met Andron before, he doesn\'t quite have the mental capacity to be that suspicious.$B$BOur leader suspects that Andron has been providing aid to some other group. He wishes to know what organization this is and requires proof of it.$B$BI want you to speak with Andron, and obtain this information. You\'ll find him at his shop near the Apothecarium.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Andron Gant in the Undercity.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, yes, I\'ve been expecting you. I have no doubt our mutual acquaintances are pleased with the information that I have provided so far?$B$BI suppose there\'s no point in asking you, I doubt they would burden you with this knowledge. Why place so much trust in the messenger, hm?' WHERE `entry`=14419;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='If you wish to join the Deathstalkers, the Dark Lady\'s elite guard, you will have to prove your worth.$B$BI will not lie to you, $N, this task could mean your death.$B$BI have some things that need attending to. I require the personal effects of Astor Hadren, a messenger who travels between Silverpine and the Undercity. I will leave the method of procurement to your discretion.$B$BIt will be better for you if you know less of the nature of this business. Succeed and I shall tell you more.',`objectives_loc1`='Get Astor\'s Letter of Introduction and return it to Mennet Carkad in the Rogues\' Quarter.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. You\'ve passed the first part of this test. Hopefully Andron will not have caught wind of your activities, and we will be able to convince him that you are, in fact, the messenger he is expecting.' WHERE `entry`=14420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You\'ll find the ledger with the information your employers seek on the bookshelf behind me. Deliver it with my regards, and tell them that I would prefer it if they sent you, if they find enough value that they should wish to continue our arrangement.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring Andron\'s Ledger to Mennet Carkad in the Rogues\' Quarter of Undercity.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, this is certainly more information than I suspected to get out of Andron. Give me a moment to peruse it, before I set you to your next task.' WHERE `entry`=14421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful! Exemplary work, $N! As you have no doubt surmised, my objective with regard to this rocket is to utilize it as a sort of astral cradle, an ark if you will, allowing my newly-forged race to slip the surly bonds of this ravaged planet and colonize a world to our own liking. You have been instrumental to our cause. Please accept this currency as I will be minting my own monetary units upon arrival. Farewell, $N!' WHERE `entry`=14422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What? ...What? Margene! Oh my sweet Margene!!' WHERE `entry`=14423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What is Clubnik talking about? Haunted construction equipment? Does it look like I have time for ghost stories? I\'ve got a laboratory in the middle of a meltdown, fires burning, animals mutated, and worst of all - projects falling behind schedule. Help!' WHERE `entry`=14424;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Amberwind was making use of an Arcane Construct? Hah! How delightfully inexperienced. It\'s like watching children play with firearms. Let\'s take a look at that journal, $N. Hold it up to the scrying stone... keep it still ...' WHERE `entry`=14428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work getting those runestones. To be honest, I only needed one, but the thought of so many night elves slain for such useless baubles fills me with a dark, giddy joy. Please hold one of those runes up to the scrying stone to let me see. Hmmm. As I suspected, an amateur effort at best.' WHERE `entry`=14429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Haha! Hah - HA! Night elf "mages" fleeing their own arcane creation. Your actions have made my month, $N. That\'s why we blood elves don\'t use arcane constructs anymore - they\'ve been outlawed for, oh, 1500 years. It\'s amusing to me to watch our foes repeat the mistakes of the past. "Mages." Indeed.' WHERE `entry`=14430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see... This definitely looks like a working draft of some sort of treaty. That\'s a worst-case scenario for us, $N: Night elves coordinating attacks with entrenched furbolg allies. My initial instinct - a full-out frontal assault - would only drive them into the arms of the Alliance. We will have to take a different approach...' WHERE `entry`=14431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah good, that\'s plenty. We\'ll boil this stuff up and you can bask in the fumes for a while - you\'ll be speaking like a furbolg in no time. Our plan is beginning to take shape...' WHERE `entry`=14432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work! Let me see those documents. Hmm. Now we know exactly when and where the final negotiations will happen. Don\'t worry if those robes don\'t fit you - I\'ve got it all worked out.' WHERE `entry`=14433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Victory! The Blackmaw won\'t know who to trust anymore. With that delicate bit of business complete, I can orchestrate a full-on assault against those beasts without worrying about them siding with the Alliance. You do good work, $N. Perhaps we should place you in the Horde diplomatic corps? Hah-har!' WHERE `entry`=14435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='For you to continue with the Rites of the Earthmother you must pass two more tests. It is time for you to broaden your experience, $N.$B$BTravel to Bloodhoof Village and seek out the Ahmo Thunderhorn. There you may continue your journey and earn the acceptance of the elders of Thunder Bluff.$B$BTake this totem to Ahmo. He will recognize my carvings and help you on your path.$B$BFollow the road out of Camp Narache and travel with haste. Do not stray or you will lose your way.',`objectives_loc1`='Take the Totem of Hawkwind to Ahmo Thunderhorn in Bloodhoof Village. Follow the road out of Camp Narache.' WHERE `entry`=14437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kill 10 Palemane Tanners, 8 Palemane Skinners, and 5 Palemane Poachers, then return to Ahmo Thunderhorn in Bloodhoof Village.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, it is good you\'ve taken my task seriously. Respect of the land and its creatures is important. Death and life are a circle... a necessity. One cannot exist without the other. Take time to ponder this and do well to never forget it.' WHERE `entry`=14438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You will now be revered within our great city. Any $R worthy of completing the Rites of the Earthmother earns that honor.$B$BFor your final quest, seek out our young leader, Baine Bloodhoof, who dwells atop the highest mesa in Thunder Bluff.' WHERE `entry`=14439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Baine Bloodhoof in Thunder Bluff wants you to bring him the Horn of Arra\'chea.' WHERE `entry`=14440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='They say that Garrosh Hellscream is one of the greatest heroes in the Horde! When I grow up, I want to be a hero of the Horde too!$B$BDo you know Garrosh, $N? Could you do me a favor, please? Could you get his autograph for me? I dunno how to ask him, and he probably wouldn\'t listen to someone like me... but you! You\'re an adventurer, like him! I bet he\'d give you his autograph easy!$B$BPlease?',`objectives_loc1`='Travel to Orgrimmar to see about getting Garrosh Hellscream\'s autograph for your ward.' WHERE `entry`=14441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you come to assist me with my work? My claws are quite dexterous, but I must reluctantly confess that my arms are debilitatingly short.' WHERE `entry`=14442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Caladis takes the hilt from you and slowly turns it over in his hands.>$B$BThis seems somehow familiar, as though I should know its origins. You say you recovered this in the citadel? Most intriguing.$B$BThere are few who possess the ability to make such a blade. Perhaps they can tell us something about your find.' WHERE `entry`=14443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We can\'t let that book remain in Sunreaver hands. If we hope to identify the sword and use it to our advantage, we have to find a way to capture the book Krasus lent them.' WHERE `entry`=14444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, oh wow! Is that who I think it is? You rescued Thrall, Warchief of the Horde?!!! Well, let\'s see about getting over to that larger island. I sure as heck don\'t want to swim the strait with all of those sharks down there.' WHERE `entry`=14445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='While we should never miss an opportunity to strike out against the Alliance, we mustn\'t forget about the Scourge.$B$BWe won\'t have the numbers here to make a proper assault in the glacier for weeks, but that won\'t keep us from learning all we can know about their defenses.$B$BI have asked our resident death knight to advise you in this effort. After all, who better knows this enemy than they?$B$BAllow me to introduce Koltira Deathweaver.' WHERE `entry`=14447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='While we should never miss an opportunity to strike out against the Alliance, we mustn\'t forget about the Scourge.$B$BWe won\'t have the numbers here to make a proper assault in the glacier for weeks, but that won\'t keep us from learning all we can know about their defenses.$B$BI have asked our resident death knight to advise you in this effort. After all, who better knows this enemy than they?$B$BAllow me to introduce Koltira Deathweaver.' WHERE `entry`=14448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to your first true test as a $R.' WHERE `entry`=14449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve fought well, $N. We may yet be saved.' WHERE `entry`=14452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the corruptors slain, the Earth Mother will mend her own wounds in due time. The roots are not meant to thrive here, and will wither. Balance will return.' WHERE `entry`=14455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. Respect your prey, and the danger it carries, but never fear it. In fear, you become prey yourself.' WHERE `entry`=14456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Arcanist Tybalin examines the captured orders.>$B$BThe agent you intercepted was supposed to transport the Wyrmrest Tome to Icecrown, after meeting with one Magister Hathorel in Sunreaver\'s Sanctuary. We have to get that book, $N, and this is our chance. It\'s not going to be easy, though.' WHERE `entry`=14457;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='More trials lay ahead, $N. I hope you\'re prepared.' WHERE `entry`=14458;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $N. Those beasts could have been a greater threat than the quilboar themselves, if we had not taken action now.' WHERE `entry`=14459;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' The Chief of the Bristleback is slain. Greatmother Hawkwind\'s spirit has been avenged!' WHERE `entry`=14460;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve not only wiped the boar pens clean, but put a stop to a horrible desecration. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=14461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re just in time, $C. I\'m about to launch a lightning-strike precision assassination. Let\'s see... Explosives? Check. Pneumatic grapplestabber? Check. Portable parachute? Check. Crippling nerve toxin? Check. Let\'s do this thing.' WHERE `entry`=14462;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. I think I speak for everyone when I say the sooner we get out of here, the better.' WHERE `entry`=14463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m impressed by the cleverness of our new goblin allies, but I\'m even more impressed by you, $N. Look at the gaze of terror frozen onto the Captain\'s face! He never saw your attack coming. Imagine the fear this will cause in Northwatch when they see what happened to one of their precious officers in night elf lands. Well done, $C. Our assault proceeds...' WHERE `entry`=14464;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N. I\'ve heard much about you. I understand you were crucial in my family\'s survival during the outbreak in Gilneas City.' WHERE `entry`=14465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you are, $N. I\'ve been expecting you. I got word of your recovery and... wait -- do you feel that?' WHERE `entry`=14466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Latest recruit, eh? I\'ll make this short and sweet. We\'re under contract to keep the naga in the ruins from reaching Gallywix or his property. You handle whatever we ask of you, and I\'ll see to it that you get paid when all of your rounds are complete. Welcome to the Bilgewater Battalion.' WHERE `entry`=14468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='First thing\'s first - we need more supplies for you and the other new recruits. There are some perfectly good standard issue packs on the bodies of our last round of recruits, in the minefield to the north.$B$BTaking their lessons to heart, I\'d recommend you avoid stepping on mines yourself.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re a light-footed bugger, aren\'t ya? Good work. Here are a few of the supplies to keep you lively.' WHERE `entry`=14469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kill Warlord Krellen and recover the SFG.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Quick work there, recruit. She\'s a beaut, isn\'t she? Assembled her myself. I\'ve got special plans for this baby.' WHERE `entry`=14470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Use a Goblin Mortar to slaughter 60 Spitelash Attackers',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Can you believe they PAY us to do this?' WHERE `entry`=14471;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='BAM! In the face! Nice shot, kid.' WHERE `entry`=14472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Looks like those monkeys will steal anything! Those thieving little monsters have driven the teraptor matriarch into a frenzy by stealing her eggs. Worse yet, the eggs have started to hatch! We\'ve got hungry teraptor hatchlings running around all over the place, looking to make a quick meal out of us!$B$BWe didn\'t start this, but it\'s our problem now. You\'ll have to head into the jungle and kill those hungry teraptor hatchlings before they kill us all.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s just hope we don\'t have to deal with their mommy later. That would be very bad.' WHERE `entry`=14473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, thank heavens that you survived, $N! I thought for sure that you\'d drowned when I saw you go over the side! Look at all of these folks you saved!' WHERE `entry`=14474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Reinforcements, at last!' WHERE `entry`=14475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sweet. Let\'s torch this banana stand!' WHERE `entry`=14476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, let them burn! Let them burn through the night, so that their flaming tower will light the battlefield beneath us as we rain terror upon their heads. Thank you, $N. Stay close: the invasion is about to begin...' WHERE `entry`=14477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome back to duty soldier. Good to have you back.' WHERE `entry`=14478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Bumpy ride?' WHERE `entry`=14479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your name\'s getting around... nearly Gob Squad status some would say. You\'re a vicious one.' WHERE `entry`=14480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not exactly the battle you had anticipated, I\'ll wager. But a battle nonetheless, as you shall soon see....' WHERE `entry`=14482;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'ve you got there? Oh hey, this is big. Real big. Most of the crazy details in one little package. Thanks - you really helped us reel this all in. Good working with ya.' WHERE `entry`=14483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glad you\'re on our side, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=14484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The hope is that that cuts off a major source of their magic. The truth is, we don\'t really have a clue. Who can pass up an opportunity to blow some stuff up though.' WHERE `entry`=14485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. Here\'s your cut. Good doing business with you.' WHERE `entry`=14486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hahah! It\'s HUGE! We\'ll have you take it back to Uncle Bedlam as soon as everything\'s cleaned up here and you\'re ready to go.' WHERE `entry`=14487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What we do here is none of your business...' WHERE `entry`=14488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The land is clearly still in great upheaval if it took such effort to calm. Remember this, $N. Do not forget seeing the fate of those who would scar the Earth Mother.' WHERE `entry`=14491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew Shandy would find a way to come through for us. Let me get this enchanted and ready for you to use. The sooner you get done with the tabard, the sooner we can get it back to Shandy and the better the chances that its owner will never have missed it.' WHERE `entry`=20438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work. Now that this is in our hands, we must get it to Caladis Brightspear as soon as possible. We can\'t risk the book falling back into Sunreaver hands.$B$BI\'ll ensure that Shandy Glossgleam gets his tabard back without incident, along with a healthy reward for his help.' WHERE `entry`=20439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $N. I will take these and bind their power into a totem of cleansing.' WHERE `entry`=20440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Be not afraid, $N. You have successfully passed the Rite of Vision.' WHERE `entry`=20441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If you are prepared to leave Camp Narache behind, I will help call the spirits to guide you onwards.' WHERE `entry`=23733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Drink the Water of Vision.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Bloodhoof Village, hero. I am glad the spirits have guided you safely here.' WHERE `entry`=24215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`objectives_loc1`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE `entry`=24216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`objectives_loc1`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE `entry`=24217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE `entry`=24218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE `entry`=24219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent news, $C! If our tactical deployments continue to be this successful, the Horde will be in full retreat before long.' WHERE `entry`=24220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=24221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Call to Arms: Eye of the Storm DEPRECATED' WHERE `entry`=24222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Win an Arathi Basin battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent news, $C! If our tactical deployments continue to be this successful, the Horde will be in full retreat before long.' WHERE `entry`=24223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE `entry`=24224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`objectives_loc1`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE `entry`=24225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=24226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Win an Eye of the Storm battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.' WHERE `entry`=24227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is no greater honor than driving invaders from Horde territories. We salute your great courage in aiding our forces today!' WHERE `entry`=24426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Win an Alterac Valley battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`objectives_loc1`='Win an Alterac Valley battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just what I wanted to hear!  A victory in Alterac Valley - even a temporary one - is crucial to our overall strategy against the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=24427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What? How did you get this? Isn\'t she... Never mind the details, I suppose. You\'ll be wanting one of these baubles as recompense, no doubt.' WHERE `entry`=24428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You have accomplished the truly impossible. The brood mother of the Black Dragonflight lies dead at your feet. Seize her head and deliver it to Neeru Fireblade.',`objectives_loc1`='Take the Head of Onyxia to Neeru Fireblade in the Cleft of Shadow.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve brought me the head of someone who is... No, best not to think about it too hard. You\'ll be wanting recompense for your heroic deeds, no doubt.' WHERE `entry`=24429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh yeah! I love the smell of freshly-cratered dirt! Word around camp is that the elven front line is collapsing back toward the river. Talk to Chawg and see if there\'s anything you can do to help seal the deal.' WHERE `entry`=24430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is quite a find, $N. I can\'t have you selling this to anyone else, so I\'m willing to offer generously.' WHERE `entry`=24431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Here you are, $C. With this you should find maneuvering in the sea to be nearly effortless. $B$BNow we must get to work. There is much to be done in little time.' WHERE `entry`=24432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lok\'tar ogar, $N! As they discover the bodies of their comrades they will learn that no place is safe from the fury of the horde, and their will to fight will crumble.' WHERE `entry`=24433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Images of a great and distant tree flood your mind. Your stomach lurches as you reorient the stone, briefly filling your senses with visions of a fiery portal, a towering mountain, a frigid wasteland, and a terrible scar across the earth. After a moment, the magical energies of the stone calm, and you feel you are but a step away from Valormok. Andorel\'s invasion can begin...' WHERE `entry`=24434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='There are a lot of Naga left on this beach. Looks like you have some wet work ahead of you, $G son:girl;.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good clean fun.' WHERE `entry`=24435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fine job there, bud. We\'ll have this beach cleaned up in no time.' WHERE `entry`=24436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah hah! Brilliant. Right fine job there, boy.' WHERE `entry`=24437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for stopping, $N. Our carriage got hit pretty bad. The one in front of us got it worse.' WHERE `entry`=24438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='...Then it is done! There are still pockets of resistance around our camp, but this rearguard action appears to be masking a full-fledged retreat to Ashenvale. Azshara is ours! The Warchief will hear of this victory and your part in it. But we will surely need the help of a $C like you elsewhere. Be sure to speak with Kroum here in camp before you leave.' WHERE `entry`=24439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Grimtotem... I\'d hoped to see the end of my days before $R attacked other $R senselessly on the very plains of Mulgore. But be proud, $N. You have done a great thing for the land, and for our people.' WHERE `entry`=24440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. The purity with which these beasts hunt is vital in the creation of the next cleansing totem. The Thunderhorn Well is a symbol of my own tribe, and to know it is being desecrated by our own kind raises a fury in me I haven\'t felt for years.' WHERE `entry`=24441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Mariel accepts the orders and the captured seeing crystal and examines both.>$B$BGood work, $N, and quick thinking. I\'m sure the theft of this trinket won\'t slow them down for long, but I think you\'ve bought us time to warn the leaders of the Horde and Alliance about the impending attacks.' WHERE `entry`=24442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! You made it in one piece, good. We\'ve got a lot of work for you to handle for us inside the ruins, but we\'re sending you in with the best to take care of it. You\'re working with GAMA Force now, Goblin Army: Mergers and Acquisitions. Molotov says you can handle it - that\'s all I need to hear.' WHERE `entry`=24448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And you come with the artifact! The operation was a success then. Mergers and Acquisitions can definitely handle themselves. This thing will fetch quite a pretty penny. And you - I heard you did some impressive work down there. You may well have cut-down expenses by 10% single-handedly. That\'s the kind of smarty businessman I want in my army! Here are your wages, as promised. And a little something extra too - I hope you like it.' WHERE `entry`=24449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work. Now that this is in our hands, we must get it to Myralion Sunblaze as soon as possible. We can\'t risk the Silver Covenant taking the book from us again.$B$BI\'ll get that tabard back to Shandy and see that he\'s well compensated for his assistance. Once the book is in Myralion\'s hands, the Silver Covenant won\'t be a threat anymore.' WHERE `entry`=24451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hahah! Sweet deal. I\'ll get the ball rolling on this. All I need now is to find a buyer and get the go-ahead from Uncle Bedlam. Here are your wages for your work here. Excellent work, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=24452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What?! I got left out of the action completely? Are you serious? Alright, alright... no shooting the messenger. Thanks for the news, bud. Maybe I\'ll see you back at town.' WHERE `entry`=24453;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Caladis accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BI knew the symbols on the blade were familiar. The weapon was most certainly forged by the dragons and gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE `entry`=24454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice to meet you soldier. Commander Molotov speaks highly of you.' WHERE `entry`=24455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done great honor for both me and my ancestors today. Please, take this with my gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=24456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I sensed you would be coming to me, $C. I can always recognize one who is trying to pass the Rites of the Earthmother.' WHERE `entry`=24457;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh! This is it! It\'s the big one! We\'re in business boys!' WHERE `entry`=24458;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well met. If Ahmo has already explained the minor quibbles of what kind of goblin we\'ll be driving from our lands, let\'s get to work.' WHERE `entry`=24459;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Hey there $C, I need you to solve the Cataclysm. Go hunt me some zombies.' WHERE `entry`=24460;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar, although Blood-Queen Lana\'thel proclaimed we could not! The blade must still be tempered, but she and her master will not stand in our way!' WHERE `entry`=24461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You say Talrendis Point has fallen? That\'s good news! It also explains the exodus of elves I\'ve seen along this road.' WHERE `entry`=24463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I am but an apprentice myself, $N, but I can still impart a lesson to you in thanks.$B$BAllow me to teach you how to harness your inner fury into a mighty battle shout.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Brave Sharphorn and learn Battle Shout.' WHERE `entry`=24466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You truly amaze me, mortal. It\'s rare to meet someone so dedicated and resourceful. Azuregos and I are likely to depart Azshara and remain discrete for a while. I do hope that we meet again someday though. Perhaps to put an end to Deathwing himself. Farewell, $N. Stay safe.' WHERE `entry`=24467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it again, $N. You have my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=24468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Impressive work, laddie. We can hold the perimeter from here on out. Here, take this for yer troubles. It might come in handy, as I\'ve got something more important to ask of ye...' WHERE `entry`=24469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... they blame us for destroying their home, ye say?  Well, that wasn\'t us, that was the horrible earthquake we had earlier today. Are they that dense that they can\'t see we nearly lost our camp too? Can\'t blame a trogg for fightin\' for his home, though.' WHERE `entry`=24470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Many of those that y\'saved have already made it back to camp. The wounds\'re well-dressed!  Ye might have a future in first aid, if ye\'re into that sorta thing.' WHERE `entry`=24471;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You definitely got the ettin angry, $N. I heard him myself. Let\'s hope this works.' WHERE `entry`=24472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Achh.. and what do YOU want?  Can\'t ye see I\'m busy in here!  Go an\' bother someone else, I haven\'t the time. Wait, what\'s that ye say?  Joren sent you to help?  Well why didn\'t ye say so?' WHERE `entry`=24473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Ahh... that hits the spot. Now we can get some work done around here.' WHERE `entry`=24474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This\'ll have to do for now. We\'ve a lot of people to feed here, but we\'ve got to make do with what we\'ve got. With any luck, King Bronzebeard in Ironforge will send us some help shortly.' WHERE `entry`=24475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I... I don\'t understand. Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade to its original condition. What has happened here?' WHERE `entry`=24476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful!  Look at this one... it must be over 200 years old! Now, onto other matters...' WHERE `entry`=24477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant. You certainly don\'t let cold feet stop you. Or cold any part for that matter! No? ...too soon?' WHERE `entry`=24478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I like the way you move, apprentice. Don\'t you worry about where I got all the souls from. They were obtained in a perfectly humane manner, I assure you.' WHERE `entry`=24479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I had not thought it possible for evil to take hold in such a sword, but I suppose it was naive of me. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BUther\'s advice is wise, $N, and I would urge you to heed it quickly.' WHERE `entry`=24480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I am but an apprentice myself, $N, but I can still impart a lesson to you in thanks.$B$BAllow me to teach you how to channel the fortitude of An\'she, and imbue yourself with great stamina.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Seer Skyhoof and learn Power Word: Fortitude.' WHERE `entry`=24482;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see you made it, $N. It looks like most everybody did. We\'re not doing too bad so far for an emergency evacuation.' WHERE `entry`=24483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. The spiders are everywhere, however, and I\'m afraid we\'ve barely put a dent in their numbers.' WHERE `entry`=24484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Seal of Righteousness',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Bowe Dawnhorn and learn Seal of Righteousness.' WHERE `entry`=24485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well would you look at this!  An axe blade, a couple of arrowheads, and what appears to be some sort of rudimentary spoon. This is indeed fascinating. Thanks again for your help, $N. I\'ve much studying to keep myself occupied while Joren\'s got us under lockdown.' WHERE `entry`=24486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $C. Are you ready to get to work?' WHERE `entry`=24487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s my boy! Now to get one of these useless hunks of metal in working order and you into the game!' WHERE `entry`=24488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... interesting. From what you\'re saying, it sounds like a fire elemental might have snuck in from Searing Gorge. Or, the earthquake opened up a crack to the elemental plane... Either way, this is bad news. You should probably report this information to Grelin.' WHERE `entry`=24489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='To Ironforge?  Well first, you\'ll need to go through Kharanos, and before that, you\'ll have to go through this tunnel.' WHERE `entry`=24490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Milo Geartwinge, reporting for duty. You sent up a distress signal?' WHERE `entry`=24491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Took you long enough. Hold on tight, and take a good hard look!  Chances are you won\'t be coming back here for quite some time.' WHERE `entry`=24492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Coldridge Valley?  I\'ve got my own problems here!  What, they can\'t deal with a couple of troggs?  And trolls?  And incursions from the elemental plane? Actually, on second thought, that\'s kind of a lot. I\'m surprised they\'re doing as well as they are. I\'ll see what I can do.' WHERE `entry`=24493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are dark days, friend. Look around you... even here in remote Coldridge, the sprits are rebelling. The land is crying out for help. Yet still, even in times such as these, the spirits will always turn an ear to those who ask for their assistance.' WHERE `entry`=24494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. It will take some time, but I\'ll try to make sense of what we have.' WHERE `entry`=24495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$N, this rune was given to me to pass on to ye. Take some time to read it when ye have a chance. I\'m thinkin\' it came from the mage trainer Teegli. Take a gander at it and go find her inside Anvilmar.',`objectives_loc1`='Read the Arcane Rune and speak to Teegli Merrowith in Coldridge Valley.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The power of the arcane is everywhere, $N. Only some of us have the ability to see it, and fewer still possess the ability to master it. You are one of those few.' WHERE `entry`=24496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s past time that these night elf scum be purged from Azshara. Glad to have an able body like you to sink the point home. Ready to get to work?' WHERE `entry`=24497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='They\'ve put our captured soldiers to work in the quarry! Kill their captors and set them free, hero, and do it quickly. We will need their aid when we confront Scourgelord Tyrannus.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE `entry`=24498;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I cannot thank you enough for coming. We\'re severely undermanned to be risking a venture into the citadel, but opportunities like this are too rare to pass up.$B$BI\'m awaiting the arrival of champions from the coliseum, but if your reputation holds true, you should be more than equipped to fight through the forge yourself. Clear the way to the far side and secure the passage to the Pit of Saron. We will need to hold it to move our men further into the citadel.$B$BPlease hurry, $N. We\'re counting on you.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just in time! Thank you, $N.$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... or maybe, just maybe, his redemption.' WHERE `entry`=24499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Uther knew a great deal about how Arthas might be defeated. It\'s hard to believe that there is much hope of defeating Arthas upon the steps of his own throne. And who will take up the crown of Lich King if it comes to that?$B$BMany questions remain, but the answers that you\'ve uncovered may be critical to ensuring Arthas\' defeat. You need to find Jaina and escape the Lich King while there\'s still time.',`objectives_loc1`='Find Lady Jaina Proudmoore and escape the Halls of Reflection',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Jaina is still catching her breath.>$B$BI can barely believe we\'re still alive. It was foolish of me to follow him. I\'ve made that mistake too many times. And you... it was reckless of you to come after me instead of escaping with the information! But... well... thank you. You truly are a hero.$B$BWith Uther\'s guidance, we may stand a chance at defeating Arthas. All the lives lost today were not in vain.' WHERE `entry`=24500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great job, $N. We\'ve heard rumors of survivors further in the mountains. Now we\'ll be able to send scouts there.' WHERE `entry`=24501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Uh... you did it, kid. You REALLY did it! We won the game and.... DID YOU SEE THAT DRAGON?!!!' WHERE `entry`=24503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Patrolling the high road is grave business, but it must be done. These narrow mountain trails are, for the time being, one of our only lifelines into Stonetalon. They must be preserved.$B$BThank you.' WHERE `entry`=24504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So the Alliance is probing the twists and turns of the high road?$B$BEven if they were to map it out, they couldn\'t attack these hills in numbers. This is our land, $N. And they will pay dearly for presuming otherwise.' WHERE `entry`=24505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. $N, I know of you. You\'ll be perfect for these tasks.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE `entry`=24506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='They\'ve put our captured soldiers to work in the quarry. Kill their captors and set them free, $C, and do it quickly. We will need their aid when we confront Scourgelord Tyrannus.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE `entry`=24507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! I\'m so glad you\'ve come.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE `entry`=24510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m glad we have someone capable to aid us in this. Delving into the citadel with so few is risky at best, but opportunities like this are too rare to pass up.$B$BI\'m awaiting the arrival of champions from the coliseum, but if your reputation holds true, you should be more than equipped to fight through the forge yourself. Clear the way to the far side and secure the passage to the Pit of Saron. We will need to hold it to move our men further into the Citadel.$B$BBe quick about it, $N. Time is short.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well timed, $C!$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... and a route to vengeance long overdue.' WHERE `entry`=24511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='From up here I got the perfect view of the havoc you just caused, $N. Our lost brothers reclaimed some of their dignity, and the Alliance dogs were sent scrambling. Sharp work, my friend!$B$BIf the Alliance sleeps comfortably at night, we are not doing our job.$B$BWe will never let up.$B$BWe will never give in.' WHERE `entry`=24512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have them? I\'ll take your word for it. Hearing Peake scream like one of his victims is reward enough for me.$B$BNow leave me be, $N. I do not wish to be a burden to my clan.' WHERE `entry`=24513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Onatay looks over the fresh hides, nodding her head slowly.>$B$BYes $N, I can work with these. You work fast!$B$BThese hides will help us hold out for reinforcements longer. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=24514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So my sister recognized the old signals? Her hunter\'s eyes are as sharp as ever.$B$B$N, when we first set up this camp we were at the edge of this jungle. Now look at it!$B$BSomething is amiss.' WHERE `entry`=24515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent, $N. It will be some time before we can assault the hold proper, but until then, we must teach them to fear the Barrens.' WHERE `entry`=24517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Kilrok pages through the plans you discovered.>$B$BThis explains much, $N. No wonder our foes are so hellbent on taking the southern Barrens. It\'s at the center of their plans for the continent!$B$BBut they didn\'t account for us, did they $C?' WHERE `entry`=24518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. We\'ve got to keep Honor\'s Stand isolated.$B$BAlone ... afraid ... $N, if we keep up the pressure, maybe someday they\'ll simply surrender the pass.' WHERE `entry`=24519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re kidding, right?! DEATHWING?!!! Okay, this\'ll work out just fine. We\'ll throw your party and by the time it\'s over, I\'m sure that the dragon will be long gone and the ground will stop shaking. If not, we can always charter a ship off of the island.' WHERE `entry`=24520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$N, Coach Crosscheck, the leader of our fearless Bilgewater Buccaneers, is looking for you.$B$BHe says that the division title against the Steamwheedle Sharks is on the line and that you\'re the only one that can bring it home for us!$B$BHead west into town. You can\'t miss Kajaro Field!' WHERE `entry`=24521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Admit you to the Sunwell? That\'s impossible! The Sunwell is the most sacred and important site of our people. We have only recently reclaimed it with the help of the Shattered Sun Offensive. It is not a place for tourists or travelers.' WHERE `entry`=24522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good, $N. I can feel the sacrifice of the land in this offering, and my spirit swells with sadness, and pride.' WHERE `entry`=24523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it. You have cleaned the wells, and healed our land. Bloodhoof village is grateful, $N.$B$BMay the wind whisper your deeds for a hundred seasons, and may the waters of Mulgore remain clean forever.' WHERE `entry`=24524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So it is done.$B$BNormally these scavengers are part of the Earthmother\'s cycle of life. But on the heels of the devastation wracked by both the Alliance and the cataclysm, their numbers grow overwhelming. It is good to thin them out.' WHERE `entry`=24525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Excellent!  Let us begin.$B$BThe first skill you will learn is that of the Primal Strike. The primal spirits, when called upon, will strengthen your arm to deliver a mighty blow.$B$BHelpful, isn\'t it?',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Primal Strike from Teo Hammerstorm, then use Primal Strike 2 times on a Training Dummy near the entrance of Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This has been but one of many footfalls on the long path of the $C. Come back to me after you\'ve had some experience in the field, and I will help guide you on your next step.' WHERE `entry`=24527;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Are ya ready to start?  Wonderful!  We\'re glad to have ya.$B$BBefore ya go back outside, I\'m gonna need ya to learn the Seal of Righteousness. It will grant Holy damage to your swings, helping ya dispatch yer enemies quicker.$B$BThe other thing yer gonna want to know is that any time ya have a seal active, ya can use the light to judge yer enemies. Yer judgement will deal damage each time ye invoke it.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Seal of Righteousness and Judgment from Bromos Grummner. After casting Seal of Righteousness on yourself, use Judgment on one of the Training Dummies at the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There, ya did it. The Light favors quick learners like you. Come back to me after you\'ve spent some time using what I\'ve taught ya, and I\'ll show ya something new.' WHERE `entry`=24528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s bad enough to have one\'s village sacked... but to spend the following night in a quilboar cage? I\'m glad you were there to help, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The life of a hunter is steeped in tradition, ye know. Trackin\' mighty beasts through rugged terrain. Drinkin\'. Travelin\' the land, yer gun at yer side. Drinkin\'. Survivin\' on wits and courage and cunning, followed by a good stiff drink.$B$BBut before we get to the good stuff, though, ye\'ll need to learn how to do the beginner stuff.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Steady Shot from Thorgas Grimson, then use Steady Shot 5 times on the Training Dummies outside the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that ye\'ve got a new $C trick under yer belt, and now that I\'ve got some of yer money, go out there an\' track some beasts!  Come back sometime in the future, an\' we\'ll talk again.' WHERE `entry`=24530;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Lesson one. Aside from your sword and shield, what\'s the most important tool you have in your arsenal?$B$B<Thran awaits your response.>$B$BOh never mind, I\'ll answer it for you. It\'s your mobility. One of the strengths of the warrior is the ability to get around the battlefield quickly. Here, $N, I\'ll train you to use your legs to your advantage.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Charge from Thran Khorman, then use Charge on one of the Training Dummies outside the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now we\'re getting somewhere. You\'ve got quite a manly bellow, sir! Come back to me in a bit, and I\'ll teach you something else.' WHERE `entry`=24531;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now, if ya DO want to become somethin\' special, ye\'ll need to talk to me. A priest is nothin\' without his spells. And I know a couple of spells that I might be able to teach ya.$B$BThe first is a quick heal that can fix ya up when you\'ve taken damage. Tell me, $G boy; lass:, do ya ever take damage?',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Flash Heal from Branstock Khalder, then cast Flash Heal 5 times on Wounded Militia members in Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. You\'ll make a fine $C in due time. Return to me after you\'ve proven yourself a bit more, and I\'ll reward you by teaching you another spell or two.' WHERE `entry`=24533;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What? He attacked you with a dozen boars? I guess quilboar have their own ideas of what "single combat" means.$B$BStill, the Bristleback will be left reeling after the blow you delivered. It will not be long before a new champion rises amongst them to stir up trouble... but at least this buys us some time to get these refugees relocated safely.$B$BThank you, $N. The survivors owe you a great debt.' WHERE `entry`=24534;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I confess that I did not expect Thalorien\'s spirit to recognize you as the heir to Quel\'Delar, but I defer to his judgment. You may enter the Sunwell, but I remind you that you are a guest in the most our most sacred of precincts, and you should act accordingly.' WHERE `entry`=24535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Get a load of these guys, would ya? Steamwheedle\'s been handling the business of holidays for years, and all of a sudden, these guys bust into the market. They\'re not Steamwheedle; the cartel hired me to get to the bottom of this. Something stinks here and it ain\'t just perfume.$B$BTake this device I brought and go analyze the perfume clouds around the guards. I want to know what they\'re putting in that stuff. Things ain\'t natural.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, thanks, kid. Give it over, let\'s take a look. Oh, that ain\'t good.' WHERE `entry`=24536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. But now on to the larger question:$B$BWhere is this overgrowth coming from? And why is it raging out of control?' WHERE `entry`=24539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome back, $N. What was done was not for revenge, or pride. It was simply to protect Thunder Bluff, and all our people, from torment and fear. Today, Mulgore is safe once more. The Earth Mother thanks you for all your brave deeds, $N, as do I. You have earned your reward, hero. May you be welcome in Thunder Bluff always.' WHERE `entry`=24540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I knew they were up to no good! There\'s some sort of mind-affecting chemical in here, but I can\'t get a handle on it with such a small sample. I need the real stuff.$B$BDon\'t just go over there and buy it! I don\'t want you giving these scumbags one copper. Nah, you gotta get it from the source, discreet-like.$B$BI\'ll disguise you as a package runner. I saw a stockpile guarded by their goons outside the gates. Go run by, and DON\'T stop, or they\'ll make you! They\'ll toss you a crate. Bring it back here.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got it, huh? Good job, kid. Top notch. Let\'s see what we got here.' WHERE `entry`=24541;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, samples from different parts of the overgrowth? These will be immensely helpful, yes. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=24542;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Kirge listens intently and then falls to one knee.>$B$BAlive! My boy still lives! Praise to the earthmother, I still have a son.$B$B<Kirge composes himself.>$B$B$C, my boy\'s mother didn\'t make it out of Taurajo alive. I will avenge her death, even if it means my son grows up without either of his parents.' WHERE `entry`=24543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A deep sense of dread washes over you as the flame devours the items.' WHERE `entry`=24545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you held your ground! With tenacity like yours we may yet drive the Alliance from our lands.' WHERE `entry`=24546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Shadow\'s Edge is among the greatest weapons a $C could hope to obtain.$B$BIs your lust for power sated, $R?$B$B<You feel Mograine\'s penetrating gaze.>$B$BI thought not. A final warning then...$B$BYou now embark on the most treacherous leg of your quest. Bridle your aspirations, for if your aims are impure then your life, your very soul, is forfeit.$B$BThe weapon you hold is but an empty husk, a mere shadow of what it may become. Only by devouring a thousand souls shall its true potential be unlocked.',`objectives_loc1`='Highlord Darion Mograine wants you to use Shadow\'s Edge to slay 1000 of the Lich King\'s minions in Icecrown Citadel. Souls can be obtained in 10 or 25 person difficulty.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You seem to have endured this leg of your trial admirably, $R. Pray that fate continues to smile upon you in your endeavor...' WHERE `entry`=24547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These should suffice, $C. Speak to me when Shadow\'s Edge has been thoroughly empowered and I will attempt its completion.' WHERE `entry`=24548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Congratulations, $C. Against insurmountable odds, you have weathered the storm. I trust that you shall find your reward proportionate to your conviction...' WHERE `entry`=24549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Thunder Bluff, $N. You\'ve done great things for our people. Tell me of your journey.' WHERE `entry`=24550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Bloodhilt looks at the badges, then allows them to spill from his hands onto the sands below. His lips curl open into a toothy grin.>$B$BNow THIS is what I like to see, $C! What is your name again?$B$BYou will go far here.' WHERE `entry`=24551;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah yes... I see a cunning in your eyes that was not present before. Well done, $C.' WHERE `entry`=24552;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE `entry`=24553;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Myralion takes the hilt from you and scrutinizes the artifact.>$B$BThis came from the citadel? What was it doing there? This blade is certainly not of Scourge manufacture.$B$BWeapons of this quality can only be crafted by a few of Azeroth\'s creatures. We will have to consult them and see if they can help us identify it.' WHERE `entry`=24554;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We must recover that book from the Silver Covenant. Without that book from Krasus, we stand little chance of solving the mystery of the sword in Icecrown or unlocking its power.' WHERE `entry`=24555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew Shandy would find a way to make it work. Let me get this enchanted and ready for you to use. With any luck, the tabard\'s owner won\'t even know it\'s missing and Shandy will cover the rest of our tracks.' WHERE `entry`=24556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Magister Hathorel reads the captured orders.>$B$BThe agent you intercepted was supposed to deliver the Wyrmrest tome to Icecrown, after meeting with one Arcanist Tybalin inside the Silver Enclave. We have to reclaim that book, $N, and we only have one chance before it leaves the city. We have to work quickly.' WHERE `entry`=24557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Myralion accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BThose symbols on the blade seemed familiar and now there\'s little wonder why. This is certainly a dragon blade, gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE `entry`=24558;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar in defiance of that Blood-Queen Lana\'thel\'s pronouncement! Now, the blade must be tempered before we can show her the folly of her words.' WHERE `entry`=24559;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade. Why hasn\'t it worked?' WHERE `entry`=24560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='How can evil take root in such a sword? I would not have thought it possible if the evidence wasn\'t here before my eyes. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BI believe Uther is right. You must heed his advice quickly, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope you understand that I can\'t just admit you to the Sunwell, $N. This is the most sacred place known to the sin\'dorei and we have only recently regained control over it.$B$BYou would raise the hopes of our people with tales of Quel\'Delar? Without proof of the truth of your claims, I see no reason to take you at your word.' WHERE `entry`=24562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You truly do carry Quel\'Delar. This is a great day for all of Quel\'Thalas and the sin\'dorei. You have my leave to enter the Sunwell and finish the sword\'s restoration. Keep your head high, $N. The children of Silvermoon have dreamt of this day for years.' WHERE `entry`=24563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. I\'m pleased to see you return intact; the viciousness I\'ve been seeing among these creatures is startling.' WHERE `entry`=24565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh dear. It seems the forces at work here are a bit difficult to control...$B$BPlease, don\'t bother Naralex with this. It will only upset him.' WHERE `entry`=24566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you are, my boy! Quick, there\'s no time to waste! We need to get one of these shredders back in working order. I\'m bringing you off the bench... you\'re going to win the game and the title for us!' WHERE `entry`=24567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good. Now, should they storm the gates, they will have to do so with infantry.$B$BDo you think they have the stomach for that?' WHERE `entry`=24569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These will do perfectly. Bright colors like these don\'t occur naturally in the barrens, but they haven\'t developed any other mutations so far.' WHERE `entry`=24570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m concerned by how...active these are. Nevertheless, it simply means we must continue to act quickly before the corruption here becomes worse.' WHERE `entry`=24571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. I\'ll have their bodies strung up along the gold road as a message to the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=24572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Winnoa bows her head.>$B$BThank you.' WHERE `entry`=24573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Yonada Eulogized',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Omusa Eulogized' WHERE `entry`=24573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Naralex slowly takes the squirming heart from you, visibly disturbed.>$B$BI\'ve been a fool. The one truth I did not want to accept has been staring me in the face this entire time...this foul thing is proof of that.$B$BYou and I have much work to do.' WHERE `entry`=24574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it again, $N. The freed villagers are eager to help us against the Forsaken in any way they can.' WHERE `entry`=24575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Roka listens with disgust as you tell her why you\'re trying to track down Snivel.>$B$BYou mean I\'ve been under the spell of an alchemist all this time? I can\'t believe I fell for that fraud! If I ever get my hands on that conniving little goblin, I\'ll tear him apart!$B$BIf he\'s finished his errands, he\'s on his way down to the zeppelin tower east of Orgrimmar\'s gates! Whatever you do, $N, you can\'t let him board that zeppelin and get away with all this!$B$BHurry to the zeppelin tower before you miss him!',`objectives_loc1`='Go to the zeppelin tower outside Orgrimmar and question Snivel Rustrocket about the supplies. Return with any evidence he gives you.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got his ledger? Really? That\'s great, $N. There\'s probably loads of good information in here.' WHERE `entry`=24576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Gar\'dul breaks into a sweat.>$B$BLook - ah - let\'s not discuss this here, in front of the men...' WHERE `entry`=24577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve been expecting you, $N. Do not be alarmed. My name is Belrysa. I am a priestess of the moon... a night elf. You might not know my people, but the destinies of our two races have been linked since the Curse befell you.' WHERE `entry`=24578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With Sartharion slain, surely Deathwing and Sinestra\'s plans are now stalled.' WHERE `entry`=24579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Word of your success precedes you, $C. Anub\'Rekhan is no more. You did him a great service, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s one less thorn in our side. With Noth destroyed, Scourge research into refining the means of creating the undead will grind to a halt.' WHERE `entry`=24581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $C. The Scourge military command out of Naxxramas has been thrown into disarray by Razuvious\'s demise.' WHERE `entry`=24582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Children everywhere will sleep easier knowing that Patchwerk is no more.' WHERE `entry`=24583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With Malygos defeated, the Nexus War should come to a swift conclusion. You have the gratitude of the Kirin Tor, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I never cease to be amazed by the horrors that can be created through the use of technology.' WHERE `entry`=24585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Razorscale normally keeps to her aerie near the Colossal Forge in Ulduar. Of late, however, she has been spotted reigning fire down upon lands outside of the titan complex.$B$BThough the broodmother\'s is a sad tale, she poses an imminent threat to all of Northrend. The Council of Six has decreed that Razorscale must die!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now Veranus can finally rest in peace.' WHERE `entry`=24586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I trust that you did not have to face too many of his iron construct assistants?' WHERE `entry`=24587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The greatest weakness of Ulduar is its masters\' blind faith in their inventions to protect it.' WHERE `entry`=24588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='All of Azeroth is fortunate that Timear foresaw the Eredar lord\'s arrival and that you were there in time to slay him.' WHERE `entry`=24589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Frozen Throne is without its chief guardian thanks to you. Our attacks upon the Lich King\'s forces will be all the more successful now.' WHERE `entry`=24590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve just learned a little something about the inner workings of Horde high command.$B$BWarlord Bloodhilt is in charge of Desolation Hold now. He may have more for you to do in the courtyard below.' WHERE `entry`=24591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I wish it could\'ve been avoided, $N. Let us ensure this is resolved without further bloodshed.' WHERE `entry`=24592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done then, $N. You are one of us now.' WHERE `entry`=24593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE `entry`=24595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to King Varian Wrynn in Stormwind.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve done it! The nightmare\'s connection to this place has been severed. The rest of the land is safe from this intrusion now, and in time, the abberations here will be subsumed by the balance of nature.$B$BI cannot thank you enough, $N. By helping to restore order here, you\'ve let me make amends for my foolish actions.' WHERE `entry`=24601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. Let us hope this works.' WHERE `entry`=24602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. Take your reward; this is only a prelude.' WHERE `entry`=24603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mahka sent you?$B$B<Mankrik\'s fury quells for a moment.>$B$BIt is a small comfort. But nothing can console me until I am done here.' WHERE `entry`=24604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are blood shards. They used to be found all over the Barrens.$B$BIt\'s said they were formed from the blood of Agamaggan, the great demigod that the quilboar sprang from. I knew the quilboar prized them, but nobody would think they\'d take the time and care to carve them like this one...$B$BThere may be more to learn here.' WHERE `entry`=24606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Anotha newblood, eh? Ya actually look ta be in shape though. Steady hands. Fierce eyes. I may be able ta turn ya into a real $C. Lets not waste anymore time \'den.' WHERE `entry`=24607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. Good! They will all die!  Their chieftains, and their women, and their children, and their foul pets!' WHERE `entry`=24608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Did you want to make a Lovely Charm Bracelet for the Lord of Ironforge? I\'m sure he\'d be thrilled.$B$BDo you already have a Lovely Charm Collector\'s Kit?',`objectives_loc1`='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to King Magni Bronzebeard in Ironforge.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Did you want to make a Lovely Charm Bracelet for the Warchief? I\'m sure he\'d be thrilled.$B$BDo you already have a Lovely Charm Collector\'s Kit?',`objectives_loc1`='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to Thrall in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to Cairne Bloodhoof in Thunder Bluff.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. The scout never had a chance.' WHERE `entry`=24616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re all right, $N!  I\'ve been waiting for this day for a long time, it truly is great to see you friend. I\'ve heard of what you\'ve done and I\'m thankful... especially for Lorna -- she\'s all I\'ve left. I will send for her right away.' WHERE `entry`=24617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! You\'re my kind of $C, $N.$B$BWith your help, we will throw these invaders back into the sea.' WHERE `entry`=24618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Calder peers into the sack of extremities and licks his lips with a dry, black tongue.>$B$BOh my. This is exciting.$B$B Aren\'t you excited, $N?' WHERE `entry`=24619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Calder grasps the gigantic heart in both hands, squeezing it and listening to the valves slurp and squish.>$B$B<His pale mask of a face splits open into an enormous, childlike grin.>$B$BIt is so very important to love one\'s work, wouldn\'t you agree, $N?$B$B<Calder chucks the heart over his shoulder into a waist-high pile of entrails.>' WHERE `entry`=24620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Calder holds the brains in an outstretched hand while withdrawing a gore-caked multi-tool from his belt.>$B$BWonderful work! Now the secret here is to leave the reptilian nervous systems intact while removing the higher cognitive functions. We can\'t have our new friend developing a conscience or remembering he\'s Alliance...$B$B<Calder digs and snips at the brain, removing large chunks.>$B$BAnd... we\'re finished! How lovely.' WHERE `entry`=24621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice ta see new faces \'round here, mon. It\'s easy ta get ta feelin\' isolated since we left Orgrimmar.' WHERE `entry`=24622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank ya so much! They can be vicious when provoked, but most of da time dey don\'t know betta.' WHERE `entry`=24623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. It will be takin\' brave and determined people like you ta drive da Darkspear up again. I hope dere are more people even half as dedicated to come.' WHERE `entry`=24624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N! Dis naga has set us back quite some time, but nothin\' will be holdin\' us down foreva. It\'s good ta be havin\' ya wit us, $N. Ya have a fierce heart within ya.' WHERE `entry`=24625;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Swiftclaw! Kijara was tellin\' me about him and he sounded like he\'d be a handful. I don\'t mind da challenge - it\'s da spirited ones like dat that be makin\' da bravest and truest companions when real times of need be comin\'. Tank ya, hon. Ya\'ve been very helpful.' WHERE `entry`=24626;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are as good as I remember, $N. It is good to have you back.' WHERE `entry`=24627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These simple leaves grow by Elune\'s grace. They will help your mind understand the need for balance and your soul will permanently earn mastery over the beast.' WHERE `entry`=24628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work, $N! People will come running to buy Crown perfumes now that they\'ve had a chance to sample their wonders. Here\'s a little something for helping us out.' WHERE `entry`=24629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The five of us have communed with the spirits, and found the source of the Quilboar\'s aggression. Charlga Razorflank leads them from within Razorfen Kraul. She holds the promise of Agamaggan\'s resurrection over their heads, whipping the tribes into frenzy to raze and pillage the land for her.$B$BPlease, $C, put a stop to this. Without Charlga, the quilboar may not be saved, but they may at least be less dangerous.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill Charlga Razorflank in Razorfen Kraul.' WHERE `entry`=24630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Tomusa snorts as he takes back his hook.>$B$BVengeance feels hollow. Still. I could not allow them to go unpunished.' WHERE `entry`=24631;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Gann looks you up and down.>$B$BWe could use your help, $C. But this is not a skirmish. We fight here to strike a killing blow... or die trying.' WHERE `entry`=24632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! The fool didn\'t destroy these orders.$B$BLet\'s see what we can learn...' WHERE `entry`=24634;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, $N! People will be buying Crown colognes by the crate-load now that they\'ve had a chance to try them. Here\'s a little something for helping us out.' WHERE `entry`=24635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lovely work, $N! People will be tripping over one another to get Crown chocolates now that they\'ve had a chance to taste those sweet, romantic treats.$B$BHere\'s a little something for helping us out.' WHERE `entry`=24636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Upon hearing the news, Bloodhilt snorts. His eyes gleam. He tips his head back and bellows a wet, cackling laugher that echoes between the blackened walls of Desolation hold and reverberates throughout the hills beyond.>$B$BSo it is done! The Butcher of Taurajo is felled at last. Cut down in the streets like a dog. Fitting.$B$BYou have done well, $N. You\'ve sowed fear into our enemies, and soon we will reap the harvest!' WHERE `entry`=24637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, mon. Ya have a natural flow to ya swings - you may have a talent for dis. Some rough edges ta be sure, but we\'ll get dose ironed out here and I\'ll teach ya a few new tings as we go.' WHERE `entry`=24639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I tink I have something I can show ya. It\'s pretty simple really, but it should help.$B$BWhen ya want ta close tha distance with an enemy quickly, ya can charge dem with a fierce roar. Dis will take them off guard, stunnin\' them and opening up an opportunity ta follow up with attacks before dey can defend demselves.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when ya tink you have it down.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Nortet to train Charge. Practice using Charge against a Tiki Target.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, mon! Dis stuff come easy to ya.' WHERE `entry`=24640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dese are some fine pelts, boy. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.' WHERE `entry`=24641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya handle yerself quite well. Ya gonna be quite powerful some day.' WHERE `entry`=24642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya tha new recruit everyone\'s talkin\' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.' WHERE `entry`=24643;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew we could count on you. You\'ve done well, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s to the east of Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands. Don\'t give me that look, okay? This is a problem for the Horde, too. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 5 Crown Agents and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon east of Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kill 5 Crown Sprinklers and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon east of Everlook in Winterspring, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, these are clearly symbols of Agamaggan. But if the quilboar are still devoted to their dead god, what is the source of their vicious agression?  It is said Agamaggan was noble, and even gave his life fighting the Burning Legion... A moment, $N. We must confer with the spirits.' WHERE `entry`=24653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re covered in hot tar and bug juice! Don\'t worry, friend. It\'ll come off.$B$BSomeday.' WHERE `entry`=24654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Get a load of these guys, would ya? Steamwheedle\'s been handling the business of holidays for years, and all of a sudden, these guys bust into the market. They\'re not Steamwheedle; the cartel hired me to get to the bottom of this. Something stinks here and it ain\'t just perfume.$B$BTake this device I brought and go analyze the perfume clouds around the guards. I want to know what they\'re putting in that stuff. Things ain\'t natural.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, thanks, kid. Give it over, let\'s take a look.$B$B<He takes the device from you and fiddles with it.>$B$BOh, that ain\'t good.' WHERE `entry`=24655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I knew they were up to no good! There\'s some sort of mind-affecting chemical in here, but I can\'t get a handle on it with such a small sample. I need the real stuff.$B$BDon\'t just go over there and buy it! I don\'t want you giving these scumbags one copper. Nah, you gotta get it from the source, discreet-like.$B$BI\'ll disguise you as a package runner. I saw a stockpile guarded by their goons outside the gates. Go run by, and DON\'T stop, or they\'ll make you! They\'ll toss you a crate. Bring it back here.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got it, huh? Good job, kid. Top notch. Let\'s see what we got here.$B$B<He cracks open the crate and rummages around inside.>' WHERE `entry`=24656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got his ledger? Really? That\'s great, $N. There\'s probably loads of good information in here.' WHERE `entry`=24657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This ledger is full of locations, and I need you to investigate and take action, pal. This has gone on long enough.$B$BHere\'s an entry I want you to check out: it\'s northeast of Westbrook Garrison right outside in Elwynn! That can\'t be good. Get out there and rough \'em up.$B$BOh, and if you see something big and dangerous enough that it needs destroying, toss this bomb at it.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 5 Crown Lackeys and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to damage one Chemical Wagon northeast of Westbrook Garrison in Elwynn Forest, then return to Inspector Snip Snagglebolt in Stormwind.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kill 5 Crown Dusters and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon just outside of Hillsbrad Village in Hillsbrad Foothills, then return to Inspector Snip Snagglebolt in Stormwind.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='REUSE ME' WHERE `entry`=24661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24666;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Is this from Crawgol? Wonderful! Despite all the turmoil in the world, we can\'t turn our back on the silithid threat. It is important to have people like Crawgol studying our enemy closely and learning its secrets for the fight ahead!$B$B<Tauna opens the book and glances over the first page. Her face falls.>$B$BOh. Well. I suppose it\'s something, at least.' WHERE `entry`=24667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Success! Was there ever any doubt? Greely, fire up the poultryizer!' WHERE `entry`=24671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! Genn... they\'ve taken Genn... they\'ve taken... our king!' WHERE `entry`=24672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='King Greymane gave me a brief rundown of the plan before he set off for the Blackwald. Doesn\'t make it sound any less crazy.' WHERE `entry`=24673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N. Our people will no longer suffer under that monstrosity\'s yolk.' WHERE `entry`=24674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N. Our men and women will have a last good meal before they set off for battle.' WHERE `entry`=24675;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We have the people of Emberstone on our side now thanks to you.' WHERE `entry`=24676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am glad to have you here, $N. We\'re surrounded by Forsaken on all sides and can use all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=24677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Use the Half-Burnt Torch to get to the other side of the tunnel beneath Gilneas City.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re here, $N. Most everyone made it through, but now we\'re stuck here... surrounded by our own... dead!' WHERE `entry`=24678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s done, $N. The dead return to their slumber.' WHERE `entry`=24679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s almost over, $N. Only one obstacle remains between us and survival.' WHERE `entry`=24681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Meet Lady Sylvanas Windrunner inside the entrace to the Pit of Saron.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Incapable fools. I begin to wonder if any of these louts from the tournament will be of any use at all. Perhaps you\'ll prove me wrong.' WHERE `entry`=24682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I underestimated this Scourgelord, and it\'s my men that paid for it. When I think that my guilt over Arthas\' betrayal cannot go any deeper, he proves me wrong yet again.$B$BWe have to press on. We cannot let their sacrifice be meaningless.' WHERE `entry`=24683;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You do good work, $C. That riot you caused at the fortress entrance has these dwarves running around with their heads cut off.' WHERE `entry`=24684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s see, let\'s see.$B$BIt looks like the artillery shells are prepped here, then loaded into the secure magazine...$B$B<Weezil rubs his hands together.>$B$B$N, are you ready to blow some stuff up?' WHERE `entry`=24685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... yes, these seeds will do nicely. You have the gratitude of the Cenarion Circle, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You return victorious. Good, good... perhaps the crater will now be a bit safer to those who travel through it.' WHERE `entry`=24687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh... did Garl send you?  How are his studies coming?  I find that he can be a bit slow at times, but he\'s truly a force to be reckoned with when he takes the form of the bear. Now, we have more pressing matters to attend to.' WHERE `entry`=24689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At last, Blazerunner is dispatched. Thanks, $N... he was driving me batty.' WHERE `entry`=24690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant!  We\'re on the cusp of something big here, $N. Here\'s your share of the inevitably huge profits. Now, on to other matters...' WHERE `entry`=24691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve completed a remarkable task, $N. You are truly worthy of commendation. Thank you, and congratulations!' WHERE `entry`=24692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very well, if Quixxil recommended you, then I suppose you\'re alright. In all our years working together, Quixxil\'s never steered me wrong.' WHERE `entry`=24693;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have been watching you, $N. Your arrival was not unforeseen. In fact, your arrival here has been predetermined for some time now.' WHERE `entry`=24694;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have proven to be both wise and agile, young $N. You have my blessing to take your newfound knowledge and spread it as you continue on your journey.' WHERE `entry`=24695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Gorilla Observation',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Pterrordax Observation' WHERE `entry`=24695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. Now we\'re a bit safer from dinosaur attacks... plus I\'ve got all this fresh meat to serve to my men.' WHERE `entry`=24697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good ol\' Nolen. How is he doing?  Hopefully better than I am...' WHERE `entry`=24698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, this tar is just the stuff...$B$BHey, wait a minute, my hands... I can\'t seem to get them apart...$B$BMaybe this wasn\'t such a good idea. Oh, but wait! Super sticky tar remover! That\'s where the real money is!' WHERE `entry`=24699;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, there they are. Great work, handsome!  Here\'s some gold. You\'ve earned it.' WHERE `entry`=24700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s a bunch of junk, but it\'s a bunch of FREE junk, and that\'s all that matters to me. Well, mostly free. Here\'s your share. Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=24701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Sturdy mount and trusted friend.$B$BDied shortly after the Cataclysm. He always hated loud noises.$B$BIn lieu of flowers, please drop off a few Bloodpetal sprouts. In life, he loved nothing more.' WHERE `entry`=24702;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You please me, $N. From this day forward, you are no longer a simple beggar, but a squire loyal to Maximillian of Northshire. Prepare yourself for our first sally, good squire, for together we shall plunge our fists elbow-deep into what they call adventure!' WHERE `entry`=24703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='...and that makes 15 of them. Justice had a name today... and that name was Maximillian of Northshire. For Doloria!' WHERE `entry`=24704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our duty is fulfilled. Even so, it troubles me that today\'s damsels were less than gracious... only the fair-haired one by the lake managed to show us any gratitude for our chivalry. Perhaps tomorrow\'s damsels will have thankfulness to match their beauty. Now we must ride. More adventures await!' WHERE `entry`=24705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Might I ask you a question?  What act have you committed to make the spirits so angry at you?  I\'m impressed that you had the patience to sit so still while they pummeled you so violently. Now we may proceed. The teeth and scales of Un\'Goro\'s greatest dragon await us.' WHERE `entry`=24706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The day is saved!  Huzzah!  Today we learned that while armor can be replaced, valor has no price. Because of your key involvement in this task, I hereby graduate you from squire to fledgling knight. No longer do the chains of servitude bind you to me; you are free to serve other masters. Go with honor, young hero!  For chivalry, the Light, and the beauty of Doloria!' WHERE `entry`=24707;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What an interesting femur you\'ve brought here, but why\'s it all sharp and curvy? ... Wait a minute, that thing\'s a TALON?  A dinosaur with a talon that size would\'ve been... well, really big, that\'s for sure. Is this the only fossil that you found there?' WHERE `entry`=24708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew it!  Durrin HAS been digging around here. And he\'s been excavating what could be the archaeological find of the century!  Now I just have to find out where he\'s stashing the bones... Thanks $N. You\'ve been a great help.' WHERE `entry`=24709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Such a senseless waste! Arthas goes too far! I can only hope what we find in the Halls of Reflection makes this somehow worth it.$B$BIf what that vile gnome said is to be trusted, Frostmourne should be there, and with it, answers to confronting Arthas.' WHERE `entry`=24710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We must press on, hero. We\'ve come so far... we\'re so close to our goal. I must delay a moment to send Elandra back to the airship. I\'m uncertain how we\'re going to escape with so many men lost and so few to keep our path in secure - we will need any help they can send.$B$BContinue on. I will meet you in the Halls of Reflection.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Halls of Reflection. Finally.$B$BLet me know when you are ready. Arthas may not be here, but it would be naive to think that he would leave Frostmourne unguarded entirely.' WHERE `entry`=24711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Halls of Reflection lie ahead. If what that vile gnome said is to be trusted, Frostmourne should be there, and with it, answers to confronting Arthas.' WHERE `entry`=24712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Keep moving, the sword is close.$B$BI need a moment to send one of my Dark Rangers back to the airship. With all of our fodder gone, I will not be caught unprepared - we will need any help they can send.$B$BGo. I will meet you in the Halls of Reflection.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Halls of Reflection. Finally.$B$BLet me know when you are ready, $C. I will not be so naive as to think that Arthas left his precious sword entirely unguarded.' WHERE `entry`=24713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A-Me lies motionless before you. No power seems to be running through her components.' WHERE `entry`=24714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You pour the coconut milk into what appears to be A-Me 01\'s oil reservoir. You hear the sound of gears whirring and actuators firing.' WHERE `entry`=24715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, 2 of each color!  You\'re certainly an overachiever, $N. My companions and I could use a $R like you around here. Ever consider a career in profiteering?' WHERE `entry`=24717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, look at this one!  Not just the color, but the size of it... you could cover a tauren with this. Here you go, $N. You\'ve earned this. Stick around, I\'m sure we can find something else for you to do.' WHERE `entry`=24718;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My mentor says that sometimes you have to take away from nature before you can give back. These raptors... I feel that they died for good cause. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now I will continue my experiments! Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You were right to bring this pylon to my attention, $N. This is just the sort of thing I\'ve been studying.' WHERE `entry`=24721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You think this may be related to the attacks on Marshal\'s Refuge, $N?' WHERE `entry`=24722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A pylon in the west?  And a relationship between titans and dinosaurs?  This is a lot to take in, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Arranging the crystals on the table, you carefully align the colors. As you push the last one into place, a burst of light fuses the crystals together.$B$BThe resulting combination is now yours.' WHERE `entry`=24724;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Arranging the crystals on the table, you carefully align the colors. As you push the last one into place, a burst of light fuses the crystals together.$B$BThe resulting combination is now yours.' WHERE `entry`=24725;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Arranging the crystals on the table, you carefully align the colors. As you push the last one into place, a burst of light fuses the crystals together.$B$BThe resulting combination is now yours.' WHERE `entry`=24726;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Arranging the crystals on the table, you carefully align the colors. As you push the last one into place, a burst of light fuses the crystals together.$B$BThe resulting combination is now yours.' WHERE `entry`=24727;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Arranging the crystals on the table, you carefully align the colors. As you push the last one into place, a burst of light fuses the crystals together.$B$BThe resulting combination is now yours.' WHERE `entry`=24728;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Arranging the crystals on the table, you carefully align the colors. As you push the last one into place, a burst of light fuses the crystals together.$B$BThe resulting combination is now yours.' WHERE `entry`=24729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent, these should do the trick. And now, if you\'ll permit me, in case anyone\'s listening... THANKS FOR DIGGING ALL OF THESE BONES OUT OF THE GROUND FOR US AND NOT HURTING THE NATIVE BEASTS IN ANY WAY. Whether you really did or didn\'t, I don\'t want to know. Let\'s keep it that way, shall we?  Here - maybe this will keep your lips shut on the whole thing. Anything to get out of here alive, I say!' WHERE `entry`=24730;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This will do nicely, $N. It seems Lar\'korwi eats well these days. Although, I wonder where he found a threshadon in this area. Odd.$B$BRegardless, I will hold onto this until you are ready for your confrontation with the beast. Do not worry for my safety--I am sure you\'ve angered Lar\'korwi enough that he will not kill me until after he\'s tasted your flesh.' WHERE `entry`=24731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, fine specimens, $N. The two pieces you\'ve found should be perfect for baiting Lar\'korwi into the open. I cannot wait to see the outcome of your fight with the monster. He is a massive thing with claws as sharp as the finest blades. You will look into his eyes and you will know death.' WHERE `entry`=24732;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Earth Mother be praised! You\'ve done it! Fair play to you, $N. You have proven to be a great hunter in your own right. Your spirit is strong. Your bravery unmatched. And your strength has been fortified. I bow down to your skills. Only the greatest of my ancestors could have accomplished something so incredible. Congratulations.' WHERE `entry`=24733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You find what appears to be Ringo\'s belongings. If he left these here, he can\'t have gone far away. Maybe you should look for him.' WHERE `entry`=24734;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ringo\'s not in the best shape, $N, but I am glad to have him back in one piece!$B$BThank you for finding him.' WHERE `entry`=24735;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, these scales are perfect. I should be able to get this flyer off the ground with these scales for sure!$B$BThanks!' WHERE `entry`=24736;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeah, this tar is pretty sticky, I guess. I mean, it\'s sticky, but it\'s not "make fistfuls of money" sticky. I guess I\'ll have to keep thinking.' WHERE `entry`=24737;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope that did the trick. I\'ll take the ash... this may come in handy sometime down the line.' WHERE `entry`=24740;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice! Look at the size of those things! There\'s no way that Grapplehammer\'s going to be able to top those!' WHERE `entry`=24741;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These results are astounding!  My boss will be pleased. Thank you, kind $R!' WHERE `entry`=24742;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Listen well, $C. In accepting this weapon your fate is sealed.$B$BOvercome or succumb.$B$BI have placed your feet upon this path. You are therefore my personal responsibility. Should you falter, I am duty-bound to deliver you from this life.$B$BRemember my words, $C, and do not fail.' WHERE `entry`=24743;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Eureka! My genius saves the day yet again! Take that Bamm Megabomb! And now, to reap the benefits!' WHERE `entry`=24744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'ve you got there? Oh hey, this is big. Real big. Most of the crazy details in one little package. Thanks - you really helped us reel this all in. Good working with ya.' WHERE `entry`=24745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Bael\'dun? Destroyed?$B$B<Wincing in pain, Gann twists his head to peer behind him, where plumes of smoke darken the skyline.>$B$B$N, my friend. You have avenged Taurajo and avenged the Tauren people. The invaders will not soon recover from that blow. Thank you.$B$B<Gann closes his eyes, his head tipping forward as his breath gives way to a series of ragged coughs.>' WHERE `entry`=24747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, at last it is done. May the people of Azeroth remember our deeds here forevermore. May the sacrifices of so many burn in their hearts eternally. May they never fail to risk mortal peril in the face of great evil.' WHERE `entry`=24748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $C. The completion of our work draws near.' WHERE `entry`=24749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Anotha newblood, eh? Ya actually have an intense look about ya though. Fiery eyes. You might have the makings of a real $C. Lets not waste anymore time \'den.' WHERE `entry`=24750;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, mon. Ya have a natural flow to ya spells - you may have a talent for dis. Some rough edges ta be sure, but we\'ll get dose ironed out here and I\'ll teach ya a few new tings as we go.' WHERE `entry`=24751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I tink I have something I can show ya. It\'s pretty simple really, but it should help.$B$BWhen ya arcane energies line up perfectly, ya can release a volley of arcane missiles dat wil be devastatin\' ya enemeis. It may take some time and some luck for ya to get a chance at practicin\' these magics, so be patient.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when ya tink you have it down.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Soratha to train Arcane Missiles. Practice using Arcane Missiles 2 times against a Tiki Target.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, mon! Dis stuff come easy to ya.' WHERE `entry`=24752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dese are some fine pelts, boy. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.' WHERE `entry`=24753;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya handle yerself quite well. Ya gonna be quite powerful some day.' WHERE `entry`=24754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya tha new recruit everyone\'s talkin\' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.' WHERE `entry`=24755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $C. Shadowmourne is nearly within reach.' WHERE `entry`=24756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The axe has drunk its fill, $R, and the forge is nearly ready for the creation of Shadowmourne...' WHERE `entry`=24757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Anotha newblood, eh? Ya actually have a weathered look about ya though. Wise eyes. You might have the makings of a real $C. Lets not waste anymore time \'den.' WHERE `entry`=24758;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, mon. Ya have a natural flow to ya spells - you may have a talent for dis. Some rough edges ta be sure, but we\'ll get dose ironed out here and I\'ll teach ya a few new tings as we go.' WHERE `entry`=24759;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I tink I have something I can show ya. It\'s pretty simple really, but it should help.$B$BFocusin\' tha power of da elements into yer weapon can allow ya to unleash a quick, vicious attack on your enemies. Dis should be easy enough for ya to make a lot of use of it.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when ya tink you have it down.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Nekali to train Primal Strike. Use Primal Strike 3 times against a Tiki Target.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, mon! Dis stuff come easy to ya.' WHERE `entry`=24760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dese are some fine pelts, boy. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.' WHERE `entry`=24761;
