UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya tha new recruit everyone\'s talkin\' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.' WHERE `entry`=24769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Anotha newblood, eh? Ya actually have a sly look about ya though. Fierce eyes. You might have the makings of a real $C. Lets not waste anymore time \'den.' WHERE `entry`=24770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, mon. Ya have a natural flow to ya swings - you may have a talent for dis. Some rough edges ta be sure, but we\'ll get dose ironed out here and I\'ll teach ya a few new tings as we go.' WHERE `entry`=24771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I tink I have something I can show ya. It\'s pretty simple really, but it should help.$B$BAs ya fight ya enemies, ya will be able to see dere weaknesses and set up for devastating combo attacks. After ya\'ve struck a few blows to weaken ya foe, finish dem off with a vicious evisceration attack.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when ya tink you have it down.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Legati to train Eviscerate. Use Eviscerate 3 times against a Tiki Target.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, mon! Dis stuff come easy to ya.' WHERE `entry`=24772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dese are some fine pelts, boy. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.' WHERE `entry`=24773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya handle yerself quite well. Ya gonna be quite powerful some day.' WHERE `entry`=24774;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya tha new recruit everyone\'s talkin\' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.' WHERE `entry`=24775;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Anotha newblood, eh? Ya actually have a wild look about ya though. Fierce eyes. You might have the makings of a real $C. Lets not waste anymore time \'den.' WHERE `entry`=24776;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, mon. Ya have a natural flow to ya attacks - you may have a talent for dis. Some rough edges ta be sure, but we\'ll get dose ironed out here and I\'ll teach ya a few new tings as we go.' WHERE `entry`=24777;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I tink I have something I can show ya. It\'s pretty simple really, but it should help.$B$BWe\'ve all manner of trick shots we can be usin\' wit bows or guns, but witout a steady hand between dose shots, ya gonna find yaself exhausted and not really managin\' to kill much. Take ya time, steady ya bow, and keep the shots pourin\' into ya target. Keep\'m off-balance.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when ya tink you have it down.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Ortezza to train Steady Shot. Use Steady Shot 5 times on a Tiki Target.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, mon! Dis stuff come easy to ya.' WHERE `entry`=24778;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dese are some fine pelts, boy. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.' WHERE `entry`=24779;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya handle yerself quite well. Ya gonna be quite powerful some day.' WHERE `entry`=24780;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya tha new recruit everyone\'s talkin\' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.' WHERE `entry`=24781;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Anotha newblood, eh? Ya actually have a balanced look about ya though. Calm eyes. You might have the makings of a real $C. Lets not waste anymore time \'den.' WHERE `entry`=24782;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, mon. Ya have a natural flow to ya spells - you may have a talent for dis. Some rough edges ta be sure, but we\'ll get dose ironed out here and I\'ll teach ya a few new tings as we go.' WHERE `entry`=24783;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I tink I have something I can show ya. It\'s pretty simple really, but it should help.$B$BWith a quick gatherin\' of holy energies, ya can bind ya wounds or the wounds of ya friends. Dis magic be quick, but it also be drainin\' on you. As time goes on, ya will learn more varieties of it that won\'t drain ya quite so heavily.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when ya tink you have it down.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Tunari to train Flash Heal. Use Flash Heal 5 times to heal Wounded Darkspear Watchers around the Darkspear Training Grounds.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, mon! Dis stuff come easy to ya.' WHERE `entry`=24784;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dese are some fine pelts, boy. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.' WHERE `entry`=24785;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya handle yerself quite well. Ya gonna be quite powerful some day.' WHERE `entry`=24786;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya tha new recruit everyone\'s talkin\' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.' WHERE `entry`=24787;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fantastic. Help is exactly what I need.' WHERE `entry`=24792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What?  Krakle sent you?' WHERE `entry`=24794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='In spite of Queen Lana\'thel\'s boasting, you have restored Quel\'Delar, $N. Long have we dreamt of reclaiming Quel\'Delar.$B$BThe Silver Covenant, and indeed all quel\'dorei owe you a debt of gratitude.$B$BAs a $C, the sword seems to know you lack the training to wield it and hasn\'t bonded to you. Where, then, will its next master come from? Perhaps the Argent Crusade can find one. Go north to the Argent Tournament Grounds and present the sword to Justicar Mariel Trueheart on behalf of the Silver Covenant.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring the Restored Quel\'Delar to Justicar Mariel Trueheart at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='That a weapon of such power has been redeemed from the clutches of evil is a great omen in these times, $N. With Quel\'Delar and staunch Silver Covenant allies at our side, the Lich King will have good reason to fear.$B$BThe crusade maintains an arsenal of exceptional weapons for our strongest allies. Allow me to offer you your choice from among them in return for entrusting us with the care of Quel\'Delar.' WHERE `entry`=24795;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is nothing short of an amazing accomplishment, $N. The day that Thalorien and Anasterian fell, the same day that Quel\'Delar was lost, was one of the darkest of my life. To see Quel\'Delar restored... it is beyond words.$B$BWithout a doubt, you are meant to be the true bearer of the blade. Quel\'Delar\'s magic is already adapting the blade to your skills and your strengths.' WHERE `entry`=24796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='At last, Quel\'Delar is restored for the glory of the Sunreavers and the sin\'dorei!$B$BAll of Silvermoon will celebrate you as a hero, $N.$B$BAs a $C, the sword seems to know you lack the training to wield it and hasn\'t bonded to you. Where, then, will its next master come from? No worthy sin\'dorei has come forward. Let us seek the Argent Crusade\'s counsel. Go north to the Argent Tournament Grounds and present the sword to Justicar Mariel Trueheart on behalf of the Sunreavers.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring the Restored Quel\'Delar to Justicar Mariel Trueheart at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='That a weapon of such power has been redeemed from the clutches of evil is a great omen in these times, $N. With Quel\'Delar and staunch Sunreaver allies at our side, the Lich King will have good reason to fear.$B$BThe crusade maintains an arsenal of exceptional weapons for our strongest allies. Allow me to offer you your choice from among them in return for entrusting us with the care of Quel\'Delar.' WHERE `entry`=24798;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='At last, Quel\'Delar is restored for the glory of the Sunreavers!$B$BAll the Horde will celebrate you as a hero, $N.$B$BAs a $C, the sword seems to know you lack the training to wield it and hasn\'t bonded to you. Where, then, will its next master come from? I will not conceal my disappointment; I had hoped it would be a worthy sin\'dorei. Let us seek the Argent Crusade\'s counsel. Go north to the Argent Tournament Grounds and present the sword to Justicar Mariel Trueheart on behalf of the Sunreavers.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring the Restored Quel\'Delar to Justicar Mariel Trueheart at the Argent Tournament Grounds.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='That a weapon of such power has been redeemed from the clutches of evil is a great omen in these times, $N. With Quel\'Delar and staunch Sunreaver allies at our side, the Lich King will have good reason to fear.$B$BThe crusade maintains an arsenal of exceptional weapons for our strongest allies. Allow me to offer you your choice from among them in return for entrusting us with the care of Quel\'Delar.' WHERE `entry`=24799;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Quel\'Delar rises again, as we sin\'dorei have risen from the ashes of defeat and betrayal. The heart and the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker are both with you, $N.$B$BI see the blade has already started adapting itself to your strengths, $N. Hold your head high and always keep Quel\'Delar at your side.' WHERE `entry`=24800;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Quel\'Delar rises again, as the sin\'dorei have risen from the ashes of defeat and betrayal. Yet, somehow, the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker has chosen to serve an outsider.$B$BBe at ease, $N. I do not mean to diminish your accomplishment, for you have done what none of my brothers could, although I do not know why. You are clearly meant to be its bearer; the blade is already adapting itself to your abilities. Wield Quel\'Delar proudly against our common foes.' WHERE `entry`=24801;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Uther knew a great deal about how Arthas might be defeated. It\'s hard to believe that there is much hope of defeating Arthas upon the steps of his own throne. And who will take up the crown of Lich King if it comes to that?$B$BMany questions remain, but the answers that you\'ve uncovered may be critical to ensuring Arthas\' defeat. You need to find Sylvanas and escape the Lich King while there\'s still time.',`objectives_loc1`='Find Lady Sylvanas Windrunner and escape the Halls of Reflection',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yet again, vengeance slips through my grasp. It\'s hard to believe how much stronger he\'s gotten.$B$BIt was foolish of you to come for me, but it\'s good to know that there are still some champions of the Horde that aren\'t useless cowards. The information Uther gave us may well be key to finally killing Arthas, though it is becoming more and more clear that the Horde will not be able to accomplish this on their own.$B$BGo, $C. I expect your prowess may be needed again very soon.' WHERE `entry`=24802;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Don\'t just stand there! Give me the shark and I\'ll declare you the winner!' WHERE `entry`=24803;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey. You got some time on your hands? I could use someone like you.' WHERE `entry`=24804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey. You got some time on your hands? I could use someone like you.' WHERE `entry`=24805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m afraid we\'ve already had a winner for today, young $N. However, if you bring a shark, I\'ll see that it\'s released back into the waters, and I might just have a little something for you...' WHERE `entry`=24806;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I could feel what occured from here, $C. It bristled every hair I have.$B$BI\'m overjoyed to hear you succeeded in pushing those horrors back, and I\'ll be sure to scour the area for any stray deviate creatures.' WHERE `entry`=24807;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well fought, young $R.' WHERE `entry`=24812;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dat should keep dem at bay.' WHERE `entry`=24813;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Tha power d\'at burst forth when tha Sea Witch died was immense. I can use d\'is power ta enact a vision of places far away. Observe, youngblood. I want ya ta be here when I make contact wit\' Thrall, perhaps it will be grantin\' ya insight as well.' WHERE `entry`=24814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='To atone for the sins I committed as one of the Lich King\'s Death Knights, I\'ve dedicated myself to creating rings of great power for our brothers and sisters to use in the struggle.$B$BYou\'ve proven yourself as a valuable ally in the fight against the Scourge, $N. As your dedication continues I can improve on the ring\'s original design.$B$BChoose your path carefully. A change of heart will come at a price.' WHERE `entry`=24815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These will do very nicely! We\'re going to combine the shark parts and the robotic remains of the Mechachicken into a submersible that should allow you to rid us of that nuisance, The Hammer!' WHERE `entry`=24816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, my boy! The Town-In-A-Box is saved and the Bilgewater Cartel will be profitable once again thanks to my overwhelmingly unbelievable intellect and tinkering know-how.' WHERE `entry`=24817;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=24823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We are here to monitor the scars of the land, and watch for further signs of instability. While we haven\'t seen any yet, a cataclysmic aftershock could devastate the Barrens even further.$B$BTo the northeast, near the chasm, earth elementals rampage out of control. To sooth the earth, these need to occasionally be destroyed, and their essence returned in a ritual. If you help us do this, $C, I would be happy to reward you.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, friend. It\'s important we try to calm this earth in every way we can.' WHERE `entry`=24824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=24826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=24827;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=24828;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a true champion of our cause, $N. None can claim to be more dedicated to the struggle than you. The enemy speaks of your name only in whispers, for they know you\'re a force to be reckoned with. Accept this humble gift as a reward for your many triumphs.' WHERE `entry`=24829;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=24832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a true champion of our cause, $N. None can claim to be more dedicated to the struggle than you. It is rumored that the minions of the Scourge fear you more than they do the Lich King himself. You are vengeance incarnate. Accept this humble gift as a reward for your many triumphs.' WHERE `entry`=24833;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=24834;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a true champion of our cause, $N. None can claim to be more dedicated to the struggle than you. You are a source of inspiration to our allies and your unshakeable valor gives pause to even the most seasoned of our enemy\'s generals. Accept this humble gift as a reward for your many triumphs.' WHERE `entry`=24835;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You... You\'re not Snivel. Did he send you? He\'s so late, I had started to give up hope...$B$B<Tears start welling up in the woman\'s eyes once she realizes that you aren\'t there to deliver a message from Snivel.>$B$BThat\'s not like my Snivel, but what other choice is there?' WHERE `entry`=24848;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='All he talked about was leaving town with all his money? Then he really has abandoned me, hasn\'t he?$B$BOh, $N, I was such a fool to fall for him, but how could I help myself? He was so irresistible!' WHERE `entry`=24849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc1`='Stormwind Counting House searched',`ObjectiveText2_loc1`='Stormwind Auction House searched' WHERE `entry`=24849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Kid, this is about more than just perfume. There were some rockets in that crate, and they had some kind of chemical payload inside. I can\'t analyze it here, but I\'ll spare ya the trip to the lab.$B$BNah, you gotta find the guy who made these. I know the maker\'s mark. Snivel Rustrocket.$B$BI hear Snivel\'s livin\' it up here in Orgrimmar. What\'s more, he\'s got himself a girlfriend -- some orc dame named Roka. She\'s supposed to meet him at Gotri\'s Travelling Goods in the Drag before they make their escape.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Roka at the Gotri\'s Travelling Goods in Orgrimmar\'s Drag district.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re not Snivel. He was supposed to be here an hour ago! What have you done with him? This isn\'t like my sweet Snivel. Do you think something\'s happened to him?' WHERE `entry`=24850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Look for Snivel Rustrocket in the Orgrimmar Bank, the Auction House, and the Barbershop in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='All he talked about was leaving town with all his money? Then he really has abandoned me, hasn\'t he? I can\'t believe I fell for such a horrible goblin! But he was so irresistible when we first met.' WHERE `entry`=24851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc1`='Orgrimmar Bank searched',`ObjectiveText2_loc1`='Orgrimmar Auction House searched' WHERE `entry`=24851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks to you, our people are free to fight for our home.' WHERE `entry`=24852;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Zen\'Aliri was wise to send you here. I\'ve hit a dead end in my studies.' WHERE `entry`=24854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The scent of bloodpetal pollen hangs about your head, $C. This is good. You\'ve earned your reward.' WHERE `entry`=24855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Boss, we gotta problem.' WHERE `entry`=24856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I wish I could have seen the looks on their scaly faces when you blew up their banners and replaced them with our own. On second thought, I don\'t want to be close enough to see their snarls.' WHERE `entry`=24858;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re going to be filthy rich, I tell you! Well, if we can get off of this island, that is.' WHERE `entry`=24859;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is balance in all things. As Greatmother Hawkwind\'s spirit takes its final journey, you will begin your first.' WHERE `entry`=24861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re ambushing the roads to Stonetalon, too? We just can\'t get a break here. Where are they coming from, anyways?' WHERE `entry`=24862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What ... our supplies? These were meant for Stonetalon. No matter, at the rate we\'re going, we need them more here. Honor\'s Stand has been cut off from the coast, $N. Commander Singleton is at his wit\'s end.' WHERE `entry`=24863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, they\'re so cute! I wish that we could turn them into little plush toys and sell them for a gazillion macaroons!' WHERE `entry`=24864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh... wow... it\'s some really old food. Hey Hol\'anyee, take a look at this!  This $R brought us those old rations that we abandoned! No, not from Marshal\'s Refuge... from the old base camp! I\'m not sure I want to peek inside. I\'ll just give it to Nolen, I guess... he\'ll know what to do with it.' WHERE `entry`=24865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well I\'ll be... that\'s Shizzle\'s old portable dinomometer!  Where did you find this? I\'m surprised it\'s still functional, even after all these years. I\'ll have it delivered to Shizzle promptly.' WHERE `entry`=24866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A faceless of the deep? What\'s that? That does NOT sound like a naga! Well, you killed it, whatever it was. It doesn\'t matter now. We have other fish to fry....' WHERE `entry`=24868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N? We\'re saved! Who am I kidding? We\'re all going to die!!!' WHERE `entry`=24897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Okay, I think that\'s good enough for now, but they took a bunch of the townsfolk captive. We\'re going to have to take the fight to them!' WHERE `entry`=24901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Plague?  Something so heinous that not even the orcs condone its use?  I\'d say this warrants notifying King Greymane.' WHERE `entry`=24902;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You present me with the most difficult choice of my life, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve driven the Forsaken back. We hold three out of the four districts. But at what cost...' WHERE `entry`=24904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc1`='Battle for Gilneas City Complete' WHERE `entry`=24904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You know, while you were out doin\' your thing, Megs stopped by here. I hadn\'t seen her in months, but she barely gave me the time of day, just wanted me to tell you she had more business lined up.$B$BShe said she was headed over to the Dunemaul Compound to set up shop, something about ogres. Since you\'re done here, might as well head over...I woundn\'t keep a goblin like her waiting.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve got a great one for you this time, $N. We\'re gonna initiate these ogres into the Horde...working directly under us.' WHERE `entry`=24905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm, mostly usable. This is good stuff. I\'ve already got buyers lined up, of course. Here\'s your advance for the rest of the work you\'re gonna do for me and the Bilgewater Cartel...partner.' WHERE `entry`=24906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Property values have already gone up since you left. People like seafront views that don\'t include briny, gnarled giants stomping around. Here\'s your cut, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Isn\'t it nice when you can do a good deed, and see enormous future financial gains from it? It warms my little goblin heart. And my big goblin wallet. You did great, kid. Gadgetzan\'s gonna be ours soon. Here\'s a little token of my appreciation.' WHERE `entry`=24910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey Hol\'anyee, look at the getup on this one! Ahem. Our recruiter sent you?  Good. Let\'s start out with a bit of honesty: Un\'Goro isn\'t the perfect nirvana that you may have been promised. You\'ve probably figured that out on the way over here, though. Shall we get to work?' WHERE `entry`=24911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Stand Clear, $C, and steady yourself.' WHERE `entry`=24912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am moved, $N. Prophet Velen has been in closely guarded seclusion. He has dared not waste his energy on anything save preparing for the final confrontation he has foretold. And yet, he came here, in person, to comfort a single dying soul. I must thank you as well, for helping me make my last effort to comfort my friend. My research will continue... and I hope that Magtoor will continue to watch over me.' WHERE `entry`=24913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Bring the Sealed Chest to Highlord Darion Mograine in Icecrown Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=24914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Impossible... Father, is it you?! You have done me a great service, hero. I offer you the reins of my faithful steed. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What... how did you manage to come by this!? You have done me a great service, hero. My heart could not bear to keep this locket, but I will place an enchantment upon it that you may find useful. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aye. I know this blade... and I will treasure it always - a moment of time that will be lost forever. You have done me a great service, hero. I offer you a gift from the Frostborn dwarves. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24917;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Sylvanas silently reflects for a moment before returning her gaze to you.>$B$BYou have done me a great service, hero. I offer you the boon of the Banshee Queen. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Uther stares at the medal, speechless for a moment.>$B$BArthas\' medal.$B$BI remember well the day I presented it to him...$B$BYou have done me a great service, hero. My soul may now rest in peace. I offer you a memory lost in time. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24919;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. Almost everybody managed to make it through.' WHERE `entry`=24920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hm? What unit are you with, $C? No matter, we need all hands. My fleet is in tatters and they\'ve broken into the hold. You armed? That\'s good enough for me.' WHERE `entry`=24921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N? What are you doing wearing that pygmy helm? Looks like it\'s about to fall apart. I\'m glad that they sent you up here. I thought for sure they were going to send that jerk, Grapplehammer and his ego-enabling assistant.' WHERE `entry`=24924;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great job, but that\'s not even half of the hostages that they took from town. Darn it all! They must have taken the rest of the captives to their other villages up in the volcano!' WHERE `entry`=24925;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='She decided to stay?  Fascinating... I\'ll have to look over this data and find out why. Thank you again, $N. I really appreciate it.' WHERE `entry`=24926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m pleased to report that our brand recognition in this area has skyrocketed now that you\'ve killed most of the people who didn\'t want us here.' WHERE `entry`=24927;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful job. Have you ever thought about becoming a full-time arsonist? I know a few people, it\'s a nice gig. Well, we\'ll chit-chat about that one later. More to do here!' WHERE `entry`=24928;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, bud! Hope he wasn\'t too tough.' WHERE `entry`=24929;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If I hadn\'t seen you kill a few of the mangy things with my own eyes, I\'d think you did not complete the task I asked of you. It looks like we\'re hardly putting a dent in their numbers.' WHERE `entry`=24930;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, perfect! Just what I need...full of potent focusing energies... ...ahem! I mean, perfect for my collection! Narain Soothfancy is in no need of artificial enhancement of any kind! Now take your pay and be off!' WHERE `entry`=24931;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This isn\'t goin\' fast enough. There\'s gotta be a faster way...' WHERE `entry`=24932;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Man, this stuff looks delicious. I\'m half tempted to just fry some up myself. No! We\'ve gotta focus on gettin\' out of here. Maybe just one piece...' WHERE `entry`=24933;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You make a hell of a marine, $N. We\'ll mop up the others. But it looks like the Horde fleet is disengaging - maybe to land more troops ashore? Admiral Aubrey will know what to do. Talk to me when you\'re ready to fly back!' WHERE `entry`=24934;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They turned some of our people into zombies? Tell me something I don\'t know....' WHERE `entry`=24937;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aubrey sent you? Good! I take it you know your way around a cannon?' WHERE `entry`=24938;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ho ho! The beach is ours! We just might keep a foothold on this miserable dustball of a continent after all.' WHERE `entry`=24939;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My star player has arrived!' WHERE `entry`=24940;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde is massing at the base of the hill. Breathlessly, you stuff the debris you collected into the muzzle of the cannon, step back, cover one ear, and tug on the igniter cord...' WHERE `entry`=24941;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it! No more zombies to worry about. Let\'s pause a moment in silence for the stinky departed. Okay, done.' WHERE `entry`=24942;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work! We\'ve knocked them on their heels, maybe long enough to shore up our defenses. Provided we find a way to take out their artillery...' WHERE `entry`=24943;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A steady stream of the walking wounded have come up the hill to see me, $N. I trust that was your work? Well done!' WHERE `entry`=24944;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I gotta tell you, that\'s a load off of my mind. That is, I won\'t have to worry about no new zombies coming after my brains!' WHERE `entry`=24945;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This will do. In fact, it\'s more than we need. I devised an ingenious idea for a weapon that the boots will be turned into once you get them to Hobart. Hand the powder over and I\'ll load it into the the Super Booster Rocket Boots.' WHERE `entry`=24946;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good thing you\'re here! I\'m gonna need a lot of help if we want to beat these gnomes to the punch.' WHERE `entry`=24947;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good! Without heavy equipment, the Horde will have to pull back to regroup. We\'ve bought ourselves some time to re-secure the fortress. Well done!' WHERE `entry`=24948;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Beautiful! And to think these idiots were just sitting on it. Here\'s a bit up front, we\'ll talk about profit-sharing bonuses later.' WHERE `entry`=24949;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sea giants? You think he was training them towards Gadgetzan on purpose? Whatever, he\'s splitsville now. And Gadgetzan owes us big time! I can\'t wait to see the look on Marin\'s face. Here\'s your cut, babe. You\'re moving up in the world.' WHERE `entry`=24950;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at the size of it! It\'s glorious. This ugly sucker\'s gonna help us bring down the whole hive.' WHERE `entry`=24951;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There\'s no time to waste, boy! What\'s wrong with the actuator on the left boot?!' WHERE `entry`=24952;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh man, that was awesome! You should\'ve seen the flames coming out of the hive! Here\'s your reward, for entertaining me as much as for clearing the hive!' WHERE `entry`=24953;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Careful with those glands, $N, careful! And now to load them into the refashioned shredder boot. I\'m certain that you\'ll be surprised and amazed by my genius invention.' WHERE `entry`=24954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, nice work! I\'m amazed you even got them to hold a pen without eating it. You can uh, just throw the suit over there. Away from me. In the fire.' WHERE `entry`=24955;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Rageroar\'s battleships intercepted our vessel as we fled from Gilneas. We were to be carried here as trophies to the Warchief. As we neared the shore, some of us fought back. Rageroar - he began killing indiscriminately - howling with laughter. Our ship capsized and he ordered his men to fire at us as we drowned. Few of us made it to land. Afterwards, I learned that he wore my brother\'s scalp as... as a trophy.' WHERE `entry`=24956;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ugh! This entire camp is like a sampler course of awful smells. Let\'s not handle these things any longer than we have to.' WHERE `entry`=24957;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I managed to get everyone else safely back to town. Jump in, we gotta get out of here before the volcano blows for good!!!' WHERE `entry`=24958;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello there. You must be... $N?' WHERE `entry`=24959;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $C. As you can see, not all of us have resigned to our fates. I\'m glad to see that you\'re at least willing to work. Valdred will be a valuable asset to the Forsaken. As for the other two... there is not much we can do. We cannot force them to join us.' WHERE `entry`=24960;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You say she ran away?  What a shame. Very well. As long as she\'s maintained her free will, there\'s still hope.' WHERE `entry`=24961;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will be here to train you as you grow in experience... find me as often as you like. I charge a minimal fee, but you\'ll find everything I can teach you to be worthwhile. Go now and test your skill. Many more things will become known to you as you gain experience, some of which I am unable to discuss with you here. Just know that Sylvanas will need hunters with your type of cunning in the future. You will be the backbone of our salvation. Do not forget it.' WHERE `entry`=24962;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job, you\'ve taught half the ogres here to fear and respect anything vaguely $R-shaped. It\'s amazing what a little reward will do to keep people under your thumb, isn\'t it? Here\'s your payment, by the way. ...what\'s with that look?' WHERE `entry`=24963;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'ve been told that I\'m supposed to train you how to be a hunter. That\'s all well and good, but in my opinion, you\'ll get more training out in the field than you will talking about theories with me.$B$BI suppose I can show you a couple of my tricks. Here, come take a look at this...',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Steady Shot from Xavier the Huntsman in Deathknell, then practice using Steady Shot 5 times on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You seem to be somewhat of a natural, $N. This is good. I can\'t teach you everything myself. Go, practice what we\'ve discussed today. Return when you\'re stronger, and we\'ll cover some more tricks and abilities.' WHERE `entry`=24964;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Let\'s get some work done, shall we?  I\'ve got a new spell for you. You interested?$B$BThis spell won\'t work like anything you\'ve previously learned. Each time you cast another spell, there\'s a chance you\'ll have an opening to cast Arcane Missiles.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Isabella in Deathknell, then practice using Arcane Missiles 2 times against a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve got to admit, the spell I just taught you probably won\'t increase your intellect severalfold. That was a lie to get you to buy my services. But it will still be a helpful spell for you and your allies. No hard feelings!' WHERE `entry`=24965;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='A Forsaken priest is a curious beast,$B$G his: her; path an unusual course.$B$G His: Her; shadowy rites cannot come from the Light, so $G he: she; seeks a more sinister source.$B$BNot only has the world forsaken us, $N... it seems the Light has left us as well. As the poem hints, however... we are not without power.$B$BFirst, I shall teach you a fast heal to repair damage. Speak with me again, and I will share with you the word\'s proper incantation.',`objectives_loc1`='Train Flash Heal from Dark Cleric Duesten in Deathknell. Then, practice casting Flash Heal 5 times on Wounded Deathguards.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re a good student, $N. You\'ll go far. If you ever need any further training, return to me and I\'ll happily oblige.' WHERE `entry`=24966;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='As you continue your career as a warlock, you\'ll find it helpful to keep your spellbook filled with the latest incantations. Lucky for you, I know these spells, and I\'m willing to train you... for a price.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Immolate from Maximillion in Deathknell, then practice casting Immolate 5 times on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Congratulations... you\'re one step closer to being a master of the dark arts. Go practice a bit, and return when you\'re stronger. I\'ll have more to teach you then.' WHERE `entry`=24968;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='If you want to become a stronger warrior, you\'ll need to work on your weapons. You\'ll find stronger swords and larger shields out on your adventures, that I have no doubt about. However, as a warrior you also shouldn\'t forget your legs. $B$BTrain with me, $N, and I\'ll show you how to move quickly around the battlefield. You care to learn?',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Charge from Dannal Stern in Deathknell, then practice using Charge on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have the makings of a great $C, $N. Go, practice what we\'ve discussed, and return when you are stronger. Then I may have more to teach you.' WHERE `entry`=24969;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N. You made it. You see those tents up there?  That\'s where we\'re headed. The battle\'s probably already started.' WHERE `entry`=24970;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Being born again under the power of a val\'kyr is a strenuous process. Many don\'t survive the shock, turning into zombies or ghouls. Others retain just enough humanity to seem normal on the outside... but they\'re sick inside. We should have slain those rotbrains the day they were raised. As for you... you\'re a strong $C, $N. I knew you\'d do well. You\'ll be headed out of Deathknell soon.' WHERE `entry`=24971;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, this is very good. You\'ve done well in obtaining this information, $N. Hmm... names of the Scarlet Crusade officers in the Tirisfal Glades... Imagine the blow we could deal to the morale of those bloody zealots if we were to kill their leaders in one swift strike. I will pass this information forward.' WHERE `entry`=24972;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, it\'s a start. It\'ll take a few weeks or months to fully clean out the infestation. After that, we\'ll have to get down there with some torches to burn away the webbing. You\'ve done your duty well, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24973;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, look at him!  Isn\'t he the most adorable thing you\'ve ever seen?  Thank you, $N. I feel more energetic already.' WHERE `entry`=24974;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have performed your bidding well, young $C. You are proving yourself to be quite an asset to The Dark Lady\'s army.' WHERE `entry`=24975;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. Now comes the fun part.' WHERE `entry`=24976;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='By the Light!  Finally some food!  Sweet, sweet pumpkin. . . .' WHERE `entry`=24977;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve the makings of a mighty $C, $R. I heard the cries of those humans from all the way over here. Perhaps soon we will be rid of this human blight.' WHERE `entry`=24978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Scarlet Crusade takes no prisoners. That they would do so with this young woman... curious. The powers that you describe are even curiouser. She passed through the bars of her prison and killed her captor?  Why hadn\'t she done that in the first place?' WHERE `entry`=24979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most excellent, $C. Your skill in the art of combat is undeniable.' WHERE `entry`=24980;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It sounds like we\'ll have to keep our eyes out for this Voss character. I don\'t expect any Forsaken to receive a reward if we capture her... I\'m just worried she\'ll eventually turn against us.' WHERE `entry`=24981;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, I\'m Brill\'s local magistrate, reporting directly to the Dark Lady. Impress me, and you may end up meeting the Banshee Queen herself. Now, onto your first task...' WHERE `entry`=24982;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Magistrate Sevren wants a report? Very well: the defenders at The Bulwark are holding the majority of the Scourge at bay, but some do slip through on occasion.$B$BWe have seen sporadic Scourge activity east of this station, with a concentration around the Balnir Farmstead.' WHERE `entry`=24983;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Long ago, the mage Gunther Arcanus, along with Bethor Iceshard and the now-Scourge Necromancer Thule Ravenclaw, were friends and students within the Kirin Tor - a society of mages in Dalaran.$B$BGunther fell to the Plague, but we thought he either remained dead, or was raised into the ranks of the Lich King. We now know he is free.$B$BWe must have him. If you travel east, you will find him on an island in Brightwater Lake. Convince him to join our ranks.',`objectives_loc1`='Report to Gunther Arcanus at Gunther\'s Retreat in Tirisfal Glades.' WHERE `entry`=24984;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I appreciate your efforts, $N. May Sylvanas recognize your bravery one day. . . .' WHERE `entry`=24988;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is troubling to hear of the Scourge slipping past the Bulwark. Even now, they are ceaseless in their assaults. But we will not give in. The Lich King is dead; we will not be taken again!' WHERE `entry`=24989;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $N and I thank you for your efforts.' WHERE `entry`=24990;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Holland?  He\'s an amateur. You don\'t need a fancy two-story apothecarium to make plague... you need love. And maybe some good assistants. Let me show you how plague is REALLY made.' WHERE `entry`=24991;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... yes, that makes sense. Since the worgen have come streaming out of Gilneas, I knew it would only be a matter of time before they arrived here in Tirisfal.' WHERE `entry`=24992;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='To think, they\'ve been right under our noses!  I\'ll put my deathguards on alert... this will NOT happen again.' WHERE `entry`=24993;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Collect 10 Doom Weed.',`objectives_loc1`='Collect 10 Doom Weed.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, my doom weed. Excellent! These will come in quite handy. You\'ve done me, uh, the Lady, a fine service today, $N. As promised, here is the reward that you deserve.' WHERE `entry`=24994;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The scales are perfect, $N. Exactly what I needed for this concoction.' WHERE `entry`=24995;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, a drink at last. What matter of ale is this?  I\'m sure it\'s no Rhapsody Malt but I\'ll take anything to wet the old whistle at this point.' WHERE `entry`=24996;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Expertly done, $N. The Scourge are mistaken if they think they can use those corpses against us, and the fluid you gathered from the Rot Hide slaves will be studied by my master. It may have secrets we can use against them.' WHERE `entry`=24997;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work!  Now if only I can convince Jerrod to let us move our operation into that shack...' WHERE `entry`=24998;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did they run from you, $N?  Good. This is better than killing them... if they live to tell the tale, then future generations of murlocs will learn to fear us.' WHERE `entry`=24999;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, you\'re tougher than you look. These terrortooth hides reflect arrows and turn axe-blades - they don\'t go down easy, but their hides are worth their weight in silver in these light-forsaken Barrens. Nice work.' WHERE `entry`=25000;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And that\'s a wrap! Nothing left here for us but sand. Good job, babe. Well, maybe I shouldn\'t be so hasty. Did you find anything in that ogre den?' WHERE `entry`=25001;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My supplies! Well, that showed some real initiative, $C. Those rap-saws or whatever they\'re called have torn lesser men to ribbons. Thank you!' WHERE `entry`=25002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your actions struck a telling blow against the Scourge. And your victory will not go unnoticed - not by the Forsaken, nor by our enemies. Continue the struggle as we all do, $N, and one day the Forsaken will have the dominion over Azeroth that they are owed!' WHERE `entry`=25003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your efforts are appreciated, $N. I will not thank you for doing what is necessary, but I will remember your name.' WHERE `entry`=25004;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Devlin Agamand?  Is that him you carry in your sack there?  Ha! Yes, I know what Coleman wants to try, and I want to try it too. I hope you\'re prepared, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25005;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, how unfortunate. Perhaps the Scourge\'s dominion over Devlin\'s mind remained too strong. Or perhaps our methods are simply not strong enough. It\'s also possible that Devlin was too simple-minded to comprehend what we were asking him.' WHERE `entry`=25006;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Not much of a $C, are you?  Well, you will be when I\'m done with you.' WHERE `entry`=25007;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ooooo-oooh aye! The best Hecklefangs are the dead ones.' WHERE `entry`=25008;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your actions will slow down the Scarlet Crusade\'s advancement in Tirisfal quite a bit... hopefully for good. But other threats loom.' WHERE `entry`=25009;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As you look over the ruins of the camp, you hear a whisper behind you. <"I could kill you right now if I wanted to. You\'d better watch your step, $R.">' WHERE `entry`=25010;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sure, I\'ll give you a ride. If High Executor Derrington asks for it, then technically I have to.' WHERE `entry`=25011;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome back, $N. I\'ve heard stories from the east. Who would have thought that a young $R $C like you would have been the one to wipe out the last whimpering remnants of the Scarlet Crusade?' WHERE `entry`=25012;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, this venom will do perfectly, $N. Everything else has been added to my concoction and boiled down. Thank you, $C!' WHERE `entry`=25013;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found that in the ogre den? That\'s... ...nothing to get excited about, I\'m sure! I\'m sure it\'s just...a perfectly benign trinket...that I\'m going to give you precisely detailed instructions on exactly how to handle. Keep your voice down and don\'t wave that thing around.' WHERE `entry`=25014;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' So, this is what the quilboar are using against us? Do you think they used these to create this jungle?' WHERE `entry`=25015;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. We would be hard pressed to face such enemies without your assistance.' WHERE `entry`=25017;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Of all the...you found this in an ogre den? Unthinkable. I\'m amazed they didn\'t try to smash it to pieces. With any luck, $C, we\'ll be able to obtain even more fascinating antiquities here...if you\'re willing to help.' WHERE `entry`=25018;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. The less interference from the Alliance, the better.' WHERE `entry`=25019;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. With that dealt with, we can focus our attentions fully on exploring the gateway.' WHERE `entry`=25020;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Dey drink de blood, dey get de power. I drink dere blood...' WHERE `entry`=25021;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work. Gaines passed through here not long ago on his way to Northwatch and a warm bath. The mission wasn\'t a total loss, though. We\'ve learned a good deal about these quilboar and their leadership structure. Now we can handle things ... MY way.' WHERE `entry`=25022;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I told you we would meet again, $N. Unfortunate that it\'s under such dire circumstances.' WHERE `entry`=25023;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve not seen a finer display of $C prowess.' WHERE `entry`=25024;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Didn\'t like ya much, eh? More in this world craves blood than just trolls, mon. Let\'s find the other blade...' WHERE `entry`=25025;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Jang\'thraze eludes me, mon...de blood is not enough. We gonna need somethin\' stronger to find it.$B$BWhen you need every troll you got to help out to scrape by, one o\' them dyin\' on ya is a big problem, mon, an\' dat\'s why de Sandfury learned to raise our dead wit\' da voodoo. You fall over, you just get back up again and keep workin...forever!$B$BDe zombies we make be imbued wit\' darkest mojo. You go on to de west an\' find a whole mess o\' dem, an\' get me dat mojo, yah?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Powerful stuff, mon...ah, if ya could see what I see now...mebbe you go try it yaself sometime. The spirits call...' WHERE `entry`=25026;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='...Torn limb from limb!? Well, I\'d almost feel bad but the burning hatred gets in the way. She got what she deserved. Problem solved.' WHERE `entry`=25027;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, samples from different parts of the overgrowth? These will be immensely helpful, yes. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25028;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Revenge has a sweet taste, don\'t you think? When you destroyed the Agamands, did you catch any hint of free will within them? I hope so. I hope they knew fear before they were smashed into oblivion.$B$BIt is a foolish hope, I know. But it is a hope I foster nonetheless.' WHERE `entry`=25029;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Is this Dargol?  He was vicious even in life, with a temper that bit deep and a blade that bit deeper. Undeath has not done him any favors, though it suits his personality. Yes, this was certainly Dargol. I can sense his malice, even from the remains you\'ve fetched. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25030;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Argh!  Get back!  Oh, you\'re not Scourge, are you? Thank the Banshee Queen that you\'re here. I\'ve greatly underestimated how bad it\'s gotten up here.' WHERE `entry`=25031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mazoga? He\'s taken the sword? That filthy... At least you escaped with your life. The Lasher\'s bite is a vicious one.' WHERE `entry`=25032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kill Meven Korgal, the messenger, at the Crusader camp, and obtain any information you can find.' WHERE `entry`=25033;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, $N! I\'ve been talking you up to the General here. Thank you again for saving my life.' WHERE `entry`=25034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to have ya, brotha. Vol\'jin makes us all proud in dese moments. It feels good ta be tacklin\' threats head on.' WHERE `entry`=25035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, Paxton says there\'s no jungle in the Barrens? What do you call THIS!? I\'ve got a pile of supplies to move to the interior and my camp has been overrun by a forest that - I swear - grows by the hour!' WHERE `entry`=25036;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oi! Tasty, mon. Thank ya for your great kindness, young one. Da spirits shall surely be regardin\' ya with great favor.' WHERE `entry`=25037;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Master want weeds. Us gots big hands and not good at picking. You help us and we not hurt you. Us need gloom weed. Many weeds around here and near road.$B$BWhen you have gloom weed you take to Master Holland in Brill.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'s this? Gloom weed?! I\'ve no need for gloom weed! That mindless mass of flesh is out there picking daisies and convincing the Lady knows how many dupes like you into doing the same. No offense. We\'ll deal with the gloom weed later. For now, we\'ve got other matters to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=25038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work! How was it? Did you enjoy the hunt? Did you run through tall grasses, the scent of your prey urging you forward, until you leapt at its throat, adrenaline surging as your slavering fangs... Well, something like that.' WHERE `entry`=25041;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oh yeah... oh ... YES! I\'ll have mine raw. I suppose I can grill some up for the others... How would you like yours?' WHERE `entry`=25042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good. We may never drive the Horde completely from these lands, but with a strong presence we can undermine their will to fight.' WHERE `entry`=25043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I have not forgotten my brush with death at the hands of the quilboar in that filthy jungle. The General here has ordered some tactical strikes, but he stops short of genocide. I have no such qualms.$B$BTake this horn that I \'borrowed\' during my negotiations. Blow the horn within the Bristleback challenge ring west of our position - you can\'t miss it. I want you to challenge the champion of the Bristleback, Sabersnout, to single combat. His death in front of his followers will leave them in utter chaos.',`objectives_loc1`='Take the Horn of Challenge to the Bristleback Challenge Ring in Southern Barrens. Blow the horn to challenge Sabersnout and kill him.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='A "Boarpocalypse," you say? These animals certainly have a unique idea of "Single combat!" No matter, you\'ve done well. With the quilboar in chaos I should have no trouble convincing the field commanders to execute any strays they find scurrying about. The General need not know we\'ve stepped up the campaign... it\'s for the better.' WHERE `entry`=25044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your report, $C? Incredible, $N! You\'re a real asset to the Alliance. I\'ll see to it that my men follow your example!' WHERE `entry`=25045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='From birth to grave to undeath, we all have our own path to follow. Some are easier than others. It sounds like this Voss girl has had a rough path so far. Hopefully she ultimately chooses to join us and follow the Dark Lady. With power like hers, we could do incredible things. By the way, $N... excellent work out there. If you\'re ever ready and willing, I may have some more work for you in the Plaguelands.' WHERE `entry`=25046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This badly broken figurine was discarded by its last owner. However, with the right materials and your skill in jewelcrafting, it could be completely restored.' WHERE `entry`=25047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most of this looks just fine! How lucky! The Steamwheedle goblins will be so happy to see their cargo back safe and sound. And here\'s a reward for your good deeds, of course! We\'ve got lots of other stuff to do though! Busy busy!' WHERE `entry`=25048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, it\'s going to be so much nicer around here now that they\'re gone! At least until more show up. But thank you!' WHERE `entry`=25049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That was great! It looks like most of the goblins we helped made it back here and didn\'t blow up. We really showed that goblin girl! Here\'s a special reward for you, mister.' WHERE `entry`=25050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is a great relief, $C. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job! We\'re really cleaning up around here!' WHERE `entry`=25052;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Isn\'t that just so pretty to watch?' WHERE `entry`=25053;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It\'s just really so wasteful that all these pirates have golden treasures laying around. Some of this stuff could be used for practical things! Like melting into wire, or intrinsic shielding matrices, or selling to other stupid races that buy gold just to keep it around.$B$BAnd speaking of other stupid races, I bet those greedy goblins are going to be taking all of it. We can\'t let that happen! Go collect that treasure for Gnomeregan!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fantastic! Gosh, this will make enough wire for an entire army. Lucky us!' WHERE `entry`=25054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The elements are restless, $C. The earthquakes that plague the land and threaten to collapse Ironforge are not normal. The Earthen Ring are convinced that we must put the elements to rest before they tear Azeroth apart. We need your help, $N.$B$BI will give you a bag of Earthen Ring supplies. In it you will find two items, elemental sapta and a cleansing totem. Use the sapta to see into the elemental world. Then use the cleansing totem to subdue the agitated earth spirits.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done $N. But for every element that is subdued another one takes it\'s place. The solution we have here is merely a stopgap. Hopefully my brethren in the Earthen Ring are making more headway.' WHERE `entry`=25055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dithers, you\'ve done it again!  These are perfect.' WHERE `entry`=25056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. Several of the looters have already crawled back, requesting clemency. I\'ll let them stew for a bit in the Northwatch brig. Thank you for helping maintain discipline in the ranks. It is important for our army to be perceived as soldiers, not common bandits.' WHERE `entry`=25057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Score one for the goblins! Stupid dwarves and gnomes.' WHERE `entry`=25058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What have you dug up for me? Hmm. Interesting. This notice from Orgrimmar indicates a change in Horde leadership is underway - I guess heads are going to roll after what we did to Taurajo. What\'s this? A death warrant for the General here! This is good to know... Very good to know...' WHERE `entry`=25059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We received reports that a goblin shipwreck occured on this beach some time ago, with the survivors left to fend for themselves. We expected there to be a modicum of survivors, perhaps some even suitable for interrogation.$B$BWhat we found was a crew of Bilgewater goblins who have all become insane, delusional, and maniacally violent...to further degrees than is normally observed, rather.$B$BIn short, they are useless and dangerous. Gnomeregan will be best served by cutting down as many as we can.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 10 Crazed Survivors.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your reports of their behavior are truly disturbing...but also slightly amusing. If only that Dreadshredder wench had escaped on these vessels instead...' WHERE `entry`=25060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m amazed that Soothfancy was capable of following a simple set of instructions. And ones that required him to keep his foolish mouth silenced as well. In addition, it is honestly good to see you again, $N. Now that I\'ve dropped the charade, you\'ll get to see how gnomes get things done around here.' WHERE `entry`=25061;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Gnomeregan previously learned that the Bilgewater goblins of the Horde survived a crash on an uncharted island near Kalmidor before arriving in Durotar. We initially came here to investigate what techniques and technology could possibly allow a hopeless pack of green-skinned imbeciles to survive such harsh conditions.$B$BWhile the goblins are at a loss, we still need to find out exactly what happened here. Search the beach for wreckage and belongings and bring anything that appears significant back to me.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'m trying not to laugh. This is classic. They have no idea they\'re even on Kalimdor! These later pages though...something more significant may be occuring here.' WHERE `entry`=25062;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, gosh, this day just keeps getting better and better! I may actually smile. When you\'re not looking. You\'ve seen enough of that already.' WHERE `entry`=25063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey there, hon. Vol\'jin sent you? So sweet of him to be thinkin\' of me. I surely could use da help, but ya have a bit more walkin\' ahead of ya.' WHERE `entry`=25064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. The contents of this chest are sure to advance Gnomeregan\'s knowledge base significantly. I believe you\'ve earned a reward.' WHERE `entry`=25065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='An impressive start. Be prepared for more.' WHERE `entry`=25067;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Marvelous. To think the shapers of our world crafted these...' WHERE `entry`=25068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This chest lies undisturbed, sealed for thousands of years.' WHERE `entry`=25069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The chest now grinds open again, the rest of the antechamber fallen silent.' WHERE `entry`=25070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for the help, this was really killin\' things here. Once you start losing men, you start losing manpower. And morale. And weapons. And the magazines you loaned to that one guy. You know how it is.' WHERE `entry`=25072;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, young $R. Ya come highly recommended, mon. It\'s nice ta finally be meetin\' ya in person.' WHERE `entry`=25073;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you heard? The General never made it! Killed in the field, like some kind of dog!' WHERE `entry`=25074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oohh look! A mostly complete exhaust manifold, a reciprocating junction box, a working counterweight slip differential ... you sure know your junk, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You have spent your young career mastering the arts of single combat. I feel it is high time that you learned a new form of combat - that of the trained pet.$B$BTake this rod and use it on a vampiric duskbat until it joins you and your cause. It may take you some time, but I have faith that you can bend the bat to your will.',`objectives_loc1`='Use the Taming Rod to befriend a Vampiric Duskbat.' WHERE `entry`=25076;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Lately we have seen some young, plagued bears passing over the mountains between here and the plaguelands. While these bears\' trek into Tirisfal tests and threatens the defenses that we have laid at the Bulwark, their passage is a blessing to us hunters.$B$BProve to me you learned something from our last lesson, and use the rod on a plagued bruin, far to the east.',`objectives_loc1`='Use the Taming Rod to befriend a Plagued Bruin.' WHERE `entry`=25077;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Your final test involves the spiders that reside in Venomweb Vale, north of the Bulwark. Yes, even these simple creatures can become a valuable trained ally. I have seen many hunters that count these venomous creatures as part of their arsenal.$B$BUse the rod to tame one, and return to me when you finish.',`objectives_loc1`='Use the Taming Rod to befriend a Vicious Night Web Spider.' WHERE `entry`=25078;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great! Set the keg down right here. I\'ll measure out some charges once I\'ve donned my full-body protective gear.' WHERE `entry`=25079;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oh, OH! That\'s nasty! I love it!' WHERE `entry`=25080;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Incredible work, $N! My men report a breakthrough. Their stronghold won\'t survive much longer...' WHERE `entry`=25081;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That oughta take care of our bug problem for a while - they\'ll be hard-pressed to tunnel their way outta that!' WHERE `entry`=25082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve my thanks, if not that of the entire Earthen Ring. Maybe someday we\'ll find a way to talk it out with these pigs, but we can\'t heal the land if we\'re dead in our sleep.' WHERE `entry`=25084;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a relief. Maybe the rest of \'em will keep to their own devices now. The less fighting around here, the better.' WHERE `entry`=25085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What? Little Logan thinks I might need protection? It\'s me doing the protectin\'! The quilboar here are poised to rampage. They\'ve choked off the entire south, and we\'re the only thing standing in their way.' WHERE `entry`=25086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Quite a name you\'re earning for yourself here in the Barrens, $N. But Roberts isn\'t going far enough. What we need is a decisive victory...' WHERE `entry`=25087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Those val\'kyr have been really busy resurrecting you newbies lately. I\'ve already seen a couple dozen new bodies run down that hill since this morning. You, however, are the most promising $C I\'ve seen today.' WHERE `entry`=25089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. I enjoyed watching you smash those $R into rotting pulp!' WHERE `entry`=25090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Marin sent you? I\'m appreciative of his help. I\'m here to seek out Sul\'thraze. If you wish to help, speak with Mazoga...he\'s been cooperative so far.' WHERE `entry`=25091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done $N. But for every element that is subdued another one takes it\'s place. The solution we have here is merely a stopgap. Hopefully my brethren in the Earthen Ring are making more headway.' WHERE `entry`=25092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. The spirits of the fallen can now be put to rest.' WHERE `entry`=25093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad. You\'ve got a ways to go, however.' WHERE `entry`=25094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Rather impressive. Few can bear to see a silithid reaver face to face, let alone defeat it.' WHERE `entry`=25095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Once again you have helped us to overcome our mutual enemy, the Alliance. Now it is time for us to help you.' WHERE `entry`=25098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Of course you can borrow Bastia. That is, if she\'ll take you.' WHERE `entry`=25099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N?! Nice kitty. Look we don\'t have much time here. You might have noticed that the volcano is blowing?!' WHERE `entry`=25100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thought you might be responsible for them clouds of dust I saw to the east. Nice work! Them bulls ain\'t sissies.' WHERE `entry`=25102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re with Megs, huh? Word is she\'s been pretty hell-bent on making nice with Noggenfogger. Not like I care. Are you ready to kill some bugs?' WHERE `entry`=25103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Father sent you? He worries too much. There\'s nothing here I can\'t handle... But I\'d still appreciate the help.' WHERE `entry`=25104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Lila\'s pet Nibbler got into my workshop again!$B$BI was making a bracelet, to be delivered today. The work was almost done, except for the gems. I spent all night cutting them, but when I stepped out for a bit of breakfast, the little beast came into my workshop and swallowed every gem in sight!  The thing can digest ANYTHING, and trust me, you\'d break your back trying to pick up its leavings.$B$BI need to get replacement gems fast; the courier is coming in tonight. Help!',`objectives_loc1`='Cut three Solid Zephyrites and give them to Isabel Jones in Stormwind City.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve really saved my skin, $N. Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=25105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My father would be proud of you, $N. Now, to get this flying machine up and about again...' WHERE `entry`=25106;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is truly incredible. The hieroglyphs are undoubtedly titan, but the markings below it... Some of these characters resemble ancient Kaldorei writings. And you say the antechamber was covered in hieroglyphs? You\'ve made a find more monumental than any riches, $N. Please, take whatever reward you prefer.' WHERE `entry`=25107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Aye, it\'s for the best I suppose.' WHERE `entry`=25108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Huh... what? Who?' WHERE `entry`=25109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Alchemists pay through the nose for these things. Sure, maybe I tell some of them they\'re dragon parts, but that ain\'t my problem, right?' WHERE `entry`=25111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice going, kid. Didn\'t lose any fingers? Good, we can get some more work for you then.' WHERE `entry`=25112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Beautiful! We\'ll have these puppies shined up and ready to sell in no time.' WHERE `entry`=25115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll rest easier knowing one of those lumbering things won\'t be wandering into my bedroom at night... again. Thanks much.' WHERE `entry`=25118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hi there! The fun\'s already started!' WHERE `entry`=25121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hate the Trade Prince, but you can\'t argue with the results of his methods. Kaja\'Cola Zero-One is a huge improvement over regular old Kaja\'Cola at half the calories and twice the ideas!' WHERE `entry`=25122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Gobber\'s mind freed',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Other goblin\'s minds freed' WHERE `entry`=25122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your soulstone has expired, Blastshadow!' WHERE `entry`=25123;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks a little rickety....' WHERE `entry`=25125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmmm, not bad, $N. But don\'t let it get to your head...you\'ll fight tougher than boars in your career.$B$BNonetheless, you\'ve proven yourself well, and your next trial will be against a considerably more dangerous opponent, so you\'ll need some extra protection.' WHERE `entry`=25126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is an important lesson that you must take away from fighting scorpids. The smallest or largest of opponents can still send you to your doom. In fierce combat, any number of things can prove your downfall.$B$BI have no more to teach you, $N. You have done well, and I will watch your progress with interest.' WHERE `entry`=25127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My blow was not enough to kill him, but looking at the damage I inflicted gives me some small measure of pride. That small measure will be all I have to sustain myself if I die, and in that light, the short list of my life\'s accomplishments fills me with anger.' WHERE `entry`=25129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='From your description of the beast, I believe you must be speaking of Sarkoth! It is no wonder that Hana\'zua was overtaken by it. Aid will be dispatched to him immediately, trouble yourself no more with Hana\'zua\'s plight.$B$BHowever, I must say, I am most impressed to hear that you brought Sarkoth to death. It is a feat to be proud of, $N. And that you would fight for a stranger\'s honor, while other tasks occupied your time, your own honor is heightened.' WHERE `entry`=25130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $N.$B$BAlthough the Vile Familiars were merely pets of the darker powers within the Burning Blade, your success against them foretells greater deeds ahead.' WHERE `entry`=25131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Slay 7 Felstalkers and obtain the Burning Blade Medallion.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You retrieved it! Well done!$B$BYour efforts within the Burning Blade Coven are key in rooting out this cult in the Valley of Trials. But I fear they have further aims in our land.$B$BWe have not seen the end of them.' WHERE `entry`=25132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hm... your report comes at a bad time. The Burning Blade is no longer seen here in Sen\'jin, but we will be vigilant in our efforts to prevent their return to the area. The orcs are friends of the Darkspear Trolls. Honorable friends. We want to help the orcs, but... we need help too.' WHERE `entry`=25133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. Maybe they\'ll think twice before slacking next time!  Thanks for the help!' WHERE `entry`=25134;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great, you got it! Thanks a lot, $N. This is my favorite pick! Now if my peons ever finish chopping down these trees, maybe we can find a nice cave to mine!' WHERE `entry`=25135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful, $N! As promised, here is your cactus apple surprise plus a little something extra.' WHERE `entry`=25136;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, where to start... introductions!  I\'m Acrypha - the one who sent you that parchment - I\'ve spent the last several years in an Undercity library, my head in a book. I learned everything I could about the arcane, and now I\'ve returned home to share it with grunts like yourself. Shall we begin?' WHERE `entry`=25138;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You already know how to fire an arcane shot. Good. But doing so depletes your focus. To gain your focus back you will need to switch to a second type of ranged attack. I can teach it to you.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Steady Shot from Karranisha in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.' WHERE `entry`=25139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Let\'s start with the basics, shall we?  I\'m the only rogue trainer in town, so you\'re going to have to learn it from me.$B$BHere\'s how it\'s going to go: you give me your money, and I\'ll teach you how to finish off a foe. Do we have a deal?',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Eviscerate from Rwag in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice using Eviscerate 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You won\'t be sorry. The ability to capitalize on the opportunities created by previous attacks is one of our greatest strengths.' WHERE `entry`=25141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I will teach you the art of the primal strike. By following these steps, you can deal additional damage to your foes with your weapon. Speak with me again and I will show you the way.$B$BAfter your lessons are complete, practice using the training dummies outside the Den.',`objectives_loc1`='Train Primal Strike from Shikrik in the Valley of Trials. Look for a training dummy near Shikrik and practice using Primal Strike 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very well. Now that you know how to speak with the elements, we will test your bond with them.' WHERE `entry`=25143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It is my duty to train you, and I intend to do just that. Speak with me again and I will show you how to wreathe your opponents in a demonic fire.$B$BOnce your lesson is complete, practice your new spell against one of the training dummies around here.',`objectives_loc1`='Train Immolate from Nartok in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice casting Immolate 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You appear to be a quick learner.' WHERE `entry`=25145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'ve been instructed to prepare you for battle. Though, from the look of you, it looks like you\'ve already spent a little time out in the field. Good.$B$BIt\'s been said that a warriors fight not only with their arms but their legs. You must learn to move quickly around the battlefield .$B$BSpeak to me again, and I will teach you how to charge.',`objectives_loc1`='Train Charge from Frang in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You understand now?  Good, let\'s try it out.' WHERE `entry`=25147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Alright, here\'s the easy part. All you have to do is listen to me. And pay me a little bit of copper.$B$BSpeak with me again and we\'ll teach you the rite of Arcane Missiles. This isn\'t just an ordinary spell, $N. Each time you attack with a spell, you\'ll have a chance to activate Arcane Missiles, so be attentive.$B$B Once your lesson is finished, practice your new spell against a training dummy.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Acrypha in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice using Arcane Missiles 2 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. Now we practice.' WHERE `entry`=25149;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Ah... that\'s the stuff. Ol\' Barkerstout... Thank you, friend. That\'ll make this... a little easier.' WHERE `entry`=25151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Finally, you are of age, $N... of age to battle in the name of the Horde. To conquer for the glory of the Warchief.$B$BYes...$B$B<Kaltunk looks you over.>$B$BYou will do nicely.$B$BNo doubt you wish to find a great dragon or demon and strangle it with your bare hands, but perhaps it would be wise to start on something less... dangerous.$B$B<Kaltunk laughs.>$B$BReport to Gornek, he should be able to assign a task better suited to a young $C. You will find him seated at the fire behind me.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Another one of Kaltunk\'s recruits, hm?$B$BA sorry state of affairs we find ourselves in if this is the best the Horde can produce. No matter. By the time we think you\'re ready to leave the Valley, you\'ll be a proud warrior of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=25152;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re a legend, $N. The other survivors and I will be telling the story of your deeds for years to come.' WHERE `entry`=25153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks!  I\'m sure to beat out that Marith Lazuria in Orgrimmar with these!  I can\'t wait to see the look in her beautiful eye when I give this to her.' WHERE `entry`=25154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your work is as good as it is rumored to be!' WHERE `entry`=25155;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks. Erm. Just set them over there. I need to figure out how to get my hand off of this jarï¿½' WHERE `entry`=25156;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It did what!?  We\'re ruined!  Hmm. Well, actually... Maybe the professor can find some other applications for it?' WHERE `entry`=25157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Lila\'s pet Nibbler got into my workshop again!$B$BI was making a bracelet, to be delivered today. The work was almost done, except for the gems. I spent all night cutting them, but when I stepped out for a bit of breakfast, the little beast came into my workshop and swallowed every gem in sight!  The thing can digest ANYTHING, and trust me, you\'d break your back trying to pick up its leavings.$B$BI need to get replacement gems fast; the courier is coming in tonight. Help!',`objectives_loc1`='Cut three Solid Zephyrites and give them to Marith Lazuria in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve really saved my skin, $N. Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=25158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It did what!?  We\'re ruined!  Hmm. Well, actually... Maybe the doctor can find some other applications for it?' WHERE `entry`=25159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks!  I\'m sure to beat out that Isabela Jones in Stormwind with these!  I can\'t wait to see the look in her beautiful eye when I give this to her.' WHERE `entry`=25160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your work is as good as it is rumored to be!' WHERE `entry`=25161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks. Erm. Just set them over there. I need to figure out how to get my hand off of this jarï¿½' WHERE `entry`=25162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad you were here, mon. Toshe be lookin\' like he wants to chase dem down. You should go help\'em.' WHERE `entry`=25164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is it!  The scorpid juju Bom\'bay been waitin\' for!  Now we gonna fix you right up, $C. You come back to Bom\'bay when you be needin\' a pickup. Bom\'bay got the spells to fix ya!' WHERE `entry`=25165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He was controlling a sea giant? Fascinating. If we\'d managed to investigate further... Oh, I mean, wow, that\'s totally crazy! But thank goodness he\'s gone, hooray! Mister Noggenfogger will be so pleased. Here\'s a nice big reward, you!' WHERE `entry`=25166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, we\'ve stymied their efforts for now, but they\'re still here. We\'ll have to press on, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A battle well-fought, $C, but I still have my doubts about our effectiveness. These humans don\'t seem to be going anywhere. You, however, have done more than could reasonably be asked of any loyal member of the Horde. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, hero. You done good for Sen\'jin today. No... you done good for all of Durotar.' WHERE `entry`=25169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya mon, that\'s tha stuff. Now we get the other jujus.' WHERE `entry`=25170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That $R wants us to send help?  Bah, he can forget it. I\'ve got my own human problems to worry about, and even those are the least of my worries right now. Sen\'jin Village is right next to Echo Isles and the Valley of Trials. Old Gadrin should find plenty of youngbloods to help him with his human infestation.' WHERE `entry`=25171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Executed with quickness and discretion. A job well done.' WHERE `entry`=25172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Word of your bravery travels fast, $C. Tales of your victory at Tiragarde Keep will be heralded in Orgrimmar.' WHERE `entry`=25173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What... WHAT!? Bael\'dun in ruins? Corpses everywhere - no. No! The Bilgewater goblins, was it? They want a fight do they? We\'ll show \'em what it means to be a part of the Horde, we will. I\'ll fill the Battlescar with their corpses. I\'ll redden the dirt with their blood. Goblins. Are going. To die!' WHERE `entry`=25174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' That was my boy, $N. My only boy. They\'ve made it personal, $C. Personal.' WHERE `entry`=25175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$G Hey there, handsome!  I\'ve had my eye on those big, beefy biceps ever since you stepped into town.: What\'re you looking at, ugly?  I\'ve seen you walking around Razor Hill, trying to steal MY men from me!;$B$BListen, I\'ve got something for you to do. I hear Gar\'Thok\'s got you headed over to Tiragarde. While you\'re there, think you could find some abandoned Kul Tiras knicknacks?$B$B$GThanks sweetie!: Don\'t ask why, just get to it!;',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You brought me my treasure!  What a sweetheart!' WHERE `entry`=25176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The scent of the sea hangs about you, $N. Your efforts may have purchased another day for Razor Hill. I will pass word of your deeds up my chain of command. You have our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=25177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$G Hey handsome, welcome back!  You wouldn\'t mind running another errand, would you?  I\'d be EVER so grateful...: You!  Stop right there, you tramp!  I\'m not finished with you yet.;$B$BI hear you\'re headed off to the shore east of here. The beach is filled with crashed ships, and those ships have gnomish tools in them... tools that I can use.$B$B$G See you soon, beefcake!: Get cracking, missy!;',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You really know how to treat a girl, you know that?  If you ever need anything...' WHERE `entry`=25178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve already spoken with several orcs that have returned from the beach. All of them told me that you were the one who saved them. You\'ve done a noble task today, $N. Lok\'tar ogar!  For the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=25179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why would Twilight\'s Hammer take an interest in these tablets? Brann himself wrote that he hardly knows their significance, although he did mention something about becoming one with the earth. I will need to confer with my fellow Explorer\'s League scholars to decipher these as soon as possible.$B$BThank you, $N. Without your aid, these tablets would\'ve fallen into enemy hands.' WHERE `entry`=25180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why would Twilight\'s Hammer take an interest in these tablets? Their contents are a mystery to our most learned scholars and deciphering them will take some time. If Twilight\'s Hammer knows about these relics and desires them, what more are they plotting?$B$BWe are most fortunate that you protected them from capture, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I want to see some dead goblins, $N! Just west of here you\'ll find a whole warren of those little insects burrowing into the mountain.$B$BLet\'s see to it that they\'re digging their grave.$B$BDestroy them. Lay waste to their whole grubby operation. They\'ve sown their own demise in Bael\'dun, $C, and it is time to meet the reaper.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 10 Frazzlecraz Miners at the Frazzlecraz Motherlode in Southern Barrens.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dead? Good. Let word of this deed spread, and with it, terror. The Horde will feel the consequences of their attack on Bael\'dun, and they\'ll rue the day they ever crossed us, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As we would say in the Tinker\'s Union, out of the heat-applied metallic cooking container and into the oxydizing, energetic mixture of reacting gases and solids!' WHERE `entry`=25184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Very nice work, $N. I suppose there\'s some strategic value in depriving the Horde of those minerals, but I\'d have done it anyway just to crush those little green monstrosities.' WHERE `entry`=25185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So our supplies aren\'t getting through? Hmmm. Honor\'s Stand just gets more and more isolated. Still, the defeat of Thunderwalk should send a signal to our foes that we mean to stay. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see... so the trick is that you need to put the LITTLE end of the spyglass up to your eye. I\'ll remember that piece of information.' WHERE `entry`=25187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Find Misha',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Find Zen\'Taji' WHERE `entry`=25187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I used that trick you taught me with the spyglass, and I watched you running around down there. Quite impressive! How\'d you make the old woman fly, by the way?' WHERE `entry`=25188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Help Misha Tor\'kren',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Help Zen\'Taji' WHERE `entry`=25188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My grandmother was a powerful shaman in her day. I thought she had lost most of her powers in her old age, but I suppose some things stay with you forever.' WHERE `entry`=25189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Good, good. One step closer to eliminating those beady-eyed, basket-wearing, hog-nosed, two-toed... ...hunchbacked, squealing, prickly... no-good... gnome-loving... GREEEAAAAGH!  Quilboar!' WHERE `entry`=25190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What, what!? Can\'t you see we\'re under attack here! Yes sure of course I\'ll give Nibb\'s findings careful study. Later. From the safety of the Eastern Kingdoms, if I have any say about it!' WHERE `entry`=25191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You\'ve done well, stranger. I\'m sorry you had to see me like that. Thank you for killing the quilboar, but maybe you should leave before I fly into another one of my rages.' WHERE `entry`=25192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $R. I will get to work on the necklace right away. Before Kron died, I had made this for him to wear. I have no use for it now, but perhaps you might.' WHERE `entry`=25193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I love all the little animals, mon. I love the big ones, too. I just hate to see you hurt them like that... but it\'s for the best.' WHERE `entry`=25194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Something happened to Screamslash when the cataclysm hit, Zen\'Taji thinks. He wasn\'t always so violent and irrational. Thank you for your help, $N. Zen\'Taji gonna get back to his studying now.' WHERE `entry`=25195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re the one who handled the Burning Blade to the south?  I\'ve got ears in all kinds of places, boy, and word travels fast.' WHERE `entry`=25196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve ventured all the way here from Honor\'s Stand? Excellent, we could use your experience here. They may have breached the walls, but Northwatch isn\'t going down without a fight.' WHERE `entry`=25197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='While we\'ve accomplished much here, it would be a tragedy if part of this corruption has escaped our notice. The corridors of the Wailing Cavern stretch throughout the entire Barrens, and if another spot of wild energy has made its way to the surface...$B$BYou\'ve done enough for me, though. I would simply ask that you let a fellow druid of mine know of what\'s happened here. You will find Winnoa Pineforest at the Fields of Blood, southwest of here.' WHERE `entry`=25198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You made it through in one piece? You have more gears then I thought, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Cheer with the Drill Sergeant',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Dance with the Drill Sergeant' WHERE `entry`=25199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t say that I was ever much of a footbomb fan, but you\'re giving me an appreciation for the game!' WHERE `entry`=25200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeah, these will do nicely. You did good, kid. I\'ll see to it that you get the best footbomb uniform ever made. In the meantime, you\'ve got other bombs to drop on the Trade Prince\'s lackeys.' WHERE `entry`=25201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He got just what he deserved. There, there, don\'t cry. You\'ll find someone else that\'ll treat you right. Here, let me take that... we wouldn\'t want people to think that you\'re crazy.' WHERE `entry`=25202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There\'s no two ways about it... he got exactly what he deserved.' WHERE `entry`=25203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='All of the lights and indicators on the control panel are going crazy!' WHERE `entry`=25204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Valve #3 released',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Valve #4 released' WHERE `entry`=25204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The moral of the story: hasty, lazy actions have ruinous results. We mustn\'t take shortcuts... we must work for our rewards. I\'ve been trying to tell this story to the "Enforcer", but I fear his Hellscream-worshipping skull is a little bit too thick.' WHERE `entry`=25205;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='See?  The shaman\'s tales are nothing but that... a youngling\'s bedtime stories. The new Horde takes what it wants, and doesn\'t waste time with such frivolity. If you get a chance, I recommend you tell Shin... and those like him... not to waste any more of your time.' WHERE `entry`=25206;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I felt the heat from the explosions all the way over here!' WHERE `entry`=25207;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re back. What did Estulan say?' WHERE `entry`=25208;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have proven yourself to be a trustworthy and dependable ally, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N. I will study the horns, but the situation has become even more dire since you left.' WHERE `entry`=25210;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll show \'em!  Nice work!' WHERE `entry`=25211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I was wondering where you were! Don\'t worry, Hobart will get that footbomb uniform converted into the most Ultimate Footbomb Uniform ever!' WHERE `entry`=25213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oops. Well, what goes up must eventually come down.' WHERE `entry`=25214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It shouldn\'t take long to cleanse the water. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=25215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Another fan of the Great Sambino! Come all this way for an autograph perhaps? I\'m far too busy to be signing anything... move along now.' WHERE `entry`=25216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Another sample. Brilliant! The rocky riches of the sea shall soon be mine!' WHERE `entry`=25217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya know, I should have given you a weight belt so that you wouldn\'t just float away, air balloon and all. Lucky for me you came down here with armor and all! Hah!' WHERE `entry`=25218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you. Seriously. If I would have had to endure another shipwreckee laughing at me, I swear I would have gored someone. I\'ll let you know if I come up with anything.' WHERE `entry`=25219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. There are still much bigger predators we\'ll have to keep an eye out for, but this will at least give us a bit of peace of mind around the cave.' WHERE `entry`=25220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Swift work. Very impressive. That Fathom-Lord got away... I don\'t see him anywhere. He\'s most certainly the key to finding our captured friends. I will hunt him down. He cannot stay hidden for long.' WHERE `entry`=25221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A friendly face! Welcome! Very kind of you to come check on us. We\'re fine. A naga scouting force did find us, but I\'m pretty sure none escaped. We should be safe for now.' WHERE `entry`=25222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I suppose your abilities are... suitable. Color me impressed.' WHERE `entry`=25223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you managed to pass this part of the test without getting yourself eaten by Smolderos or being incinerated by the fire elementals? I suppose I should congratulate you on ascending the lowest rung of our ladder. Well... congratulations, recruit!' WHERE `entry`=25224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$G Oh, sweetie, I just remembered!: Sorry if I\'ve been mean to you. Sometimes I get a little jealous when other women come into town, as I\'m a little insecure about my appearance.;$B$BMy VERY good friend Thonk works in the guard tower on that cliff, just to the northwest of Razor Hill. He said something about a river overflowing, lots of work to be done, and so on. I wasn\'t really paying attention... I was staring into those deep brown eyes of his.$B$B$GWhat, we can\'t see other people?: Thanks.;',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gail sent you?  Did... did she say anything about me?' WHERE `entry`=25227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Find Misha',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Find Zen\'Taji' WHERE `entry`=25227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Harbingers of doom are nothing new on the streets of Orgrimmar, but I\'m worried about this latest batch. These people are organized and they\'ve attracted a lot of attention in the Drag, where they seem to congregate.$B$BI\'ve thought about rounding them up or otherwise disrupting their activities, but that will just drive them underground. We need to find out more about them. Would you go to the Drag, listen to what these doomsayers are spreading, and gather any literature you can find about their ideas?',`objectives_loc1`='Listen to a speech given by a Doomsayer in the Drag and obtain copies of the pamphlets "Elemental Fire for the Soul", "What Does \'The End of All Things\' Mean for Me?", and "Finding Security and Comfort in a Doomed World".',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Torek reads over the scrolls you collected.>$B$BWhoever these people are, they really mean to gain a following. It looks like they\'re having quite a bit of success. They can\'t be allowed to incite the citizens of Ogrimmar to panic and hysteria. We must discourage interest in this group and learn as much about it as we can.' WHERE `entry`=25228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Our engineers have been working on getting our battle machines ready for our assault on Gnomeregan, but we\'re out of pilots!$B$BWe\'ve developed a device called the Motivate-a-Tron, which prevents distraction from other sources and gives the gnome the courage to enlist.$B$BAfter motivating a few Gnome Citizens, lead them out to Captain Tread Sparknozzle out at Steelgrill\'s Depot, just south of Ironforge.$B$BOh, and be careful. The device is still a little experimental.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the best group of potential pilots you could find?$B$BOkay, well, I\'ll see what I can do. I\'ve been known to turn even the biggest pile of gnarled gears into a smooth-runnin\' fightin\' machine and I expect no less with this lot.$B$BWell, I guess it\'s time to work!' WHERE `entry`=25229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These events disturb me greatly. My study of the antlers while you were gone has revealed little. We must find some way to fix this...' WHERE `entry`=25230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is quite interesting. These rites aren\'t all that different from the spells which are taught to Horde warlocks. This merits further investigation!' WHERE `entry`=25232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! The chaos we sow back here will be felt up and down the chain of command.' WHERE `entry`=25233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Augh! Cursed - this metal is cursed - it bites! What demented workmanship is this? $N, I\'ve never fought any foe like this before.' WHERE `entry`=25234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I saw you drop a few of them from here. Nice work. Here\'s your reward, on behalf of the Night Watch.' WHERE `entry`=25235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Our army needs water, and luckily the elements gave us plenty of that when the Cataclysm hit. The water that filled up the canyon to the southwest should do the trick.$B$BUnfortunately, the corpses of thunder lizards still sit at the bottom of the canyon, and their electrical discharges are a bit too dangerous. I\'ve got grunts that can lift them out of the water, but we need someone agile enough to attach the other end of the rope. Are you my $G man: woman;, $N?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The electricity was only one of the dangers. If those carcasses rot too long under the water, that entire source becomes undrinkable. Well done, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you once again, $N. I will prepare these for our final task.' WHERE `entry`=25237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=25239;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=25240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The spirits of these guardians will return in time, $N. You\'ve freed them to move on in nature\'s cycle.$B$BNow it falls to us to make sure that cycle is free of corruption and needless suffering.' WHERE `entry`=25241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a true champion of our cause, $N. None can claim to be more dedicated to the struggle than you. It is rumored that the minions of the Scourge fear you more than they do the Lich King himself. You are might incarnate. Accept this humble gift as a reward for your many triumphs.' WHERE `entry`=25242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m sure she deserved it, $N. She should never have betrayed you like that. It gives me the shivers to think that she might have kissed that monster, the Trade Prince!' WHERE `entry`=25243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Serves her right for stealing your man in the first place.' WHERE `entry`=25244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The corruption has been stemmed! The forest can begin to heal now. May you have the blessing of the Earth Mother wherever you go, friend.' WHERE `entry`=25250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it! You did it! We\'re saved, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! Even these fools will soon know that to stand against the Horde means death.' WHERE `entry`=25252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Anton reads over the scrolls you collected.>$B$BWhoever put these leaflets together knows how to get attention and from the state of things in Old Town, there\'s no lack of interest. We must act before they can build a significant following in the city. I fear they\'ll use their influence to spread panic throughout the city, paralyzing us.$B$BWe\'ve got to get inside the organization and learn as much as possible.' WHERE `entry`=25253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. I worry that our actions here may be too little, too late, but nature always has a way of rebuilding itself that never ceases to amaze.' WHERE `entry`=25255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Vek\'nag sent you?  Without telling you that I need wagon wheels, nails, and rations?  That idiot.' WHERE `entry`=25256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I watched you fight out there. How long you been a $C? You\'re alright, kid.' WHERE `entry`=25257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m at a crossroads now, $N... you defeated him easily in combat, but then again, I did get him for free, and he\'s pretty cheap to feed. Maybe we\'ll keep him around for a bit.' WHERE `entry`=25258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fine, here\'s the money... but you\'d better make yourself scarce before I reconsider my policy on keeping Horde slaves.' WHERE `entry`=25259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I ask for an orb, and you bring half of the goblin\'s arm with you?  I like the way you work. Tell you what... you\'ve already given me a hand. Allow me to return the favor.' WHERE `entry`=25260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $N. Word reached me of your coming, and of your exploits in Durotar.$B$BYou are a $C of growing skill and renown.$B$BStay on the pure path, and your future will be great indeed.' WHERE `entry`=25261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. Hiding within these collars is the secret behind the Burning Blade. And I will uncover that secret...' WHERE `entry`=25262;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Searing Collars you brought me are powerful, demonic implements. Divining their origin is, I\'m afraid, beyond my skills as a shaman. We will need a warlock to study them.$B$BTake a searing collar to Neeru Fireblade. Although he is a skilled warlock, he professes to use his powers to thwart demons, and claims his research in the occult is benign. Be that true or false, we may need his aid against the demonic cult in Durotar.$B$BYou may find Neeru in Orgrimmar in the Cleft of Shadow.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring an Example Collar to Neeru Fireblade in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, and where did you get this?  Good Margoz sent you to me, did he? Well, let me take a closer look...' WHERE `entry`=25263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is not news to me. While I appreciate your efforts, the Burning Blade will have to wait. We have other matters to which we must attend.' WHERE `entry`=25264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lok\'tar! Victory, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The goblins and orcs have accomplished too much together to part ways now, $C. I intend for the Bilgewater Cartel to become part of the Horde.$B$BI have something that I want you to deliver to the new warchief. Give this package to my Kor\'kron friend on the dock at Bladefist Bay in Durotar. He will help you to get into Orgrimmar safely.$B$BSpeak with Sassy Hardwrench on the ship when you are ready to set sail.$B$BUntil we meet again. Aka\'Magosh, a blessing on you and yours, $N!',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver the Sealed Package to the Kor\'kron Loyalist on the docks at Bladefist Bay in Durotar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I know who sent you. Did he give you something to deliver to me?' WHERE `entry`=25266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<The Kor\'kron loyalist opens the package, palming one object while reading a letter from within. As he finishes the note from Thrall, the barest hint of a fanged smile appears on his face.>$B$BYou are to take this directly to Warchief Hellscream inside Orgrimmar. Make certain that Garrosh knows that it is from Thrall.$B$BTake my battleworg. Hurry, little goblin, there is no time to waste for this message!',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver the SI:7 Emblem to Garrosh Hellscream at Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thrall had you deliver this? I understand the meaning of this all too well, $R. This smelly thing was caught unattended in the city and seems to recognize you. I have already put others of your kind to work in Azshara. Take it with you when you leave. From this day forward, you and your Bilgewater Cartel will serve the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=25267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re here to rescue me, $C? Thank you! No, no, don\'t worry about the cage for now. My life isn\'t important. We\'ve got to save the shrine, first.' WHERE `entry`=25268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lok\'tar, $C! Don\'t worry about this cage - these animals will come to fear me before long. My first priority is to clear this filth away from my beloved shrine.' WHERE `entry`=25269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Disgusting. This is like the incense we burn when we wish to commune with the spirits... but it\'s... befouled.' WHERE `entry`=25270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' As I suspected. These reagents bear the marks of the Twilight\'s Hammer. And here, the name "Lycanthoth." I believe these are used in a summoning ritual...' WHERE `entry`=25271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The actions of these feral dogs are beginning to make sense. The Twilight\'s Hammer fears the power of the ancients. They do not want Lo\'Gosh to return.$B$BSo they\'ve summoned their own wolf god - a perversion of what once was. "Lycanthoth," the corruptor.$B$B$N, Lycanthoth is but a shadow of Lo\'Gosh\'s power, but the beast must be destroyed so that the true ancient can return. Take this incense, and burn it in the maw of Lycanthoth east of here. Slay the monstrosity and free the spirit of Lo\'Gosh!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You were brave to face down Lycanthoth, $N. Like myself, he was a primal force of nature... but his origins were from a darker place. Those who birthed that beast reached deep into the blackness, channeling powers never intended for this world. Come, $C. Climb onto my back, and let us show these beasts the true face of ferocity!' WHERE `entry`=25272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You were brave to face down Lycanthoth, $N. Like myself, he was a primal force of nature... but his origins were from a darker place. Those who birthed that beast reached deep into the blackness, channeling powers never intended for this world. Come, $C. Climb onto my back, and let us show these beasts the true face of ferocity!' WHERE `entry`=25273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. I\'ll do my best to alter these documents.' WHERE `entry`=25274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Your people are busy with the terraforming of Azshara. We will remake the land in the image of the Horde so that all will know that Kalimdor is ours!$B$BGo north through the city. On the far side of the Valley of Honor you will find the Orgrimmar Rear Gate. Report to Labor Captain Grabbit outside the gates, goblin.$B$BFor the Horde!!!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N? The $N?! The rumors are already flying about you. I don\'t know if I should be thankful or frightened that you\'re here. At least we don\'t have any volcanoes in Azshara! Honestly, I can\'t believe you\'re showing your face here... Trade Prince Gallywix has setup shop atop the mountain!' WHERE `entry`=25275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Earthenfurydamus?  Let us hope your parents brought you into this world with more than just a ridiculous name.' WHERE `entry`=25276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! So you really sent some heads rolling, did you? It was said during the War of the Ancients that Lo\'Gosh fought demons for ten days solid. Hopefully you weren\'t fighting that long...' WHERE `entry`=25277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You really cleared that place out, didn\'t you? Well done! The night elves once told me a story about how Goldrinn fought and killed a dreadlord, even as three others clung to his flanks, burning his flesh. I wonder if you or I will ever have the strength to do the same?' WHERE `entry`=25278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, it was incredible! For a fleeting moment I saw Lo\'Gosh through the trees - a creature of both fury and light. My cage collapsed and the vandals melted like wax under the kiss of his claws, their screams and howls echoing through the valley... Was that your work?' WHERE `entry`=25279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, it was astounding! Goldrinn himself appeared to free us, his white fur bright like the summer moon. Our cages collapsed and the vandals melted like wax under the kiss of his claws. He was beautiful, $N. Beautiful!' WHERE `entry`=25280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='While you were away, I was able to revive some of the fallen soldiers.$B$BWe\'ll need every hand if we are to survive here.' WHERE `entry`=25281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. It\'ll take them many sleepless nights to figure out where we came from and where we disappeared to after the kills...' WHERE `entry`=25284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Here we go. This is the speech, $N!$B$BIt has everything to be a great battle starter: It\'s inspirational, has eloquent language and speaks directly to gnomes. Never has a finer speech been written!$B$BTurn this in to Captain Tread Sparknozzle and get some transportation to High Tinker Mekkatorque!',`objectives_loc1`='Give the speech to Captain Tread Sparknozzle at Steelgrill Depot.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Toby is all done with the speech?  Let me see...$B$B<Reads the speech> Pumping pistons! What a fantastic speech! I knew Toby was a good writer, but this is perhaps the best he\'s ever written.$B$BI think it\'s time to get you out to the battle.' WHERE `entry`=25286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the final draft, then?  Let me have a look...' WHERE `entry`=25287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You think you\'re ready for the next step then, Earthenfurydamus? Let\'s see what you\'re capable of.' WHERE `entry`=25291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Gann? Dead? I ... I should\'ve known. His temper... his recklessness. I knew someday it would get the better of him. But it sounds as though you\'ve already gifted him with vengeance. Thank you, $N! Turn your attention now to Dustwallow. If the Alliance finishes their cursed road through here, all your victories in the Barrens may have been for nothing.' WHERE `entry`=25292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Speak to Cultist Tokka',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Speak to Cultist Rokaga' WHERE `entry`=25293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. This little pup will grow to be strong and merciless like his father.' WHERE `entry`=25294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... so the bullets had quite a bit of spread?$B$BTo some people that may be a problem... me, though, I see it as a blessing in disguise!$B$BOur enemies will be running all over the place, so with a bit of a spread, the tank drivers won\'t need to lead the target!' WHERE `entry`=25295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent job, $N. Or should I say: "$N"damus? Give me a minute to read these.' WHERE `entry`=25296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! Let\'s hope the damage wasn\'t permanent. Judging by the poor victims still in camp here, the Twilight\'s Hammer really messed with their heads.' WHERE `entry`=25298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve succeeded, Earthenfurydamus. You\'re ready for the next step.' WHERE `entry`=25299;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Crucible of Fire Activated',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Crucible of Water Activated' WHERE `entry`=25303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These foul things will be driven back into the sea. I hope you\'re ready.' WHERE `entry`=25304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='[ph] Log Description' WHERE `entry`=25306;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent job, $N!  You\'ve outdone yourself this time.' WHERE `entry`=25308;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re on the fast-track to success. Let us hope you don\'t ruin your track record with such silly notions as compassion and humaneness. Come, then. Let us discuss your future.' WHERE `entry`=25309;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, Earthenfurydamus. We must show all would-be competitors that we are not ones to give up easily.' WHERE `entry`=25310;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sharp as always. You do not disappoint me.' WHERE `entry`=25311;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello, yes? What? You? Oh, you\'re one of the ones I sent after the Eye of Twilight, aren\'t you? Good work, very good. I suppose that\'s a valuable lesson: Never to take orders from a big purple ball.' WHERE `entry`=25312;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. Our plan\'s almost come together.' WHERE `entry`=25314;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You. You\'re clearly not with them. An ally then?' WHERE `entry`=25315;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Ysera\'s eyes look distant, as if not fully acknowledging you.>$B$BI feel it as well, $C. Ragnaros has arrived.$B$BWe must defeat his minions before he can join them and lend them his strength.$B$BSeek Malfurion Stormrage at the Tranquil Grove, west of here, and aid his forces in any way you can.$B$BI must seek answers from within the Emerald Dream. You must protect the world tree until I return.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve arrived just in time, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25317;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Make no mistake about this, $N. The outcome of this war will determine the very survival of our world as we know it.$B$BThe Twilight\'s Hammer has become more powerful than ever with Deathwing\'s return. Should they succeed in taking over the world tree, they might strike a blow from which we will never recover.$B$BIt is time we beat back the enemy. It is time we crushed the Twilight\'s Hammer.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. But I fear the battle is far from over.' WHERE `entry`=25319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Help has arrived at last!' WHERE `entry`=25320;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am thankful, $N. I will deliver my findings to our people.' WHERE `entry`=25321;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Speak to Hamuul Runetotem in Hyjal.' WHERE `entry`=25322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. This will help us turn the tide against the enemy.' WHERE `entry`=25323;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The dragon might be right. The Twilight\'s Hammer has breached our security and this is our most dangerous prisoner.' WHERE `entry`=25324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did well, $N. I will take Fandral to Moonglade myself. His prison will be far enough from the battlefront there.' WHERE `entry`=25325;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' It\'s about time! ...Can I get a little help here?' WHERE `entry`=25328;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve done it! Cho\'gall himself has been utterly humiliated by you. His minions are dead, the Gordok are scattered, and now all will know the might of the Horde! Lok\'tar, $N. You\'ve more than earned your reward.' WHERE `entry`=25329;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, Earthenfurydamus. I\'m having the servants you chose for me briefed on their new duties.' WHERE `entry`=25330;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Grandma Wahl at the Wahl cottage wants you to retrieve Chance the Cat.' WHERE `entry`=25331;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Kristoff, Kristoff... Oh yes, I remember now. I recall sending him on what amounted to a suicide mission. He survived? I suppose that means he failed. Still, you deserve at least some coin for the trouble.' WHERE `entry`=25332;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome back from the battle! The Twilight\'s Hammer have been disgraced in the eyes of the Gordunni, and driven from Feralas.$B$BWe\'ve shown the glory of the Alliance in full force today! Be proud!' WHERE `entry`=25333;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'d all suspected da naga, but I knew nothin\' of the Twilight Cult bein\' beneath the waves. Somehow dey are corruptin\' and pervertin\' the elements, makin\' demselves into dese horrors. We goin\' ta have to be fightin\' both of dese threats to stand a chance of bringin\' peace ta Vashj\'ir. We don\'t have da men ta do that yet. Come, $C, we got much ta do.' WHERE `entry`=25334;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As my master told me... Upon a violent death, the muisek of a creature may escape and seek revenge. Shrinking the creatures, as you did, $N, prevents the muisek from escaping. Now we may use it as we please!' WHERE `entry`=25336;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Master always said "after killing an animal, if we allowed the muisek to escape, it may take the form of an even greater creature." This is dangerous stuff. Thanks for helping me with my studies.' WHERE `entry`=25337;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. This is my first time working with treant muisek...' WHERE `entry`=25338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. You have put an old tauren\'s mind at peace.' WHERE `entry`=25339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now I know that Edana is truly dead. This heart, I will keep it in memory of what you did here for me, $N. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. Let me have a look at this.' WHERE `entry`=25341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'ve you got for me here? You said the Gordunni had this? Disgusting...' WHERE `entry`=25342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, I can feel the whelp in there. Let\'s get him out and ask him some questions...' WHERE `entry`=25344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. Now the spiritual powers of the faerie dragon will be available to us.$B$BI hope you willing to perform another task for me.' WHERE `entry`=25345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just imagine the possibilities of what we now possess, $N. Along with the materials that you have collected, I will be able to forever trap the muisek of these creatures into whatever I wish.' WHERE `entry`=25346;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N, but the tale of your hunt troubles me. There should not be so many. The sickness is still spreading...' WHERE `entry`=25349;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You should\'ve seen the battle from here! Bodies were falling off of the cliff! Spectacular!' WHERE `entry`=25352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='When I prayed at the shrine, Goldrinn granted me another vision. I saw you standing astride the Lightning Ledge, with lightning in your hands. Goldrinn seems to feel that this is of the utmost importance, but I don\'t understand what the Ancient has planned...$B$B$N, go to the Lightning Ledge. Twilight\'s Hammer has been running experiments with something called a "Lightning Channel." Investigate these channels, then use this totem to summon the Spirit of Goldrinn and see what he has in mind...',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, it is true! You indeed carry lightning in your hands. You are the chosen one, $N. You will be my champion, and carry my vengeance to realms where I cannot tread...' WHERE `entry`=25353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Impressive, $N. Very impressive. You embody all of the strength of the Wolf Ancient, and possess the wisdom to use your powers well. I salute you.' WHERE `entry`=25354;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Lo\'Gosh granted me a vision while you were in the hovel, $N. I saw you striding across the Lightning Ledge, with lightning bolts in your hand. The vision was powerful: Lo\'Gosh feels this is of utmost importance. We must not fail the Ancient.$B$BUpon the Lightning Ledge, Twilight\'s Hammer has been experimenting with devices they call "Lightning Channels."$B$BInvestigate one of these channels, then use this totem to summon the Spirit of Lo\'Gosh and learn what the Ancient is planning...',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, it is true! You indeed carry lightning in your hands. You are the chosen one, $N. You will be my champion, and carry my vengeance to realms where I cannot tread...' WHERE `entry`=25355;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Jawn sent you? Good! We need your help, now!' WHERE `entry`=25356;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s hope your efforts prove to be enough of a diversion...' WHERE `entry`=25357;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I trust we both know what\'s been going on inside these crates... That\'s right... ferrrmenntation! Here y\'are. My personal secret recipe. You wouldn\'t get this from any other guy!' WHERE `entry`=25358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I remember you. You were there when they attacked us back in the cave. Good to have you with me, $C. Ready for a little vengeance?' WHERE `entry`=25359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Does everything down here only come in jumbo size? Oooh! That\'s a thought. Maybe there are some hunky sea goblins around here somewhere. Thanks, by the way.' WHERE `entry`=25360;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful, $C! These will do nicely. There are enough here to make a cloak for Korrin, and possibly even more! Thank you.$B$BI hope the trip wasn\'t too dangerous? The area of Feralas is not known for being forgiving, but you\'ve obviously done well enough.$B$BThank you again, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25361;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Traitors to the Horde and traitors to their own people... I guess they\'re not all bad. They\'ll make fine drinking flasks.' WHERE `entry`=25362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is proof of a good start, $N. Your skills as a soldier are to be commended. You are not the only one I ask that task of. Many before you have fought them, and in times past, our efforts have kept them at bay. Recently though, their attempts to push northward into our area of influence have increased dramatically. Their attacks have also become more savage... almost as if they were desperate. I have a plan though, $N, that might settle things once and for all against them...' WHERE `entry`=25363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done as I have asked, and for that I salute you. Take this small reward as compensation for your efforts, $N.$B$BWith their numbers thinned and their leaders slain, the gnolls will think twice about storming the camp. This doesn\'t conclude the issue at hand, however...$B$BThere must be some reason why the gnolls have been whipped into such a frenzied state. Before they have a chance to regroup, I want to find out what is causing it.' WHERE `entry`=25364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Examining the map reveals it to be the battle plans that Hadoken Swiftstrider wants. Numerous arrows that perhaps represent troop movements are drawn on the map, though most seem to be headed toward the south rather than to the north where Camp Mojache lies.$B$BAnother section of the map has a picture of what you think is a large insect of some kind, with various tick marks under it. From the looks of the gnolls, it perhaps represents their losses against the unknown bugs...' WHERE `entry`=25365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, this is exactly what we needed. While I am not so skilled at ciphering what most of the scrawling on this map is, I\'ve seen enough battle plans in my day to understand what is happening with the gnolls. It looks like they are currently fighting a two front war. One is with us... but it seems that their main energy has been against a foe to their south.$B$BThere\'s more at hand here than meets the eye. Perhaps it is time to figure out who this other foe they face really is.' WHERE `entry`=25366;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $C. Though the extensiveness of the Zukk\'ash presence will not be thwarted with anything less than a full-scale invasion, you have bought us some time so we can devise a proper strategy.$B$BI will be sure to have these carapaces analyzed; we\'ll need to learn everything about them before we deal with what has unfortunately turned into a much larger issue than we had anticipated.' WHERE `entry`=25367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The other spirits and I are bound here by a cruel demon named Verinias. He is our captor, a twisted, mindless beast who devours our souls over milennia.$B$BThe lure of the souls and arcane magic you\'ve brought me should let you draw him out. Take this condensed essence to the dead tree at the far north of the ruins. Use it to lure Verinias and slay him, that I may finally be free...',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m free...finally! Oh, it feels so good to be free... Oh, you saw, didn\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=25368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Impressive, $C... most impressive!  If Stinglasher is indeed one of their strongest creatures, the study of the beast will prove to be quite valuable in time. It\'s now my charge to make sure we defend ourselves long enough to take advantage of it.$B$BPlease accept this coin bounty as a token of the entire camp\'s thanks, $N. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=25369;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Inciting the Elements',`details_loc1`='This is no mere natural occurrence, $N. There must be a twilight presence behind our lines that we haven\'t accounted for.$B$BIt\'s possible that whoever is instigating the elemental disturbance is using foul magic to hide themselves from our sight.$B$BSeek the aid of the faerie dragons that roam near the world tree; they can see through any of our enemy\'s illusions.$B$BFeed them the juniper berries that grow nearby to gain their trust.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. We cannot allow the Twilight\'s Hammer spies this close to the world tree!' WHERE `entry`=25370;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Amazing! You look exhausted. She must have really made you work for it. Life should be a lot easier down here going forward with a mount that swift at your beckoning. Congratulations, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25371;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the key, $N! With the seedlings you collected for me earlier, the animals you\'ve saved from around Hyjal, and the Heart of the Forest you\'ve just discovered, we can rejuvenate this land right from under the feet of Twilight\'s Hammer. Imagine their astonishment to see their work undone, as life triumphs over chaos... I will begin the ceremony at once!' WHERE `entry`=25372;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N, but there is more work to be done to keep the camp safe. Listen further.' WHERE `entry`=25373;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will be able to rest easy now, $N. You\'ve saved our camp from a terrible menace.' WHERE `entry`=25374;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. Let\'s hope the ogres are at least smart enough to realize we\'re sending a message!' WHERE `entry`=25375;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve discovered lost treasure! Your mind reels at the thought of what else might be hidden in the depths of the sea.' WHERE `entry`=25377;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve come.$B$BI am ashamed to ask this of you, $C, but I\'ve ran from him long enough. Taerar must be stopped.' WHERE `entry`=25378;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done.$B$BThis land that has suffered so much can rest now.' WHERE `entry`=25379;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. You\'ve given us the opportunity to try to reclaim the upper hand.' WHERE `entry`=25381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dead? Good! But it seems there\'s still so much to be done... fires to quench... and the soil to heal... I hope you\'ll stay close and help us reclaim Hyjal!' WHERE `entry`=25382;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are truly blessed by the Earth Mother, $N, to have the honor of fighting with the guardians of nature, and to also survive it.$B$BKnow that you have kept safe every living soul in this camp, and possibly this entire forest. Take these gifts with my deepest thanks.' WHERE `entry`=25383;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Squueeeee! Did the nice Mr. $C pull you from the flames, little friend? You\'re safe now! Hooray!' WHERE `entry`=25385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve been tussling with drakes, eh? I like it. We need someone who can pull their own weight around here. Are you ready to fight for the Horde?' WHERE `entry`=25386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am thankful you\'ve come, $C. Our camp is beset by many perils, and yet we must tend to those fleeing the devastation of the cataclysm. If there is to be any refuge here, you must help us.' WHERE `entry`=25387;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why, $N! What a surprise! If anyone ever calls your character into question you be sure to send them my way. I\'ll tell anyone who\'ll listen that in my moment of need, you gave me a case of crabs...' WHERE `entry`=25388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, my! That\'s some of the biggest, juiciest tail I\'ve ever seen!' WHERE `entry`=25389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, you\'ve found them! I was sure they were lost forever... Here you are, $N. I hope this is ample payment.' WHERE `entry`=25390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As promised, you have your choice, $N. The muisek of the creatures has been forever sealed into the power of these weapons.$B$BYou may now wield their energy as your own. Use it well.' WHERE `entry`=25391;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh yay! Happy little deer! Now they can grow up and have ADVENTURES. You\'re swell.' WHERE `entry`=25392;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Curses! We had to fall back. But Thermaplugg\'s lost, and he knows it... he\'s only bought himself time. We hold the surface, and when the radiation clears we\'ll assault and recapture Gnomeregan with a force twice this size.' WHERE `entry`=25393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This development worries me greatly. This has happened before...' WHERE `entry`=25394;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You\'ve got to help us, $G:lad:lass;. We were tasked with escorting a precious cargo to our fellow dwarves...a keg full of the finest ale you can get out here!$B$BUnfortunately, bird-brain over here fell asleep on the job! Those blasted orcs took our keg, and hauled it up into Dun Algaz where they\'re hiding.$B$BThis can\'t stand! Now, while I stay here and try to convince this idiot that it was his fault, I\'d like you to go in there and get our keg back. For Khaz Modan!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank the Makers! It\'s downright pristine. Those orcs couldn\'t figure out the tap-lock, it seems...and couldn\'t hack through the mastercraft work of Ironforge\'s keg-crafters with their crude weapons!' WHERE `entry`=25395;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The mountain giants are precious allies of our race. We must stop this corruption before it claims any more creatures of the forest.' WHERE `entry`=25396;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The spirits of these guardians will return in time, $N. You\'ve freed them to move on in nature\'s cycle.$B$BNow it falls to us to make sure that cycle is free of corruption and needless suffering.' WHERE `entry`=25397;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your bravery has seen us through! The Emerald Nightmare has been shut out from this land.$B$BThe fate of the dragon Taerar worries me...but there is much work still to be done. I cannot afford to dwell on it.' WHERE `entry`=25398;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your valor was mentioned in my briefings, $N. I commend you.' WHERE `entry`=25399;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It sounds like there were more than we thought! Thank you for your brave work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Is that it? Let me see here...' WHERE `entry`=25401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, the orb I mentioned before. A decent reason to disturb me.' WHERE `entry`=25402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you\'ve brought him. Now I merely have to suffer the fate of speaking to him.' WHERE `entry`=25403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very well, $R. I will help you mortals, even from within my bonds. But don\'t sicken me by claiming it\'s my redemption. I do this for my own ends.' WHERE `entry`=25404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hear you, $R.$B$BI understand the urgency, but these men are in no condition to fight.' WHERE `entry`=25405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful! Everything\'s going according to plan. Lady Shandris will be pleased.' WHERE `entry`=25406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wisps have always lived in harmony with night elves, and we depend on them for many things. These little guys you sent back, for example, will be helping us with some new construction and repairs.$B$BReady for more?' WHERE `entry`=25407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good. Please crush the berries into a pulpy liquid. That\'s quite an aroma isn\'t it? Now now, don\'t gag. It\'s beneath you.' WHERE `entry`=25408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A properly trained squadron of hippogryph riders can take on nearly any opposing force. Feathermoon Stronghold will be much safer with these noble beasts on our side.' WHERE `entry`=25409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They may not look it, but some treants grow to be ancient protectors. We could use a few more of those around here...' WHERE `entry`=25410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Yes, master?' WHERE `entry`=25411;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, yes! Show me the runes you discovered. "Vol\'talo Thol\'embaar." That\'s the name of your real enemy. Presumably you\'re dealing with one of Ragnaros\'s generals, sent here to scorch the mountainside and pave the way for his conquest. I will show you how to crush him.' WHERE `entry`=25412;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Speak to Cultist Wyman',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Speak to Cultist Orlunn' WHERE `entry`=25414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $C. We\'re that much closer to the secrets of Uldum.' WHERE `entry`=25420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is amazing. These hieroglyphs are undoubtedly titan, but the markings below it... If I had to hope, this is the same passage written over and over again in an entire assortment of ancient languages. We might be able to use this to decipher the hieroglyphs! If the antechamber was covered in them as you say, who knows what else we\'ll learn. I\'d like to grant you a fine reward, $N. We\'ve made the find of the century!' WHERE `entry`=25421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you! Thank you... I feel much better. With just a bit more...' WHERE `entry`=25422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You can feel their anguish, can\'t you? My poor friends. At least we can use you to fix things...' WHERE `entry`=25423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This development is troubling, $N. We must act swiftly.' WHERE `entry`=25424;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. I didn\'t think those gnolls would give you much trouble.' WHERE `entry`=25426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect. Any gnolls left will be simple prey, lost in the woods.$B$BHeh...here, soldier, take your reward before I get distracted. We\'ve got other threats to deal with.' WHERE `entry`=25427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There it is! Such a trophy! Born in the fires of another plane... Go ahead, $R. Crush it. Crush his charcoal heart in your hands and let the winds scatter the ashes... yes, yes.' WHERE `entry`=25428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are silithid after all...I wasn\'t sure, having never seen one in person. Gilneas had its problems, but at least we didn\'t have these monstrosities running around!' WHERE `entry`=25429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My duties are here, viewing the enemy\'s movement from above, commanding our armies where they\'re needed. Your aid would be most welcome.' WHERE `entry`=25430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N! You\'re proving very valuable to securing this area for the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=25431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We dealt the Gordunni ogres a large blow at Dire Maul, but we haven\'t quite finished the job. My scouts have reported a group of them amassed in the hills to the north, gathering for some reason.$B$BIt\'s possible they\'re interested in the Horde settlement nearby, but I don\'t want to take any chances. Scout the area, kill any ogres you come across, and report back.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see you back. We\'ve learned more about the ogre situation.' WHERE `entry`=25432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done once again, $N. Yet another threat removed from Feralas.' WHERE `entry`=25433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, and good riddance. I hope we never have to see another ogre here again!' WHERE `entry`=25434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I didn\'t want to scare you, but this is a grave situation. If the portal at Dream Bough was sealed, and the corruption is still spreading...' WHERE `entry`=25436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve come.$B$BI am ashamed to ask this of you, $C, but I\'ve ran from him long enough. Taerar must be stopped.' WHERE `entry`=25437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='To be drawn into a fight between dragons...I don\'t know if you\'re blessed or cursed.$B$BLady Shandris has heard of all you\'ve done, and has personally sent this reward for your bravery. I\'m glad you came back in one piece to receive it.' WHERE `entry`=25438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to have a real warrior at my side. Too often, my shaman brethren can\'t seem to stomach the work.' WHERE `entry`=25439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And with this, hopefully their attacks on us will calm for a while.' WHERE `entry`=25440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Too often, we are mistaken for druidic types. Perhaps that\'s true for some shaman, but do not let yourself be plagued by the ignorant belief that we are always peaceful. Nothing about what I do is harmonious. I command the elements to my will. There is nothing offered in return. I would have it no other way.' WHERE `entry`=25441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What is this? A pearl? Much more I think.$B$BThis is exactly what I was looking for, thank you for bringing it to me.' WHERE `entry`=25442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Did my drought work? You spoke with one of them?$B$BThen you know what to do. The name of their elemental master is written on three firestones scattered throughout the Inferno. Examine each of these stones and we will have the name we need.$B$BHurry! Your precious forest burns!',`objectives_loc1`='Assemble the true name by examining the three Firestones in the Inferno.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, yes! Show me the runes you discovered. "Vol\'talo Thol\'embaar." That\'s the name of your real enemy. Presumably you\'re dealing with one of Ragnaros\'s generals, sent here to scorch the mountainside and pave the way for his conquest. I will show you how to crush him.' WHERE `entry`=25443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These be enough for me purposes. Now comes de hard part.' WHERE `entry`=25444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, you\'d be a mighty warrior and a fierce commrade to da Darkspear trolls. De Echo Isles are OURS now and we couldn\'ta done it wit\'out ya.$B$BTake dis cloak. Wear it wit pride. You\'d be a member of da tribe now!$B$BIn no time, da trolls will have a home again and we have you to thank for dat.' WHERE `entry`=25445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m already beginnin\' to see what de frogs are seein\'. Ya done it perfectly, $N. Now Vol\'jin and I will see what Zalazane be plannin\'.' WHERE `entry`=25446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At the very least, these creatures\' suffering has ended. Let us hope their sacrifice will bring a stop to further pain.' WHERE `entry`=25447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. That\'s one less distraction for me.' WHERE `entry`=25448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did you stop and examine the texture of these hides?  Properly treated, these hides could very well be stronger than iron. Not many people know about these hides, and that in combination with the vast treating solutions I know will allow me to potentially make items with a true mark of quality... thanks to you, of course!$B$BAnd now, please choose from what I am able to offer you for your service!' WHERE `entry`=25449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent, excellent!  These are going to work out incredibly well - I can already tell that they\'re going to be much harder when properly cured.$B$BThanks again for your help $N. Here - please take one of my latest creations.' WHERE `entry`=25450;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Incredible!  You may have found the granddaddy of all yeti hides with this!$B$BYou better believe I\'ll pay you for it. I normally don\'t pay that much for a single hide, but I\'m pretty sure I can make something special from it. Thanks for thinking of me on this, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, excellent! These hides, when given a special treatment, are as resilient as iron I tell you! It will take many tries in order to get the right mix down for the tanning, but I am confident they will bring my mark of quality to the next level.$B$BAs for you, $N... your assistance has proven invaluable to me. Please take your choice from these items I have crafted.' WHERE `entry`=25452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent, excellent!  These are going to work out incredibly well - I can already tell that they\'re going to be much harder when properly cured.$B$BThanks again for your help $N. Here - please take one of my latest creations.' WHERE `entry`=25453;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is an incredible find! I believe this is the finest yeti hide specimen I have ever seen!$B$BIndeed, this is certainly worthy of an appropriate bounty. I normally don\'t pay that much for a single hide, but I\'m confident I can make something special from it. Thanks for thinking of me on this, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sam\'s in one piece then? And his poor assistant Felice? Good to hear. I hope that one day he\'ll learn to respect the elements as more than just a tool.' WHERE `entry`=25456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good riddance to foul creatures. May the naga slither back into the sea and never return.$B$BYou\'ve proven yourself on the battlefield, $N. I would ask more assistance of you in defending our lands here.' WHERE `entry`=25458;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well that\'s a load off my mind. Thank you again, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25459;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N. Your fighting prowess is admirable. You will be crucial to putting a halt to the elemental onslaught.' WHERE `entry`=25460;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N. Those little bears are shaken up but they\'ll survive. At least the ones that hit the mat.' WHERE `entry`=25462;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you here. Estulan is being...difficult. We\'re going to have to deal with these ogres for Lady Shandris on our own until he decides to deal with us.' WHERE `entry`=25463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. We cannot afford to lose any further ground in Hyjal. By stopping Baron Geddon we will have dealt a huge blow to the enemy.' WHERE `entry`=25464;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Splendifimous!  Not only am I glad to see that you\'ve returned with the residue, but also with all your major appendages intact!  That is, well, there was never any danger in using the Ultra-Shrinker, now was there!$B$BI do appreciate your effort on my behalf, $N. Truly, you are a friend to goblins everywhere. Accept this as a token of my appreciation!' WHERE `entry`=25465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Scrumdillyriffic!  These cores will keep me working for some time. Add to that the benefit of there now being fewer elementals along the coast, and I might no longer cry myself to sleep at the prospect of having set up shop in perhaps the worst place imaginable!$B$BThank you, $N, for your efforts on my behalf. While it certainly straps me financially to do this, allow me to show you some gratitude you may understand and appreciate... loot!' WHERE `entry`=25466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The satisfying sound of a chest unlocking is followed by the sight of once-hidden treasure.' WHERE `entry`=25467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aren\'t they adorable? The babies are even cuter.' WHERE `entry`=25468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent!$B$B$N, you\'ve helped bolster our forces here, and you\'ve saved many of these forest creatures from the Horde as well. With our army now ready, Feathermoon will stand against all threats, Horde or otherwise!$B$BOn behalf of Lady Feathermoon, I\'d like to award you with this weapon, fit for a Sentinel.' WHERE `entry`=25469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ello, mon! You look a bit more capable then most of dem coming through here. Come rest a bit. Make yaself at home.' WHERE `entry`=25471;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent, $N. This will be a great weapon against the enemy forces.' WHERE `entry`=25472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just so you know, you\'ll find Kaja\'Cola all over town. It\'s the Bilgewater Cartel\'s best-selling product of all time! Just remember, image is everything if we\'re going to get you promoted to Trade Prince! No, wait, profits are everything! Explosions are a close second! Then, image!' WHERE `entry`=25473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Once More, With Eeling [DEPRICATED]',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 15 of any Eel in the Kelp Forest.' WHERE `entry`=25474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You place the egg... distress beacon... inside the chicken... homing robot.$B$BHums and whirs are heard from inside the robot as it struggles to stand up. After the robot comes to life, Oglethorpe\'s voice is heard once more, but now from inside the robot:$B$B"OOX-22/FE is working at least, but it needs major repairs! It is much too heavy for you to carry it... but I think I have an idea. Are you up for watching over it some more?"' WHERE `entry`=25475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, YOU\'RE the great savior of OOX-22/FE! I cannot even begin to express my thanks for your assistance! My homing robot series needs more development, but your recovery has saved me countless hours of extra rebuilding time, as well as many gold pieces in manufacture costs!$B$BPlease, take your choice of any of these items I have. Thank you again for your generous assistance $N, my robots and I are in your debt!' WHERE `entry`=25476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='How unfortunate... Well, all things considered, it is good to see that you made it back unharmed.' WHERE `entry`=25477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nyse sent you? Good! We need your help, now!' WHERE `entry`=25478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thyssiana sent you? Good! We need your help, now!' WHERE `entry`=25479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Falfindel Waywarder sent you? Good! We need your help, now!' WHERE `entry`=25481;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This is going to take a while, but I\'m sure we\'ll beat them back.$B$BYou\'re more good to Thousand Needles elsewhere. We have reports that the gnomes and goblins out on the flooded salt flats somehow survived on a giant barge! Rendow is on the dock. He\'ll get you a boat to go there.$B$BMind helping us out a little on your way to him?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='A boat? Yes, you can have this last one.' WHERE `entry`=25486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You want a canoe to go out to the salt flats? But, surely the race track has been destroyed?! Nonetheless, for your bravery, you will have the last one!' WHERE `entry`=25487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='YES?! Do you see me interrupting your fascinating argument? No... no, please, go ahead. I\'m sure that your interruption is about something very important. More important than dealing with the survival of everyone here, in fact.' WHERE `entry`=25488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Are you ready to go, $C?$B$BOne of our braves will row you out to the Mirage Raceway. If anyone has survived out there, they\'ll desparately need your help.$B$BMay the Earth Mother smile upon you.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Heya, kid, I\'ll be right with ya. Just gotta shut this gnome twerp up first.' WHERE `entry`=25489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$N, these fiends from the Twilight\'s Hammer are attempting to scourge this whole mountain clean of all life. Even now they trail behind this inferno, leaving death and ash in their wake.$B$BArch Druid Hamuul Runetotem is behind the fires, trying to salvage the wilderness before it\'s blotted permanently from the map. Travel southeast, through the inferno and down the road beyond. Find and aid the Arch Druid.$B$BOn your way there, clear the roads by killing any Charbringers that you find.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good. The Twilight\'s Hammer must be sent the message that we will never give up.' WHERE `entry`=25490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This land has been scourged by fire, but it may yet renew itself.$B$BSome seeds deep in the soil may have withstood the scorching heat here in the flamewake. These durable plants are the key to this forest\'s regrowth. Please, collect some of these seedlings for me.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' These seedlings have survived an apocalypse. Even a handful hold great power. Life always replenishes itself, often stronger than before. Once the way is clear, we will use these to perform a miracle on this mountain, $N. You will see.' WHERE `entry`=25491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $N. There\'s a chance the forest will recover from this yet. Now, there\'s something else I need you to take care of for me...' WHERE `entry`=25492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good. We will need these to act as bait while they are still warm. Here is my plan...' WHERE `entry`=25493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent!  Our pup is ready for a fight.' WHERE `entry`=25494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At last, everythin\' be ready. Now, we show Zalazane what happen to dose who defy de Darkspears!' WHERE `entry`=25495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Erunak speaks as he places the turtle meat into a porous sack.>$B$BReady yourself, $N. There\'s no telling how this might end up, but we don\'t have much choice if we are to rescue your friends.$B$BTake this sack and use it at the sunken anchor southeast of here. Once you\'ve attracted a shark, do your best to ride it back to me here.$B$BIf you can do that, you will have a most intimidating means of transportation.',`objectives_loc1`='Use the Shark Bait at the Sunken Anchor and ride the shark to Erunak.' WHERE `entry`=25498;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh. You\'re still alive. Not bad.' WHERE `entry`=25499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Here we go. This is the speech, $N!$B$BIt has everything to be a great battle starter: It\'s inspirational, has eloquent language and speaks directly to gnomes. Never has a finer speech been written!$B$BTurn this in to Captain Tread Sparknozzle and see if there\'s anything else he needs of you.',`objectives_loc1`='Give the speech to Captain Tread Sparknozzle at Steelgrill Depot.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the speech from Toby?  Fantastic!$B$BRecruit, you\'ve done all we could possibly ask for and the Gnomeregan Army thanks you!$B$BWe\'ve got a strike team heading to Gnomeregan now and that wouldn\'t have been possible without your assistance. For all of your help, we\'d like you to join the Gnomeregan Reserves!$B$BIt doesn\'t pay very well, but you do get this snazzy helmet. Hang on to that, you might need it someday!' WHERE `entry`=25500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s good! Between your work and the work of a few others, that valley is secure from a counter-attack. I\'ve done all I can. It\'s all up to you and the Arch Druid now.' WHERE `entry`=25502;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This item was highly prized by the local gilblin population - even coveted by King Gurboggle, himself!' WHERE `entry`=25503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I don\'t have even half of that stuff!' WHERE `entry`=25504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Heya, pal, mind if I take a look at that list? What\'s Pozzik thinking? He knows that I don\'t have even half of that stuff!' WHERE `entry`=25505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Fresh and stinking, these innards will prove to be irresistible for Nemesis, the befouled turtle god created by Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BNemesis must eventually be destroyed, but first, we must collect a piece of his fiery armored shell. With it, we\'ll be able to work some magic to free the true Ancient.$B$BGo into the Flamewake and drop this bait near Nemesis. It will distract him. Pry off a piece of his shell... then run, if you hope to survive the encounter.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Nemesis is an instrument of evil, but he was forged from a shell fragment of the true Ancient. We will exploit this connection.' WHERE `entry`=25507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very well. You\'re at least competent enough to figure out which way the pointy end of the pick goes.' WHERE `entry`=25509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<The Arch Druid fills the shell fragment with water, which boils instantly. He adds a bundle of herbs and closes his eyes in a silent prayer.>$B$B$N, Tortolla the turtle ancient is ageless, a part of this world since the time of the titans. He speaks a language older than our understanding.$B$BDrink this and find a place of calm within yourself. You will be able to understand the language of Tortolla. Go to him now, in the ashen lake. Earn the ancient\'s trust. The fate of Hyjal hinges on this.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$R. This tongue. Is not yours. What do you want ... tormentor?' WHERE `entry`=25510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fantastic. I might challenge you to a duel myself someday.' WHERE `entry`=25513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You... Are not like the others. I am free once again. The others... Will pay.' WHERE `entry`=25514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Jinky rolls up her sleeves and slicks back her hair while eyeing you up and down.>$B$BFine, if Fizzle wants you to have your own boat, the first thing we\'ll need is parts. Guess who gets to go get them?$B$B<Jinky smiles as she points downward and then grabs you a spare diving helm and flippers.>$B$BThat\'s right, $G brother : sister;. You get to go down into the deeps and salvage what rocket car parts you can find at the Raceway Ruins.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This\'ll do for a start.' WHERE `entry`=25515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is a great start!' WHERE `entry`=25516;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s the spirit! You\'re a real credit to the Alliance! You know, you can go back in there and do that anytime you feel like it. I highly encourage you to do so!' WHERE `entry`=25517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes! You\'re a real credit to the Horde! You know, you can go back in there and do that anytime you feel like it. I highly encourage you to do so!' WHERE `entry`=25518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$R. You are not like the others. Braver. Stronger. A part of this world... and not the shadow that came before. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! You were able to earn the ancient\'s trust? Wonderful! We are one step closer to taking back this mountain...' WHERE `entry`=25520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh thank you, thank you! I know a bit of alchemy, I\'m not totally useless. Here goes...' WHERE `entry`=25521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t believe it! You\'re amazing! Here, please, take your reward, take anything you want! I\'ve gotta save Chelsea!' WHERE `entry`=25522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! How does it feel? It is challenging to master flight in this burning wasteland, but it is the only way. I hope you\'re ready for battle, $N...' WHERE `entry`=25523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank goodness! Now, just a little shove....' WHERE `entry`=25524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Spectacular flying, $N! Their screeches of anguish echoed about this light-forsaken cavern. But our work is not yet finished...' WHERE `entry`=25525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank goodness! Now, just a little shove....' WHERE `entry`=25526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25531;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, kid. Any close calls? Did you get grazed? No? Good, because we\'ve got more fish to fry here.' WHERE `entry`=25534;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='More help! Superb! We can certainly use it, I\'ll tell you that much.' WHERE `entry`=25535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for stepping up to take care of this, $C. I know there are a lot of concerns swarming us right now, but maintaining the safety of the survivors is paramount.' WHERE `entry`=25536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Superb! Chemicals abound! My instantaneous chemical synthesizer is already pre-tested and prepared. Your deployment compound shall be ready in the blink of an eye!' WHERE `entry`=25537;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done my odorific associate. You are both swift and assiduous, if I do say so myself. May your future travels be rampant with inspiration and opulence.' WHERE `entry`=25538;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, indeed. This is an entirely unshameful amount of clams to have gathered. The survivors back at the cave will surely be grateful.' WHERE `entry`=25539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is wonderful. I will begin cooking them immediately. It is good to know that of our many fears, starvation shall no longer need to be one of them. I imagine the Admiral will have much work for you. Let me trouble you no further for a while.' WHERE `entry`=25540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice!  Remember, gold is gold, no matter who\'s mouth, nose, or otherwise it\'s been in. It\'s all perfectly sanitary after being melted down anyway. Or at least wiped off.' WHERE `entry`=25541;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it! You did it! Thanks for saving my Speedbarge, Captain $N.' WHERE `entry`=25542;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You saved my Speedbarge! I can\'t begin to tell you how relieved I am, Captain $N!' WHERE `entry`=25543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='By the wings of Aviana - you were born to fly, $N! Quickly, let\'s get back out there and hit them again...' WHERE `entry`=25544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $C! Thanks to you, my men will be ready to confront the enemy when they attack.' WHERE `entry`=25545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This should help relieve our exhaustion. Again, we thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No time to address the troops now. Just as well. They know what must be done.' WHERE `entry`=25547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did well, $N. I\'ve a new target for you.' WHERE `entry`=25548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove your prowess, $N. At this rate Hyjal might survive this ordeal after all.' WHERE `entry`=25549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. We shall soon claim victory in Hyjal. It has been an honor to fight along your side.' WHERE `entry`=25550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hyjal has been saved, $N. And it\'s all thanks to you.' WHERE `entry`=25551;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. We will use this to draw out the Twilight matriarch.' WHERE `entry`=25552;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That went... better than expected.' WHERE `entry`=25553;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These foul books should not be allowed to exist. Yet the information inside them is of vital importance.' WHERE `entry`=25554;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done. Only the final step in your mission remains.' WHERE `entry`=25555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' How you doin\', mon?' WHERE `entry`=25556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Chief Ukorz',`details_loc1`='Take a good look, mon. This is how it goes, betrayal after betrayal. I backstab you for the sword, and then Chief Ukorz go and backstab me even better for it.$B$BThat\'s life, yah! Or was...$B$BNow, I know you don\'t got no love for Mazoga. But I know you goin\' in there anyway. Kill him for me, mon. Spill more blood on the sand, an\' give Chief Ukorz Sandscalp what every one of us in here deserves...a gory death.$B$BMaybe I leave some of my belongin\'s without a curse before passin\' on if you do, yah?' WHERE `entry`=25557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Earthen Ring has received my distress message and sent help - just in time it would seem. Hopefully more can be sent soon. We are but few against a great many.' WHERE `entry`=25558;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll teach the Horde twofold! Don\'t mess with dwarven history, and don\'t send a bunch of frail couch-dwellers to do your fighting!' WHERE `entry`=25559;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Without any defenders, the firelands eggs are vulnerable.$B$BTake wing once more and smash those eggs! Simply rush over them to crush them. Search all the nooks, crannies, and side-caves. Hurry!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='A decisive blow!' WHERE `entry`=25560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The fires may be dealt with, but those Southsea pirates are still getting ready to board the Speedbarge!$B$B$N, you need to go back to Mazzer Stripscrew and get on your boat. Use the cannon to sink them before it\'s too late!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it! You did it! Thanks for saving my Speedbarge, Captain $N.' WHERE `entry`=25561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You saved my Speedbarge! I can\'t begin to tell you how relieved I am, Captain $N!' WHERE `entry`=25562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Everything here seems to be in working order.' WHERE `entry`=25564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Would you take a look at these...not troll, not qiraji, just pure mystery waiting to be unlocked. These aren\'t going anywhere now that they\'re safely in our hands. It\'s time to make our way into the ruins!' WHERE `entry`=25565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I studied these ruins for years trying to find a way in. We even took a good chunk out of the gate, only to find impenetrable walls beneath. Now the Cataclysm may\'ve wrecked everything in there something fierce, but it\'s done what we couldn\'t and opened a way in!$B$BI\'d like you to have the honor, $Glad:lass;. Head on in there and see if anything\'s been left uncracked. Be careful though... there\'s no telling what, or who, might be stirring in there.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This chest lies undisturbed, sealed for thousands of years.' WHERE `entry`=25566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, $N, this shard does explain the occurrence of the rifts. The elemental planes have been in chaos in Outland ever since Draenor was destroyed. These shards cause a weakness in the already damaged elemental planes and allow the elementals to cross over. We\'re still collecting information on who or what is behind all of this. However, the more shards you bring me, the better prepared we will be to fight the elemental invasion here in Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=25571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent, $N. That should put a stop to the attacks once we finish these elementals off.' WHERE `entry`=25574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The weapons the Twilight\'s Hammer uses against us are crafted by Forgemaster Pyrenduis within these very halls. The metal slices through armor like cheese in the hands of its wielder. Yet, when captured, the steel turns brittle and shatters.$B$BSo be it, $N. I\'d rather see those cursed arms smashed than delivered to our enemy.$B$BSeek out the crates of twilight arms in these caverns and smash them to pieces.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. I like nothing more than to see the works of our enemy destroyed.' WHERE `entry`=25575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Here we are deep within the realm of the fire god and what do we find? The little puppets of Ragnaros, scurrying around to do his bidding.$B$BThese Dark Iron laborers are finishing and packaging the weapons Twilight\'s Hammer hopes to use in their conquest of Hyjal. I don\'t care if they\'re here of their own free will or if they\'ve been brainwashed or kidnapped... They\'re a foe of our beloved Wolf Ancient and they should pay the ultimate price.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dead? Good. They sealed their fate when they threw their lot in with Ragnaros and his kingdom of flame. Leave their bodies down here to crumble into ash.' WHERE `entry`=25576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work! There was a time when adventurers would collect these cores in order to craft mediocre fire-resistant equipment. But for now, I\'m glad just to destroy these fiends once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=25577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Alysra\'s decision might not have been the wisest, $N. Yet there is little time to worry about that now. I bring important discoveries from the Emerald Dream.' WHERE `entry`=25578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $C. I will get some of our own patrols out to make sure that no more naga get within sight of this cave. We should have the area secured within the hour.' WHERE `entry`=25579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N, and just in time too. The Admiral just started sending more men out. Strong sword arms to be sure, but I doubt they possess quite the same awareness and finesse that you do. We were lucky to have you here when things went south. I suspect you will have a large role to play in things to come as well.' WHERE `entry`=25580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you so much for taking this seriously.$B$BThis is some of the first definitive proof of other members of the Vashj family. Very interesting. And I\'d never even heard of either of the other two figures you mentioned until now.$B$BSo much of our history was lost during the sundering - it\'s exciting to have a chance at reclaiming some of it.' WHERE `entry`=25581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Ranger Valarian statue',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='High Priestess Siralen statue' WHERE `entry`=25581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is good intel. You have a sharp eye, $C. It sounds like the building tucked under the terrace at the far end of the ruins will make a suitable forward post. I will send some men immediately to start defensive preparations and we will reposition there as soon as possible.' WHERE `entry`=25582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Interesting indeed. The remains you describe sound much like the sea vrykul we encountered in Northrend. I highly doubt we will be striking any alliances with their sort, no matter the cause. Still, this information may prove useful in the future. I will think on it further if time permits. Thank you for bringing it to my attention.' WHERE `entry`=25583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It\'ll be crucial to reclaim each of the Ancients\' shrines, $N.$B$BFollow the road west of the Verdant Thicket, into Wolf\'s Run.$B$BWe have operatives stationed there. Aid them in any way that you can and work your way to the first shrine.$B$BThe wolf god was known to the elves as Goldrinn and to the orcs as Lo\'Gosh. He will be a fierce ally in our fight against the enemy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ysera sent you? Good! We need all the help we can. We\'ll never be able to recover the shrines to the ancients so long as Twilight\'s Hammer controls the roads. Somehow we\'ve got to stem the flood.' WHERE `entry`=25584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re still shooting, but not nearly as much! Yeeeeeeeeeaaaaaaaaaaah!' WHERE `entry`=25585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re still shooting, but not nearly as much! Yeeeeeeeeeaaaaaaaaaaah!' WHERE `entry`=25586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I cannot thank you enough, $R. I just hope this whole nightmare has a happy ending.' WHERE `entry`=25587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll teach those scurvy dogs! You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll teach those scurvy dogs! You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey! Get me out of here!' WHERE `entry`=25590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fantastic. I might challenge you to a duel myself someday.' WHERE `entry`=25591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You know what it is to carry yourself with honor, $C. You do Hellscream proud.' WHERE `entry`=25592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. You\'ve proven very useful.' WHERE `entry`=25593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glad you know a quick buck when you see one. Pleasure doing business with you, $G buddy:gorgeous;.' WHERE `entry`=25594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now to hold up my end of the bargain. I\'ll get this cooked and passed out immediately.$B$BYou and I will have to have a talk later. I\'m going to need help that these soldiers just can\'t offer.' WHERE `entry`=25595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey! Get me out of here!' WHERE `entry`=25596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Only once has there been a leader capable of commanding demigods and mortals alike.$B$BHis name was Jarod Shadowsong and his ability to lead in battle was such that Cenarius and the other Ancients placed themselves under his command.$B$BHe disappeared for years and his whereabouts were unknown. Until now.$B$BHe is being held captive inside a Twilight camp in Darkwhisper Gorge.$B$BYour job is to infiltrate their ranks and free Jarod. Speak to the one known as Ortell at Darkwhisper Pass to the southeast.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey there. I\'m glad to see they sent someone of your caliber for this operation. This here\'s going to call for some subtlety. We can\'t risk Commander Shadowsong getting killed.' WHERE `entry`=25597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Where would we be without you, $R! I don\'t want to even imagine!' WHERE `entry`=25598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the tome we\'ve heard about? I see... I guess it\'s good that I can read some of the elemental script. I\'ll work on translating this. Meanwhile, there\'s one final problem to take care of.' WHERE `entry`=25599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done! We\'ll seal this fiery hole up behind us and let the minions of the Twilight\'s Hammer discover the corpses we left behind. We couldn\'t have done it without you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you are, Earthenfurydamus. I\'ve been meaning to talk to you about something. I heard about the unfortunate incident that befell our poor friend, Okrog.' WHERE `entry`=25601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Outstanding! Let\'s see if this does the trick.... Stand back, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, ze junk haz arrived! Zit is ze last piece of ze puzzle! Now to zet it up! Standby, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. We might win this one yet.' WHERE `entry`=25608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh yeah! Look at all that booty. Wait a minute... bring it closer!' WHERE `entry`=25609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh yeah! Look at all that booty. Wait a minute... bring it closer!' WHERE `entry`=25610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re moving supplies to Hyjal straight from the elemental planes? That explains so much. You\'ve made Goldrinn proud by sealing that flamegate, $N, but there may be more portals to seal. You should check with the other shrines!' WHERE `entry`=25611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re moving supplies to Hyjal straight from the elemental planes? Devious. You\'ve made Lo\'Gosh proud by sealing that flamegate, $N, but there may be more portals to seal. You should check with the other shrines!' WHERE `entry`=25612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' We use guns just fine, friend. CANNONS, on the other hand, I take issue with...' WHERE `entry`=25613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. The gnome technology, while somewhat obnoxious, is highly effective. We should now have a clear path to Windshear Hold.' WHERE `entry`=25614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the airways clear our hippogryphs will be able to move into Stonetalon freely. Well done, $N! Now on to more pressing matters. What you witnessed at Trueshot Point was a small sampling of the decimation left in the wake of Hellscream\'s legacy. As Warchief of the Horde, Hellscream has declared Kalimdor as the Horde\'s sovereign territory. All that would oppose the Horde are destroyed. We are Kalimdor\'s last line of defense. Should we fall, Kalimdor will also fall. The Horde must be stopped!' WHERE `entry`=25615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the Krom\'gar incinerators dealt with, the forest may be allowed to regrow. Only time can heal the wounds left by the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=25616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you are the champion Lo\'Gosh promised! Your eyes don\'t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We\'ve got our work cut out for us here. Put aside your differences with the Alliance, there\'s plenty of danger to go around. And take this: the Fang of Lo\'Gosh will allow you to channel the ancient\'s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `entry`=25617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you are the champion Goldrinn promised! Your eyes don\'t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We\'ve got our work cut out for us here. Put aside your differences with the Horde, there\'s plenty of danger to go around. And take this: the Fang of Goldrinn will allow you to channel the ancient\'s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `entry`=25618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! It seems you were right. That broken trident is serving you just fine. I suppose I don\'t get to see you claw anything to death today after all.' WHERE `entry`=25619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, my battlemaiden, you\'ve come to me. The warrior caste whispers of nothing but your victories on the battlefield, and we\'ve only just begun our assault to take the city.$B$BYou have served me proud thus far. May the Queen favor you that you might continue to do more of the same.' WHERE `entry`=25620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Come in, $N. Can you hear me? Zis iz Professor Xakxak! *POP* *CRACKLE* PERFECT! Viz ze Gnomecorder I vill be able to direct you about Stonetalon vile staying out of harmz vay! Now, onto our next order of buziness!' WHERE `entry`=25621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Vonderful! As promised, VOILA, your reward! Now, I have a bit of news that you might find interesting.' WHERE `entry`=25622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you are the champion Goldrinn promised! Your eyes don\'t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We\'ve got our work cut out for us here. Put aside your differences with the Horde, there\'s plenty of danger to go around. And take this: the Fang of Goldrinn will allow you to channel the ancient\'s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `entry`=25623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$N! Lo\'Gosh needs you. Atop the Lightning Ledge, Twilight\'s Hammer has erected a flamegate. We don\'t know where it leads, but nobody who\'s gone through has returned. You are to venture inside and be the fangs of Lo\'Gosh within.$B$BStep into the flamegate and talk to Jordan Olafson when you get inside. He\'ll give you a token to allow you to use Lo\'Gosh\'s power inside that realm. Find out where the flamegate leads!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you are the champion Lo\'Gosh promised! Your eyes don\'t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We\'ve got our work cut out for us here. Put aside your differences with the Alliance, there\'s plenty of danger to go around. And take this: the Fang of Lo\'Gosh will allow you to channel the ancient\'s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `entry`=25624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Minions of the Old God? Two very potent foes have joined forces then. Their hope to defeat the Tidehunter may not be so foolish after all.$B$B$N, we can\'t let that happen. If Azshara defeats the Tidehunter and takes his power for herself, I\'m not sure any number of us could ever hope to oppose her on the seas.$B$BThe first step is clear at least - we need to hunt down the fiend that destroyed our ships. The navy was confident enough to bring in a new fleet, perhaps they have a plan.' WHERE `entry`=25626;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeah, yeah, yeah... I\'m sure that your little adventure into the cave was very interesting. How about we talk about it over drinks back on the Speedbarge once you get me out of this cage?' WHERE `entry`=25627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeah, yeah, yeah... I\'m sure that your little adventure into the cave was very interesting. How about we talk about it over drinks back on the Speedbarge once you get me out of this cage?' WHERE `entry`=25628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, Battlemaiden.$B$BI will attend to the eastern bridge. I need you to attend to the temple itself. The ritual must not be interrupted.' WHERE `entry`=25629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Can this wait, $C? The battle is not going well. Oh, you\'re here to help. I hope you don\'t mind a little heat...' WHERE `entry`=25630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good of you to join me, Battlemaiden. The echoes of your combat graced your approach. It was a beautiful sound to behold.' WHERE `entry`=25637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Take the Soggy Note to Erunak at Shallow\'s End.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='If he still lives, I may be able to locate this poor soul.' WHERE `entry`=25638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you again, $N. Thanks for the rescue in Ashenvale. Damn shame about all the gnomes we lost. You ready to get down to business?' WHERE `entry`=25640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done indeed... I\'d expect nothing less from my own daughter. She\'ll make a fine witch doctor someday.' WHERE `entry`=25641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not too much trouble, I hope. With these samples we should be able to figure out what they plan to do with the ore and the big bomb.' WHERE `entry`=25642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Take the Pure Twilight Egg to Aronus at the Gates of Sothann in Hyjal.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You were right to come to me with this, $N. This represents a great threat to us if we do not act swiftly and boldly.' WHERE `entry`=25644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am a fool...I was misled. This is nothing more than a rusted trinket, and my visions have no doubt been fulfilled. Forgive me, $N. But should you meet this demoness again, I pray you will triumph over her as you did Verinias.' WHERE `entry`=25645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice job, I could hear their shrill screams from out here. You\'ve turned the whole place on its head! Did you happen to find any other information about the mining operation?' WHERE `entry`=25646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Interesting. Hrm... Troubling... Can\'t understand a damn thing written here - if that is writing. Could just be toilet paper. Sure smells like it.' WHERE `entry`=25647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, you\'re here. Welcome to Azshara, the stage for the next act of the Horde\'s glorious future. Now get to work.' WHERE `entry`=25648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Uh oh... Disgusting! The good news is that this isn\'t toilet paper. The bad news is that the ink on this paper is a mixture of kodo poop and blood. That\'s not the worst of it, though...' WHERE `entry`=25649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is bad. Really, really bad. You have to warn Lord Fallowmere at Windshear Hold. What in the... It\'s MOVING! The goblin balloon is taking off! We\'re too late!' WHERE `entry`=25650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My gunpowder! You found it! I\'m not crazy after all!' WHERE `entry`=25651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Amazing story, lad. I\'d have never believed you had I not seen it with my own eyes. You did enough damage to that balloon to make those fiends pull back! Alas, the threat is far from over. We have only delayed the attack. There is much work to do if we are to stop the Horde from destroying Stonetalon!' WHERE `entry`=25652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='By relieving Tortolla of his final burdens you have acquired for us a formidable ally... and the final piece of the puzzle. Steel yourself, $N. The most difficult part of our journey is to begin. We will bring the fight to their stronghold.' WHERE `entry`=25653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These lands will finally be free of the foulness of the harpies. I cannot thank you enough.' WHERE `entry`=25654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Feels great to be off the leash, doesn\'t it?' WHERE `entry`=25655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, that\'s a start. The birds who laid these eggs will never accept them again, so we\'ll have to raise these birds as orphans in the shrine here. Were Aviana here, she never would\'ve let this travesty happen. But, on to business...' WHERE `entry`=25656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Amazing! You watch the great white beast swim off into the depths and wonder to yourself if anything could ever take him down...' WHERE `entry`=25657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Nar\'shola Wards are performing perfectly. I will inform the Mistress of the Tides of your aid immediately.$B$BThank you for your assistance, my lady.' WHERE `entry`=25658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<The Kvaldir General crumples to the ground, defeated.>$B$B<With this, the ruins of Vashj\'ir have been claimed for Lady Naz\'jar. Her ultimate goals remain uncertain, but it is clear that the naga came here with purpose.>$B$B<If only you could continue, you are sure that the answers to defeating the naga lie within this vision, but the Wavespeaker\'s magics are waning, and you are losing your connection with the Battlemaiden.>' WHERE `entry`=25659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What ya be wantin\'? Oh no you don\'t. I can see ya got Tony\'s spirit with ya, and I want nothin\' to do with it!' WHERE `entry`=25660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Fine, I be helpin\' ya. He not gettin\' outa payin\' me alimony that easy! \'Sides, there be the baby he had with me sistah ta take care of!$B$BFirst thing we needin\' is the innards of his closest friends. That\'d be his cap\'ns.$B$BGo down there an pay the three of them a visit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' They\'s gonna have ta do. It not be like he had many friends. Ain\'t that right, Two-Tusk?' WHERE `entry`=25661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We don\'t have much time. To get me out of here you are going to have to take out Warlord Roktrog. He holds the key to this prison.' WHERE `entry`=25662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' To be born again, but in darkness... I have been stolen away.' WHERE `entry`=25663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That was nasty work, $N, but it had to be done. And if Aviana is truly to be resurrected, then perhaps your actions have enabled Blaithe to someday come back as well? Now let\'s see if we can contact our long lost guardian...' WHERE `entry`=25664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Slow down, $C! You look as though you\'ve seen a ghost...' WHERE `entry`=25665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that you\'ve dealt with the wendigos, we should be able to focus our efforts on the Frostmane trolls to the east.' WHERE `entry`=25667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. The mountaineers will be glad to hear that half-rations are at an end. They\'ll need all their strength to continue fighting the Frostmanes.' WHERE `entry`=25668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A hero thwarted their plans to destroy Windshear Hold, eh? That hero was you, $N. You are the pride of the Alliance! It seems that you have bought us a little bit of time. I must plan for the battle that lies ahead of us. Seek out the other inhabitants of Windshear Hold and lend them your assistance. I will call for you when I am ready to initiate our defensive strategy.' WHERE `entry`=25669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This really ain\'t as bad as it looks...' WHERE `entry`=25670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. Their blood is on Hellscream\'s hands. Send enough of them back to Orgrimmar in a body bag and the populace of the Horde might react. Who am I kidding? They\'re monsters!' WHERE `entry`=25671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, that\'s disgustin\'! We almost there, mon. Just need ta do one more ting!' WHERE `entry`=25672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Mr. P you\'re gonna be ok! Hooray! Oh, Mr. P! I knew it!' WHERE `entry`=25673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $R. You\'ve proven that you can take down an ogre... no small feat. Now let\'s see if you can take down an Alliance iron mine...' WHERE `entry`=25674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well today, $N. Not only have you purchased more time before the next ogre attack, but I think you scared some of the captives into working harder.' WHERE `entry`=25675;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Finally... another operative shows up. I hope you\'re loosened up... it\'s time to tango, partner.' WHERE `entry`=25676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There\'s nothing quite like a big fat kick in the wallet, is there, you Alliance lunkheads?!' WHERE `entry`=25677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, friend. I like the way you do business.' WHERE `entry`=25678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, you here already. Stick around for a bit, little $R. We gonna mess with the Alliance. I love my job, mon.' WHERE `entry`=25679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So it was a demon?  Those miners never seen a demon before?  We\'re in the Blasted Lands, mon!  Demons are everywhere! Ah well... let\'s get on to da good stuff, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=25680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, mon!  Without Hondo, these guys are helpless. Dis mine\'ll be ours soon enough!' WHERE `entry`=25681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Impressive, $N. I wouldn\'t have hidden in that box, but otherwise, you have performed bravely and admirably. The battle we won today may not win us any immediate spoils, but the damage you\'ve done to the Alliance will last for a long time.' WHERE `entry`=25682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Okrilla sent you?  Okrilla the killa\'? Loramus was his name?  I\'m sorry to say that we have not seen your demon hunter... but we have ways of finding him.' WHERE `entry`=25683;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. Now that that\'s out of the way...' WHERE `entry`=25684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' More than enough, and still warm!  Now, let\'s get this ritual started, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=25685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The blood ritual was a success; I can clearly see where Loramus is right now. That is, I can see where the pieces of his body lie...' WHERE `entry`=25686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see... yes, we can work with this. Loramus Thalipedes, demon hunter. I look forward to meeting you.' WHERE `entry`=25687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You... you fool!  What have you done?' WHERE `entry`=25688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What?  LORAMUS?! Oh blast, keep it down, would ya?  If my boss gets word that I worked for Loramus, do you know how quickly I\'d be on my rear end?! Well, you weren\'t lying. Let\'s get to work.' WHERE `entry`=25689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are perfect, $N. Lynnore and I will eat well for the next several days.' WHERE `entry`=25690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope this is what he needs. We probably don\'t have time for you to return and mine any more.' WHERE `entry`=25691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There\'s no doubt about it, you found demon blood. Loramus\' requests aside, I\'m sure Dar\'toon is thankful for your efforts. They\'ve been struggling to deal with these demon distractions for some time now.' WHERE `entry`=25692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is sufficient. If you see Wazzik again, you may tell him that he performed satisfactorily. I will get the bloodmages to work on fashioning the stone knife of sealing. There is no need for questions now. All will be revealed in time. While they work, I have another task for you to complete. Actually, make that three tasks.' WHERE `entry`=25693;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your work is appreciated, soldier. $R... if you\'re still interested, I have one more small task for you...' WHERE `entry`=25694;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re certain nobody saw you?  Good. Hmph... fairly harmless stuff. Either the Alliance are foolish enough to NOT be planning something against us... or they\'re hiding their information better than I expected. Either way, well done, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=25695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Report to Rohan Sunveil at the Sunveil Excursion in the Blasted Lands.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, traveler. Thank you for responding to my summons.' WHERE `entry`=25696;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' He was an archmage, I can feel it. I will hold the amulet for you while you collect the rest.' WHERE `entry`=25697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' A warlock... and a powerful one at that. I will hold onto this until the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=25698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' He was a powerful warrior, this one. I will keep the amulet until Loramus is ready to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=25699;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It would seem that we are prepared to face our demon, $N. We have the amulet\'s blessing, we have the stone knife, and I alone know the demon\'s true name: Rakh\'likh. Together, this may be enough to defeat the Defiler.' WHERE `entry`=25700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see. So this was Loramus\' plan all along. I suspected correctly, but I suppose I refused to believe it. And now, his final instruction for me makes much more sense: He asked me to let you choose from one of these.' WHERE `entry`=25701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Salt-Flop did not shame himself by running away. Look behind me, and see for yourself. The Rockpool had no hope against the naga\'s attack.' WHERE `entry`=25702;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, brave $C. I am pleased... but I am not yet satisfied.' WHERE `entry`=25703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now we gonna bring Tony Two-Tusk back ta life. You both ready, mon?' WHERE `entry`=25704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You make an old murloc proud, $R. Thank you, and may the waves ever lap at your feet.' WHERE `entry`=25705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The last Rockpool may be taken hostage today and killed tomorrow, landwalker... but they will pass into the underworld knowing that a brave $R avenged their death. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Aye, you\'ve done well, lad. You do the Alliance proud.' WHERE `entry`=25708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s a tragedy, what happened on the Shattershore. They weren\'t even soldiers... just people looking for a new home. I think we\'ve done all we can, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... not bad. You\'re quicker than many of my men. Stick around, $N... I may have use of you yet.' WHERE `entry`=25710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re an excellent asset to the Alliance and the Kirin Tor, $N. Well done. With time, our forces will retake the mine and press these Horde dogs out of the Blasted Lands.' WHERE `entry`=25711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. Thanks to your efforts, I am confident that with time, we will take back the Nethergarde Mine.' WHERE `entry`=25712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, the sound of things going boom makes my heart pitter-pat. You\'ve made this gnome\'s day, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My associates were correct to send you to me. I have a problem which may threaten the sanctity of Nethergarde, and I need someone more capable than most.' WHERE `entry`=25714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You saw worgen?  That\'s bad. Worgen ghosts?  That\'s even worse. Those weren\'t Horde ships... they were Gilnean. And they must have been headed down to Surwich, at the bottom of the Tainted Forest. That makes a lot more sense. We\'ve got to try to help them, $N!  The worgen are our allies!' WHERE `entry`=25715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ably done, $N. Now we see if my suspicions are correct.' WHERE `entry`=25716;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. I should be a bit more up-front with you. The demons were a nuisance, but they are not the real problem. That worgen druid is our problem.' WHERE `entry`=25717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Rohan\'s sending YOU to slay his druid?  Very well. You should know: Marl Wormthorn is as much demon as he is druid. Even a druid of his power doesn\'t have a chance against the demonic energies that run so deeply through this land. That does not, however, make him any less of an obstacle.' WHERE `entry`=25718;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliantly done, $N. We have what we need to break the worgen\'s trance.' WHERE `entry`=25719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hopefully, with this druid out of the picture, we can get back to our digging. The world is full of powerful artifacts, $N. You just need to be willing to do what it takes to get to them. Feel free to take one of these. The Reliquary is always happy to share some of its trove with fellow members of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=25720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well I\'ll be. There\'s someone around here that isn\'t a disgrace to Magni, bless his poor gravelly heart.$B$BJust for that, you get first crack at the ale, $Glad:lass;. But don\'t let it get to your bloody head! We\'ve got more gorram work to do, and I won\'t tolerate you lettin\' up early!' WHERE `entry`=25721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, well. The good news is, these will do perfectly. The bad news is I can tell they\'re the wrong color for topsoil here, even drunk as I am.$B$BThat means things aren\'t looking good for the area, $N. But we\'ve got more tests to run before we hang up the towel.' WHERE `entry`=25722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The local wildlife\'s all messed up from the flood, it seems. This fen used to be full of crocolisks, but I haven\'t spotted a single one.$B$BWhat I have spotted are threshadons. Never used to be any here, so the flood must\'ve swept them all right out of Loch Modan.$B$BLucky for us, because they\'re tastier than crocolisks, and I\'m running low on provisions. Bring me back some Threshadon meat for the camp, and I\'ll gladly pay you for it.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lovely. These\'ll fry up nice, and the camp\'ll be spared a week of mushroom biscuits.' WHERE `entry`=25723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kill 5 Frostmane Seers and 7 Frostmane Snowstriders on Shimmer Ridge',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We should be able to focus our efforts on the rest of the trolls to the east, but there\'s still the matter of the wendigos in the Grizzled Den.' WHERE `entry`=25724;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These\'ll do nicely. I\'ll have the lads back on their feet as soon as I make these somewhat edible.' WHERE `entry`=25725;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh good, it\'s undamaged! Thanks a lot.$B$BYou ah, you might want to wipe yourself off a bit there.' WHERE `entry`=25726;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good riddance to bad rubbish! I\'ll burn the foul thing later so it doesn\'t stink up the camp.' WHERE `entry`=25727;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is awkward... Good job out there with the robot. You caught me a little off guard. I didn\'t realize the little girl was so... Special... Well, whatever gets the job done, right? Am I right? Probably. Have some ice cream.' WHERE `entry`=25728;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Vonderful! That\'s von more name I can scratch off of my list! I vill be in touch. Xakxak, out!' WHERE `entry`=25729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well I\'ll be a monkey\'s uncle. You actually got the beast, eh? Well, a deal\'s a deal! Here\'s your reward!' WHERE `entry`=25730;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It\'s time to get to the bottom of this. We need to interrogate the matron of these beasts, Marion Wormwing. We\'ll capture her alive. Here\'s the plan:$B$BThe Harpies communicate across the ridge using a series of signal fires. If we extinguish one, Marion is sure to come investigate.$B$BYou fight her as a distraction while I sneak up behind and grab her. I\'ll leave the questioning to you. Let\'s get her, $N!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So the Harpies are tools of some sort of dragon - "Sethria." But what are the dragons doing to those eggs? And what\'s this \'special\' egg that Sethria wanted so badly? This is beyond me, $N. I\'ve given a report to Skylord Omnuron - he\'ll know what to do next.' WHERE `entry`=25731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is it? How is this gunna remove - wait a minute...' WHERE `entry`=25732;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job. I wouldn\'t be surprised if the horrid things had eggs in there somewhere, but it\'ll do for now.' WHERE `entry`=25733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful, $Glad:lass;. This should be all we need. Let\'s have a look.' WHERE `entry`=25734;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glorious! Beautiful stuff, this ore.$B$BGood on you for not droppin\' your pick. Last person I sent out let the butt end hit the floor, and that part\'s not sparkproof.' WHERE `entry`=25735;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The thing\'s still got some fight in it! Amazing!$B$BYou\'re a tough one, $N. It\'s much appreciated. I\'d say a reward is in order before you head out.$B$BKeep doin\' your best for Ironforge, you hear? And if you ever see my sister, say hello for me.' WHERE `entry`=25736;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Don\'t worry about me. Should be ok now that big hero killed the spider queen. Can get reinforcements through safely now.' WHERE `entry`=25739;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The dragon Sethria must be stopped. We know that her roost is south of here, along the southern cliffs of Hyjal, but beyond that we know little else.$B$BI have sent Thisalee on a fact-finding mission to Sethria\'s roost. She specifically requested your help - evidently you made quite an impression with the young druid.$B$BMeet Thisalee just beyond the tunnel leading to Sethria\'s Roost. And remember, this is a fact-finding mission - don\'t do anything crazy!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, $N! I was hoping to see you out here. What, Omnuron calls this a \'fact-finding mission?\' Bah! Facts are best found on corpses. Let\'s do some damage.' WHERE `entry`=25740;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This will keep us stocked on anti-venom for the foreseeable future. Thank you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25741;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, what might have been...' WHERE `entry`=25743;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'ve got Kravel Koalbeard up there talking to one of their chiefs, but now that you\'re here, we\'ll have the rights to pump up their oil in no time!' WHERE `entry`=25744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'ve got Trackmaster Zherin up there talking to one of their chiefs, but now that you\'re here, we\'ll have the rights to pump up their oil in no time!' WHERE `entry`=25745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re good at this. I like you.' WHERE `entry`=25746;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you again, $C. I almost thought we\'d lost you to the Wavespeaker\'s fool errand.$B$BDid anything come of it?' WHERE `entry`=25747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='More naga are amassing to the south than reported too it seems. We shall have to move quickly then.' WHERE `entry`=25748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are perhaps the most dependable person I\'ve ever met. I wish I could have more men half as thorough as you.' WHERE `entry`=25749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are brave indeed! I\'ve seen you battling all manner of murloc, naga, and pointy-toothed fish, but that was nothing! The way you just sling those kelp bulbs under your arm like that is a whole new kind of fearless. BOOM! You could blow up at any second.$B$BYou\'re my kind of $R.' WHERE `entry`=25751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did great up there! You devastated their ranks, but there were far more than we accounted for, and most of our men went down out there in the masses of naga. We\'ll need to hold this position as long as possible to buy them time. Hopefully some of them will still make it to the rendezvous.' WHERE `entry`=25752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you. Truly.$B$BWe need to get these men moving as soon as possible. I\'ll meet you back at the forward post soon, I\'m sure.' WHERE `entry`=25753;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Still so many? They must want something very important here to come in such numbers.$B$BI will be honest with you, $N, because you deserve at least that: I don\'t know how much hope there is. We will retreat shortly, but we won\'t be able to defend ourselves when they strike back. We don\'t have anywhere to run... we\'re running out of options.$B$BI\'m sorry, I should keep such thoughts to myself. Do me a favor and don\'t mention any of that to the men. I\'ll figure something out.' WHERE `entry`=25754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re finished! Just in time. I don\'t think we could have held them much longer.$B$BAn artifact? Could this be something we can use against the naga? I suppose that would require finding it.$B$BWe may have to attend to more pressing matters first, until an opportunity to pursue this further presents itself.' WHERE `entry`=25755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What?! How\'d they get that much gold to offer? We don\'t have that kind of money!' WHERE `entry`=25756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What?! How\'d they get that much gold to offer? We don\'t have that kind of money!' WHERE `entry`=25757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at these things. Ugh, the runes make my eyes hurt. This one here is meant to sear flesh? Seriously? Ouch! Wait a minute... These plates are designed to be riveted directly into flesh. The pain must be unbearable!' WHERE `entry`=25758;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A Battlemaiden? I never heard of such a thing. The way you explain it, it sounds like the naga forces are far greater in scope than the Admiral could possibly have realized. We might be able to learn more through the blade if we can find other locations where this Battlemaiden was present, but the information you gave me makes me fear for the admiral and his soldiers. We must warn them.' WHERE `entry`=25760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That was some fancy bladework, $N! There\'s one less threat for us to worry about in Hyjal.' WHERE `entry`=25761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did this favor to ingratiate yourself with me, but I will not sing your praises. I know what is to come. Where the sea failed, the great air spirit will strike you and your people down for your many transgressions against the elements. Begone from my sight!' WHERE `entry`=25762;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re doing what? They\'re cloaking something? Of course - so our aerial scouts can\'t see anything with our eagle-eyes!' WHERE `entry`=25763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We did it, $N! Aviana\'s Egg should soon be tucked safely in the boughs of her shrine. Do you think this means she\'ll really return to us?' WHERE `entry`=25764;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Kosak sent you, eh? Surprising. I thought for sure that he\'d be dead by now. Well if you made it past the blockade then you definitely have something that we can use. Now, do you have any news of the Horde? What are they doing? Where are they going? Tell me everything.' WHERE `entry`=25765;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Use the Highborne Prison to bind 5 Highborne Spirits.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I assure you, simpleton, the spirits you captured are at rest. Do not let their protests move you.' WHERE `entry`=25766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful! Arcanist Valdurian will be most pleased.' WHERE `entry`=25767;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m assuming you saw the Krom\'gar hot air balloon on your way here. If not, get your eyes checked. It\'s hovering directly over the oil platform.' WHERE `entry`=25768;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you again, $N. I have some news from Mirkfallon Lake.' WHERE `entry`=25769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! Nice to see those addlebrained mountaineers knew to hand the ale off to a real man to get the job done. Welcome to my survey. If you\'re of the mind to help Ironforge by takin\' over the intended jobs of some useless, lazy sods that call themselves dwarves, you\'re in the right place!' WHERE `entry`=25770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just a shard?  Pfuh!  This gets me nothing!  Take your reward and get out of my sight. Sounds familiar?  It should, because I say it a thousand times per day. Oh how I loathe this world.' WHERE `entry`=25771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Simply amazing. I had doubted that anyone could find another sphere, yet here it is, pulsating in my hands. Well done, $N! Should you find anymore--and I believe this to be an impossibility--return them to me and I shall reward you again.' WHERE `entry`=25772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, $N, this shard does explain the occurrence of the rift. The elemental planes have been in chaos in Outland ever since Draenor was destroyed. These shards cause a weakness in the already damaged elemental planes and allow the elementals to cross into our world We\'re still looking into how these rifts are appearing in Azeroth. Keep bringing us the shards. Every shard we get brings us closer to understanding how these rifts are appearing.' WHERE `entry`=25773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Genius! Now, where\'s that gold paint? I know it\'s around here somewhere.' WHERE `entry`=25774;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Genius! Now, where\'s that gold paint? I know it\'s around here somewhere.' WHERE `entry`=25775;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sethria is slain! I knew it was worth the risk. I\'ll stay here to look for survivors, but I imagine they\'ll want to see you back at the shrine.' WHERE `entry`=25776;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s take a look here.$B$BOh, this is just lovely. "Significant geological instabilities"? "Threat of sudden, massive topological destabilization"?$B$BNice to hear that somethin\' bad might happen around here. I guess we\'ll just pick up our flooded town and fly it off somewhere safe!$B$BBah!' WHERE `entry`=25777;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just put it down on the ground, $R.' WHERE `entry`=25778;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just put it down on the ground, $R.' WHERE `entry`=25779;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He\'s dead! Thank the Makers...$B$BI don\'t like the looks of them, lad. The Dark Iron I\'ve tussled with were never this crazy. Something\'s getting to these sods...' WHERE `entry`=25780;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='THEY WHAT?!' WHERE `entry`=25790;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='THEY WHAT?!' WHERE `entry`=25791;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Finally, some good news from the Frostmane Front. I\'ll have the mountaineers press their attack immediately. Now, we must signal our gnomish allies at Steelgrill to start their advance.' WHERE `entry`=25792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Seal it off? That\'s gonna take some work, friend.' WHERE `entry`=25793;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We must make haste! As you can surely see, his time is not long.' WHERE `entry`=25794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! Is it true you led an assault against a twilight dragon? You are truly a herald of the ancients!' WHERE `entry`=25795;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll teach them. You\'ve softened the Splithoof up enough that we should be able to govern them now with a minimal guard presence from the Speedbarge. That is, once we\'ve dealt with their supposed air elemental leader.' WHERE `entry`=25796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll teach them. You\'ve softened the Splithoof up enough that we should be able to govern them now with a minimal guard presence from the Speedbarge. That is, once we\'ve dealt with their supposed air elemental leader.' WHERE `entry`=25797;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oil! Black gold! Tanaris Tea! We\'re rich! We just have to clear out the remaining pesky centaur. I\'m sure with all the money we\'re going to make, we can relocate them to some other bluff.' WHERE `entry`=25798;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oil! Black gold! Tanaris Tea! We\'re rich! We just have to clear out the remaining pesky centaur. I\'m sure with all the money we\'re going to make, we can relocate them to some other bluff.' WHERE `entry`=25799;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A hearty seafood dinner will lift everyone\'s spirits and help us get the town back in shape again. Thanks for the help, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25800;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, well done $N.$B$BAccept this as payment for fulfillment of your contract with the Merchant Marines.' WHERE `entry`=25801;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Reclaiming Goods',`details_loc1`='Not long ago a merchant vessel, the Blind Princess, was raided by Murlocs. Although the ship escaped intact, much of its cargo was dragged overboard by the creatures, including a very valuable statuette of Terenas Menethil. We want that statuette recovered.$B$BSearch the coastal Murloc hovels for crates, barrels and other evidence of lost cargo. Find the Menethil Statuette and return it to me.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This crate is covered with clawed scratches, and the marks of water damage. Prying it open reveals soggy and rotted straw, as if something of value was stored in the crate. You search through the straw...$B$B...and find an armload of red-colored bottles.' WHERE `entry`=25802;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='The Search Continues',`details_loc1`='You thoroughly search this cluster of Murloc hovels, and find no trace of the Menethil Statuette.$B$BPerhaps one of the two nearby hovels to the north and northeast will have more clues.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This barrel is largely untouched. Prying it open...$B$B...you are assaulted by the pungent odor of cheese. It\'s a little wet, but still tasty!' WHERE `entry`=25803;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Search More Hovels',`details_loc1`='This grouping of Murloc hovels, after a thorough inspection, reveals nothing.$B$B...but you\'re certain that the next clue you find will be fruitful.$B$BOne of the hovels to the north must have the Menethil Statuette!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This barrel is halfway buried amidst the mud and grass ...' WHERE `entry`=25804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Return the Statuette',`details_loc1`='After pulling the barrel free from the muck and opening it, a silvery figurine is found packed in fine straw. It depicts a young, long-haired Paladin with hammer upraised.$B$BThis must be the Menethil Statuette!  You must now return it to Karl Boran in Menethil Harbor.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The captain of the Blind Princess will be relieved to hear this precious cargo has been recovered. You\'ve well earned this payment for services rendered.$B$BIt\'s good to see dependable folk like you, especially in trying times such as these.' WHERE `entry`=25805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Hey, this thing on? Anybody there?' WHERE `entry`=25806;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I ... live. Those that tried to corrupt me and kidnap my children will soon feel the rake of my talons, $C. Believe it. Continue to push forward across Hyjal. I will collect myself and assemble with the other Ancients.' WHERE `entry`=25807;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<The Gnomecorder crackles with energy. You can hear Lieutenant Paulson on the other end.>$B$BStupid gnome junk... Is ANYBODY there? $N, are you there?$B$BMaybe $G he\'s:she\'s; dead.$B$BListen, if you can still hear me, we just got word that a Horde master assassin is in the mines, directing the other assassins. Find her, kill her, report back to me.$B$BPaulson, out.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nicely done, $N! You worked the mines like a pro. Now how about returning my goggles.' WHERE `entry`=25808;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Horde monsters!$B$B<Corporal Wocard spits.>$B$BLook at this place! They\'ve wiped out innocents! Civilians!$B$BListen, $N, you\'ve got to help us. Go into the Deep Reaches and look for surviving miners. If any are still alive they\'re probably scared witless! Check in the nooks and crannies of the mine. Maybe in mine carts! There are bound to be some left alive and in hiding.',`objectives_loc1`='Rescue 8 Frightened Miners.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank the Light! You truly are a righteous instrument of power! The Alliance is lucky to you have, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25809;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So it\'s true - Aviana has returned, with you as her herald. There\'s much to be done here. We are deep in the heart of the Firelands. Sethria smuggled stolen eggs from Mount Hyjal here to hatch her own hideous creations - birds of prey, trained for war. I hope you\'re ready to fight back!' WHERE `entry`=25810;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Plant Explosives at Third Beam',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Plant Explosives at Fourth Beam' WHERE `entry`=25811;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A... a $R? Here? I must be mad...' WHERE `entry`=25812;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well then, let\'s see them get any kind of magical hocus pocus air support now when we take over!' WHERE `entry`=25813;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well then, let\'s see them get any kind of magical hocus pocus air support now when we take over!' WHERE `entry`=25814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah!  That hits the spot, and loosens the tongue. Thanks, mate!' WHERE `entry`=25815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fitzsimmons sent you, didn\'t he? It\'s been so long...' WHERE `entry`=25816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The cries of anguish have been stifled...but the source of the curse still lurks.' WHERE `entry`=25817;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The key is rusted but it fits the lock neatly.' WHERE `entry`=25818;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Eye of Paleth? You say Fitzsimmons sent you out? By the light...not again. Fitzsimmons is dead, lad. You\'ve not the first to come to me like this, either.' WHERE `entry`=25819;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, bless your heart, to do such a thing for a married woman like me. You\'re too kind.' WHERE `entry`=25820;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew that you\'d be a special snowflake when I first set my eyes upon you, $N. So special, in fact, that I\'d trust no one else here with what I\'m about to ask of you.' WHERE `entry`=25821;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This should be enough to supply a hundred Grimtotem! Now to present the weaponry to their chieftain.' WHERE `entry`=25822;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will call for the infantry to move in and clear up whatever might be left over. If only we had ten-thousand more like you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, it\'s not encouraging, but it\'s something...' WHERE `entry`=25824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is oil! You\'re really proving yourself to be invaluable, $N! Too bad I\'m going to have to send you off now.' WHERE `entry`=25825;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is oil! You\'re the best, $N! Too bad I\'m going to have to send you off now.' WHERE `entry`=25826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Goldrinn\'s Message to Ysera',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Ysera at the World Tree in Mount Hyjal.' WHERE `entry`=25828;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I ... have not yet ... perished.' WHERE `entry`=25830;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' They stole my eggs, $C. They took them to that foul place. Corrupted them. My children stolen, tormented, killed in a vat of flame... Yes, we will make Twilight\'s Hammer pay. But I confess, part of me wants to fly up and simply watch this whole... world... burn.' WHERE `entry`=25832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The name be "Cookie," lad: greatest cook \'cross Azeroth. Now the Commander\'s told me what we be needin\' to do. To gain audience with the Grimtotem chief we\'re gonna have to cook up the finest of tauren cuisine. Ye get me the ingredients and I\'ll put together an offerin\' no tauren could refuse. Not even a grim tauren or whatever them things be.' WHERE `entry`=25834;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad that Fizzle finally sent you here. We\'re helping the tauren to retake Freewind Post and push back the Grimtotem.' WHERE `entry`=25835;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Well, it looks like it\'s time for us to part ways, at least for a while. To the northwest, the tauren of Freewind Post are in desparate need of your assistance in pushing back the Grimtotem clan!$B$BYou know, you\'ve been such a great help around here, I bet you\'re going to be their $G hero : heroine; in no-time!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am honored that you have come to help, $C. It was kind of Pozzik to send you.' WHERE `entry`=25836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Stand back, $N, there\'s about to be a flavor explosion and I wouldn\'t want ya gettin\' hurt.' WHERE `entry`=25837;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you must be the $R that Captain Tharran said he\'d be sending. I\'ve already used the deploy-a-tron to get most of the covert ops team into position at Frostmane Retreat. They\'re just waiting on your arrival.' WHERE `entry`=25838;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Don\'t worry, the feeling of being zapped won\'t stay with you for more than a few minutes. All in all, it\'s not a bad way to get where you\'re going. That parachute system needs some work, though. Very late deployment, indeed. Sometimes, too late. Anyway, we have a mission to carry out.' WHERE `entry`=25839;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent job, $N. With Battok dead, I\'ll send the signal to Captain Tharran. This should be the end of the Frostmane threat.' WHERE `entry`=25840;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Both you and the air wing performed admirably. There\'s no way that the Frostmanes will remain here now. All that remains is to begin mopping up the survivors.' WHERE `entry`=25841;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $R. I am ready now. All that I am, and all that this forest once was... it is now yours.' WHERE `entry`=25842;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The mountain blooms again! If we act quickly, we can press our advantage.$B$BOur old friend Tortolla, the Turtle Ancient, is already on the move. At his own pace, of course...$B$BFind Tortolla east of here, at the head of the path leading down into the scorched plains. Our strongholds there fell early in the campaign, but perhaps now we can reclaim them.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$R. I remember you. Savior of my children. The time has come. For vengeance.' WHERE `entry`=25843;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This... this is the greatest thing I have ever tasted. You may prove to be a valuable ally, but before the Grimtotem agree to work with the Alliance, you must agree to our terms. I will now give to you those terms as told to me by my leader. Take them back to your commander and see if he accepts.' WHERE `entry`=25844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Weapons, eh? I\'m about to make an executive decision here, $N. Let\'s hope this pays off, else King Wrynn will have my head!' WHERE `entry`=25845;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are fine weapons! Powerful steel! My warriors will be unstoppable armed with such weaponry. Magatha smiles down upon you, $N. There is but one thing I ask of you, perhaps two.' WHERE `entry`=25846;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The fight is far from over, $N. The Horde generals still live...' WHERE `entry`=25847;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Yes, ally, you have done it! It will take Hellscream weeks to recover from this blow. Southern Stonetalon belongs to the Grimtotem... and the Alliance, of course.' WHERE `entry`=25848;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='See? Not bad, eh? Why, I almost wish all my finds decided to dig themselves up for me. It\'d make my job a lot easier! Of course, you made it easier too, $N. Much obliged.' WHERE `entry`=25849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s showin\' em what for! Good on you.' WHERE `entry`=25850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Outstanding work, $N! Now our forces only need to worry about the Horde as they enter Stonetalon.' WHERE `entry`=25851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You say the Grimtotem are no longer a threat? That\'s great, but we\'ve got Horde all up our keesters!' WHERE `entry`=25852;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a relief! Maybe we can dig our way out of the hole we\'re still in, eh? No, nevermind, just a bad joke.' WHERE `entry`=25853;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful! These should be ready to hatch within the day... Now I just need to cobble up a raptor pen before they all hatch nigh-simultaneously. What could go wrong?' WHERE `entry`=25854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, wonderful! I\'ll be able to start reassembling these right away. Thank you so much!' WHERE `entry`=25855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m much obliged, $C. This\'ll go a ways towards getting my family back on their feet.' WHERE `entry`=25856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Amazing! You\'re a true hero, $N. I\'ll never forget what you\'ve done for me and my family. I know it\'s not much, but please, take this with my blessing.' WHERE `entry`=25857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Reinforcements have begun to circle the waters around the ledge, preparing for the attack. They await only your lead.' WHERE `entry`=25858;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not one slipped through to the bridge. Not one.$B$BIt was very boring. I\'d appreciate it if you shared a little next time.' WHERE `entry`=25859;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Azjentus is to be taken at his word. Lady Naz\'jar\'s Honor Guard should be sufficient to see the rest of the ritual through.' WHERE `entry`=25860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My scythe is sated. Thank you, my lady.' WHERE `entry`=25861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The crucible looks far too heavy to carry on your own, but more than enough naga forces remain to prepare it for transport.' WHERE `entry`=25862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, my Battlemaiden.$B$BThis crucible will serve as a font of power for our summoning ritual. With it, Sira\'kess will beckon our allies from the depths to bolster our already swelling forces.' WHERE `entry`=25863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A job well done. Consider this reward not from me, but from Ironforge; the preservation of Khaz Modan is a matter that concerns every dwarf.' WHERE `entry`=25864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You seem trustworthy enough to help me out with my real problem, $N. I was sent here by Ironforge to recover a shipment of gold ingots.$B$BThe ingots are part of the Ironforge Royal Treasury, stamped with the royal seal... only an idiot would steal them for profit, far too easy to trace. Oddly enough, this area is full of idiots: Mosshide Gnolls.$B$BI don\'t know how many gnolls you\'ve fought before, but they\'re foul and brutal beasts, and dangerous. I need you to slay them and recover the missing ingots.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! The Ironforge Guard appreciates this, $N. You\'ve done our city a fine favor. But something new has come up...' WHERE `entry`=25865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I don\'t suppose they agreed to come along quietly? Didn\'t think so.' WHERE `entry`=25866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That should do it! The more gnolls those fools have to chase after, the easier it\'ll be to keep them in line.' WHERE `entry`=25867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A job well done! You\'ve brought one of Ironforge\'s most wanted to justice today, $N. I\'d say you\'ve earned a mighty fine reward.' WHERE `entry`=25868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Grim business, that. No pun intended.' WHERE `entry`=25869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s a good start. Normally, I wouldn\'t wish harm on any of the Earth Mother\'s creatures. But attacking us at our most vulnerable moment?! They deserve to die!' WHERE `entry`=25870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for freeing her, $N. Those Grimtotem monsters would have killed her in cold blood.' WHERE `entry`=25871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for freeing him, $N. Those Grimtotem would have killed him in cold blood.' WHERE `entry`=25872;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A traitor amongst the tauren? I\'ve never heard of such a thing. Clan rivalries and warfare are one thing, but killing your own in cold blood.' WHERE `entry`=25873;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The cliffwatcher was a Grimtotem spy?! No wonder we had no warning! I don\'t want that damned thing. Throw it into the water and let the Longhorn name never be spoken again!' WHERE `entry`=25874;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Get in here and hug a wall! I can\'t risk blowing my cover!' WHERE `entry`=25875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='OH NO! They plan to "test" the bomb at Thal\'darah Grove! That\'s the school for young druids located in the heart of Battlescar Valley. You\'ve got to return to Barus with this information! Master Thal\'darah must be warned!' WHERE `entry`=25876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Blasted Horde! I\'ve got friends at that grove. Hopefully you know how to ride a hippogryph. We\'ve got to get you to Master Thal\'darah at the overlook immediately!' WHERE `entry`=25877;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I could see the explosions from here, $N! The Horde won\'t be refueling from Mirkfallon anymore, thanks to you!' WHERE `entry`=25878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Slowly, but surely, we pick away at the Horde\'s numbers. They won\'t have a leg to stand on when this war really opens up.' WHERE `entry`=25879;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are dire times, indeed, $N. Our outpost in Stonetalon Peak has been overrun by fiendish creatures from the depths and the Horde seeks to destroy us. We need a hero, $N; a soldier of the Alliance strong enough to guide us through these trying times.' WHERE `entry`=25880;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve assembled the survivors? Good, good. And the rest of the mountain - healed? Haha, strike me down! We\'re on the front lines again!' WHERE `entry`=25881;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you\'re the one who\'s been helping Captain Tharran beat back the Frostmane trolls? I\'ve seen your name in the reports. It\'s good to finally meet you. You might be just the $C we need to help secure the ranch.' WHERE `entry`=25882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re confident that your assault on the naga armaments has made an impact on their effectiveness.' WHERE `entry`=25883;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The waters surrounding the Holding Pens are red with the blood of the naga. Rendel would be proud!' WHERE `entry`=25884;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, yes. This is the stuff. Maybe I can gradually eat less of it and avoid that side-effect. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25885;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Terrific! Twilight\'s Hammer will no doubt try to re-take the mountain, but they\'ll have to do so without the leadership of those fat-for-brains thugs.' WHERE `entry`=25886;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is as it should be. Now the way is clear to deal these naga a crippling blow.' WHERE `entry`=25887;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let us hope for the safety of those released prisoners. In return for your noble efforts, please accept this gift.' WHERE `entry`=25888;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Praise you, $N. The hero we have been searching for has finally arrived, and not a moment too soon.' WHERE `entry`=25889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Erunak trusts this task to me?  Very well, let\'s see what we can learn from the ancient one.' WHERE `entry`=25890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do you know why the Horde destroys? The Horde destroys because they cannot comprehend beauty. They fear it and that which they fear they must destroy. Why else would they destroy Thal\'darah Grove? Together, we will make them understand. They will know that what they do comes at a great cost.' WHERE `entry`=25891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You made it! After the attack at the forward post, I thought we might be the only ones left. I\'m very glad to see you.' WHERE `entry`=25892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Impeccable timing. Like clockwork! Trouble comes. You come. Save the day. Clockwork! We\'ve devised our brilliant plan. Gloriously simple, barring the hostility of local life. Simpler yet with a you available!' WHERE `entry`=25893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Less gill goblins is good! I\'m glad that they\'re so primitive. I don\'t think I\'d want to be dealing with a race of aquatic tech-freaks right now. Not at all.' WHERE `entry`=25894;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let me see, let me see... flare gun... balloon... no rope. Never any rope. Terribly impractical if you do ask me. Rope should be mandatory.' WHERE `entry`=25895;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Kvaldir have proved a greater threat than we anticipated, but our plans are not hindered in the least. As our allies arrive, we will have a force more than sufficient to usurp the Tidehunter.$B$BAll that remains is to ensure that the ritual of summoning is completed.' WHERE `entry`=25896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is great! I love it. It should work per... ewww! Is this stuff braided with hair?$B$BDoesn\'t matter. Almost done. This thing will be ready in the twist of a rope.' WHERE `entry`=25897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect! There\'s no way they missed that, fighting or not.' WHERE `entry`=25898;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You killed how many? Well, well. Quite a show. I guess my men don\'t have any more excuses.' WHERE `entry`=25899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That didn\'t go well. For some reason, the beast won\'t speak back to me.$B$B<Duarn is clearly frustrated.>$B$BIf only Erunak had not left us!  He would know what to do.' WHERE `entry`=25900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful! Still sharp. A little blood on the fletching, but they\'ll fly true. Thank you, $N. Our defense of Hyjal can continue.' WHERE `entry`=25901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This power is ancient. Primitive. Easy. We will use it against them.' WHERE `entry`=25904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The rams you rescued have made their way back into the pen. I\'ve got members of the family on a day and night watch now. Those trolls won\'t take us by surprise again!' WHERE `entry`=25905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You were sent by the turtle god? Bless his almighty shell! I thought I was trapped down here forever.' WHERE `entry`=25906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N... although I\'m afraid I haven\'t been nearly as productive as you have.' WHERE `entry`=25907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Can you sense it?  If you have an ounce of shaman\'s blood in you, you must feel the sense of relief in the air.$B$BNespirah is pleased. Perhaps she will finally speak with us.' WHERE `entry`=25908;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' It doesn\'t look very impressive, does it?' WHERE `entry`=25909;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So it is done. Knowing that Twilight\'s Hammer is in league with creatures of malice such as these... it really curdles the blood.' WHERE `entry`=25910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That is the best news I\'ve heard in what seems like an eternity. We\'ll get the survivors moving over there to the surface as soon as possible. Perhaps we can forget that this whole nightmare ever happened. Thank you, $N. I\'m not sure there\'s anything I can do to repay you for everything you\'ve managed to accomplish in this ocean, but I will try to find a way. You should consider meeting us at the ships later, when you finish saying your goodbyes to the naga.' WHERE `entry`=25911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve found it! Elune bless you, child! Perhaps this book will give me the strength to carry on.' WHERE `entry`=25912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. Each glaive has the name of the sentinel it belonged to imprinted upon its blade. We can now send word to their families and put their souls to rest.' WHERE `entry`=25913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m afraid that the death of Harbinger Aph\'lass has not ceased the tendril attacks. You\'ve done all that you can, $N, and for that I thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah yes, yes... the secret strength of Nemesis, unearthed here in these caverns. We know all that we need to know, $N. It is time to finish this.' WHERE `entry`=25915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I had assumed that the naga were only here for those pearls. No, this makes much more sense. If they had Nespirah\'s power under their control, the amount of damage the naga could do would be catastrophic!$B$BSomething must be done.' WHERE `entry`=25916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oh, I\'m sorry. I was just imagining what these will look like with little bits of naga stuck to the ends of them. Thank you, $N. We\'ll put these to good use.' WHERE `entry`=25918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hopefully we made some progress. I\'m not sure how we\'ll know when the creature wakes up, but something tells me that it will be pretty obvious when it does.' WHERE `entry`=25919;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant work! Now I just need you and Captain Taylor to get me safely out of here. I can handle the studies from there on.' WHERE `entry`=25920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No need to bring me up to speed... Nespirah has been narrating your adventures as they happened, and Captain Taylor filled me in on the rest. Nespirah says that she is quite grateful, and that she has a small surprise ready for the naga.' WHERE `entry`=25921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It appears that I owe you my life, yet again. Thank the Light that you found me before you and your shaman activated those bio-defenses.' WHERE `entry`=25922;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The usurper has perished! Twilight\'s Hammer dreamed of creating their own pantheon of twisted ancients to rule over the land, sea, and air. With your help, they\'ve all been executed. We must tell Tortolla at once!' WHERE `entry`=25923;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not exactly the battle you had anticipated, I\'ll wager. But a battle nonetheless, as you shall soon see....' WHERE `entry`=25924;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We witnessed the detonation of the bomb. Terrible, terrible destruction... Farwatcher Glen, for better or for worse, is still intact. Unfortunately we\'ve nowhere to run.' WHERE `entry`=25925;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahhh... yes. The swamp suffers less now. More threats, though. More lurk. I can see them!' WHERE `entry`=25926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes... the flames die. There is peace now. Peace for the land.' WHERE `entry`=25927;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve been to the firelands? Nemesis is dead? So it is finished. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25928;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Here you are, $C. With this you should find maneuvering in the sea to be nearly effortless. $B$BNow we must get to work. There is much to be done in little time.' WHERE `entry`=25929;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I say, are you there, $N? It would appear that you are in the center of a dragon\'s lair.' WHERE `entry`=25930;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A smashing success! Perhaps only a minor victory against the brood of Deathwing, but a victory nonetheless!' WHERE `entry`=25931;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With your help, we\'ve managed to weaken the raiders considerably. They haven\'t suffered such losses since the raids began. Now is the time to press our advantage.' WHERE `entry`=25932;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sergeant Flinthammer? I\'m not familiar with the name, but, aye, there is a Flinthammer among the miners. He\'s one of the ones lucky enough to make it out of the mine, but most of my men are still trapped down there.' WHERE `entry`=25933;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. This will allow me to finish my last task and hopefully gain the form of the wolf!' WHERE `entry`=25934;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. The dogs will be well fed and ready to defend our outpost for weeks!' WHERE `entry`=25935;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='While you were away, I was able to revive some of the fallen warriors. We\'ll need every hand if we are to survive here.' WHERE `entry`=25936;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for recovering these artifacts. I will see to it that they are displayed in the Ironforge museum along with the story of those who died to recover them.' WHERE `entry`=25937;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hold there, stranger!' WHERE `entry`=25938;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='In sparing the land further suffering, you\'ve also helped us soothe the Greenwarden. Many thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25939;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The forest is being devoured!' WHERE `entry`=25940;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hear you, $R.$B$BI understand the urgency, but these men are in no condition to fight.' WHERE `entry`=25941;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let us hope that your work has bought us the time we need...' WHERE `entry`=25942;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good grub. Soon we\'ll be back to fighting strength.' WHERE `entry`=25943;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $R. Our chances of survival are increasing.' WHERE `entry`=25944;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='While you remain in Stonetalon and fight as a Krom\'gar soldier you will remain suited up! Am I clear? DO you hear me, grunt? If I see you without Hellscream\'s beloved tabard I will put my foot so far up your backside that you\'ll be spitting up laces.' WHERE `entry`=25945;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Take the Alliance S.E.A.L. Equipment to Legionnaire Nazgrim at The Immortal Coil.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Blood and Thunder! This changes everything, $C!' WHERE `entry`=25946;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! Now, more than ever, we are prepared to face the naga!' WHERE `entry`=25947;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No time to address the Vanguard. Just as well...' WHERE `entry`=25948;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Earthen Ring has received my distress message and sent help - just in time it would seem. Hopefully more can be sent soon. We are but few against a great many.' WHERE `entry`=25949;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Chicken and rice, $N! That will show those sorry and sad snakes who\'s the ol\' pitch and toss! Now it\'s bird lime for that tiddlywink. Finger and thumb or plink plonk?' WHERE `entry`=25950;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Get to the bridge on the east, quickly. Lady Naz\'jar and the Fathom-Lord should be there with whatever forces remain.$B$BFollow our Lady\'s direction, as always. Hold the bridge until we can complete the ritual.$B$BOnce our allies arrive, the Kvaldir will be doomed.',`objectives_loc1`='Hold the bridge on Quel\'Dormir Terrace until Lady Sira\'kess\' allies arrive.$B$BThis task is part of a Naz\'jar Battlemaiden vision. If needed, use the Blade of the Naz\'jar Battlemaiden at a time focus to return to the vision.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I could ask for no more proficient a Battlemaiden than you. You have done yourself a great honor this day.' WHERE `entry`=25951;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $C.$B$BI will get some patrols out of our own to make sure that no more naga get within sight of this cave. We should have the area secured within the hour.' WHERE `entry`=25952;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N, and just in time too. The Captain just started sending more men out. Strong axe arms, but I doubt they possess quite the same awareness and finesse that you do.$B$BWe were lucky to have you here when things went south. I suspect you will have a large role to play in things to come as well.' WHERE `entry`=25953;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you so much for taking this seriously.$B$BThis is some of the first definitive proof of other members of the Vashj family. Very interesting. And I\'d never even heard of either of the other two figures you mentioned until now.$B$BSo much of our history was lost during the sundering - it\'s exciting to have a chance at reclaiming some of it.' WHERE `entry`=25954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Ranger Valarian statue',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='High Priestess Siralen statue' WHERE `entry`=25954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is good intel. You have a sharp eye, $C.$B$BIt sounds like the building north of the gardens will make a suitable forward post. I will send some men immediately to start defensive preparations and we will reposition there as soon as possible.' WHERE `entry`=25955;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A shard of metal?$B$BThe remains you describe sound much like the sea vrykul we encountered in Northrend. We\'ll not be striking any alliances with their sort, no matter the cause. Still, this information may prove useful in the future.$B$BI will think on it further if time permits. Thank you for bringing it to my attention.' WHERE `entry`=25956;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A Battlemaiden? I never heard of such a thing.$B$BThe way you explain it, it sounds like the naga forces are far greater in scope than the Captain could possibly have realized. We might be able to learn more through the blade if we can find other locations where this Battlemaiden was present, but the information you gave me makes me fear for the captain and his soldiers. We must warn them.' WHERE `entry`=25957;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you again, $C. I almost thought we\'d lost you to the Wavespeaker\'s fool errand.$B$BDid anything come of it?' WHERE `entry`=25958;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='More naga are amassing to the south than reported too it seems. We shall have to move quickly then.' WHERE `entry`=25959;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are perhaps the most dependable $R I\'ve ever met. I wish I could have more men that showed half as much pride as you do.' WHERE `entry`=25960;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are brave indeed! I\'ve seen you battling all manner of murloc, naga, and pointy-toothed fish, but that was nothing! The way you just sling those kelp bulbs under your arm like that is a whole new kind of fearless. BOOM! You could blow up at any second.$B$BYou\'re my kind of $R.' WHERE `entry`=25962;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did great up there, soldier! You devastated their ranks, but there were far more than we accounted for, and most of my men went down out there in the masses of naga.$B$BWe\'ll need to hold this position as long as possible to buy them time. Hopefully some of them will still make it to the rendezvous.' WHERE `entry`=25963;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you. Truly.$B$BWe need to get these men moving as soon as possible. I\'ll meet you back at the forward post soon, I\'m sure.' WHERE `entry`=25964;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Still so many? They must want something very important here to come in such numbers.$B$BI will be honest with you, $N, because you deserve at least that: I don\'t know how much hope there is. We will retreat shortly, but we won\'t be able to defend ourselves when they strike back. We don\'t have anywhere to run... we\'re running out of options.$B$BI\'m sorry, I should keep such thoughts to myself. Do me a favor and don\'t mention any of that to the men. I\'ll figure something out.' WHERE `entry`=25965;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re finished! Just in time. I don\'t think we could have held them much longer.$B$BAn artifact? Could this be something we can use against the naga? I suppose that would require finding it.$B$BWe may have to attend to more pressing matters first, until an opportunity to pursue this further presents itself.' WHERE `entry`=25966;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You made it! After the attack at the forward post, I thought we might be the only ones left. It\'s good to see you in one piece, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25967;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at you, a regular aquatic hero! Trouble comes. You come. Save the day. You must be proud of yourself!$B$BWe\'ve devised our brilliant plan. Gloriously simple, barring the hostility of local life. Simpler yet with a you available!' WHERE `entry`=25968;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Less gilblins is good.$B$BI\'m glad that they\'re so primitive. I don\'t think I\'d want to be dealing with a race of aquatic tech-freaks right now.' WHERE `entry`=25969;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let me see, let me see... flare gun... balloon... no rope. Never any rope. Terribly impractical if you do ask me. Rope should be mandatory.' WHERE `entry`=25970;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is great! I love it. It should work per... ewww! Is this stuff braided with hair?$B$BDoesn\'t matter. Almost done. This thing will be ready in the twist of a rope.' WHERE `entry`=25971;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect! There\'s no way they missed that, fighting or not.' WHERE `entry`=25972;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That is the best news I\'ve ever heard. We\'ll get the survivors moving over there to the surface as soon as possible. Perhaps we can forget that this whole nightmare ever happened.$B$BThank you, $N. You\'ve shown your worth down here. There will be a glorious spot in the Horde for you.$B$BYou should consider meeting us at the ships later, when you finish saying your goodbyes to the naga.' WHERE `entry`=25973;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice, $N! That will show those naga who\'s the boss!$B$BNow it\'s time for that drink. You want rum or wine?' WHERE `entry`=25974;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That should be enough for now. We know where there\'s more should the need arise.' WHERE `entry`=25975;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a lot! And we know where there\'s more should the need arise.' WHERE `entry`=25976;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice Uncle Bob of pokin\' their general.' WHERE `entry`=25977;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it! The mountaineers are returning to camp and our medics will have their hands full. We are all in your debt, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is never easy to countenance violence against the very elements whose powers I wield, but sometimes there is no other solution. Our duty to the people of Dun Morogh comes first.' WHERE `entry`=25979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Stuck him right through, did you? I would have loved to have seen that!' WHERE `entry`=25980;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, they\'re ugly, but they mostly look harmless. Smelly though. Here, let me clean the gilblin stuff out of these. I\'ve got an idea....' WHERE `entry`=25981;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, they\'re ugly, but they mostly look harmless. Mostly. They\'re almost cute in a way.$B$BHere, let me clean the gilblin stuff out of these. I\'ve got an idea....' WHERE `entry`=25982;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s very disturbing news, but I believe our Earthen Ring friends here have a plan. And now that you\'re here....' WHERE `entry`=25983;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If it weren\'t you saying it, I wouldn\'t believe what that troublesome goblin has to say. This is troubling indeed, but I think our Earthen Ring friends have a few ideas.$B$BAnd now that you\'re here....' WHERE `entry`=25984;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, you were sent here by Tiala? A wonderful student, she\'ll do many great things. Although I sense even greater potential from you. Please, stay a while in our shrine. There\'s much to do, but you can\'t accomplish anything with a troubled mind.' WHERE `entry`=25985;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s a good thing the Senator didn\'t come out here on his own. It\'s dangerous, and we\'re going to need all the help we can get to get the situation under control.' WHERE `entry`=25986;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What happened? That thing wasn\'t completely dead! Maybe I should stick to mechanical stuff. It gave you a vision? Of killing all of us?! That doesn\'t sound good. Well, in any case, that Earthen Ring fellow, Erunak Stonespeaker, wants these specimens all taken out to him. I\'ll make sure he gets them. I don\'t want them anywhere near me.' WHERE `entry`=25987;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My bad. My name is Fiasco for a reason. I should have known that thing wasn\'t completely dead when it wiggled a little.$B$BYou say it gave you a vision? Of killing all of us?! That doesn\'t sound good.$B$BHrm, well that Earthen Ring fellow, Erunak Stonespeaker, wants these specimens all taken out to him. I\'ll make sure they get out there. It\'s not like I want them stinking up the place around here.' WHERE `entry`=25988;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Duarn looks at the crab and disguises a frown.>$B$BIt doesn\'t look very impressive, does it?' WHERE `entry`=25989;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I had assumed that the naga were only here for those pearls. No, this makes much more sense. If they had Nespirah\'s power under their control, the amount of damage the naga could do would be catastrophic!$B$BSomething must be done.' WHERE `entry`=25990;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Captain Vilethorn admires the polearms you present him.>$B$BOh, I\'m sorry. I was just imagining what these will look like with little bits of naga stuck to the ends of them. Thank you, $N. We\'ll put these to good use.' WHERE `entry`=25992;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hopefully we made some progress. I\'m not sure how we\'ll know when the creature wakes up, but something tells me that it will be pretty obvious when it does.' WHERE `entry`=25993;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant work!$B$B<Tulra tucks the pearls away beneath her armor.>$B$BNow I just need you and Legionnaire Nazgrim to get me safely out of here. I can handle the studies from there on.' WHERE `entry`=25994;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No need to bring me up to speed... Nespirah has been narrating your adventures as they happened, and Legionnaire Nazgrim filled me in on the rest.$B$B<Duarn closes his eyes and nods.>$B$BNespirah says that she is quite grateful, and that she has a small surprise ready for the naga.' WHERE `entry`=25995;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It appears that I owe you my life, yet again. Thank Hellscream that you found me before you and your shaman activated those bio-defenses.' WHERE `entry`=25996;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew they weren\'t here to see the sights. This is more serious than we thought! This is no mere raid. The Dark Irons intend to cripple the defense of Ironforge itself!' WHERE `entry`=25997;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank goodness you\'re here, $N. The airfield\'s been attacked by the Dark Irons and I don\'t think we can hold out much longer.' WHERE `entry`=25998;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You have all of your limbs intact. This is a first.' WHERE `entry`=25999;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='...$R? Here? I must be mad...' WHERE `entry`=26000;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Blastgineer Fuzzwhistle is definitely dead. It\'s probably for the best. It looks like he\'s holding a note in his hand.' WHERE `entry`=26001;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Damn shame... He was a good goblin. As for you, $N, you\'ve done well. These attack plans will help us prepare. I want you to deliver the plans to Overlord Krom\'gar personally! There\'s sure to be a promotion in it for you.' WHERE `entry`=26002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, brother! Now they will know that they cannot sneak up on the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=26003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Hmm. Perhaps this grunt is more than he would appear. Perhaps this grunt is in actuality a sergeant. Look now upon Krom\'gar Sergeant $N, soldiers. He has come to serve warning of a cowardly Alliance attack. An attack that we will CRUSH!' WHERE `entry`=26004;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Find Captain Taylor aboard Voldrin\'s Hold, on the surface above the Ruins of Vashj\'ir.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You made it out! Good to see you, $N. It\'s good to be out of the water for a bit, and to have some resources at our disposal again. I\'m sure many of the boys would give anything to turn around and head home after what we\'ve been though, but we still have a grim task ahead. What about you? Want to stick it through to the end with us? I wouldn\'t blame you if you\'ve had your fill.' WHERE `entry`=26005;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Find Legionnaire Nazgrim aboard the Stygian Bounty, on the surface above the Ruins of Vashj\'ir.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like you make it out in one piece, $C!$B$BIt\'s good to be out of that foul pit of water for a moment, and to have some resources at our disposal again. Don\'t get too comfortable though, we still have a grim task ahead.$B$BWhat about you? Had enough honor for one day, or do you want to get back in there and make Hellscream proud?' WHERE `entry`=26006;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, it\'s not encouraging, but it\'s something...' WHERE `entry`=26007;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let us hope for the safety of those released prisoners. In return for your noble efforts, please accept this gift.' WHERE `entry`=26008;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Much more blood shall be spilled upon this soil before this war is over. Alliance blood...' WHERE `entry`=26009;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lok\'tar! Alliance pigs! Enjoy the victory for it shall be short lived. Your bravery has given us more time to prepare, nothing more.' WHERE `entry`=26010;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did you find any suspicious documents at Paltrow\'s camp? Perhaps on his rotting corpse? Any insight into the Alliance\'s attack patterns would be extremely helpful in the battle for Stonetalon.' WHERE `entry`=26011;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for heeding Rhonin\'s call, brave adventurer. Let me share with you what we know regarding recent events, and any assistance you might offer would be greatly appreciated.' WHERE `entry`=26012;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$R, something terrible has transpired within the Ruby Sanctum beneath the Temple.$B$BThe entry to the Sanctum is in ruins, and its guardians violently slain. We sent scouts to investigate, but they have not returned. I cannot help but fear the worst.$B$BEnter the Ruby Sanctum and discover what has befallen the home of my flight. Once we have more information, we can plan our next steps accordingly.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you again, $C, for rescuing me from Baltharus\'s clutches! There is still much work to be done, however....' WHERE `entry`=26013;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Of course we haven\'t returned yet!  We\'ve had our fair share of setbacks... not the least of which was the passing of my dear brother Oskar. He lost his grip and floated away, the poor lad!  He thought he\'d grab some fish to bring back to the captain, but he floated off, and was eaten by one o\' those... those great-eels!  Bwaaaah ha ha haaaah!' WHERE `entry`=26014;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' There ya go. It\'s beautiful!  Oskar would be proud.' WHERE `entry`=26015;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Paltrow, establish a foothold in Windshear Valley. A strong ground assault is vital to our campaign! When we make our assault against Krom\'gar, your men will provide the chaos and confusion that the gnome flying machines will need to get close enough to bomb the orc fortress.$B$BThe flying machines will detonate the Krom\'gar bomb while it\'s sitting in their base, taking out the entire fortress in the process.$B$BBurn after reading.$B$B-Force Commander Valen$B$BNorthwatch Expedition Base Camp',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver the Orders from Base Camp to Overlord Krom\'gar at Krom\'gar Fortress in Stonetalon Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gnomish flying machines? Our anti-air cannons are still not functional! We will be sitting ducks. I require time to plan... to think... The hot air balloon and its payload cannot remain at Krom\'gar Fortress. I must make arrangements to move the balloon to another location. Our plans to destroy Windshear Hold with it are foiled.' WHERE `entry`=26016;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya did good, $N!  Ya did real good!' WHERE `entry`=26017;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Hmm... they sound like regular ol\' murlocs... just underwater. That\'ll make Cap\'n Glovaal happy.' WHERE `entry`=26018;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Whaaa... an egg?  An EEL egg? We can definitely do something with this!  Get ready kid, \'cause it\'s time for some good ol\'-fashioned Digsong revenge!' WHERE `entry`=26019;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Properly motivated? Wha... what does that mean? Listen, Sergeant, I have a built in mechanism for survival called self-interest. That is, it\'s in my best interest to NOT DIE. With that said, there\'s no fixing these guns without the right materials.' WHERE `entry`=26020;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oskar\'s alive?  Wait... what did ya say?  Ya let him FLOAT AWAY AGAIN?! Well... ya held up your end of the bargain, and I appreciate everything ya\'ve done, $N. Here... take this. I\'ve only been hanging onto it as ballast, but it doesn\'t seem to be doing much good.' WHERE `entry`=26021;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is but a prelude to the slaughter we will visit upon these lands. All will know our name. You have done well, $N. Victory for Sylvanas!' WHERE `entry`=26022;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes... I was once Prince of the fallen kingdom of Stromgarde. I was cut down by the one seeking Trol\'kalar. I rue my foolish life now. I serve...only Sylvanas.' WHERE `entry`=26023;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='A bounty has been placed on the head of Marez Cowl, a high-level advisor and operative of the Syndicate. She was last seen within the Syndicate controlled territory of Stromgarde.$B$BBounty may be collected from Captain Nials.$B$BBe warned: Marez is a skilled and cunning Warlock, known for her trafficking with demons. Extreme caution is advised when hunting her.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring Marez\'s head to Captain Nials at Refuge Pointe.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You took down Marez Cowl?  Well done, $N. Well done indeed!$B$BMarez menaced our Stromgarde defenders, and it is rumored she was an emissary between the Syndicate and some other, darker power. We are glad to see that she\'ll no longer ply her powers against us.' WHERE `entry`=26024;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My restless nights will turn to peaceful slumber when I have destroyed this orb. Thank you, $N. It is a chilling reminder of the terrible power the demons held over the orcs before Hellscream released them from their curse.' WHERE `entry`=26025;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Mr. D you\'re gonna be ok! Hooray! Oh, Mr. D! I knew it!' WHERE `entry`=26026;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Cleared out properly? Good. I doubt we\'ll even bother to lurk in Stromgarde. That ramshackle hole needs to be razed into dust. The land would make a decent spot for a new Undercity in its place.' WHERE `entry`=26027;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I am - perhaps for the first time in my life - at a loss for words. I am really not sure where Clarissa even came from...' WHERE `entry`=26028;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the fate of all who would stand in our way.' WHERE `entry`=26029;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hated the Syndicate in life as much as I do in death. To see the sigil again is a small comfort. But we have much more work to do... for Sylvanas.' WHERE `entry`=26030;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thoradin was the founder of Arathor. Just as I join these fragments together, he joined the scattered tribes of humans into their first great nation. But I\'m sure you\'re not interested in such drivel. Forgive me. Old memories are often hard to bury.' WHERE `entry`=26031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Valorcall was loyal to me in life. His death will not be something I bear lightly. But bear it I must. I am Forsaken. My old existence means nothing. The sigils are ours; Trol\'kalar awaits.' WHERE `entry`=26032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Trol\'kalar, my father\'s blade... it seems like it\'s been an eternity since I saw it.' WHERE `entry`=26033;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' We owe you a debt of gratitude, mortal, for driving the invaders from the Sanctum. But this news of the Destroyer is troubling beyond words. I have much to discuss with the other members of the Accord. Take these as a token of my thanks, as you gird yourselves for the coming storm.' WHERE `entry`=26034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad. Since it\'s clear you\'ve got your head on straight, I was hoping you could help us with a more pressing job.' WHERE `entry`=26035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant, $N. One item down an\' three more to go, based on my list. The other three items are all in Stromgarde.$B$BTake a rest an\' get your strength back--the next phase of my plan\'ll require a little more time an\' effort. Come back to me after you\'ve gotten a warm meal an\' some rest.' WHERE `entry`=26036;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You amaze me, $N. Well done again. Give me a moment to cast the proper spell an\' you\'ll be ready.' WHERE `entry`=26037;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Malin couldn\'t\'ve asked a worthier person to come here an\' aid us, $N. You\'ve done a grand job!$B$BHe\'ll be pleased to see what an overwhelming success our mission\'s been.' WHERE `entry`=26038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah! You activated these shards. Already I feel more myself!$B$BBut alas, I am still far from free...' WHERE `entry`=26039;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, yes. This is the stuff. Maybe I can wean off of it and avoid the side-effect. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26040;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You have done it!  You opened the Stones of Binding!  I can feel the shackles about me loosen, and freedom draws ever closer. You are a noble $C, $N. My rescuer!' WHERE `entry`=26041;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You place the rod in the keystone. And a shudder is felt beneath you...' WHERE `entry`=26042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A testament to the might of the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=26043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Um... Well you see, it\'s quite simple... THIS CAVE IS SWARMING WITH SOULLESS KILLING MACHINES!' WHERE `entry`=26044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll be damned! You managed to get the parts and not die. How are you only a sergeant?' WHERE `entry`=26045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Get the parts, kill the elementals and rescue the peons... We get all of that done and we\'re as good as promoted!' WHERE `entry`=26046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew it! You are a hero! If I have anything to do with it, you\'ll be promoted to legionnaire!' WHERE `entry`=26047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just in time! The flying machines are starting to mass. Attack is imminent!' WHERE `entry`=26048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As the eldritch shackles are placed around the Shards, an unhuman wail is heard from far below. The scream is followed by a roar.$B$BThe Shards of Myzrael no longer invoke feelings of warmth and security as they once did. Now they pulse with an open menace... as if the thing beneath them holds ill will toward the surface.' WHERE `entry`=26049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The goggles work perfectly now! Well done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most superb, $N! The Captain will be very pleased! And just wait until word gets back to Fleetmaster Seahorn!' WHERE `entry`=26051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So the little gnomes proved their worth after all? I knew we kept those ankle biters around for a reason!' WHERE `entry`=26052;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. The march of the Forsaken continues.' WHERE `entry`=26053;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sandfury trolls and the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer, you say? And they meant to send some giant monster into the heart of the city?! Well done! Stormwind is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=26054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work out there, $N.$B$BThose scum deserved what they got. While nothin\' will ever bring me ship or me crew back, the death of those naga gives me some solace.' WHERE `entry`=26055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I sure am glad you\'re here!' WHERE `entry`=26056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I sure am glad you\'re here!' WHERE `entry`=26057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have never seen such an act of bravery. You saved the base, sergeant - or should I say legionnaire! Lok\'tar!' WHERE `entry`=26058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see that Krom\'gar has sent his best! Good, we have much work to do. The filth that is the Alliance have entered into a treaty with the Grimtotem. Now we fend off attacks from both forces. We are spread thin across the Greatwood Vale and will soon fall beneath the concerted effort of our enemies. There is only one hope: VOODOO!' WHERE `entry`=26059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. Once I have everything I need I will mix it all together and unleash the voodoo! Woe unto our enemies!' WHERE `entry`=26060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. Once I have everything I need I will mix it all together and unleash the voodoo! Woe unto our enemies!' WHERE `entry`=26061;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Finally! Now I will create the charm that will hold the voodoo enchantment!' WHERE `entry`=26062;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Darn still not very happy, but Darn will reward you for what you have done.' WHERE `entry`=26063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. These eggs should get us through the week.' WHERE `entry`=26064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N.$B$BThese nightmarish creatures that rise from below give me pause. I fear that our efforts will be for nothing.' WHERE `entry`=26065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='In times of crisis, a desperate act may be all that is needed to secure victory. Sending a swarm of kobolds at the enemy may be the edge that we need to win.' WHERE `entry`=26066;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Victory, at last! Though it stands to reason that without a stable supply line this victory will be short lived. Enjoy it while it lasts, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26067;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Fascinating tale, friend. It would seem that our newfound kobold allies might be somewhat useful after all!' WHERE `entry`=26068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The situation is grim, $R. We need all of the help that we can get!' WHERE `entry`=26069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Our Earthen Ring friends here are wondering if we can lend them a hand. There are faceless down below in the Scalding Chasm that are defiling all of the wildlife.$B$BCan you take care of that for me?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good enough for me. Don\'t get too complacent, $N. The hard part\'s about to come.' WHERE `entry`=26070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done.$B$BDon\'t get too full of yourself, $N. The hard part\'s about to come.' WHERE `entry`=26071;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, $R, can you feel them seething with a desire to break free and destroy us?$B$BThis is good! They will be the perfect lure for their leader.' WHERE `entry`=26072;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lok\'tar ogar! You are the embodiment of what it means to be a Horde soldier, $N. If only we had more like you, this war would be over and Kalimdor would belong to the Horde - UNCONTESTED! Rise now as a champion of Krom\'gar!' WHERE `entry`=26073;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Krom\'gar has sent his champion! Well you haven\'t a thing to worry about, Champion. We\'ll get the balloon all fueled up in no time. How about you lend a hand around here while you wait?' WHERE `entry`=26074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I sure hope you didn\'t miss any. I don\'t think I can take much more of this!' WHERE `entry`=26075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And they called me crazy. I knew this place was crawling with spies. Poop too.' WHERE `entry`=26076;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Chieftain Cliffwalker and his tauren seek to commit treason against the Horde! They claim that the ancient tree at the heart of Battlescar Valley is merely a school for druids. They are blind to the fact that desperate measures are taken during war time. My scouts have assured me that the night elves hide a weapon of great power within that tree. We\'re going to end this now!' WHERE `entry`=26077;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! My men are working hard on getting our flying machines and steam tanks back into the fight.' WHERE `entry`=26078;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Stromgarde Militia has placed bounties on the heads of Lord Falconcrest, and his bodyguard Otto. Falconcrest heads the Syndicate\'s efforts in the Arathi Highlands, and his death would cause a major disruption in those efforts.$B$BHis bodyguard Otto, although not a strategic target, is a fierce opponent and has killed dozens of our defenders.$B$BTheir bounties may be collected from Captain Nials.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring Otto\'s Head and Falconcrest\'s Head to Captain Nials at Refuge Pointe.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Falconcrest and Otto? Wonderful!$B$BHere is your reward, $N. I am happy to pay it.' WHERE `entry`=26079;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see. Yes, I am rememberink now... Humphrey and Oskar vere not the strongest svimmers. The reconnaissance is helpful, and the extra fish look very tasty. If you are seeink Mister Digsong before he returns, please send him my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=26080;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The news of your victory satisfies me, $C... a rare sensation. The Dark Lady herself has mused that our conquest of Lordaeron may be the only way the Forsaken can find true satisfaction, and pehaps even relief. But it matters not. Our victory is inevitable. For your loyal service to the Forsaken, I award you in the name of Sylvanas.' WHERE `entry`=26081;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You possess quite a talent for destruction, $N. Whatever Alliance remain after your rampage across Battlescar Valley will be dealt with by the bomb.' WHERE `entry`=26082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You friends with Goutgut! Him weird ogre. Smell funny.' WHERE `entry`=26083;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Throm\'ka, $C. If your deeds for the undead are as great as you claim, I am honored to help you serve the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=26084;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The men are finding hidden reserves of strength and courage to deal with the Dark Iron onslaught. The airfield will not fall on our watch!' WHERE `entry`=26085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gah!  These fish are impossible to hit!$B$B<Orako looks at you.>$B$BMy wolf got eaten by a fish, and I\'m not going back until I find her.' WHERE `entry`=26086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Shooting fish in a barrel is easy. Shooting fish in an ocean is a little harder.$B$BHave you seen the murlocs down in the canyon, $C?  They don\'t shoot at all!  They have little balls full of glow-juice on their heads that make the fish come to THEM. Hey, we should try that!$B$BGo south, and kill the crabs and groupers in the canyon. They have lots of glow-juice in their skin. I\'ve seen it!',`objectives_loc1`='Obtain 6 gobs of Glow-Juice from Pyreshell Scuttlers and Luxscale Groupers in Underlight Canyon.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, look at how glowy it is!$B$B<Orako looks wistfully off into the distance.>$B$BMy wolf loved things that were glowy...' WHERE `entry`=26087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... you got a lot of fish, but none of these are the ones that ate my wolf. I think it was probably a bigger fish.' WHERE `entry`=26088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I know, murlocs aren\'t fish. I thought that killing them would make me feel better, but I still feel sad about my wolf.$B$B<Orako sighs.>' WHERE `entry`=26089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That is a big egg.$B$B<Orako sniffs it.>$B$BIt is big, and it smells like fish. Maybe the big fish that made this egg is the big fish that ate my wolf!' WHERE `entry`=26090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Orako is busy playing with Wolf.>$B$BOh, thank you, $N!  I knew Wolf was alive!$B$BHere, take one of these. I don\'t need them anymore.' WHERE `entry`=26091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is his report?!  That idiot...$B$BI suppose we can use the food. Thanks, $N. You\'ve done as well as can be expected.' WHERE `entry`=26092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good, $N. The last thing we need with the undead looming is a gang of common thieves distracting us.' WHERE `entry`=26093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The momentum is starting to shift, $N, largely due to your efforts. Now, it is time to strike at the Dark Iron leadership.' WHERE `entry`=26094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. We will inform the families of these fallen soldiers that they were killed in battle.$B$BIt will be grim news to bear, but it is better than the uncertainty of a missing loved one.' WHERE `entry`=26095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will use the mushrooms as a reagent to treat the corpses. We will have one ready for you soon.' WHERE `entry`=26096;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Orthus is dead. He is clutching something in his hand.' WHERE `entry`=26097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You saw with your own eyes, $N. General Grebo attacked us! Now what will we do? Surely the Warchief will have us all executed for treason.' WHERE `entry`=26099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='WHAT? My General has been killed by the tauren? This is treason! HIGH TREASON! They will pay for this grievous error.' WHERE `entry`=26100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The traitorous tauren will now stand by as we destroy his precious grove and burn his village to the ground!' WHERE `entry`=26101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve done it! Without your help, Ironforge Airfield would surely be occupied by the enemy and the Dark Irons would have a clear road to Ironforge itself. The Council of Three Hammers must be informed of what happened here.' WHERE `entry`=26102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Yes, I think this will do.' WHERE `entry`=26103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did well, $N. We need to be especially wary of Horde attacks right now. The Pincer X2 has plenty of firepower at sea, but in the back of this cave, she is exceptionally vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you considered a career in science, $N?  If you ever get tired of this $C nonsense, come see me!  I could use an assistant with your devotion to experimentation and the scientific method.' WHERE `entry`=26106;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The lethargy that overcame me even after the camps fell was so strong, I refused this gift when it was first given to me. Now, I am proud to do my part in the name of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=26107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As Tor\'gan taught me, I transfer the power and the spirit of the raptors into this orb. It will imbue our warriors with the fiery strength and intelligence of the raptor. The guile of the raptor is yours now as well, $C. Take it with pride, for the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=26108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It\'s funny. Kin and I have been through so much together, and here we find ourselves back in Arathi, like so many years ago.$B$BWe broke up a plot to create a new plague right here, her and I. It doesn\'t look like the horde learned their lesson, because they\'re all over this farm yet again.$B$BTheir undead courier is shuffling around as obvious as daylight. If you want to help, find the courier and bring back whatever they\'re carrying.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Apothecaries yet again. You think they\'d get the message. Let\'s see what it is this time...' WHERE `entry`=26110;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And now we will see if we can get you into L\'ghorek to speak with it before it dies.' WHERE `entry`=26111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And just what is this? This is impossible!' WHERE `entry`=26112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Horde have held Go\'shek farm to the east for a long time; it\'s never been of much concern compared to the rest of our problems here. But there\'s been reports of undead activity in the area.$B$BAnything more alarming than shuffling peons over there warrants investigation. This isn\'t the first time the undead have been up to no good at the farm, so I\'ve sent my best scouts there to check it out. Report to Quae and Kinelory and they\'ll fill you in.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Refuge Pointe sent you? Good to know they\'re still there. We\'ve got some interesting things to check into here, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The plague took our friends and family, but it was the Forsaken that took Phin. They\'re just as bad as the Scourge. I\'ll destroy every one of them with my own hands if I have to. When you\'re prepared, come let me know. We\'ll get started right away.' WHERE `entry`=26114;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now you truly know what it means to be a member of the Horde, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done a great service for us, $N. Thank you.$B$BI hope Kin wasn\'t too much of a handful down there. She\'s very friendly, but can be just as deadly when you\'re her enemy.' WHERE `entry`=26116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I admit I\'m impressed, $C. It\'s a small comfort amidst all that\'s happened here. You have fought the undead, struck back against the Horde, and honored the memory of the victims of Southshore. On behalf of the kingdom of Stromgarde, I present you with an official commendation, and this reward.' WHERE `entry`=26117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The ambassador will trouble us no more. He is not the only Dark Iron $R whose heart still belongs to Twilight\'s Hammer. We must remember that and remain vigilant against their schemes, else my son will inherit only ruins and ashes.' WHERE `entry`=26118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The orcs will know better than to press further west now. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=26120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You are seeink spies up above?  This is not good... not good at all, comrade.$B$BReturn to Korthun\'s End and destroy them, my friend.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did well, $N. We need to be especially wary of Horde attacks right now. The Pincer X2 has plenty of firepower at sea, but in the back of this cave, she is exceptionally vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Fiasco sticks a finger into each sample and sniffs it.>$B$BYes, I think this will do.' WHERE `entry`=26122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did well, $N. We need to be especially wary of Alliance attacks right now. The Verne\'s got plenty of firepower out at sea, but in the back of this cave, she\'s far too vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You saw spies up above?  This is not good... I won\'t have it.$B$BReturn to Seabrush and get rid of them before they start trickling into our hideout.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did well, $N. We need to be especially wary of Alliance attacks right now. The Verne\'s got plenty of firepower out at sea, but in the back of this cave, she\'s far too vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it. Starting today, I\'m shifting the Verne over to bio-fuel. I\'ll send some men up to harvest more oil.$B$BThink of all the sea creatures that we\'ve saved today, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good show, lad, but we\'ve no time to celebrate. Thandol Span\'s in danger!' WHERE `entry`=26127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And good riddance! Thandol Span\'s safe thanks to you, $N, and hopefully Calamoth is down for good this time.' WHERE `entry`=26128;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Rebel arsenals?  In my own city? What in the bloody hell was Crowley up to?' WHERE `entry`=26129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that you have unplugged L\'ghorek, we must attempt to make contact with it. I can sense that the ancient yet lives, but only barely.' WHERE `entry`=26130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You don\'t know how glad I am to see fresh faces from Ironforge. Perhaps sending Mountaineer Barleybrew wasn\'t a waste after all.' WHERE `entry`=26131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The last thing we needed was a bunch of summoned creatures swarming our forces during the final assault.' WHERE `entry`=26132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s one less thing we need to think about during the final assault.' WHERE `entry`=26133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Minions of the Old God? Two very potent foes have joined forces then. Their hope to defeat the Tidehunter may not be so foolish after all.$B$B$N, we can\'t let that happen. If Azshara defeats the Tidehunter and takes his power for herself, I\'m not sure any number of us could ever hope to oppose her on the seas.$B$BThe first step is clear at least - we need to hunt down the fiend that destroyed our ships. The navy was confident enough to bring in a new fleet, perhaps they have a plan.' WHERE `entry`=26135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, well met, $C. Stormpike sent you? About the keg? Hoo boy...' WHERE `entry`=26137;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I suppose I owe Thargas a favor for sending such a bold hero my way. Or perhaps he just wanted to keep all the clean-up for himself. Regardless, you\'ll find much to do here for the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=26139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='WISE OF... YOUR ERUNAK TO... HAVE... YOU USE... THE FACELESS\' BRAIN. I SEE... YOU NOW.$B$BI WILL DIE. THERE IS NO... STOPPING... THE INEVITABLE.$B$BBUT... YOU WILL HELP... ME DEAL WITH... THESE PARASITES FIRST.' WHERE `entry`=26140;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='WE WILL USE... THESE... RUNESTONES TO ALLOW... YOU TO POSSESS... ONE OF... THE WATER ELEMENTALS.' WHERE `entry`=26141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='THEY SHALL ASCEND... NO MORE!' WHERE `entry`=26142;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='YOU HAVE DONE... MYSELF AND... THE TIDEHUNTER GREAT... SERVICE.' WHERE `entry`=26143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am quite impressed, $N. You have done the Dwarven race a great favor by defending our lands. King Magni Bronzebeard himself would be proud!' WHERE `entry`=26145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N!  You demonstrated uncanny courage on the battlefield. Our war against the Troggs will be won with efforts such as yours. You have served King Magni well.' WHERE `entry`=26146;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew the second I laid eyes on you, $N, that you would make Ironforge proud. You have served our people well. I salute you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most excellent, $N! You have brought hope to Loch Modan. With Grawmug dead, we stand a better chance of seeing the Troggs eliminated from the land.' WHERE `entry`=26148;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A job well done. Now you don\'t need to worry about what would have happened to them if you hadn\'t been around.$B$BThe last one was even appreciative enough to give you a reward they\'d kept hidden on their person.' WHERE `entry`=26149;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='William sent you? Bless his soul. I... I\'m ok... It\'s just... Well...' WHERE `entry`=26150;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I was asked to bring this to your attention as soon as you returned from the kobold camps, $N. It appears to be a letter sealed with the insignia of the void - no doubt a message from our local warlock trainer. I wouldn\'t hesitate to read it before you go about any other business here in the Abbey.',`objectives_loc1`='Read the Dark Letter and speak to Drusilla La Salle at the graveyard in Northshire Valley.' WHERE `entry`=26151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice job, $N! Penny will be very excited for breakfast tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=26153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='THEIR DEVOTIONS ARE... SILENCED.$B$BNOW THAT... YOU HAVE... THEIR POWER... YOU MUST DESTROY... THEIR LEADER.' WHERE `entry`=26154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah!  You Nethergarde nincompoops are always two steps behind me, and I\'m nowhere near as fast as I used to be. I don\'t need Mahar\'s note to know what\'s going on. Why do you think I\'m cooped up in the back of this cave?  What I do need, however, is a strong $R like you.' WHERE `entry`=26157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent!  You\'ve managed to complete the simplest of tasks without dying. Now that that\'s out of the way...' WHERE `entry`=26158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' More than enough, and still warm!  Now, let\'s get this ritual started, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=26159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The blood ritual was a success; I can clearly see where we are going next. I\'m sorry, I misspoke. What I meant to say is, I can see where YOU are going next...' WHERE `entry`=26160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see... yes, I can work with this. Loramus Thalipedes, demon hunter. I look forward to our reunion.' WHERE `entry`=26161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You... you fool!  What have you done?' WHERE `entry`=26162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No, no, no... not Kasim again!  This is madness! Please, remain quiet. If my commander learns that I still work for the short one, do you know how quickly I will be removed from the watch? I see you speak the truth. Let us begin our business quickly, so that it may end even quicker.' WHERE `entry`=26163;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope this is what the gnome wanted.' WHERE `entry`=26164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is no doubt about it, you have found demon blood. Kasim\'s requests aside, I am sure that my Watch Commander is thankful for your efforts. They have been struggling to deal with these demon distractions for some time now.' WHERE `entry`=26165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is sufficient. If you see Grimeo again, you may tell him that he performed satisfactorily, but no... his debt is not yet cleared. I will get to work on fashioning the stone knife of sealing. There is no need for questions now. All will be revealed in time. While I work, I have another task for you to complete. Don\'t look so upset!  This task will be fun... it involves collecting body parts.' WHERE `entry`=26166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' He was an archmage, I can feel it. I will hold the amulet for you while you collect the rest.' WHERE `entry`=26167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' A warlock... and a powerful one at that. I will hold onto this until the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' He was a powerful warrior, this one. I will keep the amulet until we are ready to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=26169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It would seem that we are prepared to face our demon, $N. We have the amulet\'s blessing, we have the stone knife, and I alone know the demon\'s true name: Rakh\'likh. Together, this may be enough to defeat the Defiler.' WHERE `entry`=26170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Loramus, resurrected!?  And then he trapped the demon inside his own body... by the Light... I see. So this was Kasim\'s plan all along. I suspected correctly, but I suppose I refused to believe it. Ah, one last thing!  Kasim left one more instruction for me within his rune. I did not understand it at first, but given the events that have taken place today, it now makes much more sense: He asked me to let you choose from one of these.' WHERE `entry`=26171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are perfect, $N. I will eat well for the next several days.' WHERE `entry`=26172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your work is appreciated, soldier. $R... if you\'re still interested, I have one more small task for you...' WHERE `entry`=26173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re certain nobody saw you?  Good. Hmph... fairly harmless stuff. Either the Horde are foolish enough to NOT be planning something against us... or they\'re hiding their information better than I expected. Either way, well done, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=26174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Surwich, $R. Please, have a look around.' WHERE `entry`=26175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glad to hear you\'ve been clearing out the troggs. Let\'s have a look at this report, and... ...Is that a beer stain?' WHERE `entry`=26176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Collect 10 Canal Crabs. Deliver them to Robby Flay in Stormwind City.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='These crabs look great!  I will clean these up and make sure that the King hears about your contribution. Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=26177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I don\'t think there could be too much misinterpreting or ignoring of that signal, hm? The Venture Co. will know not to take the $R lightly, or to be so arrogant as to believe we would allow them to steal the natural resources around us without protest.' WHERE `entry`=26179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My anger is somewhat lessened at the news that the villain Fizsprocket is dead. I will go through his personal effects and see if there is any additional information about what the Venture Co. has planned for the future. Thank you for your efforts, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello again, $C.$B$BI felt L\'ghorek die. A shame that such a magnificent being is gone.$B$BIf we do not assist Neptulon, we will all meet the same fate.' WHERE `entry`=26182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These will do nicely $N. I will get to work right away on the cider.' WHERE `entry`=26183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You say the demons were all worshipping the tree? It is as I feared, then.' WHERE `entry`=26184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='While I\'m surprised that Connisport is willing to go forward with his plan, I\'m also relieved. I\'ve seen the demons rallying around Maldraz, and I share his fears.' WHERE `entry`=26185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Very well, $N. We have what we need to break Marl\'s trance and put an end to both him and his experiment.' WHERE `entry`=26186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. I, and the people of Surwich, are in your debt. Feel free to take one of these. While we haven\'t got much, we\'re happy to reward those that protect us.' WHERE `entry`=26187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, thank you, $N. Using the items you brought me, I will be able to create the remedy I need to stop the spread of the infection and, eventually, cure it completely. I owe you my life in thanks.$B$BBut I\'ll never forget that screeching call when Mazzranache came upon me, the blaze of color as its beak descended...$B$BBe wary on your travels.' WHERE `entry`=26188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you back in one piece, $N! You\'re quite a piece of work. I\'ll be tellin\' Captain Stoutfist how you took care of those orcs!' WHERE `entry`=26189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. I will get to work scaling these for the King right away.' WHERE `entry`=26190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With every day, more warriors arrive at Azshara\'s command. Soon, Neptulon the Tidehunter will hear of our preparations, but too late to stop what we have set in motion. Our numbers will be too great and our allies too powerful. Victory is only a matter of time.$B$BIn Azshara\'s name.' WHERE `entry`=26191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These sacks look like just enough, $N. Can\'t wait to see the smiles on the orphans faces.' WHERE `entry`=26192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The whispers of the elements are crowding my thoughts, $N...$B$BThe Throne of Tides is under siege!$B$BWe cannot stand idly by while the naga threaten Neptulon\'s realm.$B$BMake ready! With this submarine and its armaments, perhaps we can make a difference.$B$BSpeak to me when you are prepared for battle.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Erunak in Darkbreak Cove to enter the battle for the Abyssal Breach.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='NO! This is NOT over!' WHERE `entry`=26193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The whispers of the elements are crowding my thoughts, $N...$B$BThe Throne of Tides is under siege!$B$BWe cannot stand idly by while the naga threaten Neptulon\'s realm.$B$BMake ready! With this submarine and its armaments, perhaps we can make a difference.$B$BSpeak to me when you have made your preparations.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Erunak in Tenebrous Cavern to enter the battle for the Abyssal Breach.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='They may think they\'ve won, but my axe and I have something to say about that!' WHERE `entry`=26194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The greenwarden was a local legend. Many thought him a myth... the plant-man, protector of the wetlands. The night elves came here just to find him, and after they succeeded they ended up settling down to the east.$B$BThey\'ve got a whole grove over there to watch over the Greenwarden, and I\'ve heard he\'s been acting up, enraged by the flooding and damage to the land.$B$BThe elves are good people. They could use the help of someone like you. If you get a chance, go tell the head druid what you\'ve done here.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to the Greenwarden\'s grove, $C. I am glad Whelgar has told you of us. If you are able to lend us your assistance, I will be most grateful.' WHERE `entry`=26195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Supplies from Ferilon? Bless his heart. We\'re good on food, but we\'re runnin\' out of bullets!' WHERE `entry`=26196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, isn\'t it? It\'s a pleasure to finally meet you. While you were getting cleaned up, Nevin\'s team told me about your escape from Gnomeregan.' WHERE `entry`=26197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I want to show you a simple technique. It will allow you to focus and channel bursts of arcane power toward an opponent.$B$BAs you grow in power, you\'ll learn how to add more and more missiles to each volley.$B$BFind one of the training dummies setup in the middle of town. You won\'t always be able to cast arcane missiles right away. First, you\'ll need to cast other spells at the dummy until you\'ve created an opportunity to use arcane missiles. Try it out for yourself.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Bipsi Frostflinger to train Arcane Missiles. Once you\'ve learned the spell, successfully cast Arcane Missiles twice at a Training Dummy in New Tinkertown.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You picked that one up quickly. I can\'t wait to show you some of my other favorite tricks.' WHERE `entry`=26198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. I\'m sure your time in Gnomeregan afforded you ample opportunity to practice your arts. Things are somewhat safer here, but your talents will never go to waste.' WHERE `entry`=26199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I have a simple technique I want to show you. It\'s pretty straightforward, but it\'s still one of the most useful things I know.$B$BYou can use it to heal yourself or a wounded ally very quickly. It\'s handy for when you need to treat someone promptly and don\'t have time for something more complicated.$B$BGive it a try for yourself and let me know when you think you have it mastered.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to "Doc" Cogspin to train Flash Heal. Use Flash Heal 5 times on Wounded Infantry in New Tinkertown.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $N. You have a natural talent for our arts.' WHERE `entry`=26200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m not at all surprised that a warlock like you fought your way out of Gnomeregan. Few people, even among the gnomes, truly understand the nature of the power we wield.$B$BLet me show you a conjuration that I find handy. This spell, called Immolate, sets your target aflame, causing damage immediately and over time. Use it well, $N, and your enemies will come to fear you.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Alamar Grimm and learn Immolate, then cast Immolate on a Training Dummy in New Tinkertown 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='As you continue to gain power, return to me and I will teach you new spells and techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, another one of Nevin\'s "rescued" survivors, eh? More than likely, you saved his life from the troggs down there. Did he stumble over his words when he mentioned me? The man has a healthy respect for the demonic powers we channel.' WHERE `entry`=26202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='For a $R who has spent so much time inside Gnomeregan, you look positively fit and healthy, $N. That\'s good. Before we can complete what Operation: Gnomeregan began, we\'re going to need more warriors like you.' WHERE `entry`=26203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I want to show you a simple but useful technique.$B$BAs I tell all my recruits, a warrior who strikes first can use that momentum to gain the upper hand. This is a technique to use from a distance, before engaging your opponent. It will allow you to charge in, taking your enemy by surprise and stunning him.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when you think you\'ve mastered it.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Drill Sergeant Steamcrank to learn Charge. Locate a Training Dummy in New Tinkertown and use Charge on it.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work! Keep practicing your charge and you\'ll have an instant advantage at the start of battle.' WHERE `entry`=26204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, I never expected it to work on the first trial! Uh, I mean, we\'ve succeeded! I wonder what other uses I we can find for this handy little guy.' WHERE `entry`=26205;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. Nevin tells me that you managed to survive the dangers in Gnomeregan by using your wits. That\'s exactly what we need up here. Clever minds and quick blades.' WHERE `entry`=26206;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I have a technique I want to show you.$B$BOne of a rogue\'s most potent abilities is to chain together moves in a combination, exploiting your enemy\'s weakness and opening up the opportunity to use stronger maneuvers. The technique I want to teach you is called Eviscerate. It is intended for use at the end of a combination to provide a strong finish to your assault.$B$BTry using it after a landing a couple of Sinister Strikes.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Kelsey Steelspark to learn Eviscerate, then find a training dummy in New Tinkertown and practice using Eviscerate 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m not surprised to see you\'re such a quick study. I look forward to showing you more of our tricks of the trade.' WHERE `entry`=26207;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Even now, only the S.A.F.E. teams dare to venture far into the city to search for survivors. Meanwhile, Thermaplugg has sent one of his followers, Crushcog, to distract us and buy time for him to dig in.' WHERE `entry`=26208;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gnolls and murlocs? Horse poopy, pal! Gnolls and murlocs didn\'t kill these people. I\'ve seen what gnolls and murlocs do to people that they kill and this... isn\'t it. Too pretty. Too... perfect. Furthermore, the Furlbrow\'s had been squatting on this farm for 5 years. No, whoever wiped them out had a reason. This is murder, plain and simple and we\'re gonna get to the bottom of it...' WHERE `entry`=26209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Clue #3 obtained',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Clue #4 obtained' WHERE `entry`=26209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='MON! This is fantastic! With my best lure and the snapjaw population down, the fish will pile up.' WHERE `entry`=26210;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, mon! I can\'t thank you enough! Hopefully this here fishing pole will be reward enough for the job.' WHERE `entry`=26211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Dis hit da spot! Tanks little one. Lard make you special picnic basket for help Lard.' WHERE `entry`=26212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Is this supposed to be some kind of joke, because I\'m not laughing. Bits and pieces of red cloth? What the hell is this supposed to mean?' WHERE `entry`=26213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice find, rookie. I think I have a stack of these on my desk back at the station. We\'re basically back to square one. What do we know? Someone that likes to write fiction about the past sent the Furlbrows a letter. Looks like we got ourselves a real history... mystery.' WHERE `entry`=26214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look, we ain\'t got no room for no more... Horatio sent you? Right then... um, how can I help you? He\'s not here is he? Heh, he knows I wasn\'t hidin\' from him, right? Was just tryin\' to lay low and all that, ya know?' WHERE `entry`=26215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Vell done, Private $N. The cavern is ours, but the beast escaped. Should it raise it\'s ugly head again, ve vill make with blastink it out of the vater.' WHERE `entry`=26219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $N. These will do nicely.' WHERE `entry`=26220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $C.$B$BThat slippery beast got away! I\'ll be making a few upgrades. It won\'t be so lucky next time.' WHERE `entry`=26221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are fantastic! Let\'s see what we can put together. Would you be interested in testing out the prototype once I\'m done?' WHERE `entry`=26222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A job well done, $R. The Revantusk thank you for your contribution.' WHERE `entry`=26223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have proven a worthy ally to the Revantusk, $N. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=26224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect! I don\'t know where I\'d get this stuff if it wasn\'t for drunk humans repeatedly crashing their ships. Normally I\'d settle down and get ready to haggle with you for an hour, but you\'re in luck; I\'m too eager to crack these open. Cheers!' WHERE `entry`=26225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ugh, I never liked cooking these slimy things. Thanks for the help $N.' WHERE `entry`=26226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let me see your hands... Aha!  Your not any better at collecting these wretched things than I am!' WHERE `entry`=26227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' STOP! STOP! STOP! I don\'t wanna hear it! I don\'t wanna know and I don\'t care! That kind of information is liable to get you killed \'round these parts. I got one more bit of information for you and then we\'re done!' WHERE `entry`=26228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Back before those damned kobolds gave me a permanent limp I used to be William Pestle\'s number one candle supplier. Hell, I even came up with the line "I TAKE CANDLE!" Yea, that was me. Kobold would say "You no take candle!" and I\'d just respond "I TAKE CANDLE!" and then bash their brains in!$B$B<Jimb drifts off for a second.>$B$BGood times... The best times.$B$BNow? Can\'t even use the bathroom without assistance. You want to help me? Kill me some kobolds. You\'ll find a good load of \'em in the nearby mine.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 12 Kobold Diggers.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh SWEET justice! Killin\' those kobolds won\'t make me walk like a normal person and it sure won\'t get me a job, but damn does it feel good. Here, I think I got somethin\' for you from my kobold huntin\' days. Maybe you can put it to good use.' WHERE `entry`=26229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just smellin\' you comin\' got my stomach rumblin\'! We\'re gonna eat like kings tonight!' WHERE `entry`=26230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re dealing with an organization here, rookie. You don\'t just off the richest bum in Westfall in broad daylight and leave no witnesses. Someone with a lot of power is behind these murders. What have you learned so far?' WHERE `entry`=26232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='As you know, $N, Garrosh has relegated the Trolls of Orgrimmar to the western outskirts of the city. Fortunately, that means that we have easy access to their supplies. I am working on a large batch of jambalaya for the infantry and I need as much rice as possible. Lucky for us, the Trolls keep it stored in barrels near their structures. Retrieve these barrels of Darkspear rice for me and I should be able to finish up.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you are a skilled thief as well, $N. Don\'t worry, we will return the rice once we are done... or not.' WHERE `entry`=26233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='As you know, $N, Garrosh has relegated the Goblins of Orgrimmar to the western outskirts of the city. Fortunately, that means that we have easy access to their supplies. I am working on a large batch of jambalaya for the infantry and I need as much rice as possible. Lucky for us, the Goblins keep it stored in barrels near their structures. Retrieve these barrels of Kezan rice for me and I should be able to finish up.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you are a skilled thief as well, $N. Don\'t worry, we will return the rice once we are done... or not.' WHERE `entry`=26234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work $N!  I will see that these rations are returned to the troops immediately.' WHERE `entry`=26235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Horatio Laine? That man is a scumbag. Dirty as my underwear. Listen, friend, I don\'t often give out advice like this, but you seem like a good man. GET OUT OF WESTFALL. You\'re already in way over your head. All you\'re doing now is putting your neck on the chopping block.' WHERE `entry`=26236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, brother. You\'ve done Salma and I a great service and I promise that it won\'t soon be forgotten. I don\'t have much money, but you\'re welcome to what I do have.' WHERE `entry`=26237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That will show the Wildhammer to stay away from our lands! Crazy dwarves should\'ve stayed in the mountains...' WHERE `entry`=26238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Makes all the difference, doesn\'t it? That\'ll teach those dwarves a lesson.' WHERE `entry`=26240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Bless your heart, dear. These poor orphans haven\'t had a hot meal in days. It looks like we will have enough left over to help feed many more of the homeless of Westfall.' WHERE `entry`=26241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did what was necessary, $N. I can tell you\'re the sort of $C I\'ll get along with well.' WHERE `entry`=26244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The clues point to an obvious conclusion. Too obvious perhaps.' WHERE `entry`=26245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why would the Alliance attack the Horde just as they\'re about to deliver a fragment of the World Pillar to us.' WHERE `entry`=26246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oi, $N!  I was told I\'d have company soon.' WHERE `entry`=26247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We were bound to run into the Twilight\'s Hammer sooner or later, $N. If they\'re behind this, it\'s quite likely that the World Pillar fragment is in their possession.' WHERE `entry`=26248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This ship is filled with rats...' WHERE `entry`=26249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oi, this was a heavy one!  He nearly broke me gryphon\'s back! Are you ready to interrogate the ogre, $N?' WHERE `entry`=26250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. The Twilight\'s Hammer is an evil that we must fight anywhere we find them.' WHERE `entry`=26251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Is that... Is that the heart of one of the watchers? I\'ve heard stories about using one of these to power up a watcher for personal use. Of course I\'m really in no shape to try such things myself.' WHERE `entry`=26252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We have our answers, $N. Let\'s report back.' WHERE `entry`=26254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We must investigate your findings further, but we must not lose track of the fragment.' WHERE `entry`=26255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re keeping slaves here?  We ought to free them regardless, but perhaps they might also aid us in finding the forgemaster.' WHERE `entry`=26256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='From what I\'ve heard, all you really need to do is find a suitable harvest golem and drop in the heart. Once you\'ve done that you should be able to take full control of the creature.$B$BI think there\'s a whole field of overloaded harvest golems west of here, at the Molsen Farm. Look for the arcs of electricity.$B$BShould you manage to get it working, use the golem to destroy the energized harvest reapers at the old Molsen farm. Those monsters are much more destructive than the ones on our farm.',`objectives_loc1`='Use the Harvest Watcher Heart on an Overloaded Harvest Golem and then use the Overloaded Harvest Golem to kill 25 Energized Harvest Reapers.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It actually worked? That\'s incredible, $N. Hopefully that takes care of the harvest golem problem here in Westfall.' WHERE `entry`=26257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This must be where the world pillar fragment was brought. Let\'s have a closer look.' WHERE `entry`=26258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is still great power present in his blood, $N. I can sense it even now. Yet there is also much corruption. I am not sure we can salvage the Earthwarder\'s essence from this.' WHERE `entry`=26259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is an entry for an upcoming meeting at the Upper Silvermarsh. This must be where the Forgemaster is.' WHERE `entry`=26260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let us find this journal. We\'re getting close to the World Pillar fragment, I can sense it.' WHERE `entry`=26261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, mon. A fine hero of the Horde you are.' WHERE `entry`=26263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t wait to give this new technology a try! We\'ve lost more gnomes to radiation than we can count. It\'s time to turn that around!' WHERE `entry`=26264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What a relief! Thank you for your help. I hope that gadget Engineer Grindspark was working on helps get the airfield cleaned up permanently.' WHERE `entry`=26265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I smell Westfall stew! Mother sent you!?' WHERE `entry`=26266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Years ago, there used to be a Horde base deep within Skulk Rock. It\'s been abandoned since then, but it\'s still prime territory, worth reclaiming.$B$BThe problem is, it\'s full of oozes by now. They\'re nasty things... mindless, corrosive, eat anything they find.$B$BI need someone brave to go to Skulk Rock and get rid of those slimes. Are you brave enough, $N?',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 10 Jade Oozes.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see you back... and not missing any limbs, either.' WHERE `entry`=26267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re still intact! There\'s a lot of memories in these crate. Let\'s see what we\'ve got in the first one... Hey, banana bread! And it\'s still fresh! Here, mon, I\'ll take this and you can pick something else.' WHERE `entry`=26268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve certainly saved me a heap of trouble, $N!  I can\'t thank you enough. It shouldn\'t be long now until we see Master Nesingwary\'s book in libraries throughout the world! I\'ll leave a copy of the book right here, if you ever want to take a peek at the finished product. Thanks again, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Speak with Salma Saldean at the Saldean\'s Farm in Westfall.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Salma Saldean at the Saldean\'s Farm in Westfall.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Of course, dear. Our little girl works at Sentinel Hill and is very close with the homeless of Westfall. Perhaps she has overheard something. Before you go, let me wrap up the Westfall Stew and tell you a little bit about our dear little girl.' WHERE `entry`=26270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have a kind heart, $N. You have done a good thing, today, and that act will reflect back upon you when judgment day comes.' WHERE `entry`=26271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Anotha newblood, eh? Ya actually have an intense look about ya though. Fiery eyes. You might have the makings of a real $C. Lets not waste anymore time \'den.' WHERE `entry`=26272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, mon. Ya have a deep power in ya spells - you may have a talent for dis. Some rough edges ta be sure, but we\'ll get dose ironed out here and I\'ll teach ya a few new tings as we go.' WHERE `entry`=26273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I tink I have something I can show ya. It\'s pretty simple really, but it should help.$B$BOne of da most basic forces we can be drawin\' upon is da ability to unleash demonic fire on our enemies, viciously burnin\' them and leavin\' them on fire for a time afta.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when ya tink you have it down.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Voldreka to train Immolate. Practice using Immolate 5 times against a Tiki Target.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, mon! Dis stuff come easy to ya.' WHERE `entry`=26274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dese are some fine pelts, boy. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.' WHERE `entry`=26275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya handle yerself quite well. Ya gonna be quite powerful some day.' WHERE `entry`=26276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya tha new recruit everyone\'s talkin\' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.' WHERE `entry`=26277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Keep up the good work, $C. Hellscream\'s eyes are upon you.' WHERE `entry`=26278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you are good for more than simple egg-smashing duty. Good. The Horde can use a capable $R like you.' WHERE `entry`=26279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work. Hopefully the raids will stop for now. I have one more task for you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' The Horde thanks you, $N. Grom\'gol is protected, if only for today.' WHERE `entry`=26281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fascinating... How large did you say it was? I wonder if others could be found intact... This sample is excellent. I\'ll be sharing it with my fellow researchers.' WHERE `entry`=26283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Fer a job like this, I normally bring me whole crew o\' demolitionists. With some help in settin\' up th\' powder, th\' charges, and th\' rest o\' th\' gear, the job gets done a lot faster.$B$BThose blasted troggs have me men caged all around Frostmane Hold. Now I\'m \'ere all alone without th\' personnel I need to finish th\' job.$B$BYou look like a capable $C, though. Would you find th\' demolitionists th\' troggs captured and break them out o\' their cages?',`objectives_loc1`='Free 6 Captured Demolitionists from their cages around Frostmane Hold.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have me own thanks and th\' thanks of th\' men you rescued. I\'ve already had th\' boys start setting up the gear down inside the cave. It should be ready to go soon.' WHERE `entry`=26284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, now, that\'s more like it. We may get around to blowin\' up somethin\' after all.' WHERE `entry`=26285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Helix? I\'ve heard that name before. Recently as a matter of fact, but who is this admiral?' WHERE `entry`=26286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We were once known as the People\'s Militia. These days, though, we fight under the banner of Stormwind, with the full support of King Varian Wrynn. Our goals here in Westfall are many: to clean up the mess left behind by the Defias, to expand the reach of the Alliance and to maintain order. So far we are failing on all fronts.$B$BTimes are worse now than when the Defias ran amok. Now with the indigenous gnolls of the region up in arms, we find ourselves backed into a corner. Help us, $N!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. You have provided us a temporary reprieve from the onslaught of gnolls, but there is more work to be done.' WHERE `entry`=26287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. It will take the Riverpaw weeks to recover from the blow you just dealt. Please take an item of your choosing as a reward for what you have done.' WHERE `entry`=26288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Helix is the one responsible for the gnoll attacks? He\'s inside. He\'s been there for days. I\'ve just been waiting for an excuse to bust him.' WHERE `entry`=26289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What could possibly be going on in Moonbrook? I don\'t like this one bit, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Who IS this Shadowy Figure? We have to get to Moonbrook.' WHERE `entry`=26291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The natives are restless, $N. I don\'t know what\'s going on, but homeless activity in this area has quadrupled in the past two days. If I didn\'t know any better I\'d say they were planning something...' WHERE `entry`=26292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The "Worldbreakers" hide in a highland wilderness, squatting behind the Alliance kingdoms in the east. We will crush them, and we will do so with the mightiest army ever assembled since our victories in Northrend.$B$BI tasked our new goblin allies with the assembly of a host of war machines. Reports from the field reveal that their workmanship is sometimes... lacking.$B$BI will not go to battle with faulty machines. See Foreman Glibbs here in Orgrimmar and ensure my war machines are battle-ready!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Busy now. Go away. Wait, what? Hellscream sent you? What - uh - what can I do for you? Him? Us?' WHERE `entry`=26293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Glibbs mops sweat from his brow with a greasy handkerchief.>$B$BHellscream isn\'t happy with our work? Oh - we even NAMED the "Hellscream Demolisher" after him. This is very bad. My boys need to step it up.$B$BMaybe you can help set an example. A set of Hellscream Demolishers just rolled off the blocks and are ready for inspection. Give them a thorough going-over, and if you find any problems, give the Chief Engineer a good thrashing. Remind them that the eyes of Hellscream are upon them!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Instilled a little discipline in them, did you? Good, good! Everyone pulls their weight in my Horde, from the smallest peon to the proudest warrior. I tolerate nothing less. Our preparations for the invasion are almost complete.' WHERE `entry`=26294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='V? The only V I know is VanCleef, but he died many years ago.' WHERE `entry`=26295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I haven\'t seen a red bandana in five years. Could this shadowy figure be attempting to reform the Defias Brotherhood?' WHERE `entry`=26296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I could hear the cheers from here. It seems as if we\'ve got a huge problem on our hands, $N. We have to discover the identity of this shadowy menace before we enlist the aid of Stormwind. Perhaps there is another way...' WHERE `entry`=26297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are good tusks, $N. You prove that you have the strength to hunt the Bloodscalps.$B$BAnd that is good, because you are not done hunting them.' WHERE `entry`=26298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. I will inspect these heads to ensure poor Yenniku was spared the headhunter\'s axe.' WHERE `entry`=26299;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You place the head of Nezzliok within the cauldron...' WHERE `entry`=26300;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes. These will serve me well. When my spirit is freed, I will enter the Nether with some fine servants indeed! You are a credit to your $R clan, and you have appeased me.' WHERE `entry`=26301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Zanzil the Outcast?? If Yenniku is held by that troll, a vile and powerful witchdoctor, then I fear that only a faint hope remains. Faint. And tiny as the smallest insect. Fortunately, I have some suspicions of my own. Suspicions which may lead to Yenniku\'s salvation.' WHERE `entry`=26302;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You retrieved the eye!  Your might is the stuff of legends, $N! And in getting the Eye, you must have defeated Mai\'Zoth and sent him to the Nether. That is why the spirits would not mention him before. It is good that he is gone from the world of flesh and bone, but now that he is in the realm of spirits...I fear he will begin a new reign. But that is a worry for another time.' WHERE `entry`=26303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My mother\'s spirit rests well tonight, $N. As will I.' WHERE `entry`=26304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it!  You freed Yenniku from the will of Zanzil and the tyranny of the Skullsplitter, and completed the mission I had thought was so hopeless. Zanzil still looms a threat in the Cape of Stranglethorn, but for now, I at least know that the soul of my chief\'s son is free. Our tribe will remember your name in songs, $N, and we will etch your tale in stone so that it will live forever.' WHERE `entry`=26305;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N! Let the Vilebranch flee in terror from the sight of you!' WHERE `entry`=26306;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It won\'t be long until we\'re the only trolls left breathing on these walls.' WHERE `entry`=26307;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There are none left to oppose the Revantusk! Any stragglers will be quickly taken care of. You\'ve done my people a great honor, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26308;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='First the spiders and now this. I can smell the venom in this blood... it\'s the same as the skitterlings, but stronger. The Vilebranch and spiders... there\'s some potential here.' WHERE `entry`=26309;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh yes... I was wise to ask you to get these. How fascinating. Come here, my pretties. Into the bag you go.' WHERE `entry`=26310;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Twilight Assassins followed you to the bar? Here, in Orgrimmar? The Warchief won\'t be happy about this. Continue your preparations for the invasion and I will investigate.' WHERE `entry`=26311;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. Many Earthen Ring owe dere lives to ya dis day.' WHERE `entry`=26312;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dese are in surprisingly good condition - good work, mon.' WHERE `entry`=26313;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dat will slow their assault a bit while Norsala be findin\' a way to calm\'m. We\'ve no desire ta be remainin\' enemies of Therazane the Stonemother.' WHERE `entry`=26314;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeah, mon... dat\'s about the reaction we were expectin\'.$B$BHe mentioned Diamant though? If da two don\'t get along, perhaps this Diamant be a bit less brash den Boden. At least it\'s somethin\'.$B$BLet me see if I can get da earth to tell me where we might be findin\' dis Diamant.' WHERE `entry`=26315;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It won\'t be tough to collapse th\' tunnel, but I\'m goin\' to need my team an\' my equipment \'afore I can get to th\' task.' WHERE `entry`=26316;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Bring the Lashtail Hatchling to Far Seer Mok\'thardin at Grom\'gol Base Camp.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, the little one seems to have taken a liking to you. I suppose that one raptor alone and raised among orcs is much less deadly than a whole pack of them. Keep her, $N... she may come in handy. In fact...' WHERE `entry`=26317;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I could feel th\' explosion way up here! My boys did a fine job riggin\' up that blast, but it wouldn\'t have happened without your help. It\'s only fair that I split my contract payment with you for helpin\' me finish th\' job.' WHERE `entry`=26318;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm, yes, perhaps I could be of some assistance. When I was in Northrend I helped the people of Valgarde uncover some of the mysteries of the vrykul by delving into the spirit world. Perhaps the same could be done here.' WHERE `entry`=26319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='WHAT? VanCleef had a daughter?' WHERE `entry`=26320;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='She looks bigger already!  You can see, these raptors grow quickly. You are lucky to have found such a strong companion. Keep her by your side as long as you can, $N. I\'m sure she will prove to be an asset in the future.' WHERE `entry`=26321;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will deploy a battalion of soldiers to Westfall at once! With the Defias Brotherhood reborn, an old threat to the kingdom is renewed.' WHERE `entry`=26322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Return to Nimboya at Grom\'gol Base Camp and show him your Lashtail Hatchling\'s new skull.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='What do we have here?  A young raptor, and her pet $R. Hah! More importantly, what is that skull you have there?  This was no ordinary troll. He was big... ... and strong, too. Let\'s see what we can do with this one. Don\'t go anywhere.' WHERE `entry`=26323;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We have a map of the Highland approaches. The plan is clear: we will show ourselves in force. The Dragonmaw orcs, on seeing the might of our combined forces on their shore, will have no choice but to ally with us in our crusade to destroy the Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BThe fleet is assembling at Bilgewater Port in Azshara. I grow impatient with their progress.$B$B$C! You have a knack for greasing the wheels of my war machine. Seek out Warlord Krogg in Azshara and find out what\'s taking so long.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='What, another message from Hellscream? His patience is thinner than calf\'s hide. Have you ever worked with goblins before? Everywhere is another hidden cost! Our ships lie half-assembled and the air fleet is scattered to the winds. If this invasion is going to happen, I\'m going to need your help.' WHERE `entry`=26324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Yes... yesss... My spirit is strong again, $R, and I am ready to return to the world. Now I need a body.' WHERE `entry`=26325;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, mon! Thank ya for comin\'.$B$BWe weren\'t ready for dis kind of attack. We been expectin\' da Twilight Cult, but not elementals... we\'ve got no idea what upset dem so much that dey would turn on us like dis.$B$BYou haven\'t been out dere killin\' them, have you?' WHERE `entry`=26326;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well met! If you\'ve got a weapon on you, I\'ll take any help I can get clearing out these crazed fools!' WHERE `entry`=26327;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah... you must be the $R that I was expecting.$B$BYou have come on behalf of the Earthen Ring then?' WHERE `entry`=26328;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Splendid news! With the troggs taken care of, we should be able to turn our attention to Crushcog\'s troublemaking.' WHERE `entry`=26329;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $R. Only one more step remains before I may return.' WHERE `entry`=26330;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That should set back Crushcog\'s plans a bit, but we can\'t rest until he is defeated and Chill Breeze Valley is secure.' WHERE `entry`=26331;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Excellent work, $R. You and your raptor have done a great thing. Hakkar would be most pleased...' WHERE `entry`=26332;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mekkatorque will be pleased to hear that you\'ve ruined Crushcog\'s plans to use our old weapons for his followers. Without the mechano-tanks under his command, he\'ll be weak and vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26333;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$R. $R, $R, $R... you didn\'t think I was a friend, did you, $R?  Ah, ha ha haaaa!$B$BYou\'ve served your purpose. I\'ve returned to the realm of the living, and it\'s all thanks to you. So, instead of killing you, I\'m going to make you a deal instead.$B$BGive me the raptor.$B$BYou must already know that she\'s no normal raptor, and I need a replacement for Ohgan. Do it, or both you and the witch doctor will taste my rage.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad to see you\'ve come to your senses. Come and visit us in Zul\'Gurub sometime, $R. I\'ll be watching...' WHERE `entry`=26334;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahoy, $C. Any friend of Skuerto is a friend of mine. You\'ll find plenty of work needs doin\' around here. We\'re not sittin\' in this cove twiddlin\' our thumbs by choice.' WHERE `entry`=26336;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So they were trying to skimp on production costs? Unacceptable! I\'m glad you knocked some sense into them. If that foreman makes good on his word, our fleet will be ship-shape in time for the invasion.' WHERE `entry`=26337;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Balance is restored - for now. We may call on you again in the future, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, yes, Kelsey told me to expect you. There\'s still much to do before we can take on Crushcog.' WHERE `entry`=26339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm?  Barnil\'s the name. And you are...?' WHERE `entry`=26340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'ve scouted all over these highlands, $N, and there\'s one thing I\'ve found I haven\'t been able to explain.$B$BTo the northeast of here, there\'s a circle of stones, like the others you\'ll find everythwhere in Arathi... but the largest and most imposing of them, built into the mountainside itself.$B$BJust between you and me, I heard voices while I was there. Whispers of the earth. If you\'re the curious type, you could go see for yourself...',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Help...' WHERE `entry`=26341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve given us just the opening we\'ll need to get the drop on Crushcog. Excellent work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These skins should do. Their quality isn\'t too important, given that they\'ll make up the inside layer of the boots, but it\'s still important that they\'re comfortable.$B$BIf they\'re a bit too rigid, I\'ll use some tiger blood to soften it up. Tricks o\' the trade, you know?' WHERE `entry`=26343;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My boots... they\'re like sausages, $N. Look great, taste great. I tell you they\'re filled with nothing but the finest ingredients and meats, and you eat it, and you love it.$B$BIt\'s safer--and more enjoyable--if you just trust me, and don\'t ask too carefully what\'s really inside.' WHERE `entry`=26344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great! Thanks to your help I\'ll have this order filled and sent off to Director Riddlevox on the next boat to Undermine. Ahead of schedule, even!$B$BFor all your hard work, here, I made some extras, so take a pair. It\'s on Drizzlik.$B$BAnd remember, there\'s no boot so fine as one of Drizzlik\'s Excelsior line!' WHERE `entry`=26345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Say no more, $N. I followed up with an... "old friend" while you were gone. I should\'ve known better than to send you to those shards. We\'ve both made a grave mistake in involving ourselves in this. Luckily, I "persuaded" my boy Gerrig to tell me what to do if this happened.' WHERE `entry`=26346;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Praise you, brave $C. The rocks of the Westfall Coast shall be lit thanks to your hard work. Many lives will be spared so long as the torch is kept lit.$B$BI died needlessly on this very shore. My afterlife plight is to see that no others follow my destiny.' WHERE `entry`=26347;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. You have quite a knack for combat. Thanks to you the Coast of Westfall is a safer place.' WHERE `entry`=26348;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So the foul heathen, Murk-Eye is dead. Well done, $N. By your hands one life was laid to rest but perhaps many more were saved. The Great Sea, wrought with danger as it is, shall be a wee bit safer this night thanks to your heroics.' WHERE `entry`=26349;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mandokir is alive, yes. You are responsible, yes. You may be able to stop him still, yes.' WHERE `entry`=26350;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You bring feathers, yes. You can follow directions, yes.' WHERE `entry`=26351;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A fuel regulator?  This seems important. At least, I hope it is. We may not have ended the Venture Company\'s operations, but we at least slowed them down. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The footlocker slowly creaks open. Sand and water seem to be its only contents. But wait! A small crab scurries out with a clue to the treasure in his claws!' WHERE `entry`=26353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, treasure hunter!' WHERE `entry`=26354;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re on your way to the jackpot, treasure seeker!' WHERE `entry`=26355;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The hinges on the old chest are rusty but they still work. You force the chest open and take the booty.$B$BCongratulations!' WHERE `entry`=26356;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Such a pretty site ta see the enemy\'s hopes burnin\'...' WHERE `entry`=26357;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' What? The Captain said WHAT? It\'s HIS fault this big beast of an engine is delayed.' WHERE `entry`=26358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What did Priestess tell you? The raptor is daughter of Ohgan, heir to Mandokir\'s seat. Hah!' WHERE `entry`=26359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! I should have this here engine samophlanginated within the hour.' WHERE `entry`=26361;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Speak with Chiyu',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Escape from Zul\'Gurub' WHERE `entry`=26362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dead? All of them, around the altar? And you found these spider idols on them... A mass sacrifice. They threw their lives to Shadra.' WHERE `entry`=26363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re finally free of Razlo Crushcog and his interference! With the defeat of Crushcog and his forces, Thermaplugg can\'t afford to send any more of his followers to the surface. I can\'t wait for the day when we defeat him for good!' WHERE `entry`=26364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Heard Westfall was in some deep doody. Well, we got our own set of problems here. See them gnolls out there? Looks like they\'re actin\' up again. I don\'t like it. Don\'t like it one bit.' WHERE `entry`=26365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The look of fear and confusion on his face... this is what he deserved! Let\'s make sure all the Vilebranch wear the same look.' WHERE `entry`=26366;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I wish I could have been there to see it, $N! I\'ll have to hear the story from Ongo\'longo himself when this is over.' WHERE `entry`=26367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mmm, yes... that old nostalgic smell. You\'ve done well for the Forsaken, and the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=26368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The parts scattered, the keepers separated... I see. This is a ritual to summon Shadra. They must not have gotten far. It should be destroyed...' WHERE `entry`=26369;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Five years of work burned to the ground in five minutes. Damn the Defias! And this is only the beginning, $N! We have a long, hard road ahead of us.' WHERE `entry`=26370;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aye... I used to be flesh and blood, just like you, lad. That is, until that fateful day when the murlocs attacked the lighthouse...' WHERE `entry`=26371;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My airship has engines? At last! Now we can rip the heavens a new one! Once the ground and naval forces are ready, we\'re going to light up the skies over the Twilight Highlands.' WHERE `entry`=26372;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If Gnomeregan Covert Operations is recommending you, then you must have made quite an impression. Your help will be most welcome here, as we\'ve a wealth of enemies and few enough mountaineers to face them.' WHERE `entry`=26373;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N! Most of my soldiers have already reported for duty, some a little worse for the wear. One night in Bilgewater makes a hard orc humble. Still, fresh fighting in the Twilight Highlands should restore discipline.' WHERE `entry`=26374;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a generous $R. You give back to the earth that offers you so much. You have my respect. You shall surely have the respect of the Stone Lords with time.' WHERE `entry`=26375;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have observed you, $R.$B$BYou do not fear shedding Twilight blood.$B$BIn this, I am willing to extend you some degree of trust.$B$BIt is a start.$B$BAll things in time.' WHERE `entry`=26376;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Time brings respect to all.$B$BThe smallest pebble.$B$BThe largest mountain.$B$BThe most stubborn cultist.' WHERE `entry`=26377;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Murder, rookie. That\'s what you\'re looking at on the ground in front of us.' WHERE `entry`=26378;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These look promising. I\'ve heard great things about the Short and Stout Brewery, but I haven\'t had the chance to try their ale until now. While you\'re here, relax a little. If you need a spare hearthstone or wish to make Kharanos your home, just speak to me and I\'ll be happy to help.' WHERE `entry`=26380;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m pleased, $N. That was quicker than I expected.' WHERE `entry`=26381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. Just put them over there, I\'ve got my hands full.' WHERE `entry`=26382;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did the sentinels send you? Thank Elune. We need everyone we can get.' WHERE `entry`=26383;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Bring the Tablet of Shadra to Darkcleric Marnal.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, what have we here... Fascinating. Quite fascinating.' WHERE `entry`=26384;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It seems you have your first charge. You must travel back down to Rut\'theran Village, where we first arrived, and speak to Vesprystus to secure a ride to Lor\'danel.$B$BOnce in Lor\'danel, aid the night elves in any way that you are able. I am trusting you to treat them with the reverence that they deserve in light of all that they have done for us.$B$BI must travel to the distant city of Stormwind to meet with King Varian. I hope to see your face again very soon, $N. Until then, a fond farewell.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our allies have come to our aid? Thank Elune. Tyrande was wise to extend open arms to your people. We need help. We need everyone we can get.' WHERE `entry`=26385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' It would seem that Jin\'do has survived, and he is rallying his brothers to once again summon Hakkar into this world. It was good of you to come to speak with me. There is not much we can do now but to wait, and watch. Jin\'do is weak, and prime for striking, but I must wait for word from Rastakhan before issuing orders. Until then, you and your raptor will have to wait.' WHERE `entry`=26386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now we\'ve got a win-win situation. The spiders are going to either starve off, or find some dwarves and elves to replenish their larder, since my colleagues and I would make a poor meal.' WHERE `entry`=26387;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is a disaster, $N! Our air fleet was decimated. And reports are coming in that our navy was attacked - unprovoked - by the Alliance in open water. And what of Hellscream? Is the Warchief dead?' WHERE `entry`=26388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Blackrock orcs will surely fall now that their main force has been defeated! Only one task remains.' WHERE `entry`=26389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With Kurtok slain we are safe once again from the orcish hordes. I will send peasants to the pass in an attempt to seal the passage so that no more orcs may come through into our territory. You have the thanks of Stormwind and of the Alliance, hero!' WHERE `entry`=26390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Bless your heart, $N. You truly are a hero of the Alliance! Though the land is completely incinerated and there is nothing left of the vineyard but ash and debris, I still might be able to recover. Right? How bad can it be?' WHERE `entry`=26391;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You\'ve driven off the Blackrock orcs, and for that we are grateful! Though the vineyards have been burned to the ground, the rest of Northshire is safe, thanks to you.$B$BPlease accept this voucher outlining your bravery and deliver it to Marshal McBride. He is responsible for the safety of Northshire and he will be happy to hear about what you have done.',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver the Voucher of Bravery to Marshal McBride at Northshire Valley in Elwynn Forest.' WHERE `entry`=26392;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have to get this note to Stormwind? That\'s not a problem, you can take one of my gryphons!' WHERE `entry`=26393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, a note from Smith Argus?  I\'m not surprised he needs more gear. There are so many new recruits these days. Well thank you, $N. Here\'s some money to cover your travel costs.' WHERE `entry`=26394;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A crate for Goldshire, eh?  People sure are getting lazy. Have you been to Goldshire before?  If so, then it\'s no problem, my friend. I have plenty of gryphons trained to fly that route!' WHERE `entry`=26395;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great, you brought the armor!  We\'ll get this divvied to those who need it immediately. Thank you, $N. Your efforts have been a great help to us. And now that you\'re no stranger to gryphons, I hope you\'ll come and lend your aid to Goldshire often!' WHERE `entry`=26396;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Much has changed outside of Mulgore, $N. The world is torn, and our Horde allies have turned down dark paths. We must guide them. Even in the darkest hour, we will bravely hold our heads high, and honor the Earth Mother in all we do.$B$BYou must go, $N, and be this example. Go to Orgrimmar. Tell Warchief Hellscream how the Grimtotem were driven out. Let him know our pride and discipline, our strength and sorrow.$B$BTal at the Skytower will send you on your way. Go in peace, and never forget your people.',`objectives_loc1`='Take the Mark of Bloodhoof to Garrosh Hellscream, located in Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar.$B$BYou may speak with Tal the Wind Rider Master to travel there, or wait for the zeppelin.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Grimtotem forced from Mulgore... if Baine speaks for this, you are indeed a fierce warrior. From this day, your strength is no longer your own. It belongs to me, and the Horde, as a weapon of war. Hellscream\'s eyes are upon you, $N. Victory or death!' WHERE `entry`=26397;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You have fought bravely alongside me, $N, and done much for my people. If every $R could be as noble, the future of the Horde might not disturb me so much.$B$BI would ask you to ease my worries further. Go to Orgrimmar. Tell Warchief Hellscream how the Grimtotem were driven out. Let him know our pride and discipline, our strength and sorrow.$B$BTal at the Skytower will send you on your way. Go in peace, friend.',`objectives_loc1`='Take the Mark of Bloodhoof to Garrosh Hellscream, located in Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar.$B$BYou may speak with Tal the Wind Rider Master to travel there, or wait for the zeppelin.' WHERE `entry`=26398;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Say... have you heard about the ogres?  I got a hot tip from some fella\' named Mok\'thardin that some $R schmuck in a ridiculous $C getup found this ogre hand, and...$B$B<Skeezy trails off as he looks you over.>$B$BWhat was I just saying?  Oh yes... some $G SWASHBUCKLING HERO: BREATHTAKING HEROINE; found this ogre hand, and Mok\'thardin thinks it means that the ogres have some special artifact. I\'ve seen them guarding a chest up in some ruins behind their mound. Care to fetch it for me?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Those ogres really know how to close a treasure chest, I\'ll tell you what. A box is useless to me, hero. We\'re going to need to find a way into this crate.' WHERE `entry`=26399;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Whaaaaaa?!? I\'m... I\'m going to have to send this to... to Flem... in the south. He\'ll know what to do with it.' WHERE `entry`=26400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='How horrible... for someone so young and full of promise to fall to demons! I beg your forgiveness for sending you into danger as well, $N. I hope you don\'t cross paths with that demoness again...' WHERE `entry`=26401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Telaron has already sent word of you, $N. I\'m interested in seeing if you\'re half as skilled as he claims.$B$BI am fighting a war on multiple fronts, while keeping our currently held areas properly defended, as well as overseeing the instruction of our youngest sentinels. If you\'re a decent fighter, there will be plenty for you to do.' WHERE `entry`=26402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great!  Wonderful!  I can get a bundle for these!! That Venture Company sure picked the wrong jungle to mine in, didn\'t they?  We\'d all be in better shape if they moved out of here.' WHERE `entry`=26403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Skeezy sent you to the right place. Welcome to Hardwrench Hideaway!' WHERE `entry`=26404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As promised, your reward. You do the troll nation proud.' WHERE `entry`=26405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There it is... only one left.' WHERE `entry`=26406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Strange indeed. I will pass this on to my contacts in the east, near the Mosh\'Ogg\'s main camp. I have a feeling that they\'ll be interested in these strange scars. You have my thanks, $R.' WHERE `entry`=26407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see a new face around here! The forest crawls with Horde, but my assignment requires that I keep this outpost safe. I could really use someone who might be up for a good fight.' WHERE `entry`=26408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hiya! Lend a hand, would ya, bub?' WHERE `entry`=26409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good thing that I just happen to be a grand master of all things explosively alchemical. This won\'t ignite on its own, though.' WHERE `entry`=26410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like that did it. He should come to any moment now. I told you I was a grand master of alchemy! I\'ve got some extra resin leftover. I can make it into all kinds of explosively wonderful stuff. What do you want?' WHERE `entry`=26411;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We are honored by Flint Oremantle\'s presence. I am given to understand that the Stonefather is in possession of a fragment of the World Pillar. It is imperative that we recover all of the fragments. The instability between worlds is increasing. Soon it may become too great even for mighty Thrall to hold at bay.' WHERE `entry`=26413;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work $N!  I see you are quite the fisherman these days. Might just have to take you out on the boat soon and see what you can really do!' WHERE `entry`=26414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah!  That Cromula cracks me up. Oh, right, Stranglethorn. You\'re really going?' WHERE `entry`=26416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glad you could make it!  Let\'s get to work, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=26417;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes... it\'s finally time. Shadra will be ours!' WHERE `entry`=26418;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellently done. You have served the Dark Lady well today, $N. This virulent blood will supply our armies with all manner of powerful weapons against the disgusting Alliance. We will wipe them from these lands. For the Horde, of course... and all thanks to you.' WHERE `entry`=26419;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Those look like some nice bass, $N. Let\'s fry em\' up and see how they taste!' WHERE `entry`=26420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26424;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26425;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<The ground rumbles slightly as you approach the cave. This looks to be the entrance that Diamant and Felsen spoke of.>' WHERE `entry`=26426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='All right, help me get tied to the wheel.' WHERE `entry`=26427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You stand before me as a figure of vengeance, and I bow down before you in thanks.$B$BWith that cow\'s death, and knowing that their seed will no longer spread over the face of Azeroth, I can put my energy into something more lucrative. I hope you looted their farmstead after you finished them off.' WHERE `entry`=26428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The signs of war are upon your garments, and sweat drips from your brow. Good, very good indeed.' WHERE `entry`=26429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Not all forest trolls are foul nuisances like the Witherbark. North of here in the Hinterlands is Revantusk Village, home to the only forest troll tribe still allied with the Horde.$B$BEven they cannot escape the cruelty of their bretheren. The Vilebranch tribe wars with them, distracting them from our battle with the Alliance.$B$BYou have fought well here. Speak with Urda if you wish to fly to Revantusk. Their village will have use of your strength.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Revantusk, $C. I hope fighting the Witherbark hasn\'t exhausted you; the Vilebranch are even worse.' WHERE `entry`=26430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Accept this quest to find archaeology points on your map!',`objectives_loc1`='Accept this quest to find archaeology points on your map!' WHERE `entry`=26431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $C. We\'re gonna make the Vilebranch regret ever crossin\' us.' WHERE `entry`=26432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Ahh... do you know how hard it is to get fresh water in Stranglethorn?  It\'s no wonder that the nagas guard their shrine so ferociously! Oh, right... your artifact, and clarity. Clarity... I\'ve got it!' WHERE `entry`=26433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Excellent work, $N!  These reagents will serve perfectly.' WHERE `entry`=26434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fascinating! I\'ll need some time to study this. Why don\'t you have a look around Booty Bay and come back later?' WHERE `entry`=26435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Diamant says you are to be trusted. Diamant is patient and wise, so I shall allow you to prove yourself.$B$BAs it happens, I could use hands that are more... mobile.' WHERE `entry`=26436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh... invigorating. Thank you, fleshling.' WHERE `entry`=26437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve proven useful, $R.' WHERE `entry`=26438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$R. If you act in the service of the Stone Lords, there are those that might aid you.$B$BWatch for the Stonebound. They lie dormant all around the Shuddering Spires. It should not take much prompting to rebind them to service against the flayers.' WHERE `entry`=26439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<The stones in Pebble\'s body bounce up and down happily. He seems very appreciative.>' WHERE `entry`=26440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve made a friend, have you?$B$BAre you certain you want to feed him? He might become attached.' WHERE `entry`=26441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like the traps are working!  Thanks $N!' WHERE `entry`=26442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='By the Seven Crystals of Ata\'mal, this cannot be! They plan to attack Forest Song?! Not on my watch! No. We will not allow this to happen!' WHERE `entry`=26443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have my respect and thanks, $C. Perhaps we\'ll be able to create a new home here without having to worry about the Burning Legion yet again.' WHERE `entry`=26444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Never again will the Burning Legion threaten Ashenvale! You have delivered us from a fight we very likely would have lost, $C. I give you thanks, $N, and the deepest gratitude of the Hand of Argus. It honors me to have you at our side!' WHERE `entry`=26445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. Though it may take a great deal of your years for the seedlings to grow into ancients, in the fullness of time they will aid us in our fight against all of the enemies of Ashenvale.' WHERE `entry`=26446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dreadlords!  They plan to attack us here at Splintertree Post?! Not while I still draw breath! No. We will not allow this to happen!  They are a blight upon our world!' WHERE `entry`=26447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s better!  There\'s nothing quite like ridding our world of a demon. And they make for worthy opponents as well, unlike the weak races of the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=26448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Never again will the Burning Legion make slaves of the orcs, or any other race of the Horde!$B$BBravely fought, $C! You have the true heart of the Horde beating inside of you! You give us much honor!' WHERE `entry`=26449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, $N. Now I\'ve just got to decide what to do with all of these...' WHERE `entry`=26450;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $R!  Did you feel it?  The rush of the melee?  The true risk of free-for-all combat? As today is your first day here, I\'ll let you perform in one more competition for another reward. If you return in the future, you may compete again, once a day. Your rewards will, of course, improve as you become stronger.' WHERE `entry`=26451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $R!  I look forward to seeing you fight again soon.' WHERE `entry`=26452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see another new arrival here at Forest Song.$B$BVindicator Palanaar is sending as much help as she can muster and each set of hands is appreciated.$B$BTake a look around, $C. It may not be much now, but with time and help from our night elf allies, we\'ll build a settlement worthy of calling home. There is much to be done here and any help you can provide would be welcome.' WHERE `entry`=26453;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wood warped by foul demonic magic is of no use to the draenei at Forest Song. Nothing sound can be built with it, but I shall purify it and return it in good time to Architect Nemos and his people for their use. Some good will come from this tragedy, after all.' WHERE `entry`=26454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. There is certainly a latent power here, one that not even constant exposure to the corruption of the satyr can dim. Do you see how it still shines, after all these years?' WHERE `entry`=26455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for delivering this report, $C. From what Sentinel Melyria writes, it seems our worst fears have come to pass. With each advance we make, the Horde appears more determined to do as much damage as possible. We can\'t afford to back down; the fate of our ancestral lands hangs in the balance. With more people like you on the frontlines, I\'m certain we could triumph. Will you join our fight? A new front has just opened in Warsong Gulch to the south.' WHERE `entry`=26456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At last we have sent a message that the orcs won\'t dare ignore. Any overseer or foreman who sets foot within the camp to replace Gorthak will feel my wrath! We must press our advantage, $N, and never rest until the Warsong Lumber Camp is a distant memory and a glade of trees stands upon that ground. Now what was this about explosives...?' WHERE `entry`=26457;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Foolish blood elves toil with demonic magic. Have they not witnessed what happened with the naga and with the satyrs of Kalimdor?$B$BI fear that the blood elves will meet a similar deformation. Azeroth cannot afford to give birth to another vile race of monsters.$B$BI wish to study the brain stems of the satyr and naga so that I might deduce what fate the Sin\'dorei are headed toward. In Blackfathom Deeps, just to the west, you will find both satyr and naga.' WHERE `entry`=26459;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Strength has left me. Your help is needed!$B$BLong ago this site was a great temple of Elune. But misfortune led to ruin when the corruption of an Old God seeped up from below and tainted the sacred moonwell.$B$BAku\'Mai, servant of the Old God, rose from the waters.$B$BThe Twilight\'s Hammer cultists have allied with the naga to occupy these grounds. The cultists, led by Kelris, sacrifice innocents to Aku\'Mai for power.$B$BSlay Kelris and bring his head to Ashelan at the Blackfathom Camp, $N, please.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring the head of Twilight Lord Kelris to Ashelan Northwood at the Blackfathom Camp.' WHERE `entry`=26461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad for a city-dwellin\' $R. Good show, aye!' WHERE `entry`=26462;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Finding Teronis',`details_loc1`='A friend of mine from Astranaar, Raene Wolfrunner, asked me to send a scout west to Lake Falathim. Teronis left days ago, just before the Horde attacked.$B$BHe was searching for an item he thought could slow the furbolg attacks on our people--a rod created by a now-dead, evil wizard.$B$BBefore he left, he mentioned a gem for the rod. Unfortunately, we know that the lake has been invaded by some evil force.$B$BPlease, $N, find my friend.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Teronis\' body lies broken atop the small rise next to the Keeper. Deep slashes crisscross his corpse.' WHERE `entry`=26463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is terrible, $N. Teronis is dead?! The time for mourning will come, but for now we must focus our efforts. I will send some of the Sentinels to recover Teronis\' body and to assist the keeper. You have the gem that Teronis was seeking? It must be delivered to Astranaar.' WHERE `entry`=26464;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s quite a few that you have found! Thank you, $N! The old city of Zoram holds many secrets, and these statuettes may be the key to many of them.' WHERE `entry`=26465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found the ring! Thank you, $N. Please take this as payment, and know that your deeds today will remain forever in my memory.' WHERE `entry`=26466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Judging by the gaping wound in her side, Anilia is on the verge of death.' WHERE `entry`=26467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Anilia died? No... that can\'t be! It was just yesterday that we were running and playing together in the woods.$B$BI guess those days are over...' WHERE `entry`=26468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, kind $R. My sister\'s spirit is gladdened by your efforts.' WHERE `entry`=26469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N! With the befouled elemental numbers thinned and Tideress put back into the lake, we should be able to launch a counter-offensive on Silverwind Refuge. Just as soon as we\'re done with defending the spire....' WHERE `entry`=26470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Rest in peace, my friends. I felt the anguish of the Dor\'danil Barrows lessen, and knew that you had completed your task. It was grim work that you did, $N, for the spirits you destroyed were merely victims of the Horde\'s evil. But with their destruction, let us hope the maddened spirits will finally find peace.' WHERE `entry`=26472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you have the hair! This is a good first step. There are other ingredients that we will need, but the hair of the fallen Ancient could well be the most important. I only hope that whatever the Forsaken are devising from the plant will not be turned into a weapon. We simply do not have the numbers to remove them right now, especially with Maestra\'s Post under attack!' WHERE `entry`=26473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is from Orendil? His skill with herbs and healing is great! This cure gives me hope, when before I had little....' WHERE `entry`=26474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, you found it! Odd... it looks tarnished somehow. I will place the tear in a stew, and pray that it will cure her. Thank you! Thank you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, Raene sent you? It must be serious indeed. What can I help you with?' WHERE `entry`=26476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m pleased to see you\'re back, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The last piece of the rod is held by druids of the claw. I asked their leader, Oso Bramblescar, to give it to me, but he and his guardians nearly killed me! Clearly they too were affected by the Horde\'s corruption of the Forest Heart.$B$BBut, I have an idea for how you can get into Oso\'s cave and grab the pommel.$B$BEver since I was a faun, I\'ve been pretty good at playing possum. It works great against bears! I can teach you! Go east to the Shady Nook, and if they try to get you, just use my technique.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got it? Wonderful for you... and for Raene! I guess we\'ll have to see about reassembling it, won\'t we?' WHERE `entry`=26478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve recreated the rod Teronis had set out to find? That\'s wonderful to hear. Shael\'dryn has been indispensible in her assistance. Teronis would be proud to see his quest is continuing even after his tragic passing. Now it is time for us to make use of its power to eliminate the enemies of Ashenvale!' WHERE `entry`=26479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Use Dartol\'s Rod to be able to communicate with Krolg at Krolg\'s Hut in Ashenvale.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, yes... you appear as one of my kind, but I care not what you truly are if you can help the furbolg. The night elves and now the orcs have visited many atrocities upon my people. Corruption runs through our veins, corruption brought down upon us by the prideful night elves and the warlike orcs. They are the ones who did this to our people... They are the ones I blame for being cast out of my tribe. At night I can still see the campfires burning in the darkness.' WHERE `entry`=26480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, my friend. Now quickly, hand me Ran\'s skull. While his essence yet taints it, we shall fashion it upon Dartol\'s Rod giving you the power to influence my brethren and deliver them from evil!' WHERE `entry`=26481;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, you used the skull of the furbolg king to modify the power of Dartol\'s Rod? You then used that power to convince the captured furbolg to rise up and attack the Horde at Silverwind Refuge? I am more than pleased and impressed with your abilities, $N. The Sentinels cannot thank you enough. It should be a simple matter for us to sweep away the orcs and retake the refuge now! Teronis would be proud. You have my deepest respect.' WHERE `entry`=26482;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that\'s what I like to hear! Good on ya.' WHERE `entry`=26483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Stonefather\'s son, Flint, sent you? No time to talk. We must prevent a second front from opening up on the war!' WHERE `entry`=26484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, nice an\' fresh. I\'ll get those going while you fetch me some more goods then...' WHERE `entry`=26485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s the stuff! Wouldn\'t want any trolls or goblins gettin\' pleasure out of these, now would we! Maybe I can work a bit of this into my next brew...' WHERE `entry`=26486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey hey!  Not bad, not bad at all!  You may have a future in resource acquisition. Or hotel management.' WHERE `entry`=26487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Arnold and I used to relax down at the moat in the Valley of Heroes. One day, I lost my locket in the lake and I have never been able to find it. Rumor has it that huge royal monkfish live in that moat and that they eat anything!  I know its a long shot, but do you think you could catch a few monkfish and look for my locket?$B$BPlease let me know right away if you find it, it\'s very precious to me.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found it!  I can\'t believe it was down there all those years!  You have no idea how much this means to me $N.' WHERE `entry`=26488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew you had it in you, boss-man. You know what they say: You can take the $R out of the islands, but you can\'t take the murderous tendencies out of $N.' WHERE `entry`=26489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at it! That\'ll put some oomph into the mix!' WHERE `entry`=26490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Years ago, there used to be a Horde base deep within Skulk Rock. It\'s been abandoned since then, but it\'s still prime territory, worth takin\' for our allies!$B$BProblem is, it\'s full of dwarf-eating slimes and oozes. Those things are slightly less disgustin\' than trolls, but they\'ll still give us a hassle.$B$BWith our boys tied up fightin\' the Revantusk, I need you to go to Skulk Rock and clear the place out for me.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 10 Jade Oozes.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see you back... and not missing any limbs, either.' WHERE `entry`=26491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like it\'s still good inside! Huh... is that banana bread? Still fresh! Here, lad, take your share of goods.' WHERE `entry`=26492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great!  These look... disgusting. But probably pretty valuable. Let\'s get to splitting these up. Some for me, some for Jasper, some for Chabal...' WHERE `entry`=26493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll file these away for now. Maybe we can experiment later. Yeah, you\'ll do.' WHERE `entry`=26494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You have my thanks. I have been waiting for you to approach me, $R. I have identified you as the most promising $R here in this strange town. I have a task for you, if you would be willing to take it.' WHERE `entry`=26495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well met, $N! We\'ve got a lot of trolls to kill and only so many hands to do it with!' WHERE `entry`=26496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aye, we\'ll have these trolls cleared out yet.' WHERE `entry`=26497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It won\'t be long until we\'re the only dwarves left breathing on these walls.' WHERE `entry`=26498;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have my thanks, $N. You\'ve made all the difference, and the fate of these cowardly stone trogg ambushers is set in stone. Now we must get about the business of retaking Stonehearth.' WHERE `entry`=26499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not a bad start, though you\'ll have to destroy more of them than that if you\'re going to rescue the Stonefather. A lot more.' WHERE `entry`=26500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is good. We no longer need to worry about stone trogg attacks from the rear. Let\'s see what you can do for us on the front.' WHERE `entry`=26501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Barracks sealed',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Shrine sealed' WHERE `entry`=26501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Those\'ll do. Just put them down over there. I\'m going to have something for you to do in a moment. Maybe.' WHERE `entry`=26502;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew it! Looks like Yowler is behind this uprising - which is incredible, because we keep killing gnolls named Yowler. I don\'t know how many sons the original Yowler had, but it\'s got to be close to a hundred. Well, looks like we got ourselves another Yowler to kill. Magistrate Solomon must be notified.' WHERE `entry`=26503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A job well done deserves a reward, wouldn\'t you say? Don\'t spend this all in one place, $C. Better to spread it around, if you catch my drift.' WHERE `entry`=26504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oh, you\'re not Conacher. What have you got there? Oh for pity\'s sake. Yowler? AGAIN?' WHERE `entry`=26505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='PERFECT! I\'ll put these in the pot right away. Dinner should be ready in a few hours. Thank you, darling!' WHERE `entry`=26506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Pebble leaps upon the pile of petrified bats and rolls around in them, seeming to forget that you exist entirely. Perhaps for the best, if Kor\'s warnings are to be trusted.>' WHERE `entry`=26507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for finding my necklace mister $C... you are very kind! My kitty thanks you too - isn\'t that right Effsee?' WHERE `entry`=26508;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Finally the menace is laid to rest!  Thank you, $N, you have done me a great service. The garden shall be in full bloom this season!' WHERE `entry`=26509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! Let me make a few adjustments here and we should be good to go.' WHERE `entry`=26510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That ought to teach those murlocs a lesson. Hopefully the next time they decide to raid our town they\'ll think twice. We both know that won\'t happen.' WHERE `entry`=26511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Can you hear me, $N? Is this thing on? Ah, yes, I see you there now. Let\'s get to work!' WHERE `entry`=26512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, citizen. Without you, we would have starved or worse, been forced to go out and get food for ourselves.' WHERE `entry`=26513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Good work, $N. I\'ve just been handed some important information. It would appear that our most hated enemy, the Blackrock orcs, have wised up... I\'ve transferred a few silver over to you for the gnome, erm, gnoll kills.' WHERE `entry`=26514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ain\'t that a hoot! Wish I could\'ve seen it myself.' WHERE `entry`=26515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve cleared straight through \'em! Jintha\'Alor is as good as wiped out!' WHERE `entry`=26516;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dead? All of them, around the altar? And you found these spider idols on them... It\'s Shadra. The Spider Loa! They\'re trying to tap her power!' WHERE `entry`=26517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s one ugly mug. Maybe he was takin\' other heads tryin\' to find a prettier one!' WHERE `entry`=26518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Upon touching the orb you hear a faint click.>$B$B<You remove the orb from the pedestal.>$B$BYou now control the orb, therefore you now control the ettins. Maybe you can use an ettin to remove the huge boulder currently crushing Foreman Oslow over at Lakeshire. Find an ettin and use the orb on the ettin. Then head over to Lakeshire.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You used an ettin to remove the boulder that was crushing Foreman Oslow? Incredible work, $N! Oslow will be grateful once he regains his composure.' WHERE `entry`=26520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The elements dance, and fire consumes. Let the flame show \'em the cost of their wickedness!' WHERE `entry`=26521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='By Kurdan\'s beard... these don\'t look like any spiders I\'ve seen before. Dark magic\'s at work here.' WHERE `entry`=26523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This isn\'t just blood... it\'s venom! Spiders... venom... I hope I\'m wrong about my hunches here, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good riddance. May those horrid things never walk these lands again.' WHERE `entry`=26525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A tablet! If I can read this... this is a ritual to summon Shadra herself into this world, and a list of the idols needed. You\'ve done a good job slaying the keeper and getting ahold of this, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'d smash this tablet to bits if I had the right, but that\'s not for me to decide. Gryphonmaster Talonaxe needs to see this.$B$BYou\'ve got to return to Aerie Peak with the tablet. Gryphon Master Talonaxe is in the aviary, tending to the gryphons.$B$BBe swift... and don\'t let that tablet leave your grasp for a moment!',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver the Tablet of Shadra to Gryphon Master Talonaxe.' WHERE `entry`=26527;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. We\'ll be knockin\' on this bug\'s door in no time.' WHERE `entry`=26528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There it is... only one left, lad.' WHERE `entry`=26529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is it, lad! We\'re ready!' WHERE `entry`=26530;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Talonaxe and the boys are right behind. Let\'s do this!' WHERE `entry`=26531;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done a great thing for the Wildhammer today, $N. I wish Falstad could\'ve been here for that. On behalf of the whole clan, I\'d like to repay you for keeping these lands free from that foul shadow. You\'ve earned this reward.' WHERE `entry`=26532;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This mixture is... I don\'t understand it. Perhaps we need to run some clinical trials.' WHERE `entry`=26533;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You don\'t say!  Well, that certainly is interesting. In that case... Forget understanding how the stuff works!  I gotta get my hands on that recipe!' WHERE `entry`=26534;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is fascinating!  Just think of all the applications! Just so we\'re clear, I\'m not thinking about using this to make an army of slaves or anything like that. No, no... I\'m much more interested in the ogre explosions!' WHERE `entry`=26535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These perch look great $N. Why don\'t you join us for a fish fry tonight?' WHERE `entry`=26536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a good dent, but it\'s clear to me that we\'re going to have to handle this a slightly different way.' WHERE `entry`=26537;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' If it is Zaela\'s wish, then you shall have your supplies. Just don\'t tell the Dragonmaw Warchief...' WHERE `entry`=26538;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad you\'re here, $C. Perhaps a seasoned veteran of the Horde\'s campaigns in Northrend and elsewhere can talk some sense into the Dragonmaw leadership...' WHERE `entry`=26539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dragon\'s Blood!? We best not tell our red dragon allies that we\'ve used these. Still, it\'s powerful magic... We\'ll have our fighting force back in no time.' WHERE `entry`=26540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Gryphon Master Talonaxe at the aviary in Aerie Peak.$B$BOur new brothers in the Alliance need your help to fend off the aggressive Horde offensive in their beloved homeland. Travel north from the Arathi Highlands, through the dwarven mountain pass and follow the road northwest to Aerie Peak.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Aerie Peak, $N. On behalf of High Thane Falstad, I thank ye for comin\' to help us.' WHERE `entry`=26542;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like you found the clams, $N. These will do nicely.' WHERE `entry`=26543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Just put the missive in the little compartment and I\'ll read it. I am fluent in orcish. It looks like these orcs are here under the direct command of Yowler. That means Yowler must have the orc invasion plan.' WHERE `entry`=26544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Shadowhide army!? Damn those orcs to hell! These invasion plans speak of a massive build up of orcish and gnoll forces in the east. Looks like Gath\'Ilzogg, the Blackrock general, is preparing to march his armies across Lakeshire and attack Stormwind directly!' WHERE `entry`=26545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Treat them with respect, and they\'ll treat you with it as well. Give \'em guff and you\'ll be out an eye!' WHERE `entry`=26546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Much appreciated, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you out here! Let\'s get to it.' WHERE `entry`=26548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wake up, $N! We don\'t have much time. I rescued your gear for you. At least now you\'ve seen the foolishness of our leader first-hand. His blood is contaminated, his rage is unquenchable -- and he\'ll destroy us all trying to defeat the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=26549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is as I suspected. Zanzil is too haughty to interfere with the squabbles between the Bloodscalps and the Skullsplitters. No, he is playing a part in a grander scheme... Jin\'do the Hexxer is using him to help bring Hakkar back to Zul\'Gurub. It\'s good that we found this out now, because it offers us a simple solution.' WHERE `entry`=26550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I ask you to slay Zanzil the Outcast, a lowly, hermetic exile of the Gurubashi, and what do you do?  You dash headfirst into the Gurubashi capital and eliminate one of their High Priests!  Very nearly two!  Only one word suffices to explain such a rash and foolhardy endeavor: Heroism. Jin\'do the Hexxer still walks within Zul\'Gurub\'s walls, but he lost one of his legs when you crushed Jeklik. Today\'s battle is ours.' WHERE `entry`=26555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work $N. These samples will help us figure out what is going on in that toxic soup over there.' WHERE `entry`=26556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Outstanding!  Those sandy carp are picky eaters aren\'t they?' WHERE `entry`=26557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Marnal draws close... and Shadra even closer. Prepare for bloodshed.' WHERE `entry`=26558;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I know where they\'re holding Krakauer and Danforth. We gotta hurry. They were prepping those two for a sacrifice!' WHERE `entry`=26560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wha... Where am I? What happened? Messner? Jorgensen? OH MY GOSH! We have to get to Danforth! It might already be too late!' WHERE `entry`=26561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='About damn time you sissies showed up. My arms were gettin\' tired.' WHERE `entry`=26562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Unbelievable work, $N. You\'ve managed to rescue the entire Bravo Company from the clutches of the Blackrock orcs? With Keeshan\'s team rescued and Keeshan\'s belongings returned, there\'s no way Keeshan could refuse us.' WHERE `entry`=26563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well then. Maybe you\'re okay after all. Alright, alright... don\'t get all bent out of shape. Just give me a few moments with these parts.' WHERE `entry`=26564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So the high tinker himself has heard of my little project? Splendid! I\'ve almost finished my latest prototype, but maybe you can help me chase down those last few parts.' WHERE `entry`=26566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Help you? Help these people? These people that would rather spit on me than crack a smile?' WHERE `entry`=26567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'m not giving up on him, $N, and I\'m not giving up on Redridge. We need to boost his spirits... Rouse the slumbering monster within him!' WHERE `entry`=26568;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fantastic work, $N! These will come in handy for our next project, the Lakeshire SUPER BRIDGE, meant to traverse the length of Lake Everstill. It should be done in 20 or so years. Give or take a decade or two.' WHERE `entry`=26569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve probably bought us another day, maybe two. Nice work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Come in, $N. Do you copy? Troteman here! Great job on getting Keeshan\'s weapons back! Now there\'s one final mission you have to run. Are you up to the challenge?' WHERE `entry`=26571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You heard of the golden stonefish, $N?  The thing with these fish is that they can\'t be caught by normal means. They have jaws so strong that they snap right though any hooks or lures you try to use on \'em.$B$BYou can find a number of them in Thunder Ridge, south of Orgrimmar. That ridge used to be full of thunder lizards, but they all drowned in the flood.$B$BTake my knife, swim down there and cut off their tails. You should be able to use the tail to zap any stonefish you find.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice one, $N!  I tell ya, golden stonefish are not easy to come by so this is a nice treat.' WHERE `entry`=26572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope with these items and with his crew all rescued he\'ll have a change of heart. We can\'t do this without Keeshan.' WHERE `entry`=26573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Shadebough, $N. Lady Shandris sent word of you.' WHERE `entry`=26574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $R. You\'ve done all that I can ask of you. I shall impart my favor for you to the Stonemother.$B$BMay the stone beneath your feet hold you steady during your quest for the World Pillar.' WHERE `entry`=26575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Greetings, $R. I have been told of your coming. If you wish to aid me, then perhaps I can be of aid to you as well.' WHERE `entry`=26576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are Diamant\'s chosen. So small. So fragile. Do you realize that your actions shall be the basis by which your entire, "Earthen Ring" is judged? You truly think you can stand for so many? You are a fool. A confident fool. We shall see if you are a capable fool as well.' WHERE `entry`=26577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have appealed to Diamant. He is patient. Trusting. Perhaps too much so. You have much to prove if you wish my favor, $R. Still, this is a start.' WHERE `entry`=26578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You carry with you a certain degree of potency. I can find some respect for such strength, especially in your kind. My concerns are not yet abated. Not for the source of the overgrowth, and not for you.' WHERE `entry`=26579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good to see you again, brother. I see that your efforts go well. The Stone Lords appear to be showing you some degree of trust. We\'ve come to help. We might be of some aid in tracking down the source of this sudden growth. I highly suspect your giant friend\'s aggressions are focused in the wrong direction.' WHERE `entry`=26580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You let the mist touch your skin? I hope there weren\'t any adverse affects.' WHERE `entry`=26581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The stone troggs? And I am to trust you at your word? I have no love for the Verlok anyway. Suspicion is more than enough reason to lay waste to them. We shall see if your word is true.' WHERE `entry`=26582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $R. Gorsik shall hear of your deed. Therazane shall hear of your deed. You are quite vicious for one so small... and so soft.' WHERE `entry`=26583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done fleshling. Your presence complimented my brothers well.' WHERE `entry`=26584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So your words prove true. You have my gratitude, $R.' WHERE `entry`=26585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Keeshan? You mean JOHNNY\'S ALIVE? You bet your sweet behind I\'ll help, but first you gotta get me out of this damned cage.' WHERE `entry`=26586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Are you up for a challenge, $N?  Good, I was hoping you would be. The southfury river flows just west of Orgrimmar and your challenge can be found within its mighty flow.$B$BWe are looking for a giant furious pike. This esteemed fish used to be prevalent in these areas but ever since the floods hit, the big ones have been much harder to find. Head out to the river and let\'s see just how good of an angler you really are.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, you got one!  It\'s a rare day that I get to see such a strong, beautiful fish.' WHERE `entry`=26588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Peace, friend. I wish we could have met under less troubling circumstances.' WHERE `entry`=26589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Ahh... do you know how hard it is to get fresh water in Stranglethorn?  It\'s no wonder that the nagas guard their shrine so ferociously! Oh, right... your artifact, and clarity. Clarity... I\'ve got it!' WHERE `entry`=26590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If you ever get tired of your being a $C, come look me up. You seem very good with those fleshy hands of yours.' WHERE `entry`=26591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Yes, these will do. Now to perform the analysis... Oh, you\'re still here?  You don\'t think I\'m a fraud or something, do you?' WHERE `entry`=26592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ack! Where\'d you get these? No, don\'t tell me. I don\'t want to know!$B$BWho sent you? Sea Wolf?' WHERE `entry`=26593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Heh heh, well done! And when you showed Shaky those giblets, how hard did he shake?$B$BHah! He\'s so easy to read, when I play cards with him I can\'t help but win!$B$BThanks for your help, $N. Now it\'s your turn to get paid...' WHERE `entry`=26594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great! I can get a good price for these, especially for what\'s inside Maury\'s foot! Thanks much, $N!$B$BI hope those three learned their lesson: don\'t bet something you can\'t afford to lose.$B$BAnd maybe it\'s too late for them, but...they should be careful of who they gamble with.' WHERE `entry`=26595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeah?  Whaddya need?' WHERE `entry`=26596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='...feel strength returning.... Where might I be?  Booty Bay?  Oh my!  I had the strangest dream... ...the weakness has not completely left me....' WHERE `entry`=26597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='temp text 02 - description',`objectives_loc1`='temp text 02 - log',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Witch Doctor Unbagwa like Gorilla Fangs!  For you I talk to spirits. Make Mokk the Savage come. You protect Witch Doctor Unbagwa from other Gorilla-beast though or no Mokk for you!' WHERE `entry`=26598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found it!  What a glorious day for ol\' Hecklebury, this is. Getting back my chest cools some of the fire in me. But my revenge isn\'t complete...' WHERE `entry`=26599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This wasn\'t expensive, was it?  Well, here\'s some pieces of eight to reimburse you. Now let\'s get onto this revenge, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=26600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mok\'rash... Negolash... Gorlash... they\'re all gone. I suppose I have no excuses now. I can return to the high seas and a life of pillage and booty!  And it\'s all thanks to you. Now I just need to get myself a ship...' WHERE `entry`=26601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t believe my fortune, $N!  Meeting you has turned my luck to the better, make no mistake there! If I ever get a new ship and you\'re looking to sail the seas, you would be my honored guest.' WHERE `entry`=26602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you come to free me?' WHERE `entry`=26603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time you returned. I was beginning to worry that I was going to be eaten while you hunted. A cat eating a princess... wouldn\'t that be a fancy feast?' WHERE `entry`=26604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Looks like it\'s all here. Alright, I think I\'m ready to be rescued now.' WHERE `entry`=26605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, you have saved me from a great dishonor. If it was within my power, I would offer you a place among my tribe. But for now, all I can only offer you is this token for the courage and nobility you have shown.' WHERE `entry`=26606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' My bow... and knife! Where did you... Jade\'s amulet... My darling Jade. We got orcs to kill.' WHERE `entry`=26607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Fel Orcs from Outland have laid claim to the Dragonmaw? Obscene! If Hellscream knew what was happening here, he\'d raze their city to the ground...' WHERE `entry`=26608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='On top of the barrel, you discover a map with some hastily written text on it, along with some coins.' WHERE `entry`=26609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sure, I remember you, $C. Back from scouting I see....' WHERE `entry`=26610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Bloodsail Buccaneers attacking Booty Bay?  This isn\'t the first time that those blaggards have tried something. Booty Bay is impenetrable! Sounds like they might be changing their strategies up, though. Wouldn\'t put it past Firallon to try something crazy. Very well, let\'s see what else they\'re up to.' WHERE `entry`=26611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect, $N. Now that we know their plan, it\'s just a matter of time.$B$BAnd to think the fools have dropped anchor just off the cape....' WHERE `entry`=26612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good show, $N! And just before I need to ship out too! Can\'t thank you enough, old friend.' WHERE `entry`=26613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Shiver me timbers and timber me shivers!  Ye found me beautiful eye!  Let\'s see if she still fits. $N ho!  Blimey, I can see!!' WHERE `entry`=26614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s orc killin\' time.' WHERE `entry`=26616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That coin!  Where did you get it? Bruce... yes, I see. He was one of the Blackwater Raiders once. One of us, before Greymane closed the Gilneas ports and held his crew captive. I know that what happened in Gilneas changed the people there, but I never expected them to change their loyalties. Especially not Bruce. If you wouldn\'t mind, could I keep the coin?  I\'ll pay its worth in gold.' WHERE `entry`=26617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Don\'t go thinking that was too easy. Far greater dangers lurk deeper in the woods.' WHERE `entry`=26618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, what are your people doing? Are you attacking the Dragonmaw or are you here to rid us of Mor\'ghor\'s corruption? Ah, I see now. I like the way you think. Warchief Mor\'ghor won\'t even know what hit him. Let\'s do this!' WHERE `entry`=26619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mmm-mmm! The skirtsteak\'s the best part. It\'s not an efficient way to cook, though. Here, have this recipe. It\'s a little different, but flank meat\'s easier to come by when you really need a meal.' WHERE `entry`=26620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve lost a lot of good orcs, but the fight is going our way, $N. Mor\'ghor\'s regime is collapsing. All that remains is to destroy the beast himself.' WHERE `entry`=26621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N! You have done the Horde proud in my absence. The Dragonmaw have joined us, with Zaela as their new leader. Blood was shed, but casualties were low, and we have their complete loyalty. Our Horde grows stronger!' WHERE `entry`=26622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah yes, a nice lump you have there!  Let me just get this seasoned with my secret spices (no looking!) and get them to skittering on a skillet for a while... And, although Dusky Crab Cakes are my specialty and I won\'t give out the recipe, here\'s the recipe for a dish that\'s almost as good.' WHERE `entry`=26623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yarr, ya made a good decision, lad.' WHERE `entry`=26624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Finally, we can move forward and rescue the Stonefather.' WHERE `entry`=26625;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, welcome, stranger. I\'d offer you something, but there\'s not much here... Could I beg you to run some errands for a poor old hermit?' WHERE `entry`=26627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We survived the attack!$B$BWe could not have done it without you, $N.$B$BWe\'ll be heading out as soon as the tide rises. If you weren\'t such a promising hero I\'d offer you a place on my crew. But I can tell you have bigger fish to fry.$B$BEven if you are a puny $R....' WHERE `entry`=26628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well blow me down!  Now there\'s something ya don\'t see too often. Welcome aboard, $N. Plunder and booty await ye.' WHERE `entry`=26629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That should fool that Bloodsail dimwit. This was fun, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes... yes... I see... well, everything appears to be in order. Slayer of the great Seahorn, eh?  That doesn\'t matter on MY ship. Only thing you\'re gonna be slaying is deck stains. Grab a mop.' WHERE `entry`=26631;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Word of your prowess has spread ahead of you, $R. Let\'s see if you can help us keep these fungal horrors off of the front.' WHERE `entry`=26632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I heard the most furious mopping sounds from down here, mate. That\'s EXACTLY what your Captain likes to hear.' WHERE `entry`=26633;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll distribute these right away, $R. And I\'ll see what I can do to put in the good word for you.' WHERE `entry`=26634;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks, $N. I\'d been hearing whispers about "Pretty Boy" and a "boo-box". I don\'t think I want to go in the boo-box.' WHERE `entry`=26635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice job, rookie. I\'m gonna go ahead and put the camo in the box. We should be ready soon.' WHERE `entry`=26636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect. Those orcs won\'t know what hit \'em - literally. I\'ll need a few minutes to get these in working order and then I\'ll put them in the Bravo Company field kit.' WHERE `entry`=26637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work, $N. We need to move quickly before they send for reinforcements.' WHERE `entry`=26638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brubaker is dead. It looks like the orcs are attempting to send a message with this grizzly display. Upon closer examination you notice something in Brubaker\'s pouch.' WHERE `entry`=26639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' DAMN IT! This just got complicated. We\'ve got prisoners of war to rescue before we can blow up the valley. Not to mention the orcs have black dragons on their side. Are you ready, $N?' WHERE `entry`=26640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll see these are burnt to ash right away, and scattered to the winds for good measure.' WHERE `entry`=26641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A fresh recruit from Orgrimmar is it? I\'ll take what I can get. Keeping the roads open has been a nightmare.' WHERE `entry`=26642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A grim task for sure, $N, but it\'ll keep the spiders left alive from recovering. I thank you.' WHERE `entry`=26643;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So ye be the one that did ol\' Seahorn?  Yancey sent word, but I wanted to make sure he hadn\'t been telling his tall tales again. I\'ll make it brief. Ye did well on Keelhaul\'s crew, but I expect ye to do even better on mine. I\'ve got an entire fleet to attend to, so you\'ll be helpin\' to run the day-to-day of me ship. Welcome aboard the Crimson Veil, sailor.' WHERE `entry`=26644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Splendid, $N. For your service to the people of Darkshire you shall be rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=26645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Looks like the P.O.W.s are free. Time to initiate Operation: End All.' WHERE `entry`=26646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I like the cut of your gib, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. The eternal battle wages on, but we\'ve tipped the scales in favor of the pirates today. Firallon will be happy to hear the news.' WHERE `entry`=26648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahahaha!  Blasted \'em clear off their rigging!  I\'ll drink to that! You\'ve got a bright future, kid.' WHERE `entry`=26649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You see a set of plans unrolled on the table. They explain everything! These are the details of the impending attack on Booty Bay. Battle formations, plans of attack, and something about a group called the "Brashtide Crew".' WHERE `entry`=26650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And now, we blow the whole damned thing up.' WHERE `entry`=26651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What is this? A comb? It\'s lovely! And it glides through my hair as if it weren\'t the stiff, stringy horror that it is.$B$BOh, if only I had a mirror...' WHERE `entry`=26652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, Ghost Hair Thread is what you need, is it? I\'m afraid I have none in stock, but I can make some for you...if you can supply the ghost hair.' WHERE `entry`=26653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can make a spool of Ghost Hair Thread with this, and have a few strands to spare. Here are some coins for those extra strands.' WHERE `entry`=26654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Delightful! This will do splendidly...$B$BHere, good $N, take this as payment for your honorable deed.' WHERE `entry`=26655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. Of my main strengths, speed is not one.' WHERE `entry`=26656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not just fast it seems. You have some bite in you.$B$BWell done, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glorious.$B$BNow we will deal a blow to the stone dragons that they will remember for the next hundred years.' WHERE `entry`=26658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Impressive, fleshling. You are far more capable than I initially assumed.$B$BI will extend that sentiment to the Stonemother as well.' WHERE `entry`=26659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You need some Zombie Juice, do you? Hmm...that\'s some strong stuff - I don\'t usually get requests for it.' WHERE `entry`=26660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Gather 5 Rot Blossoms from Tranquil Gardens Cemetary.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, you got the rot blossoms. I\'ll whip up the zombie juice... it\'s strong stuff, I warn you.' WHERE `entry`=26661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Brashtide Crew aren\'t just pirates... they\'re worgen pirates!  And they\'re joining in on the attack! Revilgaz is definitely going to want to know about this.' WHERE `entry`=26662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve set the pirates back several days\' work. Hopefully this will delay their attack.' WHERE `entry`=26663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The fewer Bloodsail Buccaneers that Booty Bay has to fight, the better. However, it might be best to stop slaughtering your supposed allies before you draw suspicion to yourself.' WHERE `entry`=26664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Brashtide!?  I thought they were dead and gone YEARS ago! No, that absolutely makes sense. And it\'s not good news either. The Brashtide are formidable foes, and if their numbers are anywhere near what they were before they disappeared, we\'re in for a nasty battle.' WHERE `entry`=26665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='By the light... you actually went and got it? I\'m shocked. I suppose I owe you thanks for returning it to the archives.' WHERE `entry`=26667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did you see those orcs explode? THAT\'S HOW WE DO IT IN BRAVO COMPANY! Now to clean up the rest of these jackasses.' WHERE `entry`=26668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This was all you found? That\'s bad news, I\'m afraid...' WHERE `entry`=26669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You actually went and got it?! I don\'t know whether to call you brave or insane. But once again, my archives thank you.' WHERE `entry`=26670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t thank you enough... I had hoped for this to be a joyous reunion, but the more I learn, the less glad I am to have asked. But I must know.' WHERE `entry`=26671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='How interesting. It\'s been quite a while since I\'ve seen such a ring...' WHERE `entry`=26672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='REUSE - BREADCRUMB' WHERE `entry`=26673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m afraid I cannot give Tobias the answers he seeks. But I can help you find the only person who can...$B$BStalvan Mistmantle.$B$BTake the ring into the woods to the east, to Manor Mistmantle, where Stalvan\'s body was buried. Enter, and hold the ring before you. Let the waning moon pour its light through the ring, and the spirits will answer your call.$B$BTake heed, $N. The questions of the living can offer more comfort than the answers of the dead.',`objectives_loc1`='Use the Mistmantle Family Ring at Manor Mistmantle, east of town.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Master Harris may have been right. I would have been better to leave the past behind. I\'ve got a new life now. Whether it\'s that of a monster or a man is up to me. As for you, I cannot thank you enough for your assistance, regardless of the outcome. Please, take this with my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=26674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A thousand thanks, $N. You warm an old man\'s heart with your foolish-...I mean...with your kindness!$B$BHere you are, friend. Take this as a token of my gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=26676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, thanks. These will do just the trick!' WHERE `entry`=26677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This must be the doublerum. You pour a glass for Revilgaz, then consider pouring one for yourself...' WHERE `entry`=26678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' AH!  Much better, $N. Now, let\'s get down to business. I believe that you and I have a town to save.' WHERE `entry`=26679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank the Nec-...well, thank YOU, $N! You have more than earned your reward.$B$BAha! Happy! Happy nights ahead!!' WHERE `entry`=26680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You fool! You\'ve doomed us all!' WHERE `entry`=26681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. We\'ll be able to focus on greater threats here now.' WHERE `entry`=26682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why yes, I used to own a looking glass.' WHERE `entry`=26683;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The looking glass was one of my finest treasures until. . .the incident. After that happened, I discarded it behind the barn. There was an Insane Ghoul who used to roam back there. Perhaps he picked it up. Rumor has it the devilish beast resides in the Tranquil Gardens Cemetery.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most superb! This will work perfectly. Many thanks!' WHERE `entry`=26684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At last!  The stargazing device is complete!  Thank you, $N. Now I can continue my research. . .' WHERE `entry`=26685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The people of Darkshire thank you, $N. You have proven yourself to be a great ally of The Night Watch.' WHERE `entry`=26686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What now, soldier? Reinforcements? For the Barrens? We\'ve been bleeding supplies and men there for months! Does someone need to remind Twinbraid of the attack on Northwatch? Our losses at Honor\'s Stand? What happened to the men I sent to Triumph Hold? We\'ve nothing to spare! Listen $N, if you want to help out our cause, you\'ll focus your efforts here in Dustwallow. Between the deserters and the Horde encroachment... we could use a hand.' WHERE `entry`=26687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Impressive, $N. It would seem that you are capable enough to handle yourself. Perhaps a more suitable challenge could be found for one of your abilities.' WHERE `entry`=26688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You performed well against the Shadow Weavers, $N. But even now, years after their first arrival, there seem to be so many to replace the ones we kill. I will put my faith in Master Carevin. No doubt he will get to the bottom of the problem.' WHERE `entry`=26689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, to be honest with you, I did not believe that you would get this far, but you are clearly a $C to be reckoned with. In fact, if you wish to formally join Master Carevin\'s struggle, I will gladly write for you a letter of recommendation.' WHERE `entry`=26690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excuse me for my cold reception, $N, but as I\'m sure you can tell, I am an extremely busy man. I see that you have impressed Calor--and I assure you, that is no small feat--and that he has given his recommendation.$B$BThere are unsavory types afoot, $N, and we can use the help of all who have proven themselves. We battle against demons, the undead, and those who would provide them aid. Be vigilant, be wary, and trust none who would not give aid to our cause.$B$BGlory under the Light.' WHERE `entry`=26691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re closing in on the Blackrock high command. There\'s nowhere left for those dogs to run.' WHERE `entry`=26692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Now that the easy part is over, it\'s time for phase two.' WHERE `entry`=26693;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He teleported away? Mentioned Darkblaze? What the hell is going on here. Looks like it\'s time to strap in and finish this nonsense.' WHERE `entry`=26694;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You brought them!  I\'m beginning to think the tide is turning in our favor, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeah?  What can I do for ya?' WHERE `entry`=26696;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope those mongrels know how to doggy paddle! Actually, I take that back.' WHERE `entry`=26697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I should have known these Brashtide were alive and up to no good. I\'d written them off years ago.' WHERE `entry`=26698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We need to keep moving, $N. Booty Bay won\'t hold out for much longer.' WHERE `entry`=26699;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Attacking your former crewmen... You really have grown into a real pirate, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lok\'tar, $R. Welcome to Brackenwall.' WHERE `entry`=26701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N!  You\'re awake!  We found you bobbing in the harbor, shortly after the remaining attackers had turned tail. We were worried about you for a while there... I\'ve been meaning to thank you, $N. Not only did you provide us with the intelligence to prepare for this attack, but you helped fight off the Bloodsail AND the Brashtide. Your name will always be remembered here in Booty Bay. We here in Booty Bay pride ourselves on our booty. Care to take first pick?' WHERE `entry`=26703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We did it, $N. We\'ve started the evacuation. If we leave soon we\'ll leave the Forsaken fleet in the dust.' WHERE `entry`=26706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $C... and I\'m sure the worgen that may be returned to sanity with the potion this will make would thank you too.' WHERE `entry`=26707;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='AHHHHHHHHHHHH! AHHHHHHHHH!!!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The only thing left to deal with now are the orcs holding out at Stonewatch Keep.' WHERE `entry`=26708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I am returning to my throne. I\'ve no desire to see any more of these Earthen Ring, but you remain welcome here, $R. If you wish to help us rebuild our realm, perhaps we can help you in return.$B$BAll things in time.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You returned. This is good. The Stone Lords have been asking after you.' WHERE `entry`=26709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well. Now that these are rocklings are free to learn our ways, they will grow tall and strong. One day, we will extinguish the gyreworm infestation from our realm, and these rocklings shall no longer be plagued in their youth.' WHERE `entry`=26710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, it\'s you, ma\'am! Sorry, I didn\'t recognize you at first with all of these commoners milling about. You people cool your heels! $N is here! Here are your macaroons, ma\'am. Come back anytime if you need more.' WHERE `entry`=26711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, it\'s you, sir! Sorry, I didn\'t recognize you at first with all of these commoners milling about. You people cool your heels! $N is here! Here are your macaroons, sir. Come back anytime if you need more.' WHERE `entry`=26712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Come in, $N. Are you there? If you can hear me: Blackrock has the upper hand. I repeat. Blackrock has the upper hand. GET BRAVO COMPANY OUT OF TH...' WHERE `entry`=26713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' They died in defense of the Alliance. In defense of our kingdom! Heroes, all of them, and they will be laid to rest as such.' WHERE `entry`=26714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sounds like a close call! But he ran off without harming you further... He might be still fighting it. Master Harris must know!' WHERE `entry`=26717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to our humble camp. I wouldn\'t call it pleasant, but it\'s at least somewhat private. Beg your pardon? A worgen at the farm?' WHERE `entry`=26719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve got him! No time to lose, then. We\'ll prepare to administer the serum right away. JITTERS! Get ready!' WHERE `entry`=26720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh thank you, thank you! You\'ve saved me from having to go out in the woods with those awful things! At least for a day, that is...' WHERE `entry`=26721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='His clothes and bloodstains? If it\'s not tricks, it\'s something worse...' WHERE `entry`=26723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s heartening to see one so recently recovered be so concerned with the plight of others. Sven spares himself suffering by not dwelling on his own misfortune.' WHERE `entry`=26724;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They will never be forgotten, $N. What you and the rest of Bravo Company sacrificed in order to save Redridge will be a tale told for ages to come. While I can in no way make up for the loss of your friends, I feel that you must be rewarded for such a heroic deed. These are Keeshan\'s possessions - the only things we found when we dredged the lake for his body. Troteman has informed me that Keeshan would have wanted you to take something as the lone surviving member of Bravo Company. Remember them, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26726;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank the light, he\'s gone... I\'ll say you\'ve made amends by helping save the lives of those here, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26727;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are the help that we requested? I suppose you will have to do.' WHERE `entry`=26728;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These will do for my purposes. Though we can\'t activate the altar with bracers alone...' WHERE `entry`=26729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We have what we need. Are you ready to activate the Altar of Naias, $N?' WHERE `entry`=26730;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My colleagues within the Kirin Tor will be happy to learn that the heart is ours. Thank you for your assistance, $N. I couldn\'t have done it without you.' WHERE `entry`=26731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. Now, let\'s see what they\'ve got in this elixir of theirs...' WHERE `entry`=26732;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This will do. Please hold on for a moment while I test this out.' WHERE `entry`=26733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I knew they\'d have some more of this substance. I\'m going to send this to my contacts at Fort Livingston, to the south. Hopefully they\'ll have some more luck with it. Thank you for everything, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26734;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They KILLED him?  And all this time, I thought he had them underneath an iron bootheel...' WHERE `entry`=26735;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. It looks like my suspicions were correct... the three prisoners seem to have escaped the affliction that gripped Kurzen and the rest of his men. Before you arrived, Emerine teleported them over to Stormwind to get cleaned up after their ordeal. They promised to return soon.' WHERE `entry`=26736;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Marvelously executed, $N. My men and I can handle the rest. With Kurzen out of the picture, we may be able to continue our original expedition here in Stranglethorn, which was... ahh... No matter. Please, feel free to peruse our armor stores. You may find something that fits you well.' WHERE `entry`=26737;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Bring the Lashtail Hatchling to Corporal Sethman at the Rebel Camp in Northern Stranglethorn.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, the little one seems to have taken a liking to you. You\'re lucky... at this age, the raptors are calm, peaceful, and easily trained. Keep her, $N... she may come in handy. In fact...' WHERE `entry`=26738;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='She looks bigger already!  You can see, these raptors grow quickly. You are lucky to have found such a strong companion. Keep her by your side as long as you can, $N. I\'m sure she will prove to be an asset in the future.' WHERE `entry`=26739;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh I see, it\'s a Krazek\'s Crock Pot! An ingenious piece of work, but it can break a spring or throw a gear now and then. Let me see what\'s wrong with this one...$B$BAha! Its steam charger is rusted out, it has a cracked knuckle-gasket and its fobulator is missing teeth. I\'m surprised the pot could even boil a turnip in this state!$B$BCan I fix it? Of course I can fix it!$B$BBut there\'s a price. Oh yes, there is always a price...' WHERE `entry`=26740;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I think I can read this text... Fascinating! Tsul\'kalu, Mahamba, Pogeyan... what are these names?' WHERE `entry`=26742;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='First you save me from the madman\'s jail cell, and now you bring me some keys to understanding trollish shamanism. This is turning out to be a pretty good week! Thank you again, $N. I will see to it that you have the support of the Wildhammer clan as you continue on your journeys.' WHERE `entry`=26743;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='To be honest, I\'m sending this information home to Stormwind, for my wife and son. They love to hear about what I\'ve been doing out here in the jungle, and I only get to visit so often. Every little bit helps. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Report to Osborn Obnoticus at the Rebel Camp and show him your Lashtail Hatchling\'s new skull.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='What do we have here?  A young raptor, and her pet $R. Hah! More importantly, what is that skull you have there?  This was no ordinary troll. He was big... ... and strong, too. You know, I\'ve been meaning to try my hand at some troll magic. How hard could it be?  Let\'s use this strong fellow as a test subject, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=26745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These will provide a bit of... what\'s the troll word?  Voodoo?  Juju?  Tiklabang? It doesn\'t matter. If we\'re going to re-build a troll, we need troll magic, and these fetishes are full of it.' WHERE `entry`=26746;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $R. We have a head, a body, and some juju-voodoo-mojo nonsense. Now, just a little shock of electricity to get things started, and...' WHERE `entry`=26747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$R. You just resurrected your worst nightmare. You didn\'t think I was a friend, did you, $R?  Ah, ha ha haaaa!$B$BYou\'ve served your purpose. I\'ve returned to the realm of the living, and it\'s all thanks to you. So, instead of killing you, I\'m going to make you a deal instead.$B$BGive me that raptor.$B$BYou must already know that she\'s no normal raptor, and I need a replacement for Ohgan. Do it, or both you and the gnome will taste my rage.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad to see you\'ve come to your senses. Come and visit us in Zul\'Gurub sometime, $R. I\'ll be watching...' WHERE `entry`=26748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mandokir is alive, yes. You are responsible, yes. You may be able to stop him still, yes.' WHERE `entry`=26749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you\'ve come. Fleshlings just like you killed my daughter... my only daughter. With no provocation. Not sated at stripping me of my family, more of you flocked to Deathwing to serve him in ravaging my home. You\'re quite arrogant to come before me asking for MY help. I\'m tempted to crush you where you stand.' WHERE `entry`=26750;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Balance is restored - for now. We may call on you again in the future, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya\'ve done well, brotha. Da Stonemother be listenin\' and da World Pillar is not far from our reach.' WHERE `entry`=26752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='May the disgusting monster stay dead this time! I\'ll head down there and scatter his remains to ash myself, $N. You\'ve done a great thing; perhaps in time Duskwood can return to its former peaceful state.' WHERE `entry`=26754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a great start, $N, but we\'re going to need you to fly over into the town and stir up some trouble.' WHERE `entry`=26755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='A friend of mine, Nessa Shadowsong, is a fishing merchant in Rut\'theran Village. She needs a parcel taken to Darkshore, and is looking for someone to help her.$B$BIf you\'re interested, then to reach Nessa you must take the portal in Darnassus to Rut\'theran Village. You will find the portal west of the Temple Gardens.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Nessa Shadowsong.' WHERE `entry`=26756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The fishermen of Rut\'theran village do very well, for the fish here are extremely large and abundant. I would like to compare the bounty here with that of the mainland.$B$BI have a collection of fish bones and scales that I would like taken to a colleague of mine in Darkshore. His name is Laird, he is a fish vendor in the village of Auberdine.$B$BBring my collection to our hippogryph master, Vesprystus, and speak to him about traveling to Auberdine.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring Nessa\'s Collection to Vesprystus.' WHERE `entry`=26757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='From Rut\'theran, there are two methods of travel to Auberdine: by ferry and by hippogryph. Both are quick and reliable, but if you have not yet flown to Auberdine by hippogryph, then I suggest you do.$B$BIt is sound advice to speak with the hippogryph master in every town that has one. Once you speak to the master, you can then fly there from other towns.$B$BHere is Nessa\'s collection. Speak with me again when you are ready to fly to Auberdine and deliver Nessa\'s collection to Laird.',`objectives_loc1`='Ride a hippogryph to Auberdine from the hippogryph master Vesprystus, then bring Nessa\'s Collection to Laird.' WHERE `entry`=26758;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I must send a response to Nessa. She\'ll be very interested to know how different the fish here are from those along Teldrassil\'s coastline. We can only guess the cause, but it is my suspicion that the world tree itself is affecting the wildlife around it!$B$BPlease, take this response to Nessa. If you wish to take a hippogryph back to Rut\'theran then speak with the hippogryph master Caylais Moonfeather. If you wish to take the ferry, then one regularly departs from the dock to the northwest.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring Laird\'s Response to Nessa Shadowsong.' WHERE `entry`=26759;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Success... Finally! I can\'t thank you enough for giving me the chance to work the cure myself. Our new friend may be in need of some help as well. You might want to speak with him.' WHERE `entry`=26760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I heard about the Defias making a return. Terrible news. I wish I had better news, but it would appear that Lakeshire is under attack! We are losing citizens left and right. Our own guards are spread far too thin to handle the situation. We need a hero to step up!' WHERE `entry`=26761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That was a nice bit of work, $N. With our constructs back up and running behind their main lines, it\'s only a matter of time now before we make the big push through and rescue the Stonefather.' WHERE `entry`=26762;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These will work fine. Just a moment please. All fixed!' WHERE `entry`=26763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s fixed!  This is great, now I can get dinner started!  Thanks so much, $N. I hope Krazek didn\'t give you too much trouble.' WHERE `entry`=26765;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That should be enough to lure the beast, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s see if the snare can ground something larger than a drake.' WHERE `entry`=26768;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Gazlowe calls this 10%? You tell him I\'m going to weigh these! I suppose he expects me to pay you a delivery fee, as well? Fine, fine. Have some spoils!' WHERE `entry`=26769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A few less stone troggs is always a good thing. Glad to see that you\'re a decent $C after all. We\'ll soon know the exact location where they\'re keeping my father captive. Hope you survive until then.' WHERE `entry`=26770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. Here\'s to hoping the trap performs as well when we try it on Abyssion.' WHERE `entry`=26771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You bring feathers, yes. You can follow directions, yes.' WHERE `entry`=26772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What did Priestess tell you? The raptor is daughter of Ohgan, heir to Mandokir\'s seat. Hah!' WHERE `entry`=26773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Speak with Chiyu',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Escape from Zul\'Gurub' WHERE `entry`=26775;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' It would seem that Jin\'do has survived, and he is rallying his brothers to once again summon Hakkar into this world. It was good of you to come to speak with me. There is not much we can do now but to wait, and watch. Jin\'do is weak, and prime for striking, but I must wait for word from Rastakhan before issuing orders. Until then, you and your raptor will have to wait.' WHERE `entry`=26776;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have brought peace to those who knew only misery, $N. Be proud.' WHERE `entry`=26777;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The cries grow softer for now. Light bless you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26778;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As promised, your reward. You do the troll nation proud.' WHERE `entry`=26779;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can see the difference already. I can\'t wait until later tonight, when I get to perform my observations again!' WHERE `entry`=26780;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You retrieved the eye!  Your might is the stuff of legends, $N! And to think my brother and sister said we wouldn\'t find anything of worth here in the Vale. Hah!  And I\'m just getting started!' WHERE `entry`=26781;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This... this is not like what I expected. I had thought it would be a... a... Ahem!  I\'m sorry. I\'m not sure what came over me. I\'ll be sending this south, to the Explorers\' League Digsite in the Cape. Maybe they\'ll know what to do with it...' WHERE `entry`=26782;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This... this is not like what I expected. I had thought it would be a... a... Ahem!  I\'m sorry. I\'m not sure what came over me. I\'ll be sending this south, to the Explorers\' League Digsite in the Cape. Maybe they\'ll know what to do with it...' WHERE `entry`=26783;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are perfect! The restless waters of that troubled river will now do much more than move silt or stone... They\'ll move you across continents. Finish up the rest of your business here in Dragonmaw and then we should be able to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=26784;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Tobias is staying in town still? Master Harris warned him not to pursue his brother\'s fate. We all lead new lives now, after all. But the past is hard to let go of...' WHERE `entry`=26785;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Something troubles me, $N. The twilight dragons knew just where and when to strike our airfleet. It\'s as if they knew our plans.$B$BTwilight spies cower within our midst!$B$BI\'m going to take one of our remaining ships back to Orgrimmar to roll some heads. I need you to stay behind and secure this front. The Dragonmaw shaman are powerful; I have asked them to open up a portal to Orgrimmar, and I need you to help.$B$BSo. Start helping!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your Warchief is decisive, $N. He makes things happen. I like him. Let\'s talk about this portal that he wants!' WHERE `entry`=26786;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you! Oh, thank you. I never thought I\'d be happy to smell those brains, but I am now that I didn\'t have to get them! Here\'s your reward as promised...' WHERE `entry`=26787;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Now that\'s the stuff! I\'ll start mixing and diluting this with gravel and water. Just a few handfuls of this can enhance enough cement for an entire stone tower. We\'ve got big plans for this port, $N. You\'ll see!' WHERE `entry`=26788;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Name>, we have a problem! I\'ve tracked down the demon-hound Magmadar to this clearing, but when we resting a band of kobolds took our battle axes! I need you to retrieve them, lest Magmadar catch us off guard! Hurry, he could awaken at any moment!' WHERE `entry`=26789;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They won\'t have any more of those fungal giants to throw against us!' WHERE `entry`=26791;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. We\'ve never had such a problem in Deepholm before the destruction of the World Pillar. Your Earthen Ring must repair the damage before it\'s too late.' WHERE `entry`=26792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Morgan Ladimore?$B$BAhh, yes, of course. His was a long and sorrowful tale. I knew him, well, before he left for the war, but that was the last time I saw him. A noble and good man, he was, but he suffered a bad end.$B$BHere, I should have something here that can tell the tale better than my own recollections...' WHERE `entry`=26793;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Morgan Ladimore? Never heard of... Oh, you mean Mor\'Ladim! I guess you haven\'t heard the story? Well, I\'ll give you the short version. A powerful undead calling itself Mor\'Ladim has been wandering Duskwood. From what we\'ve gathered, it appears to be the undead body of Morgan Ladimore, of whom you apparently know. He\'s been causing us all sorts of problems, attacking Watchmen on patrol and killing people. You seem to be capable enough, maybe you could lay him to rest.' WHERE `entry`=26794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You killed him? That\'s no small accomplishment, $N! On behalf of the people of Darkshire and the Night Watch, I thank you.$B$BAh... there is one small matter, however...' WHERE `entry`=26795;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes? My father... I wish... there was something I could have done for him... If only I had talked to him before he...' WHERE `entry`=26796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is...? Sarah? Could it be she\'s still alive? The weight is removed from my shoulders... $N. Take my sword, Archeus. As my soul is put to rest, I have no more need for it. It was forged to do good, and though I have proved myself unworthy to hold it, perhaps you will carry on the Light through it. Lys, my love...' WHERE `entry`=26797;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The portal is ready!$B$BIt\'s not powerful enough to transport an army, but we can maintain the connection long enough to allow important individuals to pass back and forth.$B$BThe Warchief will want to know about our progress here. Walk through the portal to Orgrimmar, then deliver the news to Garrosh Hellscream.',`objectives_loc1`='Use the portal in Dragonmaw Port to go to Orgrimmar and report to Garrosh Hellscream.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='$C, you\'ve returned from Dragonmaw. The portal is functioning then? Good. Before you return to your work there, we\'ve got some dirty business to clean up right here in Orgrimmar...' WHERE `entry`=26798;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not even the power of the val\'kyr was enough to save these creatures. They were doomed from the beginning. I have obtained some equipment for you, $N. It\'s not much, but it will help. Please, take your pick.' WHERE `entry`=26799;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work $N. I knew you weren\'t useless. Here, take one of these. We deathguards have piles of these things just sitting around.' WHERE `entry`=26800;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re growing in strength, $N. I\'ve seen your type before. You will be moving out of Deathknell and on to greater things before long. Just make sure you don\'t lose sight of where you started. You have much to accomplish, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26801;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. This armor should help you out.$B$BHopefully, it should do you more good than the last one to wear it...' WHERE `entry`=26802;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Garrosh is brash and speaks harshly, but his intentions are good. In time, he will grow to see your people as a valuable ally.$B$BI am awaiting reports about recent Alliance activity in Durotar, but they haven\'t arrived yet. Would you be willing to visit Razor Hill and ask him for the reports in person? The easiest way to get there is by wind rider. Doras, Orgrimmar\'s wind rider master will let you use one of his wind riders for a small fee. Look for him on the rise north of the Valley of Strength.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you need to get to Razor Hill in a hurry? That\'s no problem at all. One of my wind riders will get you there very quickly and it only costs a few coins to hire one.' WHERE `entry`=26803;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Eitrigg sent you? The warchief must be getting anxious to read my reports. I\'d\'ve sent them long ago, but each day we discover more about the Alliance\'s plans for invading Durotar.' WHERE `entry`=26804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wulfred has a good eye. I think you\'ll do just fine here at my camp.' WHERE `entry`=26805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ready to return to Orgrimmar with those reports? I can arrange a flight for you right away.' WHERE `entry`=26806;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' The Alliance has grown bolder than we\'d thought! I\'ll talk to the warchief about sending reinforcements right away. Thank you for getting these reports to me so quickly. I hope this coin is enough to cover your travel expenses.' WHERE `entry`=26807;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You have my thanks. You may tell your young dwarven friend that I am not sad. I am waiting. For you. I have identified you as the most promising $R here in this strange town. I have a task for you, if you would be willing to take it.' WHERE `entry`=26808;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is as I suspected. Zanzil is too haughty to interfere with the squabbles between the Bloodscalps and the Skullsplitters. No, he is playing a part in a grander scheme... Jin\'do the Hexxer is using him to help bring Hakkar back to Zul\'Gurub. It\'s good that we found this out now, because it offers us a simple solution.' WHERE `entry`=26809;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I ask you to slay Zanzil the Outcast, a lowly, hermetic exile of the Gurubashi, and what do you do?  You dash headfirst into the Gurubashi capital and eliminate one of their High Priests!  Very nearly two!  Only one word suffices to explain such a rash and foolhardy endeavor: Heroism. Jin\'do the Hexxer still walks within Zul\'Gurub\'s walls, but he lost one of his legs when you crushed Jeklik. Today\'s battle is ours.' WHERE `entry`=26814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This mixture is... PERFECT!  Let\'s see what it does to your potentially-titan artifact here!' WHERE `entry`=26815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is fascinating!  Just think of all the applications! Thanks again, $N. Remember, if you ever need anything mixed for you... and I mean ANYTHING... you can always ask The Flask.' WHERE `entry`=26816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do you know how hard it is to get fresh water in Stranglethorn?  It\'s no wonder that the nagas guard their shrine so ferociously! Alright, let\'s get this mix started!' WHERE `entry`=26817;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' These are so nice and cushy!  I think my customers are going to LOVE them!' WHERE `entry`=26818;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hooray!  It\'s been days and days since we last had Akiris reeds!' WHERE `entry`=26819;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These statues are beautiful... Wow, I had no idea the naga were so talented. Thanks, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26820;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fascinating! I\'ll need some time to study this. Why don\'t you have a look around Booty Bay and come back later?' WHERE `entry`=26821;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahem!  Ahhh... right... Well done!  And, congratulations, on killing them, I mean. Here you go.' WHERE `entry`=26822;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Alright!  Step one - getting ingredients - is all done. Time for the next step: getting more ingredients.' WHERE `entry`=26823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew that alchemist was all talk. Well, thanks for your help, $N. I know you tried.' WHERE `entry`=26824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Hey - you must be that $G fella\': lass; that Wulfred was talkin\' about!  The one who found the ogre artifact, and helped him test out those strange stones from up north. Welcome to the digsite, $N!$B$BWe were actually working on identifying those samples right as you got here. Would you mind bringing the sample over to Dask?  I need him to help me find out how old it is.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring the Opened Mosh\'Ogg Bounty to Dask "The Flask" Gobfizzle at the Explorers\' League Digsite in the Cape of Stranglethorn.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So once again, it falls upon tiny Dask to get the Explorers\' League work done!  Alright... let\'s see what you\'ve got in there.' WHERE `entry`=26825;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Hey - you must be that $G fella\': lass; that Wulfred was talkin\' about!  Welcome to the digsite, $N.$B$BWe were actually just starting a project when you arrived. Would you mind bringing this sample over to Dask?  I need him to help me find out how old it is.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring the Opened Mosh\'Ogg Bounty to Dask "The Flask" Gobfizzle at the Explorers\' League Digsite in the Cape of Stranglethorn.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So once again, it falls upon tiny Dask to get the Explorers\' League work done!  Alright... let\'s see what you\'ve got in there.' WHERE `entry`=26826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done what I thought not possible. Quite impressive, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26827;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And so you arrive, fleshling. As promised.' WHERE `entry`=26828;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Their blood upon the earth is a sweet thing. I shall cherish every moment, slowly extinguishing the stragglers from my realm.' WHERE `entry`=26829;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I haven\'t given up my search for the Twilight\'s Hammer agents that lurk here in Orgrimmar. I need someone I can trust to collect the final evidence of treachery.$B$B<Hellscream pulls you aside.>$B$BSauranok the Mystic - my own most trusted advisor! - is under suspicion. Uncover the truth, $N, and you\'ll be rewarded.$B$BI understand Twilight\'s Hammer has infiltrated workers at the airship docks, to spread their lies all over the continent. Question them. If you discover Sauranok\'s guilt... Kill him.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sauranok, Sauranok. His own visions worked against him. Twilight\'s Hammer probably corrupted him from afar. Bah! Weak! We\'ll speak his name no more. I told him you were investigating the airship docks, $N. To flush him out. Yes, I used you as bait. You served your Horde well, and deserve a reward for outing this viper from our midst.' WHERE `entry`=26830;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good that you were here. I find my size to be inhibiting when it comes to dragon riding, strangely.' WHERE `entry`=26831;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You let Lorthuna escape? I warned you of this. Still, their forces are shattered and their resources cut off. There is little they can do to me or my allies.' WHERE `entry`=26832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gorsik has arrived. All of the pieces of the World Pillar are here, thanks to you. What you have done for us is immeasurable. These final moments shall be the most crucial. I hesitate to ask more of you, but I\'d like you to stay with us and see this through. The Twilight\'s Hammer was devastated by your attacks, but not destroyed. It\'s no stretch to assume they will try to stop us from completing our ritual.' WHERE `entry`=26833;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you again, $N. Now we\'ll get somewhere.' WHERE `entry`=26834;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, we have good news and a slight problem....' WHERE `entry`=26835;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! You did it! How will we ever repay you?' WHERE `entry`=26836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to our camp, $C. You couldn\'t have arrived at a better time.' WHERE `entry`=26838;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! I trust Orgrimmar fares well? As you can see, construction of Dragonmaw Port continues at a breakneck pace. If my people questioned the Horde\'s power before... the sight of this imposing edifice and the speed in which it was constructed leaves no doubt. A new day dawns for the Dragonmaw.' WHERE `entry`=26840;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will be your mentor and guide for now. It is my duty to teach you the arcane arts and how you might best fit in among our people. As you learn and grow in power, you will learn an immense variety of spells that should allow you to deal with nearly any situation. But until then, return to me as often as you like and I will teach you what I can in the ways of our kind.' WHERE `entry`=26841;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nicely done, $Glad:lass;. I could use a $C like you around here.' WHERE `entry`=26842;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So I was right! Now the question is what the little freaks were plotting...' WHERE `entry`=26843;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. Now we can see what\'s going on down in that mine.' WHERE `entry`=26844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a gnoll head. Are you trying to pull some funny business, $N?$B$BIf you\'re not, I\'ve not the faintest idea what\'s going on here.' WHERE `entry`=26845;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m sure that only worked because the troggs aren\'t bright to begin with. But then again, us dwarves were once creatures of the earth as well.$B$BBeing bossed around by a kobold doesn\'t sound quite dignified, and I\'m glad we didn\'t get to find out if they could pull that off.' WHERE `entry`=26846;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The king has moved south, just past Stonehearth, to the Quaking Fields.$B$BGood luck in retrieving the middle fragment of the World Pillar, but beware the giants and other creatures of the field, $N.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with King Oremantle at the Quaking Fields in Deepholm.' WHERE `entry`=26847;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The emerald colossi need to be removed from the field. It\'s conceivable that one of them has the fragment. Regardless, Therzane has moved her forces too close to Stonehearth and they pose a threat.$B$BSunder the giants with my axe. That should bring them down to a more manageable size so that you can finish them off.' WHERE `entry`=26849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We\'ll need to perform a ritual to pinpoint where the World Pillar fragment\'s been taken.$B$BGo out into the field and collect elemental ore from the ragers. With enough of it, I should be able to make you one with the ground to learn what we need.' WHERE `entry`=26850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I know a ritual of the earth that will make you one with the ground. Because I have already handled the fragment, the spirits of the ground will take you near to it.$B$BKeep your mind focused on the World Pillar and let me know when you are ready, $N.',`objectives_loc1`='Through the One With the Ground ritual, discover the location of the Middle Fragment of the World Pillar.' WHERE `entry`=26851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Fly. Fly as fast as you can, $N!$B$BGet the middle fragment back to the Temple of Earth in the middle of Deepholm!',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver the Middle Fragment of the World Pillar to Earthcaller Yevaa at the Temple of Earth in Deepholm.' WHERE `entry`=26853;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Here is the corpse of a dwarf -- mauled, frozen, and picked clean by mountain scavengers. Clutched in its hand is a book containing the roughly scribbled notes of Mori Hildelve. And around its frame, still in superior condition, is a Brigadier\'s Vest.$B$BThis grisly scene must have been where the Siege Engine pilot met his end.' WHERE `entry`=26854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is grim news, for Hildelve was a good friend. And I wish I could have been there with you when you found the beast, Mangeclaw!$B$BThank you, $N. Your deed will be remembered by the pilots of the Ironforge Siege Brigade.' WHERE `entry`=26855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it, $N! You\'ve upturned the Searing Blade\'s invasion before it could even start! Take this, as a token of my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=26856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That ought to get the dragon\'s attention, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My children will sing songs of your glories, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26858;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Much obliged! The rump\'s part of my own secret twist on the recipe... but here\'s instructions on how to make it with any kind of bear meat.$B$BAnd here\'s a fresh batch of me own. Mind you eat them fresh!' WHERE `entry`=26860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. When we make our move against Abyssion, we should be able to do so without reinforcements coming to his aid.' WHERE `entry`=26861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. The Molten Elementals\' spirits are finally back to rest.' WHERE `entry`=26862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did you see a lot of kobolds in there? The thought of their grimy hands clawing around our mine makes my stomach rumble!' WHERE `entry`=26863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gnolls and kobolds, and troggs? Oh my.$B$BI\'d laugh if I didn\'t have another twist in the story for you.' WHERE `entry`=26864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve been expecting your arrival, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve been expecting your arrival, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve been expecting your arrival, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Worked like a charm, didn\'t it? Maybe Kadrell will get off my darn back now what with savin\' the whole town and all!$B$BI suppose you\'ve done earned yourself some proper goods.' WHERE `entry`=26868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<This is it. This is the stone Diamant sent you for.>' WHERE `entry`=26869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can already feel the balance returning! Quick, talk to Muyoh to help him awaken Naralex!' WHERE `entry`=26870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, fleshling!$B$BThe gyreworms are among our most dangerous enemies.$B$BThe other Stone Lords shall have trouble not turning their head to this accomplishment.' WHERE `entry`=26871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your efforts shall not go unnoticed, $N. Thank you for your dedication.' WHERE `entry`=26872;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $N. Hopefully we can use these to prevent further nightmares.' WHERE `entry`=26873;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Twilight forces continue to stream in, but it looks like the Earthen Ring defenders can handle them.' WHERE `entry`=26875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your efforts in repairing the World Pillar are invaluable, $N. Once the Temple of Earth\'s structure is stable again, the rift between the worlds will begin to stabilize.' WHERE `entry`=26876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, $C? What brings you to this place?' WHERE `entry`=26878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='There\'s something sinister going on within this place, $N. We fear that the rumors of the Naga working with the Twilight\'s Hammer are true.$B$BI sent Thaelrid, one of our best scouts, further in to investigate the matter, but he hasn\'t returned.$B$BSeek him out. If he\'s still alive, find out all that he\'s learned.',`objectives_loc1`='Seek out Scout Thaelrid.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ashelan was good to send you. There is indeed a wicked plot underway in this corrupted place.' WHERE `entry`=26881;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Kelris has eluded us for quite some time.$B$BIt seems as though whenever evil made its presence known in these parts, Kelris had played a role. For some time we considered him either dead or missing.$B$BBut this makes perfect sense. By ending his reign you have spared the lives of many innocent people.$B$BTo sacrifice someone to a servant of an Old God for one\'s personal gain is beyond reproachful!$B$BYou have done a great deed, $N. I thank you on behalf of Ashenvale.$B$BIf only Thaelrid had survived....' WHERE `entry`=26882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Obtain 10 Twilight Pendants.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are no doubt of brave and noble blood, $N. We and all of the people of Ashenvale commend you for your efforts against evil.' WHERE `entry`=26883;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have undoubtedly faced great peril to obtain these.$B$BYour actions have been selfless. It is for the good of all Azeroth that you help me with my research. I thank you, $N, for all that you have done.$B$BNow if you\'ll excuse me I have much work to do.' WHERE `entry`=26884;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found the manuscript! What a joyous day this is! I will study it exhaustively and learn all there is to know.$B$BI\'ll make full sentinel yet!$B$BYour service to us is more than you know, $N. I hope that this gift shows you my gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=26885;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful! I hope you didn\'t get hit with too many cannonballs.' WHERE `entry`=26886;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I know we\'re here to make friends with the Steamwheedle goblins, but those awful Bilgewater goblins are so rude$B$BWhy, I just saw a bunch of them pulling gold fillings out of the teeth of the Southsea musketeers and strongarms. Do they think they can just take that for themselves?$B$BObviously, the nice thing to do is kill those pirates ourselves, take their fillings ourselves, and then give some of them to the Steamwheedle as a thank-you gift! Head on down there and beat those goblins to the punch.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='More gold! We\'ll be sure to give some of this to Mister Noggenfogger to smoothly ensure our continued relations. And only a little bit of it will go back to Gnomeregan for experimental weapons development!' WHERE `entry`=26887;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The beast is slain. I can feel his dark presence fading away forever.' WHERE `entry`=26888;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You know, I\'m usually not impressed when I see a $R, but I\'ve heard about what you\'ve been doin\' for the Steamwheedle. You\'re alright, kid.' WHERE `entry`=26889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! These will do nicely. Here\'s a reward for your hard work.' WHERE `entry`=26890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is exactly what I need! A fathom core is an incredible well of information that we will be able to draw much good from. Whatever the Twilight\'s Hammer is up to in there - and believe me when I say it is no good - my comrades and I will now uncover.$B$BYou\'ve done well here today; the Earthen Ring looks upon you warmly for assisting us. You\'ve also helped the Horde as a whole, and for that you should be proud.' WHERE `entry`=26891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can hear their cries from here! Maybe this will show them how foolish it is to wish for the return of an Old God.' WHERE `entry`=26892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='There\'s a task to be done that you\'re perfect for, $C. We need to secure the area around Blackfathom Deeps to help with that Alliance that are threatening Zoram\'gar Outpost west of here.$B$BGo to Blackfathom Deeps, north of Zoram\'gar Outpost, and speak with Je\'neu of the Earthen Ring. He will have plenty for you to do.' WHERE `entry`=26893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Naga mock us with their defiance. We will drive them and their allies out of this land for good.$B$BTravel north of here to Blackfathom Deeps and speak with Je\'neu Sancrea. He\'s already made his way inside.$B$BBe wary of Zeya, by the way. She can be a bit...temperamental at times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did Commander Grimfang send you? I\'ve asked him to find suitable recruits to aid me here.' WHERE `entry`=26894;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Another proud $C, lured by the promise of fame! Of wealth! Of VIOLENCE! Yes, welcome, friend. Welcome... to THUNDERDROME!' WHERE `entry`=26895;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Another proud $C, lured by the promise of fame! Of wealth! Of VIOLENCE! Yes, welcome, friend. Welcome... to THUNDERDROME!' WHERE `entry`=26896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Although our position is exposed, we are safe compared to our friends inside Blackfathom Deeps! They stand mere feet away from the most deadly Naga forces in the area. Speak with Sentinel Aluwyn and give them the aid they desperately need!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank Elune you\'re here! We could use all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=26897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank Elune you\'re here! We could use all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=26898;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I spare your life for your help, $R. Leave now...before I change my...mind.' WHERE `entry`=26899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! This is just what we need, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks again, friend! I told you I\'d make it worth your while.' WHERE `entry`=26903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Few people, especially among our allies, truly understand the nature of the power we wield. They shun us for pursuing knowledge that they are too weak to use properly.$B$BLet me show you a conjuration that I find handy. This spell, called Immolate, sets your target aflame, causing damage immediately and over time. Use it well, $N, and your enemies will come to fear you.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Saripal Smolderbrew and learn Immolate, then cast Immolate 5 times on a Training Dummy near the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='As you continue to gain power, return to me and I will teach you new spells and techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Take this gift. You have earned my blessing this day.' WHERE `entry`=26905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'ve been waiting for you to come here.' WHERE `entry`=26906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Overlord Ramtusk and the Death\'s Head mobilize for war. It took many scouts\' lives, but we have learned of the weapon they intend to use to overtake the rest of the Barrens.$B$BIt is known as Agathelos the Raging, an immense boar outfitted with heavy armor and force-fed the rage-inducing Kraul bat guano.$B$B$R, you must stop them before they take innocent lives!',`objectives_loc1`='Kill Aggem Thorncurse, Death Speaker Jargba, Overlord Ramtusk, and Agathelos the Raging.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well this day. Agathelos would have taken many lives in its fury.' WHERE `entry`=26907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Only a veteran like you could brave the dangers lurking here.' WHERE `entry`=26908;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Help...' WHERE `entry`=26909;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you received my note? Excellent. You\'ve proven yourself quite capable in dealing with those orcs. As you continue to grow in power, I will teach you some new techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I know, $N. I should not have sent you. Forgive me... the whispers of the past are sometimes too strong.' WHERE `entry`=26911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As the eldritch shackles are placed around the Shards, an unhuman wail is heard from far below. The scream is followed by a roar.$B$BThe Shards of Myzrael no longer invoke feelings of warmth and security as they once did. Now they pulse with an open menace... as if the thing beneath them holds ill will toward the surface.' WHERE `entry`=26912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that you\'ve had the chance to test your abilities in battle, it\'s time to show you a new combat technique -- charge. As a warrior, it\'s important to use every advantage at your disposal to get the upper hand in battle.$B$BWhat better way to do that than by charging into battle and stunning your opponent? I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Llane Bershere and purchase the Charge ability, then practice using Charge on a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re a quick learner, $N. Return to me as you grow stronger and I\'ll show you other combat techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We must take care in how we speak around the abbey and its environs, but don\'t let that deter you from the path of power.$B$BI want to show you one of my favorite spells. It will allow you to set an opponent on fire, damaging the enemy immediately and continuing to do more harm over time. I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Drusilla La Salle and purchase the Immolate ability, then practice casting Immolate 5 times on a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you have already mastered Immolation! I look forward to instructing you in the future. Do not forget to return for further lessons as you grow in power.' WHERE `entry`=26914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By now, you know the basics of combat as rogue, but I want to teach you a new skill. As rogues, we are renowned for our ability to execute chains of combat techniques, often saving the most powerful strikes for the end.$B$BLet me show you the basics of Eviscerate. After using Sinister Strike a few times, you can attack with Eviscerate to hit your opponent even harder. I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Jorik Kerridan and purchase the Eviscerate ability, then find a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey and practice Eviscerate 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve caught on quickly, $N, and a quick mind will serve you well. Return to me as you grow in power and I will show you new techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='As a mage, you will learn a variety of spells as your understanding grows. I want to show you a new technique that allows you to launch volleys of arcane energy at your opponent, Arcane Missiles. You won\'t be able to cast this spell all the time, but each time you cast another spell, there\'s a chance you\'ll create an opening to use Arcane Missiles. I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Khelden Bremen and purchase the Arcane Missiles ability, then practice casting Arcane Missiles 2 times on a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you mastered the use of Arcane Missiles already? You are a quick study in the arcane arts and you have a promising future ahead. Don\'t forget to return to me for training as you grow in power.' WHERE `entry`=26916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'ve heard about your help in clearing out some of the orcs. You\'ve shown that you can handle yourself in combat.$B$BI want to show you a new skill. I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Ashley Blank and purchase the Steady Shot ability, then find a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew you would master Steady Shot quickly. I\'m looking forward to showing you other techniques as you get more experienced in the ways of the $C.' WHERE `entry`=26917;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I want to teach you a couple of techniques for using the Light\'s power to boost your combat skills.$B$BThe first technique is applying the Seal of Righteousness. While under the effects of the seal, all of your melee attacks will inflict additional holy damage.$B$BThe second ability, Judgement, can be use periodically to unleash the seal\'s power and inflict damage.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Brother Sammuel and purchase the Seal of Righteousness and Judgement abilities. Cast Seal of Righteousness on yourself and then use Judgement on a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re a quick learner, $N. Return to me as you grow stronger and I\'ll teach you more about using the Light to vanquish your enemies and strengthen your allies.' WHERE `entry`=26918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='One of your responsibilities as a priest is caring for the wounded. With the power of the Light, you can save those who would otherwise die and speed the healing of wounds.$B$BI want to teach you a simple, quick technique you can use to heal an ally quickly.$B$B I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to use this spell to treat the injuries of wounded trainees around the abbey.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Priestess Anetta and purchase the Flash Heal ability, then use Flash Heal 5 times to treat Wounded Trainees inside Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re a quick learner, $N, and the wounded are fortunate to have your aid. Return to me as you grow stronger and I\'ll teach you other spells.' WHERE `entry`=26919;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time you arrived, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You may not act quickly, but at least you do not fail me. Very well. I will have a more important task for you, $N, when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These grenades are all explosives, nothing more. Even as a member of the Royal Apothecary Society, I recognize that some problems are not solved by throwing more plague at them.' WHERE `entry`=26922;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the behemoths out of the way, our victory against the Scourge is inevitable. Our current chances against the Alliance aren\'t quite as favorable... but that\'s no concern of yours. Not yet, anyhow.' WHERE `entry`=26923;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellently done, $N. And now, with the leader of the Scourge forces eliminated from Andorhal, we bide our time.' WHERE `entry`=26924;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Araj dead... this is good. The Royal Apothecary Society has done its part. As have you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26925;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Word arrived shortly before you did, $N. With the Scourge ejected from Andorhal, the Forsaken has cemented its foothold in Lordaeron.' WHERE `entry`=26926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Murlocs? Sure, I\'ve hunted murlocs.$B$BAnd every single stinkin\' one of them deserved what they got! You hear me?' WHERE `entry`=26927;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Phew! Ain\'t that a stench.$B$BNow you prepare yourself, because I\'m about to wow you with what\'s left of my mental faculties.' WHERE `entry`=26928;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mighty kind of you to help out an ol\' fool like me. Here\'s your reward as promised an\' all.' WHERE `entry`=26929;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Burning bodies?  No survivors?  I guessed correctly. All the better!  We\'re better off without the Scarlet taint upon Lordaeron. They epitomized all the worst things about humans.' WHERE `entry`=26930;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s a relief to have those hunters out of the way. We\'re not done killing Alliance, however...' WHERE `entry`=26931;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That should help prevent disease and illness from spreading into our remaining water. Many thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26932;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ha ha!  I hope that they come back as zombies.' WHERE `entry`=26933;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glorious!  This is the last bit I need. Actually, stick around, $N. Let me tell you a little bit more about our plan.' WHERE `entry`=26934;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Northridge, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26935;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am able to communicate with you through the Val\'kyr, $N. You have done well. Remain on Felstone Field. We must now teach these newly-converted Forsaken how to fight.' WHERE `entry`=26937;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='When Koltira gives his word, I will bring these val\'kyr into Andorhal. We will win. And yet another piece of Lordaeron will fall to the might of the Forsaken.' WHERE `entry`=26938;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope that wasn\'t too much for you. The mission is far from over!' WHERE `entry`=26939;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We are the heirs to a legacy of arcane magic and your path will not be an easy one. Many still hold us responsible for the actions of our forebears, but our talents are needed.$B$BI want to show you a new spell, Arcane Missiles. It allows you to fire volleys of arcane energy, but you won\'t be able to cast it all the time. Casting other spells has a chance to create an opportunity for you to use Arcane Missiles.$B$BI want you try it. Look for a training dummy near the southeastern edge of Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Rhyanda. Look for a Training Dummy near, and practice using Arcane Missiles twice.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew you would master this lesson quickly. You are a credit to the highborn and to all our kin. Remember, as you grow in power, return to me and will instruct you further.' WHERE `entry`=26940;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Took you long enough. Get behind the pillar with me before you blow our cover!' WHERE `entry`=26941;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'d love for you to come aboard as a full G-Team Commando, but you have other adventures to pursue. I\'m sure we\'ll meet again, and I hope you\'ll have considered joining by then. Here\'s something for your trouble.' WHERE `entry`=26942;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I used t\' have quite the home back in Ironforge. That is, I did until I was booted out to make way for the Gnomes.$B$BThey couldn\'t stop a bunch of troggs with all them gizmos and machines! An\' I have to pay for their weakness?$B$BNo, sir. No longer.$B$BGo to Gnomeregan and talk to Commando Murd Doc. Sure, he\'s a Gnome, but his crew, S.A.F.E. I think they call \'em, are going to take Gnomeregan back.$B$BGo! I want my house back!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Never thought I\'d see a $R like you down here. Any particular reason you\'re risking life and limb?' WHERE `entry`=26943;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Gnomish capital, Gnomeregan, hasn\'t been under their control for some time now. I know what it feels like to lose a home.$B$BPlease, venture inside Gnomeregan and speak to Commando Murd Doc, a member of S.A.F.E. If there\'s anything at all that you can do to help them take their home, I urge you to do so. There are dark secrets in those halls.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Never thought I\'d see a $R like you down here. Any particular reason you\'re risking life and limb?' WHERE `entry`=26944;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='There\'s no better time to get the upper hand in battle than at the start. Let me teach you a technique for charging into battle and stunning your opponent.$B$BI want you try it. Look for a training dummy near the southeastern edge of Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Charge from Alyissia. Look for a Training Dummy near, and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve proven a capable student. When it is time to resume your training, return to me and I will show you other techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26945;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m certain that by now, you\'ve mastered using Sinister Strike against your enemies, but I want to show you a technique you can use to follow a successful series of Sinister Strikes. It\'s called Eviscerate and it can be a strong way to end a combination of attacks.$B$BI want you try it. Look for a training dummy near the southeastern edge of Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Eviscerate from Frahun Shadewhisper. Look for a Training Dummy southeast of Aldrassil and practice using Eviscerate 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve learned quickly. If you are as sharp as you seem to be, you may prove to be one of my best students yet. Return to me when you are in need of further training.' WHERE `entry`=26946;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='When most people think of the kaldorei, they conjure visions of druids and sentinels, but the way of the hunter is just as ancient and just as venerable.$B$BI\'ve been observing you, and you\'ve had quite a bit of experience handling that bow. I want to show you a shooting technique that I often use in combat.$B$BI want you try it. Look for a training dummy near the southeastern edge of Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Steady Shot from Ayanna Everstride. Look for a Training Dummy southeast of Aldrassil, and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a quick study in our ways. I look forward to continuing your training in the future. Return to me when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26947;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Druids play an important role in our society, but all too often we are seen as passive dreamers in a world that is changing around us. I want to teach you a basic healing technique and with it, I want you to go out in the world and aid the ailing and the fallen.$B$BUse your new knowledge to heal the wounds of sentinels who have been injured defending Shadowglen.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Rejuvenation from Mardant Strongoak. Use Rejuvenation to treat a Wounded Sentinel in Aldrassil.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have mastered the basics of the healing ways quickly, $N. I have no doubt that your healing skills will often come in handy. Return to me when you need further training.' WHERE `entry`=26948;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='As a priest, you will often be called upon to heal the wounds of injured comrades. I want to teach you a basic healing technique and with it, you will be able to ease the suffering of the wounded and hasten their recovery.$B$BUse your new knowledge to heal the injured sentinels recovering within Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Flash Heal from Shanda. Use Flash Heal 5 times to treat the Wounded Sentinels in Aldrassil.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You will find no lack of allies in need of healing. Return to me when you need further training.' WHERE `entry`=26949;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What do you mean Thalnos was an undead? That\'s impossible. This is a holy place, the Scarlet Crusade would never allow... Take this as a reward, and get some rest. The crypts must have gotten the best of your nerves.' WHERE `entry`=26950;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks, $C. The spirits can rest now. As long as we show them respect they will bless us and our new home for a long time. Spirits be with you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26951;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $C. As you can see, our camp is a joint expedition between Argent Crusade members and Cenarion Circle druids, but we welcome all who wish to help heal the land.' WHERE `entry`=26952;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It looks like Zen\'Kiki is still having a little bit of trouble with his shapeshifting.' WHERE `entry`=26953;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now we\'re getting somewhere. How many birds did Zen\'Kiki end up killing? None?  You killed them all yourself? Alright, I suppose we\'ll have to find another use for him then. I will let you know when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='By the grace of the Earthmother, he\'s done it!  Thank you, $N! I admit, I had nearly given up hope on Zen\'Kiki. It is only due to your patience and diligence that he has come into his own as a druid and member of the Cenarion Circle. And that\'s without even mentioning the good you\'ve done for nature. You have my admiration and respect.' WHERE `entry`=26955;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$R!  I\'m glad someone\'s here to help me out.$B$BWe Cenarion druids have re-cultivated Dalson\'s Farm, immediately behind me. The land has flourished and our crops have been successful... mostly.$B$BA few plants seem to still be infected by the plague that ran through this land. Perhaps their roots were too deep, perhaps the seeds were weak... I cannot say. All I can say is that I need an able $C like you to help me remove the bad plants from the good ones.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for your help, $N. I know that picking vegetables isn\'t the most heroic task imaginable, but even the humblest tasks have their rewards.' WHERE `entry`=26956;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It would appear that I arrived before you, $N. Field Agent Kaartish gave me the details about my old home. It seems my battles with the Scourge aren\'t quite over yet.' WHERE `entry`=26957;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Let\'s start your training right away. I want to teach you a combat technique that you\'ll find useful at the start of battle. By charging your opponent before the fight begins, you can stun the enemy and momentum will be on your side.$B$BI want you to try out this technique using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site. Return to me when you think you\'ve mastered it.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Charge from Kore. Find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Keep that technique handy, $N. I find myself using it all the time. Return when you\'re ready for further training.' WHERE `entry`=26958;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew I could count on you! These fools will never know what hit them.' WHERE `entry`=26959;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent, Anduin will learn a lot by shadowing you. Remember, stay within the city\'s borders. Keep him out of trouble. And above all else, guard him with your life. Anduin, no adventures! Stay close to $N and return to the keep should you see any trouble.' WHERE `entry`=26960;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got them! Nicely done, $N!$B$BAnd you don\'t look too worse for wear, even with those berserk Troggs about. I\'m going to keep my eye on you...you show some promise.' WHERE `entry`=26961;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Herod is slain! The Armory will fall!' WHERE `entry`=26962;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Let\'s start your training right away. It\'s going to be a struggle to survive here, and you\'ll play an important role in making sure our people are safe and well-supplied. I want to show you a shooting technique that I use all the time.$B$BTry out this technique using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site. Return to me when you think you\'ve mastered it.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Steady Shot from Keilnei. Find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Keep that technique handy, $N. I find myself using it all the time. Return when you\'re ready for further training.' WHERE `entry`=26963;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most excellent! A new recruit has arrived. There is much to do... much to do I say.' WHERE `entry`=26964;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well that was unexpected. I am not one to doubt our Warchief, but... Nevermind! We have work to do. I\'m sure the Dark Lady and the Warchief will get this all worked out.' WHERE `entry`=26965;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='As a paladin, you\'re no stranger to the Light that touches all of us. But you also have the unique power to call upon the Light to help you in battle.$B$BWhile under the effects of the Seal of Righteousness, each melee attack will deal extra holy damage. From time to time, you can also use Judgement to unleash your seal\'s power for another attack.$B$BI want you to try out these techniques using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Seal of Righteousness and Judgement from Aurelon. Apply Seal of Righteousness, find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and use Judgement.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve proven yourself a quick learner, $N. I look forward to training you again when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26966;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes! The Scarlet Monastery now belongs to the Forsaken! None can escape our wrath! You\'ve completed your task with the precision of a true champion. Take this as a reward, courtesy of the Banshee Queen.' WHERE `entry`=26967;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='In your future as a mage, you\'ll be expected to master a wide variety of spells. In fact, I want to teach you one right now. It\'s called Arcane Missiles and it allows you to throw volleys of arcane energy at your opponent. However, you won\'t be able to use it all the time. Each time you cast a spell, there\'s a chance you\'ll trigger an opportunity to use the missiles.$B$BI want you to try out this technique using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Valaatu. Find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and practice using Arcane Missiles 2 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve mastered the use of this new spell quickly, $N. I only wish all of my students were as talented. Return to me when you find yourself in need of further training.' WHERE `entry`=26968;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Your walk with the elemental powers will take you to many places. Let us start your journey with a simple, but useful, lesson. I want to teach you to a basic combat technique.$B$BOnce you have completed training, go practice your new skill using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site. Return to me when you are finished.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Primal Strike from Firmanvaar. Find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and practice using Primal Strike 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is a pleasure to teach such a capable student. As long as you continue the traditons faithfully, the shamanic arts will never be lost to our people again. Return to me when you need further training.' WHERE `entry`=26969;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='As a priest, one of your most important duties is to use the Light\'s power to aid the wounded. There are no lack of people here who could use your skills, $N. Allow me to show you a quick, simple heal that you can use to treat any ally.$B$BUse your newfound knowledge to help me treat those wounded in the crash.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Flash Heal from Zalduun. Use Flash Heal 5 times to heal the wounds of Injured Draenei at the Crash Site.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ll often find your skills as a healer in demand, $N. Do not hesitate to return when you need more training.' WHERE `entry`=26970;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Maruut said when all dis started dat he would gladly give his life ta see our task done. He would be proud of dis success... of dis death. Da rift be closed on dis side. Deepholm should calm down a bit. It\'ll be takin\' time for Thrall to mend da wound in Azeroth, and we\'ll be needin\' to remain until he finishes. Thank you for all ya\'ve done. I don\'t tink we could have been accomplishin\' dis so soon without you.' WHERE `entry`=26971;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What do you mean Thalnos was an undead? That\'s impossible. The entire mission of the Scarlet Crusade is to destroy the undead! There\'s just no way... You have muddied my thoughts. Please take this reward for your achievement and leave me to rest.' WHERE `entry`=26972;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work! I just know the Light shines favorably upon us for our work. Our cause is righteous!' WHERE `entry`=26973;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So he\'s really dead? That means...I, Joseph, am the new Scarlet Champion!!! Take this. I don\'t have a need for such possessions anyways! I\'m the Scarlet Champion, after all.' WHERE `entry`=26974;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Please understand your highness, the men are working double-shifts. The scale of your father\'s operation is enormous. But we will endeavor to wrap things up. I give you my word.' WHERE `entry`=26975;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes! The Scarlet Monastery is ours! You\'re a real friend. Take this as a reward, and feel free to visit again once I\'ve taken the Undercity too. It\'ll be a Scarlet Paradise!' WHERE `entry`=26976;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmmm, yes? My investigation of the Twilight\'s Hammer. Of course. Your assistance will be valuable.' WHERE `entry`=26977;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' The drums are placed?  In their positions? Very well then, I will give the word to the High Executor. When the time is ready, he will be the one to press the ignition switch.' WHERE `entry`=26978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Leave Drum inside Ranch House',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Leave Drum inside Barn' WHERE `entry`=26978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N. The Dark Lady watches over you.' WHERE `entry`=26979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Stoutfist sent you, eh? He\'s a good captain, runs his men well. Just wish he\'d stop starin\' at my midriff. Don\'t let me catch you doin\' it either. We\'ve work to take care of here!' WHERE `entry`=26980;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well met, $C. We\'ve got raptor problems for sure... sort of. More like the entire dig site deciding to attack us. I\'ve never seen rocks and fossils get so upset!' WHERE `entry`=26981;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Captain Nials sent you? I haven\'t seen her in ages! How is she? Did she get my letter? Oh, you\'re not here for that. Well then, let\'s get down to business!' WHERE `entry`=26982;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You came here from Southshore, eh? I bet you hunger for revenge against the vile Forsaken that trashed the place. The Scarlet Crusade can help take care of that! Right after you help me realign their misguided souls, that is.' WHERE `entry`=26983;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You look pretty tough, $C. There are wrongs to be righted here. Let\'s get started.' WHERE `entry`=26984;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wait, you were sent here by THE Shandris Feathermoon? I can barely believe my ears! To know that my cause is supported by her massive army... Yes, yes, you will be perfect. You\'re the key to my future!' WHERE `entry`=26985;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Oftentimes the best way to ensure our men sustain as few injuries as possible is to cause great harm to our enemies in their very homes and prevent battles from ever occurring!$B$BTravel to the Scarlet Monastery and speak with Dark Ranger Velonara in their graveyard. She is leading a Forsaken assault there and could benefit from a seasoned $C such as yourself.',`objectives_loc1`='Report to Dark Ranger Velonara.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It looks like Darthalia sent an able $C, as I requested.' WHERE `entry`=26986;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m surprised to see Huntsman Markhor working with me for once. He\'s usually quite stubborn. He does tend to a strong hatred for magic, though. I hope you do, too, $C, because we\'re going to strip the Scarlet Crusade of theirs.' WHERE `entry`=26987;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yayo\'jin is correct, you helping me here will aid her in the Hinterlands as well. All the more reason to get started immediately.' WHERE `entry`=26988;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Holyfiresnub has returned! And in one piece! Defender of Silverpine! Redeemer of the Horde! Holyfiresnub, your bravery must be rewarded!' WHERE `entry`=26989;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sandfury trolls and the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer, you say? And they meant to send some giant monster into the heart of the city?! Well done! Thunder Bluff is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=26990;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nazeer is a strong warrior - his hatred for our enemies rivals my own. You are welcome help to my forces.' WHERE `entry`=26991;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Agony abounds, friend! The land itself threatens to devour us, and yet we persist. I wonder why that is? With this doomweed and the guts and gore that T\'Veen needs, we might have something suitable to send to the Forsaken front.' WHERE `entry`=26992;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. How about I give you a nice reward for your work, and you don\'t tell a soul that you saw me here. Deal?' WHERE `entry`=26993;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good. Yes, very good indeed. Your reward, as promised. No questions.' WHERE `entry`=26994;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! With these guts and the ferocious doomweed we\'ll be able to test out our new strain of blight. Now to select a suitable target...' WHERE `entry`=26995;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This doesn\'t make any sense, $N. Why was Samuelson sending us out here on a wild goose chase? Something doesn\'t feel right. We should poke around on our own...' WHERE `entry`=26997;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Potent enough to exterminate a thousand murlocs! I think I\'ll put that on the label. You\'ve done well, $N, and great work around here gets rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=26998;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This will be more than enough, $N. Now, I will need some time to perform my studies.' WHERE `entry`=26999;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, it sounds like they\'re certainly afraid of the mustang, but they\'re not leaving for good. I can\'t have you running around on a horse forever. Nor do I think you\'d want to. Fine. Bloodshed it is.' WHERE `entry`=27000;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s much more like it!  Now my lumberjacks can get to work again. Nice riding out there, $N. You cut a pretty impressive silhouette on that mustang.' WHERE `entry`=27001;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N. It is truly a pleasure. I know you are young, and still training, but I\'ve had my eye on you. We among the Argent Crusade are always looking for promising new recruits, and you have indeed shown great promise. I have no immediate tasks for you, but merely wished to meet you in person, and see for myself what type of $R you really were. For the time being, the amenities of Hearthglen are yours to enjoy. I look forward to our next meeting, $N. You are dismissed.' WHERE `entry`=27002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Smells like someone else was in this cell recently. Gross!' WHERE `entry`=27003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' But... but, this is just gibberish! What does this even say? What language is that?' WHERE `entry`=27004;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is just gibberish! What does this even say? What language is that?' WHERE `entry`=27005;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A waygate?! The culties dug up a Titan waygate?' WHERE `entry`=27006;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the place. Our scouts confirmed the presence of high-ranking Twilight officers nearby as well as potential trogg hunting parties. Be on the lookout, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27007;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A waygate?! They unearthed a Titan waygate. This is very interesting and potentially very bad.' WHERE `entry`=27008;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A job well done, $N. The Quilboar here can no longer be saved, but at least they are no longer organized for attack, or slaves under Amnennar\'s tyrannic rule. Leave quickly, please. Razorfen Downs is without hope. It must be purged.' WHERE `entry`=27009;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We have the information we need. Let\'s not tip our hand by engaging the enemy too soon.' WHERE `entry`=27010;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll just put this back over in the lumber stores outside. Nathaniel probably won\'t even notice it was missing.' WHERE `entry`=27011;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. I\'ll be throwing these in the fire. We don\'t want those gnolls just sneaking in and stealing them back.' WHERE `entry`=27012;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'m happy for Nathaniel: he\'s spent so long trying to return to Northridge, and now with the Scarlet Crusade out of the way, he can finally move back home. It\'s just... even for such a seemingly-idyllic setting, it\'s not really the best place to raise a family.$B$BFor example: along this valley\'s edge, you will find rabid foxes searching for innocent prey. Every once in a while I catch a glimpse of one looking right at me.$B$BPlease, $C, remove some of these foxes. I don\'t feel safe with them near.',`objectives_loc1`='Kill 12 Rabid Foxes near Northridge Lumber Mill in Western Plaguelands.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I feel a bit more relieved, $N. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27013;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Just a moment ago a messenger was looking for you, $N. I believe she was sent by the priest trainer, Seer Ravenfeather. If this note is from the seer, I would go looking for her immediately.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Seer Ravenfeather in Camp Narache.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have arrived at last. During your training in Camp Narache, I will guide you in the ways of the $C. You have much to learn and I look forward to counting you among my students.' WHERE `entry`=27014;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Just a moment ago a messenger was looking for you, $N. I believe she was sent by the paladin trainer, Sunwalker Helaku. If this note is from the sunwalker, I recommend going to see him immediately.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Sunwalker Helaku in Camp Narache.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We have much to cover. In time, the ways of the sunwalkers will be as plain and natural to you as the shaman\'s conversations with the elements.' WHERE `entry`=27015;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve killed ten already? H...hah! While you were out, I\'ve broken my previous record! To ten... hundred! Yes, ten hundred boars!$B$BA bet is a bet, I suppose... here\'s your consolation prize, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27016;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This... Gloria used to read from this prayer book every night!  How had I forgotten?  She was so devout, $N. Oh... This painting... my daughter, Andrea... she loved to... to paint...' WHERE `entry`=27017;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fantastic, I thought you looked to be the heroic type!  We\'ve got our work cut out for us $N, I\'m not going to lie to you. If we stay focused on the task at hand, we should be able to come out on top.' WHERE `entry`=27019;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The time has come for your first lesson in the ways of the warrior, $N, and a fitting lesson it is. I will teach you a technique for gaining the upper hand at the start of battle.$B$BCharge into the fray, surprising your enemy, and stunning him. After we have completed our lesson, I want you to try it for yourself.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Charge from Harutt Thunderhorn. Locate a Training Dummy in Camp Narache and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $N. Return to me when you are in need of further training.' WHERE `entry`=27020;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It is time for your first lesson, $N. You have a long way to go to master the ways of the hunter, but each new skill is a step on that path. Let me show you a useful shot.$B$BWhen our lesson is concluded, I want you to try it for yourself.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Steady Shot from Lanka Farshot. Locate a Training Dummy in Camp Narache and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $N. Return to me when you are in need of further training.' WHERE `entry`=27021;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Belnistrasz\'s sudden departure has left behind a burning brazier. As you stare in to the flame, the image of a great-winged red dragon fills your mind. A more graveled version of Belnistrasz\'s voice speaks directly to you. "Indeed mortals, you are the heroes I had hoped you would be. Thanks to you the butchery these beasts were perpetrating is a thing of the past. My faith in your kind has been once more renewed. Take this as a reward befitting of a hero."' WHERE `entry`=27022;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! Without their leaders, the Scourge will pose no significant threat.' WHERE `entry`=27024;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve been informed there\'s a bear warning active for the woodlands as well! They love those stabthistle seeds.$B$BIt\'s a good thing you gathered those so they don\'t attract more bears!' WHERE `entry`=27025;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Okay, yes, I have already been informed that bobcats are much smaller than I was assuming. But that\'s still pretty dangerous for gnomes! You\'ve done a good thing for the safety of this lodge, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27026;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I know you\'ve been busy helping the braves protect Camp Narache from the bristlebacks. We\'re going to need all the hammers and all the luck we can get. Allow me to teach you a simple combat technique to help you in battle.$B$BPrimal Strike should help you fell your enemies faster. Try it out for yourself.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Primal Strike from Meela Dawnstrider. Locate a Training Dummy in Camp Narache and practice using Primal Strike 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. I see you will have no trouble mastering our more advanced arts as you gain experience. Return to me when you need further training.' WHERE `entry`=27027;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lovely specimens you\'ve got there! Here\'s my wager, lad.' WHERE `entry`=27028;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have faith that this substance will prevent many future headaches. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27029;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, you see? Goods of the finest quality. Good work gettin\' these.' WHERE `entry`=27030;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Beautiful. you\'ve got an eye for quality!$B$BGreat minds think alike! It\'s clear you\'ve got an enthusiasm for flight and fowl, so maybe you can help me further...' WHERE `entry`=27031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'ve actually nearly perfected my dream machine: The Skystrider! The world\'s first flying Mechanostrider! But, well�$B$BWhen I was putting the finishing touches on it in my secret cavern lab, my other creations became, er, jealous. Giving mechanical birds a personality to begin with was probably a bad idea, but that\'s already done.$B$BI need the Supermechanical Robo-Widget from the original Skystrider if I want to rebuild it! Please, journey into the cave and retrieve it for me!' WHERE `entry`=27032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect! Now that I\'ve perfected the wing balance and have all the parts I need, all we need is a pilot.' WHERE `entry`=27033;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I don\'t care about my father and his silly inventions! It\'s all just nonsense!' WHERE `entry`=27034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it? You did! You fought them and won! There\'s hope after all...' WHERE `entry`=27035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Er... what\'s this? A bear\'s head, by the looks at it. Well, that\'s quite an interesting kill you have yourself there. Couldn\'t be that bear from back then... Oh, take that away take it away! Get that grisly thing out of here!' WHERE `entry`=27036;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for helping me out with my little plan, $N. I\'ve been itching for months to get back at that snooty, stuck-up boy, and I\'d say we did a pretty good job! Here, have this, you\'ve earned it.' WHERE `entry`=27037;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oh aye, \'ere\'s the stuff. But where\'s me powder? Everything\'s here but for the powder. I need explosives, man! You tell the King, no powder, no power. I need me some kersplosions or I ain\'t leavin\' port.' WHERE `entry`=27038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Belmont gets a little nervous and sends some newbie to look for me? Listen, I\'ve been staking out the old Ivar cottage from inside this outhouse for three days. Your presence threatens the whole damn operation! There\'s no time to explain. We have to act now or this mission will be compromised.' WHERE `entry`=27039;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s the ol\' spirit! One less nasty in this world that the little ones will have ta worry about when they go ta sleep at night. Not ta mention that we won\'t have ta be worrying about him none no more neither! Now let\'s see here. I think we have somethin\' in our crates that\'ll make a fittin\' reward fer ya.' WHERE `entry`=27042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='An excellent display of $C prowess. I believe that a reward is in order. Something appropriate for a powerful man such as yourself.' WHERE `entry`=27043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Y- Y- Your highness!' WHERE `entry`=27044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Alas, poor Yorick! I knew her, $N. An assassin of infinite courage... Now, tell me what\'s going on? What did you and Yorick discover?' WHERE `entry`=27045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You wage a war that we cannot. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=27046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $R. These will do well.' WHERE `entry`=27047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well played! I\'ve got this pretty sweet deal going. A bunch of shmucks go up there to Therazane\'s Throne and give all kinds of gold to D\'lom for who-knows-what kinda crap. He forks all that cash over to me for these crystals. I go home freakin\' rich for a couple chunks of rock. Don\'t tell no one though. I don\'t want no competition springin\' up. Think you can come back later to help me get another load of crystals out?' WHERE `entry`=27048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Once the growth starts, it is near impossible to stomp back into submission. Through persistence our realm will one day be cleansed.' WHERE `entry`=27049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are proficient at stepping on things. You would make an excellent giant.' WHERE `entry`=27050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $R. We will weed the rest out of their possession in time.' WHERE `entry`=27051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Cauldron Lord Soulwrath\'s key disintegrates as it touches the lock on the access panel at the base of the cauldron\'s platform. A slight clanking noise is heard within, and the access panel swings open to reveal more viscous toxins within the cauldron\'s framework. There is a small spigot that the bottle fits well enough under, allowing you to draw a sample for Field Agent Kaartish back at the Menders\' Stead.' WHERE `entry`=27053;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The orders in Malicia\'s possession incriminate Darkmaster Gandling of the Scholomance, but they also conceal another important bit of information.' WHERE `entry`=27054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have gone above and beyond, $N. Not only have we set back the Cult of the Damned in their crusade to re-plague the plaguelands, but you have uncovered another set of dire plans: they continue to re-animate the dead! Your name will definitely be mentioned when this information is presented to Highlord Fordring, $N. You have my thanks, and the blessing of the Argent Crusade.' WHERE `entry`=27055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Crowley... A gnat. An insect, waiting to be crushed beneath my boot heel. So he thinks to rouse the feral worgen of Silverpine? We shall show him and his allies the might of the Forsaken! But first we must clean up the mess made by the Warchief\'s fleet. Without their aid we may lose this war.' WHERE `entry`=27056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work. One moment please... Yes, this appears to be the same corruption that is affecting the wildlife. With this knowledge, and with your combat expertise, we may have the power to stop this.' WHERE `entry`=27057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it! You found out what the Twilight\'s Hammer were up to and you stopped them dead in their tracks! Now I\'m certain that I have something around here for you.' WHERE `entry`=27058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it! Excellent work, my boy. You found out what the Twilight\'s Hammer were up to and you stopped them dead in their tracks! Now I\'m certain that I have something around here for you.' WHERE `entry`=27059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That was a close one! I can\'t believe you stood your ground against so many at once. It looks like this site was used for some kind of twisted Twilight\'s Hammer initiation ritual. They\'re definitely active in Stormwind. What\'s this? This badge shows a crossed axe and hammer. It looks old. If we keep poking around, we might figure out what it means...' WHERE `entry`=27060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So we\'re going to have to take on Abyssion to get the fragment?  This operation just got a whole lot more difficult all of a sudden.' WHERE `entry`=27061;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You seem an able warrior. Perhaps you can help me put an end to the terrible evil here.' WHERE `entry`=27062;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You seem an able warrior. Perhaps you can help me put an end to the terrible evil here.' WHERE `entry`=27063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is REALLY suspicious, $N! Samuelson doesn\'t have a shred of info here about the Twilight Hammer - it\'s almost like he\'s not investigating them. Yet he\'s got a complete catalog of the missing explosives. And I found this funny badge with a symbol on it: A crossed axe and hammer. It all means something, but what?' WHERE `entry`=27064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This fiasco may go down as one of the biggest embarrassments in the history of naval warfare. How did this happen? Drunk happened. That\'s how.' WHERE `entry`=27065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I want to teach you a basic healing technique, $N. This spell will allow you to aid wounded allies by healing their wounds over a short period of time.$B$BMany braves have been injured in our fight to defend Camp Narache, so your healing skills will be put to good use. Practice your new healing technique on the wounded braves around Camp Narache.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Rejuvination from Gart Mistrunner. Practice using Rejuvination on a Wounded Brave in Camp Narache.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have a knack for the healing arts, $N. Wherever you go, your skills as a healer will be in demand. Return to me when you are ready for more training.' WHERE `entry`=27067;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He\'s gone? Did he have the sword? Nah...don\'t tell me. Don\'t matter no more. Mazoga don\'t care. I\'m off now, mon. De consequences of my actions await me. Take whatever I was holdin\'... I don\'t need it where I\'m goin\'...' WHERE `entry`=27068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We may not have to live down the shame of this defeat, $N. The Warchief will likely have us all executed instead.$B$BI\'ll be damned if we don\'t go down without a fight. Although the whole beachhead is overrun by Bloodfang worgen, there may still be hope. I want you to accompany one of our sea pups to the Beachhead, directly west of here, and recover our supplies. Return to me when the pup can carry no more.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Within these crates are held STEEL THUNDER! With our weaponry returned we might have a chance to redeem ourselves.' WHERE `entry`=27069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I heard that a troll in here, Hydromancer Velratha I think she was called, has come into the possession of a very rare, beautiful, and powerful piece of jewelry called the Tiara of the Deep. She uses it to control the powerful demigod Gahz\'rilla, whose very scales are said to crackle with energy. Do you know what all of that means, $R?$B$BI need it! Kill Velratha, take the Tiara of the Deep, and kill Gahz\'rilla for one of his scales. Bring them all back to me pronto! I\'ll reward you handsomly.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! This Tiara will grant me complete control of the water around here, and the Electrified Scale will serve to power all the machines I need to use it all to my advantage! You\'re going to make me a very rich and powerful goblin! You can have this, it\'s nothing compared to what I\'ll have soon.' WHERE `entry`=27070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You killed dem? All of dem? And you return alive? Take what you want off my body, den. It\'s mostly curse-free, Mazoga promises.' WHERE `entry`=27071;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' $C? What are you doing here? I\'m SI:7 Agent Jack Bauden. This is the longest day of my life.' WHERE `entry`=27072;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks as if you really gave those worgen a beating and, in the process, lifted the "shame haze" they cast over us. Perhaps the sea dogs will quit drinkin\' now. Who am I kidding? Hah!' WHERE `entry`=27073;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You hit the twilight camp at the center of the lake? Not bad, lad! If you\'re ready to take the fight right to their doorstep, I\'ve got your chance.' WHERE `entry`=27074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It may look grim, but we\'ll win with your help, $N. They won\'t keep the dwarves down.' WHERE `entry`=27075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow! I knew I could count on you! Here\'s something for your troubles.' WHERE `entry`=27076;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Shame that these half-formed things are too brittle and warped to be used for some weapons of our own. But it\'s thanks to you that we had the chance to get them out before they set. I\'m not about to complain.' WHERE `entry`=27077;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it! We may not have stopped the cult dead, but we\'ve shown them we\'re not easy pickings and given them a welt to prove it. Take this with my gratitude, and try not to blush if anyone in Thelsamar calls you "hero"!' WHERE `entry`=27078;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! Now to prepare the "meal."' WHERE `entry`=27082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thassarian and the humans made their move. I thought I had an agreement with Thassarian... but I suppose this will do.' WHERE `entry`=27083;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Merely a dent in their numbers... but the sight of their fellow men falling from the skies surely weakened their resolve.' WHERE `entry`=27084;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You fight well, $N. I wish I had your ability... and your bravery.' WHERE `entry`=27085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. With them out of the way, I have no more excuses. Soon, I must battle Thassarian, for honor and for Andorhal.' WHERE `entry`=27086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You won\'t be taking me anywhere, $N. While Koltira prances about with his playmate, Thassarian, I plan to win this battle. Then I\'ll make Koltira suffer for his weakness. Don\'t believe me?  Fine, I\'ll let you in on a little secret...' WHERE `entry`=27087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Was there ever any doubt? An ettin is no match for science!' WHERE `entry`=27088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='With the Enthralled Val\'kyr by your side, kill 5 Frightened Provincial Minutemen, then use your Call to Arms ability to turn them into Forsaken Troopers. Then find Thassarian in western Andorhal.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the body of Lurid, Thassarian\'s trusted knight. With Thassarian nowhere to be found, it would seem that the Alliance forces have withdrawn. The Forsaken have won the battle for Andorhal.' WHERE `entry`=27089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='See?  All it took was a little help from the val\'kyr. These creatures are turning to be much more helpful than I had first thought. Now, on to other matters.' WHERE `entry`=27090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='And now, it is time for your first lesson.$B$BI will show you a  great way to start combat, $N. By seizing the initiative and charging in, you can stun your opponent and give yourself the upper hand.$B$BOnce our lesson has ended, find a training dummy and practice your new skill.',`objectives_loc1`='Learn Charge from Delios. Locate a Training Dummy outside the Sunspire and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I think you\'ve mastered the basics of the charge, $N. Don\'t forget to return when you need more training.' WHERE `entry`=27091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<3 ... 2 ... 1 ...> Underneath the powder kegs you find a heap of notes and papers. Apparently the cultists were trying to destroy the evidence behind them.>' WHERE `entry`=27092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lok\'tar, $N! Once the ale wears off my orcs will be ready!' WHERE `entry`=27093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You rescued our orcs and killed the Skitterweb matriarch? We owe you a great debt of gratitude. You\'ve saved us all from certain execution, $N. I\'m sure we can rouse these drunken idiots now.' WHERE `entry`=27094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The root of this evil must be found and destroyed! The Skitterweb matriarch must be nearby. No doubt hiding in the nearby cave!' WHERE `entry`=27095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Admiral Hatchet hands you an envelope sealed with the mark of the Horde.>$B$BThis is your commendation letter. It\'s the least I could do for you given the circumstances.$B$BReturn to Lady Sylvanas Windrunner with the letter and inform her of our status. Let her know that we will be ready to march on her command.$B$BGoodbye, $N. You are an excellent soldier.$B$BNortheast, $G lad:ma\'am;. To Forsaken High Command!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' So the orcs are in order? Recovered their supplies? Killed a dozen worgen? Toppled an ettin? Freed their soldiers and destroyed the Skitterweb matriarch? I say this rarely, $N, but I am impressed. Perhaps your ability matches your aspirations. We shall see, for now you will be tested!' WHERE `entry`=27096;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see everything, $N. Through Agatha all is known to me.' WHERE `entry`=27097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do you now understand the importance of our mission here? Crowley and his Alliance dogs must be stopped!' WHERE `entry`=27098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You must strike at their leaders, $N. You will find them holed up in the old keep. Battle your way inside and find the holdouts! Turn them for your queen!$B$BNone shall escape the mighty grasp of the Forsaken!',`objectives_loc1`='Find the Refugee Leadership inside Fenris Keep.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It would seem that Crowley is more formidable than I anticipated. Still, he is a man - flesh and bone - full of secrets. Secrets that I know all about... You have served me well, $N. I could use someone of your ability at the Sepulcher. I have a plan to deal with Crowley and his insurgents once and for all. Will you help?' WHERE `entry`=27099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The notes deal with High Cultist Maziel\'s research on the elemental properties of quicksilver. His obsession with the subject borders on the insane.' WHERE `entry`=27100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Maziel\'s journal appears to be undamaged by the mercury.' WHERE `entry`=27101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve disposed of an enemy before he could grow more powerful. By eliminating Maziel you\'ve also ensured that his powers will not be used against the Earthen Ring.' WHERE `entry`=27102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done well, $C, and for that I am forever in your debt. Though the war is far from over, a great battle has been won against those who would bring about our doom. Please - accept this gold as a token of my enduring gratitude. If we ever cleanse Dire Maul, know that you will be welcomed here as a hero. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, very well done indeed. You\'ve made an old spirit very happy this day. You deserve proper thanks for the risks you\'ve taken.' WHERE `entry`=27104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is very troublesome that a water elemental was here, let alone one that powerful. Take this as my thanks for your efforts. I must examine this essence for any knowledge it may contain.' WHERE `entry`=27105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Samuelson - corrupted by the Twilight\'s Hammer? This must have been going on for years. Right here in my very keep! I am grateful that you and my son were able to get to the bottom of this before my city was brought to harm. I\'ve underestimated how much Anduin has grown - his command of the holy light just saved my life, if not the entire kingdom. As for you - words alone can\'t do justice to your heroism this day. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27106;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now you watch Master use book to kill stupid trees and stupid goat men! YAR!' WHERE `entry`=27107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This web have lots of magic! Master will be very happy now! And you make Dagg\'thol happy, $R. Take this so you believe how happy you make Dagg\'thol!' WHERE `entry`=27108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your work here was noble. Fret not, for Tendris\' soul was crying to be put to rest. He is thankful.' WHERE `entry`=27109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We thank you, hero.' WHERE `entry`=27110;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You open the chest to find...' WHERE `entry`=27111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your dedication will make this all that much easier.' WHERE `entry`=27112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our meeting is no coincidence, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s working! My father brought it!' WHERE `entry`=27115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What in blazes WAS that? A flying mechanostrider? You know what, I don\'t want to know. I\'m just going to pretend that didn\'t happen, and we\'ll be all nice and businesslike.' WHERE `entry`=27116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellently done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeah, this will do the trick. Just a slip here, and tuck here... heh - this is going to work out just fine!   Here you go, you\'re all set. Remember- this isn\'t the most securely fashioned item in the world. You\'ll have ten minutes of use before it falls apart, and then you\'re not going to fool anybody!  Try using it just before you approach him to make sure it lasts as long as you\'re going to need it.' WHERE `entry`=27119;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Here ya go $N - put this thing on, and you\'ll have ten minutes to do whatever. Good luck!$B$BOh, and if you happen to find a key to get me out of here, BY ALL MEANS LET ME KNOW!!!' WHERE `entry`=27120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, ye say? At the behest of the Cult o\' Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Ironforge is in yer debt.' WHERE `entry`=27122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve arrived just in time, $N. All our resources are tied up keeping the rift stable. We need someone like you to help us recover the fragments of the World Pillar.' WHERE `entry`=27123;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow... you ARE da true king! Old king never even ask about da gauntlet! Look - this mark on da gauntlet an old old OLD timey magic mark, older than da Gordok they say. Well, I learn one thing as little ogre - how to make mark come to life and give power back to gauntlet! I do it for you, king!  Here, take da gauntlet and rule FOREVER!' WHERE `entry`=27124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes! I can see that you were indeed successful. You have received your tribute, the Gordok advance will exist no longer, and the Gordok are blissfully ignorant! This is a true winner\'s scenario, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t thank you enough, $C. Now, let\'s see if we can get this catapult moving again.' WHERE `entry`=27126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, you say? At the behest of the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Orgrimmar is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=27127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Little $R did it! Now Horde more powerful than ever! YAR!' WHERE `entry`=27128;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you been in contact with a druid of the talon recently, $C? I can feel the lingering presence of one.' WHERE `entry`=27129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your face shows signs of desperate conflict. I honor your presence, brave $C.' WHERE `entry`=27130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I sensed your coming all the way from Dreamer\'s Rest. Your assistance would be most welcome.' WHERE `entry`=27131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I sensed your coming all the way from Camp Mojache. Your assistance would be most welcome.' WHERE `entry`=27132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Speak softly, $N. The Gordok may not be intelligent, but they are still dangerous warriors.' WHERE `entry`=27133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These ogres no pushovers. I need you help me finish Orhan\'s task, $R.' WHERE `entry`=27134;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Uh oh. Sounds like he wasn\'t very happy about the situation. How was I to know? I\'m just an initiate after all. Anyway, I\'ll worry about Magmatooth later.' WHERE `entry`=27135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. We need all the power we can muster to keep Deepholm stable.' WHERE `entry`=27136;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you are, my boy. I have something very important for you to do!' WHERE `entry`=27139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it!  They are defeated!  And the Gambit... did it work? Very interesting. You\'ve done well, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27140;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Shake it off, kid. Happens to me all the time...' WHERE `entry`=27141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ten thousand souls cry out in unison, $N! You have struck a mortal blow to the Scourge and their masters.' WHERE `entry`=27142;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $R. Alexi deserves nothing for his foolishness.' WHERE `entry`=27143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have nothing against the Knights of the Ebon Blade, but Koltira needs to be reminded who he works for now. His loyalty must lie with the Horde. Or, more specifically, the Forsaken. I wouldn\'t plan on seeing Koltira anytime soon. Now that I have him... you can rest assured that any bonds he may have had with that Alliance scum will be thoroughly broken.' WHERE `entry`=27144;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N!  It\'ll be a long time before they can grow another clutch of dragons.$B$B...At least, I hope it will!' WHERE `entry`=27145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can feel my spirit healing, $N. You have done my husband and I a great service.' WHERE `entry`=27146;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Destroy Kirtonos.',`objectives_loc1`='Destroy Kirtonos.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the death of Kirtonos, a chapter in the horrible tale of Scholomance comes to a close. You have my deepest, everlasting gratitude for your bravery.' WHERE `entry`=27147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Without a headmaster, the school will descend into chaos. It will not put forth any more of its vile \'students\' into the field. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27148;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It\'s likely that the battle for Andorhal will start up again soon. In the meantime, you could probably stand to practice your skills as a $C.$B$BEast of here is a large farm that has been taken over by the Argent Dawn and the Cenarion Circle. I don\'t doubt that they\'ll have some work for you.' WHERE `entry`=27150;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I must admit, $N... I have been using my mind vision spell to keep tabs on you. And I must say... the number of gnolls you found on the trail is truly staggering!' WHERE `entry`=27151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gnolls and necromancy... what a surprise!  And I thought that, here in the Western Plaguelands, we had put these dark days behind us. Wait... what is THAT?' WHERE `entry`=27152;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did you notice, $N?  Many names were mentioned, but one name was mentioned far more than the others. Bisp.' WHERE `entry`=27153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Speak with Bree Ironstock',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Speak with High Cleric Alphus' WHERE `entry`=27153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I suppose that we can take his aggression as an admission of guilt. You alright, $N?' WHERE `entry`=27154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m already aware of your actions, $N. I welcome you into my town, give you my blessing, and what do you do? You slay the traitor that we\'ve been hunting down for weeks. Well done. Your heroism is budding much earlier than even I had anticipated.' WHERE `entry`=27155;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m just looking over my paperwork here, and it says that we were expecting a FEMALE $R $C. You\'re not, umm... Never mind. It would appear that you are not the person that I originally hired, but you did a good job. So I\'m going to pay you anyhow.' WHERE `entry`=27156;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work!  In retrospect, I\'m glad that other $R $C never showed up... you\'ve proven to be all the help I need.' WHERE `entry`=27157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time you arrived, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You may not act quickly, but at least you do not fail me. Very well. I will have a more important task for you, $N, when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=27159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Abominations... strong. $N... stronger.' WHERE `entry`=27160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These grenades are all explosives, nothing more. I may not be a goblin engineer... but I still understand the value of being able to just explode things every once in a while.' WHERE `entry`=27161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellently done, $N. And now, with the leader of the Scourge forces eliminated from Andorhal, we bide our time.' WHERE `entry`=27162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellently done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27163;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Araj dead... this is good. That gnome has done his part in winning this war. As have you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Word arrived shortly before you did, $N. With the Scourge ejected from Andorhal, we are one step closer to retaking Lordaeron.' WHERE `entry`=27165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will have my fletchers get to work on these. I\'m glad to see you being so useful right away, $N. Perhaps later I will have some more exciting tasks for you.' WHERE `entry`=27166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You hunt like a true $C. Even if we can\'t set up our homesteads... at least we can still eat.' WHERE `entry`=27167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hopefully most of them passed on peacefully. I thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You and the humans at Chillwind Camp wish to re-take Andorhal?  I wish you luck.' WHERE `entry`=27169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Scattered all over the bottom level of the crypt, you find shattered crates that once held weapons and armor. It appears that somebody got here before you did.' WHERE `entry`=27170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Attacked by ghosts?  Strange. I suppose that crypt wasn\'t fully healed after all. You just missed Thurman Grant... you remember, that oaf of a farmer that was here earlier. He took his men with him and traveled to the nearest farm... against my orders.' WHERE `entry`=27171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, now that you\'re here, we\'ll gladly take that armor off your hands. You can keep the weapons, though. These men wouldn\'t know which end to hold.' WHERE `entry`=27172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You fight well, $R. My men could stand to learn a few moves from an experienced $C like you.' WHERE `entry`=27173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We can handle things from here. I thank you for your help, $N. I assume that when we next meet, it will be in battle. Take care of yourself until then. We\'ll need all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=27174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $C. As you can see, our camp is a joint expedition between Argent Crusade members and Cenarion Circle druids, but we welcome all who wish to help heal the land.' WHERE `entry`=27175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Let\'s have a look at this. Shall we?' WHERE `entry`=27176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at all this! You were able to recover more than I thought. We can outfit a whole squad of marines with this stuff. We have the gear. If we only had some way to bolster our numbers here in the Highlands...' WHERE `entry`=27177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll send \'em packing, $N! Cho\'gall won\'t be able to count on the naga to back him up in this fight. From here on out, it\'s just us versus the Twilight\'s Hammer. ...And the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These tablets are covered with titan writings. There\'s never-before seen information here, $N! Missing pieces to an ancient puzzle... Good work!' WHERE `entry`=27179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will see to it that these insignias are returned to the Undercity at once. The registrar will place their names in our records so that their sacrifice may never be forgotten.' WHERE `entry`=27180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You have avenged the fallen, $N, but there is more to be done.' WHERE `entry`=27181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you come here to spy on me? No?$B$BPerhaps you have an appreciation for fine cuisine, then? Good, you can help!' WHERE `entry`=27182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, that\'s the spice! Now here\'s some swampy good stew.' WHERE `entry`=27183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got the eyes! You got the eyes! Tasty, tasty spider eyes!$B$BSome eyes... when you stare at them they stare back. Eat those last. They keep you company... out in the swamp.$B$BHello, little spider eyes. Hello! You taste like chicken. Gooey, salty chicken!$B$BMmmh.' WHERE `entry`=27184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nicely done, lad! Without them new weapons, they\'re just as easy t\' kill as they were when they were alive!' WHERE `entry`=27185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a good blade. It has a good swing. It\'s a good swing blade. Thank you. Thank you, thank you, thank you!!! Now I want to try it....$B$BLater. I\'ll try it later. But like I was saying... thanks.' WHERE `entry`=27186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' From your findings, the spirits in this place must amount to everyone who ever lived on this land, not just the previous occupants. Something has been corrupting and killing them. Those who follow don\'t learn the truth until it\'s too late. We have to put an end to this, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' These match the description exactly! I prepared the torch while you were out. All that remains is to fasten the herbs to the end here.' WHERE `entry`=27189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It worked? I mean... it worked! Jarl and I are in your debt, $N. Now the only remaining problem is my friend\'s taste in furniture, and I\'m afraid that won\'t be solved as easily.' WHERE `entry`=27190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonder what it\'s like to be an ogre. Big people have to eat more. Ogres must be even hungrier than me. That doesn\'t sound very fun.' WHERE `entry`=27191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Recover a box of Fras Siabi\'s Premium Tobacco.',`objectives_loc1`='Recover a box of Fras Siabi\'s Premium Tobacco.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Truly, you have uncovered the snuff of legends. It is nearly impossible to place a value on this historical tobacco. Here, have a few coins.' WHERE `entry`=27192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This book documents a recent meeting with Ivus Bloodfang. The location mentioned is the Deep Elem Mine. I know of this place. It has only one entrance. We shall corner and crush them!' WHERE `entry`=27193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I \'spose we\'re to corner them first then crush, eh?' WHERE `entry`=27194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='WHAT!? CROWLEY!!!!! Bastards. Those were some of our strongest soldiers. I have underestimated Crowley and Bloodfang for the last time. Clearly they are an enemy the likes of which we have never seen - willing to sacrifice their own to set a trap like this... unheard of in Alliance warfare.' WHERE `entry`=27195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Would you get a load of this place!' WHERE `entry`=27196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Word has it that you helped those farmers arm themselves. Well, now they\'ve initiated the attack without my order!  They\'ve forced my hand. The battle has resumed. This time, we fight the Forsaken... and I fight Koltira, my old brother of the Ebon Blade.' WHERE `entry`=27197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You fight well, $N. I wish I had your ability... and your bravery.' WHERE `entry`=27198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. With them out of the way, I have no more excuses. Soon, I must battle Koltira, for honor and for Andorhal.' WHERE `entry`=27199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='She had me under her spell, $N. I wouldn\'t have made it out of there alive if it weren\'t for you. Thank you! Maybe the rest of the Alliance fleet can finally anchor here in peace...' WHERE `entry`=27200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='For every val\'kyr you slay, you save dozens of our men... and prevent the Forsaken forces from growing. Still, they press on. We may not win this battle after all.' WHERE `entry`=27201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You fought valiantly, but we\'re getting nowhere. Every body that falls just fuels their forces.' WHERE `entry`=27202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good to see you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I watched your victory from below. Well-fought, but ultimately, it was for naught. The val\'kyr and the Forsaken press on; soon, they will overtake us. We have lost Andorhal.' WHERE `entry`=27204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Val\'kyr?  Koltira brought val\'kyr to this fight?  Has he gone mad? No, this is not Koltira\'s work. This was Sylvanas.' WHERE `entry`=27205;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lost?  No... next, they\'ll be coming for Chillwind, I suppose. This was a major strategic blow to the Alliance\'s plans for Lordaeron. Very well. I will report the results of this battle to King Wrynn. I don\'t expect him to be happy.' WHERE `entry`=27206;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A massive prince of the wind, you say? The herald of Al\'Akir, the Windlord? Madness. All of it. Stormwind is in your debt, hero.' WHERE `entry`=27207;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good we stopped Balnazzar now. Before long, his army would have overtaken all of Stratholme, giving him a powerful center for his new unholy empire.' WHERE `entry`=27208;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A massive prince of the wind, you say? The herald of Al\'Akir, the Windlord? Madness. All of it. All of Thunder Bluff is in your debt, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. I think we managed to catch them off guard. Their agents probably thought themselves safe within the city walls.$B$BGiven time, the agitators will return and spread their lies again. We\'ll use the time you\'ve bought to shut out the deserters further.' WHERE `entry`=27210;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Excellent. All that remains is to discredit the deserters so that they\'ll never gain a foothold in Theramore again, and I have just the plan to do it.' WHERE `entry`=27211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Just as I\'d hoped! I think it\'s safe to say any deserter agents who try to infiltrate Theramore will be laughed right out of town!' WHERE `entry`=27212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gavis\' request isn\'t as outlandish as it might sound. With the proper handling, Lady Jaina can return the deserters to the fold, but that is her decision, of course.$B$BIt\'s been a pleasure working with you, $N. Without your help, I doubt the operation would\'ve gone so smoothly. When I make my report in Stormwind, it will name you as the $C who ended the deserter threat.' WHERE `entry`=27213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' So you\'ve heard about the recent shipwreck off the coast? Good, I could use some help confirming my suspicions about the survivors. Welcome aboard, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Get off my lawn... unless, that is, you want to help old "Swamp Eye" with a little bit of cooking. Whad\'ya say?' WHERE `entry`=27215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. I can use all the help you can offer. My first priority is to get that lamp re-lit.' WHERE `entry`=27216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, I have my doubts, but this is the only solution available right now. Once we have it up and running, I\'m sure there will be time to look at other ways to fuel the lamp.' WHERE `entry`=27217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, now, that was thoughtful o\' Babs to send that over. I don\'t know if you\'ve leafed through it or not, but there\'s a lot of truth to the tales in that book. Sailors didn\'t just make it all up, you know.' WHERE `entry`=27218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you want to know about sea monsters? Hmm... well, I\'ll make you a deal, but it\'s going to involve a lot of alcohol and some embarrassment on your part.' WHERE `entry`=27219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad at all, but you know, I think I\'d get a bath in as soon as possible, if I was you.$B$BNow, about your sea monster...$B$BHelp yourself to a brew or two in the meantime.' WHERE `entry`=27220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Well, it sounds like we\'ve got our work cut out for us. I\'ll make the preparations.' WHERE `entry`=27221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N! I\'ll admit, when I caught my first glimpse of that beast, I had doubts about our ability to defend the docks, but you held together the defenders brilliantly!' WHERE `entry`=27222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You may have this as a suitable reward. I found it nestled in the armor of one of the scourge here.' WHERE `entry`=27223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see that you received my message. I have something important I wish to discuss with you.' WHERE `entry`=27225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A-HA! I knew it! Lesson learned, I suppose. We will not fail again. I will be sure to have some ale on hand at the front lines.' WHERE `entry`=27226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Stratholme will become a paragon of all that is good in this world. You have my thanks for your part in this mission.' WHERE `entry`=27227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I respect the power you demonstrated in killing Ramstein. With proper rage backing your actions, I think even the Scourge can know fear.' WHERE `entry`=27228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='By Grom, I\'m glad that\'s over with. If you read that sign you may have some idea how desperate I got after trying to communicate to these lumbering oafs.' WHERE `entry`=27229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great! Without a steady flow of their weapons, we\'ll win through attrition!' WHERE `entry`=27230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Those that survived your assault on Fenris managed to drink the blood of the wolf. They turned into ferocious worgen, hell-bent on vengeance. Now they paddle across Lordamere Lake and assault my sea dogs. Many have already been killed. The worgen monsters must be stopped!$B$BMake your way to the Decrepit Fields, east of here, and kill the Hillsbrad Worgen that infest the area. Once you\'ve killed them all, make your way to the Horde communication panel, located at the docks. I\'ll be in touch.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Hatchet here, are they all dead?' WHERE `entry`=27231;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Though you killed a large number of the newly turned worgen, many more are sure to appear. Still, their assault will have softened. Well done, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $C. As you can see, our camp is a joint expedition between Argent Crusade members and Cenarion Circle druids, but we welcome all who wish to help heal the land.' WHERE `entry`=27233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' What in the world could \'precious cargo\' refer to? The Defias have done some small time smuggling back in Stormwind, but this seems out of their league. The language of these orders suggests a wealthy or noble patron.' WHERE `entry`=27234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' So there was valuable cargo on board! We have to locate it before the Defias recover it. These guys are no divers, but we\'re going to need some of their gear if you\'re to help me find the cargo.' WHERE `entry`=27235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, this is in worse shape than I\'d thought, and these tools...$B$BWell, I said I\'d get this back into working condition for you, so I\'d better get to work.' WHERE `entry`=27236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Good work. Now, let\'s see if our \'precious cargo\' is in here....' WHERE `entry`=27237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You and Renn have done excellent work in bringing this information to light and reporting it immediately. Now, we must confirm your findings. The implications are too great if we are wrong.' WHERE `entry`=27238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' A rune circle, dragonkin? The Defias have allied themselves with HER? The traitor?' WHERE `entry`=27239;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have no doubt that the king meant every word when he told you he plans to destroy the Defias once and for all. He does not make promises lightly, and the enemies of Stormwind should know it.' WHERE `entry`=27241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The patch of swamp to the northeast is home to a particularly nasty breed of raptors. We\'ve lost more than one unwary soldier to them, but I think we can turn them against our Grimtotem neighbors.$B$BTake this rope and use it to capture bloodfen raptors or bloodfen screechers that you\'ve subdued. I wouldn\'t try to capture one of the beasts until you\'ve weakened them quite a bit in combat. It\'s going to be quite a struggle.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You look a little scratched up, but nothing major. You\'re certainly in a lot better shape than the Grimtotems will be when our new raptor friends get done with them.' WHERE `entry`=27242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Good. That ought to forestall a raid or two.' WHERE `entry`=27243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $N. Our agent, Marg Nighteye, was stationed outside Theramore. He was charged to spy on the city. $B$BThis is his latest report, and it may be his last -- from your testimony, I fear that Marg met his end in the swamp...' WHERE `entry`=27244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Collect Grimtotem Keys from the Grimtotem tauren in Blackhoof Village and use them to free 5 Theramore Prisoners.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The freed captives have already begun returning from Blackhoof Village. The information the captain is receiving from the prisoners will give us an advantage in our next battle against the Grimtotems.$B$BYou have my thanks and that of the men.' WHERE `entry`=27245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hm... I can\'t read orcish very well, but this looks like a report... written by an orc spy!' WHERE `entry`=27246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A report from an orc spy! How did you find this? No matter -- let\'s see what it says...' WHERE `entry`=27247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So Theramore is interested in doing business? Well, that\'s not an offer I\'d turn down. Supplies are pretty scarce here right now, so we need all the business contacts we can get!' WHERE `entry`=27248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see that Captain Vimes is finally assigning others to this investigation.$B$BI\'ve used a reflective powder to dust the area. It will reveal suspicious objects and markings, helping you to focus your efforts. Look over anything the dust illuminates.' WHERE `entry`=27249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='James Hyal\'s his real name. He opened an inn at the edge of the Barrens. Wanted to make a nice place for travelers to stop over...$B$BMight be he was thinking too big, but the inn did do well for a while. Then we lost control of the roads in the marsh, and the ogres took over.$B$BJames was too stubborn to give up his dream for safety within our walls, and the Shady Rest Inn was burnt to the ground. We\'re investigating, but haven\'t had much luck. If you want to help out, see what you can find in the rubble.' WHERE `entry`=27251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hm, I\'m no expert with the construction of arms and armor. Their use, yes, but not their making.$B$BThis shield seems as ordinary as any, excepting the damage from the fire that engulfed the inn.' WHERE `entry`=27252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Leave this place be, errand boy, or I\'ll be sure to bring a contingent of guard with me next time to sink the lesson home.' WHERE `entry`=27253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I grant that humans have strange decorating tastes, but would they use a plain iron shield to adorn their fireplace? Perhaps this shield was placed there by the ones who burned the inn.$B$BA warning? A threat?' WHERE `entry`=27254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is good shield. Very strong, heavy, good. But Do\'gol don\'t need it. I make shields, not buy them, $N.$B$BYou should know that.' WHERE `entry`=27255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I don\'t like spiders that are so big I can\'t sit on them and squish them.$B$BThanks for getting them, $N. Now I rip them open and pour them onto the shield...' WHERE `entry`=27256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mosarn? Sounds familiar... I can\'t put my finger on it. Maybe it\'ll come to me later.$B$BIt probably isn\'t important. A shield can come from anywhere and not mean anything...' WHERE `entry`=27257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, you are certainly correct. This is a shield that I made.$B$BI\'m afraid there\'s not much more I can tell you though, $N. I craft so many different shields and sets of armor, I can\'t keep track of them all.' WHERE `entry`=27258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hoofprints... It could have been the quilboar, I suppose. Or maybe even the centaur. Their presence in the Barrens is not insignificant, and I would not think it a stretch to commit such an act.$B$BDid I tell you? It wasn\'t just that the inn was burned down... The owner\'s woman and pup were killed. Bad business, that.$B$BNonetheless, I will send Kagoro to find where the tracks lead.' WHERE `entry`=27259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... now this is interesting.' WHERE `entry`=27260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmph. It is good that Reethe will no longer be lurking around the swamp, but it is a shame that humans are built so frail that he could not recover from a little arrow wound.$B$BIt seems that this thread of the mystery has led nowhere, and we must look elsewhere.' WHERE `entry`=27261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hoofprints, eh? It is true that there is an extraordinary amount of centaur activity in the lands near the Dustwallow Marsh. In brief excursions into the Barrens, we found their camps and holdings dotting the area.$B$BI\'ll send out Falgran Hastil, one of our trackers, to see if he can find where the tracks lead.' WHERE `entry`=27262;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s never good news when a guard\'s badge is brought to me.$B$BSometimes it\'s a man or woman who\'s fallen in battle, and I\'m left to bring the news to the grieving family. Other times we never find out what happened to them. And other times it\'s even worse than that.' WHERE `entry`=27263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello, $N. You\'d like information about a specific member of the Theramore guard? Reethe, was it?$B$BJust give me a moment to find the right book.' WHERE `entry`=27264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It heartens me to see that my message found you, $N. We have much to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=27265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you\'ve arrived. Make yourself at home, $N. We have much to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=27266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It seems that the leaders of SI:7 have taken an interest in your progress and your service to the Alliance. Osborne the Night Man, a high ranking member of SI:7, has asked to speak with you. Look for him in the southern part of Stormwind\'s Old Town.$B$BI\'m not sure what Osborne wants with you, but it seemed important.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Osborne the Night Man in Stormwind\'s Old Town.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope my message didn\'t unnerve you, $N. I have called you here to recognize your accomplishments.' WHERE `entry`=27267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It heartens me to see that you received my message and responded so quickly.' WHERE `entry`=27268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to the Temple of the Moon, $N. I am glad that you chose to answer my summons so quickly.' WHERE `entry`=27269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $N. I am glad that you decided to accept my invitation.' WHERE `entry`=27270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to the Wizard\'s Sanctum, $N. I have been watching your progress with interest.' WHERE `entry`=27271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see that my message managed to reach you. Good. We have much to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=27272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad to see that you have arrived safely in Nighthaven, $N. I offer you the welcome and the hospitality of the Cenarion Circle.' WHERE `entry`=27273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see that you received my message. Excellent!' WHERE `entry`=27274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you again, $N. Let us put the fear of the Goddess into the Grimtotem.' WHERE `entry`=27275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am honored by your presence, $N. Let us put the fear of the Earth Mother into the Grimtotem.' WHERE `entry`=27276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, good. It seems my message did find you.' WHERE `entry`=27277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, you\'re here. Let\'s get started.' WHERE `entry`=27278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that you are here, we can begin.' WHERE `entry`=27279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Kardris Dreamseeker, a shaman whose wisdom is legendary in the Horde, has sent word that she wishes to speak with you. The messenger didn\'t mention what was so urgent, but you should make your way to Orgrimmar as quickly as you can and find Kardris in the Valley of Wisdom. She will be among others who offer training to young shamans.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Kardris Dreamseeker in the Valley of Wisdom.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you are both obedient and talented, $N. Stay that way, and you will go far in the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you are both obedient and talented, $N. Stay that way, and you will go far in the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$N, I have received word that you are needed back in Orgrimmar. Zevrost, one of the senior warlock trainers in the Cleft of Shadow, has something important that he wishes to discuss with you. It seems like the kind of thing that cannot wait.$B$BMake your way back to Orgrimmar and speak with him as soon as you can.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Zevrost in the Cleft of Shadow.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you\'re here at last.' WHERE `entry`=27282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Moonglade, $N. I have been looking forward to meeting you.' WHERE `entry`=27283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hm... interesting piece of iron you have here. Definitely not made by any of the blacksmiths I know over on this side of the sea, and it\'s certainly not my work.' WHERE `entry`=27284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s not much information to work on, but we\'ll have to keep it in mind. Hopefully some of the other pieces of this mystery will fall into place, and paint a more helpful picture of what happened.' WHERE `entry`=27285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Missing? That would be Tesoran\'s kind way of saying traitor.$B$BNo doubt he\'s one of those fools so blindly loyal to Admiral Daelin that he turned traitor. Isn\'t that a delicious irony? The deserters accuse us of betraying the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=27286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did Vimes send you? Couldn\'t do his dirty work himself, could he...' WHERE `entry`=27287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will send Lieutenant Caldwell to deal with the deserters at Lost Point. In addition, I will instruct him to find Reethe. The marsh is not so big and trackless that he should be unable to find him.' WHERE `entry`=27288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You\'ve done some good work, $N, best I\'ve seen from an amateur.$B$BLady Proudmoore asked that I keep her apprised of this delicate situation, and I haven\'t spoken to her for some time now.$B$BI was going to deliver my report to her later, but it seems more fitting that you should be the one to speak with her about it. You can probably answer her questions better than I could.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring Vimes\'s Report to Lady Jaina Proudmoore in Theramore.' WHERE `entry`=27289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well if it isn\'t Mesnanub! I hope you\'re ready for battle, because that\'s all you\'ll find in this hellhole. We\'re at the heart of contested territory and these worgen mongrels won\'t give an inch!' WHERE `entry`=27290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' It\'s good to know that they understand. You didn\'t tell them about James, did you? I\'ll deliver his wife\'s message to him, but I doubt he\'ll understand.' WHERE `entry`=27291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He actually said that the Grimtotems are his biggest customers? Mosarn gave us more help than he knows. With this much pointing toward the Grimtotems, I think we just found our first suspects.' WHERE `entry`=27292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' There\'s no doubt in my mind that the Grimtotems are moving against the humans. What I don\'t understand is what their intentions are toward us. We knew nothing of these plans and we lost a good man because of it. I don\'t trust that we\'re not next on their list.' WHERE `entry`=27293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='More than Coincidence',`details_loc1`='We\'ve gleaned as much as we can from the ruins of the inn. I\'m concerned about where the investigation will lead us from here, but we must know the truth.$B$BBetween the hoofprints and the shield with Mosarn\'s mark, I\'m lead to believe that the Grimtotems may have been involved. They\'ve recently established a settlement in the swamp, Blackhoof Village to the northeast. Travel to Blackhoof Village and search for more arms of Mosarn\'s manufacture.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is unmistakably the work of Mosarn. Questioning him further may draw too much attention, but we have a bit more freedom in dealing with the Grimtotems.' WHERE `entry`=27294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Krog wishes me to scry for the Grimtotems, eh? Well, I have no need of magic in this case. It seems we have a mutual enemy. The Grimtotems have built an outpost nearby and are a constant thorn in the side of me and my students.' WHERE `entry`=27295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Use Tabetha\'s Torch to burn he North Tent, East Tent, and the Northeast Tent at Direhorn Post.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Grimtotems should have no trouble understanding our latest message. As for you, your contact at Brackenwall Village will want to know of your success. If I know him, he\'ll appreciate the taste of vengeance.' WHERE `entry`=27296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'m impressed, $N. I would\'ve thought that the Grimtotem criminals would\'ve been more difficult to locate. The Alliance are truly incompetent. In truth, I just sought to answer the death of one of my men, but this situation has been more fortunate than expected. If the Grimtotem choose to retaliate, it will likely be against the Alliance. Perhaps we will soon have the manpower to drive the scum from these shores once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=27297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve heard much about you, $N. You have a bright future ahead of you in the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It won\'t be takin\' much convincin\' to turn us against da Twilight - dat\'s already our goal. We\'ve already come to battle here though, so we may be needin\' ya help before we can turn towards dey\'re fortress.$B$BDa Twilight have already brought Iso\'rath up from da ground to the south, I\'m sure ya noticed. It\'s tentacles have been burstin\' from da ground all around us. We could use a hand beatin\' them down if you be willin\'.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Tank ya, $C. A bit of breathin\' room helps a lot.' WHERE `entry`=27299;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Revenge is bittersweet, but I\'m glad we be havin\' someone as powerful as you do see dis done.' WHERE `entry`=27300;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank the elements that you\'ve come. Did my brothers send you?' WHERE `entry`=27301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that\'s what I\'m talkin\' about! Can you think of all the uses for this stuff? I definitely can\'t. But I can think of a lot, and I\'m liking the possibilities.' WHERE `entry`=27302;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. You are quite capable. I\'m extremely grateful that you\'ve chosen to aid us.' WHERE `entry`=27303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve heard much of your contributions to the Horde, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Master Fordring will be glad beyond measure to see this painting again.' WHERE `entry`=27305;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ogron? Yeah, that me. Shh. Keep voice down. Crocs hear you.' WHERE `entry`=27306;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $C. These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=27307;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Do you feel it, $C?  The elements are uneasy. We members of the Earthen Ring have struggled to find the cause of the unrest. Thus far we have been unsuccessful and now turn to others that may aid us. Speak with Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar and see what tasks she may have for you.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak to Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $C. These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=27308;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s see them wage their war now!' WHERE `entry`=27310;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let us see how well they fight without their weapons.' WHERE `entry`=27311;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Slay 20 Grimtotem tauren at Darkcloud Pinnacle.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='That put a dent in their numbers! Can\'t say that they didn\'t deserve it.' WHERE `entry`=27312;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Slay 20 Grimtotem tauren at Darkcloud Pinnacle.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='While the Earth Mother does not condone such violence, we had no choice. The Grimtotem have ignored Her teachings for too long and are reaping what they have sown.' WHERE `entry`=27313;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='She was tougher than I thought. We worked well together, but we\'re going to have to make sure not to underestimate the other Grimtotem chiefs.' WHERE `entry`=27314;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Basic brave philosophy dictates that if you kill the leaders and your enemy\'s forces, they will soon fall into disarray. We are going to do just that, $C.$B$BIsha Gloomaxe is the closest of the Grimtotem chiefs. We will test her and her axe, and she will be found wanting.',`objectives_loc1`='Slay Isha Grimtotem.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='She was more formidable than her reputation suggested. Although we worked well together, we must make certain not to underestimate the other Grimtotem chiefs.' WHERE `entry`=27315;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s true then! What is it doing here, though? And if it\'s here, that must mean that the writ and the drums are also nearby! Maybe there\'s some link between it and the wind serpent that just appeared? I think that I\'ve an idea what that creature is as well.' WHERE `entry`=27316;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is true then! What is it doing here, though? And if it is here, that must mean that the writ and the drums are also nearby! Perhaps there is some link between it and the wind serpent that just appeared? I think that I have an idea what that creature is as well.' WHERE `entry`=27317;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s two of them. Two more to go. I wonder what he meant about being "chosen"?' WHERE `entry`=27318;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That was not pleasant. I wonder what he meant by calling you, "the Chosen"?' WHERE `entry`=27319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m fairly certain that\'s it. This is very intriguing, $N. What are they doing here? Are they being used as a weapon? The wind serpent flew northwest to that next bluff. Maybe that\'s where the drums are?' WHERE `entry`=27320;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is very exciting and also worrisome, $N. What are these artifacts doing here? Are they being used as a weapons against us by the Grimtotem? The wind serpent flew northwest to that next bluff. Maybe that\'s where the drums are?' WHERE `entry`=27321;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That towering behemoth has killed hundreds of Forsaken soldiers. You\'ve done a great thing, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' What is it with you? Why do they all seem spooked by you being here?' WHERE `entry`=27323;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' There is something special about you, $N. That much is certain.' WHERE `entry`=27324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Surely that was the voice of the Elder Crone! We must be very careful, $N. Great danger lies ahead if Magatha Grimtotem has taken notice of you.' WHERE `entry`=27325;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Surely that was the voice of the Elder Crone! We must be very careful, $N. Great danger lies ahead if Magatha Grimtotem has taken notice of you.' WHERE `entry`=27326;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='For some reason they all think that you\'ve been sent by Magatha Grimtotem. I know it must have something to do with that wind serpent that\'s been hanging around. Doesn\'t matter. Their leader is dead. It\'s only a matter of time before the tauren of Freewind Post regain their home. If I were them, I\'d push back a little to teach the Grimtotem a lesson, but they probably won\'t. They\'re tauren.' WHERE `entry`=27327;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They all believed that you have been sent by Magatha Grimtotem. There is no arguing that her pet, Arikara, has been lurking about. It does not matter. Arnak is dead. It is only a matter of time before we take back Freewind Post. Perhaps now we will be able to establish a lasting peace with the Grimtotem?' WHERE `entry`=27328;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, she\'s been taken prisoner by the Twilight\'s Hammer. I can\'t say that I feel sorry for her, but she might prove even more dangerous in their hands.' WHERE `entry`=27329;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, she\'s been taken prisoner by the Twilight\'s Hammer. I can\'t say that I feel sorry for her, but she might prove even more dangerous in their hands.' WHERE `entry`=27330;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for coming to see me, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27331;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If I could still breathe I\'d let out a sigh of relief. Don\'t get too comfortable, though, $N, your mission here has just begun.' WHERE `entry`=27333;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you are, $N. I was beginning to think my message hadn\'t found you.' WHERE `entry`=27334;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $N. I\'m glad that you accepted my invitation. We have much to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=27335;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' A haze and some lightning? That\'s it? There\'s got to be more to the totem than just that! The Grimtotems aren\'t likely to bring something like this to the battlefield unless it has some kind of utility.' WHERE `entry`=27336;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ander told me to expect you. It\'s quite an honor to be crafting a weapon for you, $N. With these materials, it will be a fine blade indeed.' WHERE `entry`=27337;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Keep your head down \'fore you lose it, $C! This is MY beach. The Horde WANTS my beach. They will NOT have my beach. Is the beach situation clear?' WHERE `entry`=27338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This is absolutely perfect! He\'ll never know the difference.' WHERE `entry`=27339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Good. Can\'t say I\'ll miss the company, if you can call it that. You\'d think at least in the middle of the swamp you\'d get some privacy, you know?' WHERE `entry`=27340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s the lay of the land, soldier. If you\'re having trouble fighting here on the coast, you might consider pitching in and helping us take and hold that hill.' WHERE `entry`=27341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Good. Now just do as Forward Commander Onslaught commands. Try your best to fit in with the rest of the soldiers. We don\'t want the Gilneas Liberation Front to get suspicious. Oh, you  didn\'t know they were watching us? Right now there are five different worgen spies looking down on our position. Just be calm and follow orders. I\'ll let you know when we are ready to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=27342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lord Grayson has told me much about you and your dedication to the Light and the Alliance. It will be a great honor to craft a hammer for you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27343;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Who knew that cursed old keep hid such valuable items? I\'ll be honored to craft them into a fine weapon for you.' WHERE `entry`=27344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With this device I will be able to communicate with you in the field. Now to check the rest of our frontline outposts.' WHERE `entry`=27345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Not long ago, a goblin zeppelin crashed to the east. A representative of the Steamwheedle Cartel passed through here a few days ago.$B$BShe was looking for information about the zeppelin\'s cargo and it\'s pilot, Beezil, but none of us really got a good look at the crash. I doubt she\'ll be able to clean up after the wreck by herself, much less recover whatever cargo the vessel might have carried.$B$BIf you have time, you may want to check up on her out at Beezil\'s Wreck, due east of here, near the mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So those hermit mages sent you? How can I be sure that I can trust you?$B$BI suppose I can use the help. There\'s not much here a mage would be interested in, anyway.' WHERE `entry`=27346;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, it does look a little cleaner out there...$B$BI suppose it\'s time to get down to the business of salvaging this wreckage.' WHERE `entry`=27347;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow! You certainly found a lot more than I expected would be out there. I\'m not sure how much Drazzit thought we were going to find out here, but he\'s going to have to be happy with this for now.' WHERE `entry`=27348;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Dreadwatch is lost? This is bad, $N. Real bad. If Dreadwatch is compromised it means we\'ve lost Gilneas City.' WHERE `entry`=27349;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Th... Af... After we lost Gilneas City, the port fell. HU... HUM... HUMANS ARE HERE! Reinforcements from Stormwind! They slaughtered my men. Left me alive to witness their strength. To tell high command... To tell them that the 7th Legion are here...' WHERE `entry`=27350;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It was quite an honor to receive the commission for your weapon, $N. When Tony mentioned using so many exotic materials, I had my doubts, but it seems you managed to find them all. This will be a fine reward for all you\'ve done for the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=27351;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! I think the holy water will prove devastating in large volumes.' WHERE `entry`=27352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have rarely had the chance to work with such exotic materials, but even I can sense the power residing within them. I will have the honor of crafting an incredible weapon for you, $N. The farseer did not underestimate your abilities when she told me about you.' WHERE `entry`=27353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, I have been expecting you, $N. Maginor Dumas has spoken highly of you and the royal commission only confirms his words. It is an honor to be able to craft a staff for you.' WHERE `entry`=27354;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I won\'t ask what you had to do to come by such rare and powerful materials, but I\'m glad to have the chance to work with them. Your weapon will be magnificent!' WHERE `entry`=27355;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you must be the $C Loganaar was talking about. It is a pleasure to finally meet you. Loganaar and other members of the circle speak highly of you. It will be an honor to make a weapon for such a $C.' WHERE `entry`=27356;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is embarrassing to have been kidnapped by Arnak again. I heard the fighting outside. Did you kill him? I am happy to be free once more. Now, how can I help you, $R?' WHERE `entry`=27357;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is embarrassing to have been kidnapped by Arnak again. I heard the fighting outside. Did you kill him? I am happy to be free once more. Now, how can I help you, $C?' WHERE `entry`=27358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh my... the banshees are very tortured souls indeed. Merely holding their essence is emotionally painful... Enough of that for now. I\'ll get to work on counteracting their magic, then we\'ll have a portal up and running in no time. Stratholme will be ours soon, I just know it.' WHERE `entry`=27359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Though we were shamed in battle, the enemy was not victorious. I will not soon forget this, $N. If I make it back to Silverpine I will likely retire from the service. War is not in my blood.' WHERE `entry`=27360;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t believe you managed to get all those materials. I wouldn\'t think of venturing into Shadowfang Keep! The stories about that place are horrific. Enough of that, though. This is a time to recognize your achievements, not prattle on about my silly fears.' WHERE `entry`=27361;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t believe you managed to get all those materials. I wouldn\'t think of venturing into Shadowfang Keep! The stories about that place are horrific. Enough of that, though. This is a time to recognize your achievements, not prattle on about my silly fears.' WHERE `entry`=27362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t believe you managed to get all those materials. I wouldn\'t think of venturing into Shadowfang Keep! The stories about that place are horrific. Enough of that, though. This is a time to recognize your achievements, not prattle on about my silly fears.' WHERE `entry`=27363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' An Alliance armada is en route? How could this have happened? You\'ve got to hurry, $N. We\'re being overrun up here at Forward Command.' WHERE `entry`=27364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Grezz Ragefist told me to expect you. Those materials will make a fine sword. Always use it for the glory of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dead? By the dozen? It\'s a start, $C. It\'s a start.' WHERE `entry`=27366;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Tarenar?  Is that you? Whoever you are, would you mind helping me out of this thing?' WHERE `entry`=27367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re back?!  Thank the Light! Before you throw that acid on me, I need to ask: Are you the guy who was here before, or are you one of those eight-legged cowards?  I need to know whether or not I should smack you on my way out.' WHERE `entry`=27368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll tear that pint-size paladin to shreds before he... wait a minute are those Banshee\'s Bells?  You brought these for me? Oh, Gidwin asked you to get them for me!  That sweet little guy. Alright. He\'s off the hook for now.' WHERE `entry`=27369;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve found them, $R. The Scourge. How I\'ve longed for this day.' WHERE `entry`=27370;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Five should be good enough. Yikes, look at the time!  I need to head back to camp.' WHERE `entry`=27371;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why, this is exactly what I needed!  Fine, I\'ll forgive Tarenar for running off. $N, you\'re welcome to join us anytime.' WHERE `entry`=27372;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hope the ride wasn\'t too bumpy for you. Have a look around the tower while the horses rest. It\'s no Light\'s Hope Chapel, but I\'m sure you can find some way to keep yourself busy.' WHERE `entry`=27373;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, brotha. You\'ve chosen a harsh time to be joinin\' us, but that is to our fortune. We could use ya help.' WHERE `entry`=27374;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Save Earthmender Duarn',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Save Stormcaller Mylra' WHERE `entry`=27374;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, brotha. You\'ve chosen a harsh time to be joinin\' us, but that is to our fortune. We could use ya help.' WHERE `entry`=27375;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The tentacles swept us off of our gryphons as well! They were far more nimble than we anticipated. No matter. We were prepared for this possibility. I can summon the elemental from here if you can keep me safe.' WHERE `entry`=27376;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ve brought you back from the brink of death, hero! Deathwing is upon us! We need your help.' WHERE `entry`=27377;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re awake! Thank the elements. I\'d almost lost all hope.' WHERE `entry`=27378;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='United with the Earthen Ring, we can survive the horrors of Iso\'rath. Now it is time to turn our vengeance upon him!' WHERE `entry`=27379;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Save Earthmender Duarn',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Save Stormcaller Mylra' WHERE `entry`=27379;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You saved many of my closest allies today, $N. I can only imagine what horrors you witnessed within Iso\'rath, but you have the thanks of all of the Earthen Ring.' WHERE `entry`=27380;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Argus Highbeacon... that old guy on the top of the tower?  Great! A man his age must have been in the Argent Crusade for a long time. Maybe he can put in the good word for us at Light\'s Hope.' WHERE `entry`=27381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Of course a young $R like you would have no trouble taking care of a few wild animals. With the roads clear, my journey to the next tower will be much easier.' WHERE `entry`=27382;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello. I\'m Pamela, what\'s your name?' WHERE `entry`=27383;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found it! You found my doll! Oh, thank you!' WHERE `entry`=27384;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve seen Pamela?  She\'s alive? She\'s dead?  No!  Oh, Pamela!  Why does your spirit still suffer in this world?  Why are you perished, while fortune keeps me alive?  In an instant I would switch places with you and wander dead Darrowshire, a ghost and alone! Ah, but this news cannot change fate. Thank you, $N. Now my duty, my duty to revenge, burns hot as ever. Say, what is that sword you have there?' WHERE `entry`=27385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What is this?  A warsword?  A butter knife?  I\'m useless when it comes to blades. Let me see... Ah!  This sword was once in the hand of a great man, but there is much tragedy in that man\'s past. Are you here to help him?  It\'s far too late for him now... but perhaps we can help him in the past!' WHERE `entry`=27386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found them!  Well done, $N!  These relics hold within them the memories of the Scourge forces at Darrowshire. We will need these if we are to save your Joseph Redpath.' WHERE `entry`=27387;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have the relics?  Good. I will get to work on resolving any temporal discontinuities. Don\'t worry... that\'s not something you have to worry about. You just gather the reagents.' WHERE `entry`=27388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. Are you certain you haven\'t done this before?' WHERE `entry`=27389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The fighting is over!  I heard my daddy whisper to me. He scared away all the ghosts and he says he\'s coming home!  I\'m so happy!$B$BHe also said I should welcome you if came to our house, so I made some tea!$B$BI hope you like lots of sugar!' WHERE `entry`=27390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The key fits the lock, and the chest opens...' WHERE `entry`=27391;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s my daddy\'s sword!  How did you find it?  Did you find the bad hunter?' WHERE `entry`=27392;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Wavespeaker was right. There\'s something here.' WHERE `entry`=27393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Wavespeaker was right. There\'s something here.' WHERE `entry`=27394;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m honored that the warchief chose me to craft a weapon for you, $N. With such exotic materials, it will be a very fine bow.' WHERE `entry`=27395;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gordul told me that you would be bringing a variety of unusual materials, but I didn\'t expect anything like this. Moonsteel is said to be very rare and there\'s only one place I know to get it. You have risked much for this weapon, $N, and I\'ll see to it that you receive a fitting reward.' WHERE `entry`=27396;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The elements and spirits speak to you with clear voices, $N. You have become a powerful shaman and an example to others wishing to serve the Horde.$B$BWord has even reached the warchief, and he has commissioned his personal smith to forge a special weapon for you.$B$BThe cursed Shadowfang Keep in Silverpine Forest is the only place to get the materials you\'ll need. Travel there and obtain Lord Walden\'s talisman, the Book of Lost Souls, and essence from the ghosts haunting the keep.',`objectives_loc1`='Go to Shadowfang Keep and obtain Walden\'s Talisman from Lord Walden, the Book of Lost Souls, and 5 Ghostly Essence.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you must be $N. Kardris said that you were venturing to Shadowfang Keep to find the materials needed for this weapon and I see that you have not disappointed. I will make you a mighty weapon worthy of what you have brought.' WHERE `entry`=27397;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your aid is most timely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27398;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your aid is most timely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27399;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you must be the $C that Uthel\'nay mentioned. I\'ve heard tales about the artifacts the Silverlaine family once kept, but I haven\'t ever seen one. This should make an excellent focus for your staff. Let\'s get started.' WHERE `entry`=27400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' TORPEDOED! We had everything at the water line covered, but nothing below the line. They must have snuck in beneath our defenses and then blown our warships to smithereens. And now the rest of the Alliance fleet is nearly here...' WHERE `entry`=27401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you are the $C who will receive this staff. It will be a fitting reward for one so dedicated to the pursuit of power and the ascendancy of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I haven\'t worked with the Sunwalkers before, but from all I\'ve heard, the warchief holds you in high regard. It was a great honor to be asked to forge this weapon for you and I hope it will serve you well.' WHERE `entry`=27403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you must be the $C Loganaar was talking about. It is a pleasure to finally meet you, $N. I\'ve often heard members of the circle describe you as a talented and promising $C and I\'m heartened to see their estimations were correct.' WHERE `entry`=27404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Forward Commander Onslaught fought until the bitter end, $N. It took a pack of bloodthirsty worgen to finally bring him down. We must not let his death, or the death of all of our soldiers in Gilneas, go in vain. Our mission MUST succeed. Now I will reveal to you why we are here.' WHERE `entry`=27405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Here we are, $N. He is a little rotted, but no worse for the wear. We must hurry before the Alliance finds us!' WHERE `entry`=27406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Brogg pleased with these feathers. Very strong magic. Brogg not know what raptors do to give feathers power, but raptor feathers always best for ritual.' WHERE `entry`=27407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have Brogg\'s thanks, $N. Brogg has big plans for clan banner.' WHERE `entry`=27408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have Brogg\'s thanks, $N. Once Brogg adds their magic to the totem, it will be able to redeem the spirits of Brogg\'s fallen friends.' WHERE `entry`=27409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brogg thanks you for your help, although he knows Overlord Mok\'Morokk never will. At least surviving Stonemaul can finally focus on problems with the living and leave dead where they belong. Only one thing remains for Brogg to do.' WHERE `entry`=27410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Brogg know Onyxia dead. Brogg know her brood still there. Brogg not let them forget the Stonemaul. Brogg is grateful for your help, $N, and he will never forget what you have done for him. Brogg will never give up his quest to bring Stonemaul back where they belong.' WHERE `entry`=27411;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank goodness someone\'s finally taken me up on that offer. I was just thinking that I might need to triple the reward to get that stupid raptor killed, and our budget couldn\'t afford that!' WHERE `entry`=27412;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you! This will help keep our guys going out in the field until Moxie returns with the rest of the supplies from the zeppelin crash.' WHERE `entry`=27413;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='\'Twas a perilous affair, no doubt, collecting all of these hearts and tongues. I shall delve into the depths of the arcane to trace the origin of the black menace which has descended upon our former home.' WHERE `entry`=27414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Splendid! It will be sometime before Onyxia can produce more eggs.$B$BOn behalf of my people, I thank you, $N.$B$BI have asked much of you so far. Perhaps you can do the Stonemaul Clan one last service.$B$BMok\'Morokk is not fit to lead us. Tharg would make an excellent leader but is hindered by his injuries and age. Drive Mok\'Morokk from this place by force. Only then can we appoint a new leader to return us to our proper home in the south.' WHERE `entry`=27415;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Why you tell me \'bout dragons? Me no like dragons. Me like it here. No dragons here.' WHERE `entry`=27416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That lazy coward!$B$BMok\'Morokk displayed strength when Rexxar was our leader. But soon after Rexxar\'s departure Mok\'Morokk fell prey to temptations of power. Rather than lead, he demanded. He does not serve his people but rather expects us to serve him.$B$BSomething must be done.' WHERE `entry`=27417;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That cowardly fat mass Mok\'Morokk fled like a scared child. You have done a great service, $N.$B$BNow my people can appoint a new leader, one who will help us reclaim our old home once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=27418;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The sooner those Scourge are pushed out of the Fungal Vale, the sooner we can heal it. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Even if the flowers died out shortly after they bloomed, they proved our point to the Scourge: they are losing, and we are winning. Thank you for your assistance.' WHERE `entry`=27421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What a relief it is to see an able-bodied soldier that\'s on our side! There\'s plenty for ye to do around here, $R.' WHERE `entry`=27422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No time to bask in the battle glory, $N. We have a job to do. I have no doubt more of those beasts are on the way.' WHERE `entry`=27423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You good $R. Me miss things very much. Me like you now.' WHERE `entry`=27424;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Captain Vimes thinks the Grimtotems are behind the destruction of the Shady Rest Inn? They wouldn\'t have been first on my list of suspects, but if Captain Vimes sent you here to follow up on a lead, he must have his reasons. Regardless, the Grimtotems have been a thorn in our side for some time and we\'re always glad to have the extra help.' WHERE `entry`=27425;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'d say it doesn\'t get any clearer than this. They\'ve taken it upon themselves to fight back against human settlements in the area and I have little doubt Theramore is next on their list.' WHERE `entry`=27426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' There\'s no doubt about it. These match the description exactly, but there\'s just one problem -- these have never been used in battle. Blackhoof Village must not be the only Grimtotem post in the marsh.' WHERE `entry`=27427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you want me to scry for Grimtotems, eh? And what will you say when I tell you there\'s no need?' WHERE `entry`=27428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope the Grimtotems got the message. Any attempt to return will be met with far worse than a mere torch. My apprentices and I will see to that.' WHERE `entry`=27429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' We have avenged James and his family, but not even that can restore what was destroyed.' WHERE `entry`=27430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Talk about bringing the house down...' WHERE `entry`=27431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great, you got him!  And I hope you taught his gang a lesson too!' WHERE `entry`=27432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh aye, tha\'s the stuff! A good engineer can make anything outta just about anything. This here doo-jicker could recouple a busted cylinder casing... Oh! And who doesn\'t want a dongle? ...And you can fashion this jobby into a ... thing. Yep, perfect.' WHERE `entry`=27433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I don\'t know how you came by such a large supply of moonsteel, $N, but I haven\'t worked with it in years. It will be both a challenge and a pleasure to create this weapon for you.' WHERE `entry`=27434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Seer Liwatha mentioned that you were visiting Shadowfang Keep to find the materials for your new staff. I see now why she sent you there. Even the twisted magics gripping the keep could not extinguish the power of these items.' WHERE `entry`=27435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Shadow-Walker Zuru mentioned that you were visiting Shadowfang Keep to find the materials for your new staff. Artifacts from the keep are reputed to possess much hidden power and your efforts are proof that the tales are true. Your staff will be a masterwork.' WHERE `entry`=27436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dark Cleric Cecille mentioned that you were visiting Shadowfang Keep to find the materials for your new staff. I see now why she sent you there. Even the twisted magics gripping the keep could not extinguish the power of these items.' WHERE `entry`=27437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I had no doubt that you would succeed, $N. I hope you can understand why I kept the true purpose of your mission a secret. Should Crowley and Bloodfang have found out about our plan, they would have surely gotten to Godfrey first and disposed of the body. Stand by, $N. The time of their rebirth is at hand.' WHERE `entry`=27438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Tyelis mentioned that you were visiting Shadowfang Keep to find the materials for your new staff. Few would venture into the keep, even to retrieve such valuable things. Your new staff will be a fitting reward for your bravery.' WHERE `entry`=27439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Pardon my saying so, but I am surprised you completed the task set out before you alive. Those monsters were responsible for the deaths of countless thousands, a great many of them heroes still spoken highly of to this day. You have earned my respect and a reward for your courage.' WHERE `entry`=27440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You must be the $C that Brother Silverhallow mentioned. Welcome, $N. Let me see those materials you gathered from halfway around the world. They seem well worth the travel and you will not be disappointed with your staff.' WHERE `entry`=27441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your aid is most timely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your aid is most timely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You saw Nefarian when you fought Rend?$B$B<Acride sighs.>$B$BI wish I had accompanied you, then. I could have faced him unaware, outside his lair...but no matter. Nefarian will die by my claw.$B$BYou\'ve done well.' WHERE `entry`=27444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! It is only a matter of time before the son of Deathwing feels my claws.' WHERE `entry`=27445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Greetings and salutations, friend. Welcome to Tanaris!' WHERE `entry`=27446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well hello there, $C. Welcome to Tanaris!' WHERE `entry`=27447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve enjoyed having you ride with us, $N. Hopefully, once Gidwin and Tarenar join the Argent Crusade, we can continue to travel together.' WHERE `entry`=27448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, you are indeed strong... and I submit to you. I will join you and your friend, the worgen. My strength is yours.' WHERE `entry`=27449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... they didn\'t survive the trip out of the water as well as I had hoped. Oh well!  Seafood salad for Frederick tonight!' WHERE `entry`=27450;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello!  It\'s me. Hope you don\'t mind a little home-brewed magic to allow me to communicate with you in the field. It\'ll save us both some time. We\'re going to incorporate that living rot into a mixture that\'ll ruin their next batch of plague. That\'ll show them!' WHERE `entry`=27451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve got both pieces!  Good. These will help when trying to sneak into their death camp.' WHERE `entry`=27452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Uh oh... it looks like we may have gathered a little too much coagulated rot. Oh well, we\'ll just have to improvise, then! What could possibly go wrong?' WHERE `entry`=27453;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It should take them weeks to get their operation running again. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t believe it. We\'re literally FEET away from becoming sworn members of the Argent Crusade. We\'d be in there already if it weren\'t for Tarenar\'s dallying. If he doesn\'t quit chatting with the locals soon, I\'m going to head in there myself.' WHERE `entry`=27455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='May the Earthmother watch over you! Bless you, young one.' WHERE `entry`=27456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You brought us a shaman!  From the Earthen Ring, no less! I have no idea how we\'ll fit him in the caravan, but we\'ll find a way. Welcome aboard, Rimblat Earthshatter!' WHERE `entry`=27457;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well well well!  Someone who goes and gets things done!  Here\'s your cut, chief. I\'ll be seein\' you around.' WHERE `entry`=27458;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A $C!  Just what we needed. Your arrival couldn\'t have been more timely.' WHERE `entry`=27459;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The flare is fully assembled, and the matches lie unused next to the fuse. The fallen Argent centurion got much closer to setting off this flare than you had guessed.' WHERE `entry`=27460;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well met, $N. Can I trust you to assist me in taking this abbey away from these abominations?' WHERE `entry`=27461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll be handling things from here, $C. Fine, you want an assignment?  I suppose I can afford to send you in on a mission or two.' WHERE `entry`=27462;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Light\'s Hope Chapel. You wish to join the Crusade?  Very well. We have plenty of tasks for new recruits. But first, a test.' WHERE `entry`=27463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Remember that your ancestors always watch over you. As a brother of the Argent Crusade, you will join a family that has a long line of such fallen ancestors. Their vigil and protection will be your strength as you press forward against the Scourge. Congratulations Tarenar, Gidwin, and $N. Welcome to the Argent Crusade.' WHERE `entry`=27464;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve returned sooner than I expected. Excellent. We will continue our path into the north. Next, you will be completing a similar task - this time, in Northdale.' WHERE `entry`=27465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello, $N!  Glad to see you\'ve rejoined the caravan! Tarenar and Gidwin arrived here before you. Tarenar\'s just right there, and Gidwin\'s... well... he\'s in a little bit of a mood right now. I think he\'s in the tower.' WHERE `entry`=27466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our duty for the day is done. It is only a matter of time before we defeat the Scourge. Today, we made progress.' WHERE `entry`=27467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yep, one more tank limpin\' back home for repairs. All these trees an\' stumps an\' mud an\' rock - you couldnae drive a golfball into this turf, much less a tank. We\'re gonna need a new approach.' WHERE `entry`=27468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Oi, what\'re ye doin\' here in my camp? Bloody hell, why\'re ye in the Burnin\' Steppes at all? *hic*$B$BBah, it don\'t matter anyway.$B$BListen, I was adventurin\' the other day, as I often do, an\' I was ambushed by orcs from Blackrock Mountain! \'Cept one of \'em was different...dressed all funny an\' spoke all sophisticated like. Called hisself Acride, I think...$B$BYou ought to go to the Blackrock Spire and find that orc...just be watchin\', pretty much all of the others will want t\' kill ya. Tell him I sent ye!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello, what is your business in a place like this? I\'m sorry, who sent you? I\'m afraid I\'ve never heard of such a dwarf.' WHERE `entry`=27469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello, what is your business in a place like this? So Overseer Oilfist sent you? Listen carefully, we have much to discuss in little time.' WHERE `entry`=27470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello, what is your business in a place like this? So you come at the will of Miss Brightwing, do you? Very interesting indeed.' WHERE `entry`=27471;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Today marks a new beginning for the Forsaken and the end of the Alliance in Lordaeron!' WHERE `entry`=27472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good that you\'ve come, $N. We need all the help we can get with the situation here.' WHERE `entry`=27473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Clever mages. The codex is sealed by a magical ward. Pity that they weren\'t clever enough to realize that former archmages of Dalaran are now Forsaken.' WHERE `entry`=27474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The magi of Ambermill have employed foul magic to keep us away. Elemental servitors created with immunities that we cannot breach protect their territory.$B$BVenture east to Ambermill and slay the unyielding elemental servitors that guard the town and recover their cores. Bring their cores back to me so that I may devise a method by which we are able to destroy them all!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. The praise the Banshee Queen lavishes upon you is apparently not unfounded.' WHERE `entry`=27475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Dark Lady requires my expertise? Well of course! Give it here, boy.' WHERE `entry`=27476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Keep this up and I may have to keep you here at Eastwall, $R.' WHERE `entry`=27477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect. I hope this wasn\'t too much trouble to come by, $N. Relios was a pupil of mine back when I was a mortal man thereby making him a competent and formidable adversary. I suppose I could have warned you ahead of time. Now, let us see the ring. There we are...' WHERE `entry`=27478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, hallelujah, and praise, praise be to the Light, my brother!' WHERE `entry`=27479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Smart boy! I can most definitely use these arcane remnants in my studies. Indeed, Dalaran was built upon a massive ley line. It\'s no wonder, then, that such things exist at the crater.' WHERE `entry`=27480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My duty is not over yet. In many ways, this was the easy step.' WHERE `entry`=27481;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thought for sure that with the death of a dozen of my most hated enemies I would feel a great burden lifted from my shoulders. Sadly, I do not feel a thing. Perhaps I am a psychopath.' WHERE `entry`=27483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Only one may enter? I know just the person for this mission. I will prepare our forces and have them at the ready.' WHERE `entry`=27484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad Lira didn\'t scare you off. I won\'t say her concerns aren\'t warranted, but we have a common enemy. She is perhaps a bit overzealous.' WHERE `entry`=27485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad Lira didn\'t scare you off. I won\'t say her concerns aren\'t warranted, but we have a common enemy. She is perhaps a bit overzealous.' WHERE `entry`=27486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I couldn\'t stop him. While you and Tarenar were out, Giddy ran north all alone! Tarenar, you should have known better!  Gidwin gets so impatient sometimes, and you only egg him on. If Giddy gets into any trouble, I\'m blaming you for this.' WHERE `entry`=27487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You didn\'t see him?  Where could he have gone then? His... his prayer book?  Why would he leave that behind? Oh... By the Light, what have I done?' WHERE `entry`=27488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Time is wasting, $N. Every minute we waste gives the Scourge another chance to kill Gidwin. If he isn\'t dead already. Not that I think he is. Giddy may be a stick-in-the-mud, but when it comes down to it, he can swing the Light like a champion.' WHERE `entry`=27489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That must have been deadly. While I don\'t approve of their methods, no one can question the effectiveness of Master Mathias Shaw and his SI:7. Not to mention that you\'re here. Our victory is all but assured.' WHERE `entry`=27490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That must have been exciting. Despite any losses that the Kor\'kron may have incurred along the way, no one will be able to doubt their effectiveness, nor that of Garona. And with you in the mix, it\'s only a matter of time before victory is ours.' WHERE `entry`=27491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='As with any offensive, you first need to soften them up. We\'ve been having a heck of a time getting in there. But someone like you... well, let\'s just say I have no doubt in my mind that you can get into the Twilight Gate to the southwest and teach the Bloodeye Clan ogres and ettins a thing or two!',`objectives_loc1`='Slay 10 ogres or ettins at the Twilight Gate.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s the spirit, lad! Today\'s already shaping up to be a good one.' WHERE `entry`=27492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I want you to get in there past those boulders to the northwest at the Twilight Gate. Kill every Bloodeye Clan ogre and ettin in sight. Think you can handle that for me, $N?',`objectives_loc1`='Slay 10 Bloodeye Clan ogres or ettins at the Twilight Gate.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='And here I thought that today couldn\'t get any better. I enjoy being wrong, occasionally.' WHERE `entry`=27493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks to you, our cannoneers hit their marks. Tell me about the situation within the Twilight Gate.' WHERE `entry`=27496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Southwestern building targeted',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Southern building targeted' WHERE `entry`=27496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I must say that I rather enjoyed the sight of their buildings being hit.' WHERE `entry`=27497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Southwestern building targeted',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Southern building targeted' WHERE `entry`=27497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' That\'s quite a gruesome trophy collection you have there. I would have believed you if you had simply said they were dead. Regardless, thank you for having the foresight to take care of them. The Twilight Gate will soon be ours. Time to move up to the Twilight Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=27500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' That\'s quite a gruesome trophy collection you have there. I would have believed you if you had simply said they were dead, though I do appreciate the extra effort. Thank you for having the foresight to take care of them. The Twilight Gate will soon be ours. Time to move up to the Twilight Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=27501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Calen has become very trusting. It is not often that strangers are permitted within the redoubt.' WHERE `entry`=27504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We will take Grim Batol back from the Twilight\'s Hammer and thier allies. It may take time, but this is one charge that we cannot forsake.' WHERE `entry`=27505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$R, I have a task for you.$B$BTake these ruby seeds and plant them at the corpses of any dragonkin that you come across. Twilight or Vermillion, whelping or dragon, it matters not. We need to see that their bodies are returned to the earth so that life can continue to flourish.$B$BIn death, there should always be new life. This may be our one consolation during times of war and great tragedy.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='In this, we deny Deathwing the destruction that he so passionately seeks. In this, life continues.' WHERE `entry`=27506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have a talent for killing I see. In times like these, that has its place.' WHERE `entry`=27507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I don\'t know if you did this for me or the young inside these eggs, but it doesn\'t really matter, either way it\'s clear that you want to be an ally of our flight. I appreciate that. I cannot forgive the attacks by your allies against my brood, but for now, it seems you have chosen the right side.' WHERE `entry`=27508;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. Thank you, $R. I will not be so foolish as to let such an oversight happen again.' WHERE `entry`=27509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I only hope that we don\'t end up getting beat down by inconspicuous birds, cats and trees next... or seals. Could you imagine it?' WHERE `entry`=27510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your exploration of the Chamber of the Stars has yielded more questions than answers...' WHERE `entry`=27511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Yes, this is it. Now run the ring along the runes of the portal and you should become attuned for transdimensional travel.' WHERE `entry`=27512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Excellent work, $N. Now to eject them into our waiting hands!' WHERE `entry`=27513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aw dang crap it all. You\'re just an Alliance $C. I was hoping for a rescue.' WHERE `entry`=27514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, that\'s the stuff all right! Hope ya didn\'t eat any. Gives you the cramps something awful but it does wonders for birds.' WHERE `entry`=27515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N! Aiding that downed gryphon-rider has given us our first contact with the old Wildhammer clans. We\'ll be able to find out who\'s still left, and in what numbers. Our campaign is looking up!' WHERE `entry`=27516;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, rope! Thanks, kid. Something tells me I\'m going to need this.' WHERE `entry`=27517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Had I not witnessed what you did with my own eyes I would not have believed it, $N. Now, with the Ambermill magi on our side, there is but one thing left to do before we retake Gilneas and send those Alliance dogs running for Stormwind.' WHERE `entry`=27518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N. Orsis was punished for not joining the forces of Deathwing. Prince Nadun has offered my people refuge in his city. I must go there and tend the survivors.' WHERE `entry`=27519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You continue to prove to be a valuable ally, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='$R... please, I ask your help.$B$BSomething\'s happened to my people. Our commander, Ranger Lord Hawkspear, came upon an item of magical energy, and my friends, my family... they succumbed to its seductive power.$B$BThey\'re corrupted, $R. All of them.$B$BMy Ellaria wouldn\'t want to live like that, nor would any of my brothers. Please, put them out of their misery. Quel\'lithien Lodge is not far; it\'s just up the hill, to the northwest.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do not feel sorry for me. Those were my friends that you saw at Quel\'lithien Lodge, but they were already as good as dead.' WHERE `entry`=27521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It sounds like you were successful. Hopefully this is enough information to find Gidwin.' WHERE `entry`=27522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Duskwing, Oh How I Hate Thee...',`details_loc1`='I have seen many things in my day, $R. The peaks of Mt. Hyjal... the oddities of Outland... a wall of Scourge soldiers, proceeding into war. But I have never seen a bat as big, or as shockingly white, as Duskwing.$B$BHow he taunts me from his roost!$B$BThis albino demon bat circles to the southwest of here, due north of Blackwood Lake. Track him down and destroy him. If he flies too high for you to reach, use my flare to get his attention.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work. I can now continue my work without the distractions of that great white beast. I shall fashion this fur into something you can use.' WHERE `entry`=27523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I haven\'t found anything but brainless undead, and plenty of them. I was just about to kill my way into Stratholme when you arrived. Did you have any more success?' WHERE `entry`=27524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve got to keep moving!  We\'re getting so very close!' WHERE `entry`=27525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have no idea how happy I am to see you two!  You\'re a sight for sore eyes... sore eyes that have been starin\' through a banshee for far too long now. I\'m sorry for causing so much trouble. Will you take me back to the caravan?' WHERE `entry`=27526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Speak with Fiona at Light\'s Hope Chapel in Eastern Plaguelands.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve been more help than anyone expected of you, $N. The doors of my caravan are always open to you. The boys and I have even put together a little something special for you. Here, take your pick!' WHERE `entry`=27527;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A blessed fire cleanses even the most corrupt of flesh. They stood no chance in the face of the Light.' WHERE `entry`=27528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good to hear you found the tortured souls of my brethren and freed them. I find my strength renewed, knowing at least some of the defenders of Darrowshire no longer wallow in the vile subservience of the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=27529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a true Champion of the Light, $N. I wish you luck in your future endeavors, wherever they might take you. If you need anything in the future, you can always find me here - knee-deep in the corpses of the slain.' WHERE `entry`=27530;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I love the smell of fresh foot scrapings, don\'t you? If we\'re going to find a cure to the plague, we need to get creative with our ingredients. Now, if you don\'t mind, I\'m going to get back to work.' WHERE `entry`=27531;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Whew. Every time Argus comes plodding through that Plaguewood, I fear it to be his last. It\'s good to see that he\'s wise enough to send a youngblood like you in his stead.' WHERE `entry`=27532;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see them!  Can you?  The little pig spirits, on their way to the great sty in the sky...' WHERE `entry`=27533;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There it is! And oh my! I forgot how full it was!$B$BThis is a glorious day, $N! Stupendous! Insanely good, I say!' WHERE `entry`=27534;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve come to the right place, mister!  No place better than Terrordale, yes siree, that\'s right!  The jewel of Lordaeron!' WHERE `entry`=27535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What did I tell you, eh? Perfectly safe! I\'ll see about getting some of these over to to your friends, $N. At a discount.' WHERE `entry`=27536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My word, $N. These elemental energies are so powerful, so chaotic - no wonder the Twilight\'s Hammer has chosen to build their stronghold here! I should be able to channel these energies into something more benign and productive though. Let\'s give it a try...' WHERE `entry`=27537;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh... mud. You brought me mud? Wow - this stuff oozes with power! I see what Thordun was saying, now. I\'ll distribute this to all of the healers. Our wounded will be on their feet in no time!' WHERE `entry`=27538;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='May my pile never stop growing.' WHERE `entry`=27539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well met, $C. I am Gavan Grayfeather, emissary of the Wildhammer shaman. There is much work to be done. The leaders fear for their citizens, as many have turned to cults. We shaman are concerned with the elemental unrest. Our advice to you, $C, is to be vigilant. Help where you can, be it calming the people or putting the elementals at rest. There is plenty to do.' WHERE `entry`=27540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Odd... It looks as if someone used gemstones as lenses. I should be able to fix them without too much trouble.' WHERE `entry`=27541;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I suppose I had better work on my stealth, if you were able to find me. Are you interested in helping me heal the Plaguelands?' WHERE `entry`=27544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ho! I knew you were a $C I could count on, $N. Use that portal anytime you need to get from Stormwind back to the Highlands. Now then, time to get to business. We need to locate and unite the lost Wildhammer clans scattered around the Highlands. Talking with Thordun here is a good start!' WHERE `entry`=27545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='King\'s honor, $C. I am Captain Anton. I am leading the investigation into the cultists that have appeared in Stormwind.' WHERE `entry`=27546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What happened here today is between us. Say a word to anyone and you will find yourself in a corpse pit next to these poor fools.' WHERE `entry`=27547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I suspect we\'ll see fewer humans at the Battlefront. The risk for these cowards is too great.' WHERE `entry`=27548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, kid, it looks like you\'ve done it again. This starlight is exactly what we were missing. Now we can get to work!' WHERE `entry`=27549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The part of me that was Gilnean died at Tempest\'s Reach. Only vengeance remains, $N. To that end, we have work to do. Spare me your pointless queries.' WHERE `entry`=27550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is it!  If this missive is to be believed, then he\'s literally right over this hill! What are we waiting for, $N?' WHERE `entry`=27551;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Tarenar has laid a few holy talismans inside the caravan. They appear to be unused.$B$BThey appear to be magical in nature. If Tarenar isn\'t using them, what\'s the harm in borrowing one for a while?' WHERE `entry`=27557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope you\'re as tough as your gear suggests. The Twilight\'s Hammer have made their way within the redoubt somehow and I need someone to hunt them down.' WHERE `entry`=27564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I don\'t know how I\'m still alive. The patrols keep walking past me like I\'m not even here. ...Am I dead, $C?' WHERE `entry`=27565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good to see you, $N. Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=27566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see...she did not cooperate. Hopefully we can still stop them before something else terrible happens.' WHERE `entry`=27567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I would stay away from Oralius. Far, far, far away. He isn\'t quite right in the head. Now, let\'s get onto business!' WHERE `entry`=27568;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m sure you are up to the task I have for you if you\'ve made it this far in one piece. Between you and me, you may want to enjoy yourself in the Grim Guzzler while you\'re there. It could be the last drink you ever have.' WHERE `entry`=27569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Greetings, $C. The situation here is tense. The elements are restless and the people are scared and confused. The Warchief is trying to find a semblance of balance between leading the people and protecting Azeroth. Though it seems he will soon be leaving us to travel to Nagrand and gain insight about the elementals. Regardless of the Warchief\'s choice, we still must do what we can. Help calm the populace, scour the lands for rogue elementals. These tasks will surely help our cause.' WHERE `entry`=27570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Dark Irons took our Thunderbrew. I\'ll never let them live after that. I\'d kill \'em all myself if I could! However, look ahead and you\'ll see we have slightly more dire matters to attend to at the moment.' WHERE `entry`=27571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good to see you, $C. Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=27572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I cannot proceed any further alone, regardless of my combat experience. The Lyceum has proven too difficult for me. If you are here, though...you might be the key to all of this.' WHERE `entry`=27573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I know that face, $N. This head belongs to a former Gilnean known as Sean Dempsey. He was imprisoned with Crowley before the great outbreak. I wonder if it would be possible to put him back together. The rest of him must be in the belly of these crocolisks.' WHERE `entry`=27574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now let\'s see if I can do this. ...leg bone connects to the thigh bone... ...arm bone to torso... ...sprinkle on a little Forsaken necromancy... TA-DA!' WHERE `entry`=27575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got the dragons in the game! Good on you. We\'d already laid out plans for our ambush by the time the dragons contacted us. They\'re helping by cutting off their retreat. It\'s not too late for you to join in on the fun though. We saved some for you.' WHERE `entry`=27576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' It looks like the reinforcements from the ships in Gilneas are marching soon. Crowley and Bloodfang have set up an encampment to the southeast for the Gilneas Liberation front.' WHERE `entry`=27577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it! You\'ve actually done it! Morgan\'s years of planning and waiting have finally come to fruition. She may have lost her land and family when Ragnaros tore this land asunder, but with the Dark Iron crippled we\'ll be able to safely build a new kingdom of our own in the Burning Steppes. Not even the Firelord himself will be able to breech the capital\'s walls! Make sure you come back someday when we\'ve finished, you\'ll be our guest of the highest honor. I thank you with all my heart, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Get over here. If you blow my cover, I swear to the Warchief I\'ll kill you where you stand.' WHERE `entry`=27579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The rest of the Alliance fleet will arrive shortly, only to find their base camp decimated. Now for the second and most important part of our battle plan.' WHERE `entry`=27580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Twilight\'s Hammer\'s presence only complicates our mission here further, but you\'ve done your part for now. You\'ve earned a reward for your efforts...and some rest. Let\'s get out of here.' WHERE `entry`=27581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Beyond this door lies the commander of the Dark Iron Army, surrounded by trained soldiers. Are you up for a little killing?' WHERE `entry`=27582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Warlord Zaela sent you? Good. If you Horde are as strong as your Warchief promised, I expect to see some bloodshed on these shores.' WHERE `entry`=27583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You\'re a true fighter, $N. I liked watching you work. Perhaps the Dragonmaw really DO belong in your Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Up ahead is the Grim Guzzler. A disgusting bar full of all our enemies, intoxicated and therefore unfit for proper battle. Ripe for the slaughter.' WHERE `entry`=27585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh yeah. YEAH! These are DEFINITELY going to kill somebody. Probably naga.' WHERE `entry`=27586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can see it now: our own famous Bogpaddle Lobster-Poppers! Made fresh from the sea! Oh, it\'s like this stuff writes itself... Your help is very much appreciated, my friend. I\'ll start seeing if I can\'t cut your people a favorable arrangement, eh?' WHERE `entry`=27587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that you\'ve lured Skullcrusher the Mountain away from the Twilight Gate, I need you to signal our forces to attack!' WHERE `entry`=27588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hear quite the commotion coming from the Grim Guzzler. I see you\'ve been hard at work. If you\'ll direct your attention opposite me, you\'ll notice that we have bigger issues to worry about than toying with drunkards.' WHERE `entry`=27589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that you\'ve lured Skullcrusher the Mountain away from the Twilight Gate, I need you to signal our forces to attack!' WHERE `entry`=27590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I cannot proceed any further alone, regardless of my combat experience. The Lyceum has proven too difficult for me. If you are here, though...you might be the key to all of this.' WHERE `entry`=27591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our ice-cold, refreshing Silversnap Ice! I can\'t thank you enough, "dawg", for this entirely spontaneous act of heroism! Here, have your very own bottle as a totally sincere gesture of thanks! Be sure to tell ALL YOUR FRIENDS how good it is.' WHERE `entry`=27592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A true $C if I\'ve ever seen one! You\'ve done the impossible! I knew we could count on you. And with that, I\'d like for you to be the first to know that the Kargath Expeditionary Force is now officially back in business! I extend to you my personal gratitude for your efforts here. Remember always our motto: "First in, last out, always victorious. Remember always Kargath." You are dismissed.' WHERE `entry`=27593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done it! Finally, everything is in place. Should Crowley not accept our terms, his daughter will be turned.' WHERE `entry`=27594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Who... who are you?  Sent here... to rescue my people and fight our enemies.' WHERE `entry`=27595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have the heart! Amazing! It is even more beautiful than I imagined!$B$BPlease, $N, take this as payment!' WHERE `entry`=27596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Silversnap sent you?! I\'m DOOMED! Oh, he sent you to help me! That\'s different, haha!' WHERE `entry`=27597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll show those fish-faced freaks! Good work!' WHERE `entry`=27598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='WOW! I don\'t know why I said that. I\'m excitable! But man, there was a lot of stuff on these guys, check it out! Here, you want this?' WHERE `entry`=27599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My high-grade fuse! My imported blasting powder! And my--hello there! I\'ll just be taking that! Those are all worth more gold than what you\'re wearing, you know! Thanks for your help!' WHERE `entry`=27600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This... is not over. Godfrey and his traitorous allies will pay for what they have done as will the remaining Alliance forces occupying Lordaeron. Our work has only just begun.' WHERE `entry`=27601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Though the chest is locked, there is a plaque bearing interesting hieroglyphs above it.' WHERE `entry`=27602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Darn it! I simply HAVE to know what\'s behind that gate! This could be the discovery that makes my career, you know! Hmm....maybe a couple good explosions would do the trick...' WHERE `entry`=27603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent! I suspect that without Jammal\'an\'s leadership, the trolls will fall to infighting and Hakkar will never set his eyes upon our world.' WHERE `entry`=27604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You only defeated Eranikus\' Shade? This is most troubling... Let us hope that his full form does not still exist outside the Temple. Only Ysera herself is stronger than him in our flight.' WHERE `entry`=27605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Boom baby, boom! What? You killed the Fathom-Lord already? I suppose we should stop shelling his corpse, then.' WHERE `entry`=27606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good timing, $C. We were just about to unleash a counter-attack.' WHERE `entry`=27607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We\'re about to launch the attack upon the Twilight Gate, but there is one last loose end to tie up: Za\'brox and Beeble\'phod, the disciples of Cho\'gall.$B$BIntelligence has placed them within the Den of the Disciples, a small ogre cave at the southwest corner of the Twilight Gate.$B$BWould you go back in there and kill them?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' That\'s quite a gruesome trophy collection you have there. I would have believed you if you had simply said they were dead. Regardless, thank you for having the foresight to take care of them. The Twilight Gate will soon be ours. Time to move up to the Twilight Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=27608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now, while we\'re about to launch the attack upon the Twilight Gate, there is one last loose end to tie up: Za\'brox and Beeble\'phod, the disciples of Cho\'gall.$B$BIntelligence has placed them within the Den of the Disciples, a small ogre cave at the southwest corner of the Twilight Gate.$B$BPlease head back in and kill them.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' That\'s quite a gruesome trophy collection you have there. I would have believed you if you had simply said they were dead, though I do appreciate the extra effort. Thank you for having the foresight to take care of them. The Twilight Gate will soon be ours. Time to move up to the Twilight Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=27609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $C. Now you know the lay of the land. If you\'re ever having difficulty fighting here on the Twilight Shores, remember that capturing and holding the Beach Head will give all Horde forces here a combat advantage!' WHERE `entry`=27610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. Let them reap what they sow!' WHERE `entry`=27611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The abbey will fall shortly. We can soon move on, deeper into Tyr\'s Hand.' WHERE `entry`=27612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The death of Rohan eases my spirits a bit. I once fought beside him, you know. He was an emissary of the Scarlet Crusade; one of the few that deigned to join us in our battle against Kel\'thuzad, so many years ago. How quickly things change.' WHERE `entry`=27613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This battle was won before it started. Right now, we\'re just shooting for style points.$B$BWithin these barracks, the sniveling Scarlet Crusaders cling to their priceless artifacts, even though some of the objects are too holy for their now-undead hand to touch. So they keep them in chests, hidden from the world.$B$BYou will find these artifacts, and bring them back to me. They belong to be among the Argent Crusade. They belong in the hands of the righteous.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. I will deliver these to Tyrosus when we return.' WHERE `entry`=27614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are well on your way to becoming a true champion of the Light, $N. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=27615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='One less thing to worry about. Nice work up there.' WHERE `entry`=27616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, the abbey is ours. I never doubted Eligor\'s ability for a moment.' WHERE `entry`=27617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It sounds like Korfax really cleaned house over at the barracks. It\'s very much like him to show off like that.' WHERE `entry`=27618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, good. These barracks are as good as fallen.' WHERE `entry`=27619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='While I can\'t agree with their methods, I can\'t argue with their results. In many ways, the Scarlet were well-intentioned, but their zeal grew too strong, and their hate blinded them to reason. I only hope that the same doesn\'t happen to our Brotherhood of Light.' WHERE `entry`=27620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Come to join the patrol, lad? Glad to have ya. I need some bodies helpin\' to get our defenses under control here. Help me out and I\'ll see if I can\'t find some more prestigious work for ya.' WHERE `entry`=27621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s right baby! That\'s right! Cold steel and hot death! What should we name our new creation? The Gnugatron? No - better - the $N-o-matic. That\'s got a ring to it.' WHERE `entry`=27622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You place the two gems inside the sockets in the wall.' WHERE `entry`=27623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fine work, $N. It looks as though our work here is nearly complete.' WHERE `entry`=27624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Such aberrations in the face of the light... You are brave to face them, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27625;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank the Light. We will not let the Forsaken have anything that can be turned against us, no matter how small.' WHERE `entry`=27626;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Sapphire Scarabs Slain',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Turquoise Scarabs Slain' WHERE `entry`=27627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is just the beginning, $N. If Deathwing\'s minions can bury entire cities, we have little chance of defeating them through conventional means.' WHERE `entry`=27628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What manner of creature are you?  You will leave the king\'s lands before... Wait!  You are that $N I\'ve heard so much about. You must pardon my lack of hospitality. We have seen all manner of hostile intruders since the barrier around Uldum failed.' WHERE `entry`=27629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='War, you say. Divinations for war are always difficult. Some wars must never be fought, even if victory was assured. Some wars have to be waged even if defeat is certain.' WHERE `entry`=27630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No need to fill me in on the events in Orsis, $N. I\'ve heard about them already. And about you. Any enemy of Al\'Akir is a friend of mine.' WHERE `entry`=27631;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve obtained a map of the Vir\'Naal river delta.' WHERE `entry`=27632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have successfully stopped Hakkar here, but I fear we are far from done. The Atal\'ai transported most of the blood they produced to Zul\'Gurub, where the Hakkari work to summon The Blood God there. $N, I do not think that this was ever meant to be the place of Hakkar\'s arrival - it was merely a test to see if the blood was potent enough! Hakkar can only be summoned in Zul\'Gurub...and I fear we may be too late to stop the Hakkari with the blood they now have in their possession.' WHERE `entry`=27633;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There, now you\'re fit to head off to the surface and start your new life. The High Tinker will be delighted to hear of your arrival.' WHERE `entry`=27635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Where are the rest of my people?' WHERE `entry`=27636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='That\'s a blow to our efforts. Damn Cho\'gall!$B$BIt\'s a good thing that the squad commander told you where to find Master Shaw.' WHERE `entry`=27637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Where are the Kor\'kron?' WHERE `entry`=27638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='That\'s a heavy blow to our efforts. Damn that Cho\'gall!$B$BIt\'s a good thing that the squad commander told you where to find Garona.' WHERE `entry`=27639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If it\'s Dunwalds you be lookin\' for, it\'s Dunwalds you\'ve found. A couple of\'m anyway. I can\'t find me other brothers for the life of me.' WHERE `entry`=27640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that\'s what I\'m talkin\' about lad. My kinda $R.' WHERE `entry`=27641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That many dead, eh? Not seemin\' likely that anyone outside of me brothers fought through it then. I guess I already expected as much. Thanks for takin\' the time to look for me.' WHERE `entry`=27642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hi friend! I don\'t think I know you... I\'m Donnelly Dunwald. What\'s your name? I don\'t think I know you... Do I know you?' WHERE `entry`=27643;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Of all the buildings in all the towns to collapse, why\'d it have to be this one?!' WHERE `entry`=27644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well look at ya, all geared and fancy. Keely send you to keep an eye on old Cayden, eh? Won\'t be needin\' it. I got these louts handled. Hahah! They chose the wrong dwarf to be ambushin\' today! Ahahahahah!' WHERE `entry`=27645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found\'m! You found Beak! I like you, new friend! I\'m gonna go show Keely. Keely like Beak too.' WHERE `entry`=27646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Donnelly\'s belly! That\'s more like it. Good to not be dyin\' of the thirst again. Here, have some. Good ol\' Eoin\'s never so impolite as ta not share!' WHERE `entry`=27647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A thing of beauty, isn\'t it? An\' they keep comin\' back for more. Love it! I\'ll go find Keely and settle her nerves in a bit. Just one more go through the row.' WHERE `entry`=27648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Woooooh! That\'s exactly what my belly needs! You get me all the nice things.' WHERE `entry`=27649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for bandin\' my brothers back together. I know they\'re tough, but they\'re even tougher when they\'re side by side, and there\'s a lot of Twilight out there. You\'re good to put a gal\'s heart at ease.' WHERE `entry`=27650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for your help. You\'ve got a warrior\'s spirit in ya - you coulda fooled me for a Wildhammer if it weren\'t for your... well.. you know. I know Firebeard sent you to unite us. My love for that dwarf runs shallow, but you know now we\'ve got plenty of reasons to make enemies of Twilight. If you see him, tell him that when the battle starts, the Dunwald family will be there.' WHERE `entry`=27651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m not sure what I\'m going to do with all of these. I\'ll probably fence them and donate the proceeds to the Stormwind orphanage. Now to find someone sick enough to buy such a thing. It\'ll probably be a goblin. Or, a gnome warlock.' WHERE `entry`=27652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What do you think I should do with all of these? Maybe I\'ll melt them down and have the metal imbued into a new dagger that I can thrust into Cho\'gall\'s chest. Think there\'s time for that?' WHERE `entry`=27653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='None of us are too good to get our hands a little dirty. Or bloody, in this case.' WHERE `entry`=27654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Feels good to get a little blood on your hands, doesn\'t it? Especially when that blood belongs to such self-deluded fools.' WHERE `entry`=27655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='All taken care of? Good to hear. Takes a load off my mind. Now I can focus on proper business for the fine folk of Marshtide and Stonard, weary from the war... and all that junk.' WHERE `entry`=27656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! I\'m glad you\'re here. Of course, I\'m more than happy to lend you whatever assistance that I can.' WHERE `entry`=27657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N! I\'m glad you\'re here. Of course, I\'m more than willing to help you in any way that I can.' WHERE `entry`=27658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The last portal is deep within the mine here, but we\'ll deal with that in a bit.' WHERE `entry`=27659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I know why you are here, $N. Your reasons sing within your fluids. I know about the dead dwarf forgesmith polluting my lake. If you want to find out what his corpse remembers, you must earn it.' WHERE `entry`=27660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am pleased. Lord Cannon was always an unworthy adversary. Very well, $R, I will help you gain the information which you seek.' WHERE `entry`=27661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'d I tell you? Elementals aren\'t so bad after all, eh?' WHERE `entry`=27662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, good, good! Just what I needed.' WHERE `entry`=27663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that you have gathered all of the Ember cards together into a deck, a ninth card mysteriously appears with the same backing as the first eight. On this card is inscribed, "Return these cards to the Darkmoon Faire and be rewarded."   You have heard that this faire alternately stops at Mulgore and Goldshire every few months, so you will have to wait until they are here next.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you have put together a deck of Embers. Your gesture of returning it to us will create a tie between you and the Darkmoon that will not soon be forgotten. Allow me to present you with one of the greater Darkmoon cards as a small token of our appreciation.' WHERE `entry`=27664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that you have gathered all of the Wind cards together into a deck, a ninth card mysteriously appears with the same backing as the first eight. On this card is inscribed, "Return these cards to the Darkmoon Faire and be rewarded."   You have heard that this faire alternately stops at Mulgore and Goldshire every few months, so you will have to wait until they are here next.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you have put together a deck of Hurricanes. Your gesture of returning it to us will create a tie between you and the Darkmoon that will not soon be forgotten. Allow me to present you with one of the greater Darkmoon cards as a small token of our appreciation.' WHERE `entry`=27665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that you have gathered all of the Wave cards together into a deck, a ninth card mysteriously appears with the same backing as the first eight. On this card is inscribed, "Return these cards to the Darkmoon Faire and be rewarded."   You have heard that this faire alternately stops at Mulgore and Goldshire every few months, so you will have to wait until they are here next.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you have put together a Tsunami deck. Your gesture of returning it to us will create a tie between you and the Darkmoon that will not soon be forgotten. Allow me to present you with one of the greater Darkmoon cards as a small token of our appreciation.' WHERE `entry`=27666;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that you have gathered all of the Stone cards together into a deck, a ninth card mysteriously appears with the same backing as the first eight. On this card is inscribed, "Return these cards to the Darkmoon Faire and be rewarded."   You have heard that this faire alternately stops at Mulgore and Goldshire every few months, so you will have to wait until they are here next.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you have put together a deck of Earthquakes. Your gesture of returning it to us will create a tie between you and the Darkmoon that will not soon be forgotten. Allow me to present you with one of the greater Darkmoon cards as a small token of our appreciation.' WHERE `entry`=27667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sure enough... This looks to be something that Nazgrim will take quite an interest in.' WHERE `entry`=27668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, now. Would ya look at that! As amazing as this is, I am confident that there\'s more to our discovery than meets the eye... Much more.' WHERE `entry`=27669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. My men can take it from here. Let\'s focus on getting the other survivors out now.' WHERE `entry`=27670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I know Nevin will be pleased with all the survivors you managed to help. I still can\'t believe you managed to stay so strong down here in the radiation. You\'ve seen the shape the other survivors are in. Let\'s get you to the loading room for decontamination.' WHERE `entry`=27671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Don\'t worry about the chamber, my boys will check it out! You have more important things to do!' WHERE `entry`=27672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is incredible, $N. The power coursing through each core...the contrasting powers so close together! I\'ll take this to the proper dwarves right away. These cores are extremely important!' WHERE `entry`=27673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see you again, $N. Without your help, we wouldn\'t have been able to get so many survivors out of Gnomeregan this time. Everyone is going to be thrilled to meet you and hear your story.' WHERE `entry`=27674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fantastic! Great work! We\'ll know all that Dig Three has to tell us in no time at all!' WHERE `entry`=27676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, lad! Now go to the discs and learn all you can!' WHERE `entry`=27677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Reliquary agents are en route to investigate the chamber. You have more important matters to attend to.' WHERE `entry`=27679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a most reliable agent, $N. Proceed to the discs and learn all you can. Report back to me immediately after.' WHERE `entry`=27680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done. Dig Three and any secrets beyond that door will soon be ours and ours alone.' WHERE `entry`=27681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Both of these cores are still far more potent than most of the cores we use  to power our own protectors, and these are ancient devices! Thank you, these will prove extremely valuable to our society.' WHERE `entry`=27682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, finally... I don\'t know how much longer I can last!' WHERE `entry`=27685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s not much, but it\'s all I\'ve got down here. You\'re more than welcome to it, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That takes care of most of their leaders outside of the Bastion of Twilight. We work well together, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That takes care of most of their leaders outside of the Bastion. Not bad work, $N. Not bad at all.' WHERE `entry`=27689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Another mewling Horde whelp? Zaela saps our strength by diluting our forces with the weak. Very well, $C. Prove yourself to me, and show me what your Horde is made of.' WHERE `entry`=27690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have to wonder just what\'s out there. This is the coast of the Forbidding Sea, with nothing beyond its reaches... but all these fishy folk just stomped right out of it. What\'s more, I saw where they\'ve been going...' WHERE `entry`=27691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. As you can see, my mere presence here has resulted in a bloom of glorious life despite my mate\'s presence. Names aside, perhaps one day you will again venture into Desolace and find it a verdant oasis free of any traces of the Old Gods.' WHERE `entry`=27692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The jade statue becomes one again, and you place it in your pocket. You hear a shifting noise in the tomb\'s central chamber.' WHERE `entry`=27693;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The trolls that lurk within this temple have done grievious harm to my kind, $N. We were sent here to guard this place, and were instead used to unleash the terrible powers within.$B$BI must beg you for the help only a mortal can give. You can be my hand within the temple; should I enter by myself, I risk being turned against my brothers as well.$B$BWe shall make a pact. If you wish to help, first gather Atal\'ai artifacts from the waters around the temple, and return them to me.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The essence of the green dragonflight wafts from these artifacts; the vestiges of my corrupted kin. In purifying them, I form a bond between us. Step forward, $N, and receive the Oathstone of Ysera\'s Dragonflight.' WHERE `entry`=27694;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That thing looks sharp. Sharp enough to the do deed, at least. But if I\'m a judge of weaponry, that\'s not what Cho\'gall\'s after.' WHERE `entry`=27695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a very sharp axe. It\'ll do the job, but if I\'m any judge of weaponry, that\'s not what Cho\'gall\'s after.' WHERE `entry`=27696;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N! Eliminating Vyletongue\'s presence is a key step to freeing me and, ultimately, saving these lands from corruption. Take this as a token of my thanks and an incentive to continue your work here.' WHERE `entry`=27697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Without her powerful servants, Princess Theradras is significantly more vulnerable. Find her lair, $N...it is time to strike.' WHERE `entry`=27698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What?! Gnaws ain\'t dead?! This kinda takes the quick outta my get rich quick scheme... Them giant shark teeth are nice and all, but we can\'t stop \'til that shiney is ours!' WHERE `entry`=27699;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Isn\'t she a beauty? Let\'s see what she does now that she\'s free.' WHERE `entry`=27700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Isn\'t she beautiful? So graceful. I hope she gets her fill of revenge and then some.' WHERE `entry`=27701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our efforts to improve relations with the red dragons has really paid off, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27702;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good thing that you and Warlord Krogg made friends with the red dragons.' WHERE `entry`=27703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is it! These are the bones of my kin...' WHERE `entry`=27704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='My bretheren are being butchered here. It\'s as I thought.$B$BI must ask your help further before I enter, $N. In the passageway outside this room, the hallway proceeds left and right. To the right, it goes down to the Chamber of Blood. Here the Atal\'ai perform their dark rituals.$B$BThey have expected and prepared for my kind for years, but not for you. Enter the Chamber of Blood and slay the Priestess Udum\'bra. She is one of three foul presences here that must be vanquished before I may enter.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good riddance. Another source of corruption in this world put to rest. I thank you for your bravery, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So... this is what Al\'Akir wanted all along.' WHERE `entry`=27706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good that this operation has been undone. Soon, I must move on...' WHERE `entry`=27708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<The red statue falls over, and you place it back in your bags. You hear a rumbling noise in the tomb\'s central chamber.>' WHERE `entry`=27709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, glad you\'re back! Have I got something fun for us to do!' WHERE `entry`=27711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N, glad you\'re back! Have I got something fun for us to do!' WHERE `entry`=27712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Some story, huh?  Now you know why Deathwing hasn\'t come back here since.' WHERE `entry`=27713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The end!  No moral.' WHERE `entry`=27714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t believe those guys would interrupt me like that. My story was going so well, too... Anyhow, thanks for sticking around so long. It\'s nice to have someone new to share tall tales with. I\'m sure Lucien and Theldurin feel the same way. You have any you\'d like to share with us?' WHERE `entry`=27715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Find Deathwing',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Beat Deathwing in a knife fight' WHERE `entry`=27715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant! It will take me a while to translate, but this is precisely the kind of find I was hoping for. There\'s no knowing if we will make it out of this place, but if it comes down to it, I will find a way to float this to the surface in hopes that it will one day be found. Thank you again, $N. Here... perhaps I have something that may be of use to you.' WHERE `entry`=27716;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant! I can\'t have expected much more with the tools I gave you. I should be able to fill in the blanks and get this all written out shortly. There\'s no knowing if we will make it out of this place, but if it comes down to it, I will find a way to float this to the surface in hopes that it will one day be found. Thank you again, $N. You\'re not bad.' WHERE `entry`=27717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lok\'tar, brother! You have arrived just in time.' WHERE `entry`=27718;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Hammer of Twilight? And you say you got this information out of a drowned Wildhammer dwarf? You\'re kidding, right?' WHERE `entry`=27719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh no! My weapons and totems! They\'re destroyed!!!' WHERE `entry`=27720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc1`='Speak to Goldmine to get in the cart' WHERE `entry`=27720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We knew the Horde would send help and not a moment too soon!' WHERE `entry`=27721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our world is in danger, $N! We need the help of great heroes, like you, to save it!' WHERE `entry`=27722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Recruiter Burns in Stormwind Harbor.$B$BRecent attacks by the Horde on our trade ships must be met with swift and just force!$B$BStormwind Harbor can be found in the northwest region of Stormwind City.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance! Fight on, $G brother:sister;!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='All of our war ships are off fighting the Horde. You\'ll have to take the mercenary ship.' WHERE `entry`=27724;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yoro sends warning of the Horde? The Highvale have been cautious of an attack for some time now. In fact, we have been-- By the light... they are here!' WHERE `entry`=27725;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We knew the Alliance would send help and not a moment too soon!' WHERE `entry`=27726;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Naraat the Earthspeaker at the Eastern Earthshrine in Stormwind City.$B$BThe Earthen Ring requires our aid! They report that the elemental plane of Deepholm threatens to overtake our world and destroy all life on Azeroth!$B$BThe Eastern Earthshrine can be found directly northwest of Stormwind Keep.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance! Fight on, $G brother:sister;!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our world is in danger, $N! We need the help of great heroes, like you, to save it!' WHERE `entry`=27727;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, Mortimer just faked his own death. He\'ll probably take on his brother\'s name and continue on his \'epic schemes\'. We\'ll just have to deal with that when the time comes.' WHERE `entry`=27733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank goodness! With this fire, our men will live through this ordeal! Thank you so much, hero.' WHERE `entry`=27737;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you for what you\'ve done, $N. You can count on my vote when High Council convenes.' WHERE `entry`=27738;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have performed a deed this day unlike any I have seen in my long career. Hogger\'s death will plague the Riverpaw for years to come, and hopefully put an end to their attacks on our people. Greatest of heroes, please take this as a sign of my eternal gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=27739;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, it\'s so nice to have help dropped in. Modern convenience... I can\'t get enough of it.' WHERE `entry`=27740;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Hmm, I don\'t think that stuff\'s going to sell for much. I better give you your cut right now so you don\'t feel ripped off.' WHERE `entry`=27742;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They had it coming to them.' WHERE `entry`=27743;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll teach \'em to move in on our territory! What\'s that over across the way?' WHERE `entry`=27744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Rune of Air destroyed',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Rune of Fire destroyed' WHERE `entry`=27744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We survived and all of the portals are now shutdown! You don\'t think Magmatooth is going to hold a grudge, do you?' WHERE `entry`=27745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc1`='Use the Fire Portal Controller' WHERE `entry`=27745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='News of your conquest in Silverpine emboldens us, $N. We are prepared to fight at your command and beat back the last remaining vestiges of humanity in Hillsbrad.' WHERE `entry`=27746;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, yes. Burn them out, as you would flush groundhogs from their holes... Well done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see you\'re still in one piece, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Great! Did you get any for yourself?' WHERE `entry`=27750;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' So, $C. There\'s more to you than meets the eye. Maybe your Horde can stand with the best of my warriors. Let\'s try you out...' WHERE `entry`=27751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh aye ... we get a few of these kegs out to the boys on the front and we\'re gonna see some fireworks. Thank you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good - hardly a worm or weevil to be found! This is a lifesaver to the folk who fled here for survival.' WHERE `entry`=27753;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at that! That\'s quite a collection of trophies you have there. I\'ll spread the word. If a single Alliance $C can do this, imagine what the rest of your lot can accomplish!' WHERE `entry`=27754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They couldn\'t be saved, $N. The ancient curse that fell upon them is irrevocable.' WHERE `entry`=27755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Bzzzzzzzzzzzzt.>$B$BNicely done! A clean kill. Now continue on and see what else you can find! We\'ll crack this case wide open with you on our side, I just know it.' WHERE `entry`=27756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh my. It sounds like you ran across quite a sinister being. I wonder what one of those was doing all the way out here...' WHERE `entry`=27757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Bzzzzzzzzzzzzt.>$B$BHey, it\'s Horatio. That was intense! I\'m watching your progress on the Stormwind Communicator\'s Spyatron X3 application.$B$BThey sure are using a lot of heavily fortified doors to hide their work. Keep pushing forward and see what you find next. I bet it\'ll be a huge clue!' WHERE `entry`=27758;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Scanning subject... Cerebral cortex diagnostics indicate the absence of "tomb curse" phenomenon. Diagnostics did reveal frequent head trauma. The user would do well to exercise more caution around blunt objects in the future.' WHERE `entry`=27760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. The expedition has already doomed itself. There is no need for it to endanger the rest of the world as well.' WHERE `entry`=27761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Third Bomb Cluster disarmed',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Unstable Bomb Bot deactivated' WHERE `entry`=27761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice landing!' WHERE `entry`=27762;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Use the Teleporter in the back of Fuselight-by-the-Sea to port up the mountain, then report to Dolph Blasto at Fuselight in the Badlands.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Fuselight!' WHERE `entry`=27763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $R. You may keep the goggles, as they have already served their purpose: they brought you to me.' WHERE `entry`=27764;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for gathering these so quickly, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27765;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This grisly task was necessary, $N.$B$BAll will be revealed to you soon. For now, know this:$B$BI am no ordinary goblin.$B$BI serve a mistress of unimaginable power, and her motives here are not as dark as they might seem.' WHERE `entry`=27766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My true name is Rheastrasza, and I am an envoy of Alexstrasza herself, the Aspect of the red dragonflight.$B$BWith Deathwing currently occupied with other matters, we are going to find a way to redeem the black dragonflight.$B$BAnd you are going to help us.' WHERE `entry`=27769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We will find a shred of good within these dragons, $N. Whether it is in the wild eggs you found, the bodies of the whelplings you slew, or the eggs that we have encouraged Nyxondra to lay... we will find an untainted black dragon.' WHERE `entry`=27770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done everything that I have asked you, without question. Our job here in Lethlor Ravine is done.$B$BIt is now time that I revealed everything to you.' WHERE `entry`=27771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ooh!  Science stuff!  Let\'s see what you\'ve got here...$B$BWild eggs?  Blech. Useless. These are never any good.$B$BOoooh, what\'s this?  Some sort of... pre-engineered egg?  This looks promising, but I don\'t want to know what Rhea had to do to get it.$B$BHmm... yes, some very nice corpses. Very nice indeed.$B$BAlright, I\'ll see what I can do.' WHERE `entry`=27772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He has escaped! I should have known it would not be so easy. The path is clear, $N. It is time to return.' WHERE `entry`=27773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I wonder where all of these ogre-magi are coming from?  Curious times, indeed.' WHERE `entry`=27774;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A perfect fit!  My goat puncher is finally finished!' WHERE `entry`=27775;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done!  I have no doubt that those goats will be back, but they\'ll think twice before they nibble my cogs again!' WHERE `entry`=27776;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent job, user $N. We must obtain access to the fusion core now.' WHERE `entry`=27777;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am in control, user $N. But I cannot keep the core temperature stable indefinitely.' WHERE `entry`=27778;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done, user $N. I thank you for your assistance with this unfortunate task.' WHERE `entry`=27779;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Bzzzzzzzzzzzzt.>$B$BYou\'re nearing the heart of their domain. There will likely be an extremely fortified door protecting the inner sanctum of the entire Defias operation. See if you can find anything that might pry it open!$B$BI suggest a stealthy method!' WHERE `entry`=27781;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, you\'re back. We know where Cho\'gall\'s ultimate weapon is located!' WHERE `entry`=27782;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, you\'re back. It\'s about time. We know where Cho\'gall\'s ultimate weapon is located!' WHERE `entry`=27783;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Hammer of Twilight floats in the middle of the altar, unprotected....' WHERE `entry`=27784;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Bzzzzzzzzzzzzt.>$B$BYour exploits have gained quite the following in the intelligence community, $N. Many top members of SI:7 have been earnestly watching you infiltrate the Deadmines through their own Stormwind Communicators.$B$BMathias Shaw himself wants to speak with you! I\'ll transfer you over momentarily.' WHERE `entry`=27785;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Hammer of Twilight floats in the middle of the altar, unprotected....' WHERE `entry`=27786;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it, lad! You beat that damned gronn and sent Cho\'gall packing into the Twilight Bastion. Don\'t you worry. With your help and that of your friends, we\'ll get in there and we\'ll kill Cho\'gall once and for all!' WHERE `entry`=27787;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it, $N! You beat that damned gronn and sent Cho\'gall packing into the Twilight Bastion. Don\'t you worry. With your help and that of your friends, we\'ll get in there and we\'ll kill Cho\'gall once and for all!' WHERE `entry`=27788;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The results are in. I\'ve identified traces of corruption in all three samples you brought me. Rhea will be quite disappointed.' WHERE `entry`=27789;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Survive third wave',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Survive final wave' WHERE `entry`=27789;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You very well may have saved all of Stormwind with your efforts here today, $N. Vanessa may still be out there, but she is an insignificant threat now that the Juggernaut will be placed under our careful watch. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27790;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Titans?  You wanna know about titans?$B$BYou came to the right place, $G lad: lass;. We\'re on the brink of somethin\' big.' WHERE `entry`=27791;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Chalice... worthless.$B$BVase... counterfeit.$B$BHieroglyph... interesting, but rather common.$B$BWhat\'s this?  I\'ve never seen trogg craftsmanship of this caliber!  You\'ve stumbled upon something rare indeed, $N.$B$BAlright, fine. Let\'s talk titans, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=27792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With your inspection complete, the statues return to their original positions. Something seems different in the room, however...' WHERE `entry`=27793;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just one tiny little device? I never did understand those titans. Very well!  Let\'s see what this peeper can do.' WHERE `entry`=27794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Going toe to toe with ogres is impressive, $N. I\'m glad I\'ve got soldiers like you out here.' WHERE `entry`=27795;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Find a use for the Warden\'s Pawn within the Tomb of the Watchers in the Badlands.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='<The statue clicks into place on the large stone slab.>' WHERE `entry`=27796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<The statue slides into place on the cold marble slab.>' WHERE `entry`=27797;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Hammer of Twilight? And you say you got this information out of a drowned Wildhammer dwarf? You\'re kidding, right?' WHERE `entry`=27798;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, boy. Good to have another capable set of hands about.' WHERE `entry`=27803;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for your help. Every little bit makes a difference. We\'ll keep the water going until we can push the Twilight back.' WHERE `entry`=27804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are very generous. Thank you. There\'s a lot of darkness in our world these days. We appreciate the light that you\'ve brought here.' WHERE `entry`=27805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Greetings, $R. Sent by Keegan?' WHERE `entry`=27806;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Iain sent ya? You don\'t look like a Firebeard to me. Why exactly should I be listenin\' to anything you say?' WHERE `entry`=27807;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It seems the Doyles suffered the worst of the attacking Twilight drakes. It\'s clear that they fought to the end: not a single rider\'s footprint more than a few yards from his gryphon. It\'s doubtful there were any survivors.' WHERE `entry`=27808;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Bout that time, eh? Help us wrap things up then.' WHERE `entry`=27809;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s the stuff! Not half bad. You\'ve got a bit of fight in ya after all.' WHERE `entry`=27810;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good on you. I always feel like a part of me is missing when my gryphon isn\'t nearby. I can\'t speak for Duglas or the rest of the clan, but I\'ll be ready to ride at Firebeard\'s call.' WHERE `entry`=27811;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ya got the Mullans. Good news! They\'re worth more than their weight in a fight, and they ain\'t exactly skinny.' WHERE `entry`=27812;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s more like it. Let\'s finish gatherin\' up supplies and get back to Keegan.' WHERE `entry`=27813;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yer a good lad. Have me thanks and a little gold for yer troubles.' WHERE `entry`=27814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! Looks like their raid went mighty well then. I\'ll have to buy ol\' Forgehammer a round once we finish with this mess.' WHERE `entry`=27815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It seems you had some luck bringin\' riders back. Well timed too - we just pushed the elementals back, so we should have the arm room to lead an attack right away. Thank you, $N. You\'re a good $R.' WHERE `entry`=27816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that\'s how it\'s done, lad! With a real gryphon wing back together, we can take the fight to the rest of the Twilight. You\'re welcome to fly with us anytime.' WHERE `entry`=27817;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s have a look then... Mmm, oh dear. That\'s what I thought these were. They might still be usable, but it\'s horrid to have such things in my backyard.' WHERE `entry`=27818;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='More black on you than red... that\'s what I like to see. Looks like you\'ve got what it takes, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27821;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve had strikes on our own lumber line while you\'ve been gone. This should at least put us on equal footing for gathering rates. Good work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27822;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Wow, this stuff is strong!  I knew they had beer, but I never expected them to have shadowstout!  That\'s my favorite shadowbeer!' WHERE `entry`=27823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now here\'s some treasure!  I was beginning to worry that these weren\'t titan ruins at all! I\'ll show these to Durdin. Thanks again, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I imagine those ogres weren\'t too much trouble for you. Here - some coin for your troubles.' WHERE `entry`=27825;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll take that egg out of your hands now. We need to get this egg incubated... and hidden, quickly. There are lots of angry dragons looking for this. It\'s good to see you again, by the way.' WHERE `entry`=27826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re the $R we\'ve been waiting for?  It\'s about time you got here. My legs could use a stretch. Come on boys!  Let\'s go kill us some black dragons!' WHERE `entry`=27827;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m not what you\'d call "very strong" or "battle-hardened", but I get the job done my own way. Lookin\' forward to fightin\' with you. I never fought with a fancy-lookin\' $C before.' WHERE `entry`=27828;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='One less dragon to worry about, one step closer to redemption. Onward, my soldiers!' WHERE `entry`=27829;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Two more dangerous black dragons have been removed from this egg hunt. Your greatest task, however, still awaits.' WHERE `entry`=27830;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just think... Nyxondra may end up being the mother of the new black dragonflight. In death, she has given a gift to the future generations of Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=27831;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The egg must always be moving. We are not safe anywhere. Deathwing, even in his madness, knows all the hidden places in this world. The egg must not rest.' WHERE `entry`=27832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I\'d say we have a dragon problem, but it seems like they\'re a little more interested in New Kargath then they are in our small encampment. Nevertheless, I\'ve got top men focused on keeping the dragons at bay.$B$BOne problem that has gone unchecked, however, is the ogre camp to our southwest. A small army of combatants seems to have appeared outside of their hovel.$B$BWe can\'t sit and wait for them to flank us, soldier. Thin their ranks before they thin ours.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $R. However, I\'m afraid I don\'t have much to give you, other than this passionate round of applause. Oh, I do have these. Here, take your pick.' WHERE `entry`=27833;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I think you\'re ready, $N. You\'re getting the hang of this.' WHERE `entry`=27834;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='See?  No need to worry when Olaf is around. Just let me know, and I\'ll protect you from the monsters.' WHERE `entry`=27835;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N. This will make our prophetic visions that much clearer.' WHERE `entry`=27836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, $N. I can feel the disruption in the river fading. Yet, I feel the source of this taint still lingers.' WHERE `entry`=27837;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes. The waters are clearing up. I am certain I will be visited by a vision before the High Council meets. Be warned, $R. My vote will only be swayed by what I see. You might have helped us greatly here today, but if the vision sways me to make a case against war then that is the way my vote will be cast.' WHERE `entry`=27838;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Retrieve the Ancient Tol\'vir Armaments',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is quite timely. I will distribute these armaments to my best men and to the laborers that you recruited. I\'ve a feeling they\'ll show as much courage as my best trained captains.' WHERE `entry`=27839;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. We, are in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=27840;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Goblin Spirit in Orgrimmar\'s graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=27841;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do not be alarmed, $N. I am close to you, waiting in the shadows. You\'ve done well. You must continue the mission here - I am too valuable to risk my life against petty criminals like these.' WHERE `entry`=27842;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Once again, well done. With a few more pushes the battle will be ours.' WHERE `entry`=27843;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My employers do not take kindly to traitors. On the flip side, they are renown for their kindness towards the loyal! You deserve to be rewarded!' WHERE `entry`=27844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. Those soldiers deserve better than to be left face down in the mud.' WHERE `entry`=27845;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Acquire some Bread of the Dead and give it to the Cheerful Worgen Spirit in Darnassus\' graveyard.$B$BUse an Orange Marigold to see the otherwise invisible spirit.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=27846;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant! Now all I have to do is finish my work, and my Mayhem Reapers will cause...mayhem...on any Horde front! And there won\'t be any Defias knockoffs to steal my profits!' WHERE `entry`=27847;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s a shame that he was both a human and a worgen. Had he been a proud orc warrior I\'d have liked to charge into battle alongside such a fierce combatant. We can speak of ill-fated desires another day. It is time to take what is ours from the enemy.' WHERE `entry`=27848;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve followed orders well, $N. On behalf of the crown, I\'m rewarding you for your bravery on the battlefield.' WHERE `entry`=27849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='COWARD!!! Vanessa VanCleef is a dirty human coward! How dare she flee from battle against the Horde and leave her unworthy subordinate to fight! No matter. Her ship is reward enough. The citizens of Stormwind will bear first hand witness to our awe inspiring power using a ship made in part by the very architect of their city!' WHERE `entry`=27850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $N. With this, it\'s only a matter of time until the orcs are fleeing for the portal or begging for surrender.' WHERE `entry`=27851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We will fight to the last orc, $N. I hope you\'ll keep yourself alive long enough to properly destroy these trespassers.' WHERE `entry`=27852;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No true member of the Horde should find pleasure in killing such terrified weaklings... without challenge, victory has no true thrill. But your dirty work has helped stave off the Alliance and protect our homes here. Be proud of your work for the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27853;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a true champion, $N, to take the lives of so many on the battlefield. I hope it will be enough to save Stonard.' WHERE `entry`=27854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With no link to the outside, the Alliance must rely on what they\'ve brought to the swamp. We shall see if they can handle our home environment.' WHERE `entry`=27855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You honor both the dead and the living with your courage, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Alliance is driven out! Stonard will be safe, thanks to your ferocity. Lok\'tar Ogar!' WHERE `entry`=27857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You were not the only mortal that Rheastrasza confided in. I too earned the dragon\'s trust. I have already moved the real purified egg on to a safer location, away from the Badlands. It will continue to grow, out of Deathwing\'s sight. The red dragonflight is as benevolent as it is powerful. It was Rheastrasza\'s final wish that I give this to you.' WHERE `entry`=27859;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It still pains my heart to have asked you to do this, though I know there is no other way. You have saved those of us still holding on from a terrible menace.' WHERE `entry`=27860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I was wondering when you\'d show up, $N! Having a past champion of the Ring of Blood here will be a huge draw! We\'re gonna be rich, buddy! RICH!$B$BAnyway, this is some old Dragonmaw fighting pit. Didn\'t take much modification to tune it up to our uses. I put out a few feelers, and got some heavy hitters from all around Azeroth to join in the carnage. Bout time to make some gold!$B$BYou know the drill, $N. When you\'re ready, let me know and we\'ll get this show on the road!' WHERE `entry`=27861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Well well, if it isn\'t the once champion of anguish, $N! I\'m seeing good money in the future now that you\'re here! We\'re gonna be rollin in the dough, buddy! Filthy RICH!$B$BAnyway, this is some old Dragonmaw fighting pit. Didn\'t take much modification to tune it up to our uses. I put out a few feelers, and got some heavy hitters from all around Azeroth to join in the carnage. Bout time to make some gold!$B$BYou know the drill, $N. When you\'re ready, let me know and we\'ll get this show on the road!' WHERE `entry`=27862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, friend. You might make some gold out here - if you manage to stay alive.' WHERE `entry`=27863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No love in your heart for orcs I see. You really made a mess of that guy.' WHERE `entry`=27864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No love in your heart for dwarves I see. You really made a mess of that guy.' WHERE `entry`=27865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow! When I saw that... thing stumble into the arena, I thought you didn\'t stand a chance. But you proved me wrong. You tore it apart! Grizzly business.' WHERE `entry`=27866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You really pulled that one out. I thought you were done for sure when he wolfed and started tearing up the arena. I guess I should know by now that you don\'t go down easy.' WHERE `entry`=27867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like this title is yours! You really pulled that one out of the fire. Congratulations. I hope the coin serves you well.' WHERE `entry`=27868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The goblin sent you? She has a cunning eye, that one. She speaks the truth. I am here to stem the tide of corruption seeping from this temple. If you would save your people from a wicked fate, $N, I ask for your assistance.' WHERE `entry`=27869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Trouble within the temple... I wish we could spare forces to deal with it. The war with Stonard is already raging, and we need every man we can get.' WHERE `entry`=27870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We have no time to send orcs to the temple, $N. The humans come, and they are many. Stonard must be defended!' WHERE `entry`=27871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ysera herself sent you to me? Oh! It\'s a honor to speak with a representative of the aspects. It\'s true that our shrine is in jeopardy. The harpies we once sheltered in our boughs have suddenly turned against us. But please, don\'t rejoin the fight until you are ready. Our shrine is no mere battleground. Use its peace and power to center yourself.' WHERE `entry`=27874;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Prayerblossom has been used by the Broken as a remedy since they settled in this swamp. If it soothes the physical form, it might be used for more powerful healing...' WHERE `entry`=27875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It will have to be purified, but this will be most helpful. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent!  We\'ll bury these immediately. Those Explorers\' League dimwits will never suspect us!' WHERE `entry`=27877;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I knew it!  The High Examiner will be pleased to see this. Nice work, $R.' WHERE `entry`=27878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I imagine those ogres weren\'t too much trouble for you. Here - some coin for your troubles.' WHERE `entry`=27879;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve got the hint of a hero in you, $R. Now get out of my battlefield.' WHERE `entry`=27880;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Titans?  You come to me, asking about titans? You\'ve come to the right place, as we\'re on the brink of discovering something big. You will, however, need to earn your keep first.' WHERE `entry`=27881;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Chalice... worthless. Vase... counterfeit. Hieroglyph... interesting, but rather common. What\'s this?  I\'ve never seen trogg craftsmanship of this caliber!  You\'ve stumbled upon something rare indeed, $N. We must not be so hasty as to overlook the troggs. They may be simple, but they know things about the deep, hidden places of this world. You\'ve performed well enough. Let\'s talk titans, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=27882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Find a use for the Warden\'s Pawn within the Tomb of the Watchers in the Badlands.' WHERE `entry`=27883;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just one tiny little device? I never did understand those titans. Very well!  Let\'s see what this peeper can do.' WHERE `entry`=27888;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll take that egg out of your hands now. We need to get this egg incubated... and hidden, quickly. There are lots of angry dragons looking for this. It\'s good to see you again, by the way.' WHERE `entry`=27889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'re the $R we\'ve been waiting for?  It\'s about time you got here. My legs could use a stretch. Come on boys!  Let\'s go kill us some black dragons!' WHERE `entry`=27890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m looking forward to fighting with you.' WHERE `entry`=27891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I think you\'re ready, $N. You\'re getting the hang of this.' WHERE `entry`=27892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='See?  No need to worry when Gargal is around. Just let me know, and I\'ll protect you from the monsters.' WHERE `entry`=27893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='One less dragon to worry about, one step closer to redemption. Onward, my soldiers!' WHERE `entry`=27894;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Two more dangerous black dragons have been removed from this egg hunt. Your greatest task, however, still awaits.' WHERE `entry`=27895;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Just think... Nyxondra may end up being the mother of the new black dragonflight. In death, she has given a gift to the future generations of Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=27896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The egg must always be moving. We are not safe anywhere. Deathwing, even in his madness, knows all the hidden places in this world. The egg must not rest.' WHERE `entry`=27897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It would seem that I\'m not the only one interested in these obelisks...' WHERE `entry`=27899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a relief. Thanks, $N. Turns out I\'ve got my hands full here.' WHERE `entry`=27900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it! Good work, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Such clarity... let us hope this will aid poor Magtoor.' WHERE `entry`=27902;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='According to Harrison\'s notes, placing the lens upon this dais should re-activate this obelisk. Exactly what that means remains to be seen...' WHERE `entry`=27903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can only hope this will lead to a cure, $N. Thank you for bringing it to me.' WHERE `entry`=27904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work back there, $N. Looks like we\'ve lost them, for now at least.' WHERE `entry`=27905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope the sight of my sniveling amuses you, $N. It will be the only joy here.' WHERE `entry`=27906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will grind these and try to get him to eat. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At least I can soothe him with my own hands while he still breathes. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27908;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He can only drink so much. The rest might be used for washing his body, after...' WHERE `entry`=27909;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With Duskfang to shroud his body, he will carry the animal\'s spirit with him into the afterlife. Listen to me. An old superstitious fool. I\'m so sorry, Helgrum...' WHERE `entry`=27910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='He is gone. He is right. I must be strong for him...' WHERE `entry`=27911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You peer into the chest...' WHERE `entry`=27912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You peer into the chest...' WHERE `entry`=27913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have performed a great service for me and my kind, $N. Accept this as a symbol of my gratitude, and of your courage.' WHERE `entry`=27914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I am pleased to see you once again, $N. You are truly noble to assist me further.' WHERE `entry`=27915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I see. Thank you for this information, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The scent of freshly spilled traitor blood fills my nostrils, and it is absolutely invigorating. However, my bloodlust will not be sated until Godfrey lies on the floor as a lifeless heap. He thinks an army of mindless corpses can stop the wrath of the Bloodfang? We\'ll gnaw on their bones for years to come after our work is done!' WHERE `entry`=27917;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Anchorite Avuun is one of our uncorrupted bretheren, what other races know as Draenei. He came to The Harborage to heal us, and try to find a cure. It is he who sent me here to collect these crystals.$B$BHe watches over a very sick friend now... and despite sending word to the Exodar itself, he has not found any aid so far. Could you bring these crystals to him, $N? You may be the only one able to assist him.',`objectives_loc1`='Deliver the Draenethyst Crystals to Anchorite Avuun.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. I am afraid it may be too late... but I refuse to give up, even if the Exodar itself does not hear my cries.' WHERE `entry`=27918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We appreciate your assistance here in this swamp, $N. I would like to inform you that I have received correspondance from Nethergarde Keep.$B$BEnohar Thunderbrew has requested help in investigating the shipwrecks of the Red Reaches, but we have had none willing to make the journey, and I could not leave the Harborage.$B$BNethergarde Keep sits in the Blasted Lands, south of the Swamp of Sorrows. Do not journey too close to Stonard on your way.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, has Avuun sent ye? Good, good...' WHERE `entry`=27919;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re nearly there, $N. The time is now to charge further ahead and take out Walden!' WHERE `entry`=27920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' It won\'t be long now before the entire keep is ours, thanks to your valiant efforts.' WHERE `entry`=27921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A djinn!  We must escape as soon as possible. This unholy alliance of the Neferset with the minions of Deathwing does not bode well for us.' WHERE `entry`=27922;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes. I hear the Neferset calling each other to the east. This might yet work.' WHERE `entry`=27923;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. You\'ll see, this can\'t possibly go wrong!' WHERE `entry`=27924;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='This manual describes outlandish theories on how to efficiently manage large groups of workers as they engage in the manual labor of various types of excavation.$B$BIt becomes clear to you that the author of the book is the figure in charge of the over-aggressive pillagers here.$B$BPerhaps an introduction is in order.',`objectives_loc1`='Bring \'Efficient Excavations\' to Belloc Brightblade in Schnottz\'s Landing.' WHERE `entry`=27925;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I trust that you had no troubles fitting in with our guests, hmm?' WHERE `entry`=27926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Mingled with a Budding Artist',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Mingled with an Aspiring Starlet' WHERE `entry`=27926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They sent you to check up on us?  Pshh... I\'ve been around this desert longer than any of those chumps. We\'re just soaking in some of the scenery and telling stories about old times. You like telling stories?' WHERE `entry`=27927;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, these are exquisite! The commander will be able to make a winter uniform with these.' WHERE `entry`=27928;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You look a little battered. Those dwarves didn\'t give you any challenge, did they? Still, that was an impressive show.' WHERE `entry`=27929;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Heroes: If you are reading this, then my suspicions were correct. Deathwing has found us. The egg is destroyed, as am I. This was, actually, the plan from the beginning. You see... the egg that Deathwing destroyed was not the egg he sought. It was mine.' WHERE `entry`=27930;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, $R, you\'re here. We\'ll have to act fast if we\'re to prevent Therazane\'s forces from attacking.' WHERE `entry`=27931;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. Without all of their giants, Therazane\'s forces will have a harder time taking Stonehearth. Now, if you please, hand back the axe. I\'ll keep it safe until you can rescue the Stonefather.' WHERE `entry`=27932;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These should do. I\'ll just need a moment to prepare the ritual.' WHERE `entry`=27933;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done what few others could have. Defeating Avalanchion was no small feat. I\'m impressed, $N. Will you help us with our war against the stone troggs so that we can rescue the Stonefather?' WHERE `entry`=27935;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You have to go back and slay Avalanchion to keep Therazane\'s forces from attacking Stonehearth!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done what few others could have. Defeating Avalanchion was no small feat. I\'m impressed, $N. Will you help us with our war against the stone troggs so that we can rescue the Stonefather?' WHERE `entry`=27936;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Stonefather is waiting for you back south at Stonehearth.$B$BMake yourself presentable. You\'ve earned a heroes welcome!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our $G hero : heroine; returns!$B$BYou have saved my people, $N. You have earned that which you seek.' WHERE `entry`=27937;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Middle Fragment of the World Pillar!$B$BThank you, $N. I can only imagine what you had to go through to get this to us. I\'ll see to it that it\'s placed within the center of the chamber.' WHERE `entry`=27938;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it! Perhaps I can trust you vizh more serious matters, hmm?' WHERE `entry`=27939;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most efficient work, $C. You should rise rapidly through the ranks.' WHERE `entry`=27941;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Zhese look to be of sufficient quality. Vizh zhese, ve are vone shtep closah to zhe cleansink ritual.' WHERE `entry`=27942;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very goot! You have earned yourself a place at zhe ritual. You shall be among zhe first to velcome Gobbles back to his... original form.' WHERE `entry`=27943;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work on those spiders $N. At this rate, we will be taking that forest in no time.' WHERE `entry`=27944;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' What have we, what have we - breaches, the breaches number three. Two heads, one wholly given to its master. I see the future. A hammer united. A mountain shattered. Oh - OH!' WHERE `entry`=27945;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These glands will do nicely. We are grateful for your help, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27948;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='May their souls rest in peace.' WHERE `entry`=27949;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<The eye speaks to you, its \'voice\' reverberating as if coming from everywhere at once.>$B$BYou seek my sight, $R? My powers come at a price. These disciples of the twilight have been honoring me with the blood of Wildhammer dwarves from the nearby ruins, but still I thirst. Perhaps you can do better.$B$BSlay my old masters, and my vision is yours. Honor me with the slaughter of the Shaman of the Black. Blood is blood, after all.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Ah, the succulent thrill of life extinguished. Do you feel it, $C? Do you relish it as I do? No, I see not. You fight to protect the lives of others. Pity.' WHERE `entry`=27951;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh gosh! Someone\'s finally here to help us?' WHERE `entry`=27952;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, it\'s about time someone came to speak with us on matters most urgent.' WHERE `entry`=27953;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found one? I\'ve been searching everywhere. Give it here! Some of these eyes are won over with riddles or verse. Others require magic. What did this one demand? Ah, it\'s no matter. What matters is that it\'s ours.' WHERE `entry`=27954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve gone pale, $C. What did the Eye show you? You saw Cho\'gall? Wait - Cho\'gall saw you? He\'s watching us? He\'s watching us right now!? Damn this stupid dark magic! I\'m going to have to infiltrate Cho\'gall\'s stronghold myself.' WHERE `entry`=27955;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You didn\'t... KILL the machines to get these, right?. Right?' WHERE `entry`=27956;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This... this is way more than I expected. This will last us for months!' WHERE `entry`=27958;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve got quick hands if you were able to gather this many in such a short time. Excellent work, $N. I\'ll make sure these ones don\'t go to waste.' WHERE `entry`=27961;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yup, this was Margol\'s horn alright. No doubt about it. Barnabas was a digger, like me. He never stood a chance in combat against the beast. I\'m glad you were here to set things right.' WHERE `entry`=27962;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s see... Overseer Maltorius... we\'re quite familiar with him and his work. What\'s this?  The "archduke"?  That sounds promising.' WHERE `entry`=27963;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A... an ember?  What is this thing?' WHERE `entry`=27964;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do I know you, $R? Sounds like another one of Ragnaros\' minions. I don\'t like the sound of that.' WHERE `entry`=27965;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I didn\'t think you would be able to do it, $N. You are just full of surprises aren\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=27966;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, you made it back alive!  Can\'t say you were the first one to try this task, but you are definitely the first one to make it back alive.' WHERE `entry`=27967;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We did it, $N! At terrible cost...but victory is ours. This keep could serve well as a home for me and my pack, though we tend to prefer more natural habitats. It may be best to leave it as a reminder of Godfrey\'s betrayal and of the Bloodfang warriors that died here in battle.' WHERE `entry`=27968;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Vell done, $C. Zhere may be hope for you yet.' WHERE `entry`=27969;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it!  Maybe we can finally get some ships into port now. Thank you $N.' WHERE `entry`=27970;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work on the undead up there $N. We really appreciate the help.' WHERE `entry`=27971;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This rum will really help us out, $N. They might not feel great in the morning but at least they will go to sleep happy.' WHERE `entry`=27972;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I didn\'t think you would be able to do it, $N. You are just full of surprises aren\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=27973;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, very well done! They\'ve gotten a hold of powerful allies, but clearly nothing a $C-champion of the Banshee Queen can\'t handle!' WHERE `entry`=27974;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work $N. I will report your efforts to our highest in command immediately.' WHERE `entry`=27975;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ye\'re a good lad, ye are. I got ye a lil\' present fer yer troubles.' WHERE `entry`=27976;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fantastic work!' WHERE `entry`=27977;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work, $N!  We should not hear from the ghosts again anytime soon.' WHERE `entry`=27978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' This thing is strange, $N. I don\'t know what to make of it. It ain\'t natural, that\'s for sure.' WHERE `entry`=27979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There\'s no way you coulda killed all the spiders in the gorge, but you definitely made a dent. Fine, here\'s what I promised ya. Don\'t spend it all in one place. Unless it\'s at Thorium Point.' WHERE `entry`=27980;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yeeeeeeowch!  Don\'t just go puttin\' this stuff into a dwarf\'s open hand. This stuff is burnin\' up! Now me hands are gonna get even more swollen...' WHERE `entry`=27981;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm... the gems looked... sparklier from afar. Up close, they look kind of dingy. Ah well!  A little spit and polish should do the trick, and if not, I can use \'em to practice my disenchanting.' WHERE `entry`=27982;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have accepted my fate here in this cage, but the prayer must be found.' WHERE `entry`=27984;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And who might you be? Ah, an emissary from the Thorium Brotherhood. They\'re looking for my support?  Fine, I might be willin\' to help out... ...for a price.' WHERE `entry`=27986;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job on the recovery effort $N. These cannonballs should last us a while.' WHERE `entry`=27987;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Cromush has both a thick skull and a fool\'s brain, and we\'ll use that to our advantage. By the time anybody finds out about the plague\'s true potency, it\'ll be far too late. Thank you for keeping quiet during his tirade. I promise you won\'t regret it.' WHERE `entry`=27988;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Honey! Delicious honey! Well done, ugly creature! You may put the honey...put the honey down right there. No, to the left. Yes, there. Just leave it there.' WHERE `entry`=27989;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Auch! If I vere an inch or two taller, I\'d be dead!' WHERE `entry`=27990;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ha, we finally got Largo!  Nice one, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27991;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These parts will really help us out, $N!  Who would have thought you can find stuff this useful in all that old junk?' WHERE `entry`=27992;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to see ya, kid. Would\'ve been even better if you\'d have been here to help me take care of these little savages...' WHERE `entry`=27993;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Slay 15 Deadwood furbolg of any type.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It worked! I mean, uh, YES, the will of Ruumbo has been carried out! You have done well, creature! You may have these shiny coins!' WHERE `entry`=27994;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Those two brats... I should have known! They were smart enough to hush whenever I went to examine the totem. I\'ll be sure to find them and drag them back to Timbermaw Hold by the ears! Thank you for looking into it...' WHERE `entry`=27995;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The time has come! Godfrey will fall!' WHERE `entry`=27996;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Emerald Circle thanks you, $N. If we all work together here, we can purge these demons from our midst.' WHERE `entry`=27997;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='For a moment there, I thought all was lost. Even when surrounded by the worgen in Gilneas I had higher hopes! But you proved me wrong $N. I will see to it that Sylvanas herself hears of your triumph here today. Don\'t worry about the mess here, I will gladly see to it myself.' WHERE `entry`=27998;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a right shame. Stubborn as they were to speak to, they were just as stubborn in a fight. Would have been good to have \'em. Once this is done, we\'ll have to send some boys out to bring them back for a proper send off.' WHERE `entry`=27999;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Imps are creatures of deception. With so many of them spotted at Shadowlurk Ridge, I\'m positive something is being hidden there. Our little friend will tell us exactly how to find it... if he doesn\'t want to go back in the sack.' WHERE `entry`=28000;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Here here, WOT!? He calls ME a COWARD!? Just like a Firebeard, all hot air and not a lick of sense. I\'ve been bearing the brunt of a Dragonmaw invasion from the south, much of Thundermar is in ruins, and do any of the other clans stick up to help? NO! Ol\' Thundermar is on his own he is, and you\'d better believe I\'m usin\' everything in my arsenal just to stem the tide.' WHERE `entry`=28001;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmm, still a bit frazzled, are they? Well, you know what they say. Time heals all wounds. Except for those of the ambassador, of course...' WHERE `entry`=28002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Pretentious Businessman Chastened',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Budding Artist Counseled' WHERE `entry`=28002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Adventurers Wanted: Ragefire Chasm',`details_loc1`='The Warchief has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Ragefire Chasm, just beneath the great city of Orgrimmar, immediately!$B$BThe Searing Blade is poised to launch an attack at any moment and the city guards cannot hold for much longer! If you so choose, head to Ragefire Chasm and speak with Stone Guard Kurjack, head of the defense initiative, to end the threat to Orgrimmar once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=28003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Adventurers Wanted: Blackfathom Deeps',`details_loc1`='The Warchief has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Blackfathom Deeps, north of Zoram\'gar Outpost, immediately!$B$BThe Twilight\'s Hammer threatens the world with its actions there! If you so choose, head to Blackfathom Deeps and speak with Je\'neu Sancrea, a member of the Earthen Ring, to help stop the Twilight threat.' WHERE `entry`=28010;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Adventurers Wanted: Blackfathom Deeps',`details_loc1`='King Varian Wrynn has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Blackfathom Deeps, west of Astranaar, immediately!$B$BThe Twilight\'s Hammer threatens the world with its actions there! If you so choose, head to Blackfathom Deeps and speak with Sentinel Aluwyn, head of the night elf effort there, to help stop the Twilight threat.' WHERE `entry`=28011;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='That Overseer Oilfist couldn\'t\'a picked a worse time to ask me to join a fight. My summit\'s already under siege!$B$BIt\'s nothin\' my guards can\'t handle, but still, it won\'t be easy for me to just pick up and send some dwarves into that infernal gorge.$B$BTell ya what: you take out their marksman that\'re holding our fortress under siege, and I\'ll consider your offer. Ye\'ll find \'em slinkin\' around the flats to the east.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='If nothin\' else, you bought us some time, and some room to open up our supply lines through this siege. Yer a fine $C.' WHERE `entry`=28028;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like ye know how to light things on fire!  An admirable trait in any $R, for sure.' WHERE `entry`=28029;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Southeastern tower ablaze',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Eastern Tower Ablaze' WHERE `entry`=28029;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll just divvy these up amongst the guards. Ye have my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=28030;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That must be the new I-Scream Cryocannon! Ain\'t she a beauty?! I\'m going to let you in on a secret, my good friend: the groundwork for a vast mercantile empire is being laid right here! Tell me... how do you feel about ice cream?' WHERE `entry`=28031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ooh, these are nice. Now, leave me alone with my gizzards. I\'ve got studying to do! Yes, very interesting. Very interesting indeed...' WHERE `entry`=28032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well well well. Look who come searching for Lunk this time! This sounds like case for Lunk\'s unique brand of no-kill problem-solve.' WHERE `entry`=28033;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did I stutter?  I believe I clearly stated that I... won\'t... Wow, ye\'ve got some good moves there!  I\'m impressed!' WHERE `entry`=28034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, Rendan\'s on our side?  About time that oaf came around. Let\'s get moving, then.' WHERE `entry`=28035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You\'ve got some fight in you, $C. You might do well in the crucible.$B$BWhat!? You haven\'t heard of the Crucible of Carnage? That smarmy goblin Gurgthock and his Troll sidekick have been plastering us with leaflets ever since he set up shop here in the Highlands. Champions from all over Azeroth fight to the death in there. You should gather up some friends and see how you fare.$B$BThe Crucible is just to the southwest. Look for Wodin the Troll-Servant somewhere in the middle of a ring of bones.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, you\'re one big strong heap of $C. Can you handle the crucible? We got bookies are standing by!' WHERE `entry`=28038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Welcome, friend, welcome! I\'m going to give you the chance to get involved at the ground level of a once-in-a-lifetime opportuntity. The entrepreneurial spirit knows nothing of the differences between the Alliance and the Horde! Tell me... how do you feel about ice cream?' WHERE `entry`=28042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That was an impressive aerial display, $N, but I wish it had come at a better time. Narkrall is a great warrior, but he\'s also an impatient fool. He\'s about to get himself killed ... and we\'re about to lose one of our most important weapons in the battle for the Highlands!' WHERE `entry`=28043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Claw of Tichondrius... You hold a piece of the very demon that led the Legion to these woods, $N. Better for it to be in our hands than with the satyr. Hold still. I\'m going to pull you back to our plane and make sure you and the claw arrive here safely...' WHERE `entry`=28044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh yeah! This is going to be the greatest flavor in the world! Look out, Tigule and Foror!!!' WHERE `entry`=28045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time someone took those guys out.' WHERE `entry`=28046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do you hear that, $N? That\'s the sweet hum of the refrigeration kicking in. We\'ll be able to store our inventory down there in no time. Thank you!' WHERE `entry`=28047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Third pipe frozen',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Fourth pipe frozen' WHERE `entry`=28047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Outstanding! Nothing can stop us from being the greatest purveyors of ice cream in all of Azeroth!' WHERE `entry`=28048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh good, you\'re back! Don\'t leave me alone with her! She\'s crazy! Gimme that, I\'ll have you seeing the invisible in no time!' WHERE `entry`=28049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No way, you actually killed him?  We are having shark tacos tonight for sure!' WHERE `entry`=28050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. They gave their lives for ice cream.' WHERE `entry`=28051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, here we are. I hope you\'re ready, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28052;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done good. I don\'t like slavery either.' WHERE `entry`=28054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Strange how so many slaves cope poorly with freedom. It\'s a shame to have to do what we do, but such are the truths of war. Now, we must move on to more pressing tasks.' WHERE `entry`=28055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A fight well-fought, $N!  I\'m beginning to feel the tide turn. Now, when you\'re ready, let\'s hit these Dark Irons where it really hurts!' WHERE `entry`=28056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It\'s a little known fact that dwarves, particularly of the Dark Iron variety, need rest! Lots of rest!$B$BNow I ask you; How can they sleep without pillows?  Exactly, $N, they can\'t. This is why you must steal their pillows.$B$BOnce you\'ve finished your cushion-thievery, talk with Taskmaster Scrange. He\'s a bit deeper in the cave, working on a covert project with Hansel.',`objectives_loc1`='Obtain 16 Dark Iron Pillows.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see Evonice is up to her old tricks again. I guess I\'ll just... um... hang onto these pillows for a while. The important part is that you\'re here. We\'re going to need your help.' WHERE `entry`=28057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is better than even I could have thought possible! The Chambermaid\'s magical pillow is mine! You better believe you\'re going to get a nice reward for this accomplishment, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You killed him?  We have been trying to take that guy out for weeks!  We thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Twilight\'s Hammer, eh?  I should\'ve expected as much. I\'m glad you arrived to help them out when you did. It looks like, despite all odds, we\'ve pressed our offensive to the doorstep of Calcinder\'s lair. It\'s now time to finish the job.' WHERE `entry`=28060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for rounding these up for us, $N. Kind of hard to fight a battle without any guns.' WHERE `entry`=28063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our task is complete, and it\'s all thanks to you, $N. I\'d like to offer you your choice from our coffers. In addition, I intend to make you a full-fledged member of our order. Welcome to the Thorium Brotherhood, $N. I\'m proud to call you a brother.' WHERE `entry`=28064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You saved our men!  No words can express our gratitude $N.' WHERE `entry`=28065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='King Varian Wrynn has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Blackrock Depths, northwest of Morgan\'s Vigil, immediately!$B$BThe Dark Iron dwarves pose a serious threat to the citizens of Redridge! If you so choose, head to Blackrock Depths and speak with Morgan, who has returned from her extended absence and wishes to enact her vengeance on the Dark Iron nation.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You look eager to kill a few hundred Dark Irons in justice\'s name. Perfect.' WHERE `entry`=28068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'ve managed to take this small area, but to do anything more we\'ll need your help.' WHERE `entry`=28069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I know nothing of the Elder Crone, Magatha. What I do know is that the Twilight\'s Hammer is destroying Highperch. Will you help me to stop them, $C?' WHERE `entry`=28085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They\'re precious. One day they\'ll grow strong, but until then, they must be protected.' WHERE `entry`=28086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There\'ll be no more trapping this day!' WHERE `entry`=28087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The Twilight\'s Hammer have the alpha male of Highperch pinned down. You must head east up the ramp and release Heartrazor before the pride loses it\'s patriarch!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The great Heartrazor is a majestic creature. He has told me of his gratitude and fondness for you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I was wondering when reinforcements would show up. Suit up, $N. It\'s time to dispense some justice!' WHERE `entry`=28089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good going. Doesn\'t look like much, does it?' WHERE `entry`=28090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. Now we can start pushing our ground forces up towards Grim Batol.' WHERE `entry`=28091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Works like a charm, every time.' WHERE `entry`=28092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The gate is clear. Once your people finish clearing the canyon, we will speak to your leaders about the next move.' WHERE `entry`=28093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc1`='Grim Batol entrance secured' WHERE `entry`=28093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We make it look easy.' WHERE `entry`=28094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So how was it? Everything that you dreamed it would be? Exciting, no?$B$BNo?$B$B<Darthalia sighs.>$B$BI can see that you\'re a true $G hero:heroine;. You need action. I guess a "desk job" isn\'t for you.' WHERE `entry`=28096;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The canyon is well fortified, but the distraction that the dragons are providing should be enough to allow us to break through.' WHERE `entry`=28097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The pridelings did what? They must love you deeply for freeing them. Thank you, $N. You\'ve saved Highperch!' WHERE `entry`=28098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is, unfortunately, as I expected. These bracers bear the indelible mark of the firelord and his minions. Very well. With no Horde or Alliance forces anywhere near this godforsaken gorge, it falls upon the Thorium Brotherhood to stop this Archduke before he spreads any more of his evil.' WHERE `entry`=28099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You... yes, you! I have chosen you, $R, as my champion! You will do the work of Ruumbo!' WHERE `entry`=28100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The red dragons have agreed to help! No small feat, I\'m sure. You have the thanks of the Alliance. We\'d already laid out plans for our ambush on a Twilight caravan by the time the dragons contacted us. They\'re helping by cutting off their retreat. The battle still rages. You can definitely be of aid.' WHERE `entry`=28101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A few of the remaining satyr have fled into the deeper woods, but they have taken heavy losses. Good job, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. Now we can start pushing our ground forces up towards Grim Batol.' WHERE `entry`=28103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good going. Doesn\'t look like much, does it?' WHERE `entry`=28104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent, $N. We will make our way out of here soon enough.' WHERE `entry`=28105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We make it look easy.' WHERE `entry`=28107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Like a well-oiled machine.' WHERE `entry`=28108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The gate is clear. Once your people finish clearing the canyon, we will speak to your leaders about the next move.' WHERE `entry`=28109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re in a bit of a bind, $C. Sarus\' spiders are starting to get a little uppity as we\'ve been unable to feed them for days. If we leave the murlocs will overtake our post! Furthermore, Warden Stillwater over at the Sludge Fields is demanding that we send him more humans! He is insatiable! We need help!' WHERE `entry`=28111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is true then?  An outsider rescued Prince Nadun from the Neferset? We are truly in your debt, stranger.' WHERE `entry`=28112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='See what can get done with a little cooperation? I\'ll make sure the claw is given to people responsible enough to contain such things... assuming it can\'t be destroyed.' WHERE `entry`=28113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful! Now to place these eggs into a nice, dark alcove inside the mine and let the miracle of life happen!' WHERE `entry`=28114;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The bear gods are cruel masters. They will continue to populate this world with bears until the end of days. It is our right as civilized people to make use of this nuisance - for the betterment of us all!' WHERE `entry`=28115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wonderful. Greta chose wisely when she asked you to perform this task. I will work the herbs immediately...' WHERE `entry`=28116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You made it back out alive?  You are a stronger man than I, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Galus is dead?  Fantastic work $N, now we can send down the cleanup crew and get that cellblock ready for new prisoners.' WHERE `entry`=28118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The flowers you brought me were the essential ingredient.$B$BProtective barriers surround Shadow Hold, projected from demonic braziers. If we are to drive the Shadow Council from Felwood, then those braziers must be extinguished.$B$BThis vial has been infused with Crying Violet and the magic of the wilds. Fill it at the corrupted moonwell in the center of Jaedenar and return to me.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='This will do nicely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28119;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These journals are in excellent condition $N. We will begin deciphering them immediately. Only time will tell what secrets they hold.' WHERE `entry`=28120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, $N! With their numbers weakened, we can soon begin our assault on their forces deep within Shadow Hold.' WHERE `entry`=28121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You actually killed him?!  I can\'t believe it!' WHERE `entry`=28122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' If the stories are true, $N, it was on this length of chain that Deathwing had once fastened the Demon Soul, forged in his bid to control the other dragonflights. The Demon Stone has long been destroyed but perhaps this hunk of elementium holds some residual power... You\'ve done a great thing today.' WHERE `entry`=28123;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad that you made it. Don\'t mind my new clothes. It seemed prudent to blend in.' WHERE `entry`=28124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You sure don\'t fool around, do you, $N? Well, it\'ll have to do.' WHERE `entry`=28125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Use the Purified Moon Well Water to douse the four Braziers of Protection within Shadow Hold.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the Braziers gone, the druids of the Emerald Circle can enter Shadow Hold and clear out the last of the cultists. In time, it may even be used as the barrow den it once was. You have my thanks, $N. Please take this reward.' WHERE `entry`=28126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Extinguish the Brazier of Suffering',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Extinguish the Brazier of Hatred' WHERE `entry`=28126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You give so much of yourself without requiring anything in return. The people of Thousand Needles are grateful, as am I.' WHERE `entry`=28127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The cleansing of Shadow Hold will take much time and effort, but without your defeat of the Shadow Council, it would not be possible at all. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28128;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The demons begin to fall! Take heed, $C. You will find even stronger foes deeper within Shadow Hold.' WHERE `entry`=28129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Told you that village was full of wackos. Nice job clearing it out $N.' WHERE `entry`=28130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Another demonic menace gone. It is time to find their master.' WHERE `entry`=28131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Bring \'Efficient Excavations\' to Belloc Brightblade in Schnottz\'s Landing.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh look, it\'s one of little Schnottz\'s pamphlets. I\'ll just be taking that from you, if you don\'t mind.' WHERE `entry`=28132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Once free of the chain, Torth died rather than submit again. I admire the creature. I will have his hide fashioned into a set of armor. This much is clear to me now: The Dragonmaw cannot stand alone if the Alliance backs the Wildhammer. Narkrall proved that. And you have proven the might of the Horde, again and again. I will rebuild our drake wings and take up position outside the Bastion of Twilight. You should continue to help out here in the Gullet and elsewhere in the Highlands.' WHERE `entry`=28133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Orsis!  Of course! How could I not have seen this?' WHERE `entry`=28134;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do you see what Deathwing\'s minions have done?  Great Orsis is now all but buried in the sand!' WHERE `entry`=28135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that those three are dealt with, the combined forces from Freewind Post should be able to handle the rest of the cultists here.' WHERE `entry`=28136;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These fish will do nicely, $N. Keeping the troops fed and in good condition is our number one priority and you really came through for us here.' WHERE `entry`=28137;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These will do nicely. I do wonder what the warden has planned for them. Last I heard the Sludge Fields were overrun by some very bad things.' WHERE `entry`=28138;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good. Now there\'s only one thing left to do.' WHERE `entry`=28139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you. The rumors I\'d heard about you are proving true after all.' WHERE `entry`=28141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It took you long enough. Do you think that we are playing games here?' WHERE `entry`=28142;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You should not keep the Elder Crone waiting, $N.$B$BShe said that she\'d be up top and just outside of the Twilight Withering to the east.' WHERE `entry`=28143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At least we\'ll be prepared for any future incidents. Moving "supplies" like this around is a risky proposition. You never know who is going to open their big fat mouth.$B$B<Keyton raises what appears to be an eyebrow at you.>' WHERE `entry`=28144;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Fill the Antidote Vial with the the poison of 8 Venomblood Scorpid corpses.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. We might yet save Iset.' WHERE `entry`=28145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This should keep it happy and content for a few days. You\'ve done a good thing here, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28146;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What did you manage to get? I suppose we can piece something together from this. After all, you\'re not joining the cult. We just need to fool a few ogres.' WHERE `entry`=28147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will see these are burned swiftly and safely, $N. You have my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=28148;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dat\'s de stuff, mon! Now can you hear dem? De spirits, dey be talkin\', but dey say nothing nice. Let us bring dem to de light.' WHERE `entry`=28149;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is little time for talk, $C. The druids fight valiantly against the satyr, but fel sorcery blocks their path. Luckily, I have a plan...' WHERE `entry`=28150;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! I\'m sure Twilight\'s Hammer wanted to number those ogres among their ranks. Now they\'ll probably have to fight them off instead. This is good, $N. With one well-placed $C we managed to do the work of a small army. I\'ll let Warlord Krogg know of your work here!' WHERE `entry`=28151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, just what I was expecting. With these herbs, our preparations for Jaedenar are nearly ready.' WHERE `entry`=28152;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Shadow Council is broken! One task remains...' WHERE `entry`=28153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Muckgill you say? Never heard of him. What is this anyway? Some kind of fin or something?' WHERE `entry`=28154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Truly incredible, $N. To journey within the very lair of evil here and slay every fiend that stands before you... I am overwhelmed. The Emerald Circle thanks you for your work here in Felwood. As for Andalar, we will send scouts to rescue him at once. He shall have a hero\'s welcome.' WHERE `entry`=28155;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you ever heard the saying "survival of the fittest?" What you\'re doing conflicts with natural law, $G buddy:lady;! This idiot should have died in the mines. There\'s no telling what kind of harm he\'ll cause to himself or another person now that you\'ve saved him from his inevitable demise.$B$BAnd you know who\'s fault that\'ll be, right?' WHERE `entry`=28156;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'ll combine them into a suitable form. I\'ll keep it\'s use simple.' WHERE `entry`=28157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A simple task for a simple boy. Let us see if you have what it takes to finish the job.' WHERE `entry`=28158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Surprising... you lived. I thank you for doing my dirty work, $C. You kept my hands clean while ridding me of some incompetent Grimtotem leaders. Not only do I have the Rattle of Bones, the Writ of History, and the Drums of War, but I now have the ultimate artifact: the Doomstone!' WHERE `entry`=28159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, she\'s evil! But, what does it mean, $N? Is Magatha going to destroy us? Is she in charge of the Twilight\'s Hammer now? Whatever happens, you\'ve delivered us from our enemies. Please allow me to show you our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=28160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Wow, she\'s evil! But, what does it mean, $N? Is Magatha going to destroy us? Is she in charge of the Twilight\'s Hammer now? Whatever happens, you\'ve delivered us from our enemies. Please allow me to show you our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=28161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like you were able to get the croc hides that we needed. Thanks $N, your contributions will not go unnoticed.' WHERE `entry`=28162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Those filthy horde never stood a chance. Nice work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28163;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I just received word that you are needed in Orgrimmar, $N. Brother Silverhallow has asked for you to return to the city as quickly as you are able. His message didn\'t include any other information, and the matter seemed urgent.$B$BLook for Brother Silverhallow in the Goblin Slums of Orgrimmar.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Brother Silverhallow in the Goblin Slums of Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m glad to see you received my message.' WHERE `entry`=28164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='D-Block is all clear?  Good work, $N. We will send down a crew to start cleaning up right away.' WHERE `entry`=28165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, dis be it, mon. We be ready to bring dem spirits out de shadows now.' WHERE `entry`=28166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did Nevin send you ahead? That means he\'s getting ready to end the mission, but there are still survivors to be rescued. We have to help them!' WHERE `entry`=28167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Who are you? Did Sylvanas send you? Everything is FINE! Yes, perfectly fine! I\'ve got it all under control!$B$BWell, fine all things considered that is... We\'ve got a few problems that perhaps you could help with, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to meet you, $C. We rarely come across survivors as strong and capable as you are. I can help get you decontaminated and on your way out of here.' WHERE `entry`=28169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You see! De dead be nothing to be scared of. You brought de light to de darkness, mon, and never flinched. We can use dis cave now as a base of operations in de northern Highlands. You\'re de best, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It seems you are still with us. I\'m somewhat appreciative of that. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=28171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will see to it that these dragons are taken care of.' WHERE `entry`=28172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You seem to have made use of the disturbing implements with ease. I take solace in knowing that some tools of evil can ultimately still lead to safeguarding life. Nothing is without purpose.' WHERE `entry`=28173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you\'re in, then? Good.' WHERE `entry`=28174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve started a wonderful thing this day, amidst all of this blood shed. It may take many years, but this ravaged land will be restored. It will be beautiful again.' WHERE `entry`=28175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lirastraza sent me ahead to the lair, suspecting the black dragon we are seeking may still be here. Judging by the hatchlings, it seems she was not mistaken.' WHERE `entry`=28176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Those scorpids are easy to underestimate. You\'re lucky you didn\'t end up on the end of one of these barbs. Or maybe you\'re just good. I\'ll add these to the stockpile. We\'re not done yet, $R.' WHERE `entry`=28177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='We\'ll need worg hides, and lots of them. It doesn\'t matter if they\'re torn, burned, or bloody, but we need plenty of them.$B$BActually, it\'s probably better if they\'re a little beat-up.$B$BYou\'ll find worgs both to the west and to the east of here.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Believe me, $N... I\'m just as anxious to get to the killing as you are. We\'ve got to keep to the plan. The armageddon will come soon enough. I\'ll keep these hides here.' WHERE `entry`=28178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is exactly what we need. Don\'t worry, $N... the orc-killing will come soon enough.' WHERE `entry`=28179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gah!  Who are you? Oh, so Keeshan sent you?  Good. Would ya mind sticking around for a while?  It\'s nothing big... I just need you to kill some warlocks for me.' WHERE `entry`=28180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope that\'s what Keeshan was looking for. It\'s not doing me much good right now, anyhow.' WHERE `entry`=28181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Knowing the way those orcs operate, there\'ll be another one to take his place soon. I\'ll see if I can\'t sneak back into the altar before that happens. Thanks, buddy.' WHERE `entry`=28182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Good, good, good. We can move on. Our war takes us east, away from Blackrock Mountain... for now.' WHERE `entry`=28183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ll have to excuse me, but we\'re not taking visitors right now. I\'ll ask you to leave Chiselgrip out the same door you came in. Oh, Keeshan... is that you?' WHERE `entry`=28184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Svarnos is finally dead?  Looks like we can finally get to work setting up that cellblock then. Thank you $N.' WHERE `entry`=28185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The shackles!  We will begin the process of destroying these shackles immediately $N. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=28186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Okay, $R! Zhis just got real!$B$BSomevone zhinks zhat zhey can get rid of me zhat easily, hmm?$B$BVe shall see about zhat! Nozhink can shtop zhis vork! Nozhink!$B$B<Schnottz looks around at the encroaching flames.>$B$BVe should probably get out of here.$B$BHuury up! Time is vastink!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is times like zhese, zhat one learns who his friends really are...' WHERE `entry`=28187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You cleared that area out?  Looks like you might be more useful to us that we thought, $R.' WHERE `entry`=28188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Undoubtedly you did the right thing. Hopefully the humans that you saved will show similar mercy to you should the time of your planting ever come.$B$BThis is all assuming you rescued the humans and didn\'t splatter their brains all over the dirt - of course.$B$BKeep the shovel as a reminder of the horrors of the Sludge Fields and the depravity of mortals.' WHERE `entry`=28189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='My rage quells at the news... perhaps I will find it easier to rest and heal now.$B$BMaybe my stomach will settle as well. Urgh...' WHERE `entry`=28190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve proven a great ally. I would have never expected such upon our first meeting.' WHERE `entry`=28191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As you can see, they\'re all monsters! Most of my guards died and the ones that managed to escape are now holding down the barricades, preventing any of these potentially dangerous creatures from getting out.$B$BWe need your help!' WHERE `entry`=28192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Zhey know nozhink, you say? Very vell, zhen. Zhe search goes on...' WHERE `entry`=28193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are perfect, $C. Wish us luck!' WHERE `entry`=28194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Commander Schnottz wants you to kill Captain Margun, Captain Cork, and Captain Kronkh',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very good, $R...' WHERE `entry`=28195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Warden Stillwater flips through the journal, reading under his breath.>$B$BRamblings of a mad man! Clearly he had been ingesting the mushrooms. It is good that you brought this to me, $N. I will burn it myself!' WHERE `entry`=28196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done! Wilkes was hanged after we discovered that he was ingesting mass quantities of mushrooms and other highly toxic substances. After he died he awoke, reborn as an undead geist. Many of my guards fell to Wilkes before he ran off into hiding. Fearing something like this might happen again, we incinerated the Clerk until only bones were left!$B$BWhy would they willingly ingest toxic substances? I have no idea! This is a farm, $G sir:miss;, nothing more!' WHERE `entry`=28197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is a great honor to meet you, $N!  I\'ve heard much about you.' WHERE `entry`=28198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These samples will give us a better understanding of the mindless undead. Take these coins as a reward.' WHERE `entry`=28199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent job, $N. You might not think this adds up to much, but this might very well be the difference between life and death to one of our soldiers.' WHERE `entry`=28200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a born leader, $N. It\'ll be good to have you by our side when war comes to these lands.' WHERE `entry`=28201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it?  That\'s your disguise? I\'m feeling less confident about our chances. It was nice knowing you, kid.' WHERE `entry`=28202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it?  That\'s your disguise? I\'m feeling less confident about our chances. It was nice knowing you, kid.' WHERE `entry`=28203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it?  That\'s your disguise? I\'m feeling less confident about our chances. It was nice knowing you, kid.' WHERE `entry`=28204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it?  That\'s your disguise? I\'m feeling less confident about our chances. It was nice knowing you, kid.' WHERE `entry`=28205;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Johnny is sobbing loudly.>$B$BTw... Twinkles!!!! Th... It killed her!$B$B<Johnny continues to cry. Little snot bubbles form in his nostrils.>' WHERE `entry`=28206;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most people think the green glow is demonic corruption... but if you\'ve got an eye for shades and hues like me, you can tell it\'s the energies of the emerald dream! These little guys aren\'t being corrupted by the waters, they\'re doing their best to purify it!$B$BNow we\'ll mash \'em up and make a nice yummy paste for Mr. Tauren to eat and feel all better.' WHERE `entry`=28207;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Poor little kitty, suffering out there in the woods for so long! You did a good thing for it, $N. And probably for all the travelers it\'s been eating.$B$BThis tag will be handy...' WHERE `entry`=28208;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Lydon takes the key from you.>$B$BI\'ll let myself out, thanks.$B$BI have never been so angry! Stillwater won\'t get away with this. I will present his head to the Banshee Queen myself.$B$BYou and I will work together, $N.$B$BI don\'t know about the little girl here, but I\'d prefer she stayed behind.' WHERE `entry`=28209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well... that wasn\'t all that great, was it?' WHERE `entry`=28210;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at that - OW! Pointy! Hot! These spears should cut through that dragonhide like an electric cheese-slicing apparatus through butter.' WHERE `entry`=28211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Marvelous! I\'ll smelt this down into a delicious soup. An angry soup. Of molten metal.' WHERE `entry`=28212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hooray! The forest will be safer now!$B$BYou\'re such a hero, $N! With everything you\'ve done for me and Mr. Tauren and the trees and animals and flowers, you deserve a reward!$B$BYay!' WHERE `entry`=28213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $C. I\'m feeling much better now, and can appreciate the news that those abominations are gone.$B$BYou still might not want to stand too close, just in case...' WHERE `entry`=28214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Terrific! These coils will decompress with the force of a thousand suns! That\'s just a rough approximation of course, don\'t hold me accountable for those numbers.' WHERE `entry`=28215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aye, that\'s him. Can you believe this thing was human once? That\'s the Twilight\'s Hammer for you. What they don\'t destroy, they corrupt. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='How noble of you... to blindly kill without question, to come for my head on the barest word of another.$B$BSheathe your fury and hear my tale first. You\'ll see what noble ignorance has done to these lands.' WHERE `entry`=28217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And so my master set out to find the skull... risking his own life against an army of demons to find the source of corruption in Felwood. Imagine if he had not! Imagine what these woods would look like if the Skull of Gul\'dan had continued its work, undisturbed...' WHERE `entry`=28218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<The seedling pats its stalk with a rooty arm, as if full. It looks to have grown a bit, too!>' WHERE `entry`=28219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<The seedling coils its roots in what looks like a happy manner.>$B$BGrow... big...' WHERE `entry`=28220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So happy! Can you hear us? We\'re so many friends now.$B$BBigger and bigger, with room for each friend...' WHERE `entry`=28221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So warm and fresh and full of life. We love the sun, it makes us stronger.$B$BSoon now, very soon is the time of growing...' WHERE `entry`=28222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, the wardens key\'s. Another job well done, $N. These will come in very handy.' WHERE `entry`=28223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes... it is time.' WHERE `entry`=28224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that\'s what I like to see!  Yer alright, $R.' WHERE `entry`=28225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is exactly what we needed. I\'ll get the boys workin\' on the next batch of golems right away.' WHERE `entry`=28226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yer a lifesaver, $N. With golems like these, we won\'t have to worry about Dark Irons, Blackrock orcs... maybe even dragons! If ye ever need anything from the Thorium Brotherhood, don\'t hesitate to ask. That goes for yer friends, too.' WHERE `entry`=28227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Someday I will spread my branches across a renewed forest, full of life and hope.$B$BFarewell, $N. Have patience... and if you live long, you may see me again one day.' WHERE `entry`=28228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The moonwell water quickly seeps into the ground with a soft glow. A few moments later, a rustling noise is heard, and a small sprout pops up before your eyes.' WHERE `entry`=28229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Once we deal with the rest of the undead we will confront Stillwater!' WHERE `entry`=28230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='She may now ascend to the great horsey heaven in the stars. We will never forget you, Twinkles. NEVER!' WHERE `entry`=28231;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These rations will really help the troops out $N. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=28232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Don\'t be looking!  I\'m not wearin\' me pants!' WHERE `entry`=28233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you!  Now turn around so I can put\'em on.' WHERE `entry`=28234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now to bring Warden Stillwater to justice!' WHERE `entry`=28235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Me brother Bahrum has gone missing!$B$BHe was one of the first scouts in the area. All the others have returned safely, but there be no sign of him. Da says he\'s just dawdling somewhere, but he\'s me only brother, and I promised me mum that I would keep him safe. Will you please find him?' WHERE `entry`=28236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will deliver this head to the Banshee Queen personally. Of course I will make mention of your part in all of this, $N.$B$BAs for your reward - take from Stillwater\'s cache whatever you desire. You earned it.' WHERE `entry`=28237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='A ride to the Highlands, then? I\'ve just the thing! I\'ll make room for yeh in me seaplane. I\'ll have to ditch the cat-food I was packing, yeh know, in case we crash in the mountains and ain\'t rescued fer weeks. On second thought, jes\' keep the cat food on yer lap, aye.' WHERE `entry`=28238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Speak with Quartermaster Kaoshin at the Black Tooth Hovel in Burning Steppes.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Where have you been, grunt?  You\'re late!  Give me one reason why I shouldn\'t kill you on the spot!' WHERE `entry`=28239;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<The eye speaks to you, its \'voice\' reverberating as if coming from everywhere at once.>$B$BYou seek my sight, $R? My powers come at a price. These disciples of the twilight have been honoring me with the blood of Wildhammer dwarves from the nearby ruins, but still I thirst. Perhaps you can do better.$B$BSlay my old masters, and my vision is yours. Honor me with the slaughter of the Shaman of the Black. Blood is blood, after all.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Ah, the succulent thrill of life extinguished. Do you feel it, $C? Do you relish it as I do? No, I see not. You fight to protect the lives of others. Pity.' WHERE `entry`=28242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You found one? A gen-u-ine Eye of Twilight? Lemme see. Oh Gods. It\'s lookin\' at me. It\'s lookin\' right back! I need a drink. Can you face that thing toward the wall or somethin\'?' WHERE `entry`=28243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What did you see, $N? Cho\'gall? Wait - he saw YOU!? Oh aye, that wee sneaky eye! It looks both ways. That cheeky looker! Where\'s me hammer!?' WHERE `entry`=28244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmph. Good work, grunt.' WHERE `entry`=28245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not only did you pull off the executions, you made them all look like accidents! You were the right $R for this undercover work. Good job, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=28246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You killed Obsidia within her own lair? Impressive, $R. I\'m sorry that I could not be there. You\'re true to your word, and you most certainly have the bite to back your bellow. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=28247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. We\'re in the process of preparing the attack now.' WHERE `entry`=28248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done well, $N. We\'re in the process of preparing the attack now.' WHERE `entry`=28249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You showed those thieving little scoundrels!  Great job.' WHERE `entry`=28250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The worgen situation hasn\'t gotten any better and Helcular is really creeping me out.' WHERE `entry`=28251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I didn\'t count on obtaining an item like this. I will change our plans accordingly.' WHERE `entry`=28253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You need a disguise?  Well, you came to the right place, honey. Let me take a look... mm-hmm. I know exactly what we\'ll do.' WHERE `entry`=28254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now you are beginning to see...' WHERE `entry`=28256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Do you see now? For doing what was needed to drive the demons from these lands, my master was banished.$B$BNow these druids pick up the pieces, patting themselves on the back for scrubbing the remaining vestiges of the legion\'s forces.$B$BBut that is not why I killed them.' WHERE `entry`=28257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see you again, $N. I wish I could say that I had happy news.' WHERE `entry`=28258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you received my message. An opportunity has presented itself, $N, one which will allow us to demonstrate just how important we are to the success of Stormwind and the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=28259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll be brief, $N. Our enemies are gathering and Stormwind needs our help.' WHERE `entry`=28260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Enough! Your enthusiasm is impressive, but foolish. Gazing through the veil for too long without practice will break your mind.$B$BThe rest will be mine, $N. For now, I summon you back to me.' WHERE `entry`=28261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $N. We have much to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=28262;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see you again, $N. Stormwind has need of your skills.' WHERE `entry`=28263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I find it hard to believe everything you say, but the body of that demon is grim proof.$B$BI will order an investigation into the druids at Jadefire Run right away, and make sure my higher-ups know the demon hunter may be content to remain in exile.' WHERE `entry`=28264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='More outsiders?  What do you want?' WHERE `entry`=28265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I had a feeling you\'d be the one returning to me. I like your style, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=28266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, this Schnottz character is working with Deathwing!? This is even more distressing than you think...' WHERE `entry`=28267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I wish had good news to share with you, $N, but the truth is that I have asked you here because we have need of your talents.' WHERE `entry`=28268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='So, listen to this, $N.$B$BI knew that these obelisks were linked to the Coffer of Promise, but there\'s more to it.$B$BThere appears to be something very important about the coffer - something pertaining to a place the Makers called the Halls of Origination.$B$BNow that we know this Schnottz fellow and his crew are in league with Deathwing, it\'s all the more urgent that we get to it first.$B$BI\'ll wait for you north of here, at the Oasis of Vir\'sar$B$BHurry! They have a head start on us!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, glad you could make it. I could use a hand here.' WHERE `entry`=28269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job with Schnottz\'s men. Sounds like you gave them something to think about. Hopefully it bought us the time we need.' WHERE `entry`=28271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Yes... yes... perfect! I\'ll need some time to make sense of these, but the information is there. Good work, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome $C! You and I are going to be good friends! I can tell already.' WHERE `entry`=28273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Here we are, $N! Great things will happen here... magical things!' WHERE `entry`=28274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work on those supply ships, $N!  We knew you would be good for somethin\' around here.' WHERE `entry`=28275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aren\'t they beautiful?' WHERE `entry`=28276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Speak to Salhet and slay 30 Bloodsnarl Scavengers',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad, huh?  Maybe you can put a word in with the high commander. Maybe he\'ll put us in charge of our own squad!' WHERE `entry`=28277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have a feeling we\'ll be hearing about you and your exploits for a long time, soldier. I look forward to fighting by your side in Redridge. You are dismissed.' WHERE `entry`=28278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Without those sergeants, Thorg\'izog will be hard-pressed getting his troops ready for battle. Already the dominoes are beginning to fall, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it, $N! Alliance ingenuity to the rescue. Of course, I don\'t have anything to help you fight the dismounted riders now that they\'re on the ground. You\'re a $C; improvise!' WHERE `entry`=28280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You sure know your way around a battlefield, $C. It looks like they\'re about to fall back. All we need is one decisive blow...' WHERE `entry`=28281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='There\'s one Dragonmaw among this lot, the one they call "Narkrall: The Drake-Tamer." I don\'t know where he gets his power over those beasts, but the black terror he rides is as nasty a brute as ever took the skies over the Highlands.$B$B$N, Narkrall is the fiend who took my father\'s life and left Thundermar in my hands.$B$BI can\'t take him on alone, but I\'ve seen what you\'re capable of, $C. Maybe together we can end this.$B$BLet me know when you\'re ready, and we\'ll fight Narkrall together!',`objectives_loc1`='Slay Narkrall Rakeclaw. Speak with Colin Thundermar when you\'re ready.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We did it, $N! Narkrall Rakeclaw lies dead at my feet, and Thundermar has weathered a storm of drakes! This wouldn\'t have been possible if it weren\'t for the help of the Alliance. I owe you a debt that I don\'t think can ever be repaid.' WHERE `entry`=28282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Interesting....' WHERE `entry`=28283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Interesting....' WHERE `entry`=28284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Light has answered my prayers. At last, you have arrived.' WHERE `entry`=28285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You alright? Good. You did a fine job out there, $N. Now pack up your things. We\'re moving out of here.' WHERE `entry`=28286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $N. We will need your skills in the continuing battle against Twilight\'s Hammer.' WHERE `entry`=28287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see... their eyes are open Maybe I\'ll keep Impsy around after all. He\'s got a lot to teach me...' WHERE `entry`=28288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see you again, $N. I wish I could say that I had happy news.' WHERE `entry`=28289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde has need of your skills, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Salhet?  A tactician, you say? Hah!  Very well, if you\'ll vouch for him, we might be able to arrange something.' WHERE `entry`=28291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Uldum? What about it?' WHERE `entry`=28292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Uldum? What about Uldum? Speak quickly!' WHERE `entry`=28293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello, $C! Keegan Firebeard here has told me all about your heroics down south. Thank you for all of your efforts on behalf of the Wildhammer. I see Colin Thundermar is right behind you. The summit is ready to begin! Please stay and let\'s see how things unfold...' WHERE `entry`=28294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Harrison sent you, hmm? How fortunate!' WHERE `entry`=28295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Belloc sent you, hmm? How fortunate!' WHERE `entry`=28296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde has need of your skills, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Shattered Hand needs your skills, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I have just received word from Zevrost, Orgrimmar\'s foremost warlock trainer. He wishes you to travel to Orgrimmar and speak with him in the cleft of shadow. It sounds like he has an important mission for you.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Zevrost in Orgrimmar\'s Cleft of Shadow.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde will soon call upon your skills, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28299;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde needs your help in the battle against our enemies.' WHERE `entry`=28300;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='I just received an urgent message addressed to you, $N. It\'s from Kardris Dreamseeker, one of the shaman trainers in Orgrimmar. She wants you to travel to Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Wisdom and speak with her as soon as you can.',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with Kardris Dreamseeker in Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Wisdom.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='These are dangerous times, $N. The Horde is fortunate to have taurens like you in its ranks.' WHERE `entry`=28301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde will soon have need of your skills, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28302;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are one of the most promising young paladins I have ever trained, $N. It is for that reason that I wish to offer you a dangerous mission.' WHERE `entry`=28303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our enemies stir once more, $N, and you will be at the forefront of battle.' WHERE `entry`=28304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, hi! Did Farlus send you? I\'m so happy he remembered!$B$BBloodvenom Post is all overrun with awful slime thingies, and this poor tauren is the only one left! We\'ve got to help him!' WHERE `entry`=28305;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='You\'ve been such a big help here!$B$BI\'m gonna stay here a while and look after poor Mr. Tauren until he stops throwing up so much. Why don\'t you head north to Whisperwind Grove? It\'s really pretty there, and all the druids are so friendly!$B$BYou should tell miss Puregrove I\'m okay, she\'ll worry if I\'m gone too long. She might ask you to help with her flowers, too! So fun!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Kelnir? Hahaha... Sometimes I wonder if her chatter drove all the other dryads away. But I\'m glad she is safe. Welcome to Whisperwind Grove, $C. Hold peace in your heart, and you will find a home here.' WHERE `entry`=28306;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Tyelis, a member of the the Silvermoon delegation to Orgrimmar, has requested to meet with you next time you\'re in the city. You can find him inside Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Strength. It must be an important matter for him to send for you so directly, $N.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde has need of your talents, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28307;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc1`='Meet with Seer Liwatha',`details_loc1`='Seer Liwatha sends her greetings from the Valley of Wisdom in Orgrimmar, $N. She asked me to convey an invitation to visit her next time you\'re in the city. It sounded like she has something of importance to discuss with you.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde has need of your talents, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28308;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve arrived!  And just in time for the friendship ceremony! Captain Winky!  Where\'d Captain Winky go? No, don\'t tell me he got cold feet!' WHERE `entry`=28310;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, these will do. I will get this packed up for you.' WHERE `entry`=28311;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='To the untrained eye, these will look exactly like imps. We just need to get them to that untrained eye. I\'ll work on preparing them for delivery.' WHERE `entry`=28312;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This meat looks good... but I think it needs a little "seasoning". I\'ll make sure that gets taken care of. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28313;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' That was exactly what I needed.' WHERE `entry`=28314;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your kill count is adding up, $N. We\'re chipping away at them. And we are going to win. Redridge will NOT fall to these cowards.' WHERE `entry`=28315;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, the whelplings. I will take care of them. As for the agreement I made with your Colonel Troteman earlier, tell him that I will hold up my end of the bargain. You will have your dragon for the battle against the orcs. We hold no particular love for the Redridge Mountains, but we do share your grudge against the Blackrock clan.' WHERE `entry`=28316;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well would you look at that!  My favorite soldier comes through in the clutch! I\'ll make sure to get this distributed among the ogres. I\'ll see you in Redridge, soldier. For the glory of the Blackrock!' WHERE `entry`=28317;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What are these?  Oh, are these imps? I\'m pretty sure that imps don\'t just fall asleep in boxes! I\'ll take your word for it, though. I don\'t understand any of this warlock crap. Leave them in the corner.' WHERE `entry`=28318;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Pff!  You\'re late!  Do you know how long I\'ve been waiting for Ner\'gosh to deliver this orb? There\'s something strange about this orb... it\'s too... Never mind, it must be my nerves talking. Thank you for the delivery. For blood and honor!' WHERE `entry`=28319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Did you see them run?  They didn\'t know what was happening!  Beautiful! Our job\'s almost done, $N. It\'s time to deliver the deathblow.' WHERE `entry`=28320;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Welcome home, boys.' WHERE `entry`=28321;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You peer inside, and find...' WHERE `entry`=28322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Speak with Brother Silverhallow in Orgrimmar\'s Goblin Slums.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you got my message. Good. I have an important task for you.' WHERE `entry`=28323;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh my. 250? This thing doesn\'t go past 250. How are you still standing? You should be a puddle of goo by now. Sylvanas will be most displeased with this information. There might be some things we can do to reduce the lethality levels of the area by a few decades, but that still leaves us out by about a hundred or so years.' WHERE `entry`=28324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Recycling! It\'s all the craze these days. The Banshee Queen has decreed that we must conserve if we are to prosper as a people. Everyone must do their part, right? With that said, you will be doing our part for us.$B$BThere are likely thousands of blight canister bits and pieces all over Southshore. We can reuse those canisters for more blight bombing goodness. Just head into the ruins here and pick up whatever you can find.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. You are incredibly resilient to this blight. We\'ll have to take you in for testing some time.' WHERE `entry`=28325;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, you\'re back. I hope you\'ve still got that disguise. You\'re going back undercover, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28326;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have done your work well, $N. While this will not stop Twilight\'s Hammer, it will help sow suspicion between them and the Dark Irons.' WHERE `entry`=28328;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='All signs indicate to a breeding pool being inside the ruined town hall. You\'ll need to investigate!' WHERE `entry`=28329;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perhaps with Chet vanquished, the lethality levels of this place will decrease a tad faster. A job well done, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28330;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='As I said, the rod giveth to our dark rangers and doth taketh away from our enemy!' WHERE `entry`=28331;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We should have killed Bloodfang in Silverpine. It\'s a shame he still lives. It\'s an even bigger shame that we have as of yet been unable to turn worgen into undead. Surely there is a way...' WHERE `entry`=28332;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Efficiency in the workforce! Wonderful. Maybe I should check on the goblins inside those shredders later.' WHERE `entry`=28333;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Mangy curs think they can just waltz in here and ruin my finely-tuned operation. Hah! I told you not to look directly at the flares, right? Oops.' WHERE `entry`=28334;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You turn the largest handle you can find on the Master Control Pump, and the rattling noises in the nearby pipes stop. This gives you a few moments to hear the sound of flames outside before a familiar voice cuts in through a tinny, craclikng speaker.' WHERE `entry`=28335;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s not working! We\'re going to have to shut it off at the source. Go talk to the Deputy outside, he\'ll walk you through it!' WHERE `entry`=28336;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is but the first strike.' WHERE `entry`=28337;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I sense that you have achieved victory. Victory... such a hollow word considering what had to be done. Regardless, you\'ve proven yourself to be worthy of our trust.$B$BIt may take some time before the Timbermaw welcome you without hostility within the Hold. Still, your perseverance will erode any suspicion my brethren may have about you. So long as you never betray us and raise weapons against us, we will find common ground.' WHERE `entry`=28338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank goodness the oil is safe! Well done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All my workers got driven straight out of the cavern here by those big swamp-lookin\' things! Darla\'s sent me here to pick up the pieces, but have you seen it in there? I ain\'t goin\' in!$B$BThere\'s a ton of explosives left behind that we can\'t just leave layin\' around$B$B I\'ll make you a deal: You run in there and get those explosives gathered up, and I will stay here and not get killed by swamp-things, and if you don\'t either, I\'ll pay ya! How\'s that sound?',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, nice! I\'ll just take those... carefully... Don\'t go tellin\' the workers I didn\'t have the guts to go down there myself, you hear? Here\'s your pay... and a little somethin\' extra.' WHERE `entry`=28340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can tell just from the size of these that the fel taint is healing. Slowly... but significantly.$B$BThank you, $N. I will ensure these are properly purged.' WHERE `entry`=28341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The infernals that lurk in Shatter Scar Vale are formidable, but not invincible. Much progress has been made in thinning their numbers$B$BDestroying them is only part of the solution, however. I\'ve found that the stone that infernals are made of still contains large amounts of fel magic even after the infernal\'s death.$B$BThe rubble of slain infernals now litters Shatter Scar Vale, leeching its corruption back into the ground. If you could collect it and bring it to me, I would be grateful.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s good to see someone who cares about keeping the forest clean. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'m heartened to have the Breath of Cenarius back where it belongs and I know the rest of the circle will be impressed by your efforts. You may have also set back the plans of the Twilight\'s Hammer clan a bit, too. Excellent work.' WHERE `entry`=28343;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='*GASP* HELP! DROWNING! *GURGLE*' WHERE `entry`=28344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I... uh... the human must have cast some type of mind-altering spell on Orkus. Orkus will explain.' WHERE `entry`=28345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What? Kurdran\'s talkin\' marriage!? Didn\'t he just see me an\' ol\' Thunderface tearing each other new ones? The only eligible Thundermar is Fanny. Now, I\'ll give you this, she\'s got the looks allright. All lumpy in the right places, if you hear me. But she\'s not got that somethun\' somethun\' a Firebeard looks for in a woman, right?' WHERE `entry`=28346;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will have my vengeance, but first we must heal Kasha.' WHERE `entry`=28348;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There he is! I think you\'re going to like this!' WHERE `entry`=28349;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fine work, my boy! You\'ll master this trapping skill in no time.' WHERE `entry`=28350;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Splendid! This is shaping up to be better than I had dared to dream!' WHERE `entry`=28351;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve done it! I now have camels to spare. Perhaps one day we shall take our show on the road!' WHERE `entry`=28352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Alright, kid. My research is complete. We\'re about ready to activate the final obelisk.' WHERE `entry`=28353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This mushroom is toxic to living things, but provides a restorative boost to the undead. Let us see how Kasha reacts.' WHERE `entry`=28354;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='HAH! Those naga have some balls on them! To think that they could take Southshore from us in our own territory! Such a preposterous notion.$B$B<Helcular laughs.>$B$BYou have done well to thwart their attack - though I do wonder if they could have survived for even a minute in the blight.' WHERE `entry`=28356;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let\'s hope we put down enough of them to get the message across.' WHERE `entry`=28357;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you for hunting in my stead, $C.$B$BI\'ve found I must pace myself... finding too much thrill in hunting demons is a dangerous path.' WHERE `entry`=28358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This foul chunk is what those warlocks sought year after year. I will protect it myself, or destroy it if possible, and ensure Kroshius never rises again.' WHERE `entry`=28359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. They won\'t spread the corruption any further, and they won\'t be in pain either.' WHERE `entry`=28360;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aren\'t they just adorable? It\'s those little victories that keep me going. We\'ll save this forest one squirrel at a time.' WHERE `entry`=28361;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Stupid, stupid Drizle! I told him not to go!$B$BDrizle wanted to steal more honey from Felpaw Village... you know, just west of here? You can see it from the cliff...$B$BAnyway... I told him it was a dumb idea but he went anyway, and then the Deadwood tribe got him, and... and...$B$BSniff...$B$BI don\'t know what they\'re gonna do! Please find him, $GMr.:Ms.; $R! Even if he is a dummy! I don\'t want Drizle to get eaten!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Help! Please help!' WHERE `entry`=28362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You know, I believe I have just the thing!' WHERE `entry`=28363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, thank you! I\'m getting out of here right away! And if Ferli sent you here... don\'t tell her I was crying!' WHERE `entry`=28364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $R. An action like this will go a long way towards proving yourself as an ally of the Timbermaw.' WHERE `entry`=28366;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! I heard it from here! I wish I could\'ve been there to see it!' WHERE `entry`=28367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Land\'s sakes, pardner! You done shut off those valves but good.$B$BUnfortunately we\'ve had a critical blowout in our gosh-darned central burnoff regulator! Missus Darla\'s done sent as many workers as she can rustle to go shut it off, but those flames have a mind of their own!$B$BLiterally! They\'re hoppin\' up and grabbin\' anyone who comes near! So Darla says if you can muster up out of that cave you\'re in and beat that elemental, she\'s got a mighty fine prize in store for ya!',`objectives_loc1`='Slay Grolvitar the Everburning.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, my entire operation\'s nearly been ruined. But you came through in the clinch, $N. It could\'ve been worse! I gotta hand it to you.' WHERE `entry`=28368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Me brother sent you? Good! I could use a $C. Can ya hold yer own in a fight?' WHERE `entry`=28369;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Pretty little things, aren\'t they? I wonder if we can figure out how to make more of them.' WHERE `entry`=28370;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fez sent you, hmm? At least he\'s good for something.' WHERE `entry`=28372;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Okay, I know this is a longshot, but I figure it never hurts to ask.$B$BWhile I deal with the fallout of all the ridiculous nonsense that just went on here, I need you to go speak to some bears. The Timbermaw furbolg control the forests to the northeast, and they\'re not too fond of us.$B$BI just need someone to give them the idea the Horde isn\'t all that bad. Head northeast up the road to Timbermaw Hold--don\'t go into Felpaw village--and ask the furbolg outside if they have any favors they\'d like done.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We furbolg are not foolish, $N. We will not yield Timbermaw Hold to any askers. However, we are also in dire need of assistance. If you help us, we will grant you our favor and allow you passage.' WHERE `entry`=28373;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s hard work, but it\'s so rewarding when you see them growing up big and strong. When they\'re not covered with demonic thorns, that is!' WHERE `entry`=28374;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This place is dark... foreboding. It smells of piss and fur. There are definitely worgen here and very likely dwarves.' WHERE `entry`=28375;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Quite an accomplishment, $N. I\'ll be certain that this gets to Harrison when his expedition here is concluded.' WHERE `entry`=28376;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to have you fighting at my side again, $N! And I see the Firebeards have come as well. I suppose they\'ll provide a distraction while me and my boys do the heavy lifting.' WHERE `entry`=28377;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fanny is safe! I hear Firebeard was in there with you? Nice to hear he\'s finally pulling his weight. Wait, why are you looking at me like that, $N? Do you know something I don\'t?' WHERE `entry`=28378;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Har! My men could learn a lot by watching you work. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=28379;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s a disaster down here! The pump\'s thrown, all my men in there are gone... You gotta help!' WHERE `entry`=28380;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to the home of my pack, $C. Prepare yourself for war.' WHERE `entry`=28381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='May their blood water our tree. You fight well, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28382;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N. Now the Horde will not be able to defile these poor spirits to aid their brutish ways.' WHERE `entry`=28383;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Speak with Alton Redding near Irontree Cavern',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to the pack, $R. Let\'s hope you don\'t mind getting a bit uncivilized.' WHERE `entry`=28384;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You flip a few switches on the pump and crank a large handle all the way to the right. There\'s a shuddering rumble in the nearby walls.' WHERE `entry`=28385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect. I\'ve had the pack gather explosives from the rest of the camp as well, and with these, we\'ll have just enough to get things started once the oil is flowing.' WHERE `entry`=28386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look at them run... the live ones, that is. Glorious.' WHERE `entry`=28387;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Serves every last one of them right. Let\'s hope those in charge send the rest of their greedy scavengers somewhere else.' WHERE `entry`=28388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let the goblins and all the Horde know we will not have offers of peace and sanctuary abused... most of all not in our new home. I am grateful my people have found allies as bold as you, $N. This reward will represent your bond with our pack. You will always be welcome here.' WHERE `entry`=28389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perhaps one day, we shall slay these stone troggs more swiftly than they can breed, and in so doing, end the line of fungalmancers forever. In time.' WHERE `entry`=28390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are quite skilled at bending the dragon\'s will, $R. I would be jealous of your agility, except that it comes with such a fragile frame.' WHERE `entry`=28391;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The druids of Talonbranch Glade have assisted us before. We are still unused to "friendly" worgen in these woods, but our people are also familiar with the sorrows of curses and corruption... Sorrows that I hope you can aid us in, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28392;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I\'ll send these plans to the king and his strategists immediately. If the Dark Irons and their Twilight allies manage to recover and attack, our men will be ready for them. Well done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I know a couple of engineers who will want to take a look at those plans. They won\'t be using these golems anytime soon. Good work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28394;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look upon the carnage, $N. You and I make quite the team! Now to find those plans and deal with their leaders.' WHERE `entry`=28397;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' I\'ve already seen a dozen spells I never knew existed. This will be most helpful, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28398;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The binding stones you brought back are exceedingly powerful. It will likely take me years to learn all their secrets, but I\'m certain they\'ll prove most useful. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28399;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' He will be honored as a hero of the Horde, just as he always hoped. What you and Orkus did will save hundreds of lives and ensure that our foothold in Hillsbrad is not lost.' WHERE `entry`=28400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You have truly served both the Alliance and your calling as a $C.' WHERE `entry`=28401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Alright, $N. I think everything is in order. Let\'s do this!' WHERE `entry`=28402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Okay, $N. I think I can do this manually, but I\'ll need your help.' WHERE `entry`=28403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That should do it. Stand back!' WHERE `entry`=28404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks to your efforts, those weapons will never shed Alliance blood. Excellent work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With any luck, the poison will take out a fair number of their frontline troops before they know what\'s happening. That should stall them for the near future. SI:7 is most pleased with your work.' WHERE `entry`=28406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' You, Kurdran, Firebeard, and now my brother - everyone\'s got wedding fever! Fine, fine, I\'ll marry Keegan Firebeard. But only \'cuz he\'s strong and handsome, with a jaw that can cut gravel and an arse like an anvil. Not for any political reasons. We\'re going to need your help, though. We got a whole lotta wedding to put together, and not a lot of time to do it.' WHERE `entry`=28407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you work fast. Bold feathers for a bold woman. Well done!' WHERE `entry`=28408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, Russell the Bard is always raving about Thundermar Lager. I guess it doesn\'t have the kick of a good Wildhammer brew, but he goes on and on about the "body" or "flavor." I guess we\'ll find out, eh?' WHERE `entry`=28409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, aye! Kilts for the gents, gowns for the bridesmaids. Just don\'t tell the ladies they\'re wearing clothes fit for a blimp.' WHERE `entry`=28410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lookat that! You\'re practically bent double under the weight of all that meat. I\'d better get my people cooking.' WHERE `entry`=28411;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, it\'s catchy, that\'s for sure. But is it a classic?' WHERE `entry`=28413;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Uh... you did it, kid. You REALLY did it! We won the game and.... DID YOU SEE THAT DRAGON?!!!' WHERE `entry`=28414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ll never guess what happened!  Winky came back!  No flameflies needed. Can a dwarf get a celebratory belly rub?  Come on now!  RUBBA MAH BELLY!' WHERE `entry`=28415;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glad to have you on my side, $N. Bravo Company reunited, right? Oh, did I mention that Troteman\'s here, too?' WHERE `entry`=28416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I will see to it that these dragons are taken care of.' WHERE `entry`=28417;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you\'re in, then? Good.' WHERE `entry`=28418;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Those scorpids are easy to underestimate. You\'re lucky you didn\'t end up on the end of one of these barbs. Or maybe you\'re just good. I\'ll add these to the stockpile. We\'re not done yet, $R.' WHERE `entry`=28419;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Believe me, $N... I\'m just as anxious to get to the killing as you are. We\'ve got to keep to the plan. The armageddon will come soon enough. I\'ll keep these hides here.' WHERE `entry`=28420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is exactly what we need. Don\'t worry, $N... the killing will come soon enough.' WHERE `entry`=28421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Gah!  Who are you? Oh, so Ariok sent you?  Good. Would ya mind sticking around for a while?  It\'s nothing big... I just need you to kill some warlocks for me.' WHERE `entry`=28422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I hope that\'s what Ariok was looking for. It\'s not doing me much good right now, anyhow.' WHERE `entry`=28423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Knowing the way those orcs operate, there\'ll be another one to take his place soon. I\'ll see if I can\'t sneak back into the altar before that happens. Thanks, buddy.' WHERE `entry`=28424;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Good, good, good. We can move on. Our war takes us east, away from Blackrock Mountain... for now.' WHERE `entry`=28425;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ll have to excuse me, but we\'re not taking visitors right now. I\'ll ask you to leave Chiselgrip out the same door you came in. Oh, Ariok... is that you?' WHERE `entry`=28426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You need a disguise?  Well, you came to the right place, honey. Let me take a look... mm-hmm. I know exactly what we\'ll do.' WHERE `entry`=28427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it?  That\'s your disguise?  I\'m feeling less confident about our chances. But still confident.' WHERE `entry`=28428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it?  That\'s your disguise?  I\'m feeling less confident about our chances. But still confident.' WHERE `entry`=28429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it?  That\'s your disguise?  I\'m feeling less confident about our chances. But still confident.' WHERE `entry`=28430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s it?  That\'s your disguise?  I\'m feeling less confident about our chances. But still confident.' WHERE `entry`=28431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Speak with Quartermaster Kaoshin at the Black Tooth Hovel in Burning Steppes.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Where have you been, grunt?  You\'re late!  Give me one reason why I shouldn\'t kill you on the spot!' WHERE `entry`=28432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hmph. Good work, grunt.' WHERE `entry`=28433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not only did you pull off the executions, you managed to make them all look like accidents. You were the right $R for this undercover work. Good job, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=28434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='True, an attack on Redridge is an attack against the Alliance... but it is also an attack against innocents. I won\'t stand for that. Not as a Crusader. Not as an orc. It\'s time we taught the Blackrock clan - my old clan - that their raiding days are over.' WHERE `entry`=28436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='More outsiders?  What do you want?' WHERE `entry`=28437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I had a feeling you\'d be the one returning to me. I like your style, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=28438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I have a feeling we\'ll be hearing about you and your exploits for a long time, soldier. I look forward to fighting by your side in Redridge. You are dismissed.' WHERE `entry`=28439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Without those sergeants, Thorg\'izog will be hard-pressed getting his troops ready for battle. Already the dominoes are beginning to fall, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Are you alright? Good. You were strong out there, $N. Strong, and wise. Now pack up your things. We\'re moving out of here.' WHERE `entry`=28441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh. Visitors?' WHERE `entry`=28442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, these will do. I will get this packed up for you.' WHERE `entry`=28443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='To the untrained eye, these will look exactly like imps. We just need to get them to that untrained eye. I\'ll work on preparing them for delivery.' WHERE `entry`=28444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This meat looks good... but I think it needs a little "seasoning". I\'ll make sure that gets taken care of. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' That was exactly what I needed.' WHERE `entry`=28446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your kill count is adding up, $N. We\'re chipping away at them. And we are going to win.' WHERE `entry`=28447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, the whelplings. I will take care of them. As for the agreement I made with your father earlier, tell him that I will hold up my end of the bargain. You will have your dragon for the battle against the orcs. We share your grudge against the Blackrock clan.' WHERE `entry`=28448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good, you\'re back. I hope you\'ve still got that disguise. You\'re going back undercover, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well would you look at that!  My favorite soldier comes through in the clutch! I\'ll make sure to get this distributed among the ogres. I\'ll see you in Redridge, soldier. For the glory of the Blackrock!' WHERE `entry`=28450;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What are these?  Oh, are these imps? I\'m pretty sure that imps don\'t just fall asleep in boxes! I\'ll take your word for it, though. I don\'t understand any of this warlock crap. Leave them in the corner.' WHERE `entry`=28451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Pff!  You\'re late!  Do you know how long I\'ve been waiting for Ner\'gosh to deliver this orb? There\'s something strange about this orb... it\'s too... Never mind, it must be my nerves talking. Thank you for the delivery. For blood and honor!' WHERE `entry`=28452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Our job is almost done, $N. It\'s time to deliver the deathblow.' WHERE `entry`=28454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Welcome home, boys.' WHERE `entry`=28455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You peer inside, and find...' WHERE `entry`=28456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The warchief will be most interested in seeing these plans. You are a most loyal member of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=28457;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' There\'s a wealth of arcane knowledge in this book! We will learn much about our enemies and the arcane arts.' WHERE `entry`=28458;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The binding stones you brought back are exceedingly powerful. Not only have we dealt a blow to the Horde\'s enemies, but you have also discovered a fascinating source of power.' WHERE `entry`=28459;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks so much, $N! Now I can get back to work here.$B$BDid you find anything of interest at the Winterfall camp?' WHERE `entry`=28460;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Can you imagine what would happen if they got these models working and into the field? You\'ve done a great service for the Horde, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The poison should decimate their ranks if they\'re slow in discovering the tainted rations. Even if it does not kill most of the troops, we will have delayed them significantly. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=28463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Inside the cauldron bubbles a rotting, repulsive-smelling substance...' WHERE `entry`=28464;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your actions honor the ancestors and the Horde, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Without those weapons, the Dark Irons will never be a match for the Horde. You have served your brothers and sisters well this day, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Disturbing news indeed. This stuff\'s much more like what you\'d see in Felwood than in Winterspring...' WHERE `entry`=28467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Donova examines the contents of the crate.>$B$BI wonder if consuming this substance makes the furbolg more aggressive. They do seem much larger...' WHERE `entry`=28469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you so much, $N. I hope to get back to my studies without worry that I will be ambushed. Please accept this as a reward.' WHERE `entry`=28470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I wonder what all of this means... I can\'t make anything out...' WHERE `entry`=28471;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes, if you let me examine this for a while, I might be able to translate it for you.$B$B<Kelek flips through the pages.>$B$BWhen I am able to look over this fully, I will send word to you.$B$BThank you for sharing this with me, $N. Very little is known about the Winterfall furbolg.' WHERE `entry`=28472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your actions honor your brethren and the Horde, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This will not dissuade Twilight\'s Hammer, but perhaps it will increase the suspicion between them and the Dark Irons.' WHERE `entry`=28474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We can only hope your efforts will keep the two forces apart long enough for us to exploit their weakness.' WHERE `entry`=28475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We can only hope that the confusion and distrust you have created enables us to keep our enemies divided.' WHERE `entry`=28476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I shoulda asked you to mind control the cultists and truly tear our enemies apart. But what you did will work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It wasn\'t enough for their master to break the world, no! Twilight\'s Hammer is doing its best to unite our enemies against us, particularly in Blackrock Depths. They\'ve got a whole team of emissaries down there spreading propaganda aimed at starting a joint campaign.$B$BI\'ve always head that the medium\'s the message. Well, it\'s time to destroy the message!$B$BI be want you to go into the Domicile of Blackrock Depths and use this torch to burn those Twilight\'s Hammer books!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s the way you do it when you don\'t have an army. And now, Twilight\'s Hammer won\'t, either.' WHERE `entry`=28478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Pity me, stranger, and all the Highborne, for it was here our folly began... our folly that cursed our children, and our children\'s children, to this day.' WHERE `entry`=28479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are a valuable ally, $N. We are one step closer to defeating the enemy.' WHERE `entry`=28480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Glad you could make it, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28482;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent job, $N. Our troops will hear of your deeds.' WHERE `entry`=28483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I... um... well... turns out he doesn\'t need the hearts anymore. Sorry about that! Hope it wasn\'t too inconvenient! A deal\'s a deal though, so here is your reward. You can go ahead and keep the yeti hearts. I hear they hold excellent nutritional value - if you\'re into eating.' WHERE `entry`=28484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So it\'s true, you did kill the beast! The people of Hillsbrad are indebted to you, $N. You have made the land safer for our citizens.$B$BTake whatever you may desire from our coffers.' WHERE `entry`=28485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it, $N!  Excellent!' WHERE `entry`=28486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc1`='Higher ground secured' WHERE `entry`=28486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you, $N! I promise you that this is the last time I take this gear off.' WHERE `entry`=28487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is exactly what I was seeking. Thank you, $R.' WHERE `entry`=28488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s a hefty load you\'re carrying. It should keep my customers satisfied for the time being.$B$BHere is your pay, as promised.' WHERE `entry`=28489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Priestess Dentaria at Lor\'danel in Darkshore.$B$BThe people of Lor\'danel need your aid in caring for the survivors of Auberdine\'s destruction and securing their town against Twilight\'s Hammer. Speak to Vesprystus, the hippograph master at Rut\'theran Village outside of Darnassus and he\'ll arrange a flight to Darkshore.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So, the king has heard our plea? Thank Elune! We can use all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=28490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work!  More pets for Kibler!' WHERE `entry`=28491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Sentinel Shyela at Orendil\'s Retreat in northwestern Ashenvale.$B$BThe Horde\'s aggression in Ashenvale cannot be allowed to stand! Your help is needed to repel the invaders and restore the sacred forest. Head south through the Twilight Vale in Darkshore to reach the forest of Ashenvale.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you come to help us fight back against the forces of the Horde? Every blade and spell will be needed!' WHERE `entry`=28492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you\'re the reinforcements? I suppose you\'ll do fine as long you can kill night elves.' WHERE `entry`=28493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You look competent with a weapon or a spellbook. We could use your help in driving back the quillboars in these parts.' WHERE `entry`=28494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='WHAT!? No, don\'t tell me that, $N! It can\'t be true! My... I... I would never...$B$BI won\'t give up, $C. Just you wait and see. I will save those fawns!' WHERE `entry`=28495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Ag\'tor Bloodfist at the Orgrimmar Rear Gate in Azshara.$B$BAid in driving back the encroaching Alliance forces and assist in securing Aszhara for the glory of the Horde!$B$BDepart Orgrimmar through its northern gate to reach the Orgrimmar Rear Gate in Azshara.$B$BDestiny calls!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We could sure use some help out here.' WHERE `entry`=28496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good work, $N. Now let\'s see if we can make our way up there before they\'re able to recover.' WHERE `entry`=28497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent. Let\'s see if we can find anything of importance.' WHERE `entry`=28498;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perhaps you are as powerful as I\'ve heard afterall. You have our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=28499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is true then?  It does exist!' WHERE `entry`=28500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We did it, $N!  We held Nahom.' WHERE `entry`=28501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I thank you, $N. These savages must be punished for what they\'ve done here.' WHERE `entry`=28502;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Caryssia Moonhunter at New Thalanaar at the border between Feralas and Thousand Needles.$B$BThe sentinels need your help to turn back the marauding Grimtotem raiders who dominate the area. To reach New Thalaanar, travel to eastern Feralas, near the border with Thousand Needles.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve arrived just in time, $C. We need your help to hold off the Grimtotem.' WHERE `entry`=28503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde forces in Thousand Needles desperately need your help.' WHERE `entry`=28504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time you arrived, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The time to act is now. The Stormpike must be crushed!' WHERE `entry`=28506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Kelsey Steelspark in Gadgetzan.$B$BThe Alliance needs your help to win concessions from the local baron and access to the area\'s priceless resources. You can reach Gadgetzan by traveling south from the Shimmering Deep in Thousand Needles.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We have to persuade the goblins of Gadgetzan to side with us, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time you arrived, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28508;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I could use your help, $C. That blasted gnome is trying to persuade the Steemwheedle Cartel to favor her side!' WHERE `entry`=28509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is much wrong in Feralas. I am glad to have your help.' WHERE `entry`=28510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Telaron Windflight at Dreamer\'s Rest in Feralas.$B$BThe Alliance needs your help to overcome our enemies, the Horde and the Grimtotems. You can reach Dreamer\'s Rest by traveling south from Desolace into Feralas.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Elune has favored us with your arrival, $C. There is much to do.' WHERE `entry`=28511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well whadda we have here?  You here to help?' WHERE `entry`=28512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Crystal of Zin-Malor was stolen from a far-off temple without remorse. Its ability to control the arcane was too tempting, and when it was toyed with, its shattering cursed us all. Kel\'theril suffered until the Sundering destroyed it for good.$B$BThe curse of Zin-Malor binds all who seek its power here. I was the first to fall to its temptation. Thousands of years later, our long lost descendants would be next...' WHERE `entry`=28513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, Oilfist sent you?  Hah! Did he ever tell you how he got the name Oilfist?  You\'ll have to ask him about that one sometime.' WHERE `entry`=28514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, Oilfist sent you?  Hah! Did he ever tell you how he got the name Oilfist?  You\'ll have to ask him about that one sometime.' WHERE `entry`=28515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This oak was grown through the aid of the druids from a seed taken back on Gilneas. It stands for all that we\'ve endured, and all that we\'ve accomplished. May it serve to remind us that our curse is also our blessing.' WHERE `entry`=28517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We were shocked before we died. Shocked that one among our noble and austere kind could descend into vicious obsession so quickly. We died as naive fools, the victims of our own blithe assumptions.$B$BThe living would know that these events would play out yet again... both here, and among the entire elven race with the fall of Quel\'thalas.' WHERE `entry`=28518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The living farstrider who sent you here could not bear to see our fate. He ran... a wise decision.$B$BIf one now holds the Crystal of Zin-Malor again, it will spell the doom of all around them. It should never have been reassembled.' WHERE `entry`=28519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is done. We have defeated the Neferset inside their own city. I wish I could say that there is peace for my people at last, but I only foresee more bloodshed.' WHERE `entry`=28520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Greetings, $C - I stand guard here as both a speaker for the Timbermaw here in Winterspring and as a defender of the tribe.$B$BOur Winterfall brethren here in this frigid land have fallen under the same corruptive sway as the furbolg of Felwood. If you\'ve come here offering the Timbermaw furbolgs aid, then we are ready to accept such an offer.' WHERE `entry`=28521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Collect 10 Spirit Beads from Winterfall furbolg.',`objectives_loc1`='Collect 10 Spirit Beads from Winterfall furbolg.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank you for what you have done, as saddening as it is. Accept this as a token of thanks.$B$BI would ask of you to please continue helping us, $N. We have very few allies on which to call upon, and without your aid, the threats against my tribe would surely be too much for us to handle alone.' WHERE `entry`=28522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Once again, you prove your honor to us! I will make sure that your deeds are known amongst my kind.$B$BRemember to bring any of the Winterfall\'s beads you find to me. For each set you continue to bring to me, I will speak on your behalf to the tribe.' WHERE `entry`=28523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Delivery Salfa\'s Basket to Donova Snowden in Winterspring.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, how nice of those dear furbolg. I feel so bad for them, cooped up in that hold, afraid of the world. But can you blame them? These Winterfall furbolg are turning just as vicious as any in Felwood. I\'d like to put a stop to it... if only for the sake of my own research, let alone the dear Timbermaw.' WHERE `entry`=28524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Williden Marshal at Marshal\'s Stand.$B$BThe Alliance needs you to provide support to the Marshal Expeditions as they uncover the secrets of Un\'Goro Crater\'s ancient beasts, unique flora, and powerful crystals. You can reach the crater by departing western Tanaris and following the road all the way to Marshal\'s Stand.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='My team of explorers, researchers, and scientists is the finest in Azeroth, but we need all the help we can get to discover the truth about the crater\'s history and its denizens.' WHERE `entry`=28525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome, $C. My scientists and explorers will be glad to have your help.' WHERE `entry`=28526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Windcaller Proudhorn at Cenarion Hold. You are to aid our Cenarion allies in their battle to turn back Twilight\'s Hammer. Cho\'Gall\'s minions must not be allowed to dominate Sililthus!$B$BYou can reach Silithus by taking the northwestern road out of Un\'Goro Crater.$B$BDestiny calls!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Cenarion Hold.' WHERE `entry`=28527;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Windcaller Proudhorn at Cenarion Hold.$B$BOur Cenarion Circle allies require your assistance to fight back against the Twilight\'s Hammer onslaught. You can reach Silithus by taking the northwestern road out of the Un\'Goro Crater.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Cenarion Hold.' WHERE `entry`=28528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The scrolls are vague and appear to be a piece of a much larger puzzle, but if you are not mistaken, they seem to reveal some of the steps on the path to becoming a demon hunter.$B$BThe dark oaths and rituals necessary for becoming a demon hunter are frowned on by most of the night elves, so this is likely something they would be very interested in keeping quiet.$B$BRanger Glynda Nal\'Shea wil know what to do with these scrolls.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Where did you find these?! You haven\'t shown them to anyone else, have you? I apologize. You took me off guard. Telarius was a very powerful Demon Hunter, but he was slain during a confrontation with the warden, Maeiv, many years ago. You are fortunate that his ghost was only a shade of his former power. I wonder how many have found their way to him in those ruins. I will see to it that these scrolls make their way to the high priestess immediately. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The cauldron looked like it contained concentrated material. If the Winterfall are diluting this stuff directly in the springs, contamination could build up over time... and then the dilution would be less and less effective.$B$BThe spring to the northeast has boiled over with elementals. I thought it was because of the Cataclysm, but their appearance could be a reaction to this.$B$BCould you check them for corruption? Hunt a few and bring me any bits of green foreign material they leave behind.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s quite a bit of it... the Winterfall are slipping further and further. And now we\'ll have to worry about the other wildlife as well, in time.' WHERE `entry`=28530;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Officer Jankie on the road into Desolace at Tethris Aran.$B$BThe brave soldiers of Nijel\'s Point are beset by demons and the armies of the Horde, and they need your help. To reach Desolace, travel south on the road from the Charred Vale in the Stonetalon Mountains.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can get you to Nijel\'s Point quickly! We need all the reinforcements we can get.' WHERE `entry`=28531;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you\'re to deploy to Stonetalon? Good, we\'ll need your abilities to defeat the Alliance there.' WHERE `entry`=28532;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Very well, it looks like it\'s time. Stay and watch if you so please.' WHERE `entry`=28533;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We were proud and noble. Our faith in the light protected us, and with the Sunwell, we wanted for nothing.$B$BBecause of that blindness, we came here to repeat the tragedy of history, as our entire race would in time.' WHERE `entry`=28534;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We were not naive, as our forefathers were. We were suspicious and cunning and ready for betrayal at every turn.$B$BYet our pride and greed drove us to ruin once more. How many more will be lost to Kel\'theril?' WHERE `entry`=28535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The shade! Yes, I saw it too!' WHERE `entry`=28536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Let me see... faintly written, among the engraved incantations, is the name of its master!$B$B"Umbranse..."' WHERE `entry`=28537;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' The humans will serve us in life and in death. I will be in contact with you shortly.' WHERE `entry`=28538;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Huntress Jalin at Stardust Spire in Ashenvale.$B$BThe Horde\'s forces are poised to push into Stonetalon and they must be opposed! You can reach Stardust Spire by traveling to the southern part of Ashenvale Forest, near the border with Stonetalon.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Horde has bored a giant pass into the mountains, and we have few enough sentinels to spare. We have to find a way to stop them!' WHERE `entry`=28539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Dis is nice, big heart! If you be interested, Mau\'ari tell ya how I be gettin\' de E\'ko....' WHERE `entry`=28540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='It be hard to describe de E\'ko, but all creatures in dese lands have it... beasts, furbolg, even de frost giants. You got to open your mind and know where to look...$B$BWatch me now, an\' I show you how to pull out de E\'ko.',`objectives_loc1`='Watch Witch Doctor Mau\'ari pull the E\'ko from Rimepelt\'s body.' WHERE `entry`=28541;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome. My brothers and I are dedicated to the redemption and rejuvenation of this once-sacred forest.' WHERE `entry`=28542;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Tenell Leafrunner at the Emerald Sanctuary.$B$BHis order requires your help to redeem Felwood from the demonic influences that rule the forest. Head north from Ashenvale and follow the road into Felwood until you reach the Emerald Sanctuary.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is much work to do here. The forest is on the mend, but without our help, it will take generations to restore this once-sacred wood.' WHERE `entry`=28543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Donova Snowden at Frostfire Hotsprings.$B$BShe requires your help to overcome the threat of the Winterfall furbolg. To reach Winterspring, you must travel east from northern Felwood and traverse Timbermaw Hold.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thank goodness you\'re here. I\'ve discovered the secret of the fierce Winterfall furbolg.' WHERE `entry`=28544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Donova Snowden at Frostfire Hot Springs. Her discoveries about the Winterfall furbolg may be the key to dealing with this threat once and for all.$B$BTo reach the Frostfire Hot Springs in Winterspring, you must travel east from northern Felwood and traverse Timbermaw Hold.$B$BDestiny calls!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perhaps you can help me make sense of my discoveries about the source of the Winterfall Furbolgs\' strength.' WHERE `entry`=28545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='In Winterspring, you will fight misguided creatures known as de Winterfall furbolg. These bear-people be so angry an\' ferocious, dey live in a constant frenzy.$B$BBring me de E\'ko of de Winterfall, an\' I give you a frenzy so intense, ya legs will let you run like de wind!',`objectives_loc1`='Collect 5 Winterfall E\'ko from any Winterfall furbolg in Winterspring.' WHERE `entry`=28546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='In Winterspring, you will fight misguided creatures known as da Winterfall furbolg. Dese bear-people be so angry an\' ferocious, dey live in a constant frenzy.$B$BBring me de E\'ko of de Winterfall, an\' I give you a frenzy so intense, ya legs will let you run like de wind!',`objectives_loc1`='Collect 3 Winterfall E\'ko from any Winterfall furbolg in Winterspring.' WHERE `entry`=28547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You... arrived just in... time...' WHERE `entry`=28548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve no doubt seen what the Alliance has done to the Barrens, $C. If we don\'t act, there may not be a Horde presence here much longer.' WHERE `entry`=28549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Commander Walpole at Stonetalon Pass in the Southern Barrens.$B$BOur brave soldiers have made tremendous gains in the Barrens, but they have paid a heavy price! Your efforts are needed to consolidate our gains. You can reach the Southern Barrens from the Stonetalon Mountains by traveling southeast through Greatwood Vale.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We face heavy Horde counterattacks daily, $C. We need every pair of hands we can get to keep them at bay.' WHERE `entry`=28550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Dockmaster Lewis near Northwatch Hold.$B$BOur brave soldiers have made tremendous gains in the Barrens, but they have paid a heavy price! Your efforts are needed to consolidate our gains. You can reach the docks outside Northwatch Hold by taking a boat from Booty Bay to Ratchet and traveling south along the coast.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re facing heavy resistance from the Horde, $C. Any reinforcements are welcome.' WHERE `entry`=28551;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Calia Hastings at Theramore Isle.$B$BYou must aid SI:7\'s Calia Hastings in uncovering the threats to Theramore, both within the city and beyond its walls. You can reach Theramore Isle by taking the boat from Menethil or traveling across the marsh from the Southern Barrens.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Deserters from the city guards are spreading discontent in the ranks. We have to get to the bottom of this before it undermines our defenses.' WHERE `entry`=28552;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, well, well... look what the Ruag dragged in!' WHERE `entry`=28553;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='If we can get things straightened out here, we have a chance to strike at the Alliance while most of their forces are busy in the Barrens.' WHERE `entry`=28554;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Once Melisara is through with you we will detonate the explosives!' WHERE `entry`=28556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Pocket-Nuke Armed at the Headland',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Pocket-Nuke Armed at Gavin\'s Naze' WHERE `entry`=28556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You could be one of the very first mortals to set foot in Uldum in millenia. Just think of the treasures that await us!' WHERE `entry`=28557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Adarrah at Thistleshrub Valley in Tanaris.$B$BBe one of the first to enter glorious Uldum and claim its treasures in honor of the Alliance!$B$BYou can reach Adarrah\'s caravan by traveling to the western reaches of Tanaris.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There are wonders just waiting to be discovered beyond this valley. And they will be ours!' WHERE `entry`=28558;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Vorkhan the Elekk Herder at Kessel\'s Crossing.$B$BThe people of Bloodmyst need your help to deal with treacherous blood elves and dangerous creatures loose on the island. You can reach Kessel\'s Crossing on Bloodmyst Isle by taking the bridge north from Azuremyst Isle.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you\'re here to help? Well, there\'s plenty to do...' WHERE `entry`=28559;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Arcanist Vandril at Tranquilien in the Ghostlands.$B$BYour help is needed to turn back the numberless Scourge invaders and secure the help of the Forsaken in fighting our common enemy.$B$BTo reach Tranquilien, follow the road south from Fairbreeze Square and into the Ghostlands.$B$BDestiny calls!',`objectives_loc1`='Report to Arcanist Vandril at Tranquilien in the Ghostlands.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your arrival here is fortuitous, $C. We cannot fight the Scourge without help.' WHERE `entry`=28560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='$N!  It\'s you!  My regiment was ambushed on our way here. Our captain was slain, leaving me in command... until you got here, that is... sir!' WHERE `entry`=28561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Lieutenant Horatio Lane at the Jansen Stead.$B$BWestfall has been overrun by beggars and transients, leading to a massive increase in criminal activity. Your help is needed to restore order to the populace. You can reach the Jansen Stead in Westfall by traveling west from Elwynn Forest.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Murder, rookie. That\'s what you\'re looking at on the ground in front of us.' WHERE `entry`=28562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report Watch Captain Parker at Tower Watch in the Redridge Mountains.$B$BCaptain Parker\'s forces have come under attack from marauding gnolls and orcs. The people of Lakewood are in peril and your aid is needed to safeguard them. Travel east from the border of Elwynn Forest and into the Three Corners area of Redridge to reach Tower Watch.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Heard Westfall was in some deep doody. Well, we got our own set of problems here. See them gnolls out there? Looks like they\'re actin\' up again. I don\'t like it. Don\'t like it one bit.' WHERE `entry`=28563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Commander Althea Ebonlocke in Darkshire.$B$BThe commander\'s watchmen are stretched thin defending against marauding wolves and bands of wild worgen. They cannot hold out for long without your help. You can reach Darkshire in Duskwood by following the road south at the border between Elwynn Forest and the Redridge Mountains.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You are the help that we requested? I suppose you will have to do.' WHERE `entry`=28564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Mountaineer Rharen at Dun Algaz.$B$BIn the wake of the cataclysm\'s destruction, Wetlands has become overrun with wild beasts, orcish raiders, and savage gnolls! To reach the Wetlands, you must travel north from Loch Modan through the dwarven hold of Dun Algaz.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We haven\'t gotten much in the way of reinforcements lately. We can use every pair of hands we can get.' WHERE `entry`=28565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' They will see the bloodshed and they will hesitate. Hesitation will make them think twice about ever attacking us again.' WHERE `entry`=28566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Pilot Hammerfoot at South Gate Outpost.$B$BThe destruction of the Stonewrought Dam and the resurgence of the kobolds and troggs has the mountaineers stretched thin. Reinforcements are desperately needed! Travel east through South Gate Pass from eastern Dun Morogh to reach South Gate Outpost.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have our leaders finally heard my pleas? We\'re down to just a handful of pilots and mountaineers to defend Loch Modan.' WHERE `entry`=28567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Most excellent! A new recruit has arrived. There is much to do... much to do I say.' WHERE `entry`=28568;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Time is money, $C... and I\'ve got plenty of each. What can I do for you?' WHERE `entry`=28569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Time is money, $C... and I\'ve got plenty of each. What can I do for you?' WHERE `entry`=28570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I was wondering when reinforcements would show up. Suit up, $N. It\'s time to dispense some justice!' WHERE `entry`=28571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At last, the Warchief\'s reinforcements have arrived. The Dark Lady has plans for you, as she does for us.' WHERE `entry`=28572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Captain Nials at Refuge Pointe.$B$BAncient Stromgarde\'s honor must be redeemed! Too long have ogres and criminals sullied its streets. Travel north from the Wetlands and cross the Than\'dol Span to reach Arathi. Follow the road to Refuge Pointe and present yourself to the captain.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Would that you were a company, but we\'ll have to make do with with what we have.' WHERE `entry`=28573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Have you come to help us against the Wildhammers? The Warchief knows that what happens here will be important to the Horde\'s future.' WHERE `entry`=28574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Koltira Deathweaver at Andorhal.$B$BThe Alliance forces are advancing into the ruined city of Andorhal, seeking to claim it for themselves. We must counter their them before they can gain a foothold there!$B$BCross the Bulwark at the eastern end of Tirisfal Glades and follow the roads southest to Andorhal and meet up with our forces there.$B$BDestiny calls!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Is this all the warchief can spare? Don\'t worry, you\'ll be put to good use.' WHERE `entry`=28575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Thassarian at Andorhal.$B$BOn the heels of our early victories in Andorhal, the Forsaken have decided to launch a counterattack. Your help is needed to beat back the Scourge and Horde and reclaim lost Andorhal.$B$BTo reach Andorhal, travel north through the Hillsbrad Foothills and follow the road beyond Chillwind Camp.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='There is much to be done here. Both of our enemies are relentless and would slaughter us without mercy the moment we sheathe our blades.' WHERE `entry`=28576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perhaps you can help, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Fiona on the east bank of the Thondroril River.$B$BThe Argent Crusade needs your help to win back the Eastern Plaguelands from the grasp of the Scourge.$B$BTo reach the Eastern Plaguelands, cross the Thondroril River from the Western Plaguelands and look for Fiona on the eastern bank.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perhaps you can help, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Gek Nozzlerocket at Light\'s Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BYour help is needed to survey the damage done by Deathwing, and the disposition of Horde forces in the Badlands.$B$BGek has agreed to provide transportation to the Badlands via rocket, in exchange for your help. Look for him at Light\'s Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You must be here to help Fuselight! Let\'s get you to the Badlands right away.' WHERE `entry`=28579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Sure, I can get you to the Badlands, but when you get there, I want you to agree to help my comrades.' WHERE `entry`=28580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We, too, are suspicious of the Dark Irons\' recent activities.' WHERE `entry`=28581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Jack Rockleg at Thorium Advance.$B$BSI:7 reports that the Dark Iron dwarves of the Searing Gorge seem to be preparing to attack. Your duty is to learn all you can about their scheming and put a halt to it.$B$BYou can reach the Searing Gorge by following the road west from the Badlands.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We, too, are suspicious of the Dark Irons.' WHERE `entry`=28582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'s this? The "$N-o-matic:" a shredder with an integrated missile platform? Bah! Already patented by Labor Captain Grabbit in Azshara. Worthless! What I really need is a machine that knocks dwarves from the sky.' WHERE `entry`=28583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='There you go. Now hows about we use this blast tape on Rothman\'s mouth?' WHERE `entry`=28584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks, $N! Now if we could just get the Krazzworks stable so that our people would stop being thrown off of the platforms.' WHERE `entry`=28586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You come from Tarren Mill? You reek of death...' WHERE `entry`=28587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You got the chops for killing dwarves, that\'s for sure, $N. This is a good thing. Next up, more dwarf slayage!' WHERE `entry`=28588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s the spirit! Must be pretty humiliating being shot down by junk.' WHERE `entry`=28589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good to have you, $N. Ready to sew some chaos?' WHERE `entry`=28590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Marvels of modernized goblin destructivity, eh? I love these babies.' WHERE `entry`=28591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hahah! Wonderful show. That should be a proper welcome to the highlands.' WHERE `entry`=28592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Brilliant! Krazz will love you something mighty for bringing this one home. Good on you.' WHERE `entry`=28593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='And that\'s how it\'s done. Scattered to the wind. Not quite the fighting force they boast themselves to be, eh?' WHERE `entry`=28594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now that\'s what I wanted to see! I\'ll have this fleet back up in no time with this beauty. You know just how I like it, $N. I know just how you like it too - take this.' WHERE `entry`=28595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'s more like it. We should be able to mop this up from here.' WHERE `entry`=28596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Aye, that\'ll do \'er. Ohhh, fresh. Heady. Redridge fine grain with a hint of Westfall sulphur and a mild aftertaste. Highbank gets the good stuff.' WHERE `entry`=28597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Oh, $N. $N! That ... were beautiful.' WHERE `entry`=28598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The King himself sent you? Good to hear that Stormwind is secure. I was expecting more in the way of troops, but word is that the Alliance fleet was ambushed by the Horde on the way here. They gave as good as they got, but the fleet is in shambles. If we\'re to make any forward progress here in the Highlands, we\'re going to need the help of heroes like you.' WHERE `entry`=28599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' THEY HAVE FORSAKEN US? THEY HAVE FORSAKEN THE HORDE? This cannot be! I... I... I WILL BE FINE. We will do this without their aid. To hell with the Frostwolf!' WHERE `entry`=28600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText4_loc1`='"The Doc" Defeated' WHERE `entry`=28601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Something tells me I\'m going to need this.' WHERE `entry`=28602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Perfectly handled. You could easily be a Deathstalker. And what could they have even done to you? You acted in self defense! Now to deal with the final finger.' WHERE `entry`=28603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They won\'t die immediately, but they WILL die! When they finally piece together who was responsible for the deaths of their soldiers, you will be long gone - a phantom of death!' WHERE `entry`=28604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the Stormpike forces maimed, the time has come for detonation!' WHERE `entry`=28605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Exactly what I needed. You\'ll be an asset to the Forsaken, $N. You know, word has it that you were quite the $C in your previous life. Perhaps I should assign you to a more exciting task.' WHERE `entry`=28608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lilith wants a boulder moved inside the observatory, eh? That\'s my business: consolidated materials. I usually don\'t get individual buyers, but hey, I won\'t ask questions.' WHERE `entry`=28609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like a good amount! Here\'s your pay, as promised...' WHERE `entry`=28610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The waters of the river are nearly cleansed. Our prophetic visions will soon return.' WHERE `entry`=28611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Lucky fer you, this ol\' dwarf\'s still got a few tricks up his sleeve! Heehee! ...shoulda seen tha look on yer faces!' WHERE `entry`=28612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So far, so good...' WHERE `entry`=28613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your actions prove yourself a mighty warrior to me and all the Timbermaw! Let us hope the Winterfall will be defeated for good now...' WHERE `entry`=28614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='May the Winterfall never threaten the Timbermaw again. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='With the fingers destroyed and the hand shattered, the Stormpike will have no choice but to scurry back to their cave in Alterac Valley. Warchief Hellscream will hear about your bravery, $N. And rest assured that he will know of the Frostwolf clan\'s treason!' WHERE `entry`=28616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I think that was just the start of it, bud! MORE INCOMING!' WHERE `entry`=28617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText2_loc1`='Massive Wave Survived' WHERE `entry`=28617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, you actually brought the boulder! I\'m a bit surprised.$B$BStand back and witness the pinnacle of craftsmanship.' WHERE `entry`=28618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='At last, the Warchief\'s reinforcements have arrived. The Dark Lady has plans for you, as she does for us.' WHERE `entry`=28619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That imbecile finally sent help, did he? These two orcs are a lost cause. They are stricken with something that I have termed "Durnholde Syndrome." They were both locked up for so long that they grew an affinity for their captors. Now they sit upon my couch with their big, iron balls and cry.$B$BHopefully you will prove to be more useful.' WHERE `entry`=28620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Of course I have a plan for moving the coffer. Someday, maybe the old coot will learn to trust me.' WHERE `entry`=28621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work, lad. Looks as tho everything made the trip in one piece. I\'m beginnin\' ta see why junior keeps ye around.' WHERE `entry`=28622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve arrived just in time, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They want a tree now? Let\'s see what I got.' WHERE `entry`=28624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not a bad haul. Maybe we should look into growin\' those treants instead...' WHERE `entry`=28625;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Alright! Stand back now and watch what a true quality weapon can do!' WHERE `entry`=28626;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh, it\'s you again! I\'m so surprised!' WHERE `entry`=28627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Perfect. Now you\'ll see what really matters in a weapon... finesse.' WHERE `entry`=28628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='My friends are always coming up with great ideas. I\'ve never felt like I could match them... until today! I just drew up the plans for something great! If you promise not to tell, I\'ll let you in on the secret... $B$BI\'m going to make a mechanical yeti! Not only are my friends sure to be freaked out when they see it, but when they get over that, I know they\'ll be impressed!$B$BI need thick yeti fur from the ice thistle yeti. There\'s plenty of them in the Ice Thistle Hills to the southeast.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='These furs are perfect, $N. We\'re off to a great start here!' WHERE `entry`=28629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Part of this machine is still moving, but on closer inspection it\'s been severely manhandled. The metal is dented and cracked, and there\'s huge footprints in the snow all around it.$B$BIn fact, it sounds like something\'s approaching right now...' WHERE `entry`=28630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t wait to show my friends! Now, just wait a moment while I attach these...$B$BPerfect!' WHERE `entry`=28631;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Not bad! Let\'s hope they don\'t ask for lava or something next, right?' WHERE `entry`=28632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Of course! I had a hunch this is what we\'d find. Had no idea about the organic transformations, though, I must admit. There\'s more to this old relic than I\'d dared to hope.' WHERE `entry`=28633;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The itching has stopped - for now - but they will return.$B$BOh yes, they will return...' WHERE `entry`=28634;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Haunted? Ye could say that!' WHERE `entry`=28635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They fight for their land even after death - much like the Forsaken. I will report back to high command that Dun Garok is uninhabitable. Let them keep what they hold so dear.' WHERE `entry`=28636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Simply splendid! I\'ve been watching the Captain bring bear after bear back to camp and I can\'t wait to see them thrown on the smoker.$B$BPerhaps I\'ll have a taste of them raw...' WHERE `entry`=28637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Captain\'s been bringin\' back bags full of owl, and I can\'t wait to try it! Maybe Mr. Fancypants Francis here will even try some.' WHERE `entry`=28638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ursius is... not delicious. He tastes like a combination of pinecones and curdled milk, only... oilier.$B$BAre you sure this is Ursius?  The big bear?  In the cave?$B$BThis is horrible. It honestly tastes like his meat has been steeped in urine.$B$BI don\'t feel like I\'m getting any stronger.$B$BUgh. It\'s really bad. Do you want to try some?' WHERE `entry`=28639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Alright! Don\'t stop now, we\'re after the big ones next!' WHERE `entry`=28640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Beautiful! I\'m watching the Captain drag this all back right now and it\'s a gorgeous sight.$B$BAnd the next course...' WHERE `entry`=28641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Zephyrus was a mighty adversary. Surely the remaining elementals will challenge you further!$B$B<You open the guide that Jekyll gave to you.>' WHERE `entry`=28643;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Teracula was an even mightier adversary than Zephyrus.$B$B<You open the guide that Jekyll gave to you.>' WHERE `entry`=28644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Now you know why the monster was called Bloodvenom. What challenges remain?$B$B<You open the guide that Jekyll gave to you.>' WHERE `entry`=28645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Though you have defeated the four elements, one final challenge awaits. What could it be?$B$B<You open the guide that Jekyll gave to you.>' WHERE `entry`=28646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is the first time anyone has actually completed the challenge. You truly are a powerful $C, $N. As promised, choose your reward.' WHERE `entry`=28647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Felt good, didn\'t it? You\'re not one of them anymore, $N. You\'re Scourge. You\'re one of us. Forever...' WHERE `entry`=28649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Felt good, didn\'t it? You\'re not one of them anymore, $N. You\'re Scourge. You\'re one of us. Forever...' WHERE `entry`=28650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that the training\'s done and out of the way, why don\'t you go speak with Elreth?  She serves Shadow Priest Sarvis, and will probably have some tasks to which you can apply your new abilities.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='May the Dark Lady watch over you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Yes?  And who might you be?' WHERE `entry`=28652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Greetings, $N. I see you wield a weapon. Can you fight?' WHERE `entry`=28653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Bout time ye showed up, $Glad:lass;.$B$BNow let\'s get goin\'! There be work ta do!' WHERE `entry`=28654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We did it, $N! Fighting that ... thing side-by-side really brought all the Wildhammers together. The heads of the families are more united than I\'ve ever seen them. Drink up, $N, and celebrate!! Of course, our work is only beginning. I\'ll rally our new Wildhammer reinforcements with the rest of the Alliance and prepare to storm the Twilight Bastion. I\'m sure we\'ll meet again soon.' WHERE `entry`=28655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What\'s dis? You got de smell of de E\'ko on ya! Let Mau\'ari tell ya a little bit about de E\'ko and what it do.$B$BYou\'re lucky, $R. De E\'ko searched you out. A troll like me\'s gotta go find de E\'ko herself.$B$BAll de creatures of Winterspring have E\'ko. De furbolg, de chillwind, de shardtooth... even de Ice Thistle yeti! You kill dese creatures, and sometimes, a bit of E\'ko comes out. Different creatures... different E\'ko.$B$BGo on now. Go find de other E\'ko!' WHERE `entry`=28656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You actually killed him?!  I can\'t believe it!' WHERE `entry`=28657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Looks like you were able to get the croc hides that we needed. Thanks $N, your contributions will not go unnoticed.' WHERE `entry`=28658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Those filthy alliance never stood a chance. Nice work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You made it back out alive?  You are a stronger man than I, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Galus is dead?  Fantastic work $N, now we can send down the cleanup crew and get that cellblock ready for new prisoners.' WHERE `entry`=28661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These journals are in excellent condition $N. We will begin deciphering them immediately. Only time will tell what secrets they hold.' WHERE `entry`=28662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='D-Block is all clear?  Good work, $N. We will send down a crew to start cleaning up right away.' WHERE `entry`=28663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Svarnos is finally dead?  Looks like we can finally get to work setting up that cellblock then. Thank you $N.' WHERE `entry`=28664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The shackles!  We will begin the process of destroying these shackles immediately $N. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=28665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to John J. Keeshan at Flamestar Post.$B$BYour aid is urgently needed to put an end to the Blackrock orc menance!$B$BYou can reach the Burning Steppes by traveling south from the Searing Gorge through Blackrock Mountain. Look for Flamestar Post on the far side of the mountain.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s time for the Blackrock orcs to feel the full wrath of the Alliance. They will pay for what they\'ve done.' WHERE `entry`=28666;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='We must stop the Blackrock orcs before they can expand their influence.' WHERE `entry`=28667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You cleared that area out?  Looks like you might be more useful to us that we thought, $R.' WHERE `entry`=28668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ahh, the wardens key\'s. Another job well done, $N. These will come in very handy.' WHERE `entry`=28669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These rations will really help the troops out $N. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=28670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Our enemies are numerous, $C. It will take skill and bravery to overcome them all.' WHERE `entry`=28671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='What do we have here?  A new $C, ready for battle, eh?' WHERE `entry`=28672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Quartermaster Lungertz at Nethergarde Keep.$B$BNethergarde\'s garrison urgently needs your help to stem the Horde advance into the Blasted Lands! Travel south from the Swamp of Sorrows and follow the road east to reach Nethergarde Keep.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='For decades has the garrison at Nethergarde held firm against the threat of the Horde and we do not intend to surrender now.' WHERE `entry`=28673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Starfall, $C. We have opened our doors to all travelers in our time of need.' WHERE `entry`=28674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Trade Baron Silversnap at Bogpaddle.$B$BThe Alliance forces urgently needs the munitions provided by the baron! You must do whatever is necessary to convince the baron to keep selling our forces supplies at reasonable prices.$B$BTo get to the swamp, follow the road from the southeastern Burning Steppes through the Redridge Mountains.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Bogpaddle, $C. I fully expect you will enjoy all our facility has to offer.' WHERE `entry`=28675;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh good, another warm body!$B$BI hope that elf up there didn\'t bore you to death. We\'ve got a lot of bugs to kill here.' WHERE `entry`=28676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to beautiful Bogpaddle!' WHERE `entry`=28677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You did it!  Maybe we can finally get some ships into port now. Thank you $N.' WHERE `entry`=28678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work on the undead up there $N. We really appreciate the help.' WHERE `entry`=28679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This rum will really help us out, $N. They might not feel great in the morning but at least they will go to sleep happy.' WHERE `entry`=28680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='No way, you actually killed him?  We are having shark tacos tonight for sure!' WHERE `entry`=28681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You killed him?  We have been trying to take that guy out for weeks!  We thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Nice work on those spiders $N. At this rate, we will be taking that forest in no time.' WHERE `entry`=28683;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These glands will do nicely. We are grateful for your help, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks for rounding these up for us, $N. Kind of hard to fight a battle without any guns.' WHERE `entry`=28685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Told you that village was full of wackos. Nice job clearing it out $N.' WHERE `entry`=28686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These fish will do nicely, $N. Keeping the troops fed and in good condition is our number one priority and you really came through for us here.' WHERE `entry`=28687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Commander Aggro\'gosh at Grom\'gol Base Camp. The commander requires your aid to keep the supply routes open and free of interference from the local inhabitants and the troublesome Alliance.$B$BTo reach Grom\'gol, you can take the zeppelin Orgrimmar\'s eastern zeppelin tower or the one near Undercity.$B$BDestiny calls!',`objectives_loc1`='Report to Commander Aggro\'gosh at Grom\'gol Base Camp in the Northern Stranglethorn Vale.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='At last, the Warchief\'s reinforcements have arrived.' WHERE `entry`=28688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='May their souls rest in peace.' WHERE `entry`=28689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I didn\'t think you would be able to do it, $N. You are just full of surprises aren\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=28690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, you made it back alive!  Can\'t say you were the first one to try this task, but you are definitely the first one to make it back alive.' WHERE `entry`=28691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These parts will really help us out, $N!  Who would have thought you can find stuff this useful in all that old junk?' WHERE `entry`=28692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time someone took those guys out.' WHERE `entry`=28693;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I didn\'t think you would be able to do it, $N. You are just full of surprises aren\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=28694;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work $N. I will report your efforts to our highest in command immediately.' WHERE `entry`=28695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='The wellson shipyard is constantly receiving supplies from offshore and we need to put a stop to it. They have setup cannons along the docks for defense but if you can make it to them, we can use them to destroy their supply ships.$B$BHead down there and see what you can do. Report back to me on your progress.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work on those supply ships, $N!  We knew you would be good for somethin\' around here.' WHERE `entry`=28696;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Great work, $N!  We should not hear from the ghosts again anytime soon.' WHERE `entry`=28697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Good job on the recovery effort $N. These cannonballs should last us a while.' WHERE `entry`=28698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Lieutenant Doren at the Rebel Camp.$B$BYears after Colonel Kurzen\'s treachery against Stormwind, the truth of what happened remains a mystery. Aid the survivors in learning what became of the colonel. Travel south from Duskwood and follow the road west after crossing into the jungle to reach the Rebel Camp.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`objectives_loc1`='Report to Lieutenant Doren at the Rebel Camp in the Northern Stranglethorn Vale.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to our camp, $C, such as it is.' WHERE `entry`=28699;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ha, we finally got Largo!  Nice one, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='They may not look like much to you, but these relics hold great value to the people of Starfall. You are kind, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Bronwyn Hewstrike at the Explorers\' League Digsite.$B$BThe Explorers\' League expedition needs your help to safeguard its site and findings from marauding ogres. Travel south from Northern Stranglethorn Vale and follow the road to the Explorers\' League Digsite.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!' WHERE `entry`=28702;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hey, nice work!$B$BIf you ever want to come back and kill some more bugs for absolutely no additional reward, please, feel free!' WHERE `entry`=28703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Welcome to Hardwrench Hideaway!' WHERE `entry`=28704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Lieutenant General Orion at the Stair of Destiny.$B$BYour skills are needed to fight the Burning Legion\'s presence on the shattered remnants of Outland.$B$BGo to Orgrimmar\'s Cleft of Shadow and use the portal near the mage trainers to reach the Blasted Lands, then travel through the Dark Portal itself to reach Hellfire Peninsula.$B$BDestiny calls!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Prepare yourself for battle. The Horde has need of you here.' WHERE `entry`=28705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Bring the Box of Bugkill Fumigators to Remma Curtainfire inside the Ban\'Thallow Barrow Den.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We\'re bringing out the bug spray, eh? I guess it can\'t be helped.' WHERE `entry`=28706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Fumigators? From Rinno? Geez...' WHERE `entry`=28707;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Commander Duron in Hellfire Peninsula.$B$BThe expeditionary forces require your help to overcome the demonic armies of the Burning Legion! Use the portal on the middle level of the tower in the Mage District to travel to the Blasted Lands, then travel through the Dark Portal to reach the Stair of Destiny in Outland.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The expedition needs your help, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Recruitment Officer Blythe at Valiance Keep in Borean Tundra.$B$BThe Valiance Expedition needs your help to keep the forces of the Scourge under control and safeguard civilized lands! Make your way to the Stormwind Docks and take the ship north to Valiance Keep.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`objectives_loc1`='Report to Recruitment Officer Blythe at Valiance Keep in Borean Tundra.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The expedition needs your help, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Rinno sent you! And you brought... fumigators? Ugh!' WHERE `entry`=28710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to the Warsong Recruitment Officer at Warsong Hold.$B$BThe Warsong Offensive needs your help to overcome the continued threat from the undead Scourge.$B$BTake the zeppelin to Warsong Hold from Orgrimmar\'s western zeppelin tower and present yourself to the recruitment officer.$B$BDestiny calls!',`objectives_loc1`='Report to the Warsong Recruitment Officer at Warsong Hold in Borean Tundra.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='The Warsong Offensive could use more like you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hello again, $R. I hear you were instrumental in our push toward Grim Batol - thank you! Alexstrasza has sanctified this ground in the hopes of luring Deathwing here. She\'ll perform a ceremony to lure him out... and then destroy him within this sacred circle. Let\'s hope her plan works.' WHERE `entry`=28712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You performed your duties well, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your service to the creatures of Shadowglen is worthy of reward, $N. You confirmed my fears, however. The grellkin are still tainted by fel moss, despite Teldrassil\'s blessing. Something sinister remains within the tree. I can only hope that the Gnarlpine tribe of furbolgs are free of the corruption, or we are still in grave danger. I will look into this further and contact those who might be of aid. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Elune be praised! And you as well, young $C. There are many young night elves in need of these, but I\'d be more than happy to give you one of the bags as a reward. I\'m sure it will come in handy. Safe travels to you.' WHERE `entry`=28715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to the throne room in Stormwind Keep.$B$BKing Wrynn requires a trustworthy and proven hero for a mission of the utmost importance.$B$BStormwind Keep can be found in the eastern portion of Stormwind City.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`objectives_loc1`='Speak with King Varian Wrynn at Stormwind Keep in Stormwind.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='We are pleased that you have answered our summons, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28716;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='All able-bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Garrosh Hellscream in Grommash Hold.$B$BThe warchief requires your help to prepare for the glorious assault on the Twilight Highlands and our dual enemies, the Alliance and Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BMeet with the warchief in Grommash Hold at the center of Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Strength.$B$BDestiny calls!',`objectives_loc1`='Report to Garrosh Hellscream at Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='Soon, the assault on the Twilight Highlands will begin, and I intend for you to be a part of it.' WHERE `entry`=28717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Look around you; you\'re looking at the largest goblin-owned hunting reserve in Kalimdor! I\'ve got the licenses to shoot and eat everything that walks on the snow from here to Everlook... and lemme tell you, they\'re good eatin\'!' WHERE `entry`=28718;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='<Francis smacks his lips.>$B$BYou\'ve got to try some of this, $N. These maulers are perfectly tenderized... possibly because of the pummeling you delivered.' WHERE `entry`=28719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You saved our men!  No words can express our gratitude $N.' WHERE `entry`=28721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Hah! She\'ll think twice before making fun of my ideas again!$B$BThanks for your help, $N. I couldn\'t have had so much fun without you!' WHERE `entry`=28722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Now that you\'re practiced in your new ability, perhaps you\'d be willing to aid us in further pursuing the corruption haunting Shadowglen.$B$BDentaria Silverglade, Priestess of the Moon, has offered to aid us. You should find her between the two pools just north of our great tree. Circle around the tree to reach her and offer her any help that you can, young $C.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='It is good that you\'ve come. It seems your training progresses quickly.' WHERE `entry`=28723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='These will do perfectly. Thank you, $N. Your swiftness is appreciated.' WHERE `entry`=28724;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I see you found me, young $R. Dentaria was wise to have sent you.' WHERE `entry`=28725;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This corruption these spiders suffer from is not simply surface deep. It cannot be magic or subtle mal intent. It is bred into them. It seems our next task is clear.' WHERE `entry`=28726;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Githyiss and her brood were being corrupted by this totem. This is a furbolg totem. This is very troubling indeed. This means the Gnarlpine are still a danger to these forests. We let our guard down too soon.' WHERE `entry`=28727;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve returned! It\'s good to see you. It seems you\'ve dealt with the source of much of the corruption in Shadowglen. Teldrassil still suffers and will need attention, be we can afford a moment or two for you to finish your training here in Shadowglen.' WHERE `entry`=28728;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well done, $N. You have one task left for you before you depart Shadowglen for the open wilds of Teldrassil.' WHERE `entry`=28729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='So you have heard the first part of the aftermath of the Battle of Mount Hyjal. There is much more for you to learn and the task you have begun here will continue through the rest of your journey through Teldrassil and into Darnassus.' WHERE `entry`=28730;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ah, I see. You were sent by Tenaron. Well then, it would seem we have much to talk about, much to do. Before we get to the task at hand, you should take in the lesson of this moonwell.' WHERE `entry`=28731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Oh dear, Raz has been captured! As soon as we entered a dozen cultists and some big fat ogre jumped us. I ran while I Raz tried to fight them off. We need to save him, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28732;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='PHEW! That was close! You\'re a real natural with these plants, $C. You know, I brought the seeds here with me from Lost Isles. I figure once I get them all figured out I\'ll make a fortune in the deadly flower business! Wha... LOOK! MORE ARE COMING!' WHERE `entry`=28733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Ilthalaine sent you? He was wise to do so. I am indeed in need of help.' WHERE `entry`=28734;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' RAZ! What have they done to him!? FOLLOW HIM!' WHERE `entry`=28735;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='The enemy on Maker\'s Ascent remain a threat, but with your help we\'ve dealt a serious blow to their numbers and their morale.' WHERE `entry`=28736;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='<Finkle\'s helm gives you a slight jolt.>$B$BWhat is this place? It looks like they\'re doing something terrible to that nether dragon. The energy is being siphoned from the creature into that lady! We need to stop this ritual!$B$BKill Corla to get past this hall!',`objectives_loc1`='Kill Corla, Herald of Twilight.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`=' We haven\'t got much time. Raz looked injured. If we get to him in time there might be a chance that I can turn him back into a regular orc! Sorry about that. I figured I\'d send through some gold - for your troubles and all that...' WHERE `entry`=28737;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' That should put a stop to their armory - at least for now. Raz ran off across the ramp on the other side of the forge. GO GO GO!' WHERE `entry`=28738;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`=' Phew... That\'s one less thing I\'ll need to worry about if we ever make it out of this place.' WHERE `entry`=28740;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Poor Raz. He was the best friend a gnome ever had. At least we avenged his death and cleared out this hellish cavern!' WHERE `entry`=28741;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Amazing, kid. You\'re a cut above! I went through about five different contracted hunters trying to get that cat.$B$BWell, we found two of them after the Captain got the corpse, but let\'s not dwell on that...' WHERE `entry`=28742;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I think that made Stillwater angry. He\'s sending the heavy-hitters after us now. No time to lose, friend, let\'s go!' WHERE `entry`=28744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText2_loc1`='Massive Wave Survived' WHERE `entry`=28744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve put us in enough owls for us to sell for a month, friend. Gotta hand it to ya.' WHERE `entry`=28745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Well, I\'ve got bad news and I\'ve got...$B$BNo, scratch that. There only be bad news.' WHERE `entry`=28746;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='D... Do you hear that rumblin\'? I think Stillwater is comin\'! HOLY MOLY LOOK OUT!' WHERE `entry`=28747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText2_loc1`='Massive Wave Survived' WHERE `entry`=28747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='I can\'t believe we defeated him, $N! That was the toughest fight yet, but there are still hundreds of crazed zombies roaming around Hillsbrad. We\'ll need to stay alert.' WHERE `entry`=28748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText2_loc1`='Warden Stillwater Defeated' WHERE `entry`=28748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time you arrived, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='It\'s about time you arrived, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28750;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='That\'ll keep \'em out for today, but I know they\'ll be back tomorrow. Hopefully you\'ll be around to help me.' WHERE `entry`=28751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText2_loc1`='Massive Wave Defeated' WHERE `entry`=28751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText2_loc1`='Massive Waves Survived' WHERE `entry`=28752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Arrite, then.$B$BLet\'s deposit these discs and be done with this!' WHERE `entry`=28753;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc1`='Rajh Slain',`ObjectiveText4_loc1`='Setesh Slain' WHERE `entry`=28753;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc1`='Alexstrasza has been preparing this site for many years. Once Deathwing is lured into this circle, she will use the rejuvenating powers of its life energy to overwhelm and destroy him.$B$BIt is important that the five lifebinder stones that surround this circle remain uncorrupted during the fight. Deathwing will be concentrating solely on the Queen of Dragons herself; you may escape his notice. Kill any of his minions that try to corrupt the circle.$B$BTalk to me when you are ready to begin!',`objectives_loc1`='Help Alexstrasza try to kill Deathwing. Protect the five Lifebinder Stones that surround the circle!' WHERE `entry`=28754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='This is indeed one of the lost volumes! Tyrosus will be most pleased when he learns of your find.' WHERE `entry`=28755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Your deeds do honor to those who fell in battle defending this hallowed ground.' WHERE `entry`=28756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc1`='Kill 6 Blackrock Battle Worgs.',`offerrewardtext_loc1`='You\'ve bought us a little time, $N, but we\'ve got even bigger problems to deal with now.' WHERE `entry`=28757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Thanks to your quick action, the Dragon Queen still lives. She is being brought back to Wyrmrest to recover. But the battle wasn\'t a complete failure. Deathwing was gravely wounded. I suspect he will go into hiding to recuperate. Alexstrasza has bought us time to strike!' WHERE `entry`=28758;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Excellent work, $N. You\'ve turned out to be quite an asset to this garrison. It\'s time for you to train!' WHERE `entry`=28759;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc1`='Blessings upon you. Please accept this as a token of my gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=28760;
